<Placemark><name>Hillbilly Hot Dogs</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hillbilly Hot Dogs</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lesage 25537 &middot; &#9733; 4.6 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3047622458" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(304) 762-2458</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hillbillyhotdogs.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hillbillyhotdogs.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hillbilly+Hot+Dogs%2C+6951+Ohio+River+Rd%2C+Lesage+25537&amp;ll=38.506546,-82.298185" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6951 Ohio River Rd<br/>Lesage 25537</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Doublewide, The Home Wrecker, Beef Sauce</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Located inside two school buses stacked up to a shed, Hillbilly&#x27;s Hot Dogs is home to a menu of wild, crazy dogs, including the Egg Dog made with scrambled eggs and Pizza Dog smothered in pizza sauce. Guy&#x27;s mission? Finish the famous Home Wrecker made with &quot;15 inches of pure beef weenie.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Joints<br/>Something Different<br/>Takeout: Cross-Country Delivery</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wv/lesage/hillbilly-hot-dogs-restaurant2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.29819,38.50655,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Kounty Quarthouse</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Kounty Quarthouse</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">South Range, WI 54874 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7153985582" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(715) 398-5582</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/KountyQuarthouse" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/KountyQuarthouse</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Kounty+Quarthouse%2C+4119+County+Road+K%2C+South+Range%2C+WI+54874&amp;ll=46.614834,-91.985263" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4119 County Road K<br/>South Range, WI 54874</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Belly Sandwich, Chipotle Brisket</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy calls Kounty Quarthouse&#x27;s Chef Beth Cherny &quot;gangster&quot; for her no-fuss way of cooking. Don&#x27;t miss her chipotle brisket, which is stacked on top of cheddar biscuits and served with chipotle sauce made from scratch. The pork belly sandwich with slaw and Asian barbecue sauce is another standout.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Small Town Standouts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wi/south-range/kounty-quarthouse" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-91.98526,46.61483,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Anchor Bar, Superior</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Anchor Bar, Superior</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Superior, WI 54880 &middot; &#9733; 3.2 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7153949747" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(715) 394-9747</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.anchorbarandgrill.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.anchorbarandgrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Anchor+Bar%2C+Superior%2C+413+Tower+Ave%2C+Superior%2C+WI+54880&amp;ll=46.733305,-92.104038" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">413 Tower Ave<br/>Superior, WI 54880</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jalapeno Cream Cheese Burger, Cashew Burger, Gally Buster</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Stop by this self-proclaimed dive bar for some huge burgers at dirt-cheap prices. Triple-D fans love the Gally Buster, which is a 1-pound triple cheeseburger for only $6. If you don&#x27;t mind spicy, try the Jalapeno Cream Cheese Burger with extra bacon or go crunchy with the Cashew Burger.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Little Twisted</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wi/superior/anchor-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.10404,46.73330,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Franks Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Franks Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kenosha, WI 53140 &middot; &#9733; 4.6 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2626571017" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">262-657-1017</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.franksdinerkenosha.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.franksdinerkenosha.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Franks+Diner%2C+508+58th+St.%2C+Kenosha%2C+WI+53140&amp;ll=42.583361,-87.817521" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">508 58th St.<br/>Kenosha, WI 53140</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chorizo Garbage Plate</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Triple D, Guy takes a heaping mouthful of the famous Garbage Plate at Franks Diner. The signature dish made of hash and eggs (and everything in between) has made the Kenosha diner an institution since 1926. The French Toast Cinnamon Rolls and Peanut Butter and Jelly Pancakes don&#x27;t hurt either.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Breakfast<br/>Small Town Sensations</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wi/kenosha/franks-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.81752,42.58336,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Shorty&#x27;s Pizza &amp; Smoked Meat</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Shorty&#x27;s Pizza &amp; Smoked Meat</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Superior, WI 54880 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7157180889" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(715) 718-0889</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.shortyssuperior.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.shortyssuperior.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Shorty%27s+Pizza+%26+Smoked+Meat%2C+1015+Tower+Ave%2C+Superior%2C+WI+54880&amp;ll=46.726016,-92.104372" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1015 Tower Ave<br/>Superior, WI 54880</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meat Lover&#x27;s Pizza, Hunter&#x27;s Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Shorty&#x27;s dishes are inspired by Montreal&#x27;s obsession with smoked meat, like the Meat Lover&#x27;s pizza topped with sausage, pepperoni and bacon. Guy knows to order the hidden dish not listed on the menu - the hunter&#x27;s chicken, featuring a signature sauce that&#x27;s their take on a red wine reduction.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cross-Country Classics<br/>Meaty Masterpieces</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wi/superior/shorty_s-pizza---smoked-meat" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.10437,46.72602,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Delta Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Delta Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Delta, WI 54856 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7153726666" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(715) 372-6666</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.deltadiner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.deltadiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Delta+Diner%2C+14385+County+Highway+H%2C+Delta%2C+WI+54856&amp;ll=46.474456,-91.273663" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">14385 County Highway H<br/>Delta, WI 54856</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Norwegian Pancake</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This diner is in the middle of nowhere, but it&#x27;s worth the trip. Traditional dishes get funky twists, like the red-eye gravy made with ground espresso beans. Served over buttermilk biscuits, it has the locals hooked. Guy loves the Norwegian Pancake with jalapeno, declaring it &quot;a crepe gone wild.&quot;&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old School Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wi/delta/delta-diner" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-91.27366,46.47446,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Brick House Cafe and Catering</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Brick House Cafe and Catering</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cable, WI 54821 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7157985432" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(715) 798-5432</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thebrickhousecafe.net/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thebrickhousecafe.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Brick+House+Cafe+and+Catering%2C+13485+Reynolds+St%2C+Cable%2C+WI+54821&amp;ll=46.207645,-91.291705" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">13485 Reynolds St<br/>Cable, WI 54821</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Espresso BBQ Pulled Pork Sandwich, French Toast, Panini</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For Guy, the standout at The Brick House Cafe is the espresso BBQ pulled pork sandwich. Prepared with a homemade dry rub and then marinated, the pork is topped with a delicious barbecue sauce that gives it a smoky flavor. Another favorite is the French toast with a caramel-toffee brulee drizzle.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Extra Helpings<br/>Meat in the Middle</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wi/cable/the-brick-house-cafe-and-catering" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-91.29170,46.20764,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nora&#x27;s Fish Creek Inn</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nora&#x27;s Fish Creek Inn</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wilson, WY 83014 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3077338288" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">307-733-8288</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.norasfishcreekinn.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.norasfishcreekinn.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nora%27s+Fish+Creek+Inn%2C+5600+W+Hwy+22%2C+Wilson%2C+WY+83014&amp;ll=43.497984,-110.874584" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5600 W Hwy 22<br/>Wilson, WY 83014</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Banana Bread French Toast, Beef Stroganoff</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nora&#x27;s Fish Creek Inn is the place locals flock to for breakfast, lunch and dinner. A favorite is the banana-bread French toast topped with powdered sugar, blueberries and walnuts, which Guy likens to a &quot;breakfast avalanche.&quot; Guy also loves the &quot;super creamy&quot; beef stroganoff with mushroom sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Day Dining<br/>All-American All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wy/wilson/nora_s-fish-creek-inn" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-110.87458,43.49798,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sidewinders American Grill &amp; Tavern</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sidewinders American Grill &amp; Tavern</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Jackson, WY 83001 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3077345766" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(307) 734-5766</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sidewinderstavern.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sidewinderstavern.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sidewinders+American+Grill+%26+Tavern%2C+945+W+Broadway%2C+Jackson%2C+WY+83001&amp;ll=43.474534,-110.783885" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">945 W Broadway<br/>Jackson, WY 83001</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sidewinder Pretzel, French Onion Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">French onion soup may not be what you expect at a sports bar, but that&#x27;s exactly what Guy gets at Sidewinders and he calls it &quot;the real deal.&quot; If you are looking for more-traditional bar food, opt for the &amp;quot;S&amp;quot;idewinder Pretzel, which you can get stuffed with mozzarella, pepperoni or jalapenos.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Stuffed and Twisted</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wy/jackson/sidewinders-american-grill---tavern" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-110.78388,43.47453,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pinky G&#x27;s Pizzeria</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pinky G&#x27;s Pizzeria</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Jackson 83001 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3077347465" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">307-734-7465</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pinkygs.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pinkygs.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pinky+G%27s+Pizzeria%2C+50+W+Broadway%2C+Jackson+83001&amp;ll=43.479300,-110.763000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">50 W Broadway<br/>Jackson 83001</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Funky Chicken Pizza, The Abe Froman Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Follow Guy&#x27;s lead and satisfy your pizza cravings at Pinky G&#x27;s. Guy savors the Funky Chicken, which is smothered in basil pesto and topped with marinated chicken breasts, ricotta, red onions, artichoke hearts and mozzarella. Another must-try is The Abe Froman: Spicy sausage is the star of this pie.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old Standards, New Styles<br/>Takeout: Goin&#x27; Big and Bringin&#x27; Home<br/>Pizza Party<br/>Primetime Pork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wy/jackson/pinky-g_s-pizzeria" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-110.76300,43.47930,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pica&#x27;s Mexican Taqueria</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pica&#x27;s Mexican Taqueria</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Jackson, WY 83001 &middot; &#9733; 2.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3077344457" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(307) 734-4457</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.picastaqueria.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.picastaqueria.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pica%27s+Mexican+Taqueria%2C+1160+Alpine+Ln%2C+Jackson%2C+WY+83001&amp;ll=43.471847,-110.787297" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1160 Alpine Ln<br/>Jackson, WY 83001</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sopes de Chicken Tinga, Pork Posole Verde</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">While you may not expect good Mexican food in Wyoming, Pica&#x27;s will prove you wrong. Guy tries the Sopes de Chicken Tinga: masa boats filled with refried beans and chicken tinga, then topped with lettuce, cheese, tomato, onion, chipotle salsa and sour cream. The pork posole verde is also a must-try.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Standards to Standouts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wy/jackson/pica_s-mexican-taqueria" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-110.78730,43.47185,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lotus Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lotus Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Jackson, WY 83001 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3077340882" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(307) 734-0882</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://tetonlotuscafe.com/Lotus_Cafe/Welcome.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">tetonlotuscafe.com/Lotus_Cafe/Welcome.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lotus+Cafe%2C+145+N+Glenwood+St%2C+Jackson%2C+WY+83001&amp;ll=43.480800,-110.764000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">145 N Glenwood St<br/>Jackson, WY 83001</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bombay Bowl, Thai Curry</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A 100 percent organic joint is not what you expect in Wyoming, but local hot spot Lotus Cafe is exactly that. Guy loves the velvety texture of the Bombay Bowl with bison, vegetables, mango, roasted coconut and a special tikka sauce. The Thai curry bowl with rice noodles is another diner favorite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Something for Everyone<br/>Small Town Standouts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wy/jackson/lotus-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-110.76400,43.48080,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cafe Genevieve</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cafe Genevieve</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Jackson, WY 83001 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3077321910" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(307) 732-1910</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://genevievejh.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">genevievejh.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cafe+Genevieve%2C+135+E+Broadway%2C+Jackson%2C+WY+83001&amp;ll=43.479595,-110.760033" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">135 E Broadway<br/>Jackson, WY 83001</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ramen Noodle Bowl, Pork Neck Ragu, Pig Candy</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This renovated cabin space now houses a casual joint with an eclectic menu. One of Cafe Genevieve&#x27;s star dishes is Pig Candy (a bacon lover&#x27;s dream).Thick applewood-smoked bacon is cooked fresh daily and covered in a blend of sugars and spices; it&#x27;s baked &quot;low and slow,&quot; which results in the ultimate coating. Pig Candy became so popular that the restaurant now sells it by the box on-site and at select shops around town. At brunch, step up your salad game with the aptly named Pig Candy Salad, which features the chopped candy sprinkled on top like bacon bits.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Extra Helpings<br/>Seriously Saucy</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wy/jackson/cafe-genevieve-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-110.76003,43.47959,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cempazuchi</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cempazuchi</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Milwaukee, WI 53202 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4142915233" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(414) 291-5233</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cempazuchi.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cempazuchi.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cempazuchi%2C+1205+E+Brady+St%2C+Milwaukee%2C+WI+53202&amp;ll=43.052821,-87.896665" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1205 E Brady St<br/>Milwaukee, WI 53202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mole Poblano</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you&#x27;re skeptical on how authentic Mexican food could be in Milwaukee, you&#x27;ll change your mind after trying the mole at Cempazuchi. Owner Bryce Clark has been traveling to Mexico and seeking out recipes to deliver unique authentic dishes like duck tacos and Fajitas de Nortenos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Tacos and Dogs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wi/milwaukee/cempazuchi-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.89667,43.05282,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Comet Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Comet Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Milwaukee, WI 53202 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4142737677" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(414) 273-7677</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thecometcafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thecometcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Comet+Cafe%2C+1947+N+Farwell+Ave%2C+Milwaukee%2C+WI+53202&amp;ll=43.056128,-87.889587" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1947 N Farwell Ave<br/>Milwaukee, WI 53202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meat Mountain, Bloody Mary, Akimbo Burger, Bottomless Bacon, AJ&#x27;s Compact Turkey Dinner (Fried Balls of Turkey, Stuffing and Mashed Potatoes)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this cafe, even the bloody Mary comes with bacon. Guy could barely finish the meat mountain - a stack of meatloaf, bacon mashed potatoes and bacon on rye bread. Starving? Try the Akimbo Burger, which uses two grilled cheese sandwiches for a bun, or order a beer and get a bottomless bowl of bacon.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort Cookin&#x27;<br/>Ultimate Turkey Fest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wi/milwaukee/comet-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.88959,43.05613,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Central City Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Central City Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Huntington, WV 25704 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3045226142" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(304) 522-6142</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wv/huntington/central-city-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wv/huntington/central-city-cafe-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Central+City+Cafe%2C+529+14th+St.+W.%2C+Huntington%2C+WV+25704&amp;ll=38.411376,-82.479398" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">529 14th St. W.<br/>Huntington, WV 25704</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">White Bean Chili, Homemade Cornbread, Granny Faye&#x27;s Meatloaf</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ask a local where to find the best comfort food in Huntington, W.Va., and they&#x27;ll direct you to the Central City Cafe. A hometown favorite is the white bean chili, which wouldn&#x27;t be complete without a piece of homemade cornbread - Guy guarantees it&#x27;ll make you happy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort Food</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wv/huntington/central-city-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.47940,38.41138,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tortilla Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tortilla Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Washington, DC 20003 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2025475700" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(202) 547-5700</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tortillacafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tortillacafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tortilla+Cafe%2C+210+7th+St+SE+%23+1%2C+Washington%2C+DC+20003&amp;ll=38.886968,-76.995652" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">210 7th St SE # 1<br/>Washington, DC 20003</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork and Cheese Pupusas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For a little spice and no DC politics, Tortilla Cafe delivers with Salvadorian pork-and-cheese pupusas. On Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Guy calls these stuffed tortillas &amp;quot;out of bounds.&amp;quot; For more out-of-bounds flavor, try the chicken tamales made with a traditional masa and perfect blend of spices.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Pork to Tofu</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/dc/washington/tortilla-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.99565,38.88697,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Toki Underground</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Toki Underground</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Washington, DC 20002</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2023883086" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">202-388-3086</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://tokiunderground.com/#/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">tokiunderground.com/#</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Toki+Underground%2C+1234+H+Street+NE%2C+Washington%2C+DC+20002&amp;ll=38.900388,-76.989031" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1234 H Street NE<br/>Washington, DC 20002</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Vegetarian Dumplings, Toki Classic Ramen</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This semi-hidden noodle shop serves up addictive dishes like the Toki Classic Ramen that Guy describes as &quot;a seven-course meal sitting inside of a bowl.&quot; He also raves about the vegetarian dumplings, which feature a ginger-and-garlic-laced filling of fried tofu, shiitake mushrooms and daikon radish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">East-West Flavorfest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/dc/washington/toki-underground-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.98903,38.90039,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tune Inn Restaurant &amp; Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tune Inn Restaurant &amp; Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Washington, DC 20003 &middot; &#9733; 3.1 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2025432725" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(202) 543-2725</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Tune-Inn-Restaurant-Bar/118011451549614" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Tune-Inn-Restaurant-Bar/118011451549614</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tune+Inn+Restaurant+%26+Bar%2C+331+Pennsylvania+Ave+SE%2C+Washington%2C+DC+20003&amp;ll=38.886369,-77.001167" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">331 Pennsylvania Ave SE<br/>Washington, DC 20003</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Mike&#x27;s Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For more than 60 years, politicians and hungry tourists have ventured to DC&#x27;s Tune Inn for classic, greasy dive food. Guy raved about the Bon Ton sauce used generously for such specials as Joe&#x27;s West Virginia sandwich made with American cheese and the beer-battered burger, dripping with flavor.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tried and True</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/dc/washington/tune-inn-restaurant-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.00117,38.88637,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Oohhs &amp; Aahhs Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Oohhs &amp; Aahhs Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Washington, DC 20001 &middot; &#9733; 3.9 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2026677142" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(202) 667-7142</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.oohhsnaahhs.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.oohhsnaahhs.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Oohhs+%26+Aahhs+Restaurant%2C+1005+U+St+NW%2C+Washington%2C+DC+20001&amp;ll=38.917205,-77.026265" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1005 U St NW<br/>Washington, DC 20001</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Wings, Cajun Grilled Shrimp and Grits</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oohhs &amp;amp; Aahhs Restaurant will make you do exactly that - go &quot;ooh&quot; and &quot;aah.&quot; This joint is the real deal when it comes to soul food, as they use classic recipes passed down from the two owners&#x27; grandmothers. Guy can&#x27;t get enough of the shrimp and grits or the spicy Buffalo wings with fries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wings, Dogs and Claws</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/dc/washington/oohhs-aahhs-gourmet-deli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.02626,38.91721,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Comet Ping Pong</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Comet Ping Pong</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Washington, DC 20008 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2023640404" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">202-364-0404</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cometpingpong.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cometpingpong.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Comet+Ping+Pong%2C+5037+Connecticut+Ave+NW%2C+Washington%2C+DC+20008&amp;ll=38.955972,-77.069892" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5037 Connecticut Ave NW<br/>Washington, DC 20008</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Smoky Pizza, Yalie (Clam Pizza), Stanley (Pizza with Ricotta, Mozzarella, Peppers and Sausage), Philly Calzone, Homemade Ricotta</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">It didn&#x27;t take long for James Alefantis to realize that combining his two loves, pizza and Ping-Pong, would be a great idea. In comes Comet Ping Pong, the D.C. hangout Guy couldn&#x27;t resist visiting, as he called the Yalie clam pizza and the roasted pork Philly calzone some of the best he&#x27;s ever had.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Farm To Table<br/>Triple D Nation: Italian, Thai and Pie</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/dc/washington/comet-ping-pong-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.06989,38.95597,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Carving Room</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Carving Room</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Washington, DC 20002 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2029623947" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">202-962-3947</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://carvingroom.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">carvingroom.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Carving+Room%2C+140+M+St%2C+NE%2C+Washington%2C+DC+20002&amp;ll=38.894648,-77.001347" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">140 M St, NE<br/>Washington, DC 20002</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cigars, Pastrami Poblano on Ciabatta</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This spot earned the name &quot;carnivore compound&quot; from Guy, thanks to its meat-heavy menu of scratch-made creations that reflect the owner&#x27;s Jewish-Moroccan roots. A must-try is the Chorizo Cigar: A thin dough wrapper is stuffed with spicy, housemade sausage, then fried until flaky and golden brown.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of Meat</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/dc/washington/carving-room-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.00135,38.89465,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bub and Pop&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bub and Pop&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Washington, DC 20036 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2024571111" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">202-457-1111</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bubandpops.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bubandpops.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bub+and+Pop%27s%2C+1815+M+St+NW%2C+Washington%2C+DC+20036&amp;ll=38.905922,-77.042393" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1815 M St NW<br/>Washington, DC 20036</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jewish Hoagie, Roast Pork Sandwich, Lil&#x27; Petey&#x27;s Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Jon Taub trained in French cuisine, but it&#x27;s this Philly native&#x27;s knack for crafting hoagies that draws the crowds. Everything is scratch-made, including the condiments that adorn his creations like the Jewish Hoagie. This beauty stars four kinds of meat, including brisket braised for 14 days.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Meat Mashup<br/>Rockstar Chefs<br/>Between the Bread</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/dc/washington/bub-and-pops-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.04239,38.90592,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Once Upon A Thyme</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Once Upon A Thyme</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chehalis, Washington 98532 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3607408944" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(360) 740-8944</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/once-upon-a-thyme" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/once-upon-a-thyme</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Once+Upon+A+Thyme%2C+1090+NW+State+Ave.%2C+Chehalis%2C+Washington+98532&amp;ll=46.670983,-122.973605" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1090 NW State Ave.<br/>Chehalis, Washington 98532</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This quaint and cute restaurant serves lunch, with vegetarian and vegan options, in a friendly space that is also home to a retail store, a garden and office spaces. The dishes are made from scratch, with a few patrons can purchase for carry-out or learn to make for themselves through cooking classes offered at the restaurant.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meat and Heat</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/once-upon-a-thyme" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.97361,46.67098,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>NW Sausage and Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">NW Sausage and Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Centralia, WA 98531 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3607367760" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(360) 736-7760</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://dicksbeer.com/deli/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">dicksbeer.com/deli</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=NW+Sausage+and+Deli%2C+5945+Prather+Rd+SW%2C+Centralia%2C+WA+98531&amp;ll=46.771517,-123.007426" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5945 Prather Rd SW<br/>Centralia, WA 98531</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">NW Sausage and Deli is home to more than 20 original recipes for smoked meats. The meats are prepared Old World style and include sausage, jerky and pepperoni and can be paired with original brews on tap.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Domestic &amp; Abroad</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/nw-sausage-and-deli" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-123.00743,46.77152,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ethos Bakery &amp; Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ethos Bakery &amp; Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richland 99352 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.ethosbakery.net/ethos-bakery-cafe" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.ethosbakery.net/ethos-bakery-cafe</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ethos+Bakery+%26+Cafe%2C+2150+Keene+Rd%2C+Richland+99352&amp;ll=46.246899,-119.300803" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2150 Keene Rd<br/>Richland 99352</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Salmon Gravlax, Ethos Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and Owner Angela Kora was a mechanical engineer before bringing her attention to detail to the baking world. The menu at Ethos Bakery &amp; Cafe is designed around fresh, local fare. The bakery even mills their own grain on site. Guy was enamored with the Salmon Gravlax. &quot;You want to slow down when you eat it to appreciate the depth ... Love this,&quot; he said. He was also impressed by the over-the-top Ethos Burger which is served on a house-made croissant bun with a bacon and braised leek topping. That one of the most outside-of-the-box burgers I have ever had on DDD,&quot; said Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burger and Breakfast</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/restaurants-in-richland/ethos-bakery-and-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.30080,46.24690,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Barley&#x27;s Brewhub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Barley&#x27;s Brewhub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kennewick, WA 99336</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://barleysbrewhub.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">barleysbrewhub.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Barley%27s+Brewhub%2C+3320+W.+Kennewick+Ave%2C+Kennewick%2C+WA+99336&amp;ll=46.209920,-119.167022" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3320 W. Kennewick Ave<br/>Kennewick, WA 99336</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Gyro Sausage, Smoked Braut with Chili</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Barley&#x27;s Brewpub is known for their beer, but the restaurant is also making a mark with their menu. They offer real-deal barbecue and inventive house-made sausages in addition to a killer selection of brews.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Belly, Beef and Bratwurst</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/restaurants-in-kennewick/barleys-brewhub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.16702,46.20992,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Frost Me Sweet Bakery &amp; Bistro</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Frost Me Sweet Bakery &amp; Bistro</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richland 99352</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.frostmesweetbakeryandbistro.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.frostmesweetbakeryandbistro.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Frost+Me+Sweet+Bakery+%26+Bistro%2C+710+The+Parkway%2C+Richland+99352&amp;ll=46.275465,-119.274143" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">710 The Parkway<br/>Richland 99352</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Duck Bahn Mi, Sweet Potato Lasagna</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jason and Megan Savely started Frost Me Sweet as a bakery and it later morphed into a happening restaurant. In addition to 350 different flavors of cupcakes and elegantly decorated cakes, diners can taste Chef Jason&#x27;s unique cuisine like the Duck Bahn Mi and Sweet Potato Lasagna.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Not Your Everyday Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/restaurants-in-richland/frost-me-sweet-bakery-bistro-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.27414,46.27546,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mackinaw&#x27;s Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mackinaw&#x27;s Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chehalis 98532</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3607408000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(360) 740-8000</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.mackinawsrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mackinawsrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mackinaw%27s+Restaurant%2C+545+N+Market+Blvd+%231%2C+Chehalis+98532&amp;ll=46.665617,-122.970736" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">545 N Market Blvd #1<br/>Chehalis 98532</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mackinaw&#x27;s eclectic menu features dishes made from farm-to-table ingredients. Inspired by food from all over the map, some of their signature dishes are Duck Breast, Southwestern Braised Rabbit and Oxtail Pakistani Curry.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Regional Flavors</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/mackinaw-s-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.97074,46.66562,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Porter&#x27;s Real Barbecue</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Porter&#x27;s Real Barbecue</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richland, WA 99352 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://portersrealbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">portersrealbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Porter%27s+Real+Barbecue%2C+705+The+Parkway%2C+Richland%2C+WA+99352&amp;ll=46.275250,-119.274569" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">705 The Parkway<br/>Richland, WA 99352</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef Rib, Smoked Jalapeno Poppers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Porter Kinney is serving up monstrous meat and more at Porter&#x27;s Real Barbeque in Richland, Washington. The restaurant uses applewood and cherrywood to make favorites like the gigantic smoked beef rib and bacon-wrapped jalapeno poppers.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern to South American</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/restaurants-in-richland/porters-real-barbecue-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.27457,46.27525,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Folded Pizza Pie</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Folded Pizza Pie</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richland 99352</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/FoldedPizzaPie/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/FoldedPizzaPie</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Folded+Pizza+Pie%2C+421+Wellsian+Way%2C+Richland+99352&amp;ll=46.270391,-119.285518" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">421 Wellsian Way<br/>Richland 99352</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Folder Pie is the place to go for stuffed Italian specialties like calzone and stromboli. Chef Dale Leikam wraps savory and sweet toppings into his signature pizza dough. &quot;If it&#x27;s funky I&#x27;ll find it, and you might be getting the freaky-funky award,&quot; said Guy after trying the Chef Dale&#x27;s wild and delicious creations.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mega Meat and Sweet Treats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/restaurants-in-richland/the-folded-pizza-pie-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.28552,46.27039,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Vinny&#x27;s Bakery</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Vinny&#x27;s Bakery</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Pasco, WA 99301 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.vinnysbakery.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.vinnysbakery.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Vinny%27s+Bakery%2C+1107+W.+Lewis+St%2C+Pasco%2C+WA+99301&amp;ll=46.228352,-119.101919" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1107 W. Lewis St<br/>Pasco, WA 99301</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cuban Sandwich, Vinny&#x27;s Chicken Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owner Vinny Marim and his son Charlie are serving sweet and savory specialties at this bakery in Pasco, Washington. The Cuban Sandwich is a standout, made on house-made baguette with slow-roasted pork, slathered with their house-made hot sauce, ham and Swiss cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwich Showcase</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/restaurants-in-pasco/vinnys-bakery-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.10192,46.22835,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fish Tale Brew Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fish Tale Brew Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Olympia, WA 98501 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3609436480" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(360) 943-6480</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.fishbrewing.com/fish-tale-brewpub" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fishbrewing.com/fish-tale-brewpub</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fish+Tale+Brew+Pub%2C+515+Jefferson+St+SE%2C+Olympia%2C+WA+98501&amp;ll=47.043726,-122.896719" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">515 Jefferson St SE<br/>Olympia, WA 98501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bangers and Mash, Dungeness Crab Cannoli</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This pub is the go-to spot in Olympia for craft beer and craft food. Chef Kerin Lewis sources fresh local seafood and produce to create her northwestern flavors. Guy enjoyed the Dungeness crab cannoli with roasted red pepper sauce. Locals rave about the handmade made bangers and mash.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Land to Sea</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/olympia/fish-tale-brew-pub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.89672,47.04373,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Darby&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Darby&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Olympia, WA 98501 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3603576229" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(360) 357-6229</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.darbyscafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.darbyscafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Darby%27s+Cafe%2C+211+5th+Ave+SE%2C+Olympia%2C+WA+98501&amp;ll=47.044144,-122.899653" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">211 5th Ave SE<br/>Olympia, WA 98501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Creole Oyster Benedict, Winter Squash and Apple Hash</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Vegetarians, vegans and meat-eaters alike flock to this eatery for some good-old-fashioned cooking made with local fruits and vegetables. Guy loved the Creole oyster benedict topped with Creole cream sauce and served with a side of home fries. Loyal fans recommend the winter squash and apple hash.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hometown Haunts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/olympia/darbys-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.89965,47.04414,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Blue Plate Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Blue Plate Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City 84108 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8014631151" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">801-463-1151</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.theblueplatediner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.theblueplatediner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Blue+Plate+Diner%2C+2041+S+2100+E%2C+Salt+Lake+City+84108&amp;ll=40.725840,-111.830542" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2041 S 2100 E<br/>Salt Lake City 84108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Corned Beef Hash, Smoked Salmon, Omelet</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Blue Plate Diner prides itself on homemade food, a sentiment that is clearly evident in their popular corned beef hash and smoked salmon - both are done completely in-house. Guy was impressed by their Mexican dishes, such as tamales and pork chili verde.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners You Sent Me To<br/>Real-Deal Diners</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/blue-plate-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.83054,40.72584,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Moochie&#x27;s Meatballs and More</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Moochie&#x27;s Meatballs and More</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City, UT 84111 &middot; &#9733; 4.9 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8015961350" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">801-596-1350</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.moochiesmeatballs.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.moochiesmeatballs.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Moochie%27s+Meatballs+and+More%2C+232+E+800+South%2C+Salt+Lake+City%2C+UT+84111&amp;ll=40.751675,-111.884104" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">232 E 800 South<br/>Salt Lake City, UT 84111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meatball Subs, Philly-Style Cheesesteak, Eggplant Parmigiana Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Philadelphia native Joanna Rendi moved to Salt Lake City, she wasn&#x27;t happy with the quality of the sandwich shops in the area - so she made Moochie&#x27;s Meatballs. Guy says the meatball sub will &#x27;&#x27;knock your head off.&#x27;&#x27; Also try the authentic Philly cheese steak with Joanna&#x27;s marinara sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grabbin&#x27; a Sandwich<br/>Triple D Nation: Steak, Sausage and Salami<br/>Best of the West</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/moochies-meatballs-more-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.88410,40.75168,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Maxwell&#x27;s East Coast Eatery</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Maxwell&#x27;s East Coast Eatery</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City, UT 84111 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8013280304" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(801) 328-0304</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.maxwellsece.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.maxwellsece.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Maxwell%27s+East+Coast+Eatery%2C+357+S+Main+St%2C+Salt+Lake+City%2C+UT+84111&amp;ll=40.761359,-111.890973" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">357 S Main St<br/>Salt Lake City, UT 84111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">10oz Meatball, Chicken Parmigiano</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Chicken Parmigiano is one of Maxwell&#x27;s most-popular items; it features chicken that is lightly breaded and sauteed, topped with mozzarella, then served with Mom Mom&#x27;s Gravy (marinara sauce) and a side of fettuccine. Guy loves the 10-ounce meatball you can add to any of your pastas.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Meatballs to Lollipops</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/maxwell_s-east-coast-eatery-" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.89097,40.76136,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ruth&#x27;s Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ruth&#x27;s Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City, UT 84108 &middot; &#9733; 4.9 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8015825807" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(801) 582-5807</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.ruthsdiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.ruthsdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ruth%27s+Diner%2C+2100+Emigration+Canyon%2C+Salt+Lake+City%2C+UT+84108&amp;ll=40.785756,-111.716360" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2100 Emigration Canyon<br/>Salt Lake City, UT 84108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Biscuits and Gravy, Grandma Claire&#x27;s Baked Mac and Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Not only is Ruth&#x27;s Diner almost 90 years old, but it&#x27;s also home to &amp;quot;biscuit-baking bad boy&amp;quot; Ines Monreal, who has made nearly 3 million biscuits (including some blindfolded). Guy devoured the fluffy biscuits. Meanwhile, locals love Ruth&#x27;s braised chicken and deep-fried mac and cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Places You Sent Me</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/ruths-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.71636,40.78576,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Laziz Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Laziz Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City, UT 84101</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.lazizkitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.lazizkitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Laziz+Kitchen%2C+912+Jefferson+St.+W%2C+Salt+Lake+City%2C+UT+84101&amp;ll=40.749385,-111.895642" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">912 Jefferson St. W<br/>Salt Lake City, UT 84101</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mediterranean Platter, Shish Tawook Wrap</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Moudi Sbeity and husband Derek Kitchen run this spot unique Lebanese spot in Salt Lake City. Eating here is like taking a culinary tour of Lebanon, say diners.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">&#x27;Round the World Roundup</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/laziz-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.89564,40.74939,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lone Star Taqueria</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lone Star Taqueria</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City, UT 84121 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8019442300" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(801) 944-2300</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.lonestartaqueria.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.lonestartaqueria.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lone+Star+Taqueria%2C+2265+E+Fort+Union+Boulevard%2C+Salt+Lake+City%2C+UT+84121&amp;ll=40.624309,-111.825730" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2265 E Fort Union Boulevard<br/>Salt Lake City, UT 84121</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Adovada Burrito, Shrimp Burrito</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lone Star Taqueria near Salt Lake City always attracts the crowds - Guy said &#x27;&#x27;it felt like [he] walked into a fiesta.&#x27;&#x27; Locals love the carne adovada burritos and steak tacos made by Manuel Valdez and his brother. Guy was amazed by the shrimp burrito, calling it &#x27;&#x27;nothin&#x27; but happy.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Burgers, Burritos and Biscuits<br/>Mex to the Max<br/>Doin&#x27; Their Own Thing</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/lone-star-taqueria-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.82573,40.62431,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Red Iguana</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Red Iguana</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City 84116 &middot; &#9733; 4.9 (15 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8013221489" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(801) 322-1489</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rediguana.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rediguana.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Red+Iguana%2C+736+W+North+Temple%2C+Salt+Lake+City+84116&amp;ll=40.771914,-111.912490" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">736 W North Temple<br/>Salt Lake City 84116</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mole, Nachos, Quesadillas, Red Iguana</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Cardenas family has been serving Mexican food 365 days a year since 1965. While their extensive menu offers everything from cochinita pibil to enchiladas suizas, the collection of mouthwatering moles (seven in total) is the signature showcase and a tribute to Mexico&#x27;s national dish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Smothered and Covered<br/>Real Deal Mexican<br/>A Taste of Everywhere</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/red-iguana-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.91249,40.77191,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hruska&#x27;s Kolaches</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hruska&#x27;s Kolaches</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City 84105 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3853094379" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(385) 309-4379</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://hruskaskolaches.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">hruskaskolaches.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hruska%27s+Kolaches%2C+2030+South+900+East%2C+Salt+Lake+City+84105&amp;ll=40.726026,-111.865559" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2030 South 900 East<br/>Salt Lake City 84105</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sausage and Gravy, Raspberry Cream</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and Owner Devin Hruska and her brothers opened Hruska&#x27;s Kolaches to bring their favorite Czech stuffed pastry to Salt Lake City.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Handy Helpings<br/>Takeout: Global Comes Local</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/hruskas-kolaches-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.86556,40.72603,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Aristo&#x27;s Greek Cuisine</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Aristo&#x27;s Greek Cuisine</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City, UT 84102</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8015810888" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(801) 581-0888</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.aristosslc.com/#about" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.aristosslc.com/#about</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Aristo%27s+Greek+Cuisine%2C+224+S+1300+E%2C+Salt+Lake+City%2C+UT+84102&amp;ll=40.764174,-111.854373" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">224 S 1300 E<br/>Salt Lake City, UT 84102</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grilled Octopus, Lamb Taco</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy swings by Aristo&#x27;s for old-school Greek cuisine with a modern twist. He swears the grilled octopus drizzled with Cretan extra virgin olive oil and lemon will make a convert of anyone. The lamb tacos are also a hit; Guy says &quot;the lamb is perfect, tortillas are great (and) the feta is fantastic.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">International Family Style</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/aristo_s-greek-cuisine" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.85437,40.76417,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Oh Mai Vietnamese Sandwich</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Oh Mai Vietnamese Sandwich</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City, UT 84121 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8012779888" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(801) 277-9888</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.ohmaisandwich.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.ohmaisandwich.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Oh+Mai+Vietnamese+Sandwich%2C+6093+S+Highland+Dr%2C+Salt+Lake+City%2C+UT+84121&amp;ll=40.640370,-111.834937" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6093 S Highland Dr<br/>Salt Lake City, UT 84121</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Garlic-butter Ribeye Steak, Brisket Pho</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You can expect real-deal Vietnamese food at Oh Mai. The garlic-butter rib-eye steak topped with veggies, mayo and black pepper-onion vinaigrette is a must-try. The brisket pho is also a standout. Guy likes to put Thai basil, jalapeno, bean sprouts, lime juice and Sriracha in his for the perfect pho.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">International Family Style<br/>Amazing Asian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/oh-mai-vietnamese-sandwich" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.83494,40.64037,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Arempa&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Arempa&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City, UT 84111</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3853018905" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(385) 301-8905</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.arempas.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.arempas.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Arempa%27s%2C+350+South+State+St.%2C+Salt+Lake+City%2C+UT+84111&amp;ll=40.761545,-111.888534" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">350 South State St.<br/>Salt Lake City, UT 84111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Arepas, empanadas, cachapa and pabellon are some of theVenezuelan fare you&#x27;ll findat Arempa&#x27;s, with some vegan options.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwiches and Spice</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/arempas" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.88853,40.76155,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Finn&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Finn&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City, UT 84105 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.finnscafe.net/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.finnscafe.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Finn%27s+Cafe%2C+1624+1100+E%2C+Salt+Lake+City%2C+UT+84105&amp;ll=40.734261,-111.859980" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1624 1100 E<br/>Salt Lake City, UT 84105</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Weinerschnitzel, Jule Kake French Toast</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and owner Finn Gurholt Jr. is carrying on his father&#x27;s tradition of serving American cuisine with a Scandinavian twist at Finn&#x27;s Cafe. Customers rave about the classic Weinerschnitzel and the Jule Kake French Toast, which is made with a traditional Norwegian Christmas bread with raisins, citron and cardamom.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cultural Twist</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/finns-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.85998,40.73426,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pat&#x27;s BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pat&#x27;s BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City 84115 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8014845963" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(801) 484-5963</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.patsbbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.patsbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pat%27s+BBQ%2C+155+West+Commonwealth+Ave.%2C+Salt+Lake+City+84115&amp;ll=40.724350,-111.895505" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">155 West Commonwealth Ave.<br/>Salt Lake City 84115</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulled Pork, Ribs, Burnt Ends</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Who says great barbecue is reserved for the South? At Pat&#x27;s BBQ in Salt Lake City, Pitmaster Pat Barber is what Guy calls a &quot;culinary gangster&quot; because of his unbeatable briskets, chickens and sausages that he smokes for 10 hours at a time, or as Guy put it, &quot;cha-ching money.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: From Pork to Pot Pie<br/>Meaty Masterpieces<br/>Neighborhood Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/pats-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.89550,40.72435,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Proper Burger Company</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Proper Burger Company</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City, UT 84111 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.properburgerslc.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.properburgerslc.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Proper+Burger+Company%2C+865+Main+St.%2C+Salt+Lake+City%2C+UT+84111&amp;ll=40.750389,-111.890574" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">865 Main St.<br/>Salt Lake City, UT 84111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork City Burger, Rarebit Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brothers Rio and Liam Connelly and their friend Andrew Tendick started Proper Burger Company next to their craft brewery to feed hungry beer lovers. Chef Jeff Springer is making burger magic with their brew including the dynamite Rarebit Sauce which is infused with their house beer and two cheeses and then draped over a double stacked burger.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Handy Helpings</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/proper-burger-company-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.89057,40.75039,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Purgatory</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Purgatory</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City, UT 84111</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.purgatorybar.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.purgatorybar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Purgatory%2C+62+East+700+South%2C+Salt+Lake+City%2C+UT+84111&amp;ll=40.753839,-111.888996" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">62 East 700 South<br/>Salt Lake City, UT 84111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Belly Nigiri, Short Rib Grilled Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Purgatory is a funky spot in Salt Lake City that merges Asian and American flavors to raise the bar on bar food. Owner and chef Hiro Tagai takes standard bar food and adds his own spin. For the Pork Nigiri, marinated, cooked pork is wrapped around sushi rice, topped with eel sauce and torched. Pickled mustard seed surrounds the pork like roe and the dish is garnished with chives, leeks and house-made chili oil. &quot;It&#x27;s something you&#x27;ll never find in another restaurant,&quot; said Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Whole Lotta Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/purgatory-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.88900,40.75384,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sammy&#x27;s Bistro</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sammy&#x27;s Bistro</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Park City 84060 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4352147570" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">435-214-7570</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://sammysbistro.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">sammysbistro.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sammy%27s+Bistro%2C+1890+Bonanza+Dr%2C+Park+City+84060&amp;ll=40.661187,-111.500412" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1890 Bonanza Dr<br/>Park City 84060</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">&quot;Chivito&quot; Club Sandwich, Savory Chicken Bowl</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy stops by Sammy&#x27;s Bistro to try the gourmet items that can be had at affordable prices. He marvels at the creativity of dishes like the savory chicken bowl, featuring tender chicken coated in spices, and the &quot;Chivito&quot; Club Sandwich composed of pork tenderloin, fried eggs and other tasty fillings.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Stacked Up<br/>Triple D Nation: Italian Inspired<br/>Cross Country Comfort Food</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/park-city/sammy-s-bistro" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.50041,40.66119,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tin Roof Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tin Roof Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sandy, UT 84070 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8015665226" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">801-566-5226</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tinroofgrill.net/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tinroofgrill.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tin+Roof+Grill%2C+9284+S+700+E%2C+Sandy%2C+UT+84070&amp;ll=40.582830,-111.872738" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">9284 S 700 E<br/>Sandy, UT 84070</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Croquettes, White Bean and Steak Pizza, Raspberry Charlotte Cheesecake</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tin Roof Grill offers a little bit of everything: pizzas, burgers and even Asian-influenced appetizers. Take Guy&#x27;s lead and start with the croquettes stuffed with gooey cheddar cheese and succulent bits of smoked Canadian bacon. Then dig into a decadent pizza topped with pesto, white bean puree and tender slices of flat-iron steak. Finish with a slice of the raspberry charlotte cheesecake, which features a pound-cake crust and a creamy filling studded with fresh berries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Meatballs to Lollipops<br/>Dynamite Desserts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/sandy/tin-roof-grill" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.87274,40.58283,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Whitner&#x27;s Barbecue</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Whitner&#x27;s Barbecue</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Virginia Beach, VA 23452 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (12 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7576898215" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(757) 689-8215</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.whitnersbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.whitnersbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Whitner%27s+Barbecue%2C+869+Lynnhaven+Pkwy+%23106%2C+Virginia+Beach%2C+VA+23452&amp;ll=36.812396,-76.071578" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">869 Lynnhaven Pkwy #106<br/>Virginia Beach, VA 23452</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">KC Burnt Ends, Mr. Whitner&#x27;s Smoked Turkey Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Born and raised on barbecue, owner Warren Rogers is pursuing his passion at Whitner&#x27;s Barbecue. Guy liked the &quot;real-deal&quot; KC burnt ends seasoned with the house rub and homemade barbecue sauce. For an all-in-one Thanksgiving dinner, try Mr. Whitner&#x27;s smoked turkey sandwich with cranberry chutney.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Slammin&#x27; Sammies<br/>BBQ Legends<br/>All-American All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/virginia-beach/whitners-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.07158,36.81240,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Citrus Breakfast &amp; Lunch</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Citrus Breakfast &amp; Lunch</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Virginia Beach, VA 23451 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7572273333" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(757) 227-3333</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://citrusvb.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">citrusvb.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Citrus+Breakfast+%26+Lunch%2C+2265+W+Great+Neck+Rd%2C+Virginia+Beach%2C+VA+23451&amp;ll=36.910456,-76.071517" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2265 W Great Neck Rd<br/>Virginia Beach, VA 23451</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Citrus-Glazed Pancakes , Soft-Shell Crab Benedict</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dine here if you&#x27;re looking for some breakfast or lunch with a coastal twist. Guy enjoyed the citrus-glazed pancakes topped with cinnamon and nutmeg, bananas and pineapple. The soft-shell crab Benedict&#x27;s &amp;quot;dynamite&amp;quot; flavor also impressed. The seafood comes straight from the docks and is always fresh.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza, Pancakes and Pork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/virginia-beach/citrus-breakfast-lunch-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.07152,36.91046,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Leaping Lizards Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Leaping Lizards Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Virginia Beach 23455 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7574605327" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(757) 460-5327</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/LeapingLizardCafe" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/LeapingLizardCafe</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Leaping+Lizards+Cafe%2C+4408+Shore+Dr%2C+Virginia+Beach+23455&amp;ll=36.905570,-76.123517" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4408 Shore Dr<br/>Virginia Beach 23455</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Salad Sandwich, Duck Sammies</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Everybody in town loves this cafe and antique shop for its low prices and farm-fresh produce. The &quot;righteous&quot; gourmet panini chicken salad sandwich made with homemade bread, shredded chicken, peach chutney, curry yogurt, fresh tomatoes and mixed greens was Guy&#x27;s favorite. Also try the duck sammies.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old to New</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/virginia-beach/leaping-lizards-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.12352,36.90557,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>ZZQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">ZZQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richmond, VA 23230</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.zzqrva.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.zzqrva.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=ZZQ%2C+3201+W+Moore+St%2C+Richmond%2C+VA+23230&amp;ll=37.568726,-77.471531" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3201 W Moore St<br/>Richmond, VA 23230</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Habanero Fontina Sausage, Tres Hombres Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This is arguably the best place to find Texas barbecue outside of the Lone Star State-they even make their own sausages in house! Guy was blown away by the Smoked Habanero Fontina Sausage, which is their spiciest sausage and is served with a side of house-made pickles. &quot;It&#x27;s like I&#x27;m right in central Texas,&quot; he said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smokin&#x27; Hot BBQ</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/richmond/zzq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.47153,37.56873,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Beach Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Beach Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Virginia Beach, VA 23451 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7574228817" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(757) 422-8817</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.beachpubvb.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.beachpubvb.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Beach+Pub%2C+1001+Laskin+Rd%2C+Virginia+Beach%2C+VA+23451&amp;ll=36.856691,-75.990782" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1001 Laskin Rd<br/>Virginia Beach, VA 23451</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oysters Rockefeller, Fish Hash</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The seafood at the Beach Pub is always fresh and always delicious. Guy was crazy about the oysters Rockefeller, which were topped with spinach, bacon and feta cheese. The fish hash, an 80-year-old family recipe, also impressed Guy with its tang from the onions and richness from the bacon.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Breakfast, Lunch and Dinner</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/virginia-beach/beach-pub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.99078,36.85669,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Flip Flops VB Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Flip Flops VB Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Virginia Beach, VA 23454 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (12 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7574273547" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(757) 427-3547</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.flipflopsvb.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.flipflopsvb.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Flip+Flops+VB+Grill%2C+2217+Upton+Dr+%23814%2C+Virginia+Beach%2C+VA+23454&amp;ll=36.756198,-76.010379" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2217 Upton Dr #814<br/>Virginia Beach, VA 23454</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fish Tacos, Sweet Potato Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The coastal cuisine found at this grill is laid-back, fun and fresh. Guy, a native Californian who has high standards for fish tacos, was impressed by the fresh ahi fish tacos topped with slaw and mango barbecue sauce. Locals recommend relaxing with a drink and a basket of sweet potato fries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Matters</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/virginia-beach/flip-flops-grill-chill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.01038,36.75620,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rigoletto Italian Bakery &amp; Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rigoletto Italian Bakery &amp; Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Virginia Beach 23454 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7574273999" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(757) 427-3999</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://rigolettoitalianbakeryvb.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">rigolettoitalianbakeryvb.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rigoletto+Italian+Bakery+%26+Cafe%2C+2181+Upton+Dr+%23414%2C+Virginia+Beach+23454&amp;ll=36.757753,-76.008042" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2181 Upton Dr #414<br/>Virginia Beach 23454</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Focaccia Bread for Panini Sandwiches, Florintina Panini, Eclairs, Cannolis, Stuffed Meatballs and Spaghetti</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You&#x27;ll feel like you&#x27;re in Italy at this mother and daughter-run bakery and cafe. Guy loved the sandwich with thin-sliced Marsala-marinated beef on fresh focaccia bread. The specialty is the stuffed meatballs, which are filled with cold cuts and cheese. For dessert, try the eclairs or the cannoli.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Global Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/virginia-beach/rigoletto-italian-bakery-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.00804,36.75775,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Village Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Village Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richmond, VA 23220 &middot; &#9733; 3.9 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8043538204" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(804) 353-8204</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.villagecafeonline.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.villagecafeonline.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Village+Cafe%2C+1001+W.+Grace+St.%2C+Richmond%2C+VA+23220&amp;ll=37.550889,-77.453397" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1001 W. Grace St.<br/>Richmond, VA 23220</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Omelet, Burritos, Pizza, Calzones</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Triple D, Guy described The Village Cafe as &amp;quot;part dive, part bar, but all neighborhood joint.&amp;quot; Since 1956 they&#x27;ve been churning out a little of all three with &amp;quot;crunchy crunch&amp;quot; ale-battered onion rings and Italian classics like stromboli stuffed with ham, salami, mozzarella and green peppers.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Neighborhood Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/richmond/the-village-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.45340,37.55089,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Soul Taco</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Soul Taco</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richmond, VA 23219 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.soultacorva.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.soultacorva.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Soul+Taco%2C+321+N+2nd+St%2C+Richmond%2C+VA+23219&amp;ll=37.545145,-77.439344" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">321 N 2nd St<br/>Richmond, VA 23219</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oxtail Al Pastor</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Combine the best parts of soul food cuisine and tacos and you&#x27;ll end up with this funky joint. Guy loved the Oxtail Al Pastor, which is made with meat braised in sweet root beer. The taco comes togetherby topping the meat with fresh pineapple-jalapeno salsa and agave hot sauce. Guy described the flavors as a &quot;funky fusion.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meat Sampler</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/richmond/soul-taco-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.43934,37.54515,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Perly&#x27;s Restaurant &amp; Delicatessen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Perly&#x27;s Restaurant &amp; Delicatessen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richmond, VA 23219 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.perlysrichmond.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.perlysrichmond.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Perly%27s+Restaurant+%26+Delicatessen%2C+111+E+Grace+St%2C+Richmond%2C+VA+23219&amp;ll=37.543792,-77.441525" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">111 E Grace St<br/>Richmond, VA 23219</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Potato and Duck Pierogies, Jewish Egg Rolls</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After moving to Richmond, owner Rachelle Roberts opened this Jewish deli up to share her family&#x27;s recipes with the city. The dishes are made completely from scratch, including favorites like the potato and duck pierogies, which are stuffed with a tender duck confit and wrapped in a sour cream-based dough. Guy also loved the Jewish Egg Rolls, which are stuffed with pastrami and sauerkraut.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cruisin&#x27; Capital Cities</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/richmond/perlys-restaurant-and-delicatessen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.44153,37.54379,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Fancy Biscuit</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Fancy Biscuit</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richmond 23220 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8049383449" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">804-938-3449</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.fancybiscuitrva.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fancybiscuitrva.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Fancy+Biscuit%2C+1831+W.+Cary+St.%2C+Richmond+23220&amp;ll=37.547443,-77.465123" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1831 W. Cary St.<br/>Richmond 23220</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Home-cooked Southern staples like shrimp and grits and fried green tomatoes dominate the menu at this cozy Richmond bakery and cafe. Roll up your sleeves for the signature biscuit sandwiches, because even a fork and knife can&#x27;t save you from the delicious toppling mess the kitchen creates.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Creative Creations</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/richmond/the-fancy-biscuit-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.46512,37.54744,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pop&#x27;s Market on Grace</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pop&#x27;s Market on Grace</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richmond, VA 23219</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8046447677" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(804) 644-7677</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/richmond/pops-market-on-grace-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/richmond/pops-market-on-grace-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pop%27s+Market+on+Grace%2C+415+E+Grace+St%2C+Richmond%2C+VA+23219&amp;ll=37.541965,-77.438620" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">415 E Grace St<br/>Richmond, VA 23219</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hanger Steak Gnocchi Hash, Banh Mi</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From the outside, this might look like an ordinary deli, but inside they&#x27;re making everything on the menu from scratch, including a variety of house-baked breads and rolls and the gnocchi for their Hanger Steak Hash. The gnocchi are pan-seared and topped with mushrooms, shallots, arugula and a large piece of seared hanger steak. Guy was blown away by the flavors: &quot;That&#x27;s dangerous,&quot; he said, &quot;I&#x27;m glad I don&#x27;t live in this town.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Meals</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/richmond/pops-market-on-grace-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.43862,37.54196,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dots Back Inn</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dots Back Inn</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richmond 23227 &middot; &#9733; 4.9 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8042663167" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(804) 266-3167</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.dotsbackrichmond.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.dotsbackrichmond.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dots+Back+Inn%2C+4030+MacArthur+Ave.%2C+Richmond+23227&amp;ll=37.589920,-77.458577" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4030 MacArthur Ave.<br/>Richmond 23227</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken with Feta, White Wine and Artichokes, Homemade Pesto</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Inside this small nondescript cafe is a menu filled with &quot;tons of custom-built food.&quot; So says Guy, who visited the Richmond, Va., favorite for the Black Bean Corn Cakes loaded with fresh veggies and Chicken MacArthur pasta made with onions, tomatoes and feta cheese, which is &quot;really popping.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Something Different<br/>Triple D Nation: East Coast Eatin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/richmond/dots-back-inn-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.45858,37.58992,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Carena&#x27;s Jamaican Grille</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Carena&#x27;s Jamaican Grille</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richmond, VA 23225 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.carenasrva.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.carenasrva.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Carena%27s+Jamaican+Grille%2C+7102+Midlothian+Turnpike%2C+Richmond%2C+VA+23225&amp;ll=37.507696,-77.493502" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7102 Midlothian Turnpike<br/>Richmond, VA 23225</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oxtail Stew, Island Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When chef-owner Carena Ives first opened this restaurant in 1994 selling the food she grew up eating, it was so popular that customers were begging her to move into a bigger space. Jamaican cuisine is known for comforting stews, like the classic oxtail stew that blew Guy away. &quot;It&#x27;s luscious!&quot; He said of the tender braised meat. Another standout is the fried chicken, which is served with a bold ginger gravy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Off the Beaten Path</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/richmond/carenas-jamaican-grille-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.49350,37.50770,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Wood Shop BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Wood Shop BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Seattle, WA 98144 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2064857381" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(206) 485-7381</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thewoodshopbbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thewoodshopbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Wood+Shop+BBQ%2C+2513+S+Jackson+St%2C+Seattle%2C+WA+98144&amp;ll=47.599136,-122.299250" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2513 S Jackson St<br/>Seattle, WA 98144</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Spareribs, Texas-Style Brisket</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owners Matt Davis and James Barrington brought the best of Kansas- and Texas-style BBQ to Seattle with this family-friendly joint. Their formula is simple: tender meats smoked in solid Hickory for maximum flavor. The menu features meat by the pound (which includes a killer brisket), pork spare ribs, smoked wings, sandwiches, mac and cheese bowls and a variety of classic BBQ sides.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ Bites and Southern Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/seattle/wood-shop-bbq" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.29925,47.59914,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Slim&#x27;s Last Chance Chili Shack &amp; Watering Hole</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Slim&#x27;s Last Chance Chili Shack &amp; Watering Hole</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Seattle, WA 98108 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2067627900" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(206) 762-7900</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.slimslastchance.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.slimslastchance.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Slim%27s+Last+Chance+Chili+Shack+%26+Watering+Hole%2C+5606+1st+Ave+S%2C+Seattle%2C+WA+98108&amp;ll=47.552481,-122.333903" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5606 1st Ave S<br/>Seattle, WA 98108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chili Verde, Jalapeno Mac n&#x27; Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Come to this roadhouse for some chili that is &amp;quot;off the chain.&amp;quot; Guy&#x27;s favorite was the smoked pork Chili Verde over Jalapeno Mac and Cheese. If you&#x27;re a traditionalist, order the Texas Red, which &amp;quot;has it going on&amp;quot; with a nice mild heat. The turkey chili is another fan favorite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Burger, A Bowl and a Slice</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/seattle/slims-last-chance-chili-shack-watering-hole-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.33390,47.55248,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mike&#x27;s Chili Parlor</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mike&#x27;s Chili Parlor</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Seattle 98107 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2067822808" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(206) 782-2808</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/MikesChiliParlor/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/MikesChiliParlor</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mike%27s+Chili+Parlor%2C+1447+NW+Ballard+Way%2C+Seattle+98107&amp;ll=47.662754,-122.375752" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1447 NW Ballard Way<br/>Seattle 98107</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chili, Chili Burger, Chili Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you traveled back to 1922 and fast-forwarded to today, Mike&#x27;s Chili Parlor would still be serving the same chili recipe passed down from Greece. The all-day cooking process makes for an over-the-top bowl of chili, chili burger and tasty chili pasta. As Guy says, &quot;That&#x27;s what I&#x27;m talking about.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Local Flavor<br/>Triple D Nation: Global Goodies<br/>All in the Family</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/seattle/mikes-chili-parlor" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.37575,47.66275,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Red Door</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Red Door</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Seattle, WA 98103</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2065477521" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(206) 547-7521</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://reddoorseattle.com/menu/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">reddoorseattle.com/menu</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Red+Door%2C+3401+Evanston+Ave+N%2C+Seattle%2C+WA+98103&amp;ll=47.650107,-122.351617" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3401 Evanston Ave N<br/>Seattle, WA 98103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fish &amp; Chips, Beef Dip</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Known for its old-school pub menu and local craft beers, The Red Door is a favorite among locals. You can&#x27;t go wrong with the fish and chips-the cod is super crispy on the outside and perfectly flaky on the inside.The beef dip sandwich, made with prime rib, is another great option.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On the Hook and In the Bun</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/seattle/the-red-door" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.35162,47.65011,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Voula&#x27;s Offshore Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Voula&#x27;s Offshore Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Seattle 98105 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2066340183" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">206-634-0183</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://voulasoffshore.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">voulasoffshore.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Voula%27s+Offshore+Cafe%2C+658+NE.+Northlake+Way%2C+Seattle+98105&amp;ll=47.654801,-122.321489" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">658 NE. Northlake Way<br/>Seattle 98105</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Greek Hobo (Egg Scramble), Chinese Pancake (Egg and Ham Pancake), Smokey the Salmon (Smoked Salmon Scramble), Stuffed Grape Leaves, Blueberry Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">What started as a way to put her sons through college has turned into a full-time career for Voula and both her sons. On Triple D, Guy fills up on Voula&#x27;s Greek Hobo scramble made with Greek sausage and her unique &quot;Chinese Pancake.&quot; Take a pancake, add ham, then crack an egg right in the middle.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Tastier at Home<br/>House Specials<br/>Triple D Nation: Something for Everyone</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/seattle/voulas-offshore-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.32149,47.65480,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Piroshki on 3rd</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Piroshki on 3rd</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Seattle 98104 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.piroshkion3rd.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.piroshkion3rd.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Piroshki+on+3rd%2C+710+3rd+Ave%2C+Seattle+98104&amp;ll=47.603945,-122.332185" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">710 3rd Ave<br/>Seattle 98104</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Piroshki, Dumplings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This restaurant specializes in Russian piroshki; they serve 20 different varieties of the savory, pastry-wrapped pockets. They are also dishing out traditional soups, dumplings, salads and more. Guy gushed over the Pelmeni, chicken-filled dumplings in a steaming broth. &quot;I came here for the piroshki, but this soup is stealing the show,&quot; he said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tasty Traditions</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/seattle/piroshki-on-3rd-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.33218,47.60395,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pam&#x27;s Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pam&#x27;s Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Seattle 98103 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2066967010" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">206-696-7010</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://pams-kitchen.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">pams-kitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pam%27s+Kitchen%2C+1715+N+45th+St%2C+Seattle+98103&amp;ll=47.661171,-122.336631" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1715 N 45th St<br/>Seattle 98103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pelau, Dahlpuri, Curry Goat, Spicy Jerk Kitchen</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy says &quot;they&#x27;re knocking out the real-deal food from Trinidad&quot; at Pam&#x27;s Kitchen with dishes like Spicy Jerk Chicken and Pelau. A must-try is the Dahlpuri, an unleavened bread stuffed with yellow split peas, then rolled up and cooked to order on the flattop.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">World Class Flavor<br/>Name That Cook<br/>Triple D Nation: Poke, Pork and Chicken Parm<br/>Takeout: Worldwide Delivery</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/seattle/pams-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.33663,47.66117,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Georgia&#x27;s Greek Restaurant &amp; Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Georgia&#x27;s Greek Restaurant &amp; Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Seattle, WA 98117 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2067831228" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(206) 783-1228</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.georgiasgreekrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.georgiasgreekrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Georgia%27s+Greek+Restaurant+%26+Deli%2C+323+NW+85th+St%2C+Seattle%2C+WA+98117&amp;ll=47.690436,-122.361766" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">323 NW 85th St<br/>Seattle, WA 98117</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Keftethes, Saganaki, Lamb Gyro</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Lakis Kazakos converted his auto repair shop into a Greek taverna and is now serving up his mom&#x27;s recipes. Guy could not get enough of the keftethes, which are lamb sliders flavored with mint and parsley. The saganaki, fried cheese, was also &amp;quot;off the hook.&amp;quot; Locals enjoy the lamb gyro the most.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">World Class Flavor<br/>All Over the Map</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/seattle/georgias-greek-restaurant-deli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.36177,47.69044,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bluebird Barbecue</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bluebird Barbecue</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Burlington, VT 05401</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8024483070" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">802-448-3070</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.bluebirdbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bluebirdbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bluebird+Barbecue%2C+317+Riverside+Ave%2C+Burlington%2C+VT+05401&amp;ll=44.487893,-73.195414" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">317 Riverside Ave<br/>Burlington, VT 05401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nashville Hot Sandwich, Chocolate Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A day on the slopes in Burlington is the perfect way to work up an appetite for a big BBQ meal. At Bluebird you can warm up and refuel with hearty dishes like poutine with pulled pork, barbecue seitan on a brioche bun or a Nashville Hot sandwich (fried chicken with Nashville hot sauce, pickles and ranch dressing that comes in your choice of spicy or not). Wash it all down with a Vermont beer or cider before you move on to the s&#x27;more-like chocolate pie with graham cracker crumble. Don&#x27;t count the calories; you can ski them off the next day.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smokin&#x27; Hot BBQ</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/vt/burlington/bluebird-barbecue-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.19541,44.48789,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hong&#x27;s Chinese Dumplings</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hong&#x27;s Chinese Dumplings</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Burlington, VT 05401 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.hongsdumplings.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hongsdumplings.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hong%27s+Chinese+Dumplings%2C+77+Pearl+St%2C+Burlington%2C+VT+05401&amp;ll=44.480262,-73.215615" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">77 Pearl St<br/>Burlington, VT 05401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Dumplings, Chicken and Cheese Dumplings, Scallion Pancakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Everyone in Burlington knows Ms. Hong, thanks to her legendary dumplings. In addition to making classic Chinese versions like pork, she puts an American twist on some, like the chicken andcheddar cheese dumplings. All of them are served with her homemade dumpling sauce. &quot;I want to buy it by the gallon,&quot; Guy joked.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mom and Dad</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/vt/burlington/hongs-chinese-dumplings-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.21561,44.48026,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Butch &amp; Babe&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Butch &amp; Babe&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Burlington, VT 05401</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8024950716" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">802-495-0716</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://butchandbabes.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">butchandbabes.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Butch+%26+Babe%27s%2C+258+N+Winooski+Ave%2C+Burlington%2C+VT+05401&amp;ll=44.487025,-73.208721" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">258 N Winooski Ave<br/>Burlington, VT 05401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Vegan and Gluten-Free Buckwheat-Coconut Waffles, Mac and Cheese Pancakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owner Kortnee Bush and Chef Jaclyn Major are no strangers to fine dining, having worked respectively at Twin Farms in Vermont and Savoy in New York City. They use their experience to craft elegant New American dishes that show off what Vermont has to offer, but cultivate a friendly, relaxed atmosphere that makes Butch &amp; Babe&#x27;s feel more like a neighborhood hangout.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Creative Creations</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/vt/burlington/butch-and-babes-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.20872,44.48702,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pingala Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pingala Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Burlington, VT 05401</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.pingalacafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pingalacafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pingala+Cafe%2C+1+Mill+St%2C+Burlington%2C+VT+05401&amp;ll=44.488357,-73.184612" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1 Mill St<br/>Burlington, VT 05401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crunchwrap Supreme, French Toast Puffs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You won&#x27;t miss the meat for a second at this creative vegan spot. Guy was absolutely blown away by the Crunch Wrap, which is a tortilla stuffed with bean chili, rice, an herbed chickpea spread, two different kinds of vegan cheese sauce and a layer of crunchy tortillas inside. The whole wrap is toasted on a panini press until golden brown. &quot;Out of all the vegan and vegetarian dishes I&#x27;ve had in my life, this is easily in the top five,&quot; he said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Savory with a Side of Sweet</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/vt/burlington/pingala-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.18461,44.48836,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Taco Gordo</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Taco Gordo</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Burlington, VT 05401</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.tacogordovt.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tacogordovt.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Taco+Gordo%2C+208+N+Winooski+Ave%2C+Burlington%2C+VT+05401&amp;ll=44.485982,-73.209954" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">208 N Winooski Ave<br/>Burlington, VT 05401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Al Pastor Tacos, Grandma&#x27;s Beans Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You don&#x27;t need to go south for great Mexican food anymore: Guy swears by the tacos at this Vermont college-town joint. The pork for their Al Pastor isspit-roasted to give it a super tender texture. &quot;This is the closest I&#x27;ve had to authentic Al Pastor outside of Mexico,&quot; he said. Another standout is the Grandma&#x27;s Beans tacos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lots of Latin</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/vt/burlington/taco-gordo-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.20995,44.48598,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Silver Star Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Silver Star Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Park City, UT 84060 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4356553456" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(435) 655-3456</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thesilverstarcafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thesilverstarcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Silver+Star+Cafe%2C+1825+Three+Kings+Dr%2C+Park+City%2C+UT+84060&amp;ll=40.658809,-111.516695" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1825 Three Kings Dr<br/>Park City, UT 84060</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crispy Pork Belly, Pork Osso Bucco, Vegetarian Mushroom Stroganoff</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">With its eclectic menu and prime spot by the Silver Star chairlift, this cafe is a great place to eat after skiing. Locals rave about the pork osso bucco and the vegetarian mushroom stroganoff. Guy can&#x27;t resist the pork belly with braised white beans, caramelized apples and Carolina BBQ sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cross Country Comfort Food<br/>Triple D Nation: A Little Lighter<br/>Small Town Sensations</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/park-city/the-silver-star-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.51669,40.65881,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bok A Bok Fried Chicken &amp; Biscuits</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bok A Bok Fried Chicken &amp; Biscuits</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Seattle, WA 98106 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bokabokchicken.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bokabokchicken.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bok+A+Bok+Fried+Chicken+%26+Biscuits%2C+1521+SW+98th+St%2C+Seattle%2C+WA+98106&amp;ll=47.515375,-122.354839" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1521 SW 98th St<br/>Seattle, WA 98106</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Soy Sesame Garlic Sandwich, Bowl of Shame</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">New York chef Brian O&#x27;Conner trained in classic cuisine but ended up falling for fried chicken. The dishes at Bok A Bok Fried Chicken &amp; Biscuits highlight his love for the bird. The Soy Sesame Garlic Sandwich is fried up until potato chip crispy, topped with sweet soy sauce and arugula and served on a roll spread with lemon aioli.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Far East Flavorfest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/seattle/bok-a-bok-fried-chicken-and-biscuits-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.35484,47.51537,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Pie Dump</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Pie Dump</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Garland 84312 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.thepiedump.com/home" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thepiedump.com/home</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Pie+Dump%2C+20+W+1400+S%2C+Garland+84312&amp;ll=41.726312,-112.165001" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">20 W 1400 S<br/>Garland 84312</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Special dishes: French Dip, Maple Bar Doughnut</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Utah favorite has been open for nearly a century, and they&#x27;re as popular with the locals as ever. They&#x27;re known for cooking up a mix of savory dishes and from-scratch pastries, like doughnuts and cinnamon rolls. Guy loved their classic French Dip sandwich, which is served on the restaurant&#x27;s fresh sourdough hoagie buns. &quot;It makes me smile,&quot; he said. &quot;This is right out of the old school recipe book.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Down-Home Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/restaurants-in-garland/the-pie-dump" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.16500,41.72631,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sabores</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sabores</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Logan 84321 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://sabores.international/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">sabores.international</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sabores%2C+255+Main+St+%23+300%2C+Logan+84321&amp;ll=41.726917,-111.836476" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">255 Main St # 300<br/>Logan 84321</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The best comfort foods from around the world come together on this diverse menu, like Lomo Saltado, a Peruvian beef stir fry that&#x27;s served over rice and fries. Another standout: the Peanut Butter Burger, which is a regular burger patty topped with peanut butter, bacon, cheese, and a curry aioli. Guy explained that the combo tasted like a spicy Thai peanut sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Beef to Bao</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/logan/sabores-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.83648,41.72692,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Burger Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Burger Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Roy 84067 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8018258961" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">801-825-8961</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://burgerbarutah.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">burgerbarutah.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Burger+Bar%2C+5291+S+1900+W%2C+Roy+84067&amp;ll=41.167782,-112.026708" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5291 S 1900 W<br/>Roy 84067</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big Ben Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy says the Burger Bar in Roy, Utah, has been &quot;doing it right&quot; for 52 years. He loved the Big Ben burger, and although he ordered his as a single, you can order yours double, quarter, quad and even bigger. No burger is complete without the uber crunchy, thrice-fried fries served with fry sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All in the Family<br/>Triple D Nation: BBQ, Burgers and Beyond<br/>In the Family</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/roy/burger-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.02671,41.16778,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Los Primos</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Los Primos</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Logan, UT 84341 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.elsalvadorlosprimos.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.elsalvadorlosprimos.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Los+Primos%2C+880+S.+Main+St.%2C+Logan%2C+UT+84341&amp;ll=41.756313,-111.834407" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">880 S. Main St.<br/>Logan, UT 84341</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cabeza Sopes, Pupusa</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef-owner Luis Ramos brought the flavors of El Salvator to this small Utah college town. Los Primos specializes in pupusas, a kind of stuffed tortilla that Guy describes as a &quot;tamale meets a tortilla.&quot; Here, they&#x27;re stuffed with refried beans, cheese, and pork chicharrones before they&#x27;re cooked on the flattop until browned.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lots of Latin</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/logan/los-primos-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.83441,41.75631,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tandoori Oven</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tandoori Oven</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Logan, UT 84321 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.tandooriovenlogan.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tandooriovenlogan.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tandoori+Oven%2C+720+E+1000+N%2C+Logan%2C+UT+84321&amp;ll=41.750205,-111.837602" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">720 E 1000 N<br/>Logan, UT 84321</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Tikka Masala, Keema Samosa</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hidden at a gas station in the middle of Utah is this can&#x27;t-miss Nothern Indian joint. Everything here is super authentic and cooked from scratch, including the meat for their Chicken Tikka Masala, which marinates for two daysto give it a super-tender texture. Another standout is the Keema Samosa, which is stuffed with lamb and peas.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mom and Dad</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/logan/tandoori-oven-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.83760,41.75020,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Herm&#x27;s Inn</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Herm&#x27;s Inn</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Logan, UT 84321 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.hermsinn.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hermsinn.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Herm%27s+Inn%2C+1435+Canyon+Rd%2C+Logan%2C+UT+84321&amp;ll=41.740813,-111.799637" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1435 Canyon Rd<br/>Logan, UT 84321</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Inside-Out Grilled Cheese, Cinnamon Roll</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This roadside restaurant fuels both locals and travelers with unusual plates, like the Inside-Out Grilled Cheese. The sandwich is made with cheese on both sides of the bread, which gives it a unique combo of both crunchy and gooey textures. The sandwich is also stuffed with guacamole, beans and sriracha. Guy called the mix of textures &quot;dynamite.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Savory with a Side of Sweet</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/logan/herms-inn-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.79964,41.74081,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bizzarro Italian Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bizzarro Italian Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Seattle, WA 98103 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2066327277" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(206) 632-7277</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bizzarroitaliancafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bizzarroitaliancafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bizzarro+Italian+Cafe%2C+1307+N+46th+St%2C+Seattle%2C+WA+98103&amp;ll=47.661952,-122.341671" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1307 N 46th St<br/>Seattle, WA 98103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Linguini and Clams, Elk Bolognese, Puttanesca, Lamb Shank</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bizzarro prides itself on its locally sourced seasonal menu and whimsical atmosphere. Guy licked his plate clean after diving into the linguini and clams with house made pancetta. The elk Bolognese was &quot;monster tender&quot; and not gamy at all. Customers also enjoy the puttanesca and organic lamb shank.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">By Land and Sea<br/>Funky Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/seattle/bizzarro-italian-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.34167,47.66195,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Harvey&#x27;s Hot Dogs II</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Harvey&#x27;s Hot Dogs II</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portsmouth, VA 23703 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (40 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7574830613" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(757) 483-0613</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/portsmouth/harveys-hot-dogs-ii-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/portsmouth/harveys-hot-dogs-ii-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Harvey%27s+Hot+Dogs+II%2C+3205+Stamford+Rd.%2C+Portsmouth%2C+VA+23703&amp;ll=36.861064,-76.390819" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3205 Stamford Rd.<br/>Portsmouth, VA 23703</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hot Dogs, Chicken and Dumpling Soup, Subs, Barbecue</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This old-school local hangout is pumping out hot dogs and Southern comfort food. The tender dumplings and the rich and creamy flavor of the chicken and dumpling soup captured Guy&#x27;s heart. Locals enjoy the chili dogs as well as the subs and barbecue.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Unexpected Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/portsmouth/harveys-hot-dogs-ii-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.39082,36.86106,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Moseberth&#x27;s Fried Chicken</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Moseberth&#x27;s Fried Chicken</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portsmouth, VA 23707 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7573931721" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">757-393-1721</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.moseberths.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.moseberths.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Moseberth%27s+Fried+Chicken%2C+1505+Airline+Blvd%2C+Portsmouth%2C+VA+23707&amp;ll=36.826163,-76.347524" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1505 Airline Blvd<br/>Portsmouth, VA 23707</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This 71-year-old family-run fried chicken dive is now teaching the fourth generation the secrets to its craft. Guy loved the crunch and seasoning of the fried chicken dinner, which comes with a breast, a thigh, a wing and a long leg, as well as hush puppies, fries, coleslaw and potato salad.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Time Tested Treasures<br/>Deep-Fried Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/portsmouth/moseberths-fried-chicken-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.34752,36.82616,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Captain Chuck-A-Muck&#x27;s Sandbar and Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Captain Chuck-A-Muck&#x27;s Sandbar and Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Carrolton, VA 23424 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7573561005" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">757-356-1005</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.captainchuck-a-mucks.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.captainchuck-a-mucks.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Captain+Chuck-A-Muck%27s+Sandbar+and+Grill%2C+21088+Marina+Rd%2C+Carrolton%2C+VA+23424&amp;ll=36.994804,-76.561927" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">21088 Marina Rd<br/>Carrolton, VA 23424</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crab Cake, She-Crab Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Believe it or not, the owner of Captain Chuck-A-Muck&#x27;s in Virginia, Chuck Lawrence, is an actual sea captain, making the fact that most of the fish and seafood is locally caught not the least surprising. The restaurant is famous for its crab cakes, which Guy described as &#x27;&#x27;all killer, no filler.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Where the Locals Eat<br/>Best of the Beach</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/carrolton/captain-chuck-a-mucks-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.56193,36.99480,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Virginia Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Virginia Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wakefield, VA 23888 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (15 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7578993106" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(757) 899-3106</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.vadinerrestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.vadinerrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Virginia+Diner%2C+U.S.+Route+460%2C+Wakefield%2C+VA+23888&amp;ll=36.964362,-76.976850" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">U.S. Route 460<br/>Wakefield, VA 23888</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Virginia-Style Spoonbread, Fresh-Roasted Peanuts, Peanut Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Since opening in 1929 inside a railroad car, Virginia Diner has become a destination for classic melt-in-your-mouth Southern cuisine, including Guy&#x27;s favorite: collard greens. To finish your meal, don&#x27;t leave without ordering the Peanut Pie. This is The Peanut Capital of the World, after all.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Regional Favorites<br/>All Stacked Up</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/wakefield/virginia-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.97685,36.96436,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>La Caraquena</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">La Caraquena</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Falls Church 22040 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7035330076" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(703) 533-0076</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/falls-church/la-caraquena-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/falls-church/la-caraquena-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=La+Caraquena%2C+300+W+Broad+St%2C+Falls+Church+22040&amp;ll=38.884204,-77.173704" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">300 W Broad St<br/>Falls Church 22040</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Arepas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Don&#x27;t let the facade of this quaint restaurant in a funky hotel fool you: They have everything south of the border, including a variety of vegetarian fare. Visiting on Triple D, Guy found a taste of every Latin country, including amazing arepas stuffed so big they resemble overflowing clamshells.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gone Global</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/falls-church/la-caraquena-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.17370,38.88420,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Dirty Buffalo</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Dirty Buffalo</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Norfolk, VA 23508 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7572267851" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">757-226-7851</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://thedirtybuffalo.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">thedirtybuffalo.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Dirty+Buffalo%2C+4012+Colley+Ave%2C+Norfolk%2C+VA+23508&amp;ll=36.885070,-76.294947" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4012 Colley Ave<br/>Norfolk, VA 23508</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Patrons flock to The Dirty Buffalo for the best wings south of Buffalo. Freshwings that have never been frozen are tossed with any of the unique creations from their huge catalog of sauces. Guy loved the Buffalo Soldier sauce so much that he said he wanted &quot;to use it as a stir fry sauce.&quot;

</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Spicy to Icy</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/norfolk/dirty-buffalo-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.29495,36.88507,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pendulum Fine Meats</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pendulum Fine Meats</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Norfolk, VA 23517</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7579626990" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">757-962-6990</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pendulummeats.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pendulummeats.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pendulum+Fine+Meats%2C+820+Shirley+Ave%2C+Norfolk%2C+VA+23517&amp;ll=36.868379,-76.298740" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">820 Shirley Ave<br/>Norfolk, VA 23517</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roast Beef Sandwich, Cuban Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and Owner Dylan Wakefield is serving up sandwiches at Pendulum Fine Meats that transport Guy back to his childhood. The slow-roasted beef is &quot;so thin, it only has one side,&quot; said Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwiches, Spaetzle and Sticky Wings</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/norfolk/pendulum-fine-meats-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.29874,36.86838,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Get Fresh Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Get Fresh Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Norfolk 23504</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7579666577" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(757) 966-6577</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/norfolk/get-fresh-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/norfolk/get-fresh-cafe-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Get+Fresh+Cafe%2C+2500+Church+St%2C+Norfolk+23504&amp;ll=36.869690,-76.279333" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2500 Church St<br/>Norfolk 23504</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meatloaf Mash</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Those looking for farm-to-table eats should head straight to Get Fresh Cafe. On Triple D, Guy swung by this charming spot situated inside the Norfolk, Va., Five Points Community Farm Market. As Guy said, everything from the meatloaf mash to the vegan sloppy Joe had unbeatable &quot;knock-out&quot; flavor.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gettin&#x27; Fresh</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/norfolk/get-fresh-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.27933,36.86969,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Alkaline</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Alkaline</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Norfolk 23517</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7573954300" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(757) 395-4300</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://alkalineramen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">alkalineramen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Alkaline%2C+742+W+21st+St.%2C+Norfolk+23517&amp;ll=36.870830,-76.295079" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">742 W 21st St.<br/>Norfolk 23517</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Asian Sticky Wings, Oxtail Ramen</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and Owner Kevin Ordonez is taking Asian street food to another level at Alkaline. His popular wings are lightly coated and then fried twice for optimal crunch. He then carefully brushes each one with a sweet and spicy sauce so they don&#x27;t lose their crispiness. The braised ox tail-topped ramen was so packed with different flavors and spices that Guy never wanted to dish to end.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwiches, Spaetzle and Sticky Wings</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/norfolk/alkaline-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.29508,36.87083,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Santo Taco</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Santo Taco</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salt Lake City 84116</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8018934000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(801) 893-4000</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.santotacos.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.santotacos.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Santo+Taco%2C+910+900+W%2C+Salt+Lake+City+84116&amp;ll=40.789012,-111.916183" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">910 900 W<br/>Salt Lake City 84116</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owners Claudia and Alfonso gained hands-on culinary experience working in restaurants and professional kitchens. When they opened their own establishment, they brought their knowledge of making traditional Mexican food, as well as the skills they developed within the food industry. In addition to a namesake taco, you can find burritos, quesadillas and nacho fries as Santo Taco.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos, Tots and Chops</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ut/salt-lake-city/santo-taco" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.91618,40.78901,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Doumar&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Doumar&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Norfolk 23517 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7576274163" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">757-627-4163</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.doumars.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.doumars.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Doumar%27s%2C+1919+Monticello+Ave%2C+Norfolk+23517&amp;ll=36.866164,-76.284848" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1919 Monticello Ave<br/>Norfolk 23517</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Waffle Cone, Strawberry Willy Sundae, Limeade, Orange Sherbet Freeze</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Doumar&#x27;s hasn&#x27;t just perfected the waffle cone - they also invented it. Home of the &#x27;&#x27;World&#x27;s First Cone Machine,&#x27;&#x27; this place has been a staple of Norfolk, Va., for over a century. When Guy visited here on Triple D, he was a fan of the Strawberry Willy sundae and Doumar&#x27;s signature limeade.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brain Freeze<br/>Triple D Nation: Diners, Drive-Ins and Delis</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/norfolk/doumars-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.28485,36.86616,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Metro 29 Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Metro 29 Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Arlington, VA 22207 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7035282464" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(703) 528-2464</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.metro29diner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.metro29diner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Metro+29+Diner%2C+4711+Lee+Hwy%2C+Arlington%2C+VA+22207&amp;ll=38.898077,-77.122904" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4711 Lee Hwy<br/>Arlington, VA 22207</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roasted Leg of Lamb with Gravy, Challah French Toast</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Metro 29 Diner is your traditional monster diner with a monster menu. Swing by for breakfast and chow down on the homemade challah bread French toast. On the weekends, remember to order the leg of lamb with potatoes. For Guy, &quot;the kicker&quot; is the savory, scratch-made gravy drizzled on top. &amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sweet &#x27;n Savory</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/va/arlington/metro-29-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.12290,38.89808,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Southern Kitchen Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Southern Kitchen Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tacoma, WA 98405 &middot; &#9733; 4.1 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2536274282" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(253) 627-4282</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.southernkitchen-tacoma.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.southernkitchen-tacoma.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Southern+Kitchen+Restaurant%2C+1716+6th+Ave%2C+Tacoma%2C+WA+98405&amp;ll=47.256133,-122.462394" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1716 6th Ave<br/>Tacoma, WA 98405</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cornbread Stuffing, Fried Chicken over Mac and Cheese, Hush Puppies, Battered Catfish, Grits</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nothing lifts the spirits like some good-old Southern comfort food cooking. Guy deemed the dense cornbread stuffing the star. Also memorable is the sweet, tender and moist fried chicken over mac and cheese. The hush puppies, battered catfish and grits are also popular.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Stacked Up<br/>Homestyle</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/tacoma/southern-kitchen-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.46239,47.25613,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Crown Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Crown Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tacoma, WA 98406 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2532724177" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(253) 272-4177</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.crownbartacoma.com/index.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.crownbartacoma.com/index.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Crown+Bar%2C+2705+6th+Ave%2C+Tacoma%2C+WA+98406&amp;ll=47.255572,-122.471719" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2705 6th Ave<br/>Tacoma, WA 98406</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Moroccan Beef Kabobs, Beet Salad</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The neighborhood knows to come to Crown Bar for fresh food that is &amp;quot;eclectic, but not ethnic.&amp;quot; Guy enjoyed the Moroccan beef kabobs with fluffy couscous, raita and pita. The robust, earthy flavors of the beet salad tossed with citrus vinaigrette and topped with fresh goat cheese also impressed him.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hittin&#x27; the Grill</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/tacoma/crown-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.47172,47.25557,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bruno&#x27;s European Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bruno&#x27;s European Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tacoma, WA 98444 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2537197181" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(253) 719-7181</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.brunoseuropeanrestaurant.com/2101.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.brunoseuropeanrestaurant.com/2101.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bruno%27s+European+Restaurant%2C+10716+A+St+S%2C+Tacoma%2C+WA+98444&amp;ll=47.159523,-122.431960" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">10716 A St S<br/>Tacoma, WA 98444</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hangover Soup, Bruno&#x27;s Schnitzel, Cabbage Rolls</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Polish Chef Bruno established this cozy cafe and brought with him his stick-to-your-ribs Polish recipes. Guy loved the tang from the pickle in the Hangover soup, consisting of sausage, potatoes, bacon and an assortment of vegetables. Customers also enjoy the cabbage rolls and Bruno&#x27;s Schnitzel.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eurocentric</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/tacoma/brunos-european-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.43196,47.15952,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dirty Oscar&#x27;s Annex</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dirty Oscar&#x27;s Annex</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tacoma, WA 98405 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2535720588" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(253) 572-0588</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.dirtyoscarsannex.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.dirtyoscarsannex.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dirty+Oscar%27s+Annex%2C+2309+Sixth+Ave%2C+Tacoma%2C+WA+98405&amp;ll=47.256096,-122.462978" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2309 Sixth Ave<br/>Tacoma, WA 98405</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tasso Tacos, Moonshine, Parmesan Tots</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Aaron Grissom is taking home-style dishes to the next level. The tasso tacos filled with both tender braised pork shoulder and Creole Cajun pork were great, according to Guy. Order the crispy and gooey Parmesan Tots with sun-dried tomato ranch as an appetizer, and to drink, try the moonshine.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos and Tots</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/tacoma/dirty-oscars-annex-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.46298,47.25610,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Elk Public House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Elk Public House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Spokane, WA 99201 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5093631973" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(509) 363-1973</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.wedonthaveone.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.wedonthaveone.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Elk+Public+House%2C+1931+W+Pacific+Ave%2C+Spokane%2C+WA+99201&amp;ll=47.655279,-117.441405" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1931 W Pacific Ave<br/>Spokane, WA 99201</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ Chicken Quesadilla, Reuben</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This 1930s-era pharmacy turned pub offers an eclectic spin on traditional pub grub. Reuben sandwiches are beer braised and served with housemade sauerkraut, and folks come from afar to get their BBQ Chicken Quesadilla fix, and &amp;quot;they&#x27;re making what you might be cranking out at home ,&amp;quot; but better!</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwiches Plus</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/spokane/elk-public-house-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.44141,47.65528,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nordic Smoke BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nordic Smoke BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Spokane, WA 99224 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.nordicsmokebbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.nordicsmokebbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nordic+Smoke+BBQ%2C+14908+S+Keeney+Rd%2C+Spokane%2C+WA+99224&amp;ll=47.518532,-117.416529" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">14908 S Keeney Rd<br/>Spokane, WA 99224</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brisket, Pork Spare Ribs, BBQ Beans</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nordic Smoke is a barbeque food truck that combines classic Southern &#x27;cue with a Norwegian twist. Brothers, Dusty and Casey, turned their father&#x27;s backyard hobby into a thriving business by investing in an old hickory smoker from Mississippi. Their brisket, a standout, is injected with beer butter and then smoked for 14 hours.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwiches, Southern and South of the Border</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/spokane/nordic-smoke-BBQ-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.41653,47.51853,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ruins</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ruins</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Spokane, WA 99201 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/spokane/ruins-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/spokane/ruins-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ruins%2C+825+N+Monroe+St%2C+Spokane%2C+WA+99201&amp;ll=47.665148,-117.426913" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">825 N Monroe St<br/>Spokane, WA 99201</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dirty Fries, Gnocchi</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ruins is Tony Brown&#x27;s own personal culinary Disneyland. The menu is constantly changing but seek out the Dirty Fries. Guy was enamored with the crispy shoestring potatoes tossed with house-made aioli, salsa verde and roasted pork shoulder. &quot;This is like something you have for your last meal,&quot; he remarked. And don&#x27;t miss the Parisian-style gnocchi, made with a pate a choux dough instead of potato and then crisped up and tossed with Gruyere and tarragon.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Pork to Pasta</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/spokane/ruins-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.42691,47.66515,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hills&#x27; Restaurant and Lounge</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hills&#x27; Restaurant and Lounge</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Spokane, WA 99201 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5097473946" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(509) 747-3946</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hillsrestaurantandlounge.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hillsrestaurantandlounge.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hills%27+Restaurant+and+Lounge%2C+401+W+Main+Ave%2C+Spokane%2C+WA+99201&amp;ll=47.658786,-117.418364" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">401 W Main Ave<br/>Spokane, WA 99201</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulled Pork Sandwich, Elk Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The roof at Hill&#x27;s Restaurant and Lounge also doubles as a garden and the menu, not surprisingly, represents true garden-to-fork dining. Guy said &amp;quot;step away from my pork&amp;quot; when eating the pulled pork sandwich. But the Elk Burger is out of bounds with its homemade beer mustard and rooftop herb blend.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Po&#x27; Boys, Pasta And Pork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/spokane/hills-restaurant-and-lounge-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.41836,47.65879,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Waddell&#x27;s Pub and Grille</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Waddell&#x27;s Pub and Grille</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Spokane, WA 99223 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5094436500" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(509) 443.6500</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.waddellspubandgrill.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.waddellspubandgrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Waddell%27s+Pub+and+Grille%2C+4318+S+Regal%2C+Spokane%2C+WA+99223&amp;ll=47.614437,-117.369356" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4318 S Regal<br/>Spokane, WA 99223</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rube Waddell Burger, Big Dog Burger, Beer-Braised Lamb Philly</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">With 50 beers on tap and many giant burgers to choose from, you&#x27;re sure to have a great meal at this neighborhood spot. The Rube Waddell Burger&#x27;s 6-ounce patty, corned beef and Swiss cheese excited Guy, as did the double-patty Big Dog Burger. The beer-braised lamb Philly was appreciated too.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Meat Lovers<br/>From Crepes to Kreplach</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/spokane/waddells-pub-and-grille-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.36936,47.61444,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Picabu Neighborhood Bistro</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Picabu Neighborhood Bistro</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Spokane, WA 99204 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5096242464" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(509) 624-2464</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.picabu-bistro.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.picabu-bistro.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Picabu+Neighborhood+Bistro%2C+901+W+14th+Ave%2C+Spokane%2C+WA+99204&amp;ll=47.642667,-117.424460" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">901 W 14th Ave<br/>Spokane, WA 99204</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cactus Burger, Chicken and Corn Pot Stickers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Picabu&#x27;s menu may be small but it has huge variety. Guy enjoyed the Cactus Burger topped with pepper Jack cheese, a hot and spicy pepper/onions/bacon mix, marinated onions and the signature hamburger goo. The chicken and corn pot stickers with homemade wrappers kept him coming back for more.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Quirky Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/spokane/picabu-neighborhood-bistro-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.42446,47.64267,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Crockett&#x27;s Public House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Crockett&#x27;s Public House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Puyallup, WA 98372 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2534663075" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(253) 466-3075</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://crockettspublichouse.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">crockettspublichouse.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Crockett%27s+Public+House%2C+118+E+Stewart+Ave%2C+Puyallup%2C+WA+98372&amp;ll=47.192775,-122.292740" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">118 E Stewart Ave<br/>Puyallup, WA 98372</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fire Grilled Artichokes, Mom&#x27;s Sloppy Joe, Public House Meatballs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This place was a feed store until owner Shaun Brobak turned it into a pub. For an appetizer, Guy had the &amp;quot;nice and tender&amp;quot; Fire Grilled Artichokes with Calabrian aioli. He also enjoyed Mom&#x27;s Sloppy Joe with crispy fried onions and the Public House Meatballs topped with pistachios and Parmesan.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wildest Joints<br/>Decadent Dishes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/puyallup/crocketts-public-house-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.29274,47.19277,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Chaps Coffee Co</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Chaps Coffee Co</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Spokane, WA 99224 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5096244182" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(509) 624-4182</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.chapsgirl.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.chapsgirl.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Chaps+Coffee+Co%2C+4235+S+Cheney-Spokane+Rd%2C+Spokane%2C+WA+99224&amp;ll=47.615168,-117.428908" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4235 S Cheney-Spokane Rd<br/>Spokane, WA 99224</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">French Toast, Baked Oatmeal, Mushroom and Brie Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Re-creating foods from growing up on a farm led to the opening of Chaps Coffee Co., where Grandma&#x27;s influences reign. A farmhouse twist on French toast is pretty close to a blueberry muffin cake topped with blueberry cream cheese. Try Grandma&#x27;s baked oatmeal to satisfy that homemade craving.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fresh, Filled and Fried</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/spokane/chaps-coffee-co-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.42891,47.61517,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bobby&#x27;s Hawaiian Style Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bobby&#x27;s Hawaiian Style Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lynnwood, WA 98087 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4252591338" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(425) 259-1338</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bobbyshawaiianstylerestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bobbyshawaiianstylerestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bobby%27s+Hawaiian+Style+Restaurant%2C+14626+Hwy%2C+Lynnwood%2C+WA+98087&amp;ll=47.865478,-122.281439" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">14626 Hwy<br/>Lynnwood, WA 98087</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lomi Lomi Salmon, Kalua Pork, Lau Lau</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bobby&#x27;s Hawaiian Style may be miles away from Hawaii, but owner Bobby Nakihei stayed true to his culinary roots. Guy loved his style. Bobby&#x27;s making all the classics, like Kalua pork, Lau Lau (a pork dish wrapped in taro leaves and steamed) and the beloved Spam musubi, spam prepared sushi-style.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Around the World<br/>Viewer&#x27;s Choice<br/>Triple-D Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/everett/bobbys-hawaiian-style-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.28144,47.86548,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Madison Diner (Formerly Big Star Diner)</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Madison Diner (Formerly Big Star Diner)</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bainbridge Island, WA 98110</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2068425786" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(206) 842-5786</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/bainbridge-island/big-star-diner-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/bainbridge-island/big-star-diner-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Madison+Diner+%28Formerly+Big+Star+Diner%29%2C+305+Madison+Ave.+N.%2C+Bainbridge+Island%2C+WA+98110&amp;ll=47.626783,-122.521582" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305 Madison Ave. N.<br/>Bainbridge Island, WA 98110</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Atlantic Salmon Hash, Chorizo Scramble, Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Join Guy Fieri, host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, as he treks out to The Madison Diner, on Bainbridge Island, WA, for some casual comfort food.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Worth the Trip</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/bainbridge-island/big-star-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.52158,47.62678,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sisters and Brothers Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sisters and Brothers Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Seattle, WA 98108 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2067623767" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(206) 762-3767</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sistersandbrothersbar.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sistersandbrothersbar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sisters+and+Brothers+Bar%2C+1128+S+Albro+Pl%2C+Seattle%2C+WA+98108&amp;ll=47.545972,-122.317359" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1128 S Albro Pl<br/>Seattle, WA 98108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nashville Hot Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This knockout joint brings Nashville hot chicken to Seattle. Dig into wings, tenders, white/dark meat or a half bird with your prefered level of spice (&quot;lil bit&quot; to &quot;insane&quot;). The restaurant also has a selection of Southern favorites, such as chicken and waffles, homemade biscuits and gravy, fried green tomatoes and more.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fusion of Flavors</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/wa/seattle/sisters-and-brothers-bar" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.31736,47.54597,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Maple &amp; Motor</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Maple &amp; Motor</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Dallas, TX 75219 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2145224400" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(214) 522-4400</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://mapleandmotor.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">mapleandmotor.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Maple+%26+Motor%2C+4810+Maple+Ave%2C+Dallas%2C+TX+75219&amp;ll=32.815194,-96.827055" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4810 Maple Ave<br/>Dallas, TX 75219</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owner Jack Perkins is grilling only burgers at his dive, and he is making over 600 a day. The half-pound burger with lettuce, bacon, cheese and jalapenos tantalized Guy&#x27;s taste buds. Loyal customers enjoy customizing their burgers by adding an extra patty, chili, grilled onions and a fried egg.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grilling Greats<br/>Streamlined Sammies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/dallas/maple-motor-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.82705,32.81519,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Louie&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Louie&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Dallas, TX 75206</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2148260505" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">214-826-0505</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/dallas/louies-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/dallas/louies-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Louie%27s%2C+1839+N+Henderson+Ave%2C+Dallas%2C+TX+75206&amp;ll=32.811096,-96.774525" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1839 N Henderson Ave<br/>Dallas, TX 75206</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Don Burger, Waukegan-style Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Drop by Louie&#x27;s to sample the Don, a burger that Guy says is &amp;quot;super-mondo juicy.&amp;quot; The fresh-ground Angus patty is basted with a soy-and-garlic-laced secret sauce, layered with Swiss cheese, bacon and jalapeno, then nestled between slices of rye bread. Also try the thin-crust pizza slathered with crushed tomato sauce and topped with Angus beef-and-pork butt sausage, Wisconsin cheese, onions and green peppers.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Favorites<br/>Pizza Party</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/dallas/louies-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.77452,32.81110,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Weights and Measures</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Weights and Measures</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Houston, TX 77004</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7136541970" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(713) 654-1970</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.weights-measures.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.weights-measures.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Weights+and+Measures%2C+2808+Caroline+St.%2C+Houston%2C+TX+77004&amp;ll=29.742428,-95.373051" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2808 Caroline St.<br/>Houston, TX 77004</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Housed in a repurposed warehouse and the brainchild of four partners: a developer, a chef, a baker and a bartender; Weights + Measures is a casual restaurant, bakery and bar serving comfort food in a relaxed space.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cookin&#x27; from Scratch</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/weights-and-measures" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.37305,29.74243,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>T-Bone Tom&#x27;s Steakhouse</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">T-Bone Tom&#x27;s Steakhouse</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kemah, TX 77565 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2813342133" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(281) 334-2133</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tbonetoms.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tbonetoms.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=T-Bone+Tom%27s+Steakhouse%2C+707+Highway+146%2C+Kemah%2C+TX+77565&amp;ll=29.541789,-95.019817" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">707 Highway 146<br/>Kemah, TX 77565</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Steak, T-Bone Tom&#x27;s Choice Steak Marinade</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy Fieri, host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, goes full throttle at T-Bone Tom&#x27;s Steakhouse in Kemah, TX, a meat market turned restaurant, grilling up great house-cut steaks.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meaty Masterpieces<br/>Burgers, Steaks and Chops</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/kemah/t-bone-toms-steakhouse-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.01982,29.54179,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Niko Nikos</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Niko Nikos</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Houston 77006 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7135284976" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(713) 528-4976</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.nikonikos.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.nikonikos.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Niko+Nikos%2C+2520+Montrose+Blvd%2C+Houston+77006&amp;ll=29.746473,-95.392149" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2520 Montrose Blvd<br/>Houston 77006</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Moussaka, Gyros, Guy&#x27;s Honey Ballz: Loukomades</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Niko Niko&#x27;s, Guy calls the flavor-packed leg of lamb with potatoes &quot;one of the most lemon-forward lamb shanks&quot; he&#x27;s ever had. Other favorite dishes include the classic moussaka and hearty gyros. Be sure to try the pita bread, as this little joint&#x27;s cranking out 12,000 pitas a day.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You Can Say That Again<br/>Legends of Texas<br/>Takeout: Bringing Comfort Home</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/niko-nikos-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.39215,29.74647,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Irma&#x27;s Original</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Irma&#x27;s Original</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Houston, TX 77002 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7135889891" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">713-588-9891</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://irmasoriginal.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">irmasoriginal.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Irma%27s+Original%2C+22+N+Chenevert+St%2C+Houston%2C+TX+77002&amp;ll=29.760203,-95.351999" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">22 N Chenevert St<br/>Houston, TX 77002</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tamales, Chile Rellenos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This long-time Houston spot serves &quot;real-deal Mexican food,&quot; according to Guy, who tucked into the tamales and chiles rellenos made from owner Irma Galvan&#x27;s family recipes. &quot;Light, fluffy (and) super flavorful,&quot; Guy said after taking a bite of the tamales, which come stuffed with succulent morsels of pork smothered in cascabel chile sauce. The chiles rellenos also left him impressed. Galvan makes them the old-fashioned way, which means the poblano peppers come stuffed with a ground meat filling known as picadillo. After they&#x27;re stuffed, the peppers are dipped in an airy batter, then fried until a fluffy, crisp coating forms.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wonder Women</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/irmas-original-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.35200,29.76020,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fresco Cafe Italiano</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fresco Cafe Italiano</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Houston 77027</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2818882226" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(281) 888-2226</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.frescocafeitaliano.co" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.frescocafeitaliano.co</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fresco+Cafe+Italiano%2C+3277+Southwest+Fwy%2C+Houston+77027&amp;ll=29.729018,-95.430695" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3277 Southwest Fwy<br/>Houston 77027</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Roberto Crescini trained in Italy, honing his culinary skills for decades before bringing them to Houston to serve a variety of made-to-order meals, including classic dishes like bolognese, lamb, pasta and pizza. At Fresco Cafe Italiano, patrons can expect authentic, fresh Italian dishes made in-house with ingredients imported from Italy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cookin&#x27; from Scratch</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/fresco-cafe-italiano" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.43070,29.72902,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cuchara Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cuchara Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Houston, TX 77006 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7139420000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">713-942-0000</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://cuchararestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">cuchararestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cuchara+Restaurant%2C+214+Fairview+St%2C+Houston%2C+TX+77006&amp;ll=29.748318,-95.385055" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">214 Fairview St<br/>Houston, TX 77006</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos Crujientes de Jamaica, Tacos Chelo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy wasn&#x27;t prepared for the depth of authenticity he would experience at Cuchara. The real-deal Mexican flavors and attention to detail permeated every dish. He raved about the four-color handmade tortillas and the tacos chelo, potato-stuffed tacos topped with tangy green salsa, calling them &quot;one of the top 10 tacos&quot; he has ever had. He left calling it &quot;an outrageous experience.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Multicultural Cooking</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/cuchara-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.38506,29.74832,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Be More Specific</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Be More Specific</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Houston, TX 77007</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8325825264" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(832) 582-5264</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.bemorepacifickitchenandbar.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bemorepacifickitchenandbar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Be+More+Specific%2C+506+Yale+Street%2C+Houston%2C+TX+77007&amp;ll=29.780182,-95.398371" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">506 Yale Street<br/>Houston, TX 77007</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Be More Pacific is all about Filipino tradition: their variety of dishes have been passed down through generations and infused with each chef&#x27;s personaltouch. Be More Pacific celebrates other aspects of Filipino culture, including hosting karaoke, a kamayan eating experience and a monthly Filipino-owned market.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Domestic &amp; Abroad</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/be-more-pacific" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.39837,29.78018,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Kenny &amp; Ziggy&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Kenny &amp; Ziggy&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Houston 77056 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7138718883" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">713-871-8883</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.kennyandziggys.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.kennyandziggys.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Kenny+%26+Ziggy%27s%2C+2327+Post+Oak+Blvd%2C+Houston+77056&amp;ll=29.743227,-95.460012" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2327 Post Oak Blvd<br/>Houston 77056</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Corned Beef Sandwich, Fried Kreplach, Ziggy&#x27;s Kasha Varnishkas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you&#x27;re looking for a great sandwich, swing by Kenny &amp; Ziggy&#x27;s, the New York-style deli that&#x27;s making all the classics. You&#x27;ll find Yiddish favorites such as Mishmosh soup and 10-ounce pastrami sandwiches, plus the eight-decker mother of all deli sandwiches called The Zellagabetsky.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Comin&#x27; from All Over the Map<br/>You Picked &#x27;Em</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/kenny-ziggys-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.46001,29.74323,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Monument Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Monument Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Georgetown, TX 78627 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5128685932" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(512) 868-5932</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.themonumentcafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.themonumentcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Monument+Cafe%2C+500+S+Austin+Ave%2C+Georgetown%2C+TX+78627&amp;ll=30.638755,-97.678491" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">500 S Austin Ave<br/>Georgetown, TX 78627</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">King Ranch Chicken Casserole, Pig &#x27;n Waffle</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Matthew McConaughey brought Guy to his favorite cafe that grows its own produce. Guy and Matthew downed the hearty portion of King Ranch chicken casserole and loved its creamy texture. The contrasting flavors of the maple syrup and savory ham thrilled Guy as well in the Pig &#x27;n Waffle.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D All Stars<br/>Legends of Texas</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/georgetown/monument-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.67849,30.63875,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cafe Pita</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cafe Pita</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Houston, TX 77042 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7139537237" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(713) 953-7237</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://cafepita.weebly.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">cafepita.weebly.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cafe+Pita%2C+10890+Westheimer%2C+Houston%2C+TX+77042&amp;ll=29.736896,-95.568051" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">10890 Westheimer<br/>Houston, TX 77042</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Cheese, Fried Anchovies, Lamb Shank, Sarma, Cevap, Spinach Burek</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Guy Fieri, finds Cafe Pita in Houston, TX, a joint in a strip mall where a couple of guys from Bosnia are serving up mom-inspired classics.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Style</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/cafe-pita-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.56805,29.73690,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fred&#x27;s Texas Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fred&#x27;s Texas Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fort Worth, TX 76107 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8173320083" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">817-332-0083</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.fredstexascafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fredstexascafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fred%27s+Texas+Cafe%2C+915+Currie+St%2C+Fort+Worth%2C+TX+76107&amp;ll=32.749593,-97.358181" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">915 Currie St<br/>Fort Worth, TX 76107</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Stew, Steak with Chipotle Brown Butter, Cheeseburger, Holy Cristo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this all-American diner, chef Terry Chandler is serving up classics with a Southwestern spin. Guy could barely take the heat from the seasonal New Mexico green chile and lamb stew. The steak with chipotle brown butter was memorable for its &amp;quot;big flavor.&amp;quot; Locals enjoy ordering the cheeseburger.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/fort-worth/freds-texas-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.35818,32.74959,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lick It Up</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lick It Up</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">El Paso, TX 79902 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9153733558" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">915-373-3558</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/el-paso/lick-it-up-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/el-paso/lick-it-up-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lick+It+Up%2C+204+E.+Rio+Grande+Ave%2C+El+Paso%2C+TX+79902&amp;ll=31.764658,-106.492076" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">204 E. Rio Grande Ave<br/>El Paso, TX 79902</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Vegan Milanese Torta, Flautas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When owner Edgar Delfin had trouble finding great-tasting vegan options in Texas, he created his own. Everything on the menu of this taco truck is 100% plant-based. Guy loved theMilanese Torta:Delfin makes his own seitan steak-a plant protein made from wheat gluten-which he then coats in panko and deep fries. The sandwich comes together on torta bread by stacking a layer of black beans, the fried seitan patty, cabbage and fresh tomatoes, and is topped with avocado crema and vegan mayo. Even as a meat lover, Guy was impressed: &quot;You get such great texture in that seitan,&quot; he said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spinning the Globe</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/el-paso/lick-it-up-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-106.49208,31.76466,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rulis&#x27; International Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rulis&#x27; International Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">El Paso, TX 79902</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.rulisik.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rulisik.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rulis%27+International+Kitchen%2C+4176+N.+Mesa+St%2C+El+Paso%2C+TX+79902&amp;ll=31.793948,-106.509921" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4176 N. Mesa St<br/>El Paso, TX 79902</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pasta Chihuahua, Oxtail Tostadas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You&#x27;ve never tasted fusion like this before: this El Paso joint serves dishes made with flavors from around the world, like their Oxtail Tostadas and Pasta Chihuahua. &quot;I think you made yourself a dish that is a one of a kind,&quot; Guy said when he tasted the pasta, which is a Mexican take on a Bolognese. To make the dish, they mix a chorizo meat sauce and grilled steak with pasta and top with cotija cheese and fresh cilantro.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Australian to Asian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/el-paso/rulis-international-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-106.50992,31.79395,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>La Colonial Tortilla Factory</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">La Colonial Tortilla Factory</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">El Paso, TX 79905</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9155339691" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(915) 533-9691</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/el-paso/la-colonial-tortilla-factory-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/el-paso/la-colonial-tortilla-factory-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=La+Colonial+Tortilla+Factory%2C+212+N+Copia+St%2C+El+Paso%2C+TX+79905&amp;ll=31.770104,-106.451100" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">212 N Copia St<br/>El Paso, TX 79905</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Picadillo Tostada, Tamales</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Only a few miles from the Mexico border sits this family-run tortilla factory that&#x27;s been churning out fresh corn tortillas since 1973. Most of the tortillas they make-up to 1,000 per day-are sold to other local restaurants, but they also serve fresh Mexican dishes in house as well, like the Picadillo Tostada. Ground beef is cooked with tomatoes, jalapenos, green beans and a mix of spices before it&#x27;s added to a crisp tortilla along with beans and a house-made chile con queso. The tostada is then topped with cheese and fresh lettuce for an added crunch.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Far-Flung Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/el-paso/la-colonial-tortilla-factory-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-106.45110,31.77010,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Kaedama</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Kaedama</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">El Paso 79902</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/el-paso/kaedama-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/el-paso/kaedama-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Kaedama%2C+204+Boston+Avenue%2C+El+Paso+79902&amp;ll=31.775532,-106.501653" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">204 Boston Avenue<br/>El Paso 79902</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tokotsu</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After Guy and the team got done eating for the first time at this El Paso ramen joint, Guy knew he had to feature it on DDD. Owners Andres Romero and Gabe Valencia are dishing out a wide variety of authentic ramen and other Japanese dishes, but the must-have for first timers is the Tonkotsu.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: From Near to Far</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/el-paso/kaedama-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-106.50165,31.77553,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Red Lion Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Red Lion Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Houston, TX 77019 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7135298390" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(713) 529-8390</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.redlionhouston.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.redlionhouston.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Red+Lion+Pub%2C+2316+S+Shepherd+Dr%2C+Houston%2C+TX+77019&amp;ll=29.745606,-95.410976" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2316 S Shepherd Dr<br/>Houston, TX 77019</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Shepherd&#x27;s Pie, Chicken Tikka Masala</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Red Lion owner Craig Mallinson says true English pubs should serve the long-ignored U.K. staple: Indian food. As Guy learned, Red Lion caters to both cuisines. Try the tasty chicken tikka masala; if you&#x27;re still craving the British classics, the lamb shepherd&#x27;s pie is a perfect dish for a cold day.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">By Request<br/>Legends of Texas</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/red-lion-pub-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.41098,29.74561,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lankford Grocery and Market</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lankford Grocery and Market</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Houston, TX 77006 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7135229555" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(713) 522-9555</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/lankford-grocery-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/lankford-grocery-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lankford+Grocery+and+Market%2C+88+Dennis+St%2C+Houston%2C+TX+77006&amp;ll=29.750037,-95.383880" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">88 Dennis St<br/>Houston, TX 77006</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Texas Chicken Hash</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you&#x27;re interested in &quot;licking the volcano out of Flavortown,&quot; Guy recommends ordering Lankford&#x27;s Firehouse Burger basted with cayenne butter and loaded with hot-sauce mustard. Also check out their 12 bold burger specialties and daily lunch specials like the Chicken Fried Steak and Texas Hash.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Tacos and Dogs<br/>All-American All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/lankford-grocery-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.38388,29.75004,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Pit Room</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Pit Room</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Houston, TX 77006 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2818881929" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(281) 888.1929</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.thepitroombbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thepitroombbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Pit+Room%2C+1201+Richmond+Ave.%2C+Houston%2C+TX+77006&amp;ll=29.734192,-95.394204" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1201 Richmond Ave.<br/>Houston, TX 77006</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Michael Sambrooks andBramwell Tripp put their shared passion for delicious food and years of culinary experience together to create The Pit Room. Their dishes feature homemade recipes, created and smoked from scratch. In addition to barbeque, the pair serve up (breakfast) tacos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meat and Heat</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/the-pit-room" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.39420,29.73419,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Traveler&#x27;s Table</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Traveler&#x27;s Table</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Houston 77006</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8324095785" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(832) 409-5785</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.travelerstable.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.travelerstable.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Traveler%27s+Table%2C+520+Westheimer+Rd%2C+Houston+77006&amp;ll=29.744612,-95.387646" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">520 Westheimer Rd<br/>Houston 77006</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Traveler&#x27;s Table believes that food connects people and creates a point of connectivity, and as such, they are inspired by food and drink from around the world. On their menu, you&#x27;ll find dishes inspired by Vietnamese, Caribbean and Hawaiin cuisine, to name a few.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mouthwatering Meat</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/traveler-s-table" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.38765,29.74461,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Toasted Coconut</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Toasted Coconut</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Houston, TX 77006 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7134854775" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(713) 485-4775</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.gettoastedhtx.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.gettoastedhtx.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Toasted+Coconut%2C+1617+Richmond+Ave.%2C+Houston%2C+TX+77006&amp;ll=29.734102,-95.400276" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1617 Richmond Ave.<br/>Houston, TX 77006</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Inspired by island cuisine, Martin and Sara Stayer created The Toasted Coconut for a stay-cation culinary experience. The brunch and dinner menu feature tropical takes on curries, sandwiches and fish dishes.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Regional Flavors</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/houston/the-toasted-coconut" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.40028,29.73410,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nora Restaurant and Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nora Restaurant and Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Dallas, TX 75206 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2148280095" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">214-828-0095</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.noradallas.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.noradallas.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nora+Restaurant+and+Bar%2C+1928+Greenville+Ave%2C+Dallas%2C+TX+75206&amp;ll=32.813526,-96.770105" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1928 Greenville Ave<br/>Dallas, TX 75206</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Shank with Qabili Palao, Kofta Chalao</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Matt Pikar&#x27;s restaurant is the first Afghan place Guy has visited on DDD. The cuisine is redolent of spices like turmeric, cardamom and saffron. Guy loved the tender lamb shanks served over fragrant basmati rice and topped with raisins, carrots, pistachios and slivered almonds. The Kofta Chalao, Afghan meatballs, were another feast of spice and flavor.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Delicious Discoveries</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/dallas/nora-restaurant-and-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.77011,32.81353,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>One90 Smoked Meats</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">One90 Smoked Meats</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Dallas, TX 75238</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2143463287" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">214-346-3287</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://one90smokedmeats.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">one90smokedmeats.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=One90+Smoked+Meats%2C+10240+E.+Northwest+Highway%2C+Dallas%2C+TX+75238&amp;ll=32.863861,-96.709381" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">10240 E. Northwest Highway<br/>Dallas, TX 75238</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spicy Brisket Sandwich, D.L.T</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s been to more BBQ joints than most people so when one impresses him it&#x27;s worth trying. Chef and Owner Kyle St. Clair&#x27;s brisket was so tender that Guy remarked, &quot;You don&#x27;t even need a knife; you can cut that with a bad look.&quot; Have it on the Spicy Brisket Sandwich which is layered on a brioche bun with a roasted poblano, in-house smoked cheddar, pickles and red onion.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bird and Beef</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/dallas/one90-smoked-meats-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.70938,32.86386,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Soy Bistro</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Soy Bistro</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Brentwood, TN 37027 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6153711933" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 371-1933</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.soybistro.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.soybistro.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Soy+Bistro%2C+5008+Maryland+Way%2C+Brentwood%2C+TN+37027&amp;ll=36.033545,-86.788988" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5008 Maryland Way<br/>Brentwood, TN 37027</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A family-owned and operated restaurant that serves Korean cuisine; their house favorites are Bibimbap, Gochujang Chicken and Spicy Pork Bulgogi.Kenji Ichikawa, patron-turned-(co)owner, says he loves the level of attention Soy Bistro gives to their cuisine and to their customers, pledging to uphold the standard.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meat and Heat</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/soy-bistro" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.78899,36.03354,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Texas Pride BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Texas Pride BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Adkins, TX 78101 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2106493730" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(210) 649-3730</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.texaspridebbq.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.texaspridebbq.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Texas+Pride+BBQ%2C+2980+E+Loop+1604+S%2C+Adkins%2C+TX+78101&amp;ll=29.393334,-98.238197" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2980 E Loop 1604 S<br/>Adkins, TX 78101</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Brisket, Baked Beans, Pulled Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Barbecue joints aren&#x27;t hard to find in Texas, but San Antonio locals are still willing to drive 20 miles to Adkins to check out Texas Pride Barbecue. Guy recommends their #1 selling smoked brisket, which is made even better with a side of baked beans.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of BBQ</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/adkins/texas-pride-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.23820,29.39333,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cane Rosso</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cane Rosso</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Dallas, TX 75226 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2147411188" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">214-741-1188</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.canerosso.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.canerosso.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cane+Rosso%2C+2612+Commerce+St%2C+Dallas%2C+TX+75226&amp;ll=32.782467,-96.785493" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2612 Commerce St<br/>Dallas, TX 75226</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Delia Pie, Pasta Amatriciana, The Honey Bastard Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Jay Jerrier ditched the tech industry and followed his dream to make crazy Neapolitan pizzas like the Delia pie, topped with bacon marmalade, roasted grape tomatoes and arugula, that left Guy speechless. Cane Rosso&#x27;s most popular pie is The Honey Bastard, which is not even on the menu. This spicy-sweet pie includes mozzarella, hot soppressata, bacon marmalade and habanero-infused honey.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big Time Flavor<br/>Legends of Texas<br/>Triple D Nation: Italian, Thai and Pie</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/dallas/cane-rosso-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.78549,32.78247,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pepe&#x27;s and Mito&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pepe&#x27;s and Mito&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Dallas, TX 75226 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2147411901" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(214) 741-1901</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pepesandmitos.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pepesandmitos.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pepe%27s+and+Mito%27s%2C+2911+Elm+St%2C+Dallas%2C+TX+75226&amp;ll=32.785228,-96.781974" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2911 Elm St<br/>Dallas, TX 75226</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef Enchiladas, Beef Tacos Nortenos, Caldo Albondigas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this dive, Chef Pedro Rojos is switching things up and serving some dynamite Mex-Tex dishes. The caldo albondigas --- a Mexican meatball soup --- was &quot;outstanding,&quot; according to Guy. The beef tacos nortenos had an excellent char that also impressed him. Try ordering the beef enchiladas too.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Outside the Box<br/>Triple D Nation: Meat Mashup</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/dallas/pepe-and-mitos-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.78197,32.78523,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pecan Lodge</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pecan Lodge</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Dallas, TX 75226 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2147488900" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(214) 748-8900</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pecanlodge.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pecanlodge.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pecan+Lodge%2C+2702+Main+St%2C+Dallas%2C+TX+75226&amp;ll=32.783598,-96.783875" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2702 Main St<br/>Dallas, TX 75226</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brisket, BBQ Pulled Pork Sandwich, The &quot;Hot Mess&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For real deal barbecue, head to this popular spot. Guy adored the smoky brisket and he couldn&#x27;t get enough of the slow-smoked pork sandwich. In addition to the &#x27;cue classics of brisket, ribs and pulled pork, the restaurant is renowned for its mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese and Aunt Polly&#x27;s banana pudding.&amp;nbsp;Locals love the Hot Mess, a sweet potato stuffed with barbacoa, cheese, chipotle cream and butter.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big-Time Barbecue<br/>BBQ Road Show</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/dallas/pecan-lodge-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.78388,32.78360,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Martin&#x27;s Bar-B-Que Joint</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Martin&#x27;s Bar-B-Que Joint</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nolensville 37135 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6157761865" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">615-776-1865</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.martinsbbqjoint.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.martinsbbqjoint.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Martin%27s+Bar-B-Que+Joint%2C+7238+Nolensville+Rd%2C+Nolensville+37135&amp;ll=35.960974,-86.672336" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7238 Nolensville Rd<br/>Nolensville 37135</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Whole Hog Platter, BBQ Sandwiches, Broccoli Salad, Hushpuppies, Redneck Taco</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Martin&#x27;s Bar-B-Que Joint, to go &quot;whole hog&quot; literally means roasting a 200-pound hog in its entirety. The meat is hit with a signature blend of spices, then cooked over hickory wood for 24 hours, which Michael Symon said results in &quot;the perfect bite of pork.&quot; Michael&#x27;s favorite order is the whole hog platter accompanied by sides such as the bacon-studded broccoli salad and onion-flecked hushpuppies. The succulent meat also serves as the filling for the sliders, which made Guy Fieri a fan. He called the pork &quot;beyond juicy and moist and flavorful.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Wings &#x27;n&#x27; Things<br/>Porkapalooza<br/>BBQ Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/nolensville/martins-bar-b-que-joint-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.67234,35.96097,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>55 South</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">55 South</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Franklin 37064 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6155386001" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 538-6001</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://eat55.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">eat55.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=55+South%2C+403+Main+St%2C+Franklin+37064&amp;ll=35.924276,-86.870305" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">403 Main St<br/>Franklin 37064</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nashville Hot Chicken, Chicken and Sausage Jambalaya, Char Grilled Oysters</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">55 South serves up traditional Southern dishes like the Nashville Hot Chicken and the Chicken and Sausage Jambalaya. But the fresh seafood served here is also a major highlight. Guy loves the &quot;wood smoke component&quot; of the char-grilled oysters topped with garlic-lemon butter and Parmesan.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Small Town Sensations<br/>Soup, Salad and Seafood</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/franklin/55-south" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.87031,35.92428,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Phat Bites</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Phat Bites</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Donelson 37214 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6158714055" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 871-4055</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.phatbites.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.phatbites.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Phat+Bites%2C+2730+b.+Lebanon+Pike%2C+Donelson+37214&amp;ll=36.168907,-86.665669" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2730 b. Lebanon Pike<br/>Donelson 37214</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Long Life Salad</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy loves Phat Bites&#x27; Long Life Salad served on a bed of kale with black-eyed peas, Christmas lima beans, black beans, split lentils, red quinoa, pecans, dried cranberries, gold raisins, plums, mangoes and a citrus vinaigrette. Prefer a sandwich? Try the Big Jerk with jerk pork, cheese and onions.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Soup, Salad and Seafood</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/donelson/phat-bites" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.66567,36.16891,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Avila&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Avila&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Dallas, TX 75219 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2145202700" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(214) 520-2700</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.avilasrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.avilasrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Avila%27s%2C+4714+Maple+Ave%2C+Dallas%2C+TX+75219&amp;ll=32.814245,-96.825427" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4714 Maple Ave<br/>Dallas, TX 75219</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brisket Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Avila reflects founders Anita and Octavio Avila&#x27;s Mexican and Texan roots. The menu features specialties like chile relleno, pollo con calabaza -- a Mexican chicken stew with squash and corn -- sauteed pork in cascabel pepper sauce and, of course, the brisket tacos that Guy raved about on Triple D.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mama&#x27;s Cookin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/dallas/avilas-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.82543,32.81424,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Counter Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Counter Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Austin, TX 78703 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5127088800" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(512) 708-8800</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.countercafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.countercafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Counter+Cafe%2C+626+N+Lamar+Blvd%2C+Austin%2C+TX+78703&amp;ll=30.272585,-97.753718" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">626 N Lamar Blvd<br/>Austin, TX 78703</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Curry Chicken Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A cozy, comfortable diner, Counter Cafe specializes in comfort food like pancakes, burgers and biscuits and gravy. In addition to the classics, the 26-seat eatery offers up scratch-made Curry Chicken Burgers that Guy calls &quot;juicy as can be&quot; and a one-of-a-kind breakfast combo of quail and eggs.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big Time Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/austin/counter-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.75372,30.27258,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Casino El Camino</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Casino El Camino</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Austin, TX 78701 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (14 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5124699330" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">512-469-9330</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.casinoelcamino.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.casinoelcamino.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Casino+El+Camino%2C+517+E+6th+St.%2C+Austin%2C+TX+78701&amp;ll=30.266406,-97.737690" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">517 E 6th St.<br/>Austin, TX 78701</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Serrano Pepper and Hot Buffalo Sauce Burgers, Amarillo Burger, Hot Dogs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy Fieri calls late night spot Casino El Camino home to &amp;quot;the best burger in town.&amp;quot; Juicy and tender, the 12-ounce monsters come topped with everything from cheese and thick-cut bacon to roasted Serrano peppers and Texas-hot buffalo sauce. For a spicy side, pair your burger with Verde Chili Fries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers and Dogs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/austin/casino-el-camino-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.73769,30.26641,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Center Point Pit Barbecue</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Center Point Pit Barbecue</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hendersonville 37075 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6158249330" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 824-9330</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.centerpointbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.centerpointbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Center+Point+Pit+Barbecue%2C+1212+W+Main+St%2C+Hendersonville+37075&amp;ll=36.309645,-86.666561" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1212 W Main St<br/>Hendersonville 37075</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Holiday Ham (Sugar-Glazed Smoked Ham)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Center Point Pit Barbecue, owner Robert Duke smokes his pork until in turns &quot;black as night.&quot; But as Guy learned on DDD, the holiday ham is unlike any other. After a four-day brine and a six-hour smoke, the ham is sprinkled with sugar and torched, resulting in a delicious &quot;ham brittle,&quot; Guy says.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Holiday Hoopla<br/>Tennessee Holiday Traditions</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/hendersonville/center-point-pit-barbecue-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.66656,36.30964,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cafe Rakka</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cafe Rakka</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hendersonville 37075 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6158246264" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">615-824-6264</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://caferakka.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">caferakka.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cafe+Rakka%2C+71A+New+Shackle+Island+Rd.%2C+Hendersonville+37075&amp;ll=36.305800,-86.634923" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">71A New Shackle Island Rd.<br/>Hendersonville 37075</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Rakka, Hummus, Baba Ghanoush, Falafel and Tabbouleh</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cafe Rakka is no ordinary restaurant. Rather, it&#x27;s a &quot;Nashville-Mediterranean-Indian experience in Music City,&quot; according to Guy, where you&#x27;ll find country music legends among the regulars. Try the filet mignon kebabs, cooked on a sizzling Himalayan salt block, for a flavor-packed meal.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sauced and Spiced</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/hendersonville/cafe-rakka-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.63492,36.30580,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>South of Beale (SOB)</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">South of Beale (SOB)</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Memphis, TN 38103 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9015260388" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(901) 526-0388</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.southofbeale.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.southofbeale.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=South+of+Beale+%28SOB%29%2C+361+S+Main+St%2C+Memphis%2C+TN+38103&amp;ll=35.136619,-90.057771" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">361 S Main St<br/>Memphis, TN 38103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Duck Fried Rice, Jack and Coke Bread Pudding</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The food at this gastropub is cheap and in some cases free, but it all tastes great. One of the signature dishes is the duck fried rice, which Guy was crazy about and it costs only $5. Guy also liked the free and addictive house seasoned popcorn. Try the Jack and Coke bread pudding too.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Flavortown Medley</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/memphis/south-of-beale-sob-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.05777,35.13662,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Uncle Lou&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Uncle Lou&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Memphis 38116 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9013322367" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(901) 332-2367</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://unclelousfriedchicken.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">unclelousfriedchicken.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Uncle+Lou%27s%2C+3633+Millbranch+Rd%2C+Memphis+38116&amp;ll=35.049512,-90.007937" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3633 Millbranch Rd<br/>Memphis 38116</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Chicken, Monster Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The saying goes that if Colonel Sanders had Uncle Lou&#x27;s fried chicken recipe, he&#x27;d be a general. On The Best Thing I Ever Ate, Guy loved Lou&#x27;s &quot;crazy&quot; fried chicken that&#x27;s dipped into a sauce once called &quot;Corruption.&quot; Now, thanks to Guy, it has been rechristened Sweet Spicy Love.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crazy for Chicken<br/>Where the Locals Eat<br/>Takeout: Bringing Comfort Home</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/memphis/uncle-lous-southern-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.00794,35.04951,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rizzo&#x27;s Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rizzo&#x27;s Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Memphis, TN 38103 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9015232033" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(901) 523-2033</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rizzosdiner.com/#" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rizzosdiner.com/#</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rizzo%27s+Diner%2C+106+E+GE+Patterson+Ave%2C+Memphis%2C+TN+38103&amp;ll=35.132942,-90.058633" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">106 E GE Patterson Ave<br/>Memphis, TN 38103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chorizo Meatloaf, Lobster Pronto Pups</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this upscale diner, Chef Michael Patrick is reinventing Southern comfort food. The savory chorizo meatloaf juxtaposed with tangy green tomato gravy tantalized Guy&#x27;s taste buds, while the lobster pronto pups had a light batter and perfectly tender meat.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Savory Standouts<br/>Deep Fried All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/memphis/rizzos-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.05863,35.13294,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Leonard&#x27;s Pit Barbecue</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Leonard&#x27;s Pit Barbecue</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Memphis, TN 38115 &middot; &#9733; 4.1 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9013601963" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(901) 360-1963</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.leonardsbarbecue.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.leonardsbarbecue.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Leonard%27s+Pit+Barbecue%2C+5465+Fox+Plaza+Dr.%2C+Memphis%2C+TN+38115&amp;ll=35.074036,-89.881409" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5465 Fox Plaza Dr.<br/>Memphis, TN 38115</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chopped Pork Sandwich, Sweet Mustard Coleslaw, Onion Ring Batter, Pulled Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Leonard&#x27;s Pit Barbecue owner Dan Brown says if you visit for dinner you&#x27;ll experience the same delicious recipes passed down from &amp;quot;last century&amp;quot; to &amp;quot;last week&amp;quot; Open since 1922, this iconic Memphis, Tenn., eatery has loads of fans, like Guy, who called the chopped pork sandwich &amp;quot;all-star barbecue.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big-Time Barbecue<br/>The Memphis BBQ Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/memphis/leonards-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-89.88141,35.07404,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Marlowe&#x27;s Ribs</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Marlowe&#x27;s Ribs</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Memphis, TN 38116 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (24 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9013324159" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(901) 332-4159</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.marlowesmemphis.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.marlowesmemphis.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Marlowe%27s+Ribs%2C+4381+Elvis+Presley+Blvd.%2C+Memphis%2C+TN+38116&amp;ll=35.029045,-90.025822" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4381 Elvis Presley Blvd.<br/>Memphis, TN 38116</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ Dry Rub, Black Magic, Baby Back Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You might not see locals at Graceland, but you&#x27;ll definitely see them at Marlowe&#x27;s Ribs. Like Guy, locals know they can call Marlowe&#x27;s for a free pink-limo ride to the restaurant. Good thing too because Guy couldn&#x27;t wait to try the Elvis favorite: ribs smothered in Marlowe&#x27;s tangy barbecue sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Memphis BBQ Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/memphis/marlowes-ribs-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.02582,35.02905,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Little Tea Shop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Little Tea Shop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Memphis, TN 38103 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9015256000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">901-525-6000</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/memphis/little-tea-shop-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/memphis/little-tea-shop-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Little+Tea+Shop%2C+69+Monroe+Avenue%2C+Memphis%2C+TN+38103&amp;ll=35.144245,-90.054185" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">69 Monroe Avenue<br/>Memphis, TN 38103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Chicken, Poppin&#x27; Johns, Corn Sticks</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Suhair may be from Jerusalem, but she can cook Southern food &amp;quot;like no other.&amp;quot; Her fried chicken, which Guy describes as light and crispy, has a secret Middle Eastern twist. The menu rotates during the week, but crowd-pleasers like corn sticks and poppin&#x27; Johns are served fresh daily.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">American Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/memphis/little-tea-shop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.05419,35.14424,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Boteco</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Boteco</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Austin 78702</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.botecoatx.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.botecoatx.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Boteco%2C+1209+East+6th+St%2C+Austin+78702&amp;ll=30.264107,-97.730134" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1209 East 6th St<br/>Austin 78702</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Feijoada, Pao De Queijo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fernando Marri recreates the food he ate growing up in Brazil at his food truck in Austin. Diners, like Matthew McConaughey and his Brazilian-born wife, swear by the authenticity. Guy loved the classic Feijoada and homemade Pao De Queijo, &quot;I feel transported to Brazil.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern to South American</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/austin/boteco-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.73013,30.26411,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Farmer (formerly Elegant Farmer), Memphis</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Farmer (formerly Elegant Farmer), Memphis</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Memphis, TN 38111 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9013242221" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(901) 324-2221</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thefarmermemphis.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thefarmermemphis.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Farmer+%28formerly+Elegant+Farmer%29%2C+Memphis%2C+262+S+Highland+St%2C+Memphis%2C+TN+38111&amp;ll=35.124601,-89.944943" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">262 S Highland St<br/>Memphis, TN 38111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pan-Seared Catfish with Mac &#x27;n&#x27; Cheese, Sloppy Joe, Banh Mi</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this farm-to-table eatery Chef Mac Edwards buys his ingredients directly from the source. The pan-seared catfish with mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese and greens as well as the banh mi Guy called &quot;outstanding.&quot; Guy got messy with the sloppy joe full of &quot;big flavor.&quot; Locals love the country fried pork chops.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Handcrafted<br/>All Stacked Up</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/memphis/the-elegant-farmer-restaurant2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-89.94494,35.12460,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cozy Corner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cozy Corner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Memphis, TN 38105 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9015279158" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(901) 527-9158</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cozycornerbbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cozycornerbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cozy+Corner%2C+745+N.+Pkwy.%2C+Memphis%2C+TN+38105&amp;ll=35.150924,-89.981419" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">745 N. Pkwy.<br/>Memphis, TN 38105</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Sausage, Bologna Barbecue Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cozy Corner knows its Tennessee barbecue and locals come in droves for their ribs, wings and smoked sausage. But Guy was caught off-guard by their equally tasty whole chickens and bologna barbecue sandwiches. The real kicker? Cornish hens. Guy says you&#x27;ll just have to come over and get your own.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Memphis BBQ Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/memphis/cozy-corner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-89.98142,35.15092,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tom&#x27;s Bar-B-Q</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tom&#x27;s Bar-B-Q</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Memphis, TN 38118 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9013656690" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">901-365-6690</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.tomsbarbeque.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tomsbarbeque.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tom%27s+Bar-B-Q%2C+4087+New+Getwell+Rd.%2C+Memphis%2C+TN+38118&amp;ll=35.037009,-89.937462" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4087 New Getwell Rd.<br/>Memphis, TN 38118</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Rib Tips, Pulled Pork, Brisket, Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tom&#x27;s draws the crowds with a special Mediterranean twist on barbecue. They slather a Greek-inspired spice rub featuring thyme, oregano, pickling spice, celery salt and more on everything from brisket to turkey, including the signature rib tips, which Guy calls &amp;quot;some of the best barbecue&#x27; around.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grilling Greats<br/>The Memphis BBQ Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/memphis/toms-bar-b-q-deli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-89.93746,35.03701,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Magnolia Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Magnolia Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Austin, TX 78704 &middot; &#9733; 2.8 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5124450000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">512-445-0000</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://themagnoliacafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">themagnoliacafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Magnolia+Cafe%2C+1920+S+Congress+Ave%2C+Austin%2C+TX+78704&amp;ll=30.244473,-97.751949" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1920 S Congress Ave<br/>Austin, TX 78704</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gingerbread Pancakes, Magna Cristo, Tuna Melt, Love Migas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Locals can&#x27;t wait for Magnolia Cafe&#x27;s giant gingerbread banana pancakes, and lucky for them, they don&#x27;t have to. Guy loved the menu, packed with everything from chipotle hollandaise sauce on eggs Benedict to jambalaya stuffed in red peppers. As he says, &amp;quot;come back for the food and the funk.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Not What You&#x27;d Expect</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/austin/magnolia-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.75195,30.24447,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Alcenia&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Alcenia&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Memphis, TN 38103 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9015230200" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(901) 523-0200</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://alcenias.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">alcenias.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Alcenia%27s%2C+317+N+Main+St.%2C+Memphis%2C+TN+38103&amp;ll=35.153601,-90.049697" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">317 N Main St.<br/>Memphis, TN 38103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sweet Potato Cobbler, Egg Custard Pie, Salmon Croquettes, Fried Chicken, Ham and Cheese Omelette</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you&#x27;re from Memphis, you may have already heard of Alcenia&#x27;s famous &amp;quot;Cha Cha&amp;quot; cabbage relish or the sweet potato cobbler. Guy swooped in on this mother-daughter operation for Triple D (as did the Neelys). Locals claim it&#x27;s true Memphis cooking and Guy had this to say: &amp;quot;Mmm, that&#x27;s good.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Traditional Dishes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/memphis/alcenias-restaurant2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.04970,35.15360,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nicky&#x27;s Coal Fired</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nicky&#x27;s Coal Fired</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nashville 37209 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6156784289" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 678-4289</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.nickysnashville.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.nickysnashville.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nicky%27s+Coal+Fired%2C+5026+Centennial+Blvd.%2C+Nashville+37209&amp;ll=36.162274,-86.848795" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5026 Centennial Blvd.<br/>Nashville 37209</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nicky&#x27;s uses locally sourced ingredients and a coal fired oven to give their Italian cuisine a fresh and unique taste. They offer pizza, pasta and meatballs, one of their specialties.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Traditional Twists</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/nashville/nicky-s-coal-fired" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.84880,36.16227,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pizza Palace</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pizza Palace</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Knoxville 37914 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (27 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8655244388" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">865-524-4388</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.visitpizzapalace.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.visitpizzapalace.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pizza+Palace%2C+3132+E+Magnolia+Ave%2C+Knoxville+37914&amp;ll=35.994849,-83.885780" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3132 E Magnolia Ave<br/>Knoxville 37914</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza, Meat Sauce</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A drive-in pizzeria that also sells onion rings and salads is a rather odd combination, but the Pizza Palace has been a Knoxville, Tenn., staple for decades. Their spaghetti is served with a homemade meat sauce, created by owners Sam and Charlie Peroulas, that almost left Guy speechless.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Comin&#x27; from All Over the Map<br/>That&#x27;s Italian<br/>Pizza Party</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/knoxville/pizza-palace-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-83.88578,35.99485,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Chef Point</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Chef Point</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Watauga, TX 76148 &middot; &#9733; 4.1 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8176560080" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">817-656-0080</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.chefpointcafe.org" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.chefpointcafe.org</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Chef+Point%2C+5901+Watauga+Rd%2C+Watauga%2C+TX+76148&amp;ll=32.861056,-97.253583" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5901 Watauga Rd<br/>Watauga, TX 76148</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bread Pudding, Duck l&#x27;Orange, Lamb Chops, Maple Leaf Duck, Escargot</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A gas station&#x27;s cafe may be the last place you&#x27;d expect to fill up on gourmet eats, but that&#x27;s what you&#x27;ll find here. Guy Fieri is a fan of the bread pudding served with a scratch-made cognac sauce, while Jeff Mauro favors a spicier treat: a Bloody Mary garnished with fried chicken, bacon and more.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Funky Joints<br/>Dynamite Desserts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/watauga/chef-point-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.25358,32.86106,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hullabaloo Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hullabaloo Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wellborn, TX 77845 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9796903002" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(979) 690-3002</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hullabaloodiner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hullabaloodiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hullabaloo+Diner%2C+15045+F.M.+2154%2C+Wellborn%2C+TX+77845&amp;ll=30.532356,-96.301392" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">15045 F.M. 2154<br/>Wellborn, TX 77845</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Philly Cheesesteak Sandwiches, Biscuits and Gravy</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For a taste of the East Coast in the midst of Texas, head to this circa-1940s diner that was transported here from New York. In addition to serving Texas classics, including biscuits and gravy, owner Rich Risbon is slinging East Coast staples such as Philly cheesesteak sandwiches. Risbon offers a traditional take on the sandwich (think mounds of thinly sliced sauteed beef, grilled onions and melty slices of white American cheese), as well as beyond-basic riffs: There&#x27;s even a pizza version slathered in marinara sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">That&#x27;s Italian<br/>Real-Deal Diners</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/wellborn/hullabaloo-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.30139,30.53236,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mac &amp; Ernie&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mac &amp; Ernie&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tarpley 78883 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8305623727" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(830) 562-3727</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.macandernies.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.macandernies.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mac+%26+Ernie%27s%2C+11804+FM+470%2C+Tarpley+78883&amp;ll=29.648163,-99.303065" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">11804 FM 470<br/>Tarpley 78883</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">&quot;Cabrito&quot; Burger, Ancho Chile Honey Basted Quail, Chicken Fried Lamb Chops with Creamy Gravy</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mac &amp; Ernie&#x27;s in Tarpley, Texas, has the honor of being the first restaurant featured on Triple D. The Cabrito (that&#x27;s Spanish for little goat) burger is owner Naylene Dillingham&#x27;s own recipe. Guy was amazed by the chicken-fried lamb chop, proclaiming, &#x27;&#x27;It may be the best lamb chop I&#x27;ve ever had.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Goin&#x27; Big and Bringin&#x27; Home<br/>Triple D Nation: Fried and Smoked<br/>Classics<br/>Legends of Texas</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/tarpley/mac-ernies-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-99.30307,29.64816,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Wrigleyville</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Wrigleyville</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio, TX 78216</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.wrigleyvillegrill.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.wrigleyvillegrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Wrigleyville%2C+602+NW+LP+410%2C+San+Antonio%2C+TX+78216&amp;ll=29.519621,-98.502487" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">602 NW LP 410<br/>San Antonio, TX 78216</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Famous Italian Beef, Chili Cheese Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners head to Wrigleyville for a legit taste of Chicago in San Antonio. Chef Demetrios Tingas, aka Jimmy, spent 41 years in Chicago and brought his hometown staples with him when he moved south. &quot;That&#x27;s as close as it is to the original,&quot; Guy said between bites of the Famous Italian Beef.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Sandwiches to Stroganoff</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/wrigleyville-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.50249,29.51962,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Louie Mueller&#x27;s Barbecue</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Louie Mueller&#x27;s Barbecue</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Taylor 76574</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5123526206" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(512) 352-6206</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.louiemuellerbarbeque.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.louiemuellerbarbeque.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Louie+Mueller%27s+Barbecue%2C+206+W.+Second+St.%2C+Taylor+76574&amp;ll=30.568827,-97.411098" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">206 W. Second St.<br/>Taylor 76574</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef Brisket, Texas Beef Ribs, Beef Sausage</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Third-generation pitmaster Wayne Mueller starts lighting the fires and loading the meats as early as 3 a.m. at this joint. Such dedication pays off: The brisket is so juicy that no sauce is needed, and the monstrous beef ribs feature a thick, peppery crust that gives way to tender, luscious meat.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grilling Greats<br/>Takeout: Shipped, Sweet and Savory<br/>Triple D Nation: Beef, Barbecue and Bar Food<br/>BBQ</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/taylor/louie-mueller-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.41110,30.56883,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fat Tummy</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fat Tummy</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio, TX 78207 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.fattummyempanadassa.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fattummyempanadassa.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fat+Tummy%2C+2922+W+Commerce+St%2C+San+Antonio%2C+TX+78207&amp;ll=29.428150,-98.527940" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2922 W Commerce St<br/>San Antonio, TX 78207</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spicy Chicken, Humita, Guava and Cream Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Gustavo Plache and Norah Saleh, a husband and wife team from Argentina, are churning out their signature &quot;fat tummy&quot; empanadas in San Antonio. These extra-large hot dough pockets are filled with all kinds of savory and sweet ingredients. &quot;You&#x27;re the example of the America story,&quot; said Guy. &quot;That&#x27;s why we do Triple-D.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Sandwiches to Stroganoff</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/fat-tummy-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.52794,29.42815,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Whistle Britches</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Whistle Britches</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Dallas, TX 75252 &middot; &#9733; 3.2 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9725908991" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">972-590-8991</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://whistlebritcheschicken.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">whistlebritcheschicken.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Whistle+Britches%2C+6110+Frankford+Rd%2C+Dallas%2C+TX+75252&amp;ll=32.997679,-96.799601" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6110 Frankford Rd<br/>Dallas, TX 75252</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hot Dang, Chicken N&#x27; Waffles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Omar Flores is dishing out comfort food with a Southern spin and making some seriously crispy fried chicken at Whistle Britches. The Hot Dang is their Nashville-style hot chicken served on thick Texas toast, with cool dill ranch and house-made pickles. Their chicken and waffles are served with a drizzle of jalapeno hot honey, house-made sausage gravy and a wedge of watermelon. &quot;That&#x27;s wrong in so many ways that it makes it right,&quot; Guy said of the dish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/dallas/whistle-britches-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.79960,32.99768,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tacos Mariachi</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tacos Mariachi</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Dallas, TX 75212 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2147411239" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">214-741-1239</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tacosmariachi.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tacosmariachi.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tacos+Mariachi%2C+602+Singleton+Blvd%2C+Dallas%2C+TX+75212&amp;ll=32.778486,-96.833326" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">602 Singleton Blvd<br/>Dallas, TX 75212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulpo Tacos, Mole Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Jesus Carmona is serving up real-deal Tijuana street tacos and more in Dallas. Hisgrilled octopus tacos are topped with a spicy pesto salsa and cooled with avocado and cheese. The chef was inspired to make his signature Mole Fries by a vendor selling potato chips dipped in mole. His version substitutes crispy fries topped with house-made mole, crema fresca and cotija cheese. &quot;I came here for tacos, I&#x27;ll come back for the fritas,&quot; gushed Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Delicious Discoveries</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/dallas/Tacos-mariachi-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.83333,32.77849,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Twisted Root Burger Co.</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Twisted Root Burger Co.</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Dallas, TX 75226 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (15 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2147417668" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(214) 741-7668</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.twistedrootburgerco.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.twistedrootburgerco.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Twisted+Root+Burger+Co.%2C+2615+Commerce+St%2C+Dallas%2C+TX+75226&amp;ll=32.783013,-96.785495" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2615 Commerce St<br/>Dallas, TX 75226</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Western Burger, Venison and Bison Burger, Spicy Fried Pickles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this eatery they&#x27;re serving over 2000 burgers a week with a gourmet twist. The barbecue sauce in the half-pound Western Burger with pepper Jack, bacon, onion strings and jalapenos was the &quot;kicker&quot; according to Guy. He also enjoyed the venison and bison burger with a side of spicy fried pickles.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Burger, A Bowl and a Slice<br/>Triple D Nation: Something Sweet</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/dallas/twisted-root-burger-co-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.78550,32.78301,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Riddim N Spice</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Riddim N Spice</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nashville, TN 37208 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6159537121" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 953-7121</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="info@riddimnspice.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">info@riddimnspice.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Riddim+N+Spice%2C+2116+Meharry+Blvd.%2C+Nashville%2C+TN+37208&amp;ll=36.167775,-86.809613" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2116 Meharry Blvd.<br/>Nashville, TN 37208</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Inspired by their love for Caribbean food, Jamaican brothers Kamal Kalokoh and Rashean Conaway created Riddim N Spice for those craving a taste of island food. Their dishes including barbeque jerk jackfruit, snapper and peas and rice.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwiches and Spice</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/nashville/riddim-n-spice" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.80961,36.16777,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Savarino&#x27;s Cucina</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Savarino&#x27;s Cucina</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nashville 37212 &middot; &#9733; 2.4 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6154609878" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 460-9878</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/savarinoscucina" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/savarinoscucina</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Savarino%27s+Cucina%2C+2121+Belcourt+Ave%2C+Nashville+37212&amp;ll=36.136525,-86.802762" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2121 Belcourt Ave<br/>Nashville 37212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fettuccine, Cantaloupe Italian Ice</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Guy visited this Italian eatery on Triple D, he found one-of-a-kind homemade fettuccine that is rolled not with a pasta machine but a broomstick. Also worth a try: any of Savarino&#x27;s signature sandwiches, of which there are over a dozen, paired with cantaloupe Italian ice for dessert.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gone Global</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/nashville/savarinos-cucina-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.80276,36.13652,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Smoke Shack</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Smoke Shack</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio 78209 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2109571430" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">210-957-1430</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.smokeshacksa.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.smokeshacksa.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Smoke+Shack%2C+714+Broadway%2C+San+Antonio+78209&amp;ll=29.432019,-98.483201" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">714 Broadway<br/>San Antonio 78209</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Even in a state full of barbecue joints, this one stands out for its Big Mac Daddy. Layer upon layer of pulled pork and brisket are heaped onto a 24-inch bun, then loaded with sausage links, smothered with 2 kinds of sauces and crowned with 4 scoops of meat-studded macaroni and cheese for a seven-pound behemoth.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Bacon and BBQ</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/smoke-shack-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.48320,29.43202,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Beto&#x27;s on Broadway</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Beto&#x27;s on Broadway</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio 78209 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2109309393" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(210) 930-9393</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.betosaltmex.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.betosaltmex.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Beto%27s+on+Broadway%2C+8142+Broadway+St%2C+San+Antonio+78209&amp;ll=29.511277,-98.465916" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">8142 Broadway St<br/>San Antonio 78209</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Empanadas, Chalupa Cabra, Chicken Poblano</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this Latin American street food restaurant everything is made to order. Out of the 14 types of empanadas, Guy most enjoyed the chicken poblano, which has a nice flaky crust. He also liked the rich and satisfying chalupa cabra with guava and cream cheese rolls, cilantro, coconut slaw and curry.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Latin Street Food</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/betos-comida-latina-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.46592,29.51128,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bun &#x27;N&#x27; Barrel</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bun &#x27;N&#x27; Barrel</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio, TX 78209 &middot; &#9733; 2.6 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2108282829" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(210) 828-2829</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://bunnbarrel.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">bunnbarrel.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bun+%27N%27+Barrel%2C+1150+Austin+Hwy%2C+San+Antonio%2C+TX+78209&amp;ll=29.486710,-98.447623" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1150 Austin Hwy<br/>San Antonio, TX 78209</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brisket Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">As a San Antonio landmark of more than 60 years, the Bun &#x27;N&#x27; Barrel knocks old-school classics out of the park. Must-try favorites include the Terrace Burger and the succulent brisket sandwich. Or, if you&#x27;re Guy, try the &amp;quot;pretty addicting&amp;quot; spicy burger paired with the super fiery Thai chile sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grillin&#x27; and Smokin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/bun-n-barrel-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.44762,29.48671,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ma Harper&#x27;s Creole Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ma Harper&#x27;s Creole Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio, TX 78208 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/ma-harpers-restaurants" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/ma-harpers-restaurants</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ma+Harper%27s+Creole+Kitchen%2C+816+N.+New+Braunfels+Ave%2C+San+Antonio%2C+TX+78208&amp;ll=29.429524,-98.460948" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">816 N. New Braunfels Ave<br/>San Antonio, TX 78208</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gumbo, Fried Pork Chop</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Patrons head to Ma Harper&#x27;s Creole Kitchen for some of the most-authentic New Orleans cuisine outside of New Orleans. Alice Martinez &quot;Ma Harper&quot;, now in her 80s, got into the restaurant business after retiring from the nearby air force base. She learned to cook by feeding her 15 siblings while growing up in New Orleans.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Regional Recipes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/ma-harpers-restaurants" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.46095,29.42952,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Magnolia Pancake Haus</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Magnolia Pancake Haus</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio, TX 78216 &middot; &#9733; 4.1 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2104960828" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(210) 496-0828</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.magnoliapancakehaus.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.magnoliapancakehaus.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Magnolia+Pancake+Haus%2C+606+Embassy+Oaks%2C+San+Antonio%2C+TX+78216&amp;ll=29.564456,-98.489368" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">606 Embassy Oaks<br/>San Antonio, TX 78216</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bacon Stuffed Waffles, Apple Cinnamon Pancakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Robert Fleming&#x27;s light and airy pancakes are &amp;quot;raising the bar on breakfast.&amp;quot; The crispy corned beef hash impressed Guy with its &amp;quot;big flavor.&amp;quot; The deliciously unique Pfannekuchen is like an apple pie disguised as a pancake. Try the bacon waffles for a savory spin on a breakfast classic.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Breakfast, Lunch and Dinner<br/>Ultimate Bacon Fest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/magnolia-pancake-haus-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.48937,29.56446,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Luna Rosa Puerto Rican Grill y Tapas</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Luna Rosa Puerto Rican Grill y Tapas</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio, TX 78223 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.lunarosatapas.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.lunarosatapas.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Luna+Rosa+Puerto+Rican+Grill+y+Tapas%2C+2603+SE+Military+Dr+%23106%2C+San+Antonio%2C+TX+78223&amp;ll=29.352525,-98.451340" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2603 SE Military Dr #106<br/>San Antonio, TX 78223</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Caribbean Nachos, Chuleta Kan-Kan</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After teaching for 25 years, Chef Iris Ornelas followed her passion and opened a restaurant that celebrated her Puerto Rican heritage. Her Caribbean Nachos are made with crispy fried plantains, instead of chips and are topped with roast pork, beans, cheese and chili sauce. Also, try their unique Chuleta Kan-Kan which is an extremely large fried pork chop with the rib attached. Guy had never seen anything like it.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Piling On the Pork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/luna-rosa-puerto-rican-grill-y-tapas-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.45134,29.35252,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Moroccan Bites</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Moroccan Bites</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio 78238 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2107069700" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(210) 706-9700</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://moroccanbitestagine.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">moroccanbitestagine.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Moroccan+Bites%2C+5714+Evers+Rd%2C+San+Antonio+78238&amp;ll=29.489530,-98.598867" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5714 Evers Rd<br/>San Antonio 78238</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Moroccan Sausage Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy couldn&#x27;t stop himself from taking nibbles of Moroccan Bites&#x27; dishes. For starters, the fall-apart lamb served on fluffy couscous was playing a &quot;tune called delicious.&quot; And don&#x27;t forget the Moroccan sausage sandwich made with an earthy spice mix and totally &quot;out-of-bounds&quot; relish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Kraut to Couscous</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/moroccan-bites-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.59887,29.48953,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>El Bohio</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">El Bohio</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio 78234 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2108228075" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(210) 822-8075</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/el-bohio-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/el-bohio-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=El+Bohio%2C+1127+Harry+Wurzbach%2C+San+Antonio+78234&amp;ll=29.469692,-98.438384" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1127 Harry Wurzbach<br/>San Antonio 78234</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mofongo, Ropa Vieja</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this Puerto Rican eatery, Chef Andre Cerbones is cooking up all the classics. Guy&#x27;s favorite is the mofongo, which is made with mashed plantains, fried pork and a garlic sauce. According to Guy, &quot;there is no way you can&#x27;t love&quot; the full-flavored ropa vieja with twice-fried plantains either.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Global Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/el-bohio-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.43838,29.46969,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>De Wese&#x27;s Tip Top Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">De Wese&#x27;s Tip Top Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio 78201 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2107320191" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(210) 732-0191</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tiptopcafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tiptopcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=De+Wese%27s+Tip+Top+Cafe%2C+2814+Fredericksburg+Rd.%2C+San+Antonio+78201&amp;ll=29.470139,-98.531231" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2814 Fredericksburg Rd.<br/>San Antonio 78201</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roast Pork and Gravy, Beef Enchiladas, Fried Shrimp</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Tip Top Cafe in San Antonio hasn&#x27;t changed the menu much since it first opened over 70 years ago, but that&#x27;s because there hasn&#x27;t been any reason to do so. Guy couldn&#x27;t stop eating the open-faced roast pork and gravy sandwich, the beef enchiladas and the buttery fried shrimp.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort Food<br/>Triple-D Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/tip-top-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.53123,29.47014,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Taco Taco Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Taco Taco Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio, TX 78212 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (26 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2108229533" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(210) 822-9533</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tacotacosa.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tacotacosa.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Taco+Taco+Cafe%2C+145+E+Hildebrand+Ave%2C+San+Antonio%2C+TX+78212&amp;ll=29.466657,-98.492271" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">145 E Hildebrand Ave<br/>San Antonio, TX 78212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos de Lengua, Shredded Chicken Fried Puffy Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owner Helen Velesiotis may be Greek, but she knows how to cook up some &quot;real-deal&quot; Mexican food. Guy was skeptical about trying the Tacos de Lengua, which are beef tongue tacos. But after his first bite he was hooked on the dynamite flavor. Guy also enjoyed the shredded-chicken fried puffy tacos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crazy for Chicken<br/>Triple D Nation: International Affair<br/>Slammin&#x27; Sammies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/taco-taco-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.49227,29.46666,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Cove</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Cove</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio 78212 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2102272683" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(210) 227-2683</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://thecove.us/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">thecove.us</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Cove%2C+606+W.+Cypress+St.%2C+San+Antonio+78212&amp;ll=29.440594,-98.500578" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">606 W. Cypress St.<br/>San Antonio 78212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Latin-Spiced Lamb Burgers, Fish Tacos, Mushroom Quesadillas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Most people probably wouldn&#x27;t expect to find amazing food at a restaurant connected to a car wash and a laundromat, but The Cove in San Antonio is home to some of the best lamb burgers Guy&#x27;s ever had. Owner Lisa Avestas&#x27; fish tacos and mushroom quesadillas are hometown favorites.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Totally Unexpected<br/>Triple D Nation: Where&#x27;s the Beef?<br/>Diner&#x27;s Drive-ins and Dives: Best from the Road</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/the-cove-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.50058,29.44059,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dough Pizzeria Napoletana</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dough Pizzeria Napoletana</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio 78216 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2109796565" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">210-979.6565</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.doughpizzeria.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.doughpizzeria.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dough+Pizzeria+Napoletana%2C+6989+Blanco+Rd%2C+San+Antonio+78216&amp;ll=29.519345,-98.507484" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6989 Blanco Rd<br/>San Antonio 78216</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza Napoletana; Pork Love Pizza; Pizza with Prosciutto, Onions and Olives; Rollatini (Black Truffle, Proscuitto, Mozzerella and Arugula Antipasto Rolls)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The pizza at Dough Pizzeria Napoletana is so authentic, owner Doug Horn even has the L&#x27;Associazione Vera Pizza Napoletana certificate to prove he serves bona fide Neapolitan pizza. Guy&#x27;s visit was a lesson in &quot;mega awesome,&quot; starting with the handmade mozzarella and the irresistible prosciutto.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: A Taste of Italy<br/>Takeout: Carnivore Delivery<br/>Porktastic</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/dough-pizzeria-napolentana-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.50748,29.51935,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dignowity Meats</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dignowity Meats</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Antonio, TX 78202 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.dignowitymeats.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.dignowitymeats.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dignowity+Meats%2C+1701+E.+Houston+St.%2C+San+Antonio%2C+TX+78202&amp;ll=29.425047,-98.436761" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1701 E. Houston St.<br/>San Antonio, TX 78202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burnt End Melt, Reuben</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dignowity Meats is what happens when an East Coast boy falls in love with barbecue but misses his classic deli sandwiches. Chef Andrew Samia merges these two into his Burnt End Melt. Guy called the combo of hickory smoked prime angus brisket, mac and cheese, sliced pear and cheddar cheese, &quot;a lethal weapon.&quot; &quot;You&#x27;d have to register this in Flavortown,&quot; he mused.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Regional Recipes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/san-antonio/dignowity-meats-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-98.43676,29.42505,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bob&#x27;s Taco Station</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bob&#x27;s Taco Station</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Rosenberg, TX 77471 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2812328555" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(281) 232-8555</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bobstacos.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bobstacos.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bob%27s+Taco+Station%2C+1901+Avenue+H%2C+Rosenberg%2C+TX+77471&amp;ll=29.558473,-95.807580" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1901 Avenue H<br/>Rosenberg, TX 77471</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos, &quot;Snoball,&quot; Carne Guisada, Tamales</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Join host, Guy Fieri, of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, at Bob&#x27;s Taco Station in Rosenberg, TX, a family-run taqueria dishing out authentic Mexican cuisine.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Legends of Texas<br/>Stacked, Stuffed and Loaded</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/rosenberg/bobs-taco-station-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.80758,29.55847,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Grilled Cheeserie</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Grilled Cheeserie</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nashville 37212</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6154919640" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 491-9640</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://grilledcheeserie.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">grilledcheeserie.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Grilled+Cheeserie%2C+Roaming+Food+Truck%2C+Nashville+37212&amp;ll=36.198711,-84.789997" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Roaming Food Truck<br/>Nashville 37212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pimento Mac &amp; Chee (Pimento Mac &amp; Cheese Sandwich), Roasted Red Pepper Tomato Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This food truck&#x27;s gourmet take on comfort food draws the crowds, but regulars say it&#x27;s worth the wait. The Pimento Mac &amp; Chee has Guy dreaming of childhood. Served with tomato soup, this best-seller features pimento cheese, cheddar, macaroni, bacon bits and sliced tomato on country white bread.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">See All<br/>Triple D Nation: Between the Bread<br/>Family Time<br/>Food Truckapalooza<br/>Takeout: Bringing Comfort Home</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/nashville/the-grilled-cheeserie" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.79000,36.19871,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Luke&#x27;s Inside Out</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Luke&#x27;s Inside Out</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Austin, TX 78704 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5125898883" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(512) 589-8883</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.lukesinsideout.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.lukesinsideout.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Luke%27s+Inside+Out%2C+1109+S+Lamar+Blvd%2C+Austin%2C+TX+78704&amp;ll=30.254976,-97.761932" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1109 S Lamar Blvd<br/>Austin, TX 78704</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwiches, Korean Rabbit</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this food truck, you never know what kind of sandwich you&#x27;ll get. Guy called the Korean rabbit with rabbit meat, tater tots, kimchi, Sriracha and their secret sauce &amp;quot;the bomb.&amp;quot; The shrimp caught Guy&#x27;s attention with its tasty shrimp patty paired with blue cheese, baby spinach, onions and apples.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grilling Greats<br/>Streamlined Sammies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/austin/lukes-inside-out-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.76193,30.25498,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Taco Xpress</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Taco Xpress</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Austin, TX 78704 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5124440261" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">512-444-0261</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tacoxpress.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tacoxpress.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Taco+Xpress%2C+2529+South+Lamar+Blvd.%2C+Austin%2C+TX+78704&amp;ll=30.245909,-97.778358" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2529 South Lamar Blvd.<br/>Austin, TX 78704</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos Al Pastor (Pork Tacos), Pollo Guisado Tacos (Chicken Tacos)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">To taste the funky and weird side of Austin, Rachael gets a local tip to visit Maria&#x27;s Taco Xpress with its bright murals and good cheap eats. Rachael ordered the popular migas breakfast tacos, but for dinner, it&#x27;s all about the pollo guisado chicken tacos made with a smoky chipotle sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Real Deal Fast Food</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/austin/taco-xpress-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.77836,30.24591,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Green Mesquite</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Green Mesquite</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Austin, TX 78704 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5124790485" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">512-479-0485</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.greenmesquite.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.greenmesquite.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Green+Mesquite%2C+1400+Barton+Springs+Rd%2C+Austin%2C+TX+78704&amp;ll=30.261519,-97.759200" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1400 Barton Springs Rd<br/>Austin, TX 78704</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Wings, Pork Ribs, Beef Brisket Plate</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Green Mesquite, the BBQ gets its spectacular smoky flavor from the spot&#x27;s namesake: mesquite wood that is seasoned, or &amp;quot;green.&amp;quot; On Triple D, Guy calls the ribs, made with brown sugar, paprika, cayenne, onion and garlic, &amp;quot;awesome.&amp;quot; Other faves include brisket, pulled pork and chicken fried steak.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big-Time Barbecue<br/>BBQ &amp; More</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/austin/green-mesquite-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.75920,30.26152,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Noble Sandwich Co.</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Noble Sandwich Co.</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Austin 78750 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5123826248" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">512-382-6248</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://noblesandwiches.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">noblesandwiches.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Noble+Sandwich+Co.%2C+12233+Ranch+Rd+620+N+%23105%2C+Austin+78750&amp;ll=30.461938,-97.814671" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">12233 Ranch Rd 620 N #105<br/>Austin 78750</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Duck Pastrami, Noble Pig, Knuckle Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This spot takes its sandwiches seriously, as Guy saw firsthand. He tried the duck pastrami and was pleased with how its fatty and smoky flavors balance each other. Another standout is the Noble Pig, starring house-brined ham, pulled pork, bacon and melty provolone piled on bacon-studded bread.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Super Sandwiches<br/>Serious Sandwiches<br/>Triple D Nation: From Pork to Pot Pie</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/austin/noble-sandwich-co-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.81467,30.46194,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Foreign &amp; Domestic</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Foreign &amp; Domestic</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Austin, TX 78751 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5124591010" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">512-459-1010</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://fndaustin.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">fndaustin.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Foreign+%26+Domestic%2C+306+E+53rd+St%2C+Austin%2C+TX+78751&amp;ll=30.317082,-97.719528" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">306 E 53rd St<br/>Austin, TX 78751</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fideos and Shellfish</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Foreign &amp;amp; Domestic, it&#x27;s a culinary wedding of flavors. The husband-and-wife duo behind this restaurant have been turning foreign dishes a little domestic and vice versa. The result is a menu with savory, eclectic standouts, like Fideos pasta studded with bacon, mussels and clams or their signature Gruyere Popovers.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Belly Up<br/>Ultimate Bacon Fest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/austin/foreign-domestic-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.71953,30.31708,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Valentina&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Valentina&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Austin 78748 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5122214248" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">512-221-4248</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.valentinastexmexbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.valentinastexmexbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Valentina%27s%2C+11500+Menchaca+Rd%2C+Austin+78748&amp;ll=30.206938,-97.835568" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">11500 Menchaca Rd<br/>Austin 78748</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Real Deal Holyfield</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Valentina&#x27;s manages to excel at both classic barbecue meats and Mexican staples like carnitas and fajitas. Make it there before 11 a.m. to enjoy The Real Deal Holyfield, one of the city&#x27;s most-decadent culinary experiences and one that&#x27;s likely to knock you out for the rest of your day. The fried egg, beans, potato, bacon and tomato-serrano salsa are a meal unto themselves, but the dish enters a new realm of gluttony with a thick slice of fatty brisket.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Whole Lotta Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/austin/valentinas-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.83557,30.20694,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mas Tacos por Favor</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mas Tacos por Favor</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nashville 37206 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6155436271" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 543-6271</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.facebook.com/mastacos" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/mastacos</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mas+Tacos+por+Favor%2C+732+Mcferrin+Ave%2C+Nashville+37206&amp;ll=36.184765,-86.754677" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">732 Mcferrin Ave<br/>Nashville 37206</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pozole Verde Soup, Holiday Tamale</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mas Tacos por Favor started in a 1974 Winnebago and has since become one of Nashville&#x27;s favorite eateries, known and loved for serving scratch-made Mexican cuisine. Guy adored the holiday tamales and quinoa tacos. As for the pozole verde soup? He says, the &quot;depth of the broth is ridiculous.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Holiday Hoopla<br/>Tennessee Holiday Traditions</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/nashville/mas-tacos-por-favor-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.75468,36.18476,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jamaicaway</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jamaicaway</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nashville 37208 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6152555920" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 255-5920</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.jamaicawaycatering.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jamaicawaycatering.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jamaicaway%2C+900+Rosa+L+Parks+Blvd%2C+Nashville+37208&amp;ll=36.169442,-86.787940" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">900 Rosa L Parks Blvd<br/>Nashville 37208</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crunch Fried Chicken, Curried Goat, Oxtail Stew</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">It&#x27;s all authentic and homemade at this Jamaican hole-in-the-wall. The silky ackee and salt-fish intrigued Guy, and he enjoyed the crunchy fried chicken with mango chutney sauce and munching on the coconut drops. Customers praise the curried goat and oxtail stew.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wings &#x27;n Things</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/nashville/jamaica-way-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.78794,36.16944,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Caffe Nonna</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Caffe Nonna</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nashville 37209 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6154630133" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 463-0133</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.caffenonna.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.caffenonna.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Caffe+Nonna%2C+4427+Murphy+Rd%2C+Nashville+37209&amp;ll=36.140792,-86.840165" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4427 Murphy Rd<br/>Nashville 37209</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lasagna Nonna</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy heads to Caffe Nonna for a rustic Italian meal, and nothing on the menu is more rustic than the Lasagna Nonna. This delectable eight-layer dish is filled with butternut squash, spinach, pasta, ricotta and sauteed Swiss chard, and it&#x27;s finished off with two sauces and lots of cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Time</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/nashville/caffe-nonna" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.84016,36.14079,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Graze</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Graze</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nashville 37206 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6156861060" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 686-1060</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.grazenashville.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.grazenashville.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Graze%2C+1888+Eastland+Ave%2C+Nashville+37206&amp;ll=36.182428,-86.735565" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1888 Eastland Ave<br/>Nashville 37206</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Graze is a family-owned, locally-sourced vegan restuarant. Their brunch and dinner menus offer many options for delicious plant-based dishes to be paired with a beverage from their drink menu.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Classic and Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/nashville/graze" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.73557,36.18243,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fattoush Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fattoush Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nashville, TN 37203 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6153211667" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 321-1667</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.fattoushcafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fattoushcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fattoush+Cafe%2C+1716+Charlotte+Avenue%2C+Nashville%2C+TN+37203&amp;ll=36.158782,-86.798449" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1716 Charlotte Avenue<br/>Nashville, TN 37203</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fattoush&#x27;s halal fare is made with olive oil, grains, vegetables and meats found in the Mediterranean region. They serve upclassic Greek cuisine such as salad, falafel, gyros and baklava.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos, Tots and Chops</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/nashville/fattoush-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.79845,36.15878,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Athens Family Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Athens Family Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nashville 37212 &middot; &#9733; 3.9 (12 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6153832848" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 383-2848</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.athensfamilyrestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.athensfamilyrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Athens+Family+Restaurant%2C+2017+Belmont+Blvd%2C+Nashville+37212&amp;ll=36.123306,-86.775861" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2017 Belmont Blvd<br/>Nashville 37212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bacon and Lamb Burgers, Kotopita, Avgolemono Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Athens Family Restaurant, owner Adel Elostta aims for the &quot;best quality for the money.&quot; As Guy learned, that meant giant bacon lamb burgers (made with their &quot;love spice&quot; blend), gargantuan Greek suzukakia meatballs and kotopita, a tasty chicken turnover Guy called his kind of breakfast.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: From Brisket to Bison<br/>Burgers &#x27;n More</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/nashville/athens-family-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.77586,36.12331,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bro&#x27;s Cajun Cuisine</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bro&#x27;s Cajun Cuisine</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nashville 37209 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6153292626" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(615) 329-2626</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.broscajuncuisine.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.broscajuncuisine.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bro%27s+Cajun+Cuisine%2C+3214+Charlotte+Ave%2C+Nashville+37209&amp;ll=36.153247,-86.823405" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3214 Charlotte Ave<br/>Nashville 37209</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crawfish Boil with House Smoked Sausage, Bro&#x27;s &quot;Cajun&quot; Stuffed Pork Chops</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You don&#x27;t normally think about Cajun food in Nashville except when the owners come from Louisiana, like they do at Bro&#x27;s Cajun Cuisine. Get the gumbo, red beans and rice, crawfish cooked in fiery red spices or the Cajun-style pork chops. If the locals say &quot;it is true Cajun food,&quot; then it&#x27;s gotta be!</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Timeless</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/nashville/bros-cajun-cuisine-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.82340,36.15325,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Arnold&#x27;s Country Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Arnold&#x27;s Country Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nashville 37203 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6152564455" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">615-256-4455</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.arnoldscountrykitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.arnoldscountrykitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Arnold%27s+Country+Kitchen%2C+605+8th+Ave+S%2C+Nashville+37203&amp;ll=36.151466,-86.779609" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">605 8th Ave S<br/>Nashville 37203</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern Greens, Chess Pie, Cornbread, Black-Eyed Peas, Sliced Fresh Tomatoes, Country Fried Steak</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The &quot;Meat &amp; 3&quot; (entree and three vegetables) at Arnold&#x27;s Country Kitchen is arguably the best in Nashville, especially with the roast beef. In 2009, they even won a James Beard award. But Guy swung over not for the roast beef but for the plump chicken dumplings and &quot;super tasty&quot;&quot;turnip greens.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old Time Attitude</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tn/nashville/arnolds-country-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.77961,36.15147,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>O So Good</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">O So Good</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Garretson, SD 57030</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6055943600" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(605) 594-3600</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.osogoodgarretson.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.osogoodgarretson.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=O+So+Good%2C+529+N.+Main+Ave.%2C+Garretson%2C+SD+57030&amp;ll=43.715906,-96.503121" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">529 N. Main Ave.<br/>Garretson, SD 57030</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">O So Good Restaurnant combines the love of childhood dishes, street food, 80s food truck fare. O So Good seeks tocreate memories that can be brought back by a single bite or smell of whatever is cooking.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">South Dakota Smorgasbord</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sd/o-so-good-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.50312,43.71591,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Urban Chislic</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Urban Chislic</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sioux Falls, SD 57108 &middot; &#9733; 1.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6052756328" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(605) 275-6328</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sd/sioux-falls/urban-chislic" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sd/sioux-falls/urban-chislic</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Urban+Chislic%2C+431+W.+85th+St.%2C+Sioux+Falls%2C+SD+57108&amp;ll=43.475166,-96.733220" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">431 W. 85th St.<br/>Sioux Falls, SD 57108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Urban Chislic is an eatery dedicated to paying homage to chiclic, the iconic South Dakotan dish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">South Dakota Smorgasbord</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sd/sioux-falls/urban-chislic" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.73322,43.47517,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lalibela</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lalibela</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sioux Falls 57104</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6052710747" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(605) 271-0747</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sd/sioux-falls/lalibela" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sd/sioux-falls/lalibela</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lalibela%2C+200+South+Kiwanis+Ave.%2C+Sioux+Falls+57104&amp;ll=43.545717,-96.760730" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">200 South Kiwanis Ave.<br/>Sioux Falls 57104</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">South Dakota Smorgasbord</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sd/sioux-falls/lalibela" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.76073,43.54572,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Afrah</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Afrah</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richardson, TX 75081 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9722349898" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(972) 234-9898</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://afrah.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">afrah.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Afrah%2C+314+E+Main+St%2C+Richardson%2C+TX+75081&amp;ll=32.947943,-96.728396" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">314 E Main St<br/>Richardson, TX 75081</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Shawarma Pita Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Texas restaurant and pastry shop doesn&#x27;t whip out the typical Southern fare, but instead a Mediterranean menu which has customers and Guy singing, &amp;quot;shawarma, shawarma, shawarma.&amp;quot; But it&#x27;s not just shawarma that keep customers coming -- Afrah&#x27;s homemade baklava has them staying for dessert, too.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">International Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/richardson/afrah-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.72840,32.94794,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Look&#x27;s Market</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Look&#x27;s Market</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sioux Falls, SD 57108 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6053363104" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(605) 336-3104</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.looksmarket.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.looksmarket.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Look%27s+Market%2C+500+E.+69th+St.%2C+Sioux+Falls%2C+SD+57108&amp;ll=43.490252,-96.721764" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">500 E. 69th St.<br/>Sioux Falls, SD 57108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Look&#x27;s Marketplace, established in 1883, began as a family owned and operated business and despite ownership changing over time, its dedication to quality products and excellenct service has not. In addition to serving food, Look&#x27;s Marketplace has a bakery, deli, grocery and wine selections.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Savory Meat and a Little Sweet</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sd/sioux-falls/look-s-marketplace" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.72176,43.49025,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Daily Clean</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Daily Clean</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sioux Falls, SD 57108</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6052711736" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(605) 271-1736</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://dailycleanfood.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">dailycleanfood.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Daily+Clean%2C+6215+South+Western+Avenue%2C+Sioux+Falls%2C+SD+57108&amp;ll=43.467673,-96.747534" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6215 South Western Avenue<br/>Sioux Falls, SD 57108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Daily Clean Food &amp; Drink prepares theirfood and drinks using fresh, local and organic ingredients. They have dishes that are vegan,vegetarian, gluten free and keto, amongst other options. They believe that what goes in food and where it comes from matters to the environment, yourcommunity, and to your health.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rib-Stickers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sd/sioux-falls/daily-clean-food---drink" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.74753,43.46767,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Holy Roller</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Holy Roller</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Austin, TX 78701</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://holyrolleraustin.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">holyrolleraustin.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Holy+Roller%2C+509+Rio+Grande+St%2C+Austin%2C+TX+78701&amp;ll=30.269521,-97.749441" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">509 Rio Grande St<br/>Austin, TX 78701</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meatloaf Sandwich, Monte Bisco</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This rock-and-roll bar serves up brunch and a chill atmosphere all day long. Try the Meatloaf Sandwich made with a unique layer of crispy Parmesan and horseradish sauce. For the adventurous there&#x27;s the Monte Bisco, their take on the Monte Cristo, made with house-made biscuits dusted with powdered sugar, sweet tea-brined turkey, bologna, blackberry-thyme jam and aerated Swiss cheese sauce. &quot;It&#x27;s a beacon of funk ... but it&#x27;s delicious,&quot; said Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwich Showcase</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/austin/holy-roller-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.74944,30.26952,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bread &amp; Circus</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bread &amp; Circus</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sioux Falls, SD 57104</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6053382206" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(605) 338-2206</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.breadandcircussd.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.breadandcircussd.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bread+%26+Circus%2C+600+N.+Main+Ave.+110%2C+Sioux+Falls%2C+SD+57104&amp;ll=43.553987,-96.727905" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">600 N. Main Ave. 110<br/>Sioux Falls, SD 57104</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spicin&#x27; Things Up</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sd/sioux-falls/bread---circus-sandwich-kitchen" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.72791,43.55399,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Home Slice Pizza</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Home Slice Pizza</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Austin 78745 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5124447437" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">512-444-7437</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://homeslicepizza.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">homeslicepizza.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Home+Slice+Pizza%2C+1415+S+Congress+Ave%2C+Austin+78745&amp;ll=30.249272,-97.749515" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1415 S Congress Ave<br/>Austin 78745</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pepperoni Pizza, White Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Home Slice draws the Austin crowds with its New York-style pizzas, which have proven to be so popular that the joint sells 1,000 pies daily. Fans include Tim Love, who frequents the spot for its pepperoni and white slices. Home Slice&#x27;s pepperoni pie is slathered with a rich layer of tomato sauce, dusted with oregano, then hit with a flurry of Parmesan, provolone and mozzarella cheeses before being finished with perfect rounds of pepperoni. The white pizza features a layer of provolone and mozzarella cheeses studded with chopped garlic, mounds of baked ricotta cheese and heaps of blanched spinach. &quot;It tastes like the most amazing sauteed spinach you&#x27;ve ever had in your life,&quot; Love says.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: A Taste of Italy</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/austin/home-slice-pizza-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.74952,30.24927,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Taste of Europe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Taste of Europe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Arlington, TX 76013 &middot; &#9733; 4.6 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8172755530" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(817) 275-5530</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tasteofeuropetx.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tasteofeuropetx.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Taste+of+Europe%2C+1901+W.+Pioneer+Parkway%2C+Arlington%2C+TX+76013&amp;ll=32.709351,-97.136834" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1901 W. Pioneer Parkway<br/>Arlington, TX 76013</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Potato Pancakes, Cabbage Rolls, Russian Sweets</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Where can you &amp;quot;eat while you shop and shop while you eat&amp;quot;? At this Russian comfort food eatery, of course! Chef Irina Pavlova, a Russian native, served Guy potato pancakes with meat inside, which he described as &amp;quot;crispy, creamy and salty.&amp;quot; Customers enjoy the cabbage rolls and Russian sweets.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dynamic Dishes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/arlington/taste-of-europe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.13683,32.70935,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jamaica Gates Caribbean Cuisine</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jamaica Gates Caribbean Cuisine</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Arlington, TX 76013 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8177952600" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(817) 795-2600</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.jamaicagates.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jamaicagates.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jamaica+Gates+Caribbean+Cuisine%2C+1020+W+Arkansas+Lane%2C+Arlington%2C+TX+76013&amp;ll=32.706094,-97.119118" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1020 W Arkansas Lane<br/>Arlington, TX 76013</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Curry Goat, Goat Head Soup, Whole Red Snapper</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Locals flock to this restaurant for its authentic Jamaican home cooking. Guy enjoyed the &amp;quot;delicious heat&amp;quot; found in the curry goat. The goat head soup was &amp;quot;full flavored&amp;quot; and had tender pieces of goat. The savory and slightly spicy stewed and fried whole red snapper is a fan favorite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Who&#x27;Da Thunk It?</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/arlington/jamaica-gates-caribbean-cuisine-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.11912,32.70609,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Prince Lebanese Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Prince Lebanese Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Arlington, TX 76011 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8174691811" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">817-469-1811</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://princelebanesegrill.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">princelebanesegrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Prince+Lebanese+Grill%2C+502+W+Randol+Mill+Rd%2C+Arlington%2C+TX+76011&amp;ll=32.749758,-97.111803" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">502 W Randol Mill Rd<br/>Arlington, TX 76011</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Falafel, Pilaf, Mashwi Shish (Beef Tenderloin)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Prince Lebanese Grill channels the flavors of the Mediterranean, with familiar classics such as falafel, shawarma and tabbouleh, and some things you may have never tried before. You must get the Middle Eastern Breakfast Pizza made with za&#x27;atar - a spice blend pesto pasted on a warmed pita.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Global Grub<br/>Triple D Nation: Cultural Cookin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/arlington/prince-lebanese-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.11180,32.74976,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Chop House Burgers</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Chop House Burgers</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Arlington 76016 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6822132253" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">682-213-2253</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.theoriginalchophouseburgers.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.theoriginalchophouseburgers.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Chop+House+Burgers%2C+2502+Little+Rd%2C+Arlington+76016&amp;ll=32.720597,-97.145530" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2502 Little Rd<br/>Arlington 76016</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chop House Burger, Gumbo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this burger joint Chef Kenny Mills is cooking up real deal burgers with a twist. The Chop House Burger has a mixed patty of brisket and beef, which Guy claims is &quot;outstanding.&quot; Football player Earl Campbell loves the gumbo made with his sausage, crab and crawfish and served over rice.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crankin&#x27; Up the Classics<br/>Legends of Texas</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/tx/arlington/chop-house-burgers-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.14553,32.72060,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Percy Street Barbecue</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Percy Street Barbecue</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19147 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2156258510" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(215) 625-8510</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.percystreet.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.percystreet.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Percy+Street+Barbecue%2C+900+South+St%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19147&amp;ll=39.942585,-75.157096" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">900 South St<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19147</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Barbecue Ribs, Pork Belly Sandwich, Brisket Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Percy Street Barbecue has built up a reputation for having some of the best barbecue in Philadelphia, and Guy needed only one word to describe the ribs: &#x27;&#x27;ridiculous.&#x27;&#x27; Owner Erin O&#x27;Shea also serves up unconventional (but still delicious) fare, like a pork belly sandwich.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big-Time Barbecue<br/>Kings and Queens of &#x27;Cue</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/percy-street-barbecue" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.15710,39.94258,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Stogie Joe&#x27;s Tavern</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Stogie Joe&#x27;s Tavern</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia 19148 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2154633030" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(215) 463-3030</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.stogiejoestavern.net/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.stogiejoestavern.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Stogie+Joe%27s+Tavern%2C+1801+East+Passyunk+Ave%2C+Philadelphia+19148&amp;ll=39.927562,-75.165986" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1801 East Passyunk Ave<br/>Philadelphia 19148</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Three brothers from Philly took over a local tavern to bring the Italian recipes they loved growing up to the neighborhood. At Stogie Joe&#x27;s Tavern, the Leuzzi brothers are sharing their mother&#x27;s best recipes including her Sunday crab gravy. &quot;It&#x27;s flavorcity,&quot; said Guy of the sauce. They are also cranking out memorable square pizzas. The Stogie Joe&#x27;s Pizza is made with house-made, hand-stretched mozzarella-layered dough and topped with sopressata, fresh tomato sauce and a sprinkling of asiago. Once out of the oven the crispy pie is finished with a shower of fresh basil. Guy called it a &quot;dynamite pie.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Filling Up on Philly</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/stogie-joes-tavern-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.16599,39.92756,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Standard Tap</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Standard Tap</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19123 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2122380630" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(212) 238-0630</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.standardtap.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.standardtap.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Standard+Tap%2C+901+N+2nd+St%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19123&amp;ll=39.964156,-75.140448" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">901 N 2nd St<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19123</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grilled Octopus with Oregano Potato Salad, Chicken Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The menu at Standard Tap in Philadelphia is far from standard - for example, check out the grilled octopus served with an oregano potato salad. There&#x27;s also chicken pie (no pot necessary), covered in a flaky pastry crust that left Guy yearning for more.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pub Grub<br/>A Festival of Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/standard-tap-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.14045,39.96416,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>South Philadelphia Tap Room</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">South Philadelphia Tap Room</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19145 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2152717787" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(215) 271-7787</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://southphiladelphiataproom.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">southphiladelphiataproom.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=South+Philadelphia+Tap+Room%2C+1509+Mifflin+St%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19145&amp;ll=39.927273,-75.171461" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1509 Mifflin St<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19145</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried PB&amp;J, Ricotta Donuts, Wild Boar Head Cheese Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This South Philly neighborhood bar takes the beloved PB&amp;amp;J to the next level by breading it with frosted flakes and then deep-frying it. Guy loved the &amp;quot;big flavor&amp;quot; from the ricotta donuts and was surprised by the &amp;quot;outrageous&amp;quot; taste of the wild boar head cheese tacos with homemade salsa and guacamole.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Traditional Gone Wild<br/>Deep Fried All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/south-philadelphia-tap-room-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.17146,39.92727,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sidecar Bar and Grille</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sidecar Bar and Grille</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19146 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2157323429" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(215) 732-3429</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thesidecarbar.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thesidecarbar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sidecar+Bar+and+Grille%2C+2201+Christian+St%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19146&amp;ll=39.941841,-75.179490" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2201 Christian St<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19146</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">New England Clam Chowder with Gnocchi</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At The Sidecar Bar &amp;amp; Grille, head chef Brian Lofink put his own spin on New England clam chowder by adding gnocchi to the mix. The result is a dish that left Guy so amazed that he declared it &#x27;&#x27;literally one of the best gnocchi dishes&amp;quot; ever.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken, Chili and Chowder</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/sidecar-bar-and-grille-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.17949,39.94184,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Silk City Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Silk City Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19123 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2155928838" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">215-592-8838</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.silkcityphilly.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.silkcityphilly.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Silk+City+Diner%2C+435+Spring+Garden+St%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19123&amp;ll=39.961333,-75.146049" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">435 Spring Garden St<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19123</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Empanadas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">As a lifelong foodie, Mark Bee offers more than just the standard diner fare at his joint. Guy was left impressed by menu items such as duck confit spring rolls and pulled pork empanadas. &quot;That is an orchestra right there; that&#x27;s a medley of just great flavor,&quot; Guy said of the empanadas. They start with fresh ham, which is cooked down with a mix of chili powders and spices, then shredded and layered with sweet potatoes&lt;b&gt;; &lt;/b&gt;they&#x27;re finished in a fried dough pocket slicked with a chipotle-honey glaze.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Real-Deal Diners<br/>Totally Fried</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/silk-city-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.14605,39.96133,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dump City Dumplings</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dump City Dumplings</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bend, OR 97703 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5413236243" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(541) 323-6243</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.dumpcitydumplings.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.dumpcitydumplings.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dump+City+Dumplings%2C+384+SW+Upper+Terrace+Dr.%2C+Bend%2C+OR+97703&amp;ll=44.046430,-121.310977" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">384 SW Upper Terrace Dr.<br/>Bend, OR 97703</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You can visit Dump City&#x27;s restaurant or food cart to try one of their dumpling varieties, including Four Cheese Pizza, vegan Pad Thai and Chinese style Pork.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Traditional Twists</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/bend/dump-city-dumplings" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.31098,44.04643,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rockin&#x27; Dave&#x27;s Bagel Bisto</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rockin&#x27; Dave&#x27;s Bagel Bisto</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bend 97701 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5413188177" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(541) 318-8177</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://rockindaves.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">rockindaves.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rockin%27+Dave%27s+Bagel+Bisto%2C+661+NE+Greenwood+Ave.%2C+Bend+97701&amp;ll=44.059730,-121.296130" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">661 NE Greenwood Ave.<br/>Bend 97701</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">David Flier, a lover of food and a lover of music, combined his loves to create Rockin&#x27; Dave&#x27;s Bagel Bistro &amp; Backstage Lounge. At this friendly, casual dining restaurant, patrons can customize a bagel order, choose from an extensive menu with vegan and gluten-free options or enjoy the surprise monthly special.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwiches and Spice</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/bend/rockin-daves-bistro" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.29613,44.05973,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Zydeco</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Zydeco</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bend, OR 97701 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5413122899" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(541) 312-2899</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://zydecokitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">zydecokitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Zydeco%2C+919+Bond+St.%2C+Bend%2C+OR+97701&amp;ll=44.058669,-121.313192" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">919 Bond St.<br/>Bend, OR 97701</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Steve Helt serves up familiarNorthwestern dishes made with aSouthern twist and cocktails. Zydeco&#x27;s offers a gluten-free menu, so that there is something on the menu for everyone.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Regional Flavors</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/bend/zydeco-kitchen---cocktails" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.31319,44.05867,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Junkyard Extreme Burgers and Brats</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Junkyard Extreme Burgers and Brats</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Junction City, OR 97448 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5419983232" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(541) 998-3232</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Junkyard-Extreme-Burgers-and-Brats/203890448085?sk=info&amp;ref=page_internal" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Junkyard-Extreme-Burgers-and-Brats/203890448085?sk=info&amp;ref=page_internal</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Junkyard+Extreme+Burgers+and+Brats%2C+95410+Highway+99+E%2C+Junction+City%2C+OR+97448&amp;ll=44.270625,-123.235219" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">95410 Highway 99 E<br/>Junction City, OR 97448</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big Block, Fried Cheese Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Junkyard Extreme Burgers and Brats boasts the craziest menu, and it&#x27;s also the only restaurant in town. The Big Block is their signature burger with 1 pound of meat, bacon, what Guy estimates to be about a cup of cheese, and more. There&#x27;s also the fried cheese pizza with four different cheeses.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Small Town Standouts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/junction-city/junkyard-extreme-burgers-and-brats" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-123.23522,44.27063,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pineville Tavern</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pineville Tavern</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Pineville, PA 18946 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2155983890" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(215) 598-3890</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pinevilletavern.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pinevilletavern.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pineville+Tavern%2C+Route+413+Durham+Rd%2C+Pineville%2C+PA+18946&amp;ll=40.296261,-75.005733" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Route 413 Durham Rd<br/>Pineville, PA 18946</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Snapper Soup, Ravioli and Marinara Sauce</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This family owned and operated diner is famous for its Snapper Soup. Guy recommends this &amp;quot;savory&amp;quot; gravylike soup, which has chewy chunks of snapper turtle, to those who want to try something different. Pasta lovers should come here for the &amp;quot;perfectly balanced&amp;quot; handmade ravioli and marinara sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Soup and Sandwiches</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/pineville/pineville-tavern-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.00573,40.29626,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Starlite Lounge</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Starlite Lounge</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Blawnox 15238 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4128289842" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(412) 828-9842</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.starlite-lounge.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.starlite-lounge.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Starlite+Lounge%2C+364+Freeport+Road%2C+Blawnox+15238&amp;ll=40.493969,-79.860283" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">364 Freeport Road<br/>Blawnox 15238</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pierogis, Stuffed Green Pepper Soup, Chicken Diablo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pierogi and stuffed pepper soup might not be the first dishes that come to mind when someone thinks of a bar outside of Pittsburgh, but the Starlite Lounge has attracted locals for over 50 years. When Guy tried the Chicken Diablo, he said that owner Ron Esser&#x27;s homegrown peppers were &#x27;&#x27;dynamite.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bar Food<br/>Pub Grub</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/blawnox/starlite-lounge-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-79.86028,40.49397,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nadine&#x27;s Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nadine&#x27;s Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Pittsburgh, PA 15203 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4124811793" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(412) 481-1793</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.nadinesbar.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.nadinesbar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nadine%27s+Restaurant%2C+19+S+27th+St%2C+Pittsburgh%2C+PA+15203&amp;ll=40.426387,-79.967209" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">19 S 27th St<br/>Pittsburgh, PA 15203</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roast Beef Sandwich, Fried Bologna Sandwich, Na&#x27;s Pasta (Meat and Noodle Dish)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nadine&#x27;s in Pittsburgh provides homemade food with home-style comfort; owner Nadine Voelker even puts up birthday banners for her restaurant&#x27;s many regulars. Specialties include roast beef, fried bologna and - Guy&#x27;s favorite - Na&#x27;s Pasta, piled high with sausage, salami and ham.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cookin&#x27; It Old School</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/pittsburgh/nadines-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-79.96721,40.42639,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dor-Stop Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dor-Stop Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Pittsburgh, PA 15216 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4125619320" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">412-561-9320</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://thedorstoprestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">thedorstoprestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dor-Stop+Restaurant%2C+1430+Potomac+Ave%2C+Pittsburgh%2C+PA+15216&amp;ll=40.396012,-80.034727" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1430 Potomac Ave<br/>Pittsburgh, PA 15216</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Peanut Butter and Pumpkin Pancakes, Dor-Stop Burger, Steak &amp; Cheese Hoagie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pittsburgh locals know when it&#x27;s time for breakfast, it&#x27;s time for Dor-Stop. On Triple D, Guy swung by this family operation serving sweet pumpkin hotcakes and crunchy raspberry French toast. For egg lovers, try Jumbot, a mix of eggs, sausage, green bell peppers and &amp;quot;anything you would want.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">What&#x27;s For Breakfast</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/pittsburgh/dor-stop-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.03473,40.39601,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Big Jim&#x27;s in &quot;The Run&quot;</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Big Jim&#x27;s in &quot;The Run&quot;</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Pittsburgh, PA 15207 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4124210532" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(412) 421-0532</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bigjimsrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bigjimsrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Big+Jim%27s+in+%22The+Run%22%2C+201+Saline+St%2C+Pittsburgh%2C+PA+15207&amp;ll=40.427101,-79.949612" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">201 Saline St<br/>Pittsburgh, PA 15207</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Reuben, Big Jim&#x27;s Club</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Big Jim&#x27;s in &amp;quot;The Run,&amp;quot; diners rarely leave hungry. The signature veal Parmesan sandwich nearly matches the width of Guy&#x27;s head, which Guy deemed &amp;quot;ridiculous.&amp;quot; The hefty portion sizes don&#x27;t end there. Big Jim&#x27;s calzone packs a punch with ham, salami, capocollo, pepperoni, provolone and veggies.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Long Time Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/pittsburgh/big-jims-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-79.94961,40.42710,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Crystal On Penn (UNDER NEW OWNERSHIP)</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Crystal On Penn (UNDER NEW OWNERSHIP)</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Pittsburgh, PA 15222</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4124340480" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(412) 434-0480</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.crystalonpenn.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.crystalonpenn.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Crystal+On+Penn+%28UNDER+NEW+OWNERSHIP%29%2C+1211+Penn+Avenue%2C+Pittsburgh%2C+PA+15222&amp;ll=40.446124,-79.992252" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1211 Penn Avenue<br/>Pittsburgh, PA 15222</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hummus, Tabbouli, Kibbee</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Join host, Guy Fieri, of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, as he discovers authentic Lebanese cuisine at Crystal On Penn in Pittsburgh, PA.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Taste of Everywhere</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/pittsburgh/crystal-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-79.99225,40.44612,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Kelly O&#x27;s Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Kelly O&#x27;s Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Pittsburgh, PA 15237 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4123640473" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(412) 364-0473</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.kellyosdiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.kellyosdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Kelly+O%27s+Diner%2C+1130+Perry+Hwy%2C+Pittsburgh%2C+PA+15237&amp;ll=40.548191,-80.035441" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1130 Perry Hwy<br/>Pittsburgh, PA 15237</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Haluski (Noodles, Bacon, Cabbage), Fried Polenta with Veal Bolognese Sauce, Turkey Pot Pie Sauce</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Although Kelly O&#x27;Connor opened her diner with no cooking experience, she was armed with a handful of family recipes. Guy swung by for a DDD first: haluski. The Polish dish is made with egg noodles, onions, cabbage and bacon. For another tasty bite, try Kelly&#x27;s &amp;quot;winner-winner&amp;quot; turkey pot pie soup.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Regional Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/pittsburgh/kelly-os-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.03544,40.54819,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Woodrow&#x27;s Sandwich Shop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Woodrow&#x27;s Sandwich Shop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19147 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.woodrowsandwich.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.woodrowsandwich.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Woodrow%27s+Sandwich+Shop%2C+630+South+St%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19147&amp;ll=39.941971,-75.153226" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">630 South St<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19147</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">There&#x27;s always something new and delicious to try at this sandwich joint, and the Woodrow&#x27;s Whiz Wit is just one example. Chef and owner Kevin Kramer adds his own twist on the classic Philly cheesesteak with his homemade cherry pepper mayo. &quot;The cherry pepper mayo has a little bit of acidity,&quot; Guy said, &quot;which is really key and essential.&quot; Cheesesteak veterans and newbies alike will also fall for the homemade whiz, which is a creamy cheese sauce that&#x27;s traditionally served on top of the shaved beef. Kevin&#x27;s take on whiz features four different types of cheese and sliced truffle, and its flavors impressed Guy. &quot;It takes cheesesteak to another level!&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Authentic to Inventive</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/woodrows-sandwich-shop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.15323,39.94197,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Dining Car &amp; Market</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Dining Car &amp; Market</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19136 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2153385113" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(215) 338-5113</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thediningcar.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thediningcar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Dining+Car+%26+Market%2C+8826+Frankford+Ave%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19136&amp;ll=40.050142,-75.011149" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">8826 Frankford Ave<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19136</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chipped Beef, Crepes, Chicken Croquettes, Scrapple (Deep Fried Pork Scraps), French Onion Soup, &quot;Philly Best&quot; Jewish Apple Cake, Apple Walnut Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Dining Car &amp;amp; Market&#x27;s philosophy is simple: &amp;quot;Get what you like...like what you get!&amp;quot; Add to that, get it anytime you like. This 24/7 operation boasts a menu Guy couldn&#x27;t believe. It&#x27;s all about classic comfort foods, like chip beef, &amp;quot;funkadelic&amp;quot; chicken croquettes and crepes with ham and Swiss.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">East Coast Cruisin&#x27;<br/>Open 24/7</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/the-dining-car-market-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.01115,40.05014,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Beacon Drive-In</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Beacon Drive-In</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Spartanburg, SC 29306 &middot; &#9733; 3.2 (16 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8645859387" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(864) 585-9387</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.beacondrivein.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.beacondrivein.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Beacon+Drive-In%2C+255+John+B.+White+Sr.++Blvd%2C+Spartanburg%2C+SC+29306&amp;ll=34.940268,-81.943196" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">255 John B. White Sr.  Blvd<br/>Spartanburg, SC 29306</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chili Cheeseburger A-Plenty (with Onion Rings and Fries Piled On), Beacon Iced Tea, Sliced Pork-A-Plenty, Onion Rings, Ice Cream at the &quot;The Beacon Dairy Bar&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Everyone&#x27;s had a hamburger before, but how about a Hamburger-a-Plenty? It&#x27;s a burger covered in fries and onion rings, and the only place to find it is at the Beacon Drive-In in Spartanburg, S.C. This 60-year-old institution also serves chili and chicken stew, which Guy thought was &#x27;&#x27;so good.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners, Drive-ins and Dives<br/>Diners A-Plenty</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/spartanburg/the-beacon-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.94320,34.94027,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mom Mom&#x27;s Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mom Mom&#x27;s Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19137</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.mommomnomnom.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mommomnomnom.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mom+Mom%27s+Kitchen%2C+2551+Orthodox+St%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19137&amp;ll=40.000995,-75.076618" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2551 Orthodox St<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19137</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Self-taught chefs Kaitlin Wines and Ryan Elmore created this soulful Eastern European food spot as an homage to Kaitlin&#x27;s &quot;mom mom,&quot; or grandma. This Philly joint boasts a scratch-made menu with a mix of traditional Polish dishes and new generation flavors. Their Philly Cheesesteak Pierogis are a perfect example of this unique fusion as they are made with a homemade traditional pierogi dough, stuffed with tender ribeye and served with tangy sour cream, caramelized onions and black pepper ketchup. &quot;It&#x27;s silky, luxurious melts in your mouth,&quot; said Guy. &quot;It&#x27;s absolutely wrecking regular cheesesteaks for me right now.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pierogis, Pork and Pizza</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/mom-moms-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.07662,40.00100,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Memphis Taproom</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Memphis Taproom</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19125 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2154254460" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">215-425-4460</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.memphistaproom.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.memphistaproom.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Memphis+Taproom%2C+2331+East+Cumberland+St%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19125&amp;ll=39.980369,-75.123015" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2331 East Cumberland St<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19125</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Coconut Club</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Memphis Taproom diners are used to the unique menu from Chef Jesse Kimball. But Guy&#x27;s Triple D visit left him totally wowed. The watermelon, arugula and pork belly salad was just like a &quot;picnic basket&quot; in Guy&#x27;s mouth -- but the vegan Smoked Coconut Club with tomato mayo was completely off the hook.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Pork to Tofu<br/>Deep-Fried Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/memphis-taproom-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.12301,39.98037,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pawleys Front Porch</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pawleys Front Porch</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Columbia, SC 29205 &middot; &#9733; 3.2 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8037718001" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(803) 771-8001</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pawleysfrontporch.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pawleysfrontporch.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pawleys+Front+Porch%2C+827+Harden+St.%2C+Columbia%2C+SC+29205&amp;ll=34.000989,-81.017307" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">827 Harden St.<br/>Columbia, SC 29205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roasted Jalapeno Pimento Cheese, Burgers, Fish Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Guy and the Triple D crew headed out to visit Pawleys Front Porch, they were in for big burger flavor, done 10 different ways. The half-pound Fripp Island Burger gets loaded with a hefty smothering of &amp;quot;out-of-bounds&amp;quot; Boursin cheese and a crispy fried green tomato.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">And The Kicker Is...</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/columbia/pawleys-front-porch-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.01731,34.00099,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Three Angels Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Three Angels Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Memphis, TN 38112</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9014521111" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(901) 452-1111</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://threeangelsdiner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">threeangelsdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Three+Angels+Diner%2C+2617+Broad+Ave%2C+Memphis%2C+TN+38112&amp;ll=35.147585,-89.972173" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2617 Broad Ave<br/>Memphis, TN 38112</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Adult Grilled Cheese, Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this kid-friendly diner the mom-and-pop duo are putting a fresh spin on American classics. The fried chicken with corn on the cob and turnip greens impressed Guy. Diners also like to order the adult grilled cheese with smoked Gouda, goat and cheddar cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Family, All the Time</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ri/memphis/three-angels-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-89.97217,35.14759,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Anthony&#x27;s Seafood</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Anthony&#x27;s Seafood</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Middletown, RI 02842 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4018469620" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(401) 846-9620</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://anthonysseafood.net/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">anthonysseafood.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Anthony%27s+Seafood%2C+963+Aquidneck+Ave%2C+Middletown%2C+RI+02842&amp;ll=41.514290,-71.281958" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">963 Aquidneck Ave<br/>Middletown, RI 02842</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Stuffed Quahogs, Kung Pao Calamari</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Whether you&#x27;re a wholesale buyer, home chef or restaurant-goer, look no further than this market and restaurant where the seafood is always fresh. Guy loved the kick from the chourico and the &amp;quot;big clam flavor&amp;quot; he got from the stuffed quahogs. If you want something unique, try the Kung Pao calamari.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Noodles and Quahogs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ri/middletown/anthonys-seafood-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.28196,41.51429,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Italian Corner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Italian Corner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">East Providence, RI 02914 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4014311737" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(401) 431-1737</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.italiancorner-ri.com/default.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.italiancorner-ri.com/default.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Italian+Corner%2C+10+Boyd+Ave%2C+East+Providence%2C+RI+02914&amp;ll=41.808090,-71.348584" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">10 Boyd Ave<br/>East Providence, RI 02914</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brasato Sandwich, Tortellini Bolognese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Everything at this authentic Italian deli is from Italy including the recipes, the pasta machines and even the chef. The brasato sandwich special on a fresh-baked roll had Guy&#x27;s mouth watering. If you come on the weekend for dinner, Guy suggests ordering the homemade tortellini bolognese with ragu.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Amazing Italian<br/>Handcrafted</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ri/east-providence/italian-corner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.34858,41.80809,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Evelyn&#x27;s Drive In</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Evelyn&#x27;s Drive In</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tiverton, RI 02878 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4016243100" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(401) 624-3100</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.evelynsdrivein.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.evelynsdrivein.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Evelyn%27s+Drive+In%2C+2335+Main+Rd%2C+Tiverton%2C+RI+02878&amp;ll=41.616108,-71.200181" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2335 Main Rd<br/>Tiverton, RI 02878</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rhode Island Chowder, Fried Clams, Clam Cakes, Lobster Chow Mein</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy Fieri, host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, rips into some amazing fried clams, clam cakes and lobster chow mein at Evelyn&#x27;s Drive-In, in Tiverton, RI, a local legend where people arrive by boat.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Best of the Beach<br/>Seaside Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ri/tiverton/evelyns-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.20018,41.61611,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Edgewood Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Edgewood Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cranston, RI 02905</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4013835550" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(401) 383-5550</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://edgewoodcafe.com/Edgewood_Cafe_Cranston,_Rhode_Island_RI.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">edgewoodcafe.com/Edgewood_Cafe_Cranston,_Rhode_Island_RI.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Edgewood+Cafe%2C+1864+Broad+St%2C+Cranston%2C+RI+02905&amp;ll=41.774939,-71.398333" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1864 Broad St<br/>Cranston, RI 02905</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Little Necks over Pasta, Fish and Chips, Garlic Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this dive, Chef John Walsh is serving up classic comfort food with a gourmet twist. The littlenecks over pasta and served with toaster points was Guy&#x27;s favorite. Loyal customers order the fish and chips and garlic fries and a mud pie for dessert.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pubs and Grub</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ri/cranston/edgewood-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.39833,41.77494,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Crazy Burger Cafe &amp; Juice Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Crazy Burger Cafe &amp; Juice Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Narragansett, RI 02882 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4017831810" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">401-783-1810</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.crazyburger.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.crazyburger.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Crazy+Burger+Cafe+%26+Juice+Bar%2C+144+Boon+St%2C+Narragansett%2C+RI+02882&amp;ll=41.425976,-71.459599" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">144 Boon St<br/>Narragansett, RI 02882</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Whassupy Burger, Luna-Sea Fish Burge, Vegan Tofu Tacos, Mega Berry Smoothie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Guy visited Crazy Burger Cafe &amp;amp; Juice Bar, he marveled at the menu featuring more than 30 burgers, including the roasted tempeh Poco Loco Vegan Burger or the Mahi Mahi Taco Burger. But Guy couldn&#x27;t resist the Whassupy Burger made with melted Brie cheese and a sesame-fennel-wasabi spice mix.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">East Coast Cruisin&#x27;<br/>Stacked, Stuffed and Loaded</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ri/narragansett/crazy-burger-cafe-juice-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.45960,41.42598,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Aunt Carrie&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Aunt Carrie&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Narragansett, RI 02882 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4017837930" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(401) 783-7930</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://auntcarriesri.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">auntcarriesri.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Aunt+Carrie%27s%2C+1240+Ocean+Rd%2C+Narragansett%2C+RI+02882&amp;ll=41.372758,-71.485080" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1240 Ocean Rd<br/>Narragansett, RI 02882</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Clam Cakes, Strawberry Shortcakes, Fresh Steamers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After a day out on the beach, stop in at this third-generation family-owned diner for some fresh seafood classics. Guy loved the clam cakes, which he said were &amp;quot;simply done and done to perfection.&amp;quot; For dessert Guy recommends the homemade strawberry shortcake. Locals like the fresh steamers.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Deep Fried All-Stars<br/>Food Done Right</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ri/narragansett/aunt-carries-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.48508,41.37276,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Glass Onion</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Glass Onion</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charleston, SC 29407 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8432251717" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">843-225-1717</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.ilovetheglassonion.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.ilovetheglassonion.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Glass+Onion%2C+1219+Savannah+Hwy%2C+Charleston%2C+SC+29407&amp;ll=32.783800,-79.998069" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1219 Savannah Hwy<br/>Charleston, SC 29407</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Chicken with Collard Greens, Smoked Pork Loin Po&#x27;Boy, Shrimp and Grits, Fried Quail</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this restaurant, 5-star Southern food inspired by local ingredients is being served at 1-star prices. The fried chicken with collard greens and mashed potatoes is tender and &amp;quot;pull-apart good,&amp;quot; according to Guy Fieri. For Buddy Valastro, the shrimp-and-grits plate is a winner. A sausage-studded gravy elevates this Southern staple into a &quot;luscious dish with layers of flavor,&quot; Buddy says.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crazy for Chicken<br/>Long Standing Legacies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/charleston/the-glass-onion-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-79.99807,32.78380,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Early Bird Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Early Bird Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charleston, SC 29407 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8432772353" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(843) 277-2353</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.earlybirddiner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.earlybirddiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Early+Bird+Diner%2C+1644+Savannah+Hwy.%2C+Charleston%2C+SC+29407&amp;ll=32.787324,-80.014020" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1644 Savannah Hwy.<br/>Charleston, SC 29407</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken and Waffles, Fried Pork Chop</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this diner you can get breakfast for dinner or dinner for breakfast. According to Guy, &amp;quot;the savory, sweet, crunchy and salty&amp;quot; sensations from the chicken and waffles &amp;quot;seem so wrong, but are just so right.&amp;quot; Locals appreciate the sweet and spicy kick from the pepper jelly on the fried pork chop.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Multitaskers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/charleston/the-early-bird-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.01402,32.78732,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tattooed Moose</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tattooed Moose</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charleston, SC 29403 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8432772990" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(843) 277-2990</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://tattooedmoose.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">tattooedmoose.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tattooed+Moose%2C+1137+Morrison+Dr%2C+Charleston%2C+SC+29403&amp;ll=32.811371,-79.949359" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1137 Morrison Dr<br/>Charleston, SC 29403</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mike&#x27;s Famous Duck Club, Lucky #1 Sub</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this husband and wife-run bar, they supply markers for drawing on the tables and serve delicious food. The Duck Club with duck confit, bacon, cheddar and garlic aioli proved to be a tasty mouthful for Guy. Locals love the &amp;quot;Lucky #1&amp;quot; Sub with pork belly, kimchi, wasabi mayo and sweet chili sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meat Madness<br/>Late Night Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/charleston/tattooed-moose-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-79.94936,32.81137,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jamaican Jerk Hut</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jamaican Jerk Hut</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19146</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2155458644" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(215) 545-8644</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.jajerkhut.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jajerkhut.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jamaican+Jerk+Hut%2C+1436+South+St%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19146&amp;ll=39.943576,-75.166824" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1436 South St<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19146</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jerk Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owner Lisa Wilson and the rest of the staff at the Jamaican Jerk Hut pride themselves on authenticity - it&#x27;s the only Jamaican restaurant in the area with a charcoal jerk pit. Guy chowed down on the &#x27;&#x27;melt-in-your mouth&#x27;&#x27; jerk chicken, complete with a sauce made with Scotch bonnet peppers.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Timeless Traditions</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/jamaican-jerk-hut" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.16682,39.94358,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hardena Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hardena Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia 19145</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2152719442" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(215) 271.9442</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.hardenaphilly.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hardenaphilly.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hardena+Restaurant%2C+1754+S+Hicks+Street%2C+Philadelphia+19145&amp;ll=39.928446,-75.171266" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1754 S Hicks Street<br/>Philadelphia 19145</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Hardena, chef and owner Diana Widjojo is serving up Indonesian specialties with her mother Ena and her sister Lia. One of their stand-outs are the Tempeh Fritters which are made with house-fermented tempeh and spicy pickled veggies. &quot;The tempeh is the bomb,&quot; said Guy. Another must-have is the spicy ginger chicken. The chicken is first poached in spices, ginger paste, and coconut milk and then fried in a coating of ginger paste until crispy. It is served with rice and a house-made spicy sambal sauce. Guy loved it, saying, &quot;This is the Indonesian embassy of Flavortown.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Filling Up on Philly</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/hardena-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.17127,39.92845,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Honey&#x27;s Sit &#x27;n Eat</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Honey&#x27;s Sit &#x27;n Eat</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19123 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2159251150" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(215) 925-1150</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.honeyssitneat.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.honeyssitneat.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Honey%27s+Sit+%27n+Eat%2C+800+N+4th+St%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19123&amp;ll=39.963904,-75.144506" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">800 N 4th St<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19123</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Frito Platter, Chicken Chili Frito Pie, Matzo Ball Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This family restaurant is serving up Southern classics with Jewish flair. Guy thought the brisket Frito platter with twice-cooked brisket topped with corn chips was &amp;quot;incredibly enjoyable.&amp;quot; The chicken chili Frito pie garnered praise for its guajillo chicken. Locals enjoy the matzo ball soup.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Quirky Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/honeys-sit-n-eat-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.14451,39.96390,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Gaul &amp; Co. Malt House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Gaul &amp; Co. Malt House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia 19134 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.gaulandco.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.gaulandco.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Gaul+%26+Co.+Malt+House%2C+3133+Gaul+St%2C+Philadelphia+19134&amp;ll=39.986123,-75.106546" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3133 Gaul St<br/>Philadelphia 19134</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gaul &amp; Co. Malt House is a corner bar that&#x27;s serving up next-level food. Their popular buffalo wings are brined, baked and then fried until crisp and tossed in their house-made sauce. &quot;I&#x27;m impressed,&quot; said Guy, who&#x27;s had more than a few wings in his travels. The Wit or Witoutski, their take on a Philly cheesesteak, is made with house-made shaved kielbasa and house-made American cheese sauce. &quot;It&#x27;s unique. I don&#x27;t think I&#x27;ve ever had anything like it,&quot; said Guy. &quot;That is a destination sandwich.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Filling Up on Philly</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/gaul-and-co-malt-house-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.10655,39.98612,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Geechee Girl Rice Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Geechee Girl Rice Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19119 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2158438113" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">215-843-8113</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.geecheegirlricecafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.geecheegirlricecafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Geechee+Girl+Rice+Cafe%2C+6825+Germantown+Ave%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19119&amp;ll=40.054974,-75.186812" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6825 Germantown Ave<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19119</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">North African Chicken, Pulled Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Geechee Girl Rice Cafe; in Mount Airy, Pa., owner Valerie Erwin&#x27;s most popular dish is her take on North African chicken. Guy was surprised that the chicken was &#x27;&#x27;light but well-rounded,&#x27;&#x27; and he said the greens were up there with the best greens he&#x27;s ever had. Also try the pulled pork with slaw.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Pound Cake to Pot Pie</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/geechee-girl-rice-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.18681,40.05497,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Good Dog Bar &amp; Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Good Dog Bar &amp; Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19102-3806 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2159859600" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(215) 985-9600</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.gooddogbar.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.gooddogbar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Good+Dog+Bar+%26+Restaurant%2C+224+S+15th+St%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19102-3806&amp;ll=39.948781,-75.166320" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">224 S 15th St<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19102-3806</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Duck Pot Pie, Truffle Cheesesteak Empanadas, Stuffed Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy goes inside a 100-year-old building and finds the comfort food joint is filled with &amp;quot;mean libations, and the food&#x27;s on point.&amp;quot; You&#x27;ll get upscale comfort dishes like stuffed burgers on brioche, truffled cheesesteak empanadas and duck confit pot pie. It&#x27;s good food, good beer and great staff.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fresh, Filled and Fried</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/good-dog-bar-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.16632,39.94878,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Farmer&#x27;s Keep</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Farmer&#x27;s Keep</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Philadelphia, PA 19103 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.farmerskeep.com/home" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.farmerskeep.com/home</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Farmer%27s+Keep%2C+10+South+20th+St%2C+Philadelphia%2C+PA+19103&amp;ll=39.952876,-75.173491" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">10 South 20th St<br/>Philadelphia, PA 19103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Philadelphia joint is the perfect place to find good, fast and healthy food. Chef Josh Bullock mashes up creativity, local farm-fresh foods and a healthy attitude with his flavorful dishes that are completely allergen-free and health-conscious, like their Whiskey Cola Chicken with Beets and Sweets. The tender chicken is doused in a sweet and tangy sauce and is served with a side of garlicky greens. &quot;Scratch-made, creative, eclectic,&quot; Guy said. &quot;It&#x27;s real-deal, man.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken and Briskets</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/philadelphia/farmer-s-keep-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.17349,39.95288,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fuel Cantina</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fuel Cantina</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charleston, SC 29403 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8437375959" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(843) 737-5959</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.fuelcharleston.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fuelcharleston.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fuel+Cantina%2C+211+Rutledge+Ave%2C+Charleston%2C+SC+29403&amp;ll=32.789266,-79.947184" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">211 Rutledge Ave<br/>Charleston, SC 29403</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jerk Chicken Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s trip to South Carolina was a &amp;quot;vacay&amp;quot; from Southern comfort food when he visited Fuel Cantina. Once a gas station, Fuel now boasts an eclectic patio with a Caribbean-inspired menu of spicy island flavors. Taste for yourself with the fiery jerk chicken sandwich or fall-apart pork tacos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old Faves, New Craves</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/charleston/fuel-cantina-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-79.94718,32.78927,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dixie Supply Bakery &amp; Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dixie Supply Bakery &amp; Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charleston 29401 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8437225650" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(843) 722-5650</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/charleston/dixie-supply-bakery-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/charleston/dixie-supply-bakery-cafe-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dixie+Supply+Bakery+%26+Cafe%2C+62+State+St.%2C+Charleston+29401&amp;ll=32.780397,-79.928321" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">62 State St.<br/>Charleston 29401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Shrimp BLT, Bourbon Bacon Pecan Pie, Chicken Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Patrick Woodham, knows how to make the locals happy with his scratch-made Southern-style food. The state street biscuit with sausage gravy, and chicken fried chicken wowed Guy. He also indulged in the shrimp BLT with fried green tomatoes and bacon. Locals love the bourbon bacon pecan pie.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Coast to Coast Chow</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/charleston/dixie-supply-bakery-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-79.92832,32.78040,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Liberty Elm Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Liberty Elm Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Providence, RI 02907 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4014670777" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(401) 467-0777</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.libertyelmdiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.libertyelmdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Liberty+Elm+Diner%2C+777+Elmwood+Ave.%2C+Providence%2C+RI+02907&amp;ll=41.791031,-71.422559" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">777 Elmwood Ave.<br/>Providence, RI 02907</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Johnnycake, Roasted Turkey Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Not only does The Liberty Elm Diner succeed in serving dynamite clam chowder, but they also excel in griddling perfect johnnycakes (Rhode Island is the center of the johnnycake universe). Guy loved the cakes and couldn&#x27;t leave without trying the official state drink: coffee milk.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort Food Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ri/providence/the-liberty-elm-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.42256,41.79103,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mediterraneo Caffe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mediterraneo Caffe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Providence, RI 02903</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4013317760" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(401) 331-7760</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mediterraneocaffe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mediterraneocaffe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mediterraneo+Caffe%2C+134+Atwells+Ave%2C+Providence%2C+RI+02903&amp;ll=41.823156,-71.422357" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">134 Atwells Ave<br/>Providence, RI 02903</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spaghetti a la Vongole, Chicken Piccata, Baby Neck Clams</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Mediterraneo, real deal Italian food is made fresh daily by Chef Michele Calise. The spaghetti a la vongole, little neck and baby neck clams sauteed in white wine and served with white sauce, left Guy speechless. The chicken piccata is a local favorite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">East Coast Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ri/providence/mediterraneo-caffe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.42236,41.82316,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Louis Family Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Louis Family Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Providence, RI 02906 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4018615225" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(401) 861-5225</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.louisrestaurant.org/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.louisrestaurant.org</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Louis+Family+Restaurant%2C+286+Brook+St%2C+Providence%2C+RI+02906&amp;ll=41.824638,-71.399092" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">286 Brook St<br/>Providence, RI 02906</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Barbecued Chicken Ravioli, Granola Pancakes, Meatloaf, Grilled Pumpkin Muffins</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Get ready to go onboard at the Louis Family Restaurant with the BBQ chicken ravioli that Guy says has &amp;quot;16 tickets to Flavortown&amp;quot; - it&#x27;s made from scratch with 16 ingredients. You&#x27;ll get big portions of really delicious food, from the meatloaf dinner or lasagna to the grilled pumpkin muffins.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">East Coast Cruisin&#x27;<br/>Family Style</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ri/providence/louies-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.39909,41.82464,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Angelo&#x27;s Civita Farnese</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Angelo&#x27;s Civita Farnese</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Providence, RI 02903 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4016218171" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(401) 621-8171</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.angelosri.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.angelosri.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Angelo%27s+Civita+Farnese%2C+141+Atwells+Ave%2C+Providence%2C+RI+02903&amp;ll=41.823461,-71.422764" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">141 Atwells Ave<br/>Providence, RI 02903</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Braciola, Meatballs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This restaurant opened in 1924 and almost a century later they pump out the same delicious food. The braciola captured Guy&#x27;s heart with its tender deep flavored pork on a bed of fresh pasta. Still hungry? Try the meatballs and fries smothered in marinara sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">East Coast Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ri/providence/angelos-civita-farnese-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.42276,41.82346,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Daddypops</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Daddypops</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hatboro, PA 19040</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2156759717" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(215) 675-9717</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/hatboro/daddypops-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/hatboro/daddypops-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Daddypops%2C+232+N.+York+Rd.%2C+Hatboro%2C+PA+19040&amp;ll=40.181278,-75.104840" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">232 N. York Rd.<br/>Hatboro, PA 19040</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Scrapple, Turkey Salad, Deep-Fried Oreos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s love of potatoes is no match for Daddypops&#x27; customers. Each day Daddypops goes through nearly 200 pounds of potatoes for its beloved home fries. Since opening in 1953, Daddypops still keeps its menu old school with dishes like Philadelphia-style scrapple and scrumptious deep-fried Oreos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Neighborhood Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/hatboro/daddypops-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.10484,40.18128,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lo Bello&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lo Bello&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Coraopolis, PA 15108 &middot; &#9733; 1.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4122649721" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(412) 264-9721</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/coraopolis/lo-bellos-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/coraopolis/lo-bellos-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lo+Bello%27s%2C+809+5th+Ave%2C+Coraopolis%2C+PA+15108&amp;ll=40.519833,-80.169803" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">809 5th Ave<br/>Coraopolis, PA 15108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spaghetti, Gnocchi, Ravioli</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">What started as a hot dog stand in 1944 has become a local legend. Guy swung by Lo Bello&#x27;s for the ravioli and gnocchi handmade the old-school way and bursting with great meat flavor. With each bite of ravioli, Guy kept asking for more, admitting he could eat the delicious pasta all day</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Real Deal Italian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/pa/coraopolis/lo-bellos-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.16980,40.51983,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Farmer&#x27;s Shed</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Farmer&#x27;s Shed</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lexington, SC 29072 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8039960700" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(803) 996-0700</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/lexington/the-farmers-shed-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/lexington/the-farmers-shed-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Farmer%27s+Shed%2C+2514+Augusta+Hwy%2C+Lexington%2C+SC+29072&amp;ll=33.979046,-81.311732" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2514 Augusta Hwy<br/>Lexington, SC 29072</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Broccoli Supreme, Cornbread, Pumpkin Pie, Collard Greens, Shrimp and Grits with Tasso Gravy</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Inside The Farmer&#x27;s Shed you&#x27;ll find coconut cakes and pumpkin pies, as well as fried pork chops, Chicken Broccoli Supreme and even pot roast. But for Guy&#x27;s Triple D visit, owner Shirley showed him the straight-from-the-farm cornbread, baked in a cast-iron skillet and topped with brown sugar.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homegrown And Homemade</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/lexington/the-farmers-shed-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.31173,33.97905,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Perfectly Frank&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Perfectly Frank&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Summerville, SC 29483 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8438719730" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(843) 871-9730</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.perfectlyfranksonline.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.perfectlyfranksonline.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Perfectly+Frank%27s%2C+118+N+Main+St%2C+Summerville%2C+SC+29483&amp;ll=33.021392,-80.174831" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">118 N Main St<br/>Summerville, SC 29483</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Frank Cuda Dog, Pork Chop Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this hot dog dive, Chef Perry Cuda is topping wieners with some unusual choices like bananas and peanut butter. Guy enjoyed the Frank Cuda, a dog topped with chili, blue cheese slaw, applewood bacon, cheese and crispy onions. Locals recommend the sweet tea-marinated, fried pork chop sandwich.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern Staples<br/>Small Town Sensations</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/summerville/perfectly-franks-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.17483,33.02139,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Harold&#x27;s Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Harold&#x27;s Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Gaffney, SC 29340 &middot; &#9733; 2.1 (22 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8644899153" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(864) 489-9153</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.haroldsrestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.haroldsrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Harold%27s+Restaurant%2C+602+N.+Limestone+St.%2C+Gaffney%2C+SC+29340&amp;ll=35.076577,-81.646076" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">602 N. Limestone St.<br/>Gaffney, SC 29340</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chili Burger, Pinto Beans with Fatback</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Guy Fieri makes the journey out to Harold&#x27;s in Gaffney, SC, for some unforgettable dishes that make the long drive worth the trip.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Worth the Trip</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/sc/gaffney/harolds-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.64608,35.07658,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tortugas&#x27; Lie</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tortugas&#x27; Lie</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nags Head, NC 27959 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2524417299" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(252) 441-7299</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://tortugaslie.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">tortugaslie.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tortugas%27+Lie%2C+3014+S+Virginia+Dare+Trail%2C+Nags+Head%2C+NC+27959&amp;ll=35.978980,-75.636345" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3014 S Virginia Dare Trail<br/>Nags Head, NC 27959</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jerk-seasoned Pork Chops, Jerk-seasoned Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this surfer hangout, grill master Richard Welch is dishing out &amp;quot;ridiculous&amp;quot; Caribbean-inspired dishes. Guy thought that the habanero jelly gave the jerk-seasoned pork chops just the right amount of spice and sweetness. The wet jerk-seasoned chicken with pineapple chutney was &amp;quot;off the hook.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crazy for Chicken<br/>Layers of Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/nags-head/tortugas-lie-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.63635,35.97898,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Brine and Bottle</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Brine and Bottle</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Nags Head, NC 27959 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2527151818" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(252) 715-1818</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thebrineandbottle.com/index.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thebrineandbottle.com/index.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Brine+and+Bottle%2C+7531+S.+Virginia+Dare+Trail%2C+Nags+Head%2C+NC+27959&amp;ll=35.902092,-75.606650" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7531 S. Virginia Dare Trail<br/>Nags Head, NC 27959</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Deep Fried Pickles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">North Carolina native Andrew Donovan finally returned home start a restuarant with another prodigal North Carolinan, Ashley Whitfield, creating a comfortable down-home eatery specializing in local seasonal cuisine partnered with excellent wines.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fully Focused</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/nags-head/the-brine-and-bottle-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.60665,35.90209,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Penguin Drive-In - CLOSED</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Penguin Drive-In - CLOSED</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28205 &middot; &#9733; 2.7 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7043751925" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(704) 375-1925</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.penguindrive-in.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.penguindrive-in.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Penguin+Drive-In+-+CLOSED%2C+1921+Commonwealth+Ave.%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28205&amp;ll=35.218898,-80.812371" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1921 Commonwealth Ave.<br/>Charlotte, NC 28205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Pickles, Corn Dogs, Pimento Grilled Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Most people enjoy some french fries or onion rings with a burger, but how about fried pickles? The regulars at the Penguin in North Carolina can&#x27;t get enough of them. Head Chef Greg Auten makes his corn dogs from scratch, and Guy got addicted to his pimento grilled cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Blue Plate Special</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/the-penguin-closed-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.81237,35.21890,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Tin Kitchen Food Truck</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Tin Kitchen Food Truck</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28202</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7047500477" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">704-750-0477</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tinkitchenfoodtruck.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tinkitchenfoodtruck.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Tin+Kitchen+Food+Truck%2C+900+W+Trade+St%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28202&amp;ll=35.234673,-80.851196" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">900 W Trade St<br/>Charlotte, NC 28202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Belly Tacos, Buffalo Cauliflower Sliders</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This mobile food truck serves top-notch tacos and fusion dishes like buffalo-style cauliflower tacos.</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/the-tin-kitchen-food-truck-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.85120,35.23467,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dish</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dish</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28205 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7043440343" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(704) 344-0343</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.eatatdish.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.eatatdish.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dish%2C+1220+Thomas+Ave%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28205&amp;ll=35.219753,-80.812121" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1220 Thomas Ave<br/>Charlotte, NC 28205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken and Dumplings, Salmon Patties, Shrimp and Grits</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Walking into Dish feels like walking into someone&#x27;s grandmother&#x27;s house. It&#x27;s warm and casual and you get the feeling you&#x27;re going to be taken care of. Come for classic Southern comfort food like fried green tomatoes or chicken and biscuits, a Guy Fieri favorite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort Food Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/the-dish-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.81212,35.21975,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fud at Salud</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fud at Salud</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28205 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7042324943" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">704-232-4943</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://fudatsalud.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">fudatsalud.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fud+at+Salud%2C+3306+N+Davidson+St%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28205&amp;ll=35.247856,-80.804141" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3306 N Davidson St<br/>Charlotte, NC 28205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Waffle-Wiches</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Housed in a beer shop, this little spot churns out imaginative eats that are just as inventive as the craft brews on the shelves. The &quot;wild waffle sandwiches,&quot; as Guy called them, are a particular standout. Listed as Waffle-Wiches on the menu, these golden, fluffy creations come stuffed with a delectable array of fillings. Guy opted for a sweet variation inspired by s&#x27;mores. Two Belgian waffles made from a meringue-laced batter are sandwiched with graham cracker crumbs, chocolate sauce and a massive housemade marshmallow that&#x27;s caramelized with a torch before serving.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Not Your Typical Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/fud-at-salud-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.80414,35.24786,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pinky&#x27;s Westside Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pinky&#x27;s Westside Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte 28208 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7043320402" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">704-332-0402</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://eatatpinkys.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">eatatpinkys.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pinky%27s+Westside+Grill%2C+1600+W+Morehead+St%2C+Charlotte+28208&amp;ll=35.229108,-80.867462" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1600 W Morehead St<br/>Charlotte 28208</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple &quot;G&quot; Burger, Corn Dog Shrimp</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A converted auto repair shop, this casual restaurant serves towering burgers, snappy dogs and not-too-healthy salads topped with popcorn chicken and fried buffalo shrimp.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Funky Finds in &#x27;da House</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/pinkys-westside-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.86746,35.22911,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>South 21 Drive-in</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">South 21 Drive-in</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28205 &middot; &#9733; 4.6 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7043774509" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(704) 377-4509</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/south-21-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/south-21-drive-in-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=South+21+Drive-in%2C+3101+E+Independence+Blvd%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28205&amp;ll=35.203328,-80.790329" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3101 E Independence Blvd<br/>Charlotte, NC 28205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Super Boy (Burger with Two Patties, Coleslaw and Chili), Fish O Burger, Onion Rings, Golden Southern Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Since 1955, South 21 Drive-In has been serving more than 20,000 meals a month to Charlotte, N.C., locals; so Guy had to check them out. He&#x27;s glad he did for their classic American burgers and shakes, including the Super Boy, a signature double burger with scratch-made chili and tangy slaw.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">By Request</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/south-21-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.79033,35.20333,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pit Road Bar &amp; Grilll</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pit Road Bar &amp; Grilll</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28206 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7043773278" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">704-377-3278</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://victorylanekarting.com/pit-road-bar-and-grill" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">victorylanekarting.com/pit-road-bar-and-grill</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pit+Road+Bar+%26+Grilll%2C+2330+Tipton+Dr%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28206&amp;ll=35.271145,-80.842316" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2330 Tipton Dr<br/>Charlotte, NC 28206</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Moon Pie Burger, Hot Lap Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Set inside a Go-Kart Track, this casual restaurant serves&amp;nbsp;crowd-pleasing dishes like wings, loaded fries and the Hot Lap, a sandwich packed with spicy chicke, jalapeno crema and cheese.</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/pit-road-bar-and-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.84232,35.27114,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mert&#x27;s Heart and Soul</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mert&#x27;s Heart and Soul</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28202 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7043424222" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">704-342-4222</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://mertscharlotte.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">mertscharlotte.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mert%27s+Heart+and+Soul%2C+214+N+College+St%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28202&amp;ll=35.227318,-80.840130" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">214 N College St<br/>Charlotte, NC 28202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Soul Roll, Shrimp and Grits</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy couldn&#x27;t visit North Carolina without getting a taste of low-country cooking, so he made a beeline for this down-home Southern restaurant. Guy tried the Soul Roll, an egg roll wrap that comes stuffed with adobo-laced collard greens, black-eyed peas, seasoned rice and diced fried chicken. &quot;This is a soul food missile pop ... with everything combined in one easy-to-eat bite,&quot; Guy declared of the dish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Bowlful of Soul</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/merts-heart-and-soul-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.84013,35.22732,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Landmark Restaurant Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Landmark Restaurant Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28205 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7045321153" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(704) 532-1153</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.landmarkdinercharlottenc.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.landmarkdinercharlottenc.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Landmark+Restaurant+Diner%2C+4429+Central+Ave.%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28205&amp;ll=35.213961,-80.769473" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4429 Central Ave.<br/>Charlotte, NC 28205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Boiled Whole Turkey, Split Pea Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Landmark Restaurant Diner may be a Greek family restaurant, but the menu spans the globe, from the American Turkey Tom-Tom (&amp;quot;Thanksgiving on a plate&amp;quot;) to the Italian tiramisu (one of just 230 baked goods). Of course, they&#x27;ve got Greek too -- Guy could eat the spanakopita not once, but 36 more times.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fresh And Funky</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/landmark-restaurant-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.76947,35.21396,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lucky&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lucky&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cleveland 44113 &middot; &#9733; 4.1 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2166227773" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(216) 622-7773</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.luckyscafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.luckyscafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lucky%27s+Cafe%2C+777+Starkweather+Ave%2C+Cleveland+44113&amp;ll=41.477338,-81.683067" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">777 Starkweather Ave<br/>Cleveland 44113</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Corned Beef, Bread, Granola, Reuben, Biscuits &amp; Gravy</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Michael Symon may be an Iron Chef but that doesn&#x27;t mean he&#x27;s immune to loving the &quot;soul satisfying&quot; biscuits and gravy from Lucky&#x27;s Cafe. The combo has worked for years and for good reason. Guy also stopped by to sample them, in addition to Lucky&#x27;s Reuben and super yummy Baked Mac-N-Cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Barbequed, Baked, and Brined<br/>Takeout: Funky Finds in &#x27;da House</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/cleveland/luckyrsquos-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.68307,41.47734,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jake&#x27;s Good Eats</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jake&#x27;s Good Eats</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28227 &middot; &#9733; 4.1 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7045454741" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(704) 545-4741</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.jakesgoodeatsnc.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jakesgoodeatsnc.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jake%27s+Good+Eats%2C+12721+Albemarle+Rd%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28227&amp;ll=35.223722,-80.638651" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">12721 Albemarle Rd<br/>Charlotte, NC 28227</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Maple-Glazed Pork Chop, Venison Quesadilla</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brothers Jake and Gordon Stegall converted an old gas station to the local favorite for twists on Southern cooking. Guy&#x27;s favorite, blackened flounder with country ham grit cakes, was an out-of-bounds winner. But locals savor the super tasty venison quesadillas.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grilled, Smoked And Sauced<br/>Primetime Pork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/jakes-good-eats-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.63865,35.22372,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Krazy Fish</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Krazy Fish</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte 28205 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7043321004" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">704-332-1004</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://krazyfish.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">krazyfish.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Krazy+Fish%2C+2501+Central+Ave%2C+Charlotte+28205&amp;ll=35.219612,-80.800000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2501 Central Ave<br/>Charlotte 28205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Blackened Tuna Tacos, Seafood Creole</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Unlikely flavors come together for awesome dishes at this Charlotte seafood spot, which specializes in tacos like Szechuan-style salmon and blackened tuna.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Indulgent Dishes<br/>Rockstar Chefs<br/>Takeout: Cross-Country Delivery</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/krazy-fish-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.80000,35.21961,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>JJ&#x27;s Red Hots</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">JJ&#x27;s Red Hots</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28203 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9802258880" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">980-225-8880</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.jjsredhots.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jjsredhots.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=JJ%27s+Red+Hots%2C+1514+East+Blvd%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28203&amp;ll=35.199984,-80.842349" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1514 East Blvd<br/>Charlotte, NC 28203</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">JJ&#x27;s Red Hots is one food establishment that has gone entirely to the dogs ... hot dogs, that is. Owner Jonathan Luther draws the crowds with his menu of hot dogs and sausages that can be customized with a slew of toppings. He makes the joint&#x27;s traditional Austrian-style sausages from scratch, using an 85/15 blend of pork butt and chuck. &quot;That&#x27;s legit,&quot; Guy declared after tucking into a spice-laden, cheese-laced sausage loaded with sauerkraut, pickled onions and mustard.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Swiss, Sandwiches and Sausage</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/jjs-red-hots-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.84235,35.19998,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>P&#x27;s &amp; Q&#x27;s Market</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">P&#x27;s &amp; Q&#x27;s Market</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97211 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5038948979" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">503-894-8979</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.psandqsmarket.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.psandqsmarket.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=P%27s+%26+Q%27s+Market%2C+1301+NE+Dekum+St%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97211&amp;ll=45.571988,-122.651588" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1301 NE Dekum St<br/>Portland, OR 97211</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Biscuits and Gravy, Polenta Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Co-owners Emily Anderson and Chef Paul Davis looked to their roots when creating the menu at this homey spot. While Anderson&#x27;s California sensibility translates as a preference for fresh produce, Midwesterner Davis favors comfort food classics. He steps up housemade buttermilk biscuits by smothering them in a tomato gravy made from his grandmother&#x27;s Appalachian recipe. Crushed tomatoes are brought together with evaporated milk, whole milk and flour to make a velvety gravy that Guy called &quot;top-notch.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Port to Port</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/ps-and-qs-market-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.65159,45.57199,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pok Pok</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pok Pok</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97202 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5032321387" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(503) 232-1387</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pokpokpdx.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pokpokpdx.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pok+Pok%2C+3226+SE+Dvision+St%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97202&amp;ll=45.504577,-122.632113" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3226 SE Dvision St<br/>Portland, OR 97202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Khao Man Som Tam, Ike&#x27;s Vietnamese Fish Sauce Wings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The heavy Oregon rain doesn&#x27;t keep Chef Andy Rickers from cooking up some of his favorite dishes he brought home from his travels across Asia. Guy was all smiles as he ate the grilled boar with chile-lime garlic sauce and the spicy Vietnamese chicken wings topped with fried garlic.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You Can Say That Again<br/>Triple D Nation: Global Goodies<br/>Amazing Asian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/pok-pok-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.63211,45.50458,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Podnah&#x27;s Pit</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Podnah&#x27;s Pit</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97211 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5032813700" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">503-281-3700</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.podnahspit.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.podnahspit.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Podnah%27s+Pit%2C+1625+NE+Killingsworth%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97211&amp;ll=45.562865,-122.648256" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1625 NE Killingsworth<br/>Portland, OR 97211</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Whole Ruby Trout, Lamb Ribs, Smoked Beef Brisket</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This spot cranks out 30 tons of &#x27;cue a year. Guy is won over by the lamb ribs, saying they &quot;melt in your mouth.&quot; The Pitboss Plate is also a popular pick, as shown on Best. Ever. It comes piled with Central Texas-style brisket, ribs and sausage. Cornbread and sides round out this mouthwatering meal.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Only At This Joint</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/podnahs-pit-barbecue-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.64826,45.56287,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>PDX Six Seven One</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">PDX Six Seven One</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9715700945" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(971) 570-0945</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pdx671.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pdx671.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=PDX+Six+Seven+One%2C+Rose+City+Food+Park+at+NE+Sandy+Blvd+%26+52nd+Ave+Portland%2C+Portland%2C+OR&amp;ll=45.558617,-122.551864" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Rose City Food Park at NE Sandy Blvd &amp; 52nd Ave Portland<br/>Portland, OR</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kelaguen Mannok</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s first impression of the Guamanian food from PDX Six Seven One? &amp;quot;Simple, basic and dynamite.&amp;quot; The Kelaguen Mannok dish, a cold chicken salad served with titiya (Guamanian flat bread), instantly became a favorite. As for the name? It&#x27;s a cross between Portland&#x27;s airport and Guam&#x27;s zip code.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cannoli, Fritters and Wings<br/>Global Flavor Faves</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/pdx-six-seven-one-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.55186,45.55862,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pine State Biscuits</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pine State Biscuits</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97211 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5034776605" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(503) 477-6605</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pinestatebiscuits.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pinestatebiscuits.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pine+State+Biscuits%2C+2204+NE+Alberta%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97211&amp;ll=45.558883,-122.642727" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2204 NE Alberta<br/>Portland, OR 97211</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Biscuits and Gravy, The Reggie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this comfort food restaurant, everything is served up on biscuits. Guy could not get enough of the classic biscuits and gravy, noting that the biscuit had the &amp;quot;best texture ever.&amp;quot; He also devoured The Reggie with fried chicken, bacon, cheddar and gravy all inside a &amp;quot;flaky and light&amp;quot; biscuit.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/pine-state-biscuit-shop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.64273,45.55888,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Frank&#x27;s Noodle House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Frank&#x27;s Noodle House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5032881007" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(503) 288-1007</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.franksnoodlehouseportland.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.franksnoodlehouseportland.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Frank%27s+Noodle+House%2C+822+NE+Broadway+St.%2C+Portland%2C+OR&amp;ll=45.534861,-122.657004" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">822 NE Broadway St.<br/>Portland, OR</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hand-Pulled Noodles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy tried hand-pulling noodles, but it was no match for Frank Fong&#x27;s mastery. At Frank&#x27;s Noodle House, noodles are the star of the plate, as they&#x27;re hand-pulled and handmade every day. Frank offers the noodles with vegetables, beef and even squid. But Guy likes his with Frank&#x27;s marinated chicken.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Aces of Authenticity<br/>Triple D Nation: Meat Lovers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/franks-noodle-house-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.65700,45.53486,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Edelweiss Sausage &amp; Delicatessen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Edelweiss Sausage &amp; Delicatessen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97202 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5032384411" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(503) 238-4411</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://edelweissdeli.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">edelweissdeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Edelweiss+Sausage+%26+Delicatessen%2C+3119+SE+12th+Ave%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97202&amp;ll=45.500565,-122.653456" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3119 SE 12th Ave<br/>Portland, OR 97202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">European Sausages</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Edelweiss Sausage &amp;amp; Delicatessen has more than 120 types of handmade German sausage, including bologna, braunschweiger, bierschinken and bier sausage. Make sure to try the roasted garlic and a fresh rosemary bologna. Guy says the bologna is &quot;out of bounds&amp;quot; and one of the best he&#x27;s ever eaten.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">That&#x27;s Fresh</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/edelweiss-sausage-delicatessen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.65346,45.50056,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Byways Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Byways Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97209 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5032210011" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(503) 221-0011</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bywayscafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bywayscafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Byways+Cafe%2C+1212+NW+Glisan+St.%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97209&amp;ll=45.526487,-122.683496" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1212 NW Glisan St.<br/>Portland, OR 97209</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Breakfast Food, Omelet and Scrambles, Corned Beef Hash, Desserts, Key Lime Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Guy Fieri, uncovers some retro cuisine at the Byways Cafe, a neighborhood destination for locals and tourists alike, in Portland, OR.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Retro</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/byways-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.68350,45.52649,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bunk Sandwiches</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bunk Sandwiches</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97214 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5033282865" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">503-328-2865</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bunksandwiches.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bunksandwiches.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bunk+Sandwiches%2C+1028+SE+Water+Avenue%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97214&amp;ll=45.515329,-122.665530" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1028 SE Water Avenue<br/>Portland, OR 97214</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">House-Cured Pork Belly, Sandwiches</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On The Best Thing I Ever Ate, pork fanatic Chris Cosentino speaks anything but &quot;bunk&quot; about Bunk&#x27;s Pork Belly Cubano. Bunk&#x27;s take on the iconic Cuban sandwich uses knock-out pork belly grilled with mustard, Swiss and ham. But the roast beef sandwich with sharp cheddar is utter, delicious nonsense. Guy Fieri became a fellow fan of the sandwich shop after sampling a pork-centric spin on a Reuben, as well as a between-the-bread creation stuffed with salt cod. &quot;Get the funk at Bunk,&quot; he declared.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Upper Crust<br/>All Stacked Up<br/>Triple D Nation: Something for Everyone</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/bunk-sandwiches-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.66553,45.51533,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blueplate Lunch Counter &amp; Soda Fountain</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blueplate Lunch Counter &amp; Soda Fountain</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97204 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5032952583" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(503) 295-2583</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.eatatblueplate.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.eatatblueplate.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blueplate+Lunch+Counter+%26+Soda+Fountain%2C+308+SW+Washington+St.%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97204&amp;ll=45.519569,-122.675257" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">308 SW Washington St.<br/>Portland, OR 97204</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grilled Cheese and Tomato Soup, Soda Fountain (Floats, Chocolate Malt)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s visit to downtown Portland led him to The Blueplate Lunch Counter, where Chef Jeff Reiter excels in classic American comfort foods. Guy loved the gourmet burger sliders made with basil mayonnaise, and the &amp;quot;primo&amp;quot; mushroom and bacon mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese, adding, &amp;quot;Here&#x27;s a guy who is making it work.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old Time Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/blueplate-lunch-counter-soda-fountain-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.67526,45.51957,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Aviv</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Aviv</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland 97202</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://avivpdx.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">avivpdx.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Aviv%2C+1125+SE+Division+St%2C+Portland+97202&amp;ll=45.505273,-122.653895" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1125 SE Division St<br/>Portland 97202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mushroom Calamari, Shawarma Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and Owner Tal Caspi went vegan but that didn&#x27;t stop him from loving the flavors of his Argentinian and Israeli background. At Aviv he recreates all his Middle Eastern favorites sans meat. Standouts are the crispy Mushroom Calamari, which is served with a tahini sauce so good that Guy said he could have a cup of it, and the Shawarma Fries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hometown Inspiration</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/aviv-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.65390,45.50527,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ataula</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ataula</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97210</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5038948904" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">503-894-8904</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.ataulapdx.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.ataulapdx.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ataula%2C+1818+NW+23rd+Pl%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97210&amp;ll=45.535718,-122.699664" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1818 NW 23rd Pl<br/>Portland, OR 97210</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulpo Carpaccio, Pepito De Ternera (Veal Breast Sandwich)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Striking small plates take center stage at this Spanish restaurant, where Chef-Owner Jose Chesa turns out an artful array of tapas that are as delightful to look at as they are to eat. A real stunner is the &lt;i&gt;pulpo carpaccio&lt;/i&gt;, made from delicate slices of tender octopus that come adorned with a dazzling array of toppings that include sun-dried tomatoes, Parmigiano Reggiano, toasted pine nuts and olive oil caviar. &quot;It&#x27;s a whole symphony of flavors,&quot; Guy declared after taking a bite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Port to Port</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/ataula-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.69966,45.53572,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Arleta Library Bakery &amp; Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Arleta Library Bakery &amp; Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97206 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5037744470" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(503) 774-4470</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.arletalibrary.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.arletalibrary.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Arleta+Library+Bakery+%26+Cafe%2C+5513+SE+72nd+at+Harold%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97206&amp;ll=45.483059,-122.589249" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5513 SE 72nd at Harold<br/>Portland, OR 97206</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sicilian Hash, Sweet Potato Biscuits with Pork and Rosemary Sausage, Semolina Griddlecakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Look no further than this neighborhood cafe for comfort food with a culinary-school flair. Guy appreciated the complexity found in the savory Sicilian hash made with braciola. The sweet potato biscuits with pork and rosemary sausage were &amp;quot;dynamite.&amp;quot; Diners also enjoy the Semolina Griddlecakes.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Biscuits, Bagels and BLT&#x27;s</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/arleta-library-bakery-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.58925,45.48306,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Norman, OK 73069 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4053296642" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">405-329-6642</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/norman/the-diner-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/norman/the-diner-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Diner%2C+213+E+Main+St%2C+Norman%2C+OK+73069&amp;ll=35.221984,-97.441426" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">213 E Main St<br/>Norman, OK 73069</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chili, Fries, Burgers, Hot Dogs, Southside Chili</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This chili and sandwich shop has been around for more than 100 years and they&#x27;re famous for their two-time state of Oklahoma championship chili recipe. Try it in a classic bowl, the chili dog dinner or the chili burrito with ranchero sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners Times Three</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/norman/the-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.44143,35.22198,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Eischen&#x27;s Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Eischen&#x27;s Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Okarche, OK 73762 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4052639939" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">405-263-9939</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://eischensbar.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">eischensbar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Eischen%27s+Bar%2C+109+S+2nd+St%2C+Okarche%2C+OK+73762&amp;ll=35.725473,-97.975683" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">109 S 2nd St<br/>Okarche, OK 73762</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Chicken, Chili</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A few hundred regulars wrote in to get Triple D to stop at this fried chicken haven that&#x27;s serving theirs the same way they did in the &#x27;60s. They go through 24,000 pieces of fried chicken a week. The whole room cheered when Guy asked, &amp;quot;How&#x27;s the fried chicken?&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You Picked &#x27;Em</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/okarche/eischens-bar-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.97568,35.72547,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Travel By Taste Deli and Market</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Travel By Taste Deli and Market</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Warr Acres, OK 73122 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.travelbytasteok.com/Home_Page.php" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.travelbytasteok.com/Home_Page.php</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Travel+By+Taste+Deli+and+Market%2C+4818+N.+MacArthur%2C+Warr+Acres%2C+OK+73122&amp;ll=35.520385,-97.618864" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4818 N. MacArthur<br/>Warr Acres, OK 73122</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Head 20 minutes outside Oklahoma City to Travel by Taste to sample the international flavors that Iranian-born Parviz Rezaian and his wife grew up with. Diners love the crunchy samosas with tamarind sauce and the fragrant chicken kebabs over saffron rice.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Flavortown International</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/warr-acres/travel-by-taste-deli-and-market-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.61886,35.52038,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Rock Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Rock Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Stroud, OK 74079 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9189683990" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(918) 968-3990</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rockcafert66.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rockcafert66.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Rock+Cafe%2C+114+W.+Main+St.%2C+Stroud%2C+OK+74079&amp;ll=35.748968,-96.654426" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">114 W. Main St.<br/>Stroud, OK 74079</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">German Spaetzle, Buffalo Burger, Alligator Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Guy Fieri, travels the historic Route 66 to the Rock Cafe, in Stroud, OK, for some unbeatable roadside eats.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Route 66</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/stroud/the-rock-caf-closed-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.65443,35.74897,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Clanton&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Clanton&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Vinita, OK 74301 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9182569053" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(918) 256-9053</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.clantonscafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.clantonscafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Clanton%27s+Cafe%2C+319+E+Illinois+Ave%2C+Vinita%2C+OK+74301&amp;ll=36.637382,-95.151363" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">319 E Illinois Ave<br/>Vinita, OK 74301</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Calf Fries (Rocky Mountain Oysters), Chicken Fried Steak</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy couldn&#x27;t leave Clanton&#x27;s Cafe without sampling the 80-year-old recipe for the famous chicken-fried steak. The &amp;quot;mac daddy&amp;quot; steak has been called one of the best on Route 66, and, for a trip off the road, they&#x27;re dishing out tasty Rocky Mountain Oysters, also known as the underside of the calf.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Local Flavor<br/>Amazing Appetizers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/vinita/clantons-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.15136,36.63738,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Florence&#x27;s Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Florence&#x27;s Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oklahoma City, OK 73111 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.florences.restaurant/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.florences.restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Florence%27s+Restaurant%2C+1437+Northeast+23rd+Street%2C+Oklahoma+City%2C+OK+73111&amp;ll=35.493260,-97.486652" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1437 Northeast 23rd Street<br/>Oklahoma City, OK 73111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Pork Ribs, Yam Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Florence Jones has been running this soul food joint for 67 years. She&#x27;s known for her Yam Fried Chicken, a dish she created. To make it, Florence coats fried chicken in a candied yam sauce, and serves the chicken with a side of yams and stewed collard greens. Another standout is the Fried Pork Ribs.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Down-Home Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/oklahoma-city/florences-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.48665,35.49326,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Stone Sisters Pizza Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Stone Sisters Pizza Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oklahoma City 73103 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.stonesisterspizza.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.stonesisterspizza.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Stone+Sisters+Pizza+Bar%2C+2124+N.+Broadway+Ave%2C+Oklahoma+City+73103&amp;ll=35.490267,-97.514033" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2124 N. Broadway Ave<br/>Oklahoma City 73103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy is always on the hunt for great pizza and the three sisters of Stone Pizza Bar are dishing out something truly unique. They&#x27;ve created a healthy take on pizza crust using sprouted spelt instead of traditional flour. Diners rave about the Bossy Big Sister which sports their traditional crunchy thin crust topped with organic house-made sauce, local cheese, lots of crisp veggies, organic roasted chicken, pepperoni and gluten-friendly pasta.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken and Pie</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/oklahoma-city/stone-sisters-pizza-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.51403,35.49027,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Intermezzo Pizzeria and Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Intermezzo Pizzeria and Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28204 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7043472626" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">704-347-2626</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://intermezzopizzeria.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">intermezzopizzeria.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Intermezzo+Pizzeria+and+Cafe%2C+1427+E+10th+St%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28204&amp;ll=35.222152,-80.821684" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1427 E 10th St<br/>Charlotte, NC 28204</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Piroska, Grilled Fungi Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This pizzeria sets its menu apart with a selection of traditional Serbian dishes, including Piroska, a Balkan-style stuffed pizza. Another standout is the grilled fungi option. Inspired by the foraged mushrooms the owners&#x27; mother used to prepare, this earthy pie is scattered with grilled portobello, shiitake, oyster and button mushrooms over mozzarella before being finished with fragrant basil.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Intercontinental Flavorfest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/intermezzo-pizzeria-and-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.82168,35.22215,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cabo Fish Taco</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cabo Fish Taco</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28205 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7043328868" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(704) 332-8868</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cabofishtaco.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cabofishtaco.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cabo+Fish+Taco%2C+3201+N+Davidson+St%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28205&amp;ll=35.247251,-80.805827" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3201 N Davidson St<br/>Charlotte, NC 28205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fish Tacos, Mango BBQ Mahi Mahi Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Even though Cabo Fish Taco calls North Carolina home, its tacos take a cue from Baja, California, as well as from south of the border. Guy visited Cabo looking for a new twist on the SoCal favorite and he found it in Flavortown with Cabo&#x27;s Southern-style mango barbecue fish tacos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bringin&#x27; It Home</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/cabo-fish-taco-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.80583,35.24725,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bar-B-Q King</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bar-B-Q King</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28208 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7043998344" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(704) 399-8344</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.barbqking.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.barbqking.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bar-B-Q+King%2C+2900+Wilkinson+Blvd.%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28208&amp;ll=35.224489,-80.889125" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2900 Wilkinson Blvd.<br/>Charlotte, NC 28208</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulled Pork, BBQ Chicken, Southern Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">What flows through the river of Flavortown? Guy says it&#x27;s the Bar-B-Q Chicken at Bar-B-Q King. On The Best Thing I Ever Ate and Triple D, he chows down on their chicken that&#x27;s been fried and then dunked in their famous barbecue sauce. It&#x27;s nothing short of a tried-and-true recipe from 1959.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/barbecue-king-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.88913,35.22449,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Geraci&#x27;s Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Geraci&#x27;s Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cleveland 44118 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2163715643" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">216-371-5643</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.geracisrestaurant.net/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.geracisrestaurant.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Geraci%27s+Restaurant%2C+2266+Warrensville+Center+Rd%2C+Cleveland+44118&amp;ll=41.498216,-81.536786" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2266 Warrensville Center Rd<br/>Cleveland 44118</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meatballs, Pepperoni Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Satisfy your cravings for Italian classics at Geraci&#x27;s Restaurant, a neighborhood fixture that&#x27;s been turning out meatballs and other Old World favorites since 1956. Today the daughters of the original owners are running the joint, where cash is still the only form of payment and locals still crowd in for menu mainstays like the popular pepperoni pizza. The dough is made fresh several times a day, then rolled out, slathered in sauce, heaped with mozzarella and blanketed in extra-thick pepperoni.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Incredible Italian<br/>Triple D Nation: Italian Inspired<br/>Legacies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/cleveland/geracis-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.53679,41.49822,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>300 East</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">300 East</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Charlotte, NC 28203 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7043326507" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">704-332-6507</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.300east.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.300east.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=300+East%2C+300+East+Blvd%2C+Charlotte%2C+NC+28203&amp;ll=35.210553,-80.856673" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">300 East Blvd<br/>Charlotte, NC 28203</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Ragout, Ice Cream Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">In a historic house a mother-daughter team prepares sensational seasonal New American dishes and homey desserts like a rotating ice cream sandwich.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Indulgent Dishes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/charlotte/300-east-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.85667,35.21055,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Black Pelican Oceanfront Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Black Pelican Oceanfront Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kitty Hawk, NC 27949 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (15 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2522613171" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(252) 261-3171</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://blackpelican.com/cms/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">blackpelican.com/cms</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Black+Pelican+Oceanfront+Restaurant%2C+3848+N+Virginia+Dare+Trail%2C+Kitty+Hawk%2C+NC+27949&amp;ll=36.067086,-75.690894" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3848 N Virginia Dare Trail<br/>Kitty Hawk, NC 27949</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wanchese Fisherman&#x27;s Risotto, Citrus Rosemary Brine Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Located on the beachfront, this is where the locals know to come for fresh locally caught seafood. The Wanchese fisherman&#x27;s risotto with scallops and shrimp had Guy lickin&#x27; his chops. This eatery is also known for its juicy citrus rosemary brine chicken with smoked gouda mash potatoes.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Land to Sea</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/kitty-hawk/the-black-pelican-oceanfront-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.69089,36.06709,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Weeping Radish</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Weeping Radish</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Jarvisburg, NC 27947 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2524915205" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">252-491-5205</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.weepingradish.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.weepingradish.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Weeping+Radish%2C+6810+Caratoke+Hwy%2C+Jarvisburg%2C+NC+27947&amp;ll=36.219636,-75.869957" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6810 Caratoke Hwy<br/>Jarvisburg, NC 27947</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sweet Potato Liverwurst Crostini, Baked-Potato Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The whole idea of The Weeping Radish is to take literally everything from the farm to the restaurant table. You&#x27;ll find a farm, butchery and brewery on the premises, as well as a pub serving comfort foods like a baked-potato soup loaded with cheddar cheese and house-cured bacon.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ultimate Bacon Fest<br/>Savory Sensations</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/jarvisburg/the-weeping-radish-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.86996,36.21964,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ortegaz&#x27; Southwestern Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ortegaz&#x27; Southwestern Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Manteo, NC 27954 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2524735911" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(252) 473-5911</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://ortegaz.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">ortegaz.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ortegaz%27+Southwestern+Grill%2C+201+Sir+Walter+Raleigh+St%2C+Manteo%2C+NC+27954&amp;ll=35.909514,-75.670400" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">201 Sir Walter Raleigh St<br/>Manteo, NC 27954</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Shrimp Chorizo Alfredo, Fish Tacos, Softshell Crab</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Ortega&#x27;z you&#x27;ll find south of the border fare with an Outer Banks twist. Guy could not get enough of the &amp;quot;dynamite&amp;quot; fish tacos with sauteed tuna and pico de gallo. The giant soft-shell crab quesadilla and creamy shrimp and chorizo Aalfredo also impressed. Customers enjoy the seafood paella too.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Matches Made in Heaven</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/manteo/ortegaz-southwestern-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.67040,35.90951,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Island Frydays</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Island Frydays</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cincinnati 45219 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5134980680" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(513) 498-0680</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.islandfrydays.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.islandfrydays.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Island+Frydays%2C+2826+Vine+St%2C+Cincinnati+45219&amp;ll=39.132560,-84.508990" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2826 Vine St<br/>Cincinnati 45219</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jerk Chicken Platter, Snapper</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Island Frydays is the perfect destination for Jamaican flavors. Guy swings by to get a taste of the off-the-charts jerk chicken platter. The complex spice mix consists of pimento seeds, habaneros, cinnamon and nutmeg. The snapper with spicy Jamaican escovitch sauce is delicious and moist.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Worldwide Flavorfest<br/>Takeout: All Over the Menu</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/cincinnati/island-frydays" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.50899,39.13256,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Melt Eclectic Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Melt Eclectic Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cincinnati, OH 45223</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5136816358" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(513) 681-6358</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.meltcincy.com/main/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.meltcincy.com/main</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Melt+Eclectic+Cafe%2C+4165+Hamilton+Ave%2C+Cincinnati%2C+OH+45223&amp;ll=39.162515,-84.540042" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4165 Hamilton Ave<br/>Cincinnati, OH 45223</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Veggie 3-Way, Yeehaw BBQ Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Melt serves local flavors with healthy ingredients. The popular Veggie 3-Way with Spaghetti or Redskins is a favorite among vegetarians and meat eaters alike. Guy can&#x27;t believe there&#x27;s no meat in the dish. The Yeehaw BBQ sandwich with chicken, pico de gallo, BBQ sauce and mozzarella is also a hit.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Seriously Saucy</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/cincinnati/melt-eclectic-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.54004,39.16251,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Senate Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Senate Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cincinnati, OH 45202</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5134212020" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(513) 421-2020</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://senatepub.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">senatepub.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Senate+Pub%2C+1212+Vine+St%2C+Cincinnati%2C+OH+45202&amp;ll=39.108796,-84.514628" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1212 Vine St<br/>Cincinnati, OH 45202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">One Street Wonders</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/cincinnati/senate-pub" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.51463,39.10880,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pho Lang Thang</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pho Lang Thang</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cincinnati, OH 45202 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5133769177" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(513) 376-9177</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/dothelangthang" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/dothelangthang</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pho+Lang+Thang%2C+114+W.+Elder+St%2C+Cincinnati%2C+OH+45202&amp;ll=39.115481,-84.518891" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">114 W. Elder St<br/>Cincinnati, OH 45202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pho Lang Thang is Vietnamese comfort food at its finest. Pho, the hearty Vietnamese noodle soup, is the name of the game and this restaurant&#x27;s specialty. Locals happily queue for the fortifying beef-based broth, but if you&#x27;re in a sandwich mood be sure to check out their take on the classic banh mi, with housemade head cheese, roast pork and pickled vegetables.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Soup-Centric</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/cincinnati/pho-lang-thang" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.51889,39.11548,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Taste of Belgium</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Taste of Belgium</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cincinnati, OH 45202 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5133965800" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">513-396-5800</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://authenticwaffle.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">authenticwaffle.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Taste+of+Belgium%2C+1133+Vine+St%2C+Cincinnati%2C+OH+45202&amp;ll=39.108141,-84.514847" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1133 Vine St<br/>Cincinnati, OH 45202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Belgian Waffle, Carbonnades</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This spot serves Belgian classics that Guy finds irresistible. He declares the dense Belgian waffle to be &quot;outstanding&quot; and also digs the Belgian pretzel with a side of beer cheese. If you are in the mood for something heartier, try the Carbonnades - a traditional stew made with beer-braised beef.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">World Class Flavor<br/>One Street Wonders</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/cincinnati/taste-of-belgium" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.51485,39.10814,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blue Ash Chili</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blue Ash Chili</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cincinnati, OH 45242 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5139846107" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">513-984-6107</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.blueashchili.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.blueashchili.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blue+Ash+Chili%2C+9565+Kenwood+Rd%2C+Cincinnati%2C+OH+45242&amp;ll=39.231912,-84.376960" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">9565 Kenwood Rd<br/>Cincinnati, OH 45242</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Blue Ash Chili, No Freakin&#x27; Way</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The chili at this Cincinnatiinstitution can be served plain, 3-way, 4-way, 5-way or 6-way. Learning the lingo didn&#x27;t take long for Guy Fieri. He ordered the 6-way, which includes everything: chili, spaghetti, beans, onions, cheese and fried jalapeno caps.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort Food With Attitude<br/>Big Bites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/cincinnati/blue-ash-chili-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.37696,39.23191,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bakersfield OTR</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bakersfield OTR</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cincinnati, OH 45202 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5135790446" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(513) 579-0446</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bakersfieldotr.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bakersfieldotr.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bakersfield+OTR%2C+1213+Vine+St%2C+Cincinnati%2C+OH+45202&amp;ll=39.108687,-84.515130" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1213 Vine St<br/>Cincinnati, OH 45202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">One Street Wonders</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/cincinnati/bakersfield-otr" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.51513,39.10869,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Pit Stop Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Pit Stop Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Merrick, NY 11566 &middot; &#9733; 2.9 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5162237799" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(516) 223 -7799</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pitstopeats.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pitstopeats.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Pit+Stop+Restaurant%2C+1706+Sunrise+Hwy%2C+Merrick%2C+NY+11566&amp;ll=40.660306,-73.563153" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1706 Sunrise Hwy<br/>Merrick, NY 11566</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cuban Sandwich, Stuffed Spaghetti Squash</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Rubano family believes in serving only fresh homemade meals to Pit Stop&#x27;s loyal fans. Guy could not wait to try the hefty Cuban sandwich and enjoyed the pulled pork and Virginia ham inside it. The stuffed spaghetti squash topped with fresh mozzarella and homemade marinara sauce also impressed.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Little Twisted</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/merrick/the-pitstop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.56315,40.66031,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pounds</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pounds</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fargo, ND 58102 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="ttps://www.poundsfargo.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">ttps://www.poundsfargo.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pounds%2C+612+1st+Ave+N%2C+Fargo%2C+ND+58102&amp;ll=46.876670,-96.788260" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612 1st Ave N<br/>Fargo, ND 58102</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When high school buddies Brandon Herz and Alan Kasin started this funky college town joint, they set out to build a place that everybody loves to go. Besides being a great spot for drinking and dancing, the food at Pounds packs some serious flavor. Guy couldn&#x27;t get enough of the BBQ Porker, a loaded mac and cheese dish topped with tender, juicy pulled pork and covered with homemade barbecue sauce and jalapenos. &quot;The pork is delicious and not dried out,&quot; he said, &quot;and the real kicker to the whole thing is the diced jalapenos. Little bit of the acidity, a little bit of the heat.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken and Briskets</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nd/fargo/pounds-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.78826,46.87667,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pizza Junction</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pizza Junction</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">North Tonawanda, NY 14120 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7166926366" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">716-692-6366</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thepizzajunction.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thepizzajunction.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pizza+Junction%2C+1269+Erie+Avenue%2C+North+Tonawanda%2C+NY+14120&amp;ll=43.051209,-78.846703" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1269 Erie Avenue<br/>North Tonawanda, NY 14120</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza, Sandwiches, Novelty Cakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Join host, Guy Fieri, of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, at Pizza Junction in North Tonawanda, NY, a 37-year-old restaurant turning sandwiches into amazing pizzas.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">PIZZA, PORK AND PAPRIKASH</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/north-tonawanda/pizza-junction-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-78.84670,43.05121,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ben&#x27;s Best Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ben&#x27;s Best Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Rego Park, NY 11374 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7188971700" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(718) 897-1700</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bensbestdeli.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bensbestdeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ben%27s+Best+Deli%2C+96-40+Queens+Blvd%2C+Rego+Park%2C+NY+11374&amp;ll=40.729376,-73.861372" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">96-40 Queens Blvd<br/>Rego Park, NY 11374</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kreplachs, Pastrami, Salami, Brisket, Stuffed Cabbage Rolls</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This 65-year-old Jewish establishment is one of the last kosher delis left in New York City. Guy loved the fried kreplachs, which he described as &quot;Jewish pot stickers.&quot; The boiled chicken soup comes with kreplachs as well. He also recommends the tender and juicy stuffed cabbage rolls.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Crepes to Kreplach<br/>Best of New York</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/rego-park/bens-best-deli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.86137,40.72938,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nichole&#x27;s Fine Pastry</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nichole&#x27;s Fine Pastry</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fargo 58103</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7012326430" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">701-232-6430</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.nicholesfinepastry.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.nicholesfinepastry.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nichole%27s+Fine+Pastry%2C+13+S.+8th+St.%2C+Fargo+58103&amp;ll=46.873979,-96.791272" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">13 S. 8th St.<br/>Fargo 58103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lemon Curd Layer Cake</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After attending the Culinary Institute of America in California, Nichole Hensen returned to North Dakota, honing her skills at two local businesses before opening a spot of her own, Nichole&#x27;s Fine Pastry, in 2003. Using local, organic ingredients but European technique, Hensen turns out spectacular cakes like the Lemon Curd Layer Cake.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Savory Meat and a Little Sweet</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nd/fargo/nicholes-fine-pastry-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.79127,46.87398,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hildebrandt&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hildebrandt&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Williston Park, NY 11596 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5167410608" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">516-741-0608</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hildebrandtsrestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hildebrandtsrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hildebrandt%27s%2C+84+Hillside+Ave%2C+Williston+Park%2C+NY+11596&amp;ll=40.757405,-73.642868" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">84 Hillside Ave<br/>Williston Park, NY 11596</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homemade Butter Pecan Ice Cream, Mozzarella Sticks, Pasta Asiago</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Relive the &#x27;20s at this old-fashioned ice cream parlor, complete with a soda counter and Italian comfort food. Guy enjoyed the fan favorite: homemade butter pecan ice cream topped with whipped cream and a side of butterscotch. For a filling meal, order the mozzarella sticks and cheesy pasta Asiago.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Mozz to Matzo Balls<br/>Dynamite Desserts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/williston-park/hildebrandts-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.64287,40.75741,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sweet n Savory Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sweet n Savory Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wilmington, NC 28403 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9102560115" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(910) 256-0115</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.sweetnsavory.cafe" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sweetnsavory.cafe</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sweet+n+Savory+Cafe%2C+1611+Pavilion+Pl.%2C+Wilmington%2C+NC+28403&amp;ll=34.221185,-77.820042" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1611 Pavilion Pl.<br/>Wilmington, NC 28403</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wrightsville Beach French Toast, Mutha Heffer Sandwich (Meatloaf Sandwich)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Open for breakfast, brunch, lunch and dinner, Sweet n Savory Cafe is a must-try option while passing through Wilmington. The menu includes something for everyone with classic dishes (pot roast, chicken pot pie, meatloaf, etc.) and incredible creations from the restaurant&#x27;s Executive chef and Sous chef.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">East Coast, West Coast</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/restaurants-in-wilmington/sweet-n-savory-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.82004,34.22118,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ceviche&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ceviche&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wilmington, NC 28403 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.wbceviche.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.wbceviche.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ceviche%27s%2C+7210+Wrightsville+Ave%2C+Wilmington%2C+NC+28403&amp;ll=34.220246,-77.816378" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7210 Wrightsville Ave<br/>Wilmington, NC 28403</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ropa Vieja, Sancocho, Ceviche</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and co-owner Hunter Tiblier grew up in Panama while his dad was working on the Panama Canal. At Ceviche&#x27;s he&#x27;s bringing the Latin-inspired dishes of his childhood to North Carolina. The Ropa Vieja is a homerun. Chef Tiblier takes spicy braised flank steak and serves it with citrus cabbage slaw, coconut rice, fried plantains, salsa fresca and avocado. Not surprisingly they also do killer authentic ceviche.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lights-Out Latin</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/restaurants-in-wilmington/ceviches-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.81638,34.22025,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Copper Penny</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Copper Penny</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wilmington, NC 28401 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.copperpennync.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.copperpennync.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Copper+Penny%2C+109+Chestnut+St%2C+Wilmington%2C+NC+28401&amp;ll=34.237852,-77.948443" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">109 Chestnut St<br/>Wilmington, NC 28401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">109 Chestnut Chicken Sandwich, Hot Roasted Pork Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For a taste of Philly in North Carolina, head to Copper Penny where owner Brian Cadwallader is serving up inventive pub food. The 109 Chestnut Chicken Sandwich is a take on a chicken Philly cheesesteak. It is served with their famous onion rings. &quot;Keep those onion rings away from me,&quot; Guy said after he couldn&#x27;t stop eating them, &quot;I never want to see them again.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza, Pork and Peru</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/restaurants-in-wilmington/copper-penny-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.94844,34.23785,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mulberry Italian Ristorante</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mulberry Italian Ristorante</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lackawanna, NY 14218 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7168224292" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(716) 822-4292</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mulberryitalianristorante.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mulberryitalianristorante.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mulberry+Italian+Ristorante%2C+64+Jackson+Ave%2C+Lackawanna%2C+NY+14218&amp;ll=42.813168,-78.842255" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">64 Jackson Ave<br/>Lackawanna, NY 14218</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lasagna, Meatballs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">With meatballs larger than your standard league baseball, Mulberry Restaurant knows a thing or two about home-run meals. Guy didn&#x27;t leave hungry with their filling lobster ravioli, hand-stuffed peppers and mountain-high lasagna packed edge to edge with sausage, chicken and creamy Parmesan ricotta.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homegrown And Homemade</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/lackawanna/mulberry-cafe-llc-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-78.84226,42.81317,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Outer Banks Brewing Station</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Outer Banks Brewing Station</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kill Devils Hill, NC 27948 &middot; &#9733; 2.7 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2524492739" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(252) 449-2739</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.obbrewing.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.obbrewing.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Outer+Banks+Brewing+Station%2C+600+South+Croatan+Hwy%2C+Kill+Devils+Hill%2C+NC+27948&amp;ll=35.959638,-75.626236" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">600 South Croatan Hwy<br/>Kill Devils Hill, NC 27948</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Shrimp and Grits, Handcrafted Beer</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This pub is committed to lessening its carbon footprint and not only sources local seafood and produce but also generate its own power using a wind turbine. Guy was impressed by the shrimp and grits with redeye gravy and sweet potato chips. Locals enjoy a handcrafted beer with their meal.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pubs and Grub</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/kill-devils-hill/outer-banks-brewing-station-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.62624,35.95964,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cravings</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cravings</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Duck, NC 27949 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2524800032" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(252) 480-0032</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://coastalprovisionsmarket.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">coastalprovisionsmarket.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cravings%2C+1209+Duck+Rd%2C+Duck%2C+NC+27949&amp;ll=36.166249,-75.753986" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1209 Duck Rd<br/>Duck, NC 27949</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Seared Scallops, Steamer Pot</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cravings may seem like an unintimidating drive-through next to a gas station, but don&#x27;t be fooled. It serves what Guy calls &quot;killer seafood.&quot; Try the seared scallops with Lobster lobster sauce and truffle oil, or a traditional Carolina dish - the steamer pot loaded with seafood, corn, sausages, and more.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Far Out<br/>Fun in the Sun</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nc/duck/cravings-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.75399,36.16625,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nic&#x27;s Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nic&#x27;s Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oklahoma City 73107 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4055240999" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">405-524-0999</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Nics-Grill/183680334996829" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Nics-Grill/183680334996829</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nic%27s+Grill%2C+1201+N+Pennsylvania+Ave%2C+Oklahoma+City+73107&amp;ll=35.480936,-97.548102" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1201 N Pennsylvania Ave<br/>Oklahoma City 73107</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Onion Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This neighborhood gem is cranking out comfort food specials, like pork chops on Tuesdays and meatloaf on Fridays. The 15-seat joint became a legend for its mouthwatering half-pound burgers served with an overflowing basket of french fries and a fork.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Name That Cook<br/>Knockout Burger Joints<br/>Triple D Nation: Breakfast, Lunch and Brunch</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/oklahoma-city/nics-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.54810,35.48094,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mama E&#x27;s Wings &amp; Waffles</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mama E&#x27;s Wings &amp; Waffles</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oklahoma City, OK 73111 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4054240800" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(405) 424-0800</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/oklahoma-city/mama-es-wings-waffles-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/oklahoma-city/mama-es-wings-waffles-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mama+E%27s+Wings+%26+Waffles%2C+3838+Springlake+Dr.%2C+Oklahoma+City%2C+OK+73111&amp;ll=35.509400,-97.492167" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3838 Springlake Dr.<br/>Oklahoma City, OK 73111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wings and Waffles, Collard Greens</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Join host, Guy Fieri, of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, at Mama E&#x27;s Wings &amp; Waffles in Oklahoma City, OK, for some unforgettable soul food.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mama&#x27;s Cookin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/oklahoma-city/mama-es-wings-waffles-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.49217,35.50940,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Grover&#x27;s Bar &amp; Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Grover&#x27;s Bar &amp; Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">East Amherst, NY 14051 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7166361803" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(716) 636-1803</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Grovers-Bar-And-Grill-164012556991861/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/Grovers-Bar-And-Grill-164012556991861</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Grover%27s+Bar+%26+Grill%2C+9160+Transit+Rd%2C+East+Amherst%2C+NY+14051&amp;ll=43.018403,-78.697424" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">9160 Transit Rd<br/>East Amherst, NY 14051</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Cheeseburger Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eat your cheeseburger with a spoon - cheeseburger soup, that is - at this funky joint run by a mother-daughter duo. With a menu full of hearty comfort foods, you won&#x27;t leave hungry, especially if you order the 12-ounce Bruiser Burger with blue cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dives Worth a Drive</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/east-amherst/grovers-bar-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-78.69742,43.01840,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Sparrow Tavern</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Sparrow Tavern</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Astoria, NY 11102</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7186062260" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(718) 606-2260</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://thesparrowtavern.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">thesparrowtavern.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Sparrow+Tavern%2C+24-01+29th+St%2C+Astoria%2C+NY+11102&amp;ll=40.772773,-73.916412" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">24-01 29th St<br/>Astoria, NY 11102</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Veggie Burger, Bacon and Brie Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Even with its rock &#x27;n&#x27; roll vibe, The Sparrow Tavern has a knack for fresh and healthy bar food. As Guy discovered on Triple D, The Sparrow Tavern has a righteous bacon and Brie burger. For the ultimate twist, try the super moist veggie burger -- the maple cayenne mayo is addictive.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bar Food and Bon Bons</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/astoria/the-sparrow-tavern-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.91641,40.77277,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Earl&#x27;s Drive-In</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Earl&#x27;s Drive-In</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chaffee, NY 14030</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7164965125" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">716-496-5125</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/chaffee/earls-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/chaffee/earls-drive-in-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Earl%27s+Drive-In%2C+12139+Olean+Rd.+at+Rt+16%2C+Chaffee%2C+NY+14030&amp;ll=42.547775,-78.475935" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">12139 Olean Rd. at Rt 16<br/>Chaffee, NY 14030</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken a la King with Buttermilk Biscuits, Pies</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Join host Guy Fieri, of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, at Earl&#x27;s Drive-In in Chaffee, NY, a 42-year-old restaurant next to a farm, where they&#x27;re serving old school American classics.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Twists And Traditions</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/chaffee/earls-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-78.47594,42.54778,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Queens Comfort</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Queens Comfort</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Astoria, NY 11103 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7187282350" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(718) 728-2350</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://queenscomfort.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">queenscomfort.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Queens+Comfort%2C+4009+30th+Ave%2C+Astoria%2C+NY+11103&amp;ll=40.763853,-73.914521" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4009 30th Ave<br/>Astoria, NY 11103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Atomic Fireballs (Spicy Mac-and-Cheese Balls), Down by Law Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D meets double D - Donnie D&#x27;Alessio, the chef at Queens Comfort. Guy raves about the Down by Law sandwich packed with thin slices of smoked chicken topped with bacon jam, cheddar, chipotle sauce and lettuce. Diners also love snacking on spicy mac-and-cheese balls, aka Atomic Fireballs.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Things New York<br/>Amazing Appetizers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/astoria/queen_s-comfort" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.91452,40.76385,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sophia&#x27;s Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sophia&#x27;s Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Buffalo, NY 14216 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7164479661" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(716) 447-9661</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/buffalo/sophia-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/buffalo/sophia-restaurant-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sophia%27s+Restaurant%2C+749+Military+Rd%2C+Buffalo%2C+NY+14216&amp;ll=42.957703,-78.889090" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">749 Military Rd<br/>Buffalo, NY 14216</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Open-Faced Steak Sandwich, Souvlaki, Bologna Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sophia Ananiadias passed off her restaurant, Sophia&#x27;s Restaurant, to her son Sam. Together they&#x27;ve been cranking out Greek specials and American classics all by hand. Guy was amazed by the fresh-baked bread used for the fried bologna sandwich stacked a mile high with hot mustard and onions.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">And The Kicker Is...</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/buffalo/sophia-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-78.88909,42.95770,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lake Effect Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lake Effect Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Buffalo, NY 14214 &middot; &#9733; 2.9 (17 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7168331952" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(716) 833-1952</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.curtinrestaurants.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.curtinrestaurants.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lake+Effect+Diner%2C+3165+Main+St%2C+Buffalo%2C+NY+14214&amp;ll=42.950247,-78.826468" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3165 Main St<br/>Buffalo, NY 14214</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza; Meatballs; Chicken Parmesan; Italian Fish; House-Cured Ham with Red Eye Gravy, Eggs, Home Fries and Toast</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A &#x27;50s diner reborn with what Guy called a &amp;quot;scratch cooking gone wild&amp;quot; style, Lake Effect Diner even cures their own ham. Try upscale versions of old classics like blueberry pancakes, or expand your palate with the Italian-style Fish and a side of mac and cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Legacies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/buffalo/lake-effect-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-78.82647,42.95025,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blackthorn Restaurant &amp; Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blackthorn Restaurant &amp; Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Buffalo, NY 14210 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7168259327" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(716) 825-9327</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.blackthornrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.blackthornrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blackthorn+Restaurant+%26+Pub%2C+2134+Seneca+St%2C+Buffalo%2C+NY+14210&amp;ll=42.854378,-78.808057" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2134 Seneca St<br/>Buffalo, NY 14210</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef on Weck, Irish Beer Cheddar Soup, Triple D Platter</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy hits the Blackthorn Restaurant and Pub in Buffalo, NY, a local Irish watering hole making the home town favorite, a sandwich called &#x27;beef on weck.&#x27; Order the Triple D Platter to sample everything that was on the show: the beef on weck, crab cakes and a cup of Irish beer soup with tater tots.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Home And Away<br/>Pub Grub</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/buffalo/blackthorn-restaurant-and-pub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-78.80806,42.85438,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rincon Criollo</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rincon Criollo</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Corona-Queens, NY 11368 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7184580236" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(718) 458-0236</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rincon-criollo.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rincon-criollo.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rincon+Criollo%2C+40-09+Junction+Blvd%2C+Corona-Queens%2C+NY+11368&amp;ll=40.748795,-73.869164" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">40-09 Junction Blvd<br/>Corona-Queens, NY 11368</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Arroz con Pollo, Ropa Vieja</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Rudy Acosta has strict instructions from his great grandfather not to mess with any of their Cuban family recipes. The giant serving of arroz con pollo amazed Guy with its savory flavors. He could not get enough of the ropa vieja, a house fave with shredded beef in tomato sauce, beans and rice.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meat Madness<br/>Crazy for Chicken</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/corona-queens/rincon-criollo-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.86916,40.74880,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cattlemen&#x27;s Steakhouse</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cattlemen&#x27;s Steakhouse</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oklahoma City, OK 73108 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4052360416" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(405) 236-0416</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cattlemensrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cattlemensrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cattlemen%27s+Steakhouse%2C+1309+S+Agnew%2C+Oklahoma+City%2C+OK+73108&amp;ll=35.452384,-97.554838" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1309 S Agnew<br/>Oklahoma City, OK 73108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Steaks, Sandwiches</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You know they&#x27;re seriously cranking it out when every steak goes through a needling machine, guaranteeing it&#x27;ll be tender. Get the &quot;Presidential Choice&quot; T-Bone Steak, named after President Bush Sr., who ordered it while visiting the steakhouse. Or try the popular Pepper Steak with peppercorn sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meaty Masterpieces<br/>Blast From the Past</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/oklahoma-city/cattlemens-steakhouse-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.55484,35.45238,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Chick N Beer</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Chick N Beer</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oklahoma City 73103</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.chicknbeerokc.com/home" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.chicknbeerokc.com/home</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Chick+N+Beer%2C+715+NW+23rd+St%2C+Oklahoma+City+73103&amp;ll=35.493499,-97.524771" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">715 NW 23rd St<br/>Oklahoma City 73103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The husband and wife team at Chick -n- Beer are taking wings to all different levels. They start with juicy, brined wings and dredge them in potato flour for a lightcrunch, then double fry and coat them in one of their many sauces, like Buffalo-style kicked up with Sriracha or tangy szechuan Parmesan.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Vikings to Wings</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/oklahoma-city/chick-n-beer-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.52477,35.49350,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Melt Bar &amp; Grilled</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Melt Bar &amp; Grilled</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lakewood, OH 44107 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2162263699" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(216) 226-3699</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.meltbarandgrilled.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.meltbarandgrilled.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Melt+Bar+%26+Grilled%2C+14718+Detroit+Ave%2C+Lakewood%2C+OH+44107&amp;ll=41.485345,-81.799047" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">14718 Detroit Ave<br/>Lakewood, OH 44107</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gourmet Grilled Cheese Sandwiches, The Godfather</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">It takes a special genius to make a grilled cheese lasagna sandwich. Lucky for Anne Thornton that Matt Fish opened Melt Bar &amp;amp; Grilled with the lasagna Godfather sandwich. But he didn&#x27;t stop there: The Monster grilled cheese goes mad scientist with its 13 different cheeses and three slices of bread.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Super Sandwiches<br/>By Request</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/lakewood/melt-bar-and-grilled-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.79905,41.48534,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Leo&#x27;s BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Leo&#x27;s BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oklahoma City 73111 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4054245367" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">405-424-5367</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/oklahoma-city/leos-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/oklahoma-city/leos-bbq-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Leo%27s+BBQ%2C+3631+N+Kelley+Ave%2C+Oklahoma+City+73111&amp;ll=35.507415,-97.494674" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3631 N Kelley Ave<br/>Oklahoma City 73111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ, Ribs, Strawberry Banana Cake</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">According to Chef Charles Smith, the secret to his great tasting barbecue is love. Guy got messy with the spare ribs dripping with the house-made BBQ sauce and loved the hot links. Save some room for dessert, too, because all dinners are served with a free piece of strawberry banana cake.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Local Legends<br/>Triple D Nation: BBQ, Burgers and Beyond<br/>Dynamite Desserts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/oklahoma-city/leos-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.49467,35.50742,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ingrid&#x27;s Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ingrid&#x27;s Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oklahoma City, OK 73112 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4059468444" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(405) 946-8444</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.ingridskitchen.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.ingridskitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ingrid%27s+Kitchen%2C+3701+N+Youngs+Blvd%2C+Oklahoma+City%2C+OK+73112&amp;ll=35.507994,-97.552373" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3701 N Youngs Blvd<br/>Oklahoma City, OK 73112</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Schnitzel, Reuben, Bratwurst Sausages</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Called Oklahoma&#x27;s best-kept secret, Ingrid&#x27;s Kitchen is a go-to spot for authentic German cuisine. Guy loved the Reuben sandwich and the bratwurst plate. But the real kicker? Ingrid bakes more than nine types of rye breads each day, with more than 150 varieties of baked goods served weekly.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Home And Away</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/oklahoma-city/ingrids-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.55237,35.50799,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Sandwich League</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Sandwich League</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Eugene, OR 97402 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5412858069" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(541) 285-8069</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/TheSandwichLeague" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/TheSandwichLeague</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Sandwich+League%2C+272+Van+Buren+St%2C+Eugene%2C+OR+97402&amp;ll=44.057017,-123.109918" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">272 Van Buren St<br/>Eugene, OR 97402</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork on Pork, Meaty Cheesy Goodness</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This funky food truck is known for its meaty sandwiches. Guy calls the Pork on Pork a &quot;monster of a sandwich.&quot; It&#x27;s packed with pork and topped with bacon, fries, cilantro slaw and onions. He also raves about the &quot;rich piece of meat&quot; that gives the Meaty Cheesy Goodness grilled cheese its name.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meat in the Middle</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/eugene/the-sandwich-league" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-123.10992,44.05702,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Soup Nation Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Soup Nation Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Eugene, OR 97401 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5416831999" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">541-683-1999</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.soupnationeugene.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.soupnationeugene.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Soup+Nation+Cafe%2C+525+High+St.%2C+Eugene%2C+OR+97401&amp;ll=44.053834,-123.087858" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">525 High St.<br/>Eugene, OR 97401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Around the world in 80 bowls: Soup Nation helps diners travel the globe with a rotating menu of more than 80 international soups. From the stocks and broths to the sourdough bread, everything is made from scratch for the rotating menu of nine daily choices, which include gluten-free, vegan and nut-free options.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Soup-Centric</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/eugene/soup-nation-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-123.08786,44.05383,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cornbread Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cornbread Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Eugene, OR 97402 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5415059175" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(541) 505-9175</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cornbreadcafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cornbreadcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cornbread+Cafe%2C+1290+W+7th+Ave%2C+Eugene%2C+OR+97402&amp;ll=44.051785,-123.112284" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1290 W 7th Ave<br/>Eugene, OR 97402</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Surata Tofu, Frozen Peanut Butter Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">In a first for his show, Guy visits a 100 percent vegan eatery. This cafe &quot;veganizes&quot; Southern-style comfort food with tasty results. Guy says even diners who dislike vegan food will dig the Eugenewich, which features fried Surata tofu and a smoky sauce. The frozen peanut butter pie is also a hit.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old School Joints<br/>Dynamite Desserts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/eugene/corn-bread-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-123.11228,44.05178,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fisherman&#x27;s Market</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fisherman&#x27;s Market</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Eugene, OR 97402 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5414842722" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(541) 484-2722</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.eugenefishmarket.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.eugenefishmarket.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fisherman%27s+Market%2C+830+West+7th+St.%2C+Eugene%2C+OR+97402&amp;ll=44.051922,-123.105422" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">830 West 7th St.<br/>Eugene, OR 97402</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fresh Dungeness Crab; Crawfish Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fish is rarely fresher than at this restaurant inside a fish market. Owner Ryan Rogers, a former fisherman, wanted to serve the freshest seafood in the Pacific Northwest. Most of his dishes come from Oregon-based fishing boats, including wild-caught-crawfish pie, along with Dungeness crab that Guy samples right off the boat.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fresh Fish &amp; Funky Chicken</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/eugene/fishermans-market" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-123.10542,44.05192,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Papa&#x27;s Soul Food Kitchen and BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Papa&#x27;s Soul Food Kitchen and BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Eugene, OR 97402 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5413427500" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(541) 342-7500</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.papassoulfoodkitchen.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.papassoulfoodkitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Papa%27s+Soul+Food+Kitchen+and+BBQ%2C+400+Blair+Blvd.%2C+Eugene%2C+OR+97402&amp;ll=44.055303,-123.109391" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">400 Blair Blvd.<br/>Eugene, OR 97402</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Soul Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Papa&#x27;s Soul Food Kitchen and BBQ feels more like a party than a restaurant, with live music, good company and better-than-homemade soul food. The classic barbecue meats are exceptional for a restaurant west of the Mississippi, but the off-menu Soul Burger - a smoked pork patty with slaw and fried onions - is completely original.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Chowfest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/eugene/papas-soul-food-kitchen-and-bbq" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-123.10939,44.05530,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Shirley&#x27;s Tippy Canoe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Shirley&#x27;s Tippy Canoe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Troutdale 97060 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5034922220" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(503) 492-2220</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.shirleysfood.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.shirleysfood.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Shirley%27s+Tippy+Canoe%2C+28242+E+Historic+Columbia+River+Hwy%2C+Troutdale+97060&amp;ll=45.516423,-122.369485" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">28242 E Historic Columbia River Hwy<br/>Troutdale 97060</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Housemade Sloppy Joe</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The firecracker behind Shirley&#x27;s Tippy Canoe, Shirley Welton, has turned this former biker bar into a haven for what Guy calls &quot;real food that&#x27;s real deal.&quot; That includes homemade sloppy joes, polish sausage and The Captain&#x27;s Plate - a seafood feast with prawns, salmon, oysters and more.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Surf and Turf<br/>From the Heart<br/>All-American All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/troutdale/shirleys-tippy-canoe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.36948,45.51642,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sammich</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sammich</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ashland, OR 97520</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://sammichrestaurants.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">sammichrestaurants.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sammich%2C+424+Bridge+St%2C+Ashland%2C+OR+97520&amp;ll=42.186945,-122.693513" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">424 Bridge St<br/>Ashland, OR 97520</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicago Italian Beef, Pastrami Zombie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Melissa McMillan, aka Chef Mel, has appeared twice on Guy&#x27;s Grocery Games. She opened Sammich because she missed the food she used to get in Chicago. Try the Chicago Italian Beef, served wet with classic giardiniera and roasted peppers and the Pastrami Zombie made with their house-brined, smoked and steamed pastrami. &quot;This is like sandwich revolution,&quot; Guy said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Stuffed Stuff</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/ashland/sammich-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.69351,42.18695,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blue Toba</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blue Toba</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ashland, OR 97520</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://bluetoba.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">bluetoba.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blue+Toba%2C+1690+Ashland+St%2C+Ashland%2C+OR+97520&amp;ll=42.185344,-122.685413" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1690 Ashland St<br/>Ashland, OR 97520</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rendang, Opor</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The folks of Ashland have Chef Birong Hutabarat and his wife Leslie Hutabarat transporting them to Indonesia in the heart of Oregon. They specialize in super flavorful curries that incorporate spices brought back from fresh markets in Indonesia</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Culinary Journey</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/ashland/blue-toba-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.68541,42.18534,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Agave</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Agave</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ashland, OR 97520 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.agavetaco.net/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.agavetaco.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Agave%2C+5+Granite+St%2C+Ashland%2C+OR+97520&amp;ll=42.198091,-122.716177" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5 Granite St<br/>Ashland, OR 97520</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Carnitas Torta, Tamales</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For fresh and simple Mexican fare in Ashland, Agave is the place to go. Guy loved the Winter Squash and Portobello Tamales with house made red tamale sauce and thought the Carnitas Torta was dynamite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwiches, Southern and South of the Border</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/ashland/agave-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.71618,42.19809,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Viking Soul Food</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Viking Soul Food</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97215</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.vikingsoulfood.com/#where-to-find-us" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.vikingsoulfood.com/#where-to-find-us</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Viking+Soul+Food%2C+4255+SE+Belmont+St%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97215&amp;ll=45.516782,-122.618372" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4255 SE Belmont St<br/>Portland, OR 97215</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Take a trip through the food carts featured at The Bite on Belmont in Portland, Oregon and stop at Viking Soul Food for a taste of some big Scandinavian flavors. A popular item is the thin lefse potato bread which can be wrapped with all different fillings. Guy tried the meatball lefse which is topped with a Scandinavian cheese sauce, sweet and sour cabbage and white cabbage. &quot;How have I existed this long without having this?&quot; he asked.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Vikings to Wings</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/Viking-soul-food-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.61837,45.51678,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Matt&#x27;s BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Matt&#x27;s BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97217 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5163144739" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">516-314 4739</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mattsbbqpdx.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mattsbbqpdx.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Matt%27s+BBQ%2C+4233+N+Mississippi+Ave%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97217&amp;ll=45.556989,-122.661878" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4233 N Mississippi Ave<br/>Portland, OR 97217</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spare Ribs, The Whole Shabamwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Matt Vicedomini turns out big flavors from inside his tiny food truck, where he&#x27;s smoking meats that made Guy&#x27;s mouth water. &quot;Pull-apart tender,&quot; Guy declared of the Texas-style spare ribs smothered in an onion-and-garlic-laced glaze. Another standout is the Whole Shabamwich, a hefty sandwich that&#x27;s stacked with pulled pork, sausages, brisket and a rib, along with coleslaw and pickles. &quot;It&#x27;s dynamite, man,&quot; Guy raved.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mega Mouthfuls</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/matts-bbq" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.66188,45.55699,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Tin Shed Garden Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Tin Shed Garden Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97211</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5032886966" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(503) 288-6966</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://tinshedgardencafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">tinshedgardencafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Tin+Shed+Garden+Cafe%2C+1438+NE+Alberta+St%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97211&amp;ll=45.558951,-122.650882" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1438 NE Alberta St<br/>Portland, OR 97211</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fungus Among Us Sandwich, Heartless Artichoke Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">There&#x27;s a little something for everyone at the Tin Shed Garden Cafe. Guy devoured their ooey-gooey (and vegetarian) heartless artichoke grilled cheese. For a heartier bite, try the juicy pulled-pork barbacoa sliders or the Baby Beluga black curry lentils, available vegan or gluten-free.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort and Soul</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/the-tin-shed-garden-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.65088,45.55895,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tails &amp; Trotters</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tails &amp; Trotters</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97232</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5034778682" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">503-477-8682</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tailsandtrotters.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tailsandtrotters.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tails+%26+Trotters%2C+525+NE+24th+Ave%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97232&amp;ll=45.527081,-122.641707" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">525 NE 24th Ave<br/>Portland, OR 97232</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hazelnut-Finished Pork, Grinder Sandwich, Porchetta Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Locals head to this shop that Guy describes as a &quot;smorgasbord of pork&quot; to load up on the signature meats made from hazelnut-finished pigs. Owner Aaron Silverman offers a plethora of pork products, as well as hefty sandwiches stacked with meat. &quot;Luscious,&quot; Guy said of the house-cured coppa that&#x27;s the star of the Grinder sandwich. The coppa is layered with ham, lonza and provolone on a slab of aioli-slicked ciabatta, then topped with lettuce, red onions and a squirt of red wine vinegar.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Carnivore Creations</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/tails-and-trotters-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.64171,45.52708,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Original</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Original</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97204</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5035462666" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">503-546-2666</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://originaldinerant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">originaldinerant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Original%2C+300+SW+6th+Ave%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97204&amp;ll=45.521436,-122.676916" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">300 SW 6th Ave<br/>Portland, OR 97204</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Our Chicken &amp; Waffles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Described by its culinary team as &quot;rock &#x27;n&#x27; roll and tattoos,&quot; The Original Dinerant offers a modern take on &#x27;50s and &#x27;60s diners by way of amped-up American favorites featuring local and seasonal ingredients. Creative riffs on the classics include a cheese-smothered beef slider patty served between two piping-hot halves of a glazed housemade doughnut. Another standout is the chicken and waffles that Guy called a &quot;contender for the title.&quot; Jalapeno-and-cheddar-studded buttermilk waffles come heaped with crisp chicken confit and drenched in smoked maple syrup.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brunch, Bologna and Burgers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/the-original-dinerant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.67692,45.52144,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Industrial Cafe and Saloon</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Industrial Cafe and Saloon</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97210 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5032277002" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(503) 227-7002</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/Industrial-Cafe/126750844029465" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Industrial-Cafe/126750844029465</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Industrial+Cafe+and+Saloon%2C+2572+NW+Vaughn+St%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97210&amp;ll=45.536653,-122.704301" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2572 NW Vaughn St<br/>Portland, OR 97210</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">House Smoked Chicken Wings, Hawaiian Style Beef Ribs, Reuben</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ironwork furnishings round out The Industrial Cafe and Saloon&#x27;s menu of stick-to-your-ribs comfort food. Guy devoured the chipped beef and pastrami Reuben. As for the corned beef, it&#x27;s built from the ground up with locally raised cattle, courtesy of Lucky Tough Land Cattle. How&#x27;s that for fresh?</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Neighborhood Knockouts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/the-industrial-cafe-and-saloon-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.70430,45.53665,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Country Cat</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Country Cat</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, OR 97215 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5034081414" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(503) 408-1414</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://thecountrycat.net/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">thecountrycat.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Country+Cat%2C+7937+SE+Stark%2C+Portland%2C+OR+97215&amp;ll=45.519311,-122.581655" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7937 SE Stark<br/>Portland, OR 97215</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Whole Hog Plate, Cast-Iron Skillet Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Country Cat enticed Iron Chef winner Brad Farmerie with its home cooking and warm hospitality, but the cast-iron skillet fried chicken and red flannel hash keep him coming back. The shatteringly crisp fried chicken is served with an insane pecan-topped spoon bread that Chef Farmerie calls &quot;layers and layers and layers of delight.&quot; The red flannel hash, is a bright mixture of red beets and corned beef bound with sour cream and seasoned with freshly grated horseradish. The fuchsia mixture is pressed in a hot pan until it is an amalgamation of crispy, crunchy bits and then topped with a fried egg.
Guy also spoke highly of the fried chicken. &quot;It&#x27;s everything you want fried chicken to be,&quot; he said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meat Lover&#x27;s Paradise<br/>Rockstar Chefs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/the-country-cat-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.58165,45.51931,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Seasons &amp; Regions Seafood Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Seasons &amp; Regions Seafood Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland 97219</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.seasonsandregions.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.seasonsandregions.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Seasons+%26+Regions+Seafood+Grill%2C+6660+SW+Capitol+Hwy%2C+Portland+97219&amp;ll=45.475872,-122.705119" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6660 SW Capitol Hwy<br/>Portland 97219</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and owner Greg Schwab broke free of the corporate world to bring seasonal and regional seafood favorites to Portland, Oregon. His take on cioppino is packed with seasonal, local fish and topped with a crispy, fresh Dungeness crab cake.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sicilian and Seafood</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/Seasons-and-regions-seafood-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.70512,45.47587,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Swiss Hibiscus</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Swiss Hibiscus</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland 97211 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5034779224" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">503-477-9224</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://swisshibiscus.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">swisshibiscus.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Swiss+Hibiscus%2C+4950+NE+14th+Ave%2C+Portland+97211&amp;ll=45.558764,-122.651537" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4950 NE 14th Ave<br/>Portland 97211</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy stopped here to sample authentic Swiss dishes without stepping foot outside of the United States. Co-owner Jennie Wyss is carrying on the culinary legacy of her Swiss-born father by serving true European cuisine. Standouts include the spaetzle and paprika schnitzel. &quot;I can&#x27;t shovel this in my face fast enough,&quot; said Guy of the buttery, crunchy egg noodles and the paprika-laced pork medallions. He also raved about the emince zurichoise, a thinly sliced pork sirloin that comes smothered in a mushroom-studded sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Swiss, Sandwiches and Sausage</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/swiss-hibiscus-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.65154,45.55876,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sweet Carrot</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sweet Carrot</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Columbus, OH 43212</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6144887151" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">614-488-7151</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://sweetcarrot.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">sweetcarrot.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sweet+Carrot%2C+1417+W+5th+Ave%2C+Columbus%2C+OH+43212&amp;ll=39.988691,-83.044188" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1417 W 5th Ave<br/>Columbus, OH 43212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and owner Angela Petro brings creativity and fun to the cuisine at Sweet Carrot. The gorgeous Ohio Chicken Meatball sandwich is drizzled with a slightly-sweet, sesame-ginger sauce and topped with house-made spicy, roasted-corn salsa. &quot;I&#x27;d order that again for the next five years,&quot; said Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Breakfast, Brisket and Belly</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/columbus/sweet-carrot-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-83.04419,39.98869,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pierogi Mountain</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pierogi Mountain</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Columbus 43215 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6147453139" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">614 745 3139</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.pierogimountain.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pierogimountain.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pierogi+Mountain%2C+105+N+Grant+Ave%2C+Columbus+43215&amp;ll=39.965556,-82.991925" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">105 N Grant Ave<br/>Columbus 43215</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pierogi, Chicken Paprikash</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pierogi Mountain is a dive bar that serves pierogi and comfort food during the day and adds a side of punk rock at night. Vegetarians and vegans are welcome as eight of the nine pierogi offerings are vegetarian or vegan.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">College-Town Champs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/columbus/pierogi-mountain-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.99193,39.96556,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ena&#x27;s Caribbean Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ena&#x27;s Caribbean Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Columbus, OH 43211 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6142620988" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">614-262-0988</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/columbus/enas-caribbean-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/columbus/enas-caribbean-kitchen-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ena%27s+Caribbean+Kitchen%2C+2444+Cleveland+Ave%2C+Columbus%2C+OH+43211&amp;ll=40.017155,-82.965118" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2444 Cleveland Ave<br/>Columbus, OH 43211</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jerk Chicken, Red Snapper Escabeche</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ena&#x27;s Caribbean Kitchen is a family-filled Jamaican joint where Island favorite are fired up. Try the authentic jerk chicken or the whole red snapper which is deep fried and served with a vinegary escabeche sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mom&#x27;s Kitchen</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/columbus/enas-caribbean-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.96512,40.01716,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Loops</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Loops</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Columbus, OH 43212 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6146708808" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">614-670-8808</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.loopsgoodfood.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.loopsgoodfood.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Loops%2C+1629+Northwest+Blvd%2C+Columbus%2C+OH+43212&amp;ll=39.991624,-83.040858" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1629 Northwest Blvd<br/>Columbus, OH 43212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Italian Beef Sandwich, Gyros</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Head to this family-owned joint for a taste of Chicago favorites in Columbus, Ohio. Try the authentic Greek gyro made &#x27;the right way&#x27; with shaved spit-roasted pork shoulder and house-made tzatziki sauce. Don&#x27;t miss the Italian Beef sandwich which is drenched with a warm au jus and piled high with hot giardiniera for a tangy crunch.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sammies and Spice</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/columbus/loops-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-83.04086,39.99162,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ray Ray&#x27;s Hog Pit</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ray Ray&#x27;s Hog Pit</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Columbus, OH 43202 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6147531191" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">614-753-1191</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.rayrayshogpit.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rayrayshogpit.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ray+Ray%27s+Hog+Pit%2C+2619+N+High+St%2C+Columbus%2C+OH+43202&amp;ll=40.015742,-83.012137" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2619 N High St<br/>Columbus, OH 43202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mangalista Brat Burger, St. Louis Spare Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and Owner James Anderson raises his own pigs for the succulent smoked offerings at Ray Ray&#x27;s Hog Pit, a one-of-a-kind barbecue truck in Columbus, Ohio. Guy tried the super-moist Mangalitsa Brat Burger and St. Louis Spare Ribs.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">College-Town Champs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/columbus/ray-rays-hog-pit-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-83.01214,40.01574,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Momo Ghar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Momo Ghar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Columbus, OH 43229 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6147492901" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">614-749-2901</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/columbus/momo-ghar-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/columbus/momo-ghar-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Momo+Ghar%2C+1265+Morse+Rd%2C+Columbus%2C+OH+43229&amp;ll=40.060932,-82.985078" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1265 Morse Rd<br/>Columbus, OH 43229</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Johl Mo Mo, Choila Set</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and Owner Phinsto Lama is cooking up Tibetan and Nepalese specialties in the middle of an international market in Columbus. Her signature dish is Johl Mo Mo, Tibetan steamed dumplings filled with chicken and enrobed in a spicy fenugreek tomato sauce. The Choila Set, a Tibetan chicken salad with rice, potatoes and black-eyed peas is &quot;one of the most-unique dishes&quot; Guy has ever tried on DDD.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Delicious Discoveries</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/columbus/momo-ghar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.98508,40.06093,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sterle&#x27;s Slovenian Country House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sterle&#x27;s Slovenian Country House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cleveland, OH 44103 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2168814181" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(216) 881-4181</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sterlescountryhouse.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sterlescountryhouse.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sterle%27s+Slovenian+Country+House%2C+1401+E+55th+St%2C+Cleveland%2C+OH+44103&amp;ll=41.520771,-81.651582" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1401 E 55th St<br/>Cleveland, OH 44103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Paprikash, Wienerschnitzel</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Guy Fieri, gets served at Sterle&#x27;s Slovenian Country House in Cleveland, OH, a family place serving authentic European favorites like Chicken Paprikash.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">PIZZA, PORK AND PAPRIKASH</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/cleveland/sterles-slovenian-country-house-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.65158,41.52077,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Guyutes</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Guyutes</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oklahoma City, OK 73103 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://guyutes.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">guyutes.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Guyutes%2C+730+NW+23rd+St%2C+Oklahoma+City%2C+OK+73103&amp;ll=35.493174,-97.525582" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">730 NW 23rd St<br/>Oklahoma City, OK 73103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On DDD, there are some funky joints with some funky names, and Guyutes is no exception. This little oasis of cool was started by high school buddies Jarrod Friedel and Wayne Perotka, two Phish fans who named the restaurant after one of the band&#x27;s songs. Jarrod and Wayne&#x27;s unique take on food can be seen in menu items like The Guyute, the restaurant&#x27;s namesake dish comprised of creamy mashed potatoes, juicy pork belly, crispy wonton and basil whipped cream. Guy was impressed with the dish&#x27;s combination of flavors, saying that &quot;every bite is a little bit different.&quot; According to Guy, this place is &quot;just as funky as Phish.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Authentic to Inventive</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ok/oklahoma-city/guyutes-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.52558,35.49317,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Parkview Niteclub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Parkview Niteclub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cleveland, OH 44102 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2169611341" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(216) 961-1341</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.parkviewniteclub.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.parkviewniteclub.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Parkview+Niteclub%2C+1261+W+58th+St%2C+Cleveland%2C+OH+44102&amp;ll=41.488710,-81.726048" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1261 W 58th St<br/>Cleveland, OH 44102</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Salmon BLT</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Locals claim this laid-back Cleveland hangout is the go-to spot for a &amp;quot;good time with good food.&amp;quot; Sample their daily specials, like Tuesday&#x27;s Honey Chipotle Pork Tacos made with smoked jalapeno or Friday&#x27;s Fish Fries, or enjoy the Smoked Salmon BLT any day of the week.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dives Worth a Drive</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/cleveland/parkview-niteclub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.72605,41.48871,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Otto&#x27;s Sausage Kitchen &amp; Meat Market</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Otto&#x27;s Sausage Kitchen &amp; Meat Market</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland 97202 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5037716714" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(503) 771-6714</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.ottossausage.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.ottossausage.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Otto%27s+Sausage+Kitchen+%26+Meat+Market%2C+4138+SE+Woodstock+Blvd%2C+Portland+97202&amp;ll=45.478945,-122.619763" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4138 SE Woodstock Blvd<br/>Portland 97202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homemade Hot Dogs, Smoked Pastrami, Sausage, Otto&#x27;s Beer Cheese Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Otto&#x27;s they&#x27;re serving up 50 different kinds of sausages 7 days a week. The old-fashioned hot dogs are &quot;tender and creamy,&quot; according to Guy. Besides assorted bratwursts, deli meats like corned beef and roast beef are also available. For his sandwich, Guy got the &quot;killer&quot; smoked pastrami.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Go-To Joints<br/>Takeout: Best of the West Roundup</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/ottos-sausage-kitchen-meat-market-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.61976,45.47895,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Momocho</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Momocho</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cleveland 44113 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2166942122" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(216) 694-2122</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.momocho.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.momocho.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Momocho%2C+1835+Fulton+Rd%2C+Cleveland+44113&amp;ll=41.484004,-81.709808" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1835 Fulton Rd<br/>Cleveland 44113</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tuna Tacos with Blood Orange Marmalade and Guacamole with House Smoked Trout.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Momocho&#x27;s modern Mexican cuisine is fresh-to-order, meaning they&#x27;ve ditched the walk-in freezers and heat lamps. Guy paid a visit for the guacamole served six different ways (think goat cheese, crab and pineapple). But regulars love the machaca, a tender coffee and chile braised beef brisket.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Dinner and Dessert That Delivers<br/>Real Deal Mexican<br/>Twists And Traditions<br/>Triple D Nation: From Pork to Po&#x27; Boys</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/oh/cleveland/momocho-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.70981,41.48400,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Empire Brewing Company</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Empire Brewing Company</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Syracuse 13202 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3154752337" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(315) 475-2337</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/syracuse/empire-brewing-company-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/syracuse/empire-brewing-company-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Empire+Brewing+Company%2C+120+Walton+St%2C+Syracuse+13202&amp;ll=43.048096,-76.154607" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">120 Walton St<br/>Syracuse 13202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sweet Fire Fajitas, Sweet Potato Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Whether you&#x27;re looking for some Sunday brunch or a Sunday brew, this joint is just for you. Guy enjoyed the sweet fire fajitas with andouille sausage and marinated onions and peppers topped with cheddar Jack cheese. Diners enjoy drinking the craft beer with a side of sweet potato fries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Land to Sea</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/syracuse/empire-brewing-company-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.15461,43.04810,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Kitty Hoynes</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Kitty Hoynes</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Syracuse, NY 13202 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3154241974" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(315) 424-1974</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://kittyhoynes.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">kittyhoynes.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Kitty+Hoynes%2C+301+W+Fayette+St%2C+Syracuse%2C+NY+13202&amp;ll=43.048552,-76.155798" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">301 W Fayette St<br/>Syracuse, NY 13202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Reuben Fritters, Irish Meatloaf</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this top-of-the-line Irish Pub, Chef Damien Brownlow serves up pub food with a twist. Guy loved the Reuben fritters because of their creamy &quot;melt-in-your-mouth&quot; flavor and the accompanying honey mustard horseradish. He also liked the Irish meatloaf with cabbage cream sauce and champ potatoes.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turn On Traditional<br/>Northeast Feast</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/syracuse/kitty-hoynes-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.15580,43.04855,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Funk &#x27;n Waffles</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Funk &#x27;n Waffles</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Syracuse 13202 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3154741060" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">315-474-1060</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://funknwaffles.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">funknwaffles.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Funk+%27n+Waffles%2C+307+-+313+S+Clinton+St%2C+Syracuse+13202&amp;ll=43.042119,-76.136118" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">307 - 313 S Clinton St<br/>Syracuse 13202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jive Turkey (Turkey Dinner on a Stuffing Waffle), Chicken and Waffles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owner Adam Gold is still serving up waffles and blasting tunes just like he did at his college parties. Guy savored the &quot;sweet and crispy&quot; fried chicken and waffles with hot sauce syrup and devoured the stuffing waffle with smoked turkey, cranberry sauce and mashed potatoes.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Funky Finds in &#x27;da House<br/>Ultimate Turkey Fest<br/>Wildest Joints<br/>Far Out</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/syracuse/funk-n-waffles-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.13612,43.04212,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Eva&#x27;s European Sweets</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Eva&#x27;s European Sweets</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Syracuse, NY 13204 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3154872722" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(315) 487-2722</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.evaspolish.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.evaspolish.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Eva%27s+European+Sweets%2C+1305+Milton+Ave.%2C+Syracuse%2C+NY+13204&amp;ll=43.059612,-76.199611" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1305 Milton Ave.<br/>Syracuse, NY 13204</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Potato Pancakes, Sauerkraut</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The authentic home-style Polish comfort food and family atmosphere found at this cafe causes some to feel that they are actually in Poland. The crispy potato pancakes with gravy solicited an &amp;quot;Mmm&amp;quot; from Guy as he devoured the dish. Locals recommend the delicious pierogis and the savory kielbasa.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eurocentric</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/syracuse/evas-european-sweets-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.19961,43.05961,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Guero</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Guero</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland 97232</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.guerotortas.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.guerotortas.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Guero%2C+200+NE+28th+Ave%2C+Portland+97232&amp;ll=45.524456,-122.637075" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">200 NE 28th Ave<br/>Portland 97232</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Megan Sanchez and husband Alec Morrison started out delivering tacos but fell in love with tortas after a trip to Mexico. At Guero, they work to infuse deep flavor into all aspects of these traditional Mexican sandwiches. The Masa y Papa is a vegetarian option stuffed with a fried masa and potato pancake, tamarind roasted tomatoes, avocado, onion, cilantro, queso botanero, cabbage and pickled onion. &quot;That might be one of the best vegetarian Mexican tortas I&#x27;ve ever had,&quot; said Guy. &quot;I&#x27;d order that every day.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Flavortown International</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/or/portland/guero-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.63707,45.52446,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mama&#x27;s Food Shop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mama&#x27;s Food Shop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New York, NY 10009</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2127774425" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(212) 777-4425</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://mamasfoodshop.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">mamasfoodshop.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mama%27s+Food+Shop%2C+200+E.+Third+St.%2C+New+York%2C+NY+10009&amp;ll=40.722671,-73.983355" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">200 E. Third St.<br/>New York, NY 10009</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Guy Fieri visits Mama&#x27;s Food Shop in New York, NY, for homemade fried chicken and peach cobbler like mom used to make.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern Staples</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/new-york/mamas-food-shop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.98336,40.72267,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Keste Pizza &amp; Vino</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Keste Pizza &amp; Vino</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New York 10014</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://kestepizzeria.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">kestepizzeria.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Keste+Pizza+%26+Vino%2C+271+Bleecker+St.%2C+New+York+10014&amp;ll=40.731542,-74.002928" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">271 Bleecker St.<br/>New York 10014</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Margherita Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The tomatoes are San Marzano, the flour is superfine Italian, the cheese is buffalo mozzarella and the crust is, dare we say it, flawless: puffy, chewy and just a little charred.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Dinner and Dessert That Delivers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/new-york/keste-pizza-vino-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.00293,40.73154,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Defonte&#x27;s Sandwich Shop, Brooklyn</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Defonte&#x27;s Sandwich Shop, Brooklyn</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Brooklyn, NY 11231 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7186258052" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(718) 625 -8052</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.defontesofbrooklyn.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.defontesofbrooklyn.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Defonte%27s+Sandwich+Shop%2C+Brooklyn%2C+379+Columbia+St%2C+Brooklyn%2C+NY+11231&amp;ll=40.678946,-74.005354" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">379 Columbia St<br/>Brooklyn, NY 11231</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sinatra Special, Roast Beef</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Since 1922, this multigenerational old-school Italian deli in Brooklyn has been a local staple. Guy adored the tender steak pizzaiola with fresh mozzarella in the Sinatra Special. He called the thinly sliced roast beef, fried eggplant and mozzarella sandwich ridiculous and the real deal.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Long Standing Legacies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/brooklyn/defontes-sandwich-shop-brooklyn-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.00535,40.67895,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Smoke Joint</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Smoke Joint</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Brooklyn, NY 11217 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7187971011" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(718) 797-1011</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thesmokejoint.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thesmokejoint.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Smoke+Joint%2C+87+S.+Elliot+Place%2C+Brooklyn%2C+NY+11217&amp;ll=40.686921,-73.975337" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">87 S. Elliot Place<br/>Brooklyn, NY 11217</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Barbecue, Short Ribs, Smoked Buffalo Wings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">In Fort Greene Brooklyn, The Smoke Joint is smoking up some seriously mouth-watering, succulent, fall off the bone &#x27;cue. The short ribs are Brontosaurus-sized, and the Buffalo wings are funkified by smoking them first. It&#x27;s a veritable melting pot of a barbecue joint, much like the city it&#x27;s in.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Matches Made in Heaven<br/>Best of New York</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/brooklyn/the-smoke-joint-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.97534,40.68692,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>John&#x27;s of 12th Street</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">John&#x27;s of 12th Street</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New York, NY 10003 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2124759531" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(212) 475-9531</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.johnsof12thstreet.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.johnsof12thstreet.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=John%27s+of+12th+Street%2C+302+E+12th+St%2C+New+York%2C+NY+10003&amp;ll=40.730605,-73.985535" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">302 E 12th St<br/>New York, NY 10003</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza, Homemade Pappardelle with Ragu, Veal Meatballs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At 100+ years old, John&#x27;s of 12th Street is a hidden Italian gem in NYC. According to Guy, the Marsala wine in the tender all-veal meatballs gives them a little sweetness that pairs well with the savory marinara. Guy found the Tuscan Ragu over Homemade Pappardelle to be irresistibly delicious.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Global Traditions<br/>Best of New York</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/new-york/johns-of-12th-street-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.98554,40.73060,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pies &#x27;N&#x27; Thighs</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pies &#x27;N&#x27; Thighs</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Brooklyn 11211 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3475296090" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(347) 529-6090</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://news.piesnthighs.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">news.piesnthighs.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pies+%27N%27+Thighs%2C+166+S+4th+St%2C+Brooklyn+11211&amp;ll=40.711168,-73.961426" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">166 S 4th St<br/>Brooklyn 11211</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken and Waffles, Pecan Crunch Donut, Pulled Pork Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The three innovative female chefs that run this Brooklyn establishment are pumping out classic American cuisine with a Southern spin. Guy loved the savory buckwheat waffles and fried chicken, which were light and crisp. He also devoured the addictive Pecan Crunch Donut coated with homemade toffee.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Decadent Dishes<br/>Best of New York<br/>Takeout: All Over the Menu</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/brooklyn/pies-n-thighs-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.96143,40.71117,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Eveready Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Eveready Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hyde Park, NY 12538 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8452298100" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">845-229-8100</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.theevereadydiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.theevereadydiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Eveready+Diner%2C+4189+Albany+Post+Rd.+Route+9+N.%2C+Hyde+Park%2C+NY+12538&amp;ll=41.766760,-73.901525" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4189 Albany Post Rd. Route 9 N.<br/>Hyde Park, NY 12538</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">3-Cheese Macaroni and Cheese, Shepherd&#x27;s Pie in a Half-Roasted Squash, Lobster Quesadillas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The band of cousins who run this diner are always ready with more than 40 different types of homemade cakes, pies and bread. Guy was a fan of the focaccia bread topped with feta, onions, olives and tomatoes, but the short ribs for dinner and the brownie Sunday for dessert were Guy&#x27;s favorites.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Local Legends<br/>Triple-D Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/hyde-park/eveready-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.90153,41.76676,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tortilleria Nixtamal</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tortilleria Nixtamal</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Corona, NY 11368 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7186992434" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(718) 699-2434</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tortillerianixtamal.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tortillerianixtamal.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tortilleria+Nixtamal%2C+10405+47th+Ave%2C+Corona%2C+NY+11368&amp;ll=40.745935,-73.859248" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">10405 47th Ave<br/>Corona, NY 11368</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos al Pastor, Tortillas, Tortas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Thousands of pounds of masa and up to 10,000 tortillas a day come from Tortilleria Nixtamal. Guy liked the sweet and savory taco al pastor with pineapple, topped with white onion, cilantro and lime. The hearty pozole Guy found comforting and soothing. Regulars enjoy the tamales and tortas as well.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Latin Street Food<br/>Real Deal Mexican</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/corona/tortilleria-nixtamal-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.85925,40.74594,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sidecar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sidecar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Brooklyn, NY 11215 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7183690077" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(718) 369-0077</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sidecarbrooklyn.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sidecarbrooklyn.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sidecar%2C+560+Fifth+Ave%2C+Brooklyn%2C+NY+11215&amp;ll=40.665398,-73.989783" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">560 Fifth Ave<br/>Brooklyn, NY 11215</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Escabeche, Cuban Sandwich, Duck Confit With Kimchi</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Two brothers run this joint where they serve up custom cocktails and freshly prepared food. Guy was in heaven when he tried the escabeche topped with red onions; he called the ham in the Cuban sandwich &amp;quot;righteous.&amp;quot; Sidecar&#x27;s pork belly confit on a bed of kimchi also garners rave reviews.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Late Night Legends<br/>Family Matters</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/brooklyn/side-car-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.98978,40.66540,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>MOgridder&#x27;s BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">MOgridder&#x27;s BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bronx, NY 10474 &middot; &#9733; 1.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7189913046" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">718-991-3046</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mogridder.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mogridder.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=MOgridder%27s+BBQ%2C+565+Hunt%27s+Point+Ave%2C+Bronx%2C+NY+10474&amp;ll=40.811793,-73.883540" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">565 Hunt&#x27;s Point Ave<br/>Bronx, NY 10474</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ribs, Beef Brisket, Pulled Pork Sandwich, BBQ Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A few years ago, auto shop owner Fred Donnelly took up barbecue as a hobby. Then he started selling it from a trailer outside his Queens shop. Soon he was serving 150 lunches a day at MOgridder&#x27;s BBQ. Dig into Fred&#x27;s ribs and the brisket, which Guy said would &#x27;&#x27;challenge any good Texas brisket.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">East Coast Cruisin&#x27;<br/>Worth the Trip</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/bronx/mo-gridders-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.88354,40.81179,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jimmy&#x27;s Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jimmy&#x27;s Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Brooklyn, NY 11211 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7182187174" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(718) 218-7174</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://jimmysdinerbrooklyn.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">jimmysdinerbrooklyn.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jimmy%27s+Diner%2C+577+Union+Ave%2C+Brooklyn%2C+NY+11211&amp;ll=40.717697,-73.952458" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">577 Union Ave<br/>Brooklyn, NY 11211</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Apple Skillet Waffle, Empanadas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Come hungry to Jimmy&#x27;s Diner and you&#x27;ll leave satisfied. Guy thought the skillet apple waffle was &amp;quot;killer&amp;quot; and liked the salty-sweet combination of the pancetta and maple syrup. The spicy salsa verde and golden raisins elevated the empanadas in the Chico Grande plate to a new level according to Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Savory Sensations</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/brooklyn/jimmys-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.95246,40.71770,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Byblos Mediterranean Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Byblos Mediterranean Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Syracuse, NY 13202</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3154783333" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(315) 478-3333</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.byblossyr.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.byblossyr.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Byblos+Mediterranean+Cafe%2C+223+N.+Clinton+St.%2C+Syracuse%2C+NY+13202&amp;ll=43.052054,-76.153667" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">223 N. Clinton St.<br/>Syracuse, NY 13202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Falafel Sandwich, Baklava</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Byblos is a Lebanese joint in downtown Syracuse putting mama&#x27;s touch on Middle Eastern food. Violet Khabbaz, along with her son Fady and husband Phillip, makes a seasoned falafel sandwich Guy can&#x27;t get enough of, and a big time baklava for a serious sweet tooth.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Authentic Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/syracuse/byblos-mediterranean-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.15367,43.05205,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bun-ker Vietnamese</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bun-ker Vietnamese</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Brooklyn, NY 11237 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7183864282" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">718-386-4282</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://bunkernyc.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">bunkernyc.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bun-ker+Vietnamese%2C+99+Scott+Ave%2C+Brooklyn%2C+NY+11237&amp;ll=40.710564,-73.923398" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">99 Scott Ave<br/>Brooklyn, NY 11237</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grilled Pork Chops, Crispy Crepe</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bun-Ker Vietnamese may seem like it is in the middle of nowhere, but the trip is worth it for Vietnamese street foods that Guy could eat &quot;till (his) head falls off.&quot; This joint serves up Southeast Asian-style favorites like grilled pork chops and crispy crepe with bacon, shrimp and bean sprouts.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big Time Bites<br/>Amazing Asian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/queens/bun-ker-vietnamese" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.92340,40.71056,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sage General Store</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sage General Store</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Long Island City, NY 11101</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/long-island-city/sage-general-store-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/long-island-city/sage-general-store-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sage+General+Store%2C+24-20+Jackson+Ave%2C+Long+Island+City%2C+NY+11101&amp;ll=40.746067,-73.944329" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">24-20 Jackson Ave<br/>Long Island City, NY 11101</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bacon Mac &#x27;n&#x27; Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The 14-seat Sage General Store restaurant may be small, but the menu&#x27;s all about big flavor. Sage loves their bacon brownie, bacon pizza and the most delicious artisanal bacon mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese. Meanwhile, Guy couldn&#x27;t get enough of the juicy rotisserie chicken, spinning in the back.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Funky Finds<br/>Ultimate Bacon Fest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/long-island-city/sage-general-store-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.94433,40.74607,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Gazala&#x27;s Place</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Gazala&#x27;s Place</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New York, NY 10036 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2122450709" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(212) 245-0709</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.gazalasplace.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.gazalasplace.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Gazala%27s+Place%2C+709+9th+Ave%2C+New+York%2C+NY+10036&amp;ll=40.762604,-73.989655" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">709 9th Ave<br/>New York, NY 10036</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Osh Al-Saria</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Gazala Halabi might work in a tiny New York kitchen. But her Druze dishes had Guy taking big bites. Move along, fluffy pita-bread lovers. Here, pita bread comes &amp;quot;New York Times thin.&amp;quot; After kebabs and bourekas, save room for Osh Al-Saria, a creamy yogurt pudding made with orange and rosewater.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">International Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/new-york/gazalas-place-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.98966,40.76260,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Washoe Public House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Washoe Public House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Reno, NV 89501</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.washoepublichouse.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.washoepublichouse.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Washoe+Public+House%2C+275+Hill+St%2C+Reno%2C+NV+89501&amp;ll=39.522273,-119.814638" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">275 Hill St<br/>Reno, NV 89501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Double Elk Chop, Wild Boar Schnitzel</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The food revolution is alive and well in Reno at this one-of a kind spot serving creative dishes like Double Elk Chops with luxardo cherry demi-glace and Wild Boar Schnitzel with house-made rye spatzle and pickled mushrooms. Guy was floored by the schnitzel, &quot;Wow. Please tell me this is on the menu forever.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bagels, Biscuit and Boar</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/reno/washoe-public-house-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.81464,39.52227,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Yosh&#x27;s Unique Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Yosh&#x27;s Unique Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Reno, NV 89511 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://yoshsdeli.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">yoshsdeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Yosh%27s+Unique+Deli%2C+85+Foothill+Rd+%234%2C+Reno%2C+NV+89511&amp;ll=39.438737,-119.771224" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">85 Foothill Rd #4<br/>Reno, NV 89511</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Belly Bahn Mi, Meatloaf Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef-owner Josh Codding was born into a family of deli owners, so after spending six years as a professional firefighter he decided to take his own shot at the family business with this creative sandwich spot. If you&#x27;re in the mood for comfort food, opt for the meatloaf sandwich: tender slices of house-made meatloaf are layered on bread with gravy, caramelized onions, mashed potatoes and melted provolone cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Unique Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/reno/yoshs-unique-deli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.77122,39.43874,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Louis&#x27; Basque Corner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Louis&#x27; Basque Corner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Reno 89512 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7753237203" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(775) 323-7203</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.louisbasquecorner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.louisbasquecorner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Louis%27+Basque+Corner%2C+301+E+4th+St%2C+Reno+89512&amp;ll=39.530916,-119.810116" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">301 E 4th St<br/>Reno 89512</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oxtail Bourguignon, Hunter&#x27;s Rabbit</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Since 1967, Louis Basque Corner has been treating Renoites to the traditional cuisine of the Basque region. Everything from oxtail stew to sweetbreads had Guy&#x27;s attention. But for the ultimate dish, rabbit stew, Guy asked, &quot;are you kidding me?&quot; In other words, he absolutely loved it.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Smothered and Covered<br/>Globetrottin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/reno/louis-basque-corner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.81012,39.53092,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Gold &#x27;N Silver Inn</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Gold &#x27;N Silver Inn</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Reno, NV 89503 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7753232696" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(775) 323-2696</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.goldnsilverreno.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.goldnsilverreno.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Gold+%27N+Silver+Inn%2C+790+W+4th+St%2C+Reno%2C+NV+89503&amp;ll=39.527635,-119.824985" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">790 W 4th St<br/>Reno, NV 89503</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef Burgers, Baked Lemonade Pork Chops</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For more than 56 years the Gold &#x27;N Silver Inn has been serving up delicious all-American classics with a twist. The lemonade pork chops Guy called &amp;quot;flavor city,&amp;quot; while the tri-tip sandwich drenched in mahogany sauce, made with ketchup and grape jelly, had him coming back for more.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Surf &#x27;n Turf</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/reno/gold-n-silver-inn-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.82498,39.52763,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dish Cafe &amp; Catering</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dish Cafe &amp; Catering</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Reno, NV 89502 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7753488264" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(775) 348-8264</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.dishcafecatering.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.dishcafecatering.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dish+Cafe+%26+Catering%2C+855+Mill+St%2C+Reno%2C+NV+89502&amp;ll=39.525812,-119.799249" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">855 Mill St<br/>Reno, NV 89502</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Granola, Cowgirl Tri-Tip Panini</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Renoites love waking up with DISH Cafe for the coffee and the homemade granola. And even though the kitchen&#x27;s small - a whopping 84 square feet - Guy says they&#x27;re still all about local, seasonal cooking, like the &amp;quot;woop-woop&amp;quot; tri-tip Cowgirl Panini &amp;quot;done right&amp;quot; with caramelized onions.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fresh And Funky</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/reno/dish-cafe-catering-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.79925,39.52581,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>UNLV</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">UNLV</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Las Vegas, NV 89154</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7028953011" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(702) 895-3011</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.unlv.edu/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.unlv.edu</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=UNLV%2C+4505+S+Maryland+Pkwy%2C+Las+Vegas%2C+NV+89154&amp;ll=36.104941,-115.143821" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4505 S Maryland Pkwy<br/>Las Vegas, NV 89154</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Thai Shrimp</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At the University of Nevada Las Vegas, Guy&#x27;s alma mater, the culinary school is running both the back and the front of the University restaurant, UNLV Dining, and creating culinary delights. Guy liked the Thai shrimp on sticky rice and slaw. The menu rotates so come visit and try something new.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Vegas, All the Time<br/>Vegas Greats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/unlv-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-115.14382,36.10494,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Those Guys Pies</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Those Guys Pies</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Las Vegas, NV 89117 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7026292626" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">702-629-2626</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thoseguyspies.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thoseguyspies.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Those+Guys+Pies%2C+2916+Lake+East+Dr%2C+Las+Vegas%2C+NV+89117&amp;ll=36.138515,-115.284355" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2916 Lake East Dr<br/>Las Vegas, NV 89117</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Maui Wowie, Cheesesteak Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Two New Jersey transplants serve classic New York pizzas and creatively topped options like a Cheesesteak Pie and the Maui Wowie, with barbecue sauce, bacon, pineapple and pickled jalapenos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Griddles and Vittles</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/those-guys-pies-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-115.28436,36.13852,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Cube</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Cube</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Albuquerque, NM 87106 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5052430023" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 243-0023</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thecuberestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thecuberestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Cube%2C+1520+Central+Ave+SE%2C+Albuquerque%2C+NM+87106&amp;ll=35.081410,-106.629501" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1520 Central Ave SE<br/>Albuquerque, NM 87106</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guadalajara Dog</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The philosophy behind The Cube is simple: &amp;quot;Real food with a real smile.&amp;quot; That includes whipping up scratch-made barbecue every day over hickory and cherry wood, served with housemade barbecue sauce and classic Texas toast. Guy loved the Guadalajara Dog fried with applewood-smoked bacon.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork, Pasta and Barbecue</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/albuquerque/the-cube-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-106.62950,35.08141,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Torino&#x27;s at Home</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Torino&#x27;s at Home</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Albuquerque, NM &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5057974491" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 797-4491</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://torinosfoods.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">torinosfoods.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Torino%27s+at+Home%2C+7600+Jefferson+St+NE%2C+Albuquerque%2C+NM&amp;ll=35.165703,-106.591055" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7600 Jefferson St NE<br/>Albuquerque, NM</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pollo e Carciofini, Jamie&#x27;s Caprese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owners Daniela and Maxime Bouneou modeled Torinos&#x27; @ Home after Italy&#x27;s great trattorias. Guy swung by on DDD, and he learned that the food is honest and authentic, with dishes like handmade squid ink pasta and tender beef cheek manicotti that&#x27;s &amp;quot;no filler, all thriller.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Aces of Authenticity<br/>Amazing Italian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/albuquerque/torinos-at-home-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-106.59106,35.16570,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Standard Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Standard Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Albuquerque, NM 87102 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5052431440" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">505-243-1440</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.standarddiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.standarddiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Standard+Diner%2C+320+Central+Ave+SE%2C+Albuquerque%2C+NM+87102&amp;ll=35.083350,-106.643774" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">320 Central Ave SE<br/>Albuquerque, NM 87102</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meatloaf Wrapped in Bacon, The Standard Burger, Green Chili Chicken Chowder</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Standard Diner wanted to &amp;quot;rethink&amp;quot; the diner with dishes that are anything but standard. They converted a 1930s gas station into a modern restaurant with a menu to match. Guy devoured the bacon-wrapped meatloaf with bourbon-infused butter - an &amp;quot;on-point&amp;quot; dish for sure.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Return to Route 66</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/albuquerque/standard-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-106.64377,35.08335,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Monte Carlo Steak House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Monte Carlo Steak House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Albuquerque, NM 87105 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5058369886" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 836-9886</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/albuquerque/monte-carlo-steak-house-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/albuquerque/monte-carlo-steak-house-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Monte+Carlo+Steak+House%2C+3916+Central+Ave.+SW%2C+Albuquerque%2C+NM+87105&amp;ll=35.086121,-106.683503" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3916 Central Ave. SW<br/>Albuquerque, NM 87105</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rib Eye Steak, Greek Pork Kebab, Greek Meatballs with Spaghetti, Greek Marinated Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ever seen a first-class steakhouse behind a liquor store? At first Guy couldn&#x27;t believe it either, but at the Monte Carlo Steakhouse in Albuquerque, N.M., he was impressed by owner Lou Katsaros&#x27; grilled rib eye. Monte Carlo also serves Greek specialties like pork kebabs and marinated chicken.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Where the Locals Go<br/>Triple D Nation: Something Sweet</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/albuquerque/monte-carlo-steak-house-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-106.68350,35.08612,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sophia&#x27;s Place</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sophia&#x27;s Place</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Albuquerque 87107 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5053453935" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 345-3935</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Sophias-Place/111669672203435" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Sophias-Place/111669672203435</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sophia%27s+Place%2C+6313+4th+St+NW%2C+Albuquerque+87107&amp;ll=35.149476,-106.639470" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6313 4th St NW<br/>Albuquerque 87107</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Duck Enchiladas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Regulars describe the fare at Sophia&#x27;s Place as &quot;eclectic food with a New Mexican twist.&quot; But Guy called Chef Dennis Apodaca &quot;Captain Electric.&quot; In his tiny kitchen, Dennis creates plates exploding with flavor, including scallop tacos and spicy duck enchiladas topped with a tomatillo sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Not What You&#x27;d Expect</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/albuquerque/sophias-place-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-106.63947,35.14948,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Osaka Japanese Bistro</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Osaka Japanese Bistro</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Las Vegas, NV 89102 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7028764988" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">702-876-4988</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.lasvegas-sushi.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.lasvegas-sushi.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Osaka+Japanese+Bistro%2C+4205+West+Sahara+Ave%2C+Las+Vegas%2C+NV+89102&amp;ll=36.143944,-115.196947" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4205 West Sahara Ave<br/>Las Vegas, NV 89102</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roppongi Roll, Nabeyaki Udon</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy took a detour off the Las Vegas Strip to dig into top-rated sushi at Osaka Japanese Bistro, which has been serving its addictive rolls since 1967. &quot;It&#x27;s dynamite,&quot; said Guy of the Roppongi Roll, which features spicy tuna atop a layer of shrimp. The combo comes enveloped in a seaweed sheet that&#x27;s coated with rice, then topped with tuna, smelt eggs, green onions and a mix of sweet and spicy sauces.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Taste of Asia</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/osaka-japanese-bistro-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-115.19695,36.14394,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Naked City Pizza</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Naked City Pizza</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Las Vegas, NV 89102 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7022436277" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">702-243-6277</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.nakedcitylv.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.nakedcitylv.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Naked+City+Pizza%2C+3240+S+Arville+St%2C+Las+Vegas%2C+NV+89102&amp;ll=36.131013,-115.199116" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3240 S Arville St<br/>Las Vegas, NV 89102</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guinea Pie, Suicide Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tucked away in a bar, this pizza place serves gourmet pies in a frill-free setting. Guy liked the rich and creamy Guinea topped with meatballs, white garlic sauce, spinach, mozzarella and ricotta. Craving spicy? Try the Suicide Fries served with a medley of peppers for an awesome kick.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Vegas Greats<br/>All Vegas, All the Time<br/>Best of Pizza</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/naked-city-pizza-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-115.19912,36.13101,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ducks Eatery</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ducks Eatery</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New York, NY 10003 &middot; &#9733; 2.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2124323825" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(212) 432-3825</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.duckseatery.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.duckseatery.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ducks+Eatery%2C+351+E+12th+St%2C+New+York%2C+NY+10003&amp;ll=40.730185,-73.983921" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">351 E 12th St<br/>New York, NY 10003</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Goat Neck, Pig Ear</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Siblings Will and Julie Horowitz are making culinary waves in NYC&#x27;s East Village with their restaurant, Ducks Eatery. Largely inspired by his extensive travels and his chef grandparents, Will serves up creative dishes like goat neck and pig ears. Guy also recommends the whole, smoked chicken wings.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dynamite Duos</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/new-york/duck_s-eatery" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.98392,40.73018,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Don Antonio</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Don Antonio</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New York 10019 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6467191043" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(646) 719-1043</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.donantoniopizza.com/Welcome" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.donantoniopizza.com/Welcome</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Don+Antonio%2C+309+W+50th+St%2C+New+York+10019&amp;ll=40.762718,-73.986708" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">309 W 50th St<br/>New York 10019</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Montanara Starita (Fried Pizza with Tomato, Basil and Smoked Mozzerella), Pistachio and Sausage Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When New Yorkers and Italians call it the best pizza they&#x27;ve ever had, it has to be legit. Guy digs into the pistachio and sausage pizza fresh out of the wood-fired oven imported from Naples. He also can&#x27;t get enough of the Montanara Starita, a fried pizza with a smoky flavor and fluffy crust.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Dinner and Dessert That Delivers<br/>East Coast Cruisin&#x27;<br/>Keepin&#x27; It Real</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/new-york/don-antonio" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.98671,40.76272,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Defonte&#x27;s Sandwich Shop, Manhattan</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Defonte&#x27;s Sandwich Shop, Manhattan</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New York, NY 10010 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2126141500" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">212-614-1500</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.defontesofbrooklyn.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.defontesofbrooklyn.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Defonte%27s+Sandwich+Shop%2C+Manhattan%2C+261+Third+Ave%2C+New+York%2C+NY+10010&amp;ll=40.737325,-73.983881" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">261 Third Ave<br/>New York, NY 10010</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sinatra Special, Roast Beef</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Since 1922, this multigenerational old-school Italian deli in Brooklyn has been a local staple. Guy adored the tender steak pizzaiola with fresh mozzarella in the Sinatra Special. He called the thinly sliced roast beef, fried eggplant and mozzarella sandwich ridiculous and the real deal.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Long Standing Legacies<br/>Best of New York</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/new-york/defontes-sandwich-shop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.98388,40.73732,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Brindle Room</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Brindle Room</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New York, NY 10009</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2125299702" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(212) 529-9702</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://brindleroom.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">brindleroom.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Brindle+Room%2C+277+E+10th+St%2C+New+York%2C+NY+10009&amp;ll=40.728287,-73.982699" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">277 E 10th St<br/>New York, NY 10009</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burger, Duck Confit Poutine</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Former Chopped contestant Jeremy Spector lures locals to his spot with a scratch-made menu. The star is Sebastian&#x27;s Steakhouse Burger: a patty-cheddar-onion combo that Guy calls &quot;dynamite.&quot; The duck confit poutine made with hand-cut fries, cheese curds and, of course, duck confit, is also a hit.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Extra Helpings<br/>Big Time Bites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/new-york/brindle-room-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.98270,40.72829,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Black Tree</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Black Tree</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New York, NY 10002 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2125334684" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(212) 533-4684</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://blacktreenyc.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">blacktreenyc.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Black+Tree%2C+131+Orchard+St%2C+New+York%2C+NY+10002&amp;ll=40.719761,-73.989650" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">131 Orchard St<br/>New York, NY 10002</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Winter Pig, Lamb Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy calls Black Tree &quot;hard core&quot; because this spot takes its farm-to-table mantra very seriously. He feasts on the Winter Pig, a cheesy pork-belly sandwich that he likens to &quot;an enormous roast-pork dinner ... in a sandwich.&quot; Menu items change with the seasons, but all have a reputation for tastiness.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Extra Helpings<br/>All Things New York</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/new-york/black-tree" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.98965,40.71976,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Anchorage Tavern and Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Anchorage Tavern and Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Somers Point, NJ 08244 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6099261776" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609-926-1776</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.anchoragetavernrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.anchoragetavernrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Anchorage+Tavern+and+Restaurant%2C+823+Bay+Ave%2C+Somers+Point%2C+NJ+08244&amp;ll=39.310866,-74.594688" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">823 Bay Ave<br/>Somers Point, NJ 08244</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Buffalo Crab Cakes, Flounder Gorgonzola</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Set just off the water, this historic tavern is an ideal place for seafood, including crab-stuffed flounder, Buffalo Shrimp and Scallops Parmigiana.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roadtrippin</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/somers-point/the-anchorage-tavern-and-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.59469,39.31087,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Grilled Cheese &amp; Crab Cake Co</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Grilled Cheese &amp; Crab Cake Co</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Somers Point, NJ 08244</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6096017533" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609-601-7533</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://grilledcheeseandcrabcakeco.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">grilledcheeseandcrabcakeco.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Grilled+Cheese+%26+Crab+Cake+Co%2C+55+W+Laurel+Dr%2C+Somers+Point%2C+NJ+08244&amp;ll=39.318948,-74.610193" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">55 W Laurel Dr<br/>Somers Point, NJ 08244</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crab Melt</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The name of the game here is grilled cheese and crab cakes. Try them together in the popular Crab Melt with a side of Crabby Bacon French Fries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Atlantic to Pacific<br/>By Land and Sea</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/somers-point/the-grilled-cheese-and-crab-cake-co-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.61019,39.31895,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Brownstone Diner &amp; Pancake Factory</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Brownstone Diner &amp; Pancake Factory</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Jersey City, NJ 07302 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2014330471" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(201) 433-0471</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://brownstonediner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">brownstonediner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Brownstone+Diner+%26+Pancake+Factory%2C+426+Jersey+Ave.%2C+Jersey+City%2C+NJ+07302&amp;ll=40.716783,-74.048392" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">426 Jersey Ave.<br/>Jersey City, NJ 07302</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pancakes, Greek Moussaka</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Triple D, Guy stops by The Brownstone Diner for a big bite of breakfast. Luckily, Brownstone does not disappoint, with 31 varieties of pancakes and its own take on a breakfast burrito made with a pancake for a wrap. After breakfast hours, Guy recommends the signature Greek moussaka.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big Breakfast<br/>All in the Family</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/jersey-city/brownstone-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.04839,40.71678,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Ritz Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Ritz Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Livingston, NJ 07039 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9735331213" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">973-533-1213</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Ritz-Diner-108109165897879/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/Ritz-Diner-108109165897879</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Ritz+Diner%2C+72+E+Mount+Pleasant+Ave%2C+Livingston%2C+NJ+07039&amp;ll=40.796303,-74.311985" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">72 E Mount Pleasant Ave<br/>Livingston, NJ 07039</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cheesecakes, Carrot Cake, Chocolate Babka, Apple Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Open since 1984, Ritz Diner is the quintessential New Jersey joint. Popular eats include the Taylor ham, egg and cheese sandwich, the steak sandwich, and the matzo ball. Guy recommends ending your meal with a slice of tasty apple pie. Any of the daily-baked desserts will make for a sweet finish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dynamite Desserts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/livingston/the-ritz-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.31199,40.79630,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Quahog&#x27;s Seafood Shack</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Quahog&#x27;s Seafood Shack</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Stone Harbor, NJ 08084 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6093686300" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(609) 368-6300</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.quahogsshack.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.quahogsshack.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Quahog%27s+Seafood+Shack%2C+206+97th+St%2C+Stone+Harbor%2C+NJ+08084&amp;ll=39.053209,-74.759368" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">206 97th St<br/>Stone Harbor, NJ 08084</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pacu Pacu Fish Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Quahog&#x27;s Seafood Shack (pronounced co-HOG), you&#x27;ll find clam strips and clams on the half shell but you&#x27;ll also find a Triple D favorite. Guy scarfed down the glorious BBQ Pacu Pacu Fish Ribs. The Moqueca fish stew was also full of surprises, as it&#x27;s made with coconut milk and edamame.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Funky Finds</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/stone-harbor/quahogs-seafood-shack-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.75937,39.05321,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Marie&#x27;s Italian Specialties</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Marie&#x27;s Italian Specialties</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chatham, NJ 07928 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9733777878" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">973-377-7878</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mariesdeli.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mariesdeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Marie%27s+Italian+Specialties%2C+641+Shunpike+Rd%2C+Chatham%2C+NJ+07928&amp;ll=40.745460,-74.431764" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">641 Shunpike Rd<br/>Chatham, NJ 07928</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Arancini, Baked Fried Chicken, Mac &#x27;n&#x27; Cheese, Sacred Swine</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A husband and wife team are serving Italian-style comfort food at this popular New Jersey spot. Guy called the Sacred Swine, a sandwich filled with pork shoulder, broccoli rabe, vodka sauce and polenta, &amp;quot;outstanding.&amp;quot; The baked fried chicken with a side of mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese also garners rave reviews.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Deep Fried All-Stars<br/>Hometown Haunts<br/>Amazing Italian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/chatham/maries-italian-specialties-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.43176,40.74546,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>45 Market Street Bakery and Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">45 Market Street Bakery and Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Somersworth, NH 03878 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6036924511" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">603-692-4511</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nh/45-market-street-bakery-and-cafe-resturant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nh/45-market-street-bakery-and-cafe-resturant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=45+Market+Street+Bakery+and+Cafe%2C+45+Market+St%2C+Somersworth%2C+NH+03878&amp;ll=43.264373,-70.864239" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">45 Market St<br/>Somersworth, NH 03878</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey Meatloaf Sandwich, Haddock Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Locals crowd into this vibrant cafe for the baked goods and fresh sandwiches turned out by co-owners Celeste Gingras and Cheryl Arsenault. A standout is the turkey meatloaf sandwich held together by two hefty slices of anadama bread baked right on the premises. This homemade creation comes crammed with slabs of turkey meatloaf blanketed in melted provolone cheese and topped with a housemade barbecue sauce. &quot;It&#x27;s sturdy as I get dirty,&quot; Guy declared after biting into the massive sandwich.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey-giving</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nh/45-market-street-bakery-and-cafe-resturant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.86424,43.26437,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tuckaway Tavern &amp; Butchery</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tuckaway Tavern &amp; Butchery</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Raymond 03077 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6032442431" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">603-244-2431</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thetuckaway.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thetuckaway.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tuckaway+Tavern+%26+Butchery%2C+58+NH-27%2C+Raymond+03077&amp;ll=43.039164,-71.164577" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">58 NH-27<br/>Raymond 03077</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chili &amp; Cheese Corn Holes, Whole Tuckin&#x27; Farm Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Tuckaway Tavern draws a steady stream of diners, thanks to a stellar menu dreamed up by Chef Bobby Marcotte. He sources many of his ingredients straight from the adjacent butcher shop, which features a dizzying array of housemade sausages, marinated meats and more. Standout menu items include the Chili &amp; Cheese Corn Holes. For this dish, Chef Marcotte reinterprets classic corn dogs as bite-size spheres of house-ground meat doused with spices, studded with melty cheese and covered in a golden crust.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Home Delivery<br/>Big Food, Small Towns</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nh/raymond/tuckaway-tavern-and-butchery" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.16458,43.03916,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Moxy</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Moxy</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portsmouth, NH 03801 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6033198178" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">603-319-8178</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.moxyrestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.moxyrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Moxy%2C+106+Penhallow+St%2C+Portsmouth%2C+NH+03801&amp;ll=43.077769,-70.756994" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">106 Penhallow St<br/>Portsmouth, NH 03801</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">New England Dinner 2.0, Goat Stroganoff</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Moxy is more than just the name of this spot - it also defines the attitude of Chef-Owner Matt Louis. He embraces the notion of risk with his clever dishes that challenge long-held traditions of the New England culinary canon. Take his New England Dinner 2.0, for instance. Hefty slices of corned beef brisket are served with pickled vegetables (which lend a modern touch to the dish) and fresh cabbage leaves, so each diner can create individual lettuce wraps from the components on his or her plate.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cosmopolitan Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nh/portsmouth/moxy-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.75699,43.07777,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Vida Cantina</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Vida Cantina</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portsmouth, NH 03801 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6035010648" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">603-501-0648</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.vidacantinanh.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.vidacantinanh.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Vida+Cantina%2C+2456+Lafayette+Rd%2C+Portsmouth%2C+NH+03801&amp;ll=43.033483,-70.784493" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2456 Lafayette Rd<br/>Portsmouth, NH 03801</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Belly Tacos, Pig Head Platter</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This former fast-food joint dances with vibrant colors and serves bright, beautiful dishes to match. Chef-Owner David Vargas channels the traditional tastes of Mexico, but delivers them in slightly tweaked formats. His pork belly tacos are a popular pick. Housemade tortillas are layered with jicama slaw and crisp slabs of spice-laden pork belly, then topped with mango salsa, Cotija cheese and a flurry of fresh flower petals.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Port to Port</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nh/portsmouth/vida-cantina-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.78449,43.03348,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portsmouth, NH 03801 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6033198630" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">603-319-8630</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thekitchennh.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thekitchennh.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Kitchen%2C+171+Islington+St%2C+Portsmouth%2C+NH+03801&amp;ll=43.074407,-70.764089" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">171 Islington St<br/>Portsmouth, NH 03801</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ribs, Apu Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This spot takes its inspiration from New York-style delis, which means the menu is rife with hefty sandwiches, as expected. So Guy was surprised to discover St. Louis-style spare ribs, which are The Kitchen&#x27;s&amp;nbsp;sleeper hit. The pork is soaked in a red wine vinegar brine studded with star anise, juniper berries and red pepper flakes, then hit with a smoked paprika rub. The ribs are grilled until beautifully caramelized and come drenched in an agrodolce sauce that adds both sweetness and spice.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Buns and Bagels</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nh/portsmouth/the-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.76409,43.07441,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Street Food 360</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Street Food 360</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portsmouth, NH 03801 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6034360860" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">603-436-0860</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.streetfood360.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.streetfood360.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Street+Food+360%2C+801+Islington+St%2C+Portsmouth%2C+NH+03801&amp;ll=43.069093,-70.773060" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">801 Islington St<br/>Portsmouth, NH 03801</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Seamita Sandwich, Lamb Shawarma</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The husband-and-wife duo behind Street Food 360 share tastes of their world travels with fresh spins on global favorites. For instance, their version of Mexico&#x27;s&lt;i&gt; cemita&lt;/i&gt; sandwich substitutes a seafood patty for the standard meat fillings. Pollock fish pulled from local waters is combined with shrimp, scallops, shallots and a mix of spices to make the fried patty. It&#x27;s placed on a sesame bun, then topped with a hefty slice of griddled cheese, pickled red onions, cilantro and housemade chipotle mayo.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sausage, Seafood and Shawarma</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nh/portsmouth/street-food-360-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.77306,43.06909,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Red Arrow Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Red Arrow Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Manchester, NH 03101 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6036261118" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">603-626-1118</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.redarrowdiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.redarrowdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Red+Arrow+Diner%2C+61+Lowell+St.%2C+Manchester%2C+NH+03101&amp;ll=42.993449,-71.461422" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">61 Lowell St.<br/>Manchester, NH 03101</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried French Toast, American Chop Suey (Macaroni, Beef, Tomato), Pork Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Since 1922, Red Arrow Diner has kept open 24 hours a day (except for the 16 hours over Christmas) to serve nearly 500,000 breakfasts a year. On Triple D, Guy took his place in line to sample their iconic dishes: Fried French toast, American Chop Suey, and their handmade twinkies, Dinah Fingers.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">House Specials</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nh/manchester/red-arrow-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.46142,42.99345,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Redhead</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Redhead</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New York 10003 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2125336212" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(212) 533-6212</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/new-york/the-redhead-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/new-york/the-redhead-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Redhead%2C+349+E+13th+St%2C+New+York+10003&amp;ll=40.730933,-73.983354" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">349 E 13th St<br/>New York 10003</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homemade Pretzels With Beer Cheese, Bacon Peanut Brittles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At unassuming East Village gastropub The Redhead, seasonal, Southern-inflected food and carefully-made cocktails reign supreme. On Triple D, Guy was blown away by chef Meg Grace&#x27;s Homemade Pretzels With Beer Cheese. For a comforting main course, try the Buttermilk Fried Chicken or Shrimp and Grits.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Best of New York<br/>Scratch Made Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ny/new-york/the-redhead-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.98335,40.73093,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rocky Hill Inn</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rocky Hill Inn</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Rocky Hill, NJ 08553 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6096838930" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609-683-8930</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rockyhilltavern.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rockyhilltavern.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rocky+Hill+Inn%2C+137+Washington+St%2C+Rocky+Hill%2C+NJ+08553&amp;ll=40.399898,-74.634581" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">137 Washington St<br/>Rocky Hill, NJ 08553</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Belly Disco Fries, Fried Green Tomato Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Evan Blomgren draws the crowds with his elevated takes on traditional bar bites served inside a beautiful, historical building. For instance, he takes that New Jersey comfort food staple known as disco fries and amps it up with the addition of pork belly. The meat is seasoned and cubed, then layered on a thatch of housemade fries, along with a heap of banana peppers, a melty blanket of fontina cheese, a flurry of scallions and a drizzle of malt vinaigrette that Guy says &quot;turbocharges the dish.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big Food, Small Towns</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/rocky-hill-inn-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.63458,40.39990,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Vincentown Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Vincentown Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Vincentown, NJ 08088 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6092673033" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609-267-3033</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://vincentowndiner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">vincentowndiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Vincentown+Diner%2C+2357+US-206%2C+Vincentown%2C+NJ+08088&amp;ll=39.970891,-74.735878" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2357 US-206<br/>Vincentown, NJ 08088</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mile High Meatloaf, French Toast</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This massive diner dishes up scratch-made classics made from fresh, locally sourced ingredients. The Mile High Meatloaf, for instance, features grass-fed beef from a nearby farm. Hefty slabs of beautifully caramelized meatloaf are layered with mashed potatoes, then doused with a gravy made with mirepoix, veal bone stock and prime rib. &quot;This is tender; this is juicy,&quot; Guy said of the dish. &quot;Look at me - I can&#x27;t stop eating it.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big Food, Small Towns</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/vincentown-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.73588,39.97089,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bagel Street</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bagel Street</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Plainsboro Township, NJ 08536</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6099361755" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609-936-1755</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bagelstreetgrill.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bagelstreetgrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bagel+Street%2C+660+Plainsboro+Rd%2C+Plainsboro+Township%2C+NJ+08536&amp;ll=40.327419,-74.575591" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">660 Plainsboro Rd<br/>Plainsboro Township, NJ 08536</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jalapeno Cheddar Bagel, Pork Roll Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bagels are the name of the game at this shop, where brothers and owners Jimmy and Doug Rohr are slinging around 15,000 per week. There are 20 options available, including one fiery pick whose dough is mixed with shredded cheddar cheese and chopped jalapenos before being proofed overnight, then boiled and baked until a delectable crust forms. The brothers also serve inventive combinations that include a sliced Asiago bagel stuffed with a pork-roll-studded burger and a heap of Tater Tots.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Buns and Bagels</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/bagel-street-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.57559,40.32742,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Piccini</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Piccini</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ocean City, NJ 08226 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6095250767" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609-525-0767</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.picciniocnj.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.picciniocnj.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Piccini%2C+1260+West+Ave%2C+Ocean+City%2C+NJ+08226&amp;ll=39.275253,-74.582660" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1260 West Ave<br/>Ocean City, NJ 08226</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bacon Cheeseburger Pizza, Chicken and Farfalle with Vodka Sauce</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy stops here to try a fun comfort food mash-up: bacon cheeseburger pizza. This creative pie uses ketchup and mustard in place of sauce. Guy is skeptical of the switch until he bites into a slice loaded with seasoned ground beef, melted cheddar, bacon and pickles, which he declares &quot;nicely done.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">East-West Flavorfest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/ocean-city/piccini-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.58266,39.27525,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jammin&#x27; Crepes</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jammin&#x27; Crepes</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Princeton, NJ 08542 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6099245387" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609-924-5387</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.jammincrepes.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jammincrepes.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jammin%27+Crepes%2C+20+Nassau+St%2C+Princeton%2C+NJ+08542&amp;ll=40.349051,-74.662772" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">20 Nassau St<br/>Princeton, NJ 08542</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jammin&#x27; Turkey Club, 20-Layer Orchard Lemon Crepe Cake</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">As the name suggests, this spot churns out a dizzying array of crepes, with options that include meat and fruit fillings. A popular pick is the Jammin&#x27; Turkey Club, a sturdy and crisp crepe that&#x27;s slathered with housemade peach chutney and stuffed with roasted turkey breast, mozzarella cheese, applewood-smoked bacon slices and mixed greens. Horseradish aioli finishes the creation. &quot;You haven&#x27;t missed a beat in this,&quot; Guy declared when he stopped by with Rev Run (aka Joseph Simmons).</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey-giving</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/princeton/jammin-crepes-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.66277,40.34905,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>10th Avenue Burrito</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">10th Avenue Burrito</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Belmar, NJ 07719 &middot; &#9733; 3.9 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7322801515" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">732-280-1515</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tenthaveburrito.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tenthaveburrito.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=10th+Avenue+Burrito%2C+801+Belmar+Plaza%2C+Belmar%2C+NJ+07719&amp;ll=40.180233,-74.026849" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">801 Belmar Plaza<br/>Belmar, NJ 07719</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Adobo Wings, Burrito</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Driveone hour and 30 minutes from NYC to discover this funky little joint in Belmar, N.J., and sample its take on California-inspired Mexican food. Try the mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese and chicken wings; both have a little extra spice, compliments of adobo. For big appetites, get a burrito smothered in Chipotle Cream Sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wings &#x27;n Things<br/>Amazing Appetizers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/belmar/10th-ave-burrito-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.02685,40.18023,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bayway Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bayway Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Linden, NJ 07036 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9088623207" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(908) 862-3207</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.baywaycatering.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.baywaycatering.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bayway+Diner%2C+2019+S+Wood+Ave%2C+Linden%2C+NJ+07036&amp;ll=40.620783,-74.235143" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2019 S Wood Ave<br/>Linden, NJ 07036</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Joe&#x27;s Famous Tri-color Pasta with Chicken, Philly Cheese Steak, Bayway Special, Bayway Monster Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bayway Diner started out as a nine-seater. But after overwhelming popularity, the funky joint expanded to an outdoor seating area and now offers catering services as well. Guy loves the no-fuss dishes featured on the menu, like the master burger, the Philly cheese steak and the Buffalo chicken.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners, Drive-ins and Dives<br/>Made to Order<br/>Diners A-Plenty</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/linden/bay-way-diner-restaurant2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.23514,40.62078,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Carluccio&#x27;s Coal Fired Pizza</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Carluccio&#x27;s Coal Fired Pizza</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Northfield, NJ 08225 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6096414011" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609-641-4011</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.carluccioscoalfiredpizza.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.carluccioscoalfiredpizza.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Carluccio%27s+Coal+Fired+Pizza%2C+1200+New+Rd%2C+Northfield%2C+NJ+08225&amp;ll=39.375020,-74.553081" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1200 New Rd<br/>Northfield, NJ 08225</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grandma&#x27;s Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If the pizza at this BYOB tastes as good as what your Italian grandmother would make, that&#x27;s because the signature Grandma&#x27;s Pizza is a recipe from the owner&#x27;s own grandparents.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Globe Tasting</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/northfield/carluccios-coal-fired-pizza-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.55308,39.37502,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>White Manna</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">White Manna</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hackensack, NJ 07601 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2013420914" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">201-342-0914</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/hackensack/white-manna-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/hackensack/white-manna-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=White+Manna%2C+358+River+St%2C+Hackensack%2C+NJ+07601&amp;ll=40.889191,-74.038413" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">358 River St<br/>Hackensack, NJ 07601</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Slider Burgers with Cheese and Onions</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Slider Burgers with Cheese and Onions served at this Hackensack fixture are a favorite of both Alex Guarnaschelli and Guy Fieri (who said he could eat &quot;18 or 75&quot; of them). These three-bite beauties feature griddled patties cooked with thin-sliced onions and served beneath a blanket of melty American cheese. Michael Psilakis likens these sliders to &quot;tiny hockey pucks of joy.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Knockout Burger Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/hackensack/white-manna-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.03841,40.88919,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dolce &amp; Clemente&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dolce &amp; Clemente&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Robbinsville, NJ 08691 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6092590072" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609-259-0072</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.dolceandclementes.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.dolceandclementes.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dolce+%26+Clemente%27s%2C+2+N+Commerce+Square%2C+%23101%2C+Robbinsville%2C+NJ+08691&amp;ll=40.218952,-74.627307" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2 N Commerce Square, #101<br/>Robbinsville, NJ 08691</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Prosciutto Bread, Boss of the Sauce</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy was dazzled by the immense selection at this old-school Italian deli, which turns out dozens of fresh items daily. One popular pick is the prosciutto bread, which comes stuffed with provolone cheese and a medley of Italian meats. &quot;The depth of flavor in this is massive,&quot; Guy declared. He also raved about the Boss of the Sauce, a meaty dish composed of beef braciole, pork braciole, sausages and meatballs served in a hearty homemade sauce that&#x27;s ladled over a mound of pasta.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mega Mouthfuls</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/robbinsville/dolce-and-clementes-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.62731,40.21895,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sam&#x27;s Rialto Bar &amp; Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sam&#x27;s Rialto Bar &amp; Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Pleasantville, NJ 08232</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6096465128" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609-646-5128</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://eatsams.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">eatsams.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sam%27s+Rialto+Bar+%26+Grill%2C+18+S+Main+St%2C+Pleasantville%2C+NJ+08232&amp;ll=39.391402,-74.522525" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">18 S Main St<br/>Pleasantville, NJ 08232</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken &#x27;N Waffles, Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Locals head here for the scratch-made Southern eats created by Sam Hunter, whose legacy is carried on by his widow. She&#x27;s still slinging classics like Chicken &#x27;n Waffles: The buttermilk-marinated bird is served with a cinnamon-and-sugar-dusted homemade waffle that Guy calls &quot;the key&quot; to the dish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Legacies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/pleasantville/sams-rialto-bar-and-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.52252,39.39140,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>La Isla Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">La Isla Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hoboken, NJ 07030 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2016598197" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">201-659-8197</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.laislarestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.laislarestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=La+Isla+Restaurant%2C+104+Washington+St%2C+Hoboken%2C+NJ+07030&amp;ll=40.737755,-74.031202" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">104 Washington St<br/>Hoboken, NJ 07030</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Papa Rellena, Tasajo Con Boniato</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">&amp;quot;Good Cuban food makes you put a smile on your face,&amp;quot; says a diner at La Isla. It&#x27;s a small place right on Washington St. in Hoboken that specializes in world-class flavors in a down-home environment. Guy stopped in and ate so much of the spicy food, his eyeballs started sweating.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Deep Fried All-Stars<br/>Far Out</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/hoboken/la-isla-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.03120,40.73776,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ernest and Son</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ernest and Son</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Brigantine, NJ 08203 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6092661588" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(609) 266-1588</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.ernestandson.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.ernestandson.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ernest+and+Son%2C+3305+Brigantine+Blvd.%2C+Brigantine%2C+NJ+08203&amp;ll=39.394855,-74.388083" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3305 Brigantine Blvd.<br/>Brigantine, NJ 08203</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef Jerky; The Tailgater</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ernest and Son is the ideal neighborhood butcher shop. Everything is cut and made fresh here, from the sausages to the beef jerky. This butcher also makes sandwiches to order, including the Tailgater - featuring housemade sausage with grilled peppers and onions.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oldies But Goodies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/brigantine/ernest-and-son" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.38808,39.39485,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Kelsey and Kim&#x27;s Southern Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Kelsey and Kim&#x27;s Southern Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlantic City, NJ 08401 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6093506800" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(609) 350-6800</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.kelseyandkims.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.kelseyandkims.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Kelsey+and+Kim%27s+Southern+Cafe%2C+201+Melrose+Ave.%2C+Atlantic+City%2C+NJ+08401&amp;ll=39.372391,-74.416254" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">201 Melrose Ave.<br/>Atlantic City, NJ 08401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey Chop; Pork Trotters</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern-raised chef Kelsey Jackson serves the food he grew up on at Kelsey and Kim&#x27;s in South Jersey. Winning dishes include succulent braised pork trotters and the fried turkey chop, which is smothered in gravy.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fish, Fries and Feet</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/atlantic-city/kelsey-and-kims-southern-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.41625,39.37239,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Vagabond Kitchen &amp; Tap House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Vagabond Kitchen &amp; Tap House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlantic City, NJ 08401 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6093506721" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609-350-6721</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.vagabondac.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.vagabondac.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Vagabond+Kitchen+%26+Tap+House%2C+672+N+Trenton+Ave%2C+Atlantic+City%2C+NJ+08401&amp;ll=39.359650,-74.463119" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">672 N Trenton Ave<br/>Atlantic City, NJ 08401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Three Way Sandwich, Tequila Shrimp Bangers, Turkey Apple Brie Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You&#x27;ll find far more than the usual pub grub at this tavern that was resurrected after Hurricane Sandy hit. This new incarnation offers elevated takes on classic comfort food eats like a hot turkey sandwich. Brie cheese and apples top the oven-roasted bird, which is served on cranberry-walnut toast.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Between the Bread</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/atlantic-city/vagabond-kitchen-and-tap-house-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.46312,39.35965,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lola&#x27;s - A Louisiana Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lola&#x27;s - A Louisiana Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Las Vegas, NV 89102 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (24 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7022275652" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(702) 227-5652</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://lolaslasvegas.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">lolaslasvegas.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lola%27s+-+A+Louisiana+Kitchen%2C+241+W+Charleston+Blvd%2C+Las+Vegas%2C+NV+89102&amp;ll=36.158264,-115.157967" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">241 W Charleston Blvd<br/>Las Vegas, NV 89102</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roast Beef Po&#x27; Boy, Crawfish, Seafood Gumbo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lola&#x27;s, a New Orleans style restaurant, has brought the Big Easy to Sin City. Guy says the roast beef po&#x27; boy with gravy is &amp;quot;on point.&amp;quot; The crawfish, according to Guy, is &amp;quot;tender, sweet and out of bounds.&amp;quot; Locals recommend the seafood gumbo, shrimp and grits and oysters.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Serious Sandwiches</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/lolas-a-louisiana-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-115.15797,36.15826,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>John Mull&#x27;s Meats and Road Kill Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">John Mull&#x27;s Meats and Road Kill Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Las Vegas 89130 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (29 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7026451200" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(702) 645-1200</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.johnmullsmeats.com/road-kill-grill" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.johnmullsmeats.com/road-kill-grill</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=John+Mull%27s+Meats+and+Road+Kill+Grill%2C+3730+Thom+Blvd.%2C+Las+Vegas+89130&amp;ll=36.227207,-115.211478" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3730 Thom Blvd.<br/>Las Vegas 89130</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hot Link Sausage, Ribs, Pulled Pork, Mac &#x27;n&#x27; Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Barbecue master Chuck Frommer has the best barbecue in Vegas and the locals know it. Guy fell in love with the hot links, which are cured for 16 hours and smoked for six, and savored the flavorful ribs. The pulled pork and mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese are also popular.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Vegas Greats<br/>BBQ Road Show<br/>Takeout: Carnivore Delivery<br/>BBQ Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/john-mulls-meats-and-road-kill-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-115.21148,36.22721,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Guy Fieri&#x27;s Kitchen and Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Guy Fieri&#x27;s Kitchen and Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Las Vegas, NV 89109 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:18006346441" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1-800-634-6441</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.caesars.com/linq/restaurants/guy-fieri" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.caesars.com/linq/restaurants/guy-fieri</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Guy+Fieri%27s+Kitchen+and+Bar%2C+The+Linq+Hotel+%26+Casino%2C+Las+Vegas%2C+NV+89109&amp;ll=36.117874,-115.171169" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">The Linq Hotel &amp; Casino<br/>Las Vegas, NV 89109</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bacon Mac &#x27;n&#x27; Cheese Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For the ultimate in comfort food indulgence, order the Bacon Mac &#x27;n&#x27; Cheese Burger at Guy&#x27;s joint in Las Vegas. This monster of a between-the-bun meal features a beef patty topped with a scoop of macaroni and cheese, a blanket of a cheese slice, strips of smoky bacon and Guy&#x27;s mayo-based sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Griddles and Vittles</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/guy-fieri-s-kitchen-and-bar" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-115.17117,36.11787,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Carolina Kitchen &amp; BBQ Co.</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Carolina Kitchen &amp; BBQ Co.</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sparks, NV 89431</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://carolinakitchenbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">carolinakitchenbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Carolina+Kitchen+%26+BBQ+Co.%2C+950+Glendale+Ave.%2C+Sparks%2C+NV+89431&amp;ll=39.528101,-119.754677" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">950 Glendale Ave.<br/>Sparks, NV 89431</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Brisket, Smoked Wing Nachos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After a career working as a chef in fine restaurants on the East Coast, owner Clay Cobb moved back home to Nevada to get back to his roots and open this barbecue joint with his mom. Guy was blown away by the smoked brisket, which is slathered in a house-made moonshine barbecue sauce and served with collard greens, cornbread and beans. &quot;This is the best brisket I&#x27;ve seen outside of Texas,&quot; Guy said. &quot;It&#x27;s real deal.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Northern Southern</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/sparks/carolina-kitchen-and-bbq-co-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.75468,39.52810,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Coffee Cup Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Coffee Cup Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boulder City, NV 89005 &middot; &#9733; 4.9 (16 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7022940517" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">702-294-0517</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.worldfamouscoffeecup.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.worldfamouscoffeecup.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Coffee+Cup+Cafe%2C+512+Nevada+Way%2C+Boulder+City%2C+NV+89005&amp;ll=35.977708,-114.838063" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">512 Nevada Way<br/>Boulder City, NV 89005</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Peanut Butter Pancakes, Pork Chili Verde Omelet, Coffee, Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From peanut butter pancakes to huevos rancheros, this roadside diner makes dishes fresh to order under a &quot;world famous&quot; tagline. The eatery is easy to miss, and when Guy stopped by on Triple D, he regretted his earlier drive-bys. The Pork Chili Verde omelet was nothing short of &quot;the bomb.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Breakfast<br/>Best of the West<br/>Triple D Nation: Burgers, Burritos and Biscuits</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/boulder-city/the-coffee-cup-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-114.83806,35.97771,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Maui&#x27;s Dog House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Maui&#x27;s Dog House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wildwood, NJ 08260</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6098460444" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(609) 846-0444</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mauisdoghouse.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mauisdoghouse.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Maui%27s+Dog+House%2C+806+New+Jersey+Ave%2C+Wildwood%2C+NJ+08260&amp;ll=39.003933,-74.798839" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">806 New Jersey Ave<br/>Wildwood, NJ 08260</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Salty Balls</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Come here next time you&#x27;re on the Jersey Shore and get &amp;quot;sarcasm with great food&amp;quot; served in dog bowls. Maui&#x27;s is famous for their 29+ hot dog toppings, with best-sellers like the Soprano and the Cardiac. If you&#x27;re early and lucky, try their potato Salty Balls before they&#x27;re all sold out.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwiches Plus</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/wildwood/mauis-dog-house-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.79884,39.00393,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>George&#x27;s Place</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">George&#x27;s Place</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cape May, NJ 08204 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6098846088" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(609) 884-6088</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.georgesplace.com/george.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.georgesplace.com/george.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=George%27s+Place%2C+301+Beach+Ave%2C+Cape+May%2C+NJ+08204&amp;ll=38.930407,-74.922996" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">301 Beach Ave<br/>Cape May, NJ 08204</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey Confit, Greek Leg of Lamb</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At George&#x27;s Place, you get a bit of Greek with every dish whether it&#x27;s breakfast, lunch or dinner. When Guy visited on Thanksgiving, he sampled an unforgettable turkey confit and classic Greek leg of lamb.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Triple D Thanksgiving</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/cape-may/georges-place-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.92300,38.93041,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cecilia&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cecilia&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Albuquerque, NM 87102 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5052437070" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 243-7070</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/albuquerque/cecilias-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/albuquerque/cecilias-cafe-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cecilia%27s+Cafe%2C+230+Sixth+St.+SW%2C+Albuquerque%2C+NM+87102&amp;ll=35.083112,-106.654234" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">230 Sixth St. SW<br/>Albuquerque, NM 87102</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Huevos Rancheros, Enchiladas, Breakfast Burrito</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you order chicharones from Cecilia&#x27;s Cafe, don&#x27;t expect fried pork skins. Cecilia&#x27;s chicharones are hunks of stewed pork layered inside a warm tortilla with cheese and green chile sauce. Still hungry? Try Guy&#x27;s pick: sopapillas stuffed with shredded chicken and the &amp;quot;whole jala and peno.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Regional Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/albuquerque/cecilias-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-106.65423,35.08311,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bocadillos</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bocadillos</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Albuquerque, NM 87102 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5052433995" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">505-243-3995</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bocadillos505.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bocadillos505.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bocadillos%2C+200+Lomas+Blvd+NW%2C+Albuquerque%2C+NM+87102&amp;ll=35.110828,-106.662138" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">200 Lomas Blvd NW<br/>Albuquerque, NM 87102</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">&quot;Duke City Ruben&quot; Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Before Marie Yniguez makes her chipotle-infused Duke City Ruben sandwich, she feeds nearly 1,000 charter school students with fresh, scratch-made food. Guy&#x27;s trip was no different, as he felt &quot;the love&quot; for Bocadillos and its gratifying biscuits and gravy, saying, &quot;This isn&#x27;t your grandma&#x27;s gravy.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ultimate Turkey Fest<br/>Sammies and Stew<br/>Triple D Nation: Trottin&#x27; Out the Turkey</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/albuquerque/bocadillos-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-106.66214,35.11083,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nexus Brewery and Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nexus Brewery and Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Albuquerque, NM 87109 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5052424100" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 242-4100</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://nexusbrewery.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">nexusbrewery.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nexus+Brewery+and+Restaurant%2C+4730+Pan+American+Freeway+East%2C+NE%2C+Albuquerque%2C+NM+87109&amp;ll=35.133311,-106.606561" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4730 Pan American Freeway East, NE<br/>Albuquerque, NM 87109</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern Fried Chicken &amp; Waffles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Nexus Brewery and Restaurant, Guy learned about a new cuisine: New Mexican soul food. The restaurant is named after Star Trek but it&#x27;s clearly a union of southern-New Mexican flavors with dishes like green-chile mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese, pico de gallo gumbo and Guy&#x27;s pick: hot sauce chicken and waffles.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort and Soul</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/albuquerque/nexus-brewery-and-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-106.60656,35.13331,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Golden Crown Panaderia</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Golden Crown Panaderia</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Albuquerque, NM &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5052432424" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 243-2424</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.goldencrown.biz" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.goldencrown.biz</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Golden+Crown+Panaderia%2C+1103+Mountain+Rd+NW%2C+Albuquerque%2C+NM&amp;ll=35.095617,-106.658340" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1103 Mountain Rd NW<br/>Albuquerque, NM</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey Bread (Turkey-Shaped Bread Loaf)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Golden Crown Panaderia&#x27;s recipe for success began in 1972. The bakery remains a favorite for its old-fashioned baked goods, including the state cookie of New Mexico, biscochito, a crisp butter cookie. Guy sampled the Turkey Bread, a turkey-shaped honey wheat bread complete with drumsticks and wings.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ultimate Turkey Fest<br/>All Kinds of Gobble Gobble</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/albuquerque/golden-crown-panaderia-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-106.65834,35.09562,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Paper Dosa</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Paper Dosa</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe 87505</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5059305521" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">505-930-5521</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://paper-dosa.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">paper-dosa.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Paper+Dosa%2C+551+W+Cordova+Rd%2C+Santa+Fe+87505&amp;ll=35.674432,-105.952338" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">551 W Cordova Rd<br/>Santa Fe 87505</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Curry, Masala Dosa</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This warm spot serves up typical south Indian specialties including Masala Dosa, a large crepe filled with spiced potatoes and served with a variety of house-made chutneys. Guy was also blown away by the tender lamb curry stew. &quot;I want to jump right in it,&quot; he said after the first bite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Unique Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/paper-dosa-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.95234,35.67443,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dr. Field Good&#x27;s Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dr. Field Good&#x27;s Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe, NM 87501 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5059823033" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">505-982-3033</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://drfieldgoods.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">drfieldgoods.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dr.+Field+Good%27s+Kitchen%2C+187+Paseo+De+Peralta%2C+Santa+Fe%2C+NM+87501&amp;ll=35.692057,-105.948675" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">187 Paseo De Peralta<br/>Santa Fe, NM 87501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This restaurant serves unique dishes with a New Mexican flair. Hannah tries The Goat Torta which features tender, braised goat layered with habanero goat cheese, refried beans and honey habanero hot sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza Plus</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/dr-field-goods-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.94867,35.69206,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Zia Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Zia Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe, NM 87501 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5059887008" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 988-7008</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.ziadiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.ziadiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Zia+Diner%2C+326+S+Guadalupe+St%2C+Santa+Fe%2C+NM+87501&amp;ll=35.685657,-105.945418" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">326 S Guadalupe St<br/>Santa Fe, NM 87501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Salmon Quesadilla, Corned Beef Hash, Corn and Avocado Gazpacho</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Enjoy classic scratch-made diner fare with a Southwest twist at Zia&#x27;s. Guy appreciated the balance between the savory salmon and the sweet caramelized shallots in the smoked salmon quesadilla. He also recommends the corned beef hash and the refreshing corn and avocado gazpacho.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homestyle</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/zia-diner-angel-food-catering-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.94542,35.68566,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Full Belly Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Full Belly Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Reno, NV 89502</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://eatfullbellydeli.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">eatfullbellydeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Full+Belly+Deli%2C+3064+Mill+St.%2C+Reno%2C+NV+89502&amp;ll=39.517021,-119.774826" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3064 Mill St.<br/>Reno, NV 89502</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Biscuits and Gravy Burrito, Dirka Dirka Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Talk about living up to your name-this sandwich shop is known for serving up inventive sandwiches in huge portions. Their biscuits and gravy burrito is stuffed to the brim with cheese, hash browns, sausage and chorizo gravy, and an entire house-baked biscuit. It sounds intense, but it&#x27;s definitely a must-try. &quot;I was scared at first, but the way you seasoned it, it isn&#x27;t overly heavy,&quot; said Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Off the Beaten Path</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/reno/full-belly-deli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.77483,39.51702,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rowley Farmhouse Ales</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rowley Farmhouse Ales</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe, NM 87505 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.rowleyfarmhouse.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rowleyfarmhouse.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rowley+Farmhouse+Ales%2C+1405+Maclovia+St%2C+Santa+Fe%2C+NM+87505&amp;ll=35.660930,-105.983500" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1405 Maclovia St<br/>Santa Fe, NM 87505</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken and Biscuit, New England Clam Chowder</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners head to Rowley Farmhouse Ales for upscale farm-to-table comfort food paired with homemade rustic farmhouse and sour ales plus some of the best brews in the world. Their cooked-to-order new England Clam Chowder is some of the freshest you&#x27;ll ever have.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bagels, Biscuit and Boar</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/rowley-farmhouse-ales-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.98350,35.66093,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jambo Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jambo Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe 87505 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5054731269" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">505-473-1269</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://jambocafe.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">jambocafe.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jambo+Cafe%2C+2010+Cerrillos+Rd.%2C+Santa+Fe+87505&amp;ll=35.660434,-105.977784" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2010 Cerrillos Rd.<br/>Santa Fe 87505</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Caribbean Goat Stew; Banana Leaf-Wrapped Mahi Mahi</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Jambo Cafe, Chef Ahmed Obo brings African-Caribbean Cuisine to the Sante Fe locals. The Kenyan native uses a collection of Caribbean spices and flavors for the grilled mahi mahi platter. But as Guy learned, the goat stew is nothing short of &quot;the real deal,&quot; with its tender goat and handmade roti. The food is so popular, Obo has opened a second location, in Albuquerque&#x27;s NE Heights.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sammies and Stew</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/jambo-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.97778,35.66043,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Joseph&#x27;s Culinary Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Joseph&#x27;s Culinary Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe, NM 87501 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.josephsofsantafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.josephsofsantafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Joseph%27s+Culinary+Pub%2C+428+Agua+Fria+St%2C+Santa+Fe%2C+NM+87501&amp;ll=35.686532,-105.946108" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">428 Agua Fria St<br/>Santa Fe, NM 87501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Neck Confit, Organic Crispy Chicken Tamale</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Head to Joseph&#x27;s Culinary Pub for upscale food in a laid-back atmosphere. In addition to decadent dishes like Lamb Neck Confit, Guy was surprised by the Organic Crispy Chicken Tamale: After steaming chicken, green chile and masa in a corn husk, Chef Joseph then takes the tamale out of the husk and fries it in duck fat. Guy was impressed with the combination of flavors and textures. &quot;This makes me wonder why I haven&#x27;t had more duck fat-fried tamales,&quot; he said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Full of Surprises</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/josephs-culinary-pub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.94611,35.68653,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Casa Chimayo</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Casa Chimayo</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe, NM &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5054280391" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 428-0391</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.casachimayosantafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.casachimayosantafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Casa+Chimayo%2C+409+West+Water+St.%2C+Santa+Fe%2C+NM&amp;ll=35.687988,-105.944042" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">409 West Water St.<br/>Santa Fe, NM</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chimayo Tortilla Burger, Blue Corn Enchiladas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Casa Chimayo may as well be called Casa Abuelita. As Guy discovered on DDD, it&#x27;s like &amp;quot;walking into your grandmother&#x27;s house.&amp;quot; With its heartwarming New Mexican food (and chiles) on every inch of the menu, it&#x27;s no wonder Guy said the dynamite blue corn chicken enchiladas really hit the spot.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Aces of Authenticity</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/casa-chimayo-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.94404,35.68799,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Oyster Creek Inn</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Oyster Creek Inn</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Leeds Point, NJ 08220 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6096528565" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(609) 652-8565</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://oystercreekinnnj.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">oystercreekinnnj.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Oyster+Creek+Inn%2C+41+North+Oyster+Creek+Rd.%2C+Leeds+Point%2C+NJ+08220&amp;ll=39.504902,-74.417360" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">41 North Oyster Creek Rd.<br/>Leeds Point, NJ 08220</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Clams Mexicali; Jersey Devil Shrimp</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Oyster Creek Inn has an unbeatable location, set on a creek within what is now a national wildlife preserve. Accessible by car or boat, the restaurant prepares ultra-fresh seafood, including Guy&#x27;s recommendations of the spicy Jersey Devil shrimp with homemade hot sauce, and the Clams Mexicali, which are stuffed with chorizo, peppers and Mexican cheese. Make sure to get a seat outside when it&#x27;s warm.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oldies But Goodies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/leeds-point/oyster-creek-inn" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.41736,39.50490,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Back Road Pizza</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Back Road Pizza</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe, NM 87505 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5059559055" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 955-9055</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.backroadpizza.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.backroadpizza.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Back+Road+Pizza%2C+1807+2nd+St%2C+Santa+Fe%2C+NM+87505&amp;ll=35.662808,-105.965280" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1807 2nd St<br/>Santa Fe, NM 87505</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Texan Pizza, Penny&#x27;s Buschetta</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The thin cornmeal crust sprinkled with sesame seeds is the secret to all the pies at this pizzeria. Guy, a meat lover, devoured the Texan pizza topped with sausage, green chiles, pepperoni and Canadian bacon. The homemade pesto and balsamic vinegar sent Penny&#x27;s Bruschetta over the edge.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Who&#x27;Da Thunk It?<br/>Triple D Nation: Slurpin&#x27; Soup</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/backroad-pizza-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.96528,35.66281,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Back Street Bistro</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Back Street Bistro</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe, NM</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5059823500" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 982-3500</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://backstreetbistrodailysoup.blogspot.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">backstreetbistrodailysoup.blogspot.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Back+Street+Bistro%2C+513+Camino+de+los+Marquez%2C+Santa+Fe%2C+NM&amp;ll=35.673694,-105.949960" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">513 Camino de los Marquez<br/>Santa Fe, NM</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Turkey Wild Rice Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This &amp;quot;blink and you&#x27;ll miss it&amp;quot; restaurant brings a little bit of Brooklyn to Santa Fe, N.M. With owner David Jacoby, aka the &amp;quot;Duke of Soup,&amp;quot; Guy discovered the secrets to the &amp;quot;dynamite,&amp;quot; award-winning Smoked Turkey Wild Rice soup. For an unforgettable finish, try the scratch-made pumpkin pie.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of Gobble Gobble</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/back-street-bistro-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.94996,35.67369,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bert&#x27;s Burger Bowl</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bert&#x27;s Burger Bowl</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe, NM 87501 &middot; &#9733; 1.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5059820215" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 982-0215</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bertsburgerbowl.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bertsburgerbowl.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bert%27s+Burger+Bowl%2C+235+N+Guadalupe+St.%2C+Santa+Fe%2C+NM+87501&amp;ll=35.690740,-105.944487" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">235 N Guadalupe St.<br/>Santa Fe, NM 87501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Green Chile Cheeseburgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy Fieri tracks down fast food done right at Bert&#x27;s Burger Bowl in Santa Fe, NM, home of the Green Chile Cheeseburger, on Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of Fast Foods</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/berts-burger-bowl-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.94449,35.69074,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tune-Up Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tune-Up Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe, NM 87505 &middot; &#9733; 4.6 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5059837060" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 983-7060</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://tuneupsantafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">tuneupsantafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tune-Up+Cafe%2C+1115+Hickox+St.%2C+Santa+Fe%2C+NM+87505&amp;ll=35.681261,-105.958586" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1115 Hickox St.<br/>Santa Fe, NM 87505</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Banana Leaf Wrapped Tamales, Pupusas, Chile Relleno</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When husband and wife team Jesus and Charlotte Rivera opened Tune-Up Cafe, locals became instant fans of the Salvadorian pupusas and salmon eggs Benedict. The real kicker? Guy loved the chile relleno with cheese &quot;oozing out like lava on the Flavortown volcano.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Cultural Cookin&#x27;<br/>Neighborhood Favorites<br/>All in the Family</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/tune-up-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.95859,35.68126,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Harry&#x27;s Roadhouse</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Harry&#x27;s Roadhouse</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe, NM 87505 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5059894629" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">505-989-4629</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.harrysroadhousesantafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.harrysroadhousesantafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Harry%27s+Roadhouse%2C+96+B+Old+Las+Vegas+Hwy%2C+Santa+Fe%2C+NM+87505&amp;ll=35.626480,-105.920724" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">96 B Old Las Vegas Hwy<br/>Santa Fe, NM 87505</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brioche Stuffed with Peaches, Lemon Ricotta Pancakes, Huevos Divorciados</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Harry&#x27;s Roadhouse may be in Santa Fe but On Triple D, Harry tells Guy the pork butt scrapple with polenta and sage comes straight from Philadelphia. Not to worry, he still serves New Mexican favorites such as Blue Cornmeal Waffles or southwestern Migas with pickled Jalapeno and killer cinnamon rolls.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">What&#x27;s For Breakfast<br/>Best of the West</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/harrys-roadhouse-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.92072,35.62648,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tecolote Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tecolote Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe, NM 87505 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5059881362" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(505) 988-1362</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tecolotecafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tecolotecafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tecolote+Cafe%2C+1616+St+Michaels+Dr%2C+Santa+Fe%2C+NM+87505&amp;ll=35.672160,-105.961860" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1616 St Michaels Dr<br/>Santa Fe, NM 87505</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Huevos Yucatecos, Blue Corn Pancakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tecolote Cafe takes chiles seriously and guarantees theirs are straight from Santa Fe, N.M. The peppers make up the signature sauce Guy called &quot;a hot tub in Flavortown.&quot; Here&#x27;s a tip: If you want to sound like a local, order the Huevos Yucatecos &quot;Christmas&quot; style, with both red and green salsa.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Regional Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/tecolote-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.96186,35.67216,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Arable</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Arable</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Fe, NM 87508</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.arablesantafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.arablesantafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Arable%2C+7+Avenida+Vista+Grande%2C+Santa+Fe%2C+NM+87508&amp;ll=35.538712,-105.891649" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7 Avenida Vista Grande<br/>Santa Fe, NM 87508</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bison Dirty Fries, Lamb Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You&#x27;d never expect to find a restaurant with such big flavors tucked inside a strip mall, but that&#x27;s exactly what this off-the-beaten-path spot is doing. Nearly everything at the restaurant is sourced locally, from the potatoes in their Bison Fries to the meat in their Lamb Sandwich. To make the sandwich, homemade bread is spread with house-made tomato aioli and olive tapenade and is topped with feta, mozzarella, roasted red peppers and tender braised lamb. Guy was impressed with the combination of flavors: &quot;It&#x27;s really a Greek lamb dinner inside of a sandwich,&quot; he said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Loaded, Stuffed and Fried</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nm/santa-fe/arable-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.89165,35.53871,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jersey Girl Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jersey Girl Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hamilton Township, NJ 08619 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6098389799" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609-838-9799</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.jerseygirlcafenj.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jerseygirlcafenj.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jersey+Girl+Cafe%2C+731+Rte+33%2C+Hamilton+Township%2C+NJ+08619&amp;ll=40.231483,-74.679085" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">731 Rte 33<br/>Hamilton Township, NJ 08619</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kogi Steak Sandwich, Rosie Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Former computer programmer Kathy Rana left the tech world behind to open this cafe, where she now spends her days churning out comforting dishes and creative sandwiches. One filling favorite is the Kogi Steak. Rana douses thin slices of top round beef with a housemade Bulgogi marinade, then piles the meat onto a torpedo roll along with crisp lettuce, Jersey ripe tomatoes and spicy pickles. &quot;That thin-sliced meat is just so nice and light and tender,&quot; Guy declared after biting into the sandwich.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Carnivore Creations</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nj/hamilton-township/jersey-girl-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-74.67909,40.23148,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Crepe Expectations</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Crepe Expectations</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Las Vegas 89123 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (12 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7025834939" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">702-583-4939</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://crepeexpectations.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">crepeexpectations.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Crepe+Expectations%2C+9500+S+Eastern+Ave%2C+Las+Vegas+89123&amp;ll=36.016493,-115.117069" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">9500 S Eastern Ave<br/>Las Vegas 89123</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Sonora Crepe, The William Tell Crepe</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">In over-the-top Sin City, even the classic crepe gets revamped in outrageous new ways, as Guy learned during a visit to this Las Vegas restaurant. &quot;That citrus and the carne asada is fantastic,&quot; he said of the Sonora crepe, which comes stuffed with teres major steak that&#x27;s cooked down with orange, lemon and carne asada seasoning. Cheese, guacamole and fire-roasted salsa complete the creation.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Bowlful of Soul<br/>Takeout: Shipped, Sweet and Savory</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/crepe-expectations-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-115.11707,36.01649,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bachi Burger</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bachi Burger</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Las Vegas 89123 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (18 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7022422244" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">702-242-2244</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/bachi-burger-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/bachi-burger-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bachi+Burger%2C+470+E+Windmill+Ln+%23100%2C+Las+Vegas+89123&amp;ll=36.042614,-115.153053" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">470 E Windmill Ln #100<br/>Las Vegas 89123</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bachi Burger, The Banh-Mi Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Las Vegas burger joint is serving big American burgers with an Asian twist. Guy visited Bachi for its oxtail chili cheese fries and its signature Bachi Burger made with beef, pork and shrimp. Its unique flavor combos blew Guy away on Triple D, with him quipping: &quot;This is BurgerBomb.com.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Vegas Greats<br/>Top 10 Burgers<br/>International Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/bachi-burger-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-115.15305,36.04261,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Four Kegs Sports Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Four Kegs Sports Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Las Vegas 89107 &middot; &#9733; 3.2 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7028700255" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(702) 870-0255</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.fourkegs.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fourkegs.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Four+Kegs+Sports+Pub%2C+276+N+Jones+Blvd%2C+Las+Vegas+89107&amp;ll=36.175910,-115.223068" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">276 N Jones Blvd<br/>Las Vegas 89107</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza, Stromoboli, Cocktails</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">One of Guy&#x27;s favorite hangouts in college was the Four Kegs Sports Pub in Las Vegas, and to this day he swears they make the best stromboli he&#x27;s ever had. Owner Mario Perkins makes sure to keep a thin delicate crust on all of the stromboli he makes, and it&#x27;s just as good as Guy remembers it.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Guy&#x27;s Going Home<br/>That&#x27;s Italian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/four-kegs-sports-pub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-115.22307,36.17591,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fat Choy Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fat Choy Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Las Vegas, NV 89104 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7027943464" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">702-794-3464</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://fatchoylv.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">fatchoylv.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fat+Choy+Restaurant%2C+595+E+Sahara+Ave%2C+Las+Vegas%2C+NV+89104&amp;ll=36.143473,-115.146884" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">595 E Sahara Ave<br/>Las Vegas, NV 89104</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Belly Bao, Short-Rib Grilled Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Sheridan Su&#x27;s gamble of opening a food truck in Las Vegas in 2011 paid off big, as the crowds kept coming back for more of his Asian-American dishes. The popularity grew to the point where Chef Su now owns a restaurant, where he&#x27;s dishing up a Pork Belly Bao that Guy just had to try. The bao (or steamed bun) comes loaded with marinated pork belly, sauteed mustard greens, crushed peanuts and cilantro.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Taste of Asia</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/fat-choy-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-115.14688,36.14347,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Forte European Tapas Bar and Bistro</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Forte European Tapas Bar and Bistro</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Las Vegas 89103 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7022203876" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(702) 220-3876</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.barforte.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.barforte.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Forte+European+Tapas+Bar+and+Bistro%2C+4180+S+Rainbow+Blvd%2C+Las+Vegas+89103&amp;ll=36.112219,-115.241792" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4180 S Rainbow Blvd<br/>Las Vegas 89103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mixed Grill Plate, Thracian Clay Pot</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">While still in college, Chef Nina Manchev opened her Bulgarian restaurant at the age of 23. The mixed grill plate with three different types of Bulgarian sausage captured Guy&#x27;s heart. Topped with dry cured Bulgarian charcuterie, the Thracian Clay Pot was another one of Guy&#x27;s favorites.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Beef, Barbecue and Bar Food<br/>Vegas Greats<br/>Takeout: Flavortown Comes Home<br/>All Vegas, All the Time</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/forte-european-tapas-bar-bistro-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-115.24179,36.11222,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Shed Barbecue &amp; Blues Joint</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Shed Barbecue &amp; Blues Joint</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ocean Springs, MS 39565 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (29 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2288759590" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(228) 875-9590</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.theshedbbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.theshedbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Shed+Barbecue+%26+Blues+Joint%2C+7501+Hwy+57%2C+Ocean+Springs%2C+MS+39565&amp;ll=30.447320,-88.718422" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7501 Hwy 57<br/>Ocean Springs, MS 39565</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Baby Back Ribs, Brisket</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Down by the Mississippi you&#x27;ll find a sizable &quot;shed&quot; that houses a loyal community of barbecue lovers and live blues music. The house specialty is baby back ribs, which Guy calls &quot;as tender as you can get.&quot; They also serve up some righteous chicken &quot;wangs&quot; and brisket in massive quantities.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of BBQ</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ms/ocean-springs/the-shed-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-88.71842,30.44732,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Memphis Barbecue Co.</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Memphis Barbecue Co.</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Horn Lake, MS 38637 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6625363763" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(662) 536-3763</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://memphisbbqco.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">memphisbbqco.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Memphis+Barbecue+Co.%2C+709+Desoto+Cove%2C+Horn+Lake%2C+MS+38637&amp;ll=34.963325,-90.002368" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">709 Desoto Cove<br/>Horn Lake, MS 38637</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Baby Back Ribs, Pork Rinds, Cheese Fritters</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pit master Melissa Cookston is the only female to be a world BBQ champion. Guy got messy with the deliciously tender baby back ribs and he loved the crunch burger with pork rinds and juke sauce. The cheese fritters, pulled pork and brisket are the local favorites.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Deep Fried All-Stars<br/>Surf &#x27;N&#x27; Turf Jackpot</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ms/horn-lake/memphis-barbecue-co-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.00237,34.96332,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Memphis Street Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Memphis Street Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hernando, MS 38632 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6624299299" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(662) 429-9299</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://memphisstreetcafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">memphisstreetcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Memphis+Street+Cafe%2C+2476+Memphis+St%2C+Hernando%2C+MS+38632&amp;ll=34.823712,-89.994661" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2476 Memphis St<br/>Hernando, MS 38632</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Banana Bread French Toast, Shrimp with Grits</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this underground cafe, scratch-made Southern food is prepared fresh daily. Guy recommends the banana bread French toast smothered with caramelized bananas spiked with cognac and topped off with two scoops of vanilla-bean-and-fresh-ginger ice cream. The shrimp with grits is a local favorite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Unconventional Comforts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ms/hernando/memphis-street-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-89.99466,34.82371,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Louie &amp; the Redhead Lady</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Louie &amp; the Redhead Lady</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bay St. Louis 39520 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2283443338" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">228-344-3338</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.louieandtheredheadlady.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.louieandtheredheadlady.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Louie+%26+the+Redhead+Lady%2C+136+Blaize+Ave%2C+Bay+St.+Louis+39520&amp;ll=30.307403,-89.334908" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">136 Blaize Ave<br/>Bay St. Louis 39520</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oysters a la Louisiana, Shrimp and Fried Green Tomatoes, Grits and Grillades (Grits and Veal Patty)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Classic Louisiana fare is a staple at this family owned and operated diner. The oysters a la Louisiana were &quot;super fresh&quot; according to Guy. The delicate texture of the shrimp and fried green tomatoes with aioli was also appreciated. For a hearty breakfast, try the grits and veal grillades.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Quirky Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ms/bay-st--louis/louie-the-red-head-lady-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-89.33491,30.30740,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blow Fly Inn</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blow Fly Inn</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Gulfport 39507 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2282658225" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">228-265-8225</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/BlowFlyInnCourtneyLesley/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/BlowFlyInnCourtneyLesley</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blow+Fly+Inn%2C+1201+Washington+Ave%2C+Gulfport+39507&amp;ll=30.403040,-89.031541" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1201 Washington Ave<br/>Gulfport 39507</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jumbo Lump Crab Cake, 6 oz Hamburger Steak, Gumbo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Every dish at Blow Fly Inn is topped with a fly. Don&#x27;t be alarmed, as the fly is tiny, plastic and has become a signature garnish at the Blow Fly Inn. When Guy swung by, he looked past the fly and dove right into the bayou classics, including smoked sausage and Blow Fly&#x27;s gumbo made with okra.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Neighborhood Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ms/gulfport/blow-fly-inn-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-89.03154,30.40304,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rustica</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rustica</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Moorhead, MN 56560</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2182275388" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(218) 227-5388</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.dinerustica.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.dinerustica.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rustica%2C+315+Main+Avenue%2C+Moorhead%2C+MN+56560&amp;ll=46.873574,-96.774261" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">315 Main Avenue<br/>Moorhead, MN 56560</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rustica boasts a cozy neighborhood atmosphere in the historic 1898 Kassenborg Block building. The Eatery features rustic ambiance with exposed brick creating a warm, comfortable dining experience. Executive Chef Micah Leitel is dedicated to offering high quality, seasonally focused products and executes the diverse menu based on traditional American fare with European influences.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pasta, Potatoes and Pescatarian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/rustica" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.77426,46.87357,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Joe Tess Place</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Joe Tess Place</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Omaha, NE 68102 &middot; &#9733; 2.6 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4027334638" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">402-733-4638</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.joetessplace.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.joetessplace.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Joe+Tess+Place%2C+5424+S+24th+St%2C+Omaha%2C+NE+68102&amp;ll=41.202787,-95.947408" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5424 S 24th St<br/>Omaha, NE 68102</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Carp Sandwich, Fisherman&#x27;s Chowder, Catfish Fingers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Since 1967, Joe Tess has been home to the famous fried carp sandwich. The carp is brought in fresh each day from all over the Midwest and is used for more than just frying. Guy and the Triple D crew sampled everything from carp chowder to pickled carp and the carp combo dinner.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Deep-Fried Favorites<br/>Long Time Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ne/omaha/joe-tess-place-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.94741,41.20279,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pak&#x27;s Green Corner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pak&#x27;s Green Corner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Duluth, MN 55807 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2186249999" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(218) 624-9999</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/PaksGreenCorner" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/PaksGreenCorner</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pak%27s+Green+Corner%2C+4131+Grand+Ave%2C+Duluth%2C+MN+55807&amp;ll=46.750061,-92.154049" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4131 Grand Ave<br/>Duluth, MN 55807</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Curry, Pad Thai Burrito</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pak&#x27;s Green Corner serves Thai-native Pak&#x27;s version of good, comforting food. Guy loves the creativity behind the pad thai burrito. Another diner favorite is the tender, succulent lamb curry, with zucchini, carrots and potatoes, topped with sour cream and served with basmati rice.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Worldwide Flavorfest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/duluth/pak-s-green-corner" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.15405,46.75006,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Donatelli&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Donatelli&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">White Bear Lake, MN 55110 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6517779199" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">651-777-9199</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.donatellis.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.donatellis.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Donatelli%27s%2C+2692+E+County+Road+E%2C+White+Bear+Lake%2C+MN+55110&amp;ll=45.050128,-92.986042" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2692 E County Road E<br/>White Bear Lake, MN 55110</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meat Sauce, Southwest Chicken Turnover, Baked Mostaccoli with Pink Sauce</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this Italian comfort-food dive they&#x27;re making everything from meatballs to pizza and eight different types of pasta. Guy was enthusiastic about the fresh mostaccioli and special red sauce and he loved the Heart Stopper pizza loaded with sausage, hamburger, pepperoni, ham, bacon and cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Traditional Dishes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/white-bear-lake/donatellis-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.98604,45.05013,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bayport BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bayport BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bayport, MN 55003 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6519556337" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">651-955-6337</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://bayportbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">bayportbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bayport+BBQ%2C+328+5th+Ave+N%2C+Bayport%2C+MN+55003&amp;ll=45.021741,-92.781608" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">328 5th Ave N<br/>Bayport, MN 55003</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brisket Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The motto of this small-town barbecue joint is &quot;we aren&#x27;t for everyone,&quot; but Guy certainly liked what he found at this family-run joint. &quot;I give you all the props for doing it your way,&quot; said Guy, after tucking into white oak-smoked brisket topped with coleslaw and bread-and-butter pickles, all piled on a freshly baked hunk of bread.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">By Hand and By Fork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/bayport/bayport-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.78161,45.02174,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Northern Waters Smokehaus</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Northern Waters Smokehaus</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Duluth, MN 55802 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2187247307" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(218) 724-7307</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.northernwaterssmokehaus.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.northernwaterssmokehaus.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Northern+Waters+Smokehaus%2C+394+S+Lake+Ave+%23106%2C+Duluth%2C+MN+55802&amp;ll=46.781948,-92.094636" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">394 S Lake Ave #106<br/>Duluth, MN 55802</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Fish, Deli Meats, Sausage, Sandwiches</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked-fish fanatics will get a mouthful at Northern Waters Smokehaus, where they&#x27;re smoking everything from salmon to lamb and even curing their own salumi. But Guy had to stop by for their bison pastrami, Pastrami Mommy sandwich and whitefish basket - a quintessential Lake Superior dish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">By Land and Sea<br/>Fast Food Their Way</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/duluth/northern-waters-smokehaus-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.09464,46.78195,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Duluth Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Duluth Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Duluth, MN 55806 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2187261150" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(218) 726-1150</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.duluthgrill.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.duluthgrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Duluth+Grill%2C+118+S+27th+Ave+W%2C+Duluth%2C+MN+55806&amp;ll=46.760614,-92.130050" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">118 S 27th Ave W<br/>Duluth, MN 55806</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Banana Cream Pie, Pot Roast</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Whether it&#x27;s the homemade comfort food like pies, pasties or pot roast (made with bison, of course) or the commitment to doing strange things like raising bees on the roof, Duluth Grill makes you take notice. Guy loves their banana cream pie, a not-too-sweet, flaky concoction presented beautifully.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sweet &#x27;n Savory</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/duluth/duluth-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.13005,46.76061,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>At Sara&#x27;s Table Chester Creek Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">At Sara&#x27;s Table Chester Creek Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Duluth, MN 55812 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2187246811" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(218) 724-6811</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.astccc.net/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.astccc.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=At+Sara%27s+Table+Chester+Creek+Cafe%2C+1902+E+8th+St%2C+Duluth%2C+MN+55812&amp;ll=46.810364,-92.082933" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1902 E 8th St<br/>Duluth, MN 55812</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brisket Sandwich, Fruit Pies</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The ingredients at this farm-to-table restaurant are sourced locally. Try the harvested cranberry wild rice bread in the French toast. You&#x27;ll find all the American classics and pop culture favorites, such as Korean-style barbecue ribs, pizza and Baja fish tacos, plus a gluten-free selection.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sauced and Spiced</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/duluth/at-saras-table-chester-creek-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.08293,46.81036,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Nook</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Nook</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">St. Paul, MN 55116 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6516984347" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">651-698-4347</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.crnook.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.crnook.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Nook%2C+492+Hamline+Ave+S%2C+St.+Paul%2C+MN+55116&amp;ll=44.926570,-93.156669" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">492 Hamline Ave S<br/>St. Paul, MN 55116</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Juicy Nookie Burger, Guy&#x27;s Big Bite Burger, Hand-Cut French Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Nook is a no-fuss burger joint that has mastered the art of stuffed burgers. The Spanish Fly consists of a 50/50 blend of beef and Spanish-spiced pork filled with queso. In honor of Guy, they created Guys Big Bite, a pepper Jack-stuffed burger with bacon, topped with roast beef and cheddar.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Serious Sandwiches<br/>Top 10 Burgers<br/>Burgers, Rings and Fries</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/st-paul/the-nook-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.15667,44.92657,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Blue Door Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Blue Door Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">St. Paul, MN 55104 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6514931865" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(651) 493-1865</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thebdp.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thebdp.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Blue+Door+Pub%2C+1811+Selby+Ave%2C+St.+Paul%2C+MN+55104&amp;ll=44.946728,-93.176753" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1811 Selby Ave<br/>St. Paul, MN 55104</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Blucy</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Visit The Blue Door Pub to find out why Guy said, &amp;quot;I&#x27;d like to float on that burger to Flavortown!&amp;quot; Try the signature stuffed burger made with blue cheese and garlic, known as the Blucy, or go bold and sample more-unusual offerings, like the burger topped with red currant jelly.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Made to Order</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/st-paul/the-blue-door-pub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.17675,44.94673,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Amato&#x27;s Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Amato&#x27;s Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Omaha, NE 68016 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4025585010" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">402-558-5010</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ne/omaha/amatos-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ne/omaha/amatos-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Amato%27s+Restaurant%2C+6405+Center+St%2C+Omaha%2C+NE+68016&amp;ll=41.237578,-96.012229" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6405 Center St<br/>Omaha, NE 68016</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Italian Sausage, Chicken Fried Steak, Ricotta-Stuffed Pancake</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sammy Amato has been making his family&#x27;s Italian sausage recipe since he was a child, and soon went from a small fair stand to a full-fledged restaurant of his own in Omaha. Guy recommends the chicken fried steak and the ricotta-stuffed pancakes, complete with homemade ricotta cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Steak, Sausage and Salami<br/>Incredible Italian<br/>Better Than Ever</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ne/omaha/amatos-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.01223,41.23758,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Big Mama&#x27;s Kitchen &amp; Catering</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Big Mama&#x27;s Kitchen &amp; Catering</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Omaha, NE 68104 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4024556262" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(402) 455-6262</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bigmamaskitchen.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bigmamaskitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Big+Mama%27s+Kitchen+%26+Catering%2C+3223+North+45th+Street%2C+Omaha%2C+NE+68104&amp;ll=41.295473,-95.993834" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3223 North 45th Street<br/>Omaha, NE 68104</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big Mama&#x27;s Kitchen Oven Fried Chicken, Afro Burger, Pig Ear Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">What better place to have old-school comfort food than in a former school building? Patricia Barron of Big Mama&#x27;s Kitchen serves up her grandma&#x27;s fried chicken, spicy Afro Burgers and pig ears at this Omaha, Neb., staple. While initially skeptical, Guy quickly became a fan of the Pig Ear Sandwich.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Fried and Smoked<br/>Cookin&#x27; It Old School</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ne/omaha/big-mamas-kitchen-catering-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.99383,41.29547,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Firehole Bar-B-Que Company</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Firehole Bar-B-Que Company</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">West Yellowstone, MT 59758 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Fireholebbq/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/Fireholebbq</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Firehole+Bar-B-Que+Company%2C+120+Firehole+Ave%2C+West+Yellowstone%2C+MT+59758&amp;ll=44.662148,-111.098735" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">120 Firehole Ave<br/>West Yellowstone, MT 59758</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brisket, Ribs, Corn Salad</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy stumbled upon this barbecue joint four days after it opened. Little Mike Shults and his father Big Mike Shults, restaurant vets with a place in Idaho, are smoking meats in a trailer right outside of Yellowstone National Park. Their simple, straightforward barbecue won Guy over.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: From Brisket to Bison</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mt/restaurants-in-west-yellowstone/firehole-bar-b-que-company-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.09873,44.66215,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Storm Castle Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Storm Castle Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bozeman, MT 59715 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.stormcastlecafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.stormcastlecafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Storm+Castle+Cafe%2C+5+Tai+Ln%2C+Bozeman%2C+MT+59715&amp;ll=45.663802,-111.053982" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5 Tai Ln<br/>Bozeman, MT 59715</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Monte Cristo, Pork Carnitas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and owner Scott Pearson and his wife, Nicole Warner, are dishing up a true farm-to-table experience in Bozeman, Montana. The farm that provides some of the food for the restaurant has been in his family since the 1970s. Guy was floored by Chef Pearson&#x27;s take on the Monte Cristo, which uses ham raised at the family farm. &quot;This is next level,&quot; said Guy. &quot;This is a destination dish.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pretzels, Pork and Paella</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mt/bozeman/storm-castle-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.05398,45.66380,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Iron Barley</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Iron Barley</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">High Ridge, MO 63049 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6366719911" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">636-671-9911</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.ironbarleyshighhogridge.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.ironbarleyshighhogridge.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Iron+Barley%2C+3367+High+Ridge+Blvd%2C+High+Ridge%2C+MO+63049&amp;ll=38.564807,-90.245906" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3367 High Ridge Blvd<br/>High Ridge, MO 63049</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">German Spaetzle, Zarzuela, Ballistic Elvis Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Iron Barley may be a tavern but Guy discovered &quot;spectacular&quot; food within. Iron Barley calls its cuisine &quot;traditional yet unusual,&quot; as the menu features Zarzuela, a Spanish seafood stew, next to a Ballistic Elvis sandwich made of peanut butter, banana, American cheese and strawberry preserves.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Neighborhood Joints<br/>All Stacked Up</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/high-ridge/iron-barley-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.24591,38.56481,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Highway 61 Roadhouse and Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Highway 61 Roadhouse and Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Webster Groves, MO 63119 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3149680061" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(314) 968-0061</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hwy61roadhouse.com/index.php" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hwy61roadhouse.com/index.php</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Highway+61+Roadhouse+and+Kitchen%2C+34+S+Old+Orchard+Ave%2C+Webster+Groves%2C+MO+63119&amp;ll=38.589924,-90.338627" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">34 S Old Orchard Ave<br/>Webster Groves, MO 63119</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ Spaghetti</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Highway 61 is a stretch of road known as &quot;The Blues Highway,&quot; connecting St. Louis to New Orleans. The Roadhouse celebrates all the great food in this region, from Midwestern comfort food to barbecue and all the way down to Cajun and Creole. Guy tried the BBQ Spaghetti (yes, you read that right).</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Authentic Eats<br/>Pub Grub</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/webster-groves/highway-61-roadhouse-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.33863,38.58992,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sweetie Pie&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sweetie Pie&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">St. Louis, MO 63110 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3143710304" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(314) 371-0304</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://sweetiepieskitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">sweetiepieskitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sweetie+Pie%27s%2C+4270+Manchester+Ave%2C+St.+Louis%2C+MO+63110&amp;ll=38.626827,-90.256704" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4270 Manchester Ave<br/>St. Louis, MO 63110</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mac &#x27;n&#x27; Cheese, Smothered Pork, Okra, Mashed Potatoes, Sweet Potatoes, Rice and Gravy, Cabbage and Greens</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Miss Robbie Montgomery, an ex-background singer for Ike and Tina Turner, hung up her microphone she decided to pick up a spoon and start cooking the soul food recipes her mother taught her as a girl. Guy loves her mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese, not to mention the sass she serves along with it.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Like Mama Made</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/st-louis/sweetie-pies-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.25670,38.62683,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Shaved Duck</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Shaved Duck</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">St. Louis, MO 63118 &middot; &#9733; 3.9 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3147761407" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(314) 776-1407</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.theshavedduck.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.theshavedduck.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Shaved+Duck%2C+2900+Virginia+Ave%2C+St.+Louis%2C+MO+63118&amp;ll=38.603625,-90.235908" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2900 Virginia Ave<br/>St. Louis, MO 63118</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cheese Fries, Smoked Duck</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This grocery store turned restaurant was founded on &amp;quot;barbecue, folk and soul.&amp;quot; Guy got extra messy as he dug into the cheese fries piled high with smoked pork butt and rib meat. Topped with cherry juniper jam, the smoked duck was so good with its crispy skin that Guy devoured it.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Food Done Right</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/st-louis/the-shaved-duck-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.23591,38.60363,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Guerrilla Street Food</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Guerrilla Street Food</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">St. Louis, MO 63110</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.guerrillastreetfood.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.guerrillastreetfood.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Guerrilla+Street+Food%2C+Roaming+Food+Truck%2C+St.+Louis%2C+MO+63110&amp;ll=38.621247,-90.252616" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Roaming Food Truck<br/>St. Louis, MO 63110</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Blue Crab Ceviche, Pancit, One Inch Punch</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Brian Hardesty and co-owner Joel Crespo are crankin&#x27; out Filipino street food. On a hot summer day, Guy enjoys the blue crab ceviche and an order of pancit made with fresh noodles. To finish off your meal, order the One Inch Punch with black currant juice, pineapple juice, coconut milk and mint.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Noodles and Quahogs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/st-louis/guerilla-street-food-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.25262,38.62125,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dressel&#x27;s Public House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dressel&#x27;s Public House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">St. Louis, MO 63108 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3143611060" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(314) 361-1060</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://dresselspublichouse.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">dresselspublichouse.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dressel%27s+Public+House%2C+419+N+Euclid+Ave%2C+St.+Louis%2C+MO+63108&amp;ll=38.649143,-90.261140" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">419 N Euclid Ave<br/>St. Louis, MO 63108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Porchetta &quot;Louie,&quot; Pretzel</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this slow-food dive the food is scratch-made with a farm-to-table attitude. According to Guy, the porchetta &amp;quot;Louie&amp;quot; with provel, rapini and pepperoncini on a toasted baguette was nothing short of &amp;quot;spectacular.&amp;quot; The salt, the crust and the chew was why Guy loved the pretzel with rarebit sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pubs and Grub</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/st-louis/dressels-public-house-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.26114,38.64914,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Anthonino&#x27;s Taverna</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Anthonino&#x27;s Taverna</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">St. Louis, MO 63110 &middot; &#9733; 4.6 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3147734455" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(314) 773-4455</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://anthoninos.com/index.php" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">anthoninos.com/index.php</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Anthonino%27s+Taverna%2C+2225+Macklind+Ave%2C+St.+Louis%2C+MO+63110&amp;ll=38.614373,-90.277805" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2225 Macklind Ave<br/>St. Louis, MO 63110</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Toaster Raviolis, Chicken Slovakia</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The two brothers who run this dive are both Greek and Italian so naturally they&#x27;re serving Greek and Italian comfort food with a St. Louis spin. The toaster raviolis served with homemade marinara dipping sauce and topped with Romano cheese impressed Guy. Feeling Greek? Try the chicken slovakia.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Family, All the Time</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/st-louis/anthoninos-taverna-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.27781,38.61437,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Smokin&#x27; Guns BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Smokin&#x27; Guns BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">North Kansas City, MO 64116 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8162212535" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">816-221-2535</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.smokingunsbbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.smokingunsbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Smokin%27+Guns+BBQ%2C+1218+Swift+Ave%2C+North+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64116&amp;ll=39.131000,-94.577793" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1218 Swift Ave<br/>North Kansas City, MO 64116</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Brisket Sandwich, Burnt Ends, Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Those not in the know might drive right by Smokin&#x27; Guns BBQ in North Kansas City&#x27;s industrial district, but they would miss what Guy calls &quot;one killer brisket.&quot; Helmed by Phil Hopkins and his wife, Linda, the eatery boasts &quot;competition-worthy&quot; &#x27;cue that has earned more than 400 awards to date.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kansas City Barbecue Tour<br/>Triple D Nation: Meat Mashup</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/north-kansas-city/smokin-guns-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.57779,39.13100,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Espino&#x27;s Mexican Bar and Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Espino&#x27;s Mexican Bar and Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chesterfield, MO 63005 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6365190044" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(636) 519-0044</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://espinosmexicanbargrill.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">espinosmexicanbargrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Espino%27s+Mexican+Bar+and+Grill%2C+17409+Chesterfield+Airport+Rd%2C+Chesterfield%2C+MO+63005&amp;ll=38.668893,-90.608124" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">17409 Chesterfield Airport Rd<br/>Chesterfield, MO 63005</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Chili Verde, Ribs, Mole</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Locals love coming to this dive for Chef Espino&#x27;s authentic Mexican family recipes packed full of flavor. The pork chili verde with yellow rice and refried beans Guy called &quot;off the hook&quot; and thought it had the perfect amount of spice. Diners also like to order the ribs and the mole.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mex to the Max<br/>Turn On Traditional</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/chesterfield/espinos-mexican-bar-and-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.60812,38.66889,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Swagger Fine Spirits &amp; Food</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Swagger Fine Spirits &amp; Food</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64114 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8163614388" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(816) 361-4388</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.facebook.com/Swaggerkc/info" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/Swaggerkc/info</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Swagger+Fine+Spirits+%26+Food%2C+8431+Wornall+Rd%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64114&amp;ll=38.974779,-94.594742" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">8431 Wornall Rd<br/>Kansas City, MO 64114</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Flying Monkey Chili, Dead Texan and Suribachi Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">In the case of Derek Boone and Dustin Craighead, ignorance was bliss when they first chose to open Swagger Fine Spirits &amp;amp; Food. Neither had any restaurant experience but Guy couldn&#x27;t tell. Their monstrous Suribachi Burger redefines burgers with its tempura-battered, deep-fried beef patty.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Top 10 Burgers<br/>Burgers &#x27;n More</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/swagger-fine-spirits-and-food-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.59474,38.97478,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Succotash</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Succotash</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64108</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8164212807" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(816) 421-2807</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.succotashkc.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.succotashkc.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Succotash%2C+2601+Holmes+St%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64108&amp;ll=39.079055,-94.575809" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2601 Holmes St<br/>Kansas City, MO 64108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eight-Layer Citrus Cake</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Succotash&#x27;s eclectic vibe can be seen in everything from the eight-layer citrus cake with teal frosting to their artistic, kitschy decor. For breakfast, locals love the pork hash with sides of black beans and potatoes. Guy says of this spicy plate, &quot;Holy hash, Batman.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork, Pasta and Barbecue<br/>Triple D Nation: Something Sweet</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/succotash-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.57581,39.07905,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Extra Virgin</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Extra Virgin</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64108</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8168422205" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(816) 842-2205</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.extravirginkc.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.extravirginkc.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Extra+Virgin%2C+1900+Main+St.%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64108&amp;ll=39.090244,-94.583881" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1900 Main St.<br/>Kansas City, MO 64108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Duck Tongue Tacos, Braised Pork Jowl</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Curtis Stone has eaten every nightcrawler imaginable but Extra Virgin&#x27;s high-end duck tongue tacos were a first. The tongues, marinated in spicy achiote paste and grilled with duck neck, truly exemplify Extra Virgin&#x27;s unique take on exotic cuisine. Up next: how about beef tongue ravioli?</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Full of Surprises</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/extra-virgin-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.58388,39.09024,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Danny Edward&#x27;s BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Danny Edward&#x27;s BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64108 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8162830880" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(816) 283-0880</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.dannyedwardsblvdbbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.dannyedwardsblvdbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Danny+Edward%27s+BBQ%2C+2900+SW+Blvd%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64108&amp;ll=39.090502,-94.564308" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2900 SW Blvd<br/>Kansas City, MO 64108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burnt Ends, Beef Brisket</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This spot&#x27;s famous for its beef brisket, especially the burnt ends sandwich. Called &amp;quot;Ol&#x27; Smoky,&amp;quot; the beefy bomb features the flavorful edges of the brisket, slow-smoked with hickory. They also offer beef, turkey and pork by the pound and a three-meat special for those on a carnivorous streak.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of Gobble Gobble</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/danny-edwards-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.56431,39.09050,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cupini&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cupini&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64111 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8167537662" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(816) 753-7662</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cupinis.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cupinis.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cupini%27s%2C+1809+Westport+Rd%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64111&amp;ll=39.050062,-94.606941" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1809 Westport Rd<br/>Kansas City, MO 64111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gnocchi, Ravioli, Lasagna</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From the cannoli to the gnocchi, everything from Cupini&#x27;s comes out fresh. As Guy learned on DDD, even the pasta sheets are made in-house for the signature six-layer lasagna topped with a hearty marina sauce and fresh mozzarella. Guy&#x27;s reaction? &amp;quot;This is everything that you want in lasagna.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork, Pasta and Barbecue</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/cupinis-restaurant2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.60694,39.05006,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Banksia Bakehouse</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Banksia Bakehouse</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64105 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://banksiabakehouse.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">banksiabakehouse.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Banksia+Bakehouse%2C+109+W.+9th+St%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64105&amp;ll=39.103527,-94.584507" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">109 W. 9th St<br/>Kansas City, MO 64105</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork and Fennel Sausage Roll, Meat Pie with Cheesy Potato Topping</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After retiring from his longtime job in the pharmaceutical industry, chef-owner Rob Joseph decided to bring authentic dishes from Australia to the Midwest with this creative bakery. His most unique item is the Pork and Fennel Sausage Roll: pastry dough that&#x27;s layered with butter, folded 1,000 times and wrapped around a tender house-made sausage. Guy had never tasted anything like it: &quot;That is its own entity, and it is dynamite,&quot; he said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Australian to Asian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/banksia-bakehouse-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.58451,39.10353,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blue Koi</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blue Koi</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64111 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8165615003" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(816) 561-5003</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bluekoi.net/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bluekoi.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blue+Koi%2C+1803+W+39th+St%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64111&amp;ll=39.057174,-94.606402" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1803 W 39th St<br/>Kansas City, MO 64111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chili Pepper Wontons, Firebird Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Blue Koi, two sisters cook up traditional Chinese dishes with some tasty twists. Guy devours an entire dish of the chili pepper wontons filled with a mouthwatering mixture of shrimp, pork and chicken and topped with chili sauce. Want even more heat? Add the firebird chicken noodles to your meal.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Time<br/>Triple D Nation: A Family Affair</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/blue-koi" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.60640,39.05717,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>YJ&#x27;s Snack Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">YJ&#x27;s Snack Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64108 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8164725533" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(816) 472-5533</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.yjs-snackbar.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.yjs-snackbar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=YJ%27s+Snack+Bar%2C+128+W.+18th+St.%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64108&amp;ll=39.092004,-94.585697" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">128 W. 18th St.<br/>Kansas City, MO 64108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chorizo, Meatloaf Sandwich, Mayan Tostadas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Using his world travels as inspiration, David Ford opened YJ&#x27;s Snackbar as a way to pay homage to his favorite worldly dishes. Guy devoured each culinary adventure, from the North African lamb kebabs to the Turkish stuffed figs. Here, every dish is different and so is each day&#x27;s menu.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A World of Flavors</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/yjs-snack-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.58570,39.09200,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>BB&#x27;s Lawnside BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">BB&#x27;s Lawnside BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64131 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8168227427" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(816) 822-7427</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://bbslawnsidebbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">bbslawnsidebbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=BB%27s+Lawnside+BBQ%2C+1205+E+85th+St.%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64131&amp;ll=38.973163,-94.574737" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1205 E 85th St.<br/>Kansas City, MO 64131</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ Sundae</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At BB&#x27;s Lawnside BBQ, it&#x27;s one juicy Kansas City-style barbecue plate after another. Lawnside still uses the original 1950s smoker for their burnt ends and hickory-smoked pork spareribs. For a real treat, try the BBQ Sundae, a three-layered Mason jar of pit beans, coleslaw and pulled pork.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort and Soul</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/bb-s-lawnside-bbq" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.57474,38.97316,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mama&#x27;s 39th Street</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mama&#x27;s 39th Street</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64111 &middot; &#9733; 1.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8165316422" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">816-531-6422</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/39th-street-mamas-closed-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/39th-street-mamas-closed-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mama%27s+39th+Street%2C+3906+Waddell+St.%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64111&amp;ll=39.056596,-94.595957" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3906 Waddell St.<br/>Kansas City, MO 64111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy Fieri visits one of America&#x27;s greatest breakfast joints, Mama&#x27;s 39th Street, in Kansas City, MO, for some outrageous homemade hash and 60 different omelets on Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big Breakfast</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/39th-street-mamas-closed-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.59596,39.05660,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Brick</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Brick</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64108 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8164211634" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(816) 421-1634</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thebrickkcmo.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thebrickkcmo.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Brick%2C+1727+McGee+St%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64108&amp;ll=39.092327,-94.579764" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1727 McGee St<br/>Kansas City, MO 64108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bacon-Wrapped and Beer-Battered Deep-Fried Hot Dog, Meatloaf Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">What else can you ask for besides a music venue with homemade food? Guy says &quot;they don&#x27;t skimp on the goodness at this pub-grub joint,&quot; and would you want them to? This is where you want to go to hear music, have a meatloaf sandwich and have a good night.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pub Grub<br/>Wings, Dogs and Claws</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/the-brick-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.57976,39.09233,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Klubb Krokstrom</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Klubb Krokstrom</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64111 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://klubbkrokstrom.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">klubbkrokstrom.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Klubb+Krokstrom%2C+3601+Broadway+Blvd%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64111&amp;ll=39.062019,-94.590244" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3601 Broadway Blvd<br/>Kansas City, MO 64111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mushroom Strudel, Flying Jacob</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This modern Scandinavian eatery is bringing one of a kind dishes to the Midwest, like their savory take on strudel. Instead of a sweet filling, they stuff the typical puff pastry with a mix of roasted mushrooms and goat cheese before baking. The crispy pastry is then served over a cream made with aquavit, a Scandinavian spirit similar to gin, and is drizzled with a mulled wine sauce. One bite of the dish immediately reminded Guy of food he had as a student traveling in Norway: &quot;The concentration of flavors is through the roof,&quot; he said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Far-Flung Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/klubb-krokstrom-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.59024,39.06202,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pigwich</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pigwich</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64106 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://thelocalpig.com/pigwich/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">thelocalpig.com/pigwich</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pigwich%2C+20+E.+5th+St.%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64106&amp;ll=39.108687,-94.582167" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">20 E. 5th St.<br/>Kansas City, MO 64106</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big Pig Sandwich, Short Rib Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This sandwich shop isn&#x27;t for vegetarians: most of their dishes are centered around beef and pork, which are all fresh cuts from the in-house butcher. Go all in and order the Big Pig sandwich: a pulled pork burger patty and fried pork tenderloin are topped with a trio of cheeses, barbecue sauce, picked jalapenos, nduja sausage and house-made ranch. Guy also loved the Short Rib Burger, which he called a &quot;flavor punch.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s All-Star Guests</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/pigwich-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.58217,39.10869,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>PotPie</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">PotPie</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64111 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8165612702" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(816) 561-2702</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.kcpotpie.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.kcpotpie.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=PotPie%2C+904+Westport+Rd%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64111&amp;ll=39.050807,-94.597093" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">904 Westport Rd<br/>Kansas City, MO 64111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Pot Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At PotPie, a menu of simple, refined dishes draws the crowds. Here, pot pie gets the French treatment, resulting in a mouthwatering dish made of fresh chicken, veggie-laden broth and puff pastry. Guy can&#x27;t get enough of this Frenchified comfort-food staple, which he calls &quot;creamy&quot; and &quot;delicious.&quot; &amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crazy for Chicken<br/>Soup, Salad and Seafood</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/potpie" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.59709,39.05081,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Kansas City Taco Company</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Kansas City Taco Company</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64106 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.kctacocompany.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.kctacocompany.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Kansas+City+Taco+Company%2C+520+Walnut+St%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64106&amp;ll=39.108255,-94.581667" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">520 Walnut St<br/>Kansas City, MO 64106</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cowboy Burrito, Korean Pork Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You&#x27;ll find more than traditional Mexican food at this inventive taco joint. At Kansas City Taco Company, Arthur Leduc packs all kinds of funky regional and international flavors into tortillas. A local favorite is the Cowboy Burrito, which highlights the classic flavors of Kansas City. To make it, a flour tortilla is packed with pulled pork and hot chorizo and then deep fried. It&#x27;s then slathered with a gooey, house-made queso blanco and served with rice and spicy pinto beans. &quot;You know what that&#x27;s lacking?&quot; Guy asked after a bite. &quot;Nothing!&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spinning the Globe</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/kansas-city-taco-company-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.58167,39.10826,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Brewburger&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Brewburger&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Omaha, NE 68127 &middot; &#9733; 2.1 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4026147644" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(402) 614-7644</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.brewburgersomaha.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.brewburgersomaha.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Brewburger%27s%2C+4629+South+108th+Street%2C+Omaha%2C+NE+68127&amp;ll=41.213184,-96.080681" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4629 South 108th Street<br/>Omaha, NE 68127</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old Fashioned Brisket Sandwich, The Maverick Burger, Cheesy Sacramento Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After moving to Omaha, Neb., Canadian native Yves Menard decided to bring the smoked brisket sandwich there, which Guy thought was &#x27;&#x27;dynamite.&#x27;&#x27; Of course, the place wouldn&#x27;t be called Brewburger&#x27;s without burgers like the Cheesy Sacramento, which Yves was inspired to make after watching Triple D.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Doin&#x27; Their Own Thing</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ne/omaha/brewburgers-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-96.08068,41.21318,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Happy Gillis Cafe &amp; Hangout</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Happy Gillis Cafe &amp; Hangout</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, MO 64106 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8164713663" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(816) 471-3663</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.happygillis.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.happygillis.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Happy+Gillis+Cafe+%26+Hangout%2C+549+Gillis+St%2C+Kansas+City%2C+MO+64106&amp;ll=39.108998,-94.570275" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">549 Gillis St<br/>Kansas City, MO 64106</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Flank Steak Sandwich Marinated in Red Wine and Cola, Posole Verde</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Not your typical run-of-the-mill soup and sandwich shop, Happy Gillis Cafe is owned by a husband and wife duo known for flank steak sandwiches marinated in cola and wine. &amp;quot;It&#x27;s so outside the box,&amp;quot; says Guy. Locals chime in: &amp;quot;You can taste how much they love food here.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/happy-gillis-cafe-hangout-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.57027,39.10900,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>California Tacos</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">California Tacos</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Omaha, NE 68131 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4023420212" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">402-342-0212</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.californiatacosandmore.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.californiatacosandmore.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=California+Tacos%2C+3235+California+Street%2C+Omaha%2C+NE+68131&amp;ll=41.264713,-95.961344" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3235 California Street<br/>Omaha, NE 68131</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">California Taco, Deep Fried Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owner Brad Bogard&#x27;s signature dishes and cooking Mexican his way keeps regulars coming back for heavy hitters like the puffy shelled taco called the California Taco. Try the Chicken Enchilada, made with tortillas dipped in sauce before being pan-fried, delivering a burst of flavors with every bite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mex to the Max<br/>All Kinds of Fast Foods</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ne/omaha/california-tacos-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.96134,41.26471,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dari-Ette Drive-In</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dari-Ette Drive-In</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">St. Paul, MN 55106 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6517763470" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(651) 776-3470</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Dari-ette-Drive-In/107157469329242" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Dari-ette-Drive-In/107157469329242</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dari-Ette+Drive-In%2C+1440+E+Minnehaha+Ave%2C+St.+Paul%2C+MN+55106&amp;ll=44.962919,-93.039762" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1440 E Minnehaha Ave<br/>St. Paul, MN 55106</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Sausage, Spaghetti with Meatballs, Italiano, Mac Daddy Meatball Sandwich, Homemade Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Authentic Italian food at a drive-in restaurant is a rarity, but that&#x27;s exactly what Angela Fida and her family have been doing at Dari-Ette Drive-In for more than 50 years. Angela cooks up fried sausage, meatballs and spaghetti with a sauce that&#x27;s so secret she won&#x27;t even tell Guy what&#x27;s in it.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">American Cookin&#x27;<br/>Diners, Drive-ins and Dives</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/st-paul/dari-ette-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.03976,44.96292,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Andale Taqueria y Mercado</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Andale Taqueria y Mercado</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Richfield, MN 55423 &middot; &#9733; 3.2 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6122598868" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612-259-8868</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://andaletaqueriaymercado.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">andaletaqueriaymercado.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Andale+Taqueria+y+Mercado%2C+W+77th+St%2C+Richfield%2C+MN+55423&amp;ll=44.865442,-93.297313" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">W 77th St<br/>Richfield, MN 55423</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos Al Pastor, Carnitas Tamales</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When some of Guy&#x27;s Minnesota-based DDD crew told him he could find a &quot;real-deal Mexican joint&quot; just a short drive from downtown Minneapolis, he just had to check it out. &quot;There is no way we&#x27;re in Minnesota,&quot; Guy said after one bite of the tacos al pastor bursting with the flavors of Mexico (think achiote-marinated pork and creamy avocado salsa).</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mex to the Max<br/>Homeland Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/richfield/andale-taqueria-y-mercado-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.29731,44.86544,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Smalley&#x27;s Caribbean Barbeque &amp; Pirate Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Smalley&#x27;s Caribbean Barbeque &amp; Pirate Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Stillwater, MN 55082 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6514395375" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(651) 439-5375</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://smalleyscaribbeanbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">smalleyscaribbeanbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Smalley%27s+Caribbean+Barbeque+%26+Pirate+Bar%2C+423+Main+St+S%2C+Stillwater%2C+MN+55082&amp;ll=45.053914,-92.804151" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">423 Main St S<br/>Stillwater, MN 55082</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jerk Chicken, Jerk Pork Tacos, Triple Six Wings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This diner is serving up Caribbean BBQ with a fiery-hot twist. Follow Guy&#x27;s lead and dig into the jerk pork tacos with grilled scallion aioli, which he says have &amp;quot;fantastic flavor.&amp;quot; Or try the spicy jerk chicken, as seen on Best. Ever. Smoked slow and low, it is packed with a potent punch of heat.&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;&lt;/i&gt;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crazy for Chicken<br/>Unexpected Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/stillwater/smalleys-caribbean-barbeque-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.80415,45.05391,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Victor&#x27;s 1959 Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Victor&#x27;s 1959 Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55409 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6128278948" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(612) 827-8948</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.victors1959cafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.victors1959cafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Victor%27s+1959+Cafe%2C+3756+Grand+Ave+S%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55409&amp;ll=44.934233,-93.284728" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3756 Grand Ave S<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55409</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Picadillo and Creole Sauce, Rachero Cubano, Cuban Sandwich, Flank Steak</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Florida isn&#x27;t the only place to get delicious Cuban food in the United States - just take a look at Victor&#x27;s 1959 Cafe in Minneapolis. Owner Niki Stavrou uses authentic Cuban recipes for meals such as ranchero Cubano and picadillo. Guy thought the Cuban sandwich was &#x27;&#x27;as legit as they come.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Global Goodies<br/>Triple D Nation: Something for Everyone</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/victors-1959-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.28473,44.93423,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Unideli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Unideli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55404 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6127216677" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612-721-6677</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.unideliramen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.unideliramen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Unideli%2C+2014+E+24th+St%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55404&amp;ll=44.959170,-93.243401" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2014 E 24th St<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55404</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dramen</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tucked away in a massive Asian grocery store in Minneapolis, this little shop is churning out ramen dishes that had Guy hooked. &quot;If they made this in the 50-gallon drum, I&#x27;d be having a hot tub in it,&quot; said Guy of the Dramen, which comes loaded with sliced pork belly, Asian greens, noodles, peanuts and chile flakes. A combination of chicken and pork broths adds to the richness.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Piggin&#x27; Out</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/unideli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.24340,44.95917,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Town Talk Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Town Talk Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55406</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6127221312" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612-722-1312</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.towntalkdiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.towntalkdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Town+Talk+Diner%2C+2707+1%2F2+E+Lake+St.%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55406&amp;ll=44.948252,-93.232739" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2707 1/2 E Lake St.<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55406</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Macaroni and Cheese, Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Take a drive out to Town Talk Diner in Minneapolis, MN, with Guy Fieri, host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, for some creative spins on classic dishes like macaroni and cheese, meatloaf and fried chicken.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners You Sent Me To</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/town-talk-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.23274,44.94825,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Wienery</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Wienery</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55467 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6123335798" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(612) 333-5798</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.wienery.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.wienery.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Wienery%2C+414+Cedar+Ave.+S.%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55467&amp;ll=44.969595,-93.247446" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">414 Cedar Ave. S.<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55467</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Vienna Beef Hot Dogs, Philly Cheesesteaks, Italian Combo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Don&#x27;t expect to find any shredders, slicers or food processors at the Wienery in Minneapolis - chef and owner Pat Starr hand-cuts everything by himself, even the fries. Guy gave his thumbs-up to the Italian Combo, which includes Italian sausage, roast beef, cheese and habanero peppers.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers and Dogs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/the-wienery-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.24745,44.96959,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Herbivorous Butcher</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Herbivorous Butcher</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55413</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6122080992" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612-208-0992</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.theherbivorousbutcher.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.theherbivorousbutcher.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Herbivorous+Butcher%2C+507+1st+Ave+NE%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55413&amp;ll=44.990419,-93.253985" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">507 1st Ave NE<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55413</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey Dill Havarti, Italian Sub</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sibling duo Aubry and Kale Walch are changing the culinary game at their vegan butcher shop, which Guy calls &quot;groundbreaking.&quot; Using a mix of complex flours and plant-based ingredients, they replicate the flavors and textures of cold-cut meats and cheeses. Guy favors the Italian Sub, which is piled high with vegan versions of salami, ham, pastrami and mozzarella, then topped with lettuce, onions and cherry peppers.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Creole, Cold Cuts and Crepes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/the-herbivorous-butcher-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.25398,44.99042,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Smack Shack</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Smack Shack</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55401 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6122597288" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612-259-7288</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.smack-shack.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.smack-shack.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Smack+Shack%2C+603+Washington+Avenue+N%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55401&amp;ll=44.986801,-93.276389" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">603 Washington Avenue N<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Po&#x27; boy, Lobster Mac &#x27;n&#x27; Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">What started as a mobile operation has grown into a bustling brick-and-mortar restaurant. The menu has expanded with the space, as the Smack Shack now offers a slew of seafood favorites (and fun cocktails) in addition to the fresh lobster rolls that started it all. There are options aplenty, including fish boils and lobster-studded mac and cheese (which was featured on Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives). You can also get your seafood in sandwich form, as po&#x27; boys dominate the menu.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Surf and Turf</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/smack-shack-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.27639,44.98680,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Surly Brewing Company</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Surly Brewing Company</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55414 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7639994040" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">763-999-4040</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://surlybrewing.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">surlybrewing.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Surly+Brewing+Company%2C+520+Malcolm+Avenue+SE%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55414&amp;ll=44.973229,-93.209766" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">520 Malcolm Avenue SE<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55414</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulled Pork Platter, Chopped Brisket Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The minds behind Surly Brewing know a thing or two about overcoming obstacles. They actually paved the way for small-production brewers to sell beer onsite, which was illegal in Minnesota before 2011. Once the &quot;Surly bill&quot; became law, Ansari and his team built a 50,000-square-foot hall where visitors can indulge in a cold one paired with classic comfort foods, including the Pulled Pork Platter. Huge slices of smoky pork are served with fried Thai chili Brussels sprouts and buttery cheddar grits.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chew and Brew</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/surly-brewing-company-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.20977,44.97323,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Smack Shack at The 1029 Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Smack Shack at The 1029 Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55413 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6123794322" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(612) 379-4322</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://the1029bar.com/Smack_Shack.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">the1029bar.com/Smack_Shack.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Smack+Shack+at+The+1029+Bar%2C+1029+Marshall+St+NE%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55413&amp;ll=44.998103,-93.268292" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1029 Marshall St NE<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55413</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Slow-Cooked Lamb Sandwich, Lobster Mac &#x27;n&#x27; Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This food truck is parked in a bar so you can order quality food and kick back with a cold one. The slow-cooked lamb sandwich with harissa and saffron aioli and dipped in a savory au jus blew Guy away. Guy also enjoyed the creamy lobster mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese topped with sweet corn and crunchy panko.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Streamlined Sammies<br/>Super Sandwiches</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/smack-shack-at-the-1029-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.26829,44.99810,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Red Wagon Pizza Company</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Red Wagon Pizza Company</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis 55419 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6122597147" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612-259-7147</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.redwagon-mpls.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.redwagon-mpls.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Red+Wagon+Pizza+Company%2C+5416+Penn+Ave+S%2C+Minneapolis+55419&amp;ll=44.904596,-93.308979" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5416 Penn Ave S<br/>Minneapolis 55419</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Red Wagon Pizza, Tortellini</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza has long been a way of life for Chef-Owner Peter Campbell, whose family made pies as a regular pastime. These days, he&#x27;s serving artisan pizzas that have won over fans like the DDD crew. Guy stopped in for the Red Wagon Pizza. This meaty pie is slathered with housemade sauce, then topped with a mix of mozzarella and provolone cheeses, a flurry of banana peppers, and meaty ribbons of soppressata and hearty housemade sausage, which makes for a well-balanced pizza that Guy declared &quot;dynamite.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Pancakes, Potatoes and Pizza<br/>Rockstar Chefs<br/>Sausage, Seafood and Shawarma<br/>Takeout: Home Delivery</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/red-wagon-pizza-company-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.30898,44.90460,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Grinders</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Grinders</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City 64108 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8164725454" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">816-472-5454</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.grinderspizza.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.grinderspizza.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Grinders%2C+417+E+18th+St%2C+Kansas+City+64108&amp;ll=39.091609,-94.578362" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">417 E 18th St<br/>Kansas City 64108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bengal Tiger Pizza, Famous Chili Bomb Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sculptor-turned-pizza-slinger Stretch has brought his creative touch to Grinder&#x27;s. Hand-welded Army helmet lamps hang above the bar, which features a draft-beer tower made from an oxygen tank. As for the pizza menu, Stretch churns out creative pies like the Bengal Tiger, which is slicked with pesto sauce and studded with tandoori chicken, crabmeat and hearts of palm. &quot;Funkalicious,&quot; Guy declared.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Off the Hook Specials<br/>Takeout: Flavortown Comes Home<br/>Triple D Nation: Layered, Stuffed and Stacked<br/>Pizza Party</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mo/kansas-city/grinders-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.57836,39.09161,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nye&#x27;s Polonaise Room</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nye&#x27;s Polonaise Room</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55414 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6123792021" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(612) 379-2021</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.nyespolonaise.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.nyespolonaise.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nye%27s+Polonaise+Room%2C+112+E+Hennepin+Ave%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55414&amp;ll=44.987091,-93.258248" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">112 E Hennepin Ave<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55414</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Prime Rib Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The polka music, Polish party atmosphere and great-tasting food make this establishment a local favorite. Guy thought that the fried potato and cheese pierogi were delicious and he loved the savory and fatty prime rib sandwich. After dinner, don&#x27;t be afraid to break out some of your polka moves.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Time Tested Treasures<br/>Late Night Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/nyes-polonaise-room-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.25825,44.98709,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Modern Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Modern Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55413</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6123789882" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(612) 378-9882</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.moderncafeminneapolis.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.moderncafeminneapolis.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Modern+Cafe%2C+337+13th+Ave+NE%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55413&amp;ll=45.000975,-93.262681" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">337 13th Ave NE<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55413</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Burger, Chicken Wings, Gnocchi, Fish Cakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Jim Grell opened Modern Cafe in 1994, his goal was to make classic diner dishes with a contemporary twist. The menu includes lamb burger with tomato relish, chicken wings with hoisin sauce, gnocchi with oyster mushrooms and fish cakes, which Guy thought were &#x27;&#x27;beyond&#x27;&#x27; tender.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Doin&#x27; Their Own Thing</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/modern-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.26268,45.00097,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Northbound Smokehouse and Brewpub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Northbound Smokehouse and Brewpub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55406 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6122081450" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612-208-1450</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.northboundbrewpub.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.northboundbrewpub.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Northbound+Smokehouse+and+Brewpub%2C+2716+East+38th+St%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55406&amp;ll=44.934278,-93.232480" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2716 East 38th St<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55406</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">18-Hour Porketta</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">To get their pub off the ground, Amy Johnson and Jamie Robinson got creative by offering free beer for life to anyone who invested $1,000. Customers may have signed up for the brews, but they&#x27;re staying for the food, thanks to a menu of mouthwatering smoked dishes like the 18-Hour Porketta. This meaty sandwich features succulent pork and sauteed onions blanketed with a layer of melty Swiss cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Piggin&#x27; Out</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/northbound-smokehouse-and-brewpub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.23248,44.93428,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Marla&#x27;s Caribbean Cuisine</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Marla&#x27;s Caribbean Cuisine</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55407 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6127243088" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(612) 724-3088</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.marlascuisine.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.marlascuisine.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Marla%27s+Caribbean+Cuisine%2C+3761+Bloomington+Ave+S%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55407&amp;ll=44.934254,-93.252121" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3761 Bloomington Ave S<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55407</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dhalpourie, Oxtail with Red Beans</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Marla, a native Trinidadian, is bringing a new kind of spice to the Twin Cities. Guy could not believe that the delicious Dhalpourie, made with curried chickpeas and potatoes, was vegan. The oxtail with red beans and rice had a sweet and savory flavor that Guy could not resist devouring.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big Time Flavor<br/>Global Flavor Faves</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/marlas-caribbean-cuisine-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.25212,44.93425,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Gandhi Mahal Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Gandhi Mahal Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55406 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6127295222" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612-729-5222</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://gandhimahal.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">gandhimahal.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Gandhi+Mahal+Restaurant%2C+3009+27th+Ave+S%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55406&amp;ll=44.947929,-93.232913" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3009 27th Ave S<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55406</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Tikka Masala, Dal with Naan</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef-Owner Ruhel Islam delivers the flavors of India to the diners of Minneapolis at his restaurant. He&#x27;s so dedicated to fresh ingredients that he grows vegetables and herbs in the basement, and collects honey from a beehive on the roof. When Guy stopped by, he tried the buttery Chicken Tikka Masala. &quot;If you don&#x27;t think you like Indian food, let this be your visa,&quot; Guy said of the dish.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Asia, Africa and India</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/gandhi-mahal-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.23291,44.94793,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>George and the Dragon</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">George and the Dragon</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55419 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6122081047" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612-208-1047</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.ganddpub.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.ganddpub.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=George+and+the+Dragon%2C+813+W+50th+St%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55419&amp;ll=44.912150,-93.290439" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">813 W 50th St<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55419</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bacon &amp; Onion Dip, Banh Mi Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">England meets the Philippines at this cozy Minneapolis pub. Head here for &quot;the kind of cooking that happens when fans of British culture mix it up with old family recipes,&quot; as Guy describes it. Fred and Stacy Navarro (who have Irish, French and Filipino ancestries between them) have dreamed up an eclectic menu of mouthwatering eats (we&#x27;re talking bacon and onion dip, a banh mi sandwich and more).</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Finger Lickin&#x27; Food</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/george-and-the-dragon-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.29044,44.91215,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Al&#x27;s Breakfast</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Al&#x27;s Breakfast</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55414 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6123319991" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(612) 331-9991</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Als-Breakfast/92308895353" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Als-Breakfast/92308895353</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Al%27s+Breakfast%2C+413+14th+Ave+SE%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55414&amp;ll=44.981061,-93.235656" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">413 14th Ave SE<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55414</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Corned Beef Hash, French Toast Batter, Jelly Omelet, Jose (Poached Eggs, Salsa, Hash Browns), Pancakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Guy revisits Al&#x27;s Breakfast for the second time, he finds the popular spot is &amp;quot;still packed and still run by the king of the joint.&amp;quot; Regulars often enjoy Jelly Omelets in the 14-stool classic American eatery. Their short-order style hasn&#x27;t changed in 60 years, and we don&#x27;t want it to, either.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">American Cookin&#x27;<br/>Best of Breakfast<br/>Diners, Drive-ins and Dives<br/>You Found Em</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/als-breakfast-restaurant4" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.23566,44.98106,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Prairie Dogs</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Prairie Dogs</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55408</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6122238984" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612-223-8984</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.prairiedogsausage.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.prairiedogsausage.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Prairie+Dogs%2C+610+W+Lake+St%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55408&amp;ll=44.948530,-93.287556" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">610 W Lake St<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55408</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jimmy Two Times Sausage &amp; Beef Combo, Foietine</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fittingly, Chef Craig Johnson&#x27;s first job was slinging hot dogs. He now spends his days creating beyond-basic riffs on sausages as the owner of Prairie Dogs. Johnson delivers a one-two punch of meaty flavor with his Jimmy Two Times creation. He grills housemade Italian sausage in duck fat, then pairs it with jus-drenched slices of Italian beef (also made in-house) on a Vietnamese-style baguette. The sandwich comes smothered with marinara sauce and a giardiniera that Guy declared &quot;the real surprise.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cosmopolitan Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/prairie-dogs-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.28756,44.94853,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Psycho Suzie&#x27;s Motor Lounge</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Psycho Suzie&#x27;s Motor Lounge</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55418 &middot; &#9733; 4.1 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6127889069" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612-788-9069</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.psychosuzis.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.psychosuzis.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Psycho+Suzie%27s+Motor+Lounge%2C+1900+Marshall+St+NE%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55418&amp;ll=45.007492,-93.272389" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1900 Marshall St NE<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55418</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mini Mex Rolls</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">As the name suggests, Psycho Suzi&#x27;s Motor Lounge doesn&#x27;t play by the rules - and that wasn&#x27;t a problem for Guy. The food was right up his alley, with beer-battered asparagus and fried cheese curds (and fried mini wieners and Snickers too). But the fried Mini Mex Rolls? Two words: &amp;quot;crazy tasty.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Viewer&#x27;s Choice</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/psycho-suzies-motor-lounge-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.27239,45.00749,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pizzeria Lola</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pizzeria Lola</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55410 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6124248338" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(612) 424-8338</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pizzerialola.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pizzerialola.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pizzeria+Lola%2C+5557+Xerxes+Ave+S%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55410&amp;ll=44.901803,-93.318459" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5557 Xerxes Ave S<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55410</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">My Sha-Roni!, Lady ZaZa, Sunnyside Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Andrew Zimmern introduced Guy to this pizzeria, where Guy indulged in the Sunnyside pizza despite his aversion to eggs. The My Sha-Roni! captured Guy&#x27;s heart with its pepperoni and Berkshire pork sausage, while the Lady ZaZa with Korean sausage, kimchi and soy chili glaze had &amp;quot;dynamite&amp;quot; flavor.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D All Stars<br/>Best of Pizza</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/pizzeria-lola-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.31846,44.90180,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Yayo Taco</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Yayo Taco</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Las Vegas, NV 89119 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7022620201" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(702) 262-0201</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://yayotaco.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">yayotaco.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Yayo+Taco%2C+4632+S+Maryland+Pkwy%2C+Las+Vegas%2C+NV+89119&amp;ll=36.105026,-115.135948" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4632 S Maryland Pkwy<br/>Las Vegas, NV 89119</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pollo Taco, Shanghai Taco</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Cho Yiu has combined flavors from around the world to create his fusion tacos. The pollo taco with chicken in adobo mole sauce wowed Guy with its richness, depth and complexity. The Shanghai taco with wasabi seared steak and Chinese preserved black bean salsa Guy called &quot;crazy but awesome.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dynamic Dishes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/nv/las-vegas/yayo-taco-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-115.13595,36.10503,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Gordy&#x27;s Hi-Hat</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Gordy&#x27;s Hi-Hat</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cloquet, MN 55720 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2188796125" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">218-879-6125</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.gordys-hihat.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.gordys-hihat.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Gordy%27s+Hi-Hat%2C+415+Sunnyside+Dr%2C+Cloquet%2C+MN+55720&amp;ll=46.733684,-92.467890" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">415 Sunnyside Dr<br/>Cloquet, MN 55720</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Double Cheeseburger, Gordy&#x27;s Fresh Homemade Chili, Onion Rings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Locals eagerly await the reopening of Gordy&#x27;s Hi-Hat every spring, as this seasonal joint slings old-school favorites like a double cheeseburger that&#x27;s built right on the flat top. The patties are seasoned with salt and pepper, grilled and then topped with onions, cheese and pickles. &quot;When you think about the all-American drive-in, that&#x27;s the kind of burger they&#x27;re talking about,&quot; Guy declared.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You Called It<br/>Knockout Burger Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/cloquet/gordys-hi-hat-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.46789,46.73368,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Q fanatic BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Q fanatic BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Champlin, MN 55316 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7633236550" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(763) 323-6550</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.qfanatic.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.qfanatic.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Q+fanatic+BBQ%2C+180+Miller+Rd%2C+Champlin%2C+MN+55316&amp;ll=45.187851,-93.395102" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">180 Miller Rd<br/>Champlin, MN 55316</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Espresso BBQ Sauce</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Q Fanatic BBQ boasts a long line of delicious, smoky briskets, but it also has eight homemade sauces, four being an ode to Kansas City-style barbecue. The most popular sauce will also give you a caffeine boost, as Guy discovered the Espresso BBQ sauce mixes in an unusually large shot of espresso.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Po&#x27; Boys, Pasta And Pork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/champlin/q-fanatic-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.39510,45.18785,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Purple Carrot</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Purple Carrot</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Okemos, MI 48864</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.thepurplecarrottruck.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thepurplecarrottruck.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Purple+Carrot%2C+4480+S+Hagadorn+Rd%2C+Okemos%2C+MI+48864&amp;ll=42.711156,-84.461821" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4480 S Hagadorn Rd<br/>Okemos, MI 48864</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Seafood and Savory</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/restaurants-in-okemos/the-purple-carrot-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.46182,42.71116,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Joe&#x27;s Gizzard City</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Joe&#x27;s Gizzard City</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Potterville, MI 48876 &middot; &#9733; 2.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5176452120" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(517) 645-2120</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.gizzardcity.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.gizzardcity.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Joe%27s+Gizzard+City%2C+120+W+Main+St%2C+Potterville%2C+MI+48876&amp;ll=42.629401,-84.742716" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">120 W Main St<br/>Potterville, MI 48876</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The &quot;DDD&quot; Burger, Frinkies, Gizzards</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you want to eat at Joe&#x27;s Gizzard City, you&#x27;ll get a quick lesson in gizzards (best described as a chicken&#x27;s second stomach). Guy was a fast learner and dove right into his basket of tender fried gizzards. But Joe&#x27;s doesn&#x27;t stop there. They&#x27;re frying Twinkies, too, or, as they call them, Frinkies.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">One of a Kind</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/potterville/joes-gizzard-city-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.74272,42.62940,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Cosmos</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Cosmos</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lansing, MI 48906 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://thecosmoslansing.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">thecosmoslansing.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Cosmos%2C+611+E+Grand+River+Ave%2C+Lansing%2C+MI+48906&amp;ll=42.747579,-84.543977" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">611 E Grand River Ave<br/>Lansing, MI 48906</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Trust Us, The Spaceball</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For otherworldly pizza with the freshest mozzarella you can get head to Cosmos. Owner Sam Short was inspired by the pizza parlor he visited with his father as a kid. He infused the casual, fun atmosphere with some seriously delicious pies. Try any of their creative offerings or opt for the &quot;Trust Us&quot; and let them bring out a surprise offering that will wow you.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza, Pork and Peru</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/lansing/the-cosmos-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.54398,42.74758,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Eastside Fish Fry &amp; Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Eastside Fish Fry &amp; Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lansing, MI 48912 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5179935988" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">517-993-5988</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://eastsidefishfry.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">eastsidefishfry.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Eastside+Fish+Fry+%26+Grill%2C+417+East+Kalamazoo+St%2C+Lansing%2C+MI+48912&amp;ll=42.729728,-84.543584" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">417 East Kalamazoo St<br/>Lansing, MI 48912</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Wings, Pig Skins, Fried Gizzards</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eastside Fish Fry &amp; Grill is known for its amazing chicken wings, prepared with a 48-hour dry rub marinade and fried to order. The adventurous can also findlocal delicacies like crispy fried gizzards and pig skins, aka deep-fried bacon strips.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Pied to Fried</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/lansing/eastside-fish-fry-and-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.54358,42.72973,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Capital City BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Capital City BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lansing 48915 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5177211500" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(517) 721-1500</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/capitalcitybbq/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/capitalcitybbq</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Capital+City+BBQ%2C+1026+W.+Saginaw+St%2C+Lansing+48915&amp;ll=42.741190,-84.566970" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1026 W. Saginaw St<br/>Lansing 48915</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brisket Banh Mi, Pork and Shrimp Spring Roll</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">In an odd location, inside of a cellular store, Chef and Owner Linh Lee and Co-Owner Regan Louchart are fusing their two cultures together for a truly unique dining experience. The Brisket Bahn Mi is a combination of meltingly tender smoked brisket and the classic banh mi toppings like pickled daikon, cucumber and cilantro.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Passport of Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/lansing/capital-city-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.56697,42.74119,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Meat Southern B.B.Q. and Carnivore Cuisine</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Meat Southern B.B.Q. and Carnivore Cuisine</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lansing, MI 48906 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5175804400" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">517-580-4400</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://meatbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">meatbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Meat+Southern+B.B.Q.+and+Carnivore+Cuisine%2C+1224+Turner+St%2C+Lansing%2C+MI+48906&amp;ll=42.748111,-84.549256" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1224 Turner St<br/>Lansing, MI 48906</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Belly Reuben, Pickle Fries, Smoked Chicken Wings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy steps into a rock and roll fantasy straight out of Flavortown at this Southern-style barbeque joint. Standouts include the house-smoked pork belly pastrami and pickle fries that are &quot;another level of ridiculous.&quot; Don&#x27;t miss the smoked wings with the coffee-kissed Black Magic sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ocean Coasts and Great Lakes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/lansing/meat-southern-bbq-and-carnivore-cuisine-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.54926,42.74811,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Clarkston Union Bar &amp; Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Clarkston Union Bar &amp; Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Village of Clarkston, MI 48346 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2486206100" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(248) 620-6100</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://clarkstonunion.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">clarkstonunion.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Clarkston+Union+Bar+%26+Kitchen%2C+54+S+Main+St%2C+Village+of+Clarkston%2C+MI+48346&amp;ll=42.734121,-83.419060" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">54 S Main St<br/>Village of Clarkston, MI 48346</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mac &amp; Cheese, Beer</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owner Curt Catallo has transformed an old church into a comfort food diner. Kid Rock and Guy liked the deliciously creamy mac and cheese, calling it the &amp;quot;most macked mac &amp;amp; cheese.&amp;quot; Locals also enjoy coming here for the great atmosphere and a glass of cold beer.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kid Rock&#x27;s Detroit Tour<br/>Wildest Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/village-of-clarkston/clarkston-union-bar-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-83.41906,42.73412,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rosie&#x27;s Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rosie&#x27;s Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Rockford, MI 49341</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6168663663" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">616-866-3663</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rosiesdiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rosiesdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rosie%27s+Diner%2C+4500+14+Mile+Rd.%2C+Rockford%2C+MI+49341&amp;ll=43.176105,-85.558720" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4500 14 Mile Rd.<br/>Rockford, MI 49341</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cobblestone French Toast, Burgers, Rosie&#x27;s Classic Breakfast, Southern Bounty</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy Fieri, host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, satisfies his craving for American cookin&#x27; at Rosie&#x27;s Diner in Rockford, MI, which is located in the heart of their local community.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">American Cookin&#x27;<br/>Diners, Drive-ins and Dives</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/rockford/rosies-diner-restaurant2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-85.55872,43.17610,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Union Woodshop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Union Woodshop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Clarkston, MI 48346 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2486255660" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(248) 625-5660</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://unionwoodshop.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">unionwoodshop.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Union+Woodshop%2C+18+S+Main+St%2C+Clarkston%2C+MI+48346&amp;ll=42.735433,-83.418863" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">18 S Main St<br/>Clarkston, MI 48346</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Porker (Ground Pork Patty, Maple Bacon and Hotlink Sandwich), Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All the locals know to come to Union Woodshop for great barbecue, especially Kid Rock. The unctuous flavor from The Porker, which has a house-ground pork patty, housemade Michigan maple bacon and housemade hotlinks, wowed Guy. Diners also enjoy the pizza kitchen and whiskey bar.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kid Rock&#x27;s Detroit Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/clarkston/union-woodshop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-83.41886,42.73543,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Broadway Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Broadway Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore, MD 21224 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4106315666" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">410-631-5666</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.broadwaydiner1.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.broadwaydiner1.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Broadway+Diner%2C+6501+Eastern+Ave%2C+Baltimore%2C+MD+21224&amp;ll=39.287494,-76.536548" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6501 Eastern Ave<br/>Baltimore, MD 21224</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Broadway Festival, Hungarian Goulash, Potato Crusted Salmon, Shrimp Creole</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Broadway Diner in Baltimore is a family-owned restaurant known for delicious food and huge portions. In fact, Guy called the diner&#x27;s Broadway Festival &#x27;&#x27;a seafood buffet for 90.&#x27;&#x27; Guy also thought that the Potato Crust Salmon was &#x27;&#x27;one of the coolest things I&#x27;ve ever seen on Triple D.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners You Sent Me To</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/broadway-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.53655,39.28749,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Boulevard Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Boulevard Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Dundalk, MD 21222 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4102858660" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(410) 285-8660</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://boulevarddiner.com/index.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">boulevarddiner.com/index.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Boulevard+Diner%2C+1660+Merritt+Blvd%2C+Dundalk%2C+MD+21222&amp;ll=39.270833,-76.503523" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1660 Merritt Blvd<br/>Dundalk, MD 21222</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Stuffed Grape Leaves, Sour Beef and Dumplings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fueled by tradition and strong family ties, this Greek diner is serving old-school menu items as well as some crazy new ones. The stuffed grape leaves, from a family recipe, were so good that Guy wanted to take some home. The unique German-Asian fusion sour beef and dumplings taste great too!</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Amazing Appetizers<br/>Multitaskers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/dundalk/boulevard-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.50352,39.27083,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The General Store</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The General Store</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Silver Spring, MD 20910</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3015628787" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">301-562-8787</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/silver-spring/the-general-store-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/silver-spring/the-general-store-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+General+Store%2C+6+Post+Office+Road%2C+Silver+Spring%2C+MD+20910&amp;ll=39.015222,-77.055591" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6 Post Office Road<br/>Silver Spring, MD 20910</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Corndogs, Chicken &#x27;n Waffles, The General Store Chili</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Guy Fieri, discovers The General Store in Silver Spring, MD, a 19th century post office turned restaurant cranking out American standards like corndogs and chicken &#x27;n waffles.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Timeless</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/silver-spring/the-general-store-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-77.05559,39.01522,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>A1 Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">A1 Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Gardiner, ME 04345 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2075824804" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">207-582-4804</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/A1Diner" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/A1Diner</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=A1+Diner%2C+3+Bridge+St%2C+Gardiner%2C+ME+04345&amp;ll=44.230070,-69.774553" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3 Bridge St<br/>Gardiner, ME 04345</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Greek Stuffed Flank Steak Roulade, Duck with Mojito Glaze, Pancakes, Omelet, Burgers, Soup, Biscuits</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This original Worcester Diner car #790 serves everything from burgers to Greek stuffed flank steak roulade. The ingredients here are all fresh and prepared by hand. Guy was impressed by the Mojito-glazed duck and recommends the potato hash, which they&#x27;ve been frying up for over 50 years.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Local Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/me/gardiner/a1-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-69.77455,44.23007,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Maine Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Maine Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wells, ME 04090 &middot; &#9733; 3.1 (12 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2076464441" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(207) 646-4441</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mainediner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mainediner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Maine+Diner%2C+2265+Post+Rd%2C+Wells%2C+ME+04090&amp;ll=43.341794,-70.563127" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2265 Post Rd<br/>Wells, ME 04090</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Seafood Chowder, Grandmother&#x27;s Lobster Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s visit to the Maine Diner had him sampling &quot;Maine in a bowl.&quot; The signature Lobster Pie contains fresh Maine lobster meat with a delicious, secret stuffing baked in a casserole dish. But for more than just a pie, try &quot;The Triple D,&quot; which comes with chowder, lobster pie and a codfish cake.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Northeast Feast<br/>Old Time Attitude</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/me/wells/maine-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.56313,43.34179,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bob&#x27;s Clam Hut</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bob&#x27;s Clam Hut</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kittery, ME 03904 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (16 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2074394233" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">207-439-4233</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bobsclamhut.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bobsclamhut.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bob%27s+Clam+Hut%2C+315+US+Rte+1%2C+Kittery%2C+ME+03904&amp;ll=43.112391,-70.733969" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">315 US Rte 1<br/>Kittery, ME 03904</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bob&#x27;s Traditional Fried Clams, Lillian Clams (with Egg Wash), Clam Roll, Lobster Stew</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If Guy was &amp;quot;jammin&#x27; like you&#x27;re clammin&#x27;&amp;quot; at Bob&#x27;s Clam Hut, you might be too. They&#x27;ve been doing clam dinners the same way here since the &#x27;50s. Get an order of Bob&#x27;s clams, in which whole belly clams are dredged in a corn-and-white-flour blend, or try Lillian&#x27;s version, in which the clams get a milk-and-egg wash before frying.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tried and True</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/me/kittery/bobs-clam-hut-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.73397,43.11239,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Becky&#x27;s Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Becky&#x27;s Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, ME 04101 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2077737070" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(207) 773-7070</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.beckysdiner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.beckysdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Becky%27s+Diner%2C+390+Commercial+St%2C+Portland%2C+ME+04101&amp;ll=43.649658,-70.254722" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">390 Commercial St<br/>Portland, ME 04101</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Stuffed Lobster, Lobster Rolls, Fried Clams, Blueberry Cake</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Every November, Becky&#x27;s Diner pairs Thanksgiving dinner with the local catch of the day, going &quot;outside of the box and not stuffing turkeys,&quot; but lobsters instead. Not visiting for the holiday? Any day of the year, the seaside spot offers family favorites like lobster rolls and fried clams.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Triple D Thanksgiving</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/me/portland/beckys-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.25472,43.64966,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>La. Pines Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">La. Pines Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Slidell, LA 70458 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9856416196" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(985) 641-6196</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.lapinescafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.lapinescafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=La.+Pines+Cafe%2C+1061+Robert+Rd%2C+Slidell%2C+LA+70458&amp;ll=30.289281,-89.771087" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1061 Robert Rd<br/>Slidell, LA 70458</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Prime Rib Po&#x27; Boy, Cajun Corn Pudding, Rib Plate</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This cafe is the local hangout where Chef Jim Vandenburg prepares good old Louisiana comfort food. When Guy bit into the smoked prime rib po&#x27; boy drenched in au jus and smothered with horseradish, &amp;quot;Angels were singing.&amp;quot; Faithful customers applaud the Cajun corn pudding and smoked rib plate too.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Signature Sandwiches</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/slidell/la-pines-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-89.77109,30.28928,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Rivershack Tavern</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Rivershack Tavern</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Jefferson, LA 70121 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5048344938" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">504-834-4938</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://rivershacktavern.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">rivershacktavern.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Rivershack+Tavern%2C+3449+River+Rd.%2C+Jefferson%2C+LA+70121&amp;ll=29.958232,-90.160677" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3449 River Rd.<br/>Jefferson, LA 70121</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rabbit, Sherried Turtle Soup, Po&#x27; Boy</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Rivershack Tavern draws a loyal local crowd. While their classically trained chef Mike Baskind does all the basics, like burgers and po&#x27; boys, he is known for daily specials including Turtle Soup, Rabbit With Spaetzle and more deliciously creative dishes you wouldn&#x27;t expect in the average bar.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Where the Locals Go</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/jefferson/the-rivershack-tavern-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.16068,29.95823,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Parkside Market</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Parkside Market</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Falmouth, MA 02540</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7747632066" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">774-763-2066</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://parksidemarket.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">parksidemarket.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Parkside+Market%2C+281+Main+St%2C+Falmouth%2C+MA+02540&amp;ll=41.551940,-70.614453" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">281 Main St<br/>Falmouth, MA 02540</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cab Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Want to fuel up for the day with a hearty morning feast? Follow Guy&#x27;s lead and head to this spot that&#x27;s serving up filling breakfast dishes made from fresh, local ingredients. Breakfast is served all day, but come lunchtime, you can also get standout sandwiches like the Cab, which comes piled with slice upon slice of chicken breast topped with melted cheese, bacon and avocado.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">By Hand and By Fork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/falmouth/parkside-market-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.61445,41.55194,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Charlie&#x27;s Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Charlie&#x27;s Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Spencer, MA 01562 &middot; &#9733; 2.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5088854033" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(508) 885-4033</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.charliesdiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.charliesdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Charlie%27s+Diner%2C+5+Meadow+Rd%2C+Spencer%2C+MA+01562&amp;ll=42.237964,-72.009176" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5 Meadow Rd<br/>Spencer, MA 01562</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bourbon-Marinated Steak Tips, Corned-Beef Hash</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy Fieri, host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, uncovers Charlie&#x27;s Diner in Spencer, MA, a family-owned restaurant, where they have been cranking out classic American plates for decades.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Owned</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/spencer/charlies-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-72.00918,42.23796,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pickle Jar Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pickle Jar Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Falmouth, MA 02540 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5085406760" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">508-540-6760</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.picklejarkitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.picklejarkitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pickle+Jar+Kitchen%2C+170+Main+St%2C+Falmouth%2C+MA+02540&amp;ll=41.552653,-70.617210" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">170 Main St<br/>Falmouth, MA 02540</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Open Faced BBQ Boneless Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Not just the name of this restaurant is unusual -- its menu is chock-full of dishes totally unexpected in a beach town like Cape Cod. Instead of fried clams, you&#x27;ll find dishes like pulled pork with smoky cheddar sauce on a scallion scone. &quot;It&#x27;s different, it&#x27;s refreshing, it&#x27;s creative,&quot; Guy said when he stopped in on Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Name That Kitchen</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/falmouth/pickle-jar-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.61721,41.55265,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Shuckers World Famous Raw Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Shuckers World Famous Raw Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Woods Hole, MA 02543</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5085403850" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">508-540-3850</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.woodshole.com/shuckers/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.woodshole.com/shuckers</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Shuckers+World+Famous+Raw+Bar%2C+91+Water+St%2C+Woods+Hole%2C+MA+02543&amp;ll=41.524747,-70.670869" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">91 Water St<br/>Woods Hole, MA 02543</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Baked Stuffed Scrod</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tucked away by the spot where the ferry leaves for Martha&#x27;s Vineyard, this harbor hideaway offers outdoor dining and fresh seafood dishes like the Baked Stuffed Scrod. For this dish, cod that&#x27;s been plucked straight from the bay is stuffed with a rich filling of lobster tail meat, cracker crumbs and melted butter. &quot;It tastes bright and fresh and like the sea,&quot; Guy enthused about the dish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Finger Lickin&#x27; Food</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/woods-hole/shuckers-world-famous-raw-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.67087,41.52475,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dana&#x27;s Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dana&#x27;s Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Falmouth, MA 02540</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5085407900" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">508-540-7900</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.danas-kitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.danas-kitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dana%27s+Kitchen%2C+881+Palmer+Ave%2C+Falmouth%2C+MA+02540&amp;ll=41.581228,-70.628029" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">881 Palmer Ave<br/>Falmouth, MA 02540</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Portuguese Kale Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This quaint Cape Cod cafe is open year-round, serving up pastries, sandwiches and soups that made a fan out of Guy. &quot;It&#x27;s just what I wanted when I pulled up - little cottage tucked away in the woods ... grabbed some sausage and kale soup,&quot; Guy declared. A menu favorite, the Portuguese kale soup combines homemade chicken stock with linguica sausage, kale, kidney beans, russets and plenty of hot sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Name That Kitchen</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/falmouth/danas-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.62803,41.58123,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cafe Polonia</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cafe Polonia</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boston, MA 02127 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6172690110" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 269-0110</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cafepolonia.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cafepolonia.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cafe+Polonia%2C+611+Dorchester+Ave%2C+Boston%2C+MA+02127&amp;ll=42.328810,-71.057136" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">611 Dorchester Ave<br/>Boston, MA 02127</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meat Pierogi, Knight&#x27;s Cutlet</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cafe Polonia is a real-deal Polish joint where everything is cooked the proper way. They serve all the traditional Polish dishes, like their handmade meat pierogi that Guy says will change the way you think about these bites. Also have a taste of the Knight&#x27;s Cutlet, which is a stuffed pork loin.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roadtrippin&#x27; in Beantown</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/boston/cafe-polonia" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.05714,42.32881,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Casa Razdora</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Casa Razdora</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boston, MA 02109 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6173386700" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">617-338-6700</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://casarazdora.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">casarazdora.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Casa+Razdora%2C+115+Water+St%2C+Boston%2C+MA+02109&amp;ll=42.358028,-71.054649" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">115 Water St<br/>Boston, MA 02109</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nestled in the financial district of Boston, Casa Razdora is where locals go for real-deal Italian food. Guy recommends the porcini cascioni, which has an &quot;outrageous&quot; filling with sausage, Gorgonzola, button mushrooms and porcini mushrooms. Another must-try is the rosettes, a ham-and-cheese pasta. &amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Worldwide Flavorfest<br/>Incredible Italian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/boston/casa-razdora" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.05465,42.35803,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Yankee Lobster Company</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Yankee Lobster Company</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boston, MA 02210 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6173459799" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 345-9799</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.yankeelobstercompany.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.yankeelobstercompany.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Yankee+Lobster+Company%2C+300+Northern+Ave%2C+Boston%2C+MA+02210&amp;ll=42.348006,-71.035812" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">300 Northern Ave<br/>Boston, MA 02210</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cod Cakes, Lobster Mac &#x27;n&#x27; Cheese, Crab</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The lobster here is extra fresh especially because the water for the aquariums is pumped directly from the ocean. The lobster mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese Guy called &quot;ridiculous,&quot; while the cod cakes tasted like the &quot;perfect storm.&quot; Locals like the crab and other seafood-inspired dishes as well.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Stacked Up<br/>Turn On Traditional</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/boston/yankee-lobster-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.03581,42.34801,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sam LaGrassa&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sam LaGrassa&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boston, MA 02108 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6173576861" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 357-6861</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.samlagrassas.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.samlagrassas.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sam+LaGrassa%27s%2C+44+Province+St%2C+Boston%2C+MA+02108&amp;ll=42.356825,-71.060035" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">44 Province St<br/>Boston, MA 02108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Clam Chowder, Chipotle Pastrami Sandwiches</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Locals claim they&#x27;re serving the world&#x27;s best sandwiches here, and they may not be lying. Try their best-seller, the Chipotle Pastrami topped with coleslaw and pressed on a double-faced grill, or the &amp;quot;real-deal-style New England Clam Chowder&amp;quot; made with fresh clams.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Blast From the Past</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/boston/sam-lagrassas-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.06003,42.35683,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Saus</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Saus</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boston 02108</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6172488835" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 248-8835</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.sausboston.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sausboston.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Saus%2C+33+Union+St%2C+Boston+02108&amp;ll=42.345217,-71.148792" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">33 Union St<br/>Boston 02108</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sloppy Jacques, Chicken Pocket</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Saus translates as &quot;sauce&quot; in Dutch, and that&#x27;s exactly what this Dutch-Greek joint is all about - condiments. Pick and choose from 20 sauces. Some standout dishes include the lemongrass chicken pocket with peanut sauce and what Guy calls the &quot;over-the-top&quot; Sloppy Jacques.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Seriously Saucy</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/boston/saus" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.14879,42.34522,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rino&#x27;s Place</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rino&#x27;s Place</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boston 02128 &middot; &#9733; 4.9 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6175677412" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 567-7412</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rinosplace.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rinosplace.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rino%27s+Place%2C+258+Saratoga+St%2C+Boston+02128&amp;ll=42.378294,-71.032076" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">258 Saratoga St<br/>Boston 02128</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Shrimp with Lemon Liquor, Rino&#x27;s Special, Lobster Ravioli</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Rino&#x27;s Place, Guy claims they&#x27;re following all the rules and offering &quot;authentic Italian dishes just like they do in Italy,&quot; with one addition: ridiculously large portions. You&#x27;ll taste the passion for the food in dishes like Shrimp With Lemon Liquor, Rino&#x27;s Special and the Lobster Ravioli.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Made to Order<br/>Amazing Italian<br/>Takeout: Dinner and Dessert That Delivers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/boston/rinos-place-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.03208,42.37829,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pauli&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pauli&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boston, MA 02113</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://paulisnorthend.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">paulisnorthend.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pauli%27s%2C+65+Salem+Street%2C+Boston%2C+MA+02113&amp;ll=42.363260,-71.055906" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">65 Salem Street<br/>Boston, MA 02113</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fat Felix, U.S.S. Lobstitution</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you&#x27;re craving a true New England experience, this is the restaurant to hit. Bring a group of friends and split the U.S.S. Lobstitution, the biggest lobster roll in Boston: 28 ounces of New England fresh lobster meat served on a grilled and buttered baguette-sized roll. Guy was blown away by how incredibly fresh it tasted: &quot;That&#x27;s probably the most honest lobster roll I&#x27;ve ever tried.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s All-Star Guests</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/boston/paulis-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.05591,42.36326,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mike&#x27;s City Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mike&#x27;s City Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boston, MA 02118 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6172679393" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">617-267-9393</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mikescitydiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mikescitydiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mike%27s+City+Diner%2C+1714+Washington+St%2C+Boston%2C+MA+02118&amp;ll=42.336922,-71.076025" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1714 Washington St<br/>Boston, MA 02118</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Corned Beef Hash, Stuffing, Mike&#x27;s Clam Chowder, Turkey Dinner, The Pilgrim Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This spot is a Boston tradition, serving cops, construction workers and even Bill Clinton. Try The Pilgrim Sandwich, which stars a Thanksgiving feast on a massive roll. This beauty comes layered with homemade cranberry sauce, fresh-roasted turkey and savory stuffing topped with herbaceous gravy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ultimate Turkey Fest<br/>Triple D Nation: Trottin&#x27; Out the Turkey<br/>Takeout: Tastier at Home<br/>Talkin&#x27; Turkey</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/boston/mikes-city-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.07603,42.33692,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Boston Burger</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Boston Burger</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boston 02215 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8572334560" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">857-233-4560</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.bostonburgercompany.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bostonburgercompany.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Boston+Burger%2C+1100+Boylston+St.%2C+Boston+02215&amp;ll=42.346809,-71.088462" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1100 Boylston St.<br/>Boston 02215</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mac Attack, Killer Bee, Pilgrim</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this burger stronghold, Chef Paul Malvone is grilling fresh handmade burgers 28 different ways. The Mac Attack, Guy&#x27;s favorite, is piled with homemade mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese, bacon and a fresh 8 ounce patty. Locals love the Killer Bee with a stack of onion rings and the Pilgrim with cranberry mayo.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Noodles and Quahogs<br/>Takeout: Worldwide Delivery<br/>Top 10 Burgers<br/>Triple D Nation: From Near to Far<br/>Knockout Burger Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/boston/boston-burger-company-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.08846,42.34681,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blunch</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blunch</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boston, MA 02118 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6172478100" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 247-8100</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.eatblunch.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.eatblunch.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blunch%2C+59+E+Springfield+St%2C+Boston%2C+MA+02118&amp;ll=42.335426,-71.074788" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">59 E Springfield St<br/>Boston, MA 02118</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Bird, The Provencal</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy swings by Blunch to sample the gourmet sandwiches that have made it a local favorite. Follow Guy&#x27;s lead and devour The Bird, whose seasoned chicken breast is accompanied by mozzarella, roasted tomatoes, artichoke aioli and greens nestled on a baguette. For a vegetarian option, try The Provencal.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Stuffed and Twisted</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/boston/blunch" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.07479,42.33543,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>R&amp;R Taqueria</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">R&amp;R Taqueria</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Elkridge, MD 21075 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4107990001" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(410) 799-0001</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rrtaqueria.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rrtaqueria.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=R%26R+Taqueria%2C+7894+Washington+Blvd%2C+Elkridge%2C+MD+21075&amp;ll=39.172570,-76.784777" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7894 Washington Blvd<br/>Elkridge, MD 21075</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Taco Enchiladas, Tacos Al Pastor</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hidden behind a gas station is a small hole in the wall where Chef Rodrigo Albarran-Torres is using his mother&#x27;s recipes to cook up some authentic Mexican food. Guy and Joe Theismann, former NFL quarterback, devoured the lamb taco enchiladas and tacos al pastor, praising the balance of flavors.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Time Tested Treasures<br/>Wildest Joints<br/>Triple D Nation: Layered, Stuffed and Stacked</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/elkridge/rr-taqueria-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.78478,39.17257,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Krazy Jim&#x27;s Blimpy Burger</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Krazy Jim&#x27;s Blimpy Burger</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ann Arbor, MI 48104 &middot; &#9733; 2.5 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7346634590" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">734-663-4590</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.blimpyburger.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.blimpyburger.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Krazy+Jim%27s+Blimpy+Burger%2C+304+S+Ashley+St%2C+Ann+Arbor%2C+MI+48104&amp;ll=42.274541,-83.744342" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">304 S Ashley St<br/>Ann Arbor, MI 48104</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Onion Rings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The counter at Krazy Jim&#x27;s is no joke. To savor the fresh-ground burgers, you&#x27;d best order correctly: first the size, then the bun and toppings, and finally the cheese. &quot;Look at the festival of funk,&quot; Guy said of his burger piled with onions, peppers, bacon, salami and mushroom. Dress up your double, triple, quad or quint with a side of crunchy onion rings and buckle up - this is the real deal.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Rings and Fries<br/>Big Bites<br/>Knockout Burger Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/ann-arbor/krazy-jims-blimpy-burger-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-83.74434,42.27454,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Polish Village Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Polish Village Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hamtramck 48212 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3138745726" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(313) 874-5726</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.polishvillage.cafe/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.polishvillage.cafe</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Polish+Village+Cafe%2C+2990+Yemans+St%2C+Hamtramck+48212&amp;ll=42.398103,-83.056651" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2990 Yemans St<br/>Hamtramck 48212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dill Pickle Soup, Hungarian Pancake</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you can&#x27;t make it to &quot;the old country,&quot; Guy recommends stopping by the Polish Village Cafe. The Hungarian pancakes are fried and topped with a goulash made with pork butt. Guy loved the crunch from the pancakes and the &quot;megatender&quot; meat. Feeling adventurous? Try the tangy dill pickle soup.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old to New</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/hamtramck/polish-village-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-83.05665,42.39810,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Michigan Brewing Co.</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Michigan Brewing Co.</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Webberville, MI 48892</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5175213600" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(517) 521-3600</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/webberville/michigan-brewing-co-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/webberville/michigan-brewing-co-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Michigan+Brewing+Co.%2C+1093+Highview+Dr%2C+Webberville%2C+MI+48892&amp;ll=42.661602,-84.194654" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1093 Highview Dr<br/>Webberville, MI 48892</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Kid Rock takes Guy Fieri on a thirst-quenching tour of Michigan Brewing Co. in Webberville, MI.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kid Rock&#x27;s Detroit Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/webberville/michigan-brewing-co-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.19465,42.66160,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Fly Trap</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Fly Trap</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ferndale, MI 48220 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2483995150" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(248) 399-5150</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.theflytrapferndale.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.theflytrapferndale.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Fly+Trap%2C+22950+Woodward+Ave%2C+Ferndale%2C+MI+48220&amp;ll=42.462204,-83.135149" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">22950 Woodward Ave<br/>Ferndale, MI 48220</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Vietnamese Pho Bowls, Thai-Style Peanut Chicken, Homemade Salmon Burger, Gingerbread Waffles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Here&#x27;s a first - Triple D meets tofu (awesome!). The Fly Trap &quot;finer diner&quot; keeps it classic with their gingerbread waffles, but isn&#x27;t afraid to travel to the Far East. Trade your greasy spoon for chopsticks and get down with their Asian-inspired tofu fried rice and the fattest pho bowl in town.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Off the Hook Specials</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/ferndale/the-fly-trap-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-83.13515,42.46220,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Supino Pizzeria</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Supino Pizzeria</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Detroit, MI 48207 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3135677879" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(313) 567-7879</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.supinopizza.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.supinopizza.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Supino+Pizzeria%2C+2457+Russell+St%2C+Detroit%2C+MI+48207&amp;ll=42.345385,-83.040155" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2457 Russell St<br/>Detroit, MI 48207</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">City Wing Thing Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A trip to Italy inspired Chef Dave Mancini to open his own pizzeria. The &amp;quot;light and crispy&amp;quot; City Wing Thing pizza topped with smoked turkey, cherry peppers, smoked Gouda, mozzarella and roasted garlic was Guy&#x27;s favorite. If you&#x27;re feeling creative, try inventing your own topping combination.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza, Pancakes and Pork<br/>Ultimate Turkey Fest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/detroit/supino-pizzeria-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-83.04015,42.34539,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Traffic Jam &amp; Snug</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Traffic Jam &amp; Snug</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Detroit, MI 48201 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3138319470" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(313) 831-9470</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.trafficjamdetroit.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.trafficjamdetroit.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Traffic+Jam+%26+Snug%2C+511+W+Canfield+St%2C+Detroit%2C+MI+48201&amp;ll=42.350958,-83.066088" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">511 W Canfield St<br/>Detroit, MI 48201</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Loin Kamatsu Salad, Braised-Beef Panini</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Almost everything at this husband and wife-run restaurant is &amp;quot;so local, it comes from the same address.&amp;quot; The hot-sauce jelly beans in the pork loin kamatsu salad provide the dish with a good amount of heat, according to Guy. Locals also enjoy the huge braised-beef panini made with fresh baked bread.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Seafood &amp; Sammies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mi/detroit/traffic-jam-snug-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-83.06609,42.35096,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Patti&#x27;s Pierogis</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Patti&#x27;s Pierogis</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fall River, MA 02724 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5086794001" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">508-679-4001</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://pattispierogis.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">pattispierogis.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Patti%27s+Pierogis%2C+1019+S+Main+St%2C+Fall+River%2C+MA+02724&amp;ll=41.690788,-71.166015" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1019 S Main St<br/>Fall River, MA 02724</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cabbage and Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">What is the Polish version of a ravioli called? A pierogi, of course! And as the name suggests, that&#x27;s what this place is all about. There&#x27;s a rotating menu of pierogis, with more than 103 varieties in owner Patti Geary&#x27;s repertoire. Guy couldn&#x27;t pass up the chance to tuck into the most-popular option, the cabbage and pork pierogi. &quot;I&#x27;m in pierogi paradise,&quot; Guy declared after biting into the buttery dumpling stuffed with a well-seasoned mixture of onions, ground pork, sauerkraut and cabbage.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">World Class Flavor<br/>East Coast Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/fall-river/pattis-pierogis-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.16601,41.69079,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Surrey&#x27;s Cafe &amp; Juice Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Surrey&#x27;s Cafe &amp; Juice Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70130 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5045243828" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(504) 524-3828</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.surreysnola.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.surreysnola.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Surrey%27s+Cafe+%26+Juice+Bar%2C+1418+Magazine+St%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70130&amp;ll=29.935856,-90.071717" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1418 Magazine St<br/>New Orleans, LA 70130</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Handmade Bagels, Fresh Juice</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy made his first bagel thanks to Surrey&#x27;s Cafe &amp; Juice Bar. All the bagels at Surrey&#x27;s are handmade and go great with handmade lox or one of Surrey&#x27;s fresh-squeezed juices. But they&#x27;ve got the New Orleans classics too. How about boudin hash packed with savory andouille?</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">What&#x27;s For Breakfast</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/surreys-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.07172,29.93586,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sammy&#x27;s Food Service &amp; Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sammy&#x27;s Food Service &amp; Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70122</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5049470675" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(504) 947-0675</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sammysfood.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sammysfood.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sammy%27s+Food+Service+%26+Deli%2C+3000+Elysian+Fields%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70122&amp;ll=29.988929,-90.058896" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3000 Elysian Fields<br/>New Orleans, LA 70122</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey Dinner (with Oyster Gravy Stuffing), Pumpkin Bread Pudding</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Looking for a killer Thanksgiving meal, Mardi Gras style? This former butcher shop turned sandwich shop may be the stop you&#x27;ve been seeking. Get a taste of New Orleans with every bite of your turkey loaded with oyster stuffing, but don&#x27;t leave before trying the pumpkin bread pudding.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ultimate Turkey Fest<br/>Triple D Nation: Trottin&#x27; Out the Turkey<br/>A Triple D Thanksgiving</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/sammys-food-service-deli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.05890,29.98893,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Joey K&#x27;s Restaurant &amp; Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Joey K&#x27;s Restaurant &amp; Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70115 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5048910997" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">504-891-0997</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.joeyksrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.joeyksrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Joey+K%27s+Restaurant+%26+Bar%2C+3001+Magazine+Street%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70115&amp;ll=29.925116,-90.084842" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3001 Magazine Street<br/>New Orleans, LA 70115</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jambalaya, Oyster Po&#x27; Boy, Shrimp Magazine</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A family-owned eatery located in a charming century-old building, Joey K&#x27;s is the place to go for &amp;quot;a real taste of Louisiana soul food.&amp;quot; Many items on the menu, like the popular Shrimp Magazine, are named after local streets. Also try the classic Red Beans and Rice, Fried Oysters and Jambalaya.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Regional Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/joey-ks-restaurant-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.08484,29.92512,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Lobster Shanty</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Lobster Shanty</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Salem, MA 01970 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9787455449" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(978) 745-5449</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.lobstershantysalem.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.lobstershantysalem.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Lobster+Shanty%2C+25+Front+St.%2C+Salem%2C+MA+01970&amp;ll=42.520507,-70.894408" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">25 Front St.<br/>Salem, MA 01970</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lobster Martini, Stout Marinated Steak Tips</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At The Lobster Shanty, you can enjoy lobster pie, lobster mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese and even lobster risotto. But the signature Lobstertini has lobster fans -- and Guy -- taking a second look. With lemon, &amp;quot;lobster essence&amp;quot; and a lobster claw hanging on the rim, Guy calls it an &amp;quot;absolutely lobster martini.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Small Town Sensations<br/>Wings, Dogs and Claws</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/salem/the-lobster-shanty-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.89441,42.52051,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Joint</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Joint</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70117 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5049493232" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">504-949-3232</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.alwayssmokin.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.alwayssmokin.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Joint%2C+701+Mazant+St.%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70117&amp;ll=29.961320,-90.035514" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">701 Mazant St.<br/>New Orleans, LA 70117</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulled Pork, Ribs, Brisket Sandwiches</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Everything at this Big Easy spot comes out of the smoker, from racks of ribs, pork butt and brisket sandwiches to Cajun sausage and even salad dressing. Guy calls their special North Carolina-style sauce, made with apple cider vinegar, brown sugar, pepper and cayenne, &amp;quot;an orchestra of flavor.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of BBQ</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/the-joint-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.03551,29.96132,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Turkey and the Wolf</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Turkey and the Wolf</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70130</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.turkeyandthewolf.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.turkeyandthewolf.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Turkey+and+the+Wolf%2C+739+Jackson+Ave%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70130&amp;ll=29.926647,-90.074376" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">739 Jackson Ave<br/>New Orleans, LA 70130</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hog&#x27;s Head Taco, Collard Green Reuben.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and Owner Mason Hereford somehow manages to make crazy, off-the-wall cuisine feel familiar. He makes homemade head cheese for the Hog&#x27;s Head Tacos and also serves a delicious vegetarian Collard Green Reuben.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Piling On the Pork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/turkey-and-the-wolf-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.07438,29.92665,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cutty&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cutty&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Brookline, MA 02445</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6175051844" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 505-1844</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cuttyfoods.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cuttyfoods.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cutty%27s%2C+284+Washington+St%2C+Brookline%2C+MA+02445&amp;ll=42.333068,-71.119420" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">284 Washington St<br/>Brookline, MA 02445</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Fennel, Roast Beef 1000</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A husband-and-wife team could never find the perfect sandwich, so they started making their own and sharing them with the world. Guy couldn&#x27;t get enough of the roast beef 1000 with crispy shallots and the pork fennel on a torta roll. Guy guarantees that all the sandwich are &quot;out of bounds.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Massachusetts Madness<br/>Northeast Feast</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/brookline/cuttys-restaurant2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.11942,42.33307,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>In A Pickle Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">In A Pickle Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Waltham, MA 02453 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.in-a-pickle.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.in-a-pickle.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=In+A+Pickle+Restaurant%2C+265+Moody+St%2C+Waltham%2C+MA+02453&amp;ll=42.371607,-71.236978" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">265 Moody St<br/>Waltham, MA 02453</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Toro Loco Burger, Pumpkin Bread French Toast</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this creative breakfast and lunch joint, chef-owner Tim Burke serves over-the-top dishes like the Toro Loco Burger: two patties stacked on a bed of arugula, topped with sriracha aioli, jalapeno sour cream aioli, a patty of fried pepper jack cheese and onion rings breaded with flaming-hot Cheetos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s All-Star Guests</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/waltham/in-a-pickle-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.23698,42.37161,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Porthole Restaurant &amp; Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Porthole Restaurant &amp; Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Portland, ME 04101 &middot; &#9733; 2.8 (15 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2077734653" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">207-773-4653</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://portholemaine.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">portholemaine.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Porthole+Restaurant+%26+Pub%2C+20+Custom+House+Wharf%2C+Portland%2C+ME+04101&amp;ll=43.656434,-70.250176" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">20 Custom House Wharf<br/>Portland, ME 04101</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Host Guy Fieri, of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, drops in at Porthole Restaurant in Portland, ME, where an 80-year-old waterfront spot is serving up boat-to-table fresh lobster on a house baked brioche.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fresh, Filled and Fried</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/me/portland/porthole-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.25018,43.65643,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Stoney Creek Inn</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Stoney Creek Inn</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Greenland Beach, MD 21226 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4104393123" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">410-439-3123</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.stoneycreekinnrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.stoneycreekinnrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Stoney+Creek+Inn%2C+8238+Fort+Smallwood+Rd.%2C+Greenland+Beach%2C+MD+21226&amp;ll=39.163983,-76.526996" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">8238 Fort Smallwood Rd.<br/>Greenland Beach, MD 21226</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crab Feast, Crab Cakes, Deep-Fried Crab, Cream of Crab</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You can&#x27;t be afraid to get your hands a little messy at this crab shack. Naturally, Guy&#x27;s favorite meal here is the traditional Maryland crab feast, but he loved the crab cakes too. Other local favorites include deep-fried crab, cream of crab, crab toast and shrimp stuffed with crab.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Traditional Dishes<br/>Northeast Feast</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/greenland-beach/stoney-creek-inn-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.52700,39.16398,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>JT Farnham&#x27;s Seafood &amp; Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">JT Farnham&#x27;s Seafood &amp; Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">South Essex, MA 01929 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9787686643" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">978-768-6643</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/south-essex/jt-farnhams-seafood-grill-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/south-essex/jt-farnhams-seafood-grill-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=JT+Farnham%27s+Seafood+%26+Grill%2C+88+Eastern+Ave+%28Rte+133%29%2C+South+Essex%2C+MA+01929&amp;ll=42.633029,-70.762848" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">88 Eastern Ave (Rte 133)<br/>South Essex, MA 01929</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Whole Belly Clams</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">With a recipe dating back to 1956, JT Farnham&#x27;s holds the key to delicious fried clams. By frying locally caught whole-belly clams to &amp;quot;just beyond canary yellow&amp;quot; it&#x27;s amassed a huge fan base. For newcomers, try the Fisherman&#x27;s Combo with everything from fish to fries and, of course, fried clams.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Deep-Fried Favorites<br/>One of a Kind</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/south-essex/jt-farnhams-seafood-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.76285,42.63303,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Little Depot Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Little Depot Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Peabody, MA 01960 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9789777775" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">978-977-7775</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thelittledepotdiner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thelittledepotdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Little+Depot+Diner%2C+1+Railroad+Ave%2C+Peabody%2C+MA+01960&amp;ll=42.527054,-70.927553" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1 Railroad Ave<br/>Peabody, MA 01960</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Boston Baked Beans, Mulligatawny Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Start your day with a tasty breakfast at the eclectic Little Depot Diner, an old lunch car turned diner, which once had wheels under the entire place. Try the Meatloaf and Eggs or French Canadian Creton, a pork and spice spread perfect for enjoying on crackers or with the curried Mulligatawny Soup.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners Times Three</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/peabody/the-little-depot-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.92755,42.52705,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Trina&#x27;s Starlite Lounge</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Trina&#x27;s Starlite Lounge</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Somerville 02143 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6175760006" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 576-0006</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://trinastarlitelounge.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">trinastarlitelounge.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Trina%27s+Starlite+Lounge%2C+3+Beacon+St%2C+Somerville+02143&amp;ll=42.374534,-71.101528" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3 Beacon St<br/>Somerville 02143</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Chicken &amp; Buttermilk Waffles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Trina&#x27;s Starlite Lounge brings a Southern splash to the East Coast. Their best seller is the fried chicken and buttermilk waffles with hot pepper syrup. Don&#x27;t miss their homemade Tater Tots with rosemary garlic aioli and Parm. These soft and crunchy tots get Guy&#x27;s stamp of approval.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Ordering All Kinds of Flavor<br/>Cross-Country Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/somerville/trinas-starlight-lounge-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.10153,42.37453,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Kelly&#x27;s Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Kelly&#x27;s Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Somerville, MA 02144-2220 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6176238102" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 623-8102</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.kellysdiner.net/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.kellysdiner.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Kelly%27s+Diner%2C+674+Broadway%2C+Somerville%2C+MA+02144-2220&amp;ll=42.399533,-71.111651" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">674 Broadway<br/>Somerville, MA 02144-2220</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lobster Roll, Pancakes, Corned Beef Hash, Meatloaf</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jay Holmes loved going to diners as a child, so he jumped at the chance to restore an old Delaware diner and transport it up to Somerville, Mass. Now it&#x27;s rechristened Kelly&#x27;s Diner and dishing out New England classics. This place is seriously legendary: it was the first diner Guy ever visted on Triple D. Guy felt the lobster roll was just right: lots of lobster and not too much mayo.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners, Drive-ins and Dives<br/>Diners A-Plenty<br/>Triple D Nation: A Little Lighter</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/somerville/kellys-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.11165,42.39953,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Deep Ellum</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Deep Ellum</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Allston, MA 02134 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6177872337" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 787-2337</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.deepellum-boston.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.deepellum-boston.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Deep+Ellum%2C+477+Cambridge+St%2C+Allston%2C+MA+02134&amp;ll=42.353834,-71.136826" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">477 Cambridge St<br/>Allston, MA 02134</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken 2 Ways</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Deep Ellum is a go-to destination for high-quality bar food and drinks. For brunch, Guy orders the house-cured salmon sandwich. Chicken 2 Ways is what he devours for dinner. The dish features smoked andouille-style sausage, confit thigh, cheese grits, braised collard greens and peach relish.&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roadtrippin&#x27; in Beantown</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/allston/deep-ellum" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.13683,42.35383,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lone Star Taco Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lone Star Taco Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Allston, MA 02134</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6177828226" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 782-8226</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.lonestar-boston.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.lonestar-boston.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lone+Star+Taco+Bar%2C+479+Cambridge+St%2C+Allston%2C+MA+02134&amp;ll=42.353806,-71.136888" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">479 Cambridge St<br/>Allston, MA 02134</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Ranchero Tostada, Grilled Street Corn, Beef Barbacoa</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Head over to Lone Star Taco Bar for the most-authentic Mexican street food on the East Coast. Diners love the Chicken Ranchero Tostada, with house beans, ranchero braised chicken, napa cabbage and crema placed on a crispy tortilla. Guy also recommends the grilled street corn and the beef barbacoa.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roadtrippin&#x27; in Beantown</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/allston/lone-star-taco-bar" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.13689,42.35381,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blue-Eyed Crab Caribbean Grill and Rum Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blue-Eyed Crab Caribbean Grill and Rum Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Plymouth, MA 02360 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5087476776" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">508-747-6776</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.blue-eyedcrab.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.blue-eyedcrab.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blue-Eyed+Crab+Caribbean+Grill+and+Rum+Bar%2C+170+Water+St%2C+Plymouth%2C+MA+02360&amp;ll=41.962291,-70.669175" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">170 Water St<br/>Plymouth, MA 02360</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lobster and Lump Crab Creole, Banana Garlic Chicken Wings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Jim Casey has dreamt up a menu that takes inspiration from the islands, as it&#x27;s loaded with seafood dishes that have a Caribbean twist (lobster and lump crab Creole, anyone?). The flavors of the tropics also shine through in Chef Casey&#x27;s assortment of next-level bar eats like the banana garlic chicken wings that Guy described as &quot;a calypso band meets Metallica.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Isle-talian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/plymouth/blue-eyed-crab-caribbean-grill-and-rum-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.66918,41.96229,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Italian Express Pizzeria</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Italian Express Pizzeria</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">East Boston 02128 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6175610038" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">617-561-0038</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.italianexpresspizzeria.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.italianexpresspizzeria.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Italian+Express+Pizzeria%2C+336+Sumner+St%2C+East+Boston+02128&amp;ll=42.367298,-71.035711" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">336 Sumner St<br/>East Boston 02128</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Frutti Di Mare, Haddock Margarita</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this eatery the food is fresh, handmade and inspired by nonni. The frutti di mare wowed Guy with its generous portions of mussels, shrimp and calamari on a bed of homemade fettuccine. Another standout is the tender, flaky haddock that comes slathered in a white wine sauce and flanked by a side of pan-roasted potatoes.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Incredible Italian<br/>Triple D Nation: From Near to Far<br/>Massachusetts Madness</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/east-boston/italian-express-pizzeria-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.03571,42.36730,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Driftwood Publick House and Oysteria</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Driftwood Publick House and Oysteria</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Plymouth, MA 02360</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5089274060" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">508-927-4060</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/plymouth/driftwood-publick-house-and-oysteria-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/plymouth/driftwood-publick-house-and-oysteria-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Driftwood+Publick+House+and+Oysteria%2C+39+Court+St%2C+Plymouth%2C+MA+02360&amp;ll=41.958186,-70.666804" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">39 Court St<br/>Plymouth, MA 02360</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Philly Pretzel</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Classic home cooking with a unique twist is what you&#x27;ll get at this gastropub that had Guy declaring it &quot;out of bounds!&quot; One standout that draws the crowds is the Philly Pretzel. This massive pretzel comes stuffed with shredded beer-braised beef shoulder and melted American cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef It Up</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/plymouth/driftwood-publick-house-and-oysteria-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-70.66680,41.95819,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Galway Bay Irish Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Galway Bay Irish Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Annapolis, MD 21401 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4102638333" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(410) 263-8333</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.galwaybaymd.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.galwaybaymd.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Galway+Bay+Irish+Pub%2C+63+Maryland+Ave%2C+Annapolis%2C+MD+21401&amp;ll=38.979699,-76.489715" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">63 Maryland Ave<br/>Annapolis, MD 21401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cabbage Wraps</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Mike Marone is putting his funky touches on traditional Irish pub food at Galway Bay Irish Pub. The low-key, casual environment is serving what Guy likes to call &quot;Irish sushi&quot; - steamed cabbage leaves stuffed with potato and corned beef, and served with a whole-grain mustard sauce.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Long Standing Legacies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/annapolis/galway-bay-irish-pub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.48971,38.97970,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Smoking Swine</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Smoking Swine</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore, MD 21231 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4435794630" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">443-579-4630</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://thesmokingswine.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">thesmokingswine.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Smoking+Swine%2C+Roaming+Food+Truck%2C+Baltimore%2C+MD+21231&amp;ll=39.287866,-76.592166" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Roaming Food Truck<br/>Baltimore, MD 21231</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Carolina, Beef Short Rib</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Loyal fans line up at Drew Pumphrey&#x27;s mobile food truck to get their fill of his smoked specialties like short ribs and pulled pork sandwiches. A favorite sandwich is The Carolina: Boneless pork butt is hit with a brown sugar dry rub, smoked for 12 hours, then doused with a spicy barbecue sauce that has Guy hooked. A topping of homemade slaw laced with chipotle powder adds kick to the bite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoke and Seafood</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/the-smoking-swine-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.59217,39.28787,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Davis&#x27; Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Davis&#x27; Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Annapolis, MD 21403 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4102687432" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(410) 268-7432</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://davispub.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">davispub.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Davis%27+Pub%2C+400+Chester+Ave%2C+Annapolis%2C+MD+21403&amp;ll=38.969175,-76.480305" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">400 Chester Ave<br/>Annapolis, MD 21403</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chipotle Habanero Barbecue Sandwich, Baltimore-Style Steamed Shrimp</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this dive &amp;quot;there are no strangers, only people you haven&#x27;t met yet.&amp;quot; The chipotle habanero barbecue sandwich with coleslaw and a light tangy barbecue sauce was the highlight of Guy&#x27;s visit. Locals can&#x27;t get enough of the Baltimore-style steamed shrimp and the crab cake sandwich.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Savory Standouts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/annapolis/davis-pub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.48031,38.96918,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Miss Shirley&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Miss Shirley&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore 21210 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4108895272" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">410-889-5272</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.missshirleys.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.missshirleys.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Miss+Shirley%27s+Cafe%2C+513+W+Cold+Spring+Ln%2C+Baltimore+21210&amp;ll=39.344355,-76.631441" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">513 W Cold Spring Ln<br/>Baltimore 21210</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Coconut Cream Stuffed French Toast, Bay-O Po&#x27; Boy</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crowds flock here for the decadent eats that reflect the Southern-inspired vision of late owner Eddie Dopkin (his son continues the dream). Guy favors Chef Brigitte Bledsoe&#x27;s French toast: Slabs of challah bread come stuffed with a rich coconut filling made from a mascarpone-and-cream-cheese base. Prefer something savory? Try the Southern Slammer Sandwich featuring fried green tomato, applewood-smoked bacon, mashed avocado, cheddar and a fried egg piled on pumpernickel bread.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rockstar Chefs<br/>Family Legacies<br/>Triple D Nation: Breakfast, Lunch and Brunch</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/miss-shirleys-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.63144,39.34435,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Grano Pasta Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Grano Pasta Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore 21211</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4438693429" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(443) 869-3429</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://granopastabar.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">granopastabar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Grano+Pasta+Bar%2C+1031+W+36th+St%2C+Baltimore+21211&amp;ll=39.330802,-76.633578" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1031 W 36th St<br/>Baltimore 21211</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tagliolini Pasta, Handmade Ravioli</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This small joint specializes in one thing only: pasta. Guy digs the tagliolini pasta topped with baby clams, whose simple ingredients combine to create lots of flavor. He also raves about the handmade ravioli with a filling made from mushrooms and various cheeses, calling it rich, light and earthy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meat in the Middle</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/grano-pasta-bar" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.63358,39.33080,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>G&amp;A Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">G&amp;A Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore, MD 21224 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4102769422" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(410) 276-9422</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.gandarestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.gandarestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=G%26A+Restaurant%2C+3802+Eastern+Avenue%2C+Baltimore%2C+MD+21224&amp;ll=39.286986,-76.565114" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3802 Eastern Avenue<br/>Baltimore, MD 21224</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Coney Dogs, Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The only place to find authentic Coney Island-style hot dogs in Baltimore is at G&amp;A Restaurant, owned by Andy Farantos. Their Coney Island chili sauce - or, as Guy calls it, their &#x27;&#x27;crazy meat concoction&#x27;&#x27; -combines ground beef with chili powder, celery salt and other secret spices.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diner&#x27;s Drive-ins and Dives: Best from the Road<br/>Burgers and Dogs<br/>All-American All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/ga-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.56511,39.28699,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>DiPasquale&#x27;s Italian Marketplace</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">DiPasquale&#x27;s Italian Marketplace</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore 21224 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4102766787" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(410) 276-6787</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.dipasquales.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.dipasquales.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=DiPasquale%27s+Italian+Marketplace%2C+3700+Gough+St%2C+Baltimore+21224&amp;ll=39.288904,-76.566489" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3700 Gough St<br/>Baltimore 21224</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homemade Pasta, Lasagna, Ravioli, Arancini, Homemade Mozzarella</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">DiPasquale&#x27;s bills itself as &quot;your place for everything Italian.&quot; Guy would agree, as they sell their own homemade bread, cannoli and mozzarella right next to the aisles of Italian goods and imports. Guy devoured the Sicilian favorite, arancini, calling it a &quot;winner-winner rice ball dinner.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">East Coast Cruisin&#x27;<br/>Triple D Nation: Italian Inspired<br/>Real Deal Italian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/di-pasquales-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.56649,39.28890,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Alewife Baltimore</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Alewife Baltimore</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore 21201</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4105455112" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">410-545-5112</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/alewife-baltimore-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/alewife-baltimore-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Alewife+Baltimore%2C+21+N+Eutaw+St%2C+Baltimore+21201&amp;ll=39.290263,-76.620748" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">21 N Eutaw St<br/>Baltimore 21201</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wild Boar Sliders, Pork Belly Mac &amp; Cheese Fries, Snakehead Cakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This bar offers 90-plus beers, but Guy homes in on the unusual eats. He raves about the &quot;dense, big flavor&quot; of the wild boar meat used in the sliders. A topping of pickled carrots and ginger dressing cuts the richness of the meat, making for a combination that was &quot;built to go together,&quot; Guy says.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of Meat</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/alewife-baltimore-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.62075,39.29026,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Angela&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Angela&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">East Boston 02128 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6175674972" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 567-4972</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://angelascafeboston.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">angelascafeboston.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Angela%27s+Cafe%2C+131+Lexington+St%2C+East+Boston+02128&amp;ll=42.378526,-71.034965" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">131 Lexington St<br/>East Boston 02128</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chilaquiles Verdes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owner Luis Garcia and his mother are cooking up authentic bites from Puebla, Mexico, their hometown. Nothing here comes from a can including the tomatillo sauce for the chilaquiles verdes with chicken, which Guy absolutely adored.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: East Coast Eatin&#x27;<br/>Food Done Right</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/east-boston/angelas-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.03497,42.37853,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Morin&#x27;s Hometown Bar &amp; Grille</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Morin&#x27;s Hometown Bar &amp; Grille</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Attleboro, MA 02703 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5082229875" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(508) 222-9875</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.morins1911.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.morins1911.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Morin%27s+Hometown+Bar+%26+Grille%2C+16+S+Main+St%2C+Attleboro%2C+MA+02703&amp;ll=41.943983,-71.284137" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">16 S Main St<br/>Attleboro, MA 02703</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">10-inch French Meat Pie, Fisherman&#x27;s Stew</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Attleboro, Mass., landmark - currently in its third generation - has been making its French Meat Pies the same way for over 100 years. Try the French meat pie served with mashed potatoes and a gravy that&#x27;s got a hint of cinnamon and cloves, which Guy calls &amp;quot;the zip&amp;quot; in the dish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Legacies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/attleboro/morins-hometown-bar-grille-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.28414,41.94398,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tupelo</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tupelo</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cambridge, MA 02139 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6178680004" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">617-868-0004</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://tupelo02139.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">tupelo02139.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tupelo%2C+1193+Cambridge+St%2C+Cambridge%2C+MA+02139&amp;ll=42.373413,-71.097163" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1193 Cambridge St<br/>Cambridge, MA 02139</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Confit Pork Belly Corn Dogs, Shrimp and Grits, Gumbo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When it comes to New Orleans-style cuisine, no one adds as much flair to their cooking as Chef Rembs Layman. The confit pork belly corn dogs with a side of pickled habanero and onions electrified Guy&#x27;s taste buds. Fans adore the shrimp and grits, gumbo and beer-batter crepes.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">East Coast Comfort<br/>Deep Fried All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/cambridge/tupelo-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.09716,42.37341,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Veggie Galaxy</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Veggie Galaxy</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cambridge, MA 02139 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6174971513" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">617-497-1513</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.veggiegalaxy.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.veggiegalaxy.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Veggie+Galaxy%2C+450+Massachusetts+Ave%2C+Cambridge%2C+MA+02139&amp;ll=42.363424,-71.101296" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">450 Massachusetts Ave<br/>Cambridge, MA 02139</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pancakes, Shepherd&#x27;s Pie, Mac and Stack, Vegan Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Head here for American diner staples with a vegetarian makeover, as well as fresh baked goods from the restaurant&#x27;s 100-percent-vegan bakery. Try the fluffy pancakes topped with your choice of caramelized banana butter or mixed berries and coconut whipped cream. Dinner options include a hearty shepherd&#x27;s pie (a combination of quinoa, button mushrooms, peas, carrots and corn).</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Unique Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/cambridge/veggie-galaxy-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.10130,42.36342,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bagelsaurus</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bagelsaurus</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cambridge, MA 02140</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bagelsaurus.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bagelsaurus.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bagelsaurus%2C+1796+Massachusetts+Ave%2C+Cambridge%2C+MA+02140&amp;ll=42.385951,-71.119614" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1796 Massachusetts Ave<br/>Cambridge, MA 02140</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BLT, Hot Smoked</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Mary Ting Hyatt was planning on being a schoolteacher but decided to open a bagel restaurant instead and ended up starting a bagel revolution in the Boston area. Customers rave that her house-made bagels and bialys are some of the best they&#x27;ve ever had. Her version of a BLT is made on a fresh onion bagel with spicy cream cheese, slow-roasted tomatoes, lettuce and a mound of crispy bacon. &quot;You&#x27;re a dangerous woman,&quot; said Guy after tasting the sandwich.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bagels, Biscuit and Boar</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/cambridge/bagelsaurus-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.11961,42.38595,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sip &amp; Bite Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sip &amp; Bite Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore, MD 21231 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4106757077" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(410) 675-7077</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sipandbite.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sipandbite.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sip+%26+Bite+Restaurant%2C+2200+Boston+St%2C+Baltimore%2C+MD+21231&amp;ll=39.284028,-76.585502" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2200 Boston St<br/>Baltimore, MD 21231</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crab Cakes, Spanakopita</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This third-generation family-owned diner serves classic Greek- and Maryland-inspired fare. Guy loved the meaty texture and generous portions of the crab cakes. The spanakopita, cooked according to the family recipe, sent Guy head over heels when he experienced its cheesy flavor.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Passin&#x27; The Baton<br/>Late Night Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/sip-bite-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.58550,39.28403,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Slainte Irish Pub and Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Slainte Irish Pub and Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore, MD 21231 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4105636600" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">410-563-6600</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.slaintepub.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.slaintepub.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Slainte+Irish+Pub+and+Restaurant%2C+Historic+Fells+Point%2C+1700+Thames+St.%2C+Baltimore%2C+MD+21231&amp;ll=39.282091,-76.591318" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Historic Fells Point, 1700 Thames St.<br/>Baltimore, MD 21231</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Seafood Gumbo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Slainte puts a distinctly Baltimorean spin on the classic Irish pub, with excellent seafood dishes like gumbo packed with shrimp, crayfish and Maryland blue crab. Chef Chris Marquis puts a Korean spin on Irish pub classic corned beef, revamping the dish as hearty bibimbap.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Soup-Centric</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/slainte-irish-pub-and-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.59132,39.28209,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Johnny Rad&#x27;s Pizzeria Tavern</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Johnny Rad&#x27;s Pizzeria Tavern</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore, MD 21231 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4437596464" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(443) 759-6464</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.johnnyrads.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.johnnyrads.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Johnny+Rad%27s+Pizzeria+Tavern%2C+2108+Eastern+Ave.%2C+Baltimore%2C+MD+21231&amp;ll=39.286029,-76.586554" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2108 Eastern Ave.<br/>Baltimore, MD 21231</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Risotto Balls</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Want a little punk rock with your pizza? Johnny Rad&#x27;s specializes in pies like the Trainwreck, which features mushrooms, spinach, olives and fresh mozzarella - a vegetarian pizza that is hearty enough to keep carnivores happy. Prep for the pizzas with an order of vegan chili, hush puppies or fried risotto balls.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pub Grub<br/>All Baltimore, All the Time</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/johnny-rads-pizzeria-tavern" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.58655,39.28603,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Swallow at the Hollow</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Swallow at the Hollow</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore, MD 21212 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4105327542" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(410) 532-7542</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thehollowbar.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thehollowbar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Swallow+at+the+Hollow%2C+5921+York+Rd.%2C+Baltimore%2C+MD+21212&amp;ll=39.364854,-76.609721" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5921 York Rd.<br/>Baltimore, MD 21212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Honey Ghost Wings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Swallow at the Hollow is a dive with a catchy name, but it&#x27;s the food you won&#x27;t forget. Guy was reluctant to try the Honey Ghost wings, which feature fiery ghost peppers in the sauce, but he found the wings to be perfectly balanced, with the right amount of heat and sweetness.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Chowfest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/swallow-at-the-hollow" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.60972,39.36485,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Clementine</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Clementine</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore, MD 21214 &middot; &#9733; 1.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4104441497" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(410) 444-1497</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.clementinebaltimore.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.clementinebaltimore.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Clementine%2C+5402+Harford+Rd.%2C+Baltimore%2C+MD+21214&amp;ll=39.351408,-76.562474" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5402 Harford Rd.<br/>Baltimore, MD 21214</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bacon Wrapped Meatloaf; Asian Braised Pork Cheeks</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Clementine is a farm-to-table joint that&#x27;s turning heads not just for its philosophy, but also for its delicious food. Chef Winston Blick cures all of his own meat, including bacon, which stars in his house-smoked bacon-wrapped meatloaf. Blick&#x27;s menu also features excellent lesser-known cuts of meat, like Asian-style braised pork cheeks.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Baltimore, All the Time</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/clementine" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.56247,39.35141,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Joe Squared Pizza</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Joe Squared Pizza</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore, MD 21201 &middot; &#9733; 4.6 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4105450444" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(410) 545-0444</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.joesquared.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.joesquared.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Joe+Squared+Pizza%2C+133+W+North+Ave%2C+Baltimore%2C+MD+21201&amp;ll=39.310603,-76.619102" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">133 W North Ave<br/>Baltimore, MD 21201</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bacon and Clam Pizza, Flag Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The starter for the dough from this pizza shop is from an Italian island and is 200 years old. The &amp;quot;crazy good&amp;quot; Bacon and Clam Pizza impressed Guy with its generous amounts of toppings, great texture and chew. He also appreciated the salami and beef filled fried ravioli with marinara dipping sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Outside the Box<br/>Best of Pizza</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/joe-squared-pizza-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.61910,39.31060,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jimmy&#x27;s Famous Seafood</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jimmy&#x27;s Famous Seafood</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore 21224 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (129 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4106334040" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">410-633-4040</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.jimmysfamousseafood.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jimmysfamousseafood.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jimmy%27s+Famous+Seafood%2C+6526+Holabird+Ave%2C+Baltimore+21224&amp;ll=39.272761,-76.534746" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6526 Holabird Ave<br/>Baltimore 21224</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crab Cakes, Seafood UFO, Jimmy&#x27;s Oysters</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If this spot deserves fame for one thing, it&#x27;s the crab cakes. As Guy puts it, &quot;This is 95 percent crab, 5 percent binding.&quot; The crab cakes - which are about the size of your hand - are packed with fresh Maryland lump blue-crab meat. Another worthwhile menu item is the massive Seafood UFO. The oversized slices of bread that hold this sandwich together can barely contain all the fillings: colossal crab cakes and crab-studded mac and cheese balls, along with mounds of fried shrimp, fried oysters and shrimp salad.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: All Over the Menu<br/>Triple D Nation: Slurpin&#x27; Soup<br/>All Baltimore, All the Time</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/jimmys-famous-seafood" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.53475,39.27276,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dirty Water Dough</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dirty Water Dough</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boston, MA 02116</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.dirtywaterdough.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.dirtywaterdough.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dirty+Water+Dough%2C+222+Newbury+St%2C+Boston%2C+MA+02116&amp;ll=42.349758,-71.081080" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">222 Newbury St<br/>Boston, MA 02116</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Taco Pizza, Steak and Cola Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This inventive pizza shop uses beer to make their dough instead of water, which gives each slice a soft inside and a perfectly crispy outside. Plus, they&#x27;re topping pies with unusual combos. Their Taco Pizza is layered with taco meat, cheese, lettuce, tomato and crushed nacho cheese chips and is finished with a sour cream swirl. Guy loved the combo so much, he couldn&#x27;t help but immediately get his son Ryder on the phone to tell him about it. &quot;He&#x27;s going to lose his mind on this one,&quot; Guy said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza Plus</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/boston/dirty-water-dough-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.08108,42.34976,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mr. Bartley&#x27;s Gourmet Burgers</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mr. Bartley&#x27;s Gourmet Burgers</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cambridge, MA 02138 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6173546559" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 354-6559</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mrbartley.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mrbartley.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mr.+Bartley%27s+Gourmet+Burgers%2C+1246+Massachusetts+Ave.%2C+Cambridge%2C+MA+02138&amp;ll=42.372521,-71.116321" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1246 Massachusetts Ave.<br/>Cambridge, MA 02138</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Triple D Burger, The Drone Burger, Frappes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Harvard Square institution serves classic American burgers with classic and creative toppings, often named for celebrities. The Triple-D burger tops two patties with bacon, cheese, barbecue sauce adn grilled onions, with onion rings.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Steaks and Chops<br/>Top 10 Burgers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/cambridge/mr-bartleys-gourmet-burgers-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.11632,42.37252,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Chaps Pit Beef</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Chaps Pit Beef</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore 21205 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4104832379" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">410-483-2379</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.chapspitbeef.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.chapspitbeef.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Chaps+Pit+Beef%2C+5801+Pulaski+Hwy%2C+Baltimore+21205&amp;ll=39.301302,-76.548062" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5801 Pulaski Hwy<br/>Baltimore 21205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pit Beef, Chaps Submarine, Bull Dog Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Guy and Duff stop by one of Baltimore&#x27;s finest. From beef to turkey, Chaps Pit Beef infuses each bite with a hint of smoky charcoal goodness. Either way you cut it - rare, medium rare or well done - Chaps knows mouthwatering pit beef.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Flavortown Medley<br/>Big Bites<br/>Triple D Nation: East Coast Eatin&#x27;<br/>Super Sandwiches<br/>Takeout: Global Comes Local<br/>In the Family</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/chaps-pit-beef-restaurant2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.54806,39.30130,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Highland Fried</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Highland Fried</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cambridge, MA 02139</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.highlandfried.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.highlandfried.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Highland+Fried%2C+1271+Cambridge+St.%2C+Cambridge%2C+MA+02139&amp;ll=42.373543,-71.098536" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1271 Cambridge St.<br/>Cambridge, MA 02139</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nashville Fried Chicken, Gumbo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After owner Mark Romano won awards at his other restaurant for the bestfried chicken in Boston, he decided to open up this joint to focus exclusively on the dish. His chicken is tender and crispy, and pairs well with his drink menu, which is an entire lineup of classic Tiki drinks, like the Mai Tai and the Painkiller. Guy and Hunter also loved the barbecue gumbo.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Northern Southern</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/cambridge/highland-fried-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.09854,42.37354,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Greek Corner Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Greek Corner Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Cambridge, MA 02140 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6176615655" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(617) 661-5655</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.greekcorner.us/index.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.greekcorner.us/index.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Greek+Corner+Restaurant%2C+2366+Massachusetts+Ave%2C+Cambridge%2C+MA+02140&amp;ll=42.396358,-71.129563" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2366 Massachusetts Ave<br/>Cambridge, MA 02140</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spit-Roasted Lamb, Pastitsio</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this authentic eatery, you&#x27;re getting real Greek food made by two brothers who once left Greece to go to college and ended up serving their mother&#x27;s recipes at Greek Corner instead. Enjoy a meat attack, just as Guy did with the &quot;tetris of meat and lamb&quot; in their layered meat gyro.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Layered, Stuffed and Stacked<br/>Timeless</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ma/cambridge/greek-corner-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-71.12956,42.39636,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blue Moon Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blue Moon Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baltimore, MD 21321 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4105223940" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(410) 522-3940</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://bluemoonbaltimore.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">bluemoonbaltimore.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blue+Moon+Cafe%2C+1621+Aliceanna+St.%2C+Baltimore%2C+MD+21321&amp;ll=39.283319,-76.594229" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1621 Aliceanna St.<br/>Baltimore, MD 21321</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cap&#x27;n Crunch Encrusted French Toast, Sweet Baby Jesus with Scrapple</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The most-famous dish at the Blue Moon Cafe in Baltimore is the Cap&#x27;n Crunch-encrusted French toast - two breakfast classics that taste great together. Guy loves owner Sarah Simington&#x27;s homestyle dishes, calling them the definition of comfort food. Duff favors the Sweet Baby Jesus with Scrapple - layers of fried hash browns, crabmeat, cheese, tomatoes and eggs, smothered in housemade hollandaise.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort Food</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/md/baltimore/blue-moon-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-76.59423,39.28332,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Kramarczuk&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Kramarczuk&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55414 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6123793018" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(612) 379-3018</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.kramarczuk.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.kramarczuk.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Kramarczuk%27s%2C+215+E+Hennepin+Ave%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55414&amp;ll=44.987890,-93.257365" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">215 E Hennepin Ave<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55414</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Boiled Cabbage Rolls Stuffed with Pork, Varenyky (Pierogis), Krakowska (Polish Sausage), Szegedin Goulash</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Take a ride with Guy to Kramarczuk&#x27;s, an old European country food spot known for &amp;quot;stick-to-your-ribs food.&amp;quot; If you&#x27;re a sausage lover, then this is the place to get homemade sausage and boiled cabbage rolls. You can&#x27;t leave without trying Varenyky, the dish with three meats and three potatoes.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/kramarczuks-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.25737,44.98789,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Emily&#x27;s Lebanese Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Emily&#x27;s Lebanese Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55413 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6123794069" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612-379-4069</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.emilyslebanesedeli.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.emilyslebanesedeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Emily%27s+Lebanese+Deli%2C+641+University+Ave+NE%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55413&amp;ll=44.995645,-93.261340" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">641 University Ave NE<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55413</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Kabob, Lamb Tongue, Kibbi, Meat Pie (Lamb and Beef Baked in Flour Crust), Hummus Bi-Tahini, Stuffed Grape Leaves</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">In downtown Minneapolis, Emily&#x27;s has been serving family-style Lebanese food for more than 38 years. The signature lamb shish kebab had Guy singing its praises. The kibbi made with raw ground beef and spices was equally delicious - Guy described it as the Lebanese version of steak tartare.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Something from Everywhere</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/emilys-lebanese-delicatessen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.26134,44.99565,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Buster&#x27;s on 28th</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Buster&#x27;s on 28th</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55406 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6127290911" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">612-729-0911</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://busterson28th.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">busterson28th.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Buster%27s+on+28th%2C+4204+S+28th+Ave%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55406&amp;ll=44.926612,-93.232295" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4204 S 28th Ave<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55406</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beer-Braised Beef</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Buster&#x27;s on 28th is so beloved that local fans rallied to raise money to rebuild it after the gastropub burned down in 2013. Crowds flock here for the friendly vibe and elevated pub grub like beer-braised brisket. After being hit with a simple rub, the cubed beef is braised in heavy stout, then served on a bun smothered with roasted red pepper cream cheese. &quot;That is fantastic,&quot; Guy said of the dish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef It Up<br/>Meaty Masterpieces</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/busters-on-28th-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.23229,44.92661,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Colossal Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Colossal Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis, MN 55407 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6127292377" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(612) 729-2377</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.colossalcafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.colossalcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Colossal+Cafe%2C+1839+E+42nd+St%2C+Minneapolis%2C+MN+55407&amp;ll=44.926922,-93.246380" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1839 E 42nd St<br/>Minneapolis, MN 55407</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meatloaf Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Don&#x27;t let the small 500-square-foot space fool you: They&#x27;re not skimping on ingredients at the Colossal Cafe. Try their Apple, Walnuts &amp;amp; Brie pancakes or go with the best-selling meatloaf sandwich topped with citrus-infused cranberry compote and served on fresh bread that is baked daily.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwiches Plus</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/colossal-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.24638,44.92692,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Broders&#x27; Cucina Italiana</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Broders&#x27; Cucina Italiana</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Minneapolis 55410 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6129253113" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(612) 925-3113</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://broders.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">broders.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Broders%27+Cucina+Italiana%2C+2308+W+50th+St%2C+Minneapolis+55410&amp;ll=44.912579,-93.309134" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2308 W 50th St<br/>Minneapolis 55410</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Prosciutto and Arugula Pizza, Fettuccine alla Bolognese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Anthony Rodriguez, director of photography for Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives insisted that this family-owned Italian restaurant is to die for. After trying the tender fettuccine alla Bolognese and experiencing the thin-crust Dynamite pizza with prosciutto, mozzarella and arugula, Guy was convinced.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Real Deal Delivery<br/>Crankin&#x27; Up the Classics<br/>Best of Pizza</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/mn/minneapolis/broders-cucina-italiana-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.30913,44.91258,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Piece of Meat</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Piece of Meat</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans 70119</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://pieceofmeatbutcher.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">pieceofmeatbutcher.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Piece+of+Meat%2C+3301+Bienville+St%2C+New+Orleans+70119&amp;ll=29.971222,-90.091304" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3301 Bienville St<br/>New Orleans 70119</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Piece of Meat, a full-service butcher shop and restaurant in New Orleans, was the brain child of chefs Leighann Smith and Daniel Jackson. Aside from unbeatable house-smoked and cured meats, they&#x27;re adding their own twist to local favorites. To make the Boudin Egg Rolls, they wrap house-made boudin sausage around pepper jack cheese and then roll it into wonton wrapper and deep fry it. &quot;That wrecks boudin for me from now on,&quot; said Guy.  &quot;You take things that people love and you show them how great it could have been for all these years.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eating Up New Orleans</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/piece-of-meat-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.09130,29.97122,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Parasol&#x27;s Bar &amp; Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Parasol&#x27;s Bar &amp; Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70130 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5043021543" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">504-302-1543</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/parasols-bar-and-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/parasols-bar-and-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Parasol%27s+Bar+%26+Restaurant%2C+2533+Constance+St%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70130&amp;ll=29.926456,-90.080156" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2533 Constance St<br/>New Orleans, LA 70130</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Po&#x27; Boys, Muffaletta</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Every dish at Parasol&#x27;s Bar &amp; Restaurant is made with tender loving care. As Guy soon discovered, that means po&#x27; boys stuffed with &quot;capital-T tender&quot; roast beef. But the real heavy hitter had to be the quintessential New Orleans muffaletta sandwich. Guy called it an absolute must-try.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Places You Sent Me</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/parasols-bar-and-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.08016,29.92646,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Red&#x27;s Chinese</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Red&#x27;s Chinese</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70117 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5043046030" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">504-304-6030</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.redschinese.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.redschinese.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Red%27s+Chinese%2C+3048+St+Claude+Ave%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70117&amp;ll=29.967772,-90.045086" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3048 St Claude Ave<br/>New Orleans, LA 70117</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eggplans, Crawfish Rangoon, Swallow Cloud Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This spunky Bywater restaurant brings New Orleans flavor to Chinese food with crawfish-packed fried wontons, tingly MaPo Dauphine with tofu, and Bywater Eggplant, spiced with gochujang.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cultural Twist</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/reds-chinese-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.04509,29.96777,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Gralehaus</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Gralehaus</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Louisville 40204 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5024547075" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">502-454-7075</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.thegrales.com/gralehaus" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thegrales.com/gralehaus</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Gralehaus%2C+1001+Baxter+Ave%2C+Louisville+40204&amp;ll=38.239153,-85.723184" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1001 Baxter Ave<br/>Louisville 40204</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bologna, Egg &amp; Cheese Sandwich, Lamb &amp; Grits</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A litany of comfort food favorites with a Southern lilt has earned Gralehaus a legion of loyal fans, with Damaris Phillips among them. She brought Guy Fieri to her hometown haunt, where he was won over by two indulgent menu items: a cheesy bologna sandwich and a meaty grits dish. &quot;Dynamite,&quot; Guy declared of the sandwich, which features two fried slices of housemade bologna perched on a cheese-smothered brioche bun. A sunny-side up egg, mustard greens and splash of hot sauce finish the creation.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brunch, Bologna and Burgers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/louisville/gralehaus-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-85.72318,38.23915,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bobo&#x27;s Drive In</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bobo&#x27;s Drive In</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Topeka, KS 66604 &middot; &#9733; 4.1 (14 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7852344511" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">785-234-4511</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ks/topeka/bobo-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ks/topeka/bobo-drive-in-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bobo%27s+Drive+In%2C+2300+SW+10th+Ave.%2C+Topeka%2C+KS+66604&amp;ll=39.051556,-95.706284" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2300 SW 10th Ave.<br/>Topeka, KS 66604</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Onion Rings, Double Cheeseburger, Bobo&#x27;s Chili, Spanish Burger, Spanish Sauce, Apple Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Drive-in restaurants may not be as commonplace as they used to be, but that hasn&#x27;t stopped Bobo&#x27;s Drive-In from attracting customers with the same recipes they&#x27;ve had for over 50 years. Their classic cheeseburger is often served with their signature Spanish sauce; as Guy says, &#x27;&#x27;that&#x27;s good eats.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">American Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ks/topeka/bobo-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.70628,39.05156,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jarocho</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jarocho</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, KS 66105</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.jarochokc.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jarochokc.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jarocho%2C+719+Kansas+Ave%2C+Kansas+City%2C+KS+66105&amp;ll=39.087439,-94.626863" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">719 Kansas Ave<br/>Kansas City, KS 66105</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef-owner Carlos Falcon grew up living right next to the ocean in Mexico, so when he decided to open a restaurant in landlocked Kansas City, he figured out how to bring in fresh fish daily to recreate the flavors of his childhood. The standout dish is the whole fried sea bass, which is salt brined for 24 hours before it&#x27;s fried to give it a crisp, salty exterior. It&#x27;s served with a side of fresh cabbage slaw and a drizzle of chipotle sauce, and is so incredibly simple. &quot;I don&#x27;t care if this is the only thing on the menu, I will be back,&quot; Guy said after his first bite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Loaded, Stuffed and Fried</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ks/kansas-city/jarocho-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.62686,39.08744,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Woodyard Bar-B-Que</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Woodyard Bar-B-Que</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kansas City, KS 66106 &middot; &#9733; 4.1 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9133628000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(913) 362-8000</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.woodyardbbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.woodyardbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Woodyard+Bar-B-Que%2C+3001+Merriam+Ln%2C+Kansas+City%2C+KS+66106&amp;ll=39.045578,-94.662458" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3001 Merriam Ln<br/>Kansas City, KS 66106</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Ribs, Burnt Ends Sandwich, Smoked Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Woodyard had been supplying wood to Kansas City BBQ restaurants since 1913, when in 2005, owner Frank Schloegel decided that if it&#x27;s good enough for everybody else, he&#x27;d start cooking on it, too. Now the Smoked Chicken and BurntEnds Sandwich are local faves, and Guy calls the Pork Ribs &amp;quot;a knockout.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kansas City Barbecue Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ks/kansas-city/woodyard-bar-b-que-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.66246,39.04558,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>RJ&#x27;s Bob-Be-Que Shack</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">RJ&#x27;s Bob-Be-Que Shack</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Mission, KS 66062 &middot; &#9733; 4.9 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9132627300" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(913) 262-7300</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rjsbbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rjsbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=RJ%27s+Bob-Be-Que+Shack%2C+5835+Lamar+Ave%2C+Mission%2C+KS+66062&amp;ll=39.022812,-94.658092" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5835 Lamar Ave<br/>Mission, KS 66062</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jalapeno Sausage, Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Bob Palmgreen spent years in high-end NYC restaurants, entering BBQ competitions on the side, until after receiving dozens of awards he decided to take his hobby full time with RJ&#x27;s Bob-Be-Que Shack. Guy calls their Jalapeno Sausage &quot;tremendous,&quot; and the Lamb Ribs are a bonafide top seller.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Fried, Baked and Barbecued<br/>Kansas City Barbecue Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ks/mission/rjs-bob-be-que-shack-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.65809,39.02281,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Johnny&#x27;s Bar-B-Q</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Johnny&#x27;s Bar-B-Q</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Mission, KS 66201 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9134320777" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(913) 432-0777</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.johnnysbbqkc.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.johnnysbbqkc.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Johnny%27s+Bar-B-Q%2C+5959+Broadmoor%2C+Mission%2C+KS+66201&amp;ll=39.020761,-94.665238" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5959 Broadmoor<br/>Mission, KS 66201</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken, Pulled Pork with Some Serious Bite, Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">According to Guy, Johnny&#x27;s Bar-B-Q &amp;quot;just screams tradition.&amp;quot; With a handmade pit, over three decades of happy customers and an owner who&#x27;s been making BBQ since he was 14 that comes as no surprise. Try the nice and crispy, super-juicy smoked-and-deep-fried chicken with award-winning mild BBQ rub.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kansas City Barbecue Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ks/mission/johnnys-bar-b-q-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.66524,39.02076,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Brint&#x27;s Diner - UNDER NEW OWNERSHIP</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Brint&#x27;s Diner - UNDER NEW OWNERSHIP</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wichita, KS 67216 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3166840290" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(316) 684-0290</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ks/wichita/brints-diner-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ks/wichita/brints-diner-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Brint%27s+Diner+-+UNDER+NEW+OWNERSHIP%2C+4834+E.+Lincoln+Street%2C+Wichita%2C+KS+67216&amp;ll=37.672859,-97.279162" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4834 E. Lincoln Street<br/>Wichita, KS 67216</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eggs, Omelet, Pancakes, Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy Fieri visits Brint&#x27;s Diner in Wichita, KS, in search of the perfect American breakfast on Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ks/wichita/brints-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-97.27916,37.67286,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Indy&#x27;s Historic Steer-In Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Indy&#x27;s Historic Steer-In Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Indianapolis, IN 46219 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (15 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3173560996" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(317) 356- 0996</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.steerin.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.steerin.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Indy%27s+Historic+Steer-In+Restaurant%2C+5130+E+10th+St%2C+Indianapolis%2C+IN+46219&amp;ll=39.781813,-86.082333" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5130 E 10th St<br/>Indianapolis, IN 46219</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meatball Sandwich, Beef and Noodles, Stuffed Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This community establishment was about to disappear before a mother and son bought and revived it. Guy enjoyed the meatball sandwich with homemade marinara sauce. The noodles are made fresh for the stick-to-your-ribs beef and noodles. Feeling hungry? Try the stuffed pizza made to order.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meaty Masterpieces<br/>Soup and Sandwiches</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/in/indianapolis/indys-historic-steer-in-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.08233,39.78181,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Paradise Pup</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Paradise Pup</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Des Plaines, IL 60018 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8476998590" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(847) 699-8590</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Paradise-Pup/223310754348325" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Paradise-Pup/223310754348325</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Paradise+Pup%2C+1724+S+River+Rd%2C+Des+Plaines%2C+IL+60018&amp;ll=42.022159,-87.876079" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1724 S River Rd<br/>Des Plaines, IL 60018</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Char-Burgers and Three-Layer Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Join host, Guy Fieri, of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, at the Paradise Pup in Des Plaines, IL, a legendary burger joint where folks are lining up for the char-burgers and three-layer fries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Owned</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/des-plaines/paradise-pup-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.87608,42.02216,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hackney&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hackney&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Glenview, IL 60025 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8477245577" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">847-724-5577</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hackneys.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hackneys.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hackney%27s%2C+1241+Harms+Rd%2C+Glenview%2C+IL+60025&amp;ll=42.077655,-87.770632" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1241 Harms Rd<br/>Glenview, IL 60025</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Famous Hackneyburger, Hackney&#x27;s Original French Fried Onions</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This spot has been slinging burgers since original owner Helen &quot;Bebe&quot; Hackney served them with brews on her back porch during the Prohibition era. A standout is The Famous Hackneyburger, served on dark rye with a brick (yes, a brick) of onion rings on the side. As Guy proclaimed, &#x27;&#x27;It&#x27;s all-American, baby.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers<br/>Knockout Burger Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/glenview/hackneys-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.77063,42.07766,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Chuck&#x27;s Southern Comforts Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Chuck&#x27;s Southern Comforts Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Burbank, IL 60459 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7082298700" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(708) 229-8700</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.chuckscafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.chuckscafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Chuck%27s+Southern+Comforts+Cafe%2C+6501+W+79th+St%2C+Burbank%2C+IL+60459&amp;ll=41.748040,-87.782966" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6501 W 79th St<br/>Burbank, IL 60459</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From barbecue to Tex-Mex, Chef Chuck Pine is serving up all types of Southern comfort food. The &amp;quot;incredible&amp;quot; cochinita pibil captured Guy&#x27;s heart with its delicious shredded pork and spicy habanero salsa. Regulars enjoy ordering the full slab of ribs, catfish po&#x27; boy and chicken fried chicken.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Global Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/burbank/chucks-southern-comforts-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.78297,41.74804,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dell Rhea&#x27;s Chicken Basket</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dell Rhea&#x27;s Chicken Basket</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Willowbrook, IL 60527 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6303250780" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(630) 325-0780</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.chickenbasket.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.chickenbasket.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dell+Rhea%27s+Chicken+Basket%2C+645+Joliet+Rd.%2C+Willowbrook%2C+IL+60527&amp;ll=41.745610,-87.939204" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">645 Joliet Rd.<br/>Willowbrook, IL 60527</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Chicken, Mac &#x27;n&#x27; Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy couldn&#x27;t help but drive his fire-red Chevy up to Dell Rhea&#x27;s Chicken Basket. The iconic restaurant off Route 66 makes 2,000 pounds of their world-famous slow-cooked chicken each week. Guy loved the chicken, and nicknamed Chef Patrick Rhea &quot;Captain Creamy&quot; for the scrumptious mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Return to Route 66<br/>All-American All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/willowbrook/dell-rheas-chicken-basket-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.93920,41.74561,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rex Italian Foods</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rex Italian Foods</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Norridge 60706 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7084570177" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">708-457-0177</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://rexitalianfoods.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">rexitalianfoods.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rex+Italian+Foods%2C+4431+N+Harlem+Ave%2C+Norridge+60706&amp;ll=41.961710,-87.806761" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4431 N Harlem Ave<br/>Norridge 60706</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sicilian Schiacciata, Italian Deli Meats</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Following his nonna&#x27;s recipes, Chef Anthony Pinello and his mother are cooking &quot;real deal&quot; Italian food. Guy swooned over the Sicilian schiacciata filled with ham, pepperoni, peppers, mild giardiniera and mozzarella. Customers on-the-go enjoy the homemade frozen soups and Italian deli meats.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Unconventional Comforts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/norridge/rex-italian-foods-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.80676,41.96171,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Marjie&#x27;s Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Marjie&#x27;s Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70119</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.marjiesgrill.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.marjiesgrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Marjie%27s+Grill%2C+320+S+Broad+Ave%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70119&amp;ll=29.956499,-90.095091" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">320 S Broad Ave<br/>New Orleans, LA 70119</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Honey Butter Yardbird, Crispy Pork Knuckles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The food at Marjie&#x27;s Grill is a completely unique amalgmationof Southeast Asian and New Orleans&#x27; influences. Chef Marcus Jacobs combines Gulf Coast ingredients with Thai, Vietnamese and Laotian spices. &quot;You know what you&#x27;re doing,&quot; said Guy, after trying their Honey Butter Yardbird and Crispy Pork Knuckles.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Piling On the Pork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/marjies-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.09509,29.95650,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mahony&#x27;s Po-Boy Shop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mahony&#x27;s Po-Boy Shop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70115 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5048993374" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(504) 899-3374</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mahonyspoboys.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mahonyspoboys.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mahony%27s+Po-Boy+Shop%2C+3454+Magazine+St%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70115&amp;ll=29.922227,-90.090322" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3454 Magazine St<br/>New Orleans, LA 70115</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Peace Maker, Sweet Potato Crunch Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Mahony&#x27;s, Chef Benjamin Wick&#x27;s isn&#x27;t just making sandwiches, he&#x27;s making po&#x27;- boys 22 different ways. Guy chowed-down on the Peace Maker, a po&#x27;- boy stuffed with fried oysters, bacon, and cheddar. For dessert, Guy had a slice of the sweet potato crunch pie.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Super Sandwiches<br/>Po&#x27; Boys, Pasta And Pork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/mahonys-po-boy-shop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.09032,29.92223,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Little Jewel of New Orleans</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Little Jewel of New Orleans</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 91002</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2136200461" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(213) 620-0461</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="littlejewel.la" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">littlejewel.la</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Little+Jewel+of+New+Orleans%2C+207+Ord+St%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+91002&amp;ll=34.060086,-118.238194" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">207 Ord St<br/>Los Angeles, CA 91002</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Little Jewel of New Orleans provides popular dishes based on the rich and varied culinary traditions of the City of New Orleans. Theypride themselves on authenticity, as demonstrated by all of theirsausages, cooking meats,baked goods, desserts and dressingsmade in-house. The Little Jewel of New Orleans also hosts aSouthern market and delicatessen, which makes available many of the popular as well as &quot;harder to find&quot; items from Louisiana (and the South in general), while offering everyday convenience items to the public at large.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Shipped, Sweet and Savory</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/little-jewel-of-new-orleans" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.23819,34.06009,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Katie&#x27;s Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Katie&#x27;s Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70119 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5044886582" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(504) 488-6582</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.katiesinmidcity.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.katiesinmidcity.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Katie%27s+Restaurant%2C+3701+Iberville+St%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70119&amp;ll=29.973086,-90.095906" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3701 Iberville St<br/>New Orleans, LA 70119</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Barge</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Located in New Orleans Mid-City neighborhood, Katie&#x27;s Restaurant is known for serving top-notch local cuisine, including a seafood sandwich so large it&#x27;s known as The Barge. When Guy Fieri swung by on Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, he couldn&#x27;t help but praise the handmade pizza topped with Cajun pork.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Flavortown Favorites<br/>Fully Loaded</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/katies-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.09591,29.97309,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Casamento&#x27;s Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Casamento&#x27;s Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70115 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://casamentosrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">casamentosrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Casamento%27s+Restaurant%2C+4330+Magazine+St.%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70115&amp;ll=29.920594,-90.101054" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4330 Magazine St.<br/>New Orleans, LA 70115</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Louisiana Oysters, Deep Fried Oysters, Oyster Stew</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crispy fried oysters on soft (not crusty) white bread make the restaurant&#x27;s popular dish a perfect alterna-po&amp;rsquo;boy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cookin&#x27; It Old School</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/casamentos-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.10105,29.92059,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Casamento&#x27;s Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Casamento&#x27;s Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70115 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5048959761" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">504-895-9761</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.casamentosrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.casamentosrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Casamento%27s+Restaurant%2C+4330+Magazine+St.%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70115&amp;ll=29.920594,-90.101054" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4330 Magazine St.<br/>New Orleans, LA 70115</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Louisiana Oysters, Deep Fried Oysters, Oyster Stew</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Casamento&#x27;s Restaurant, the raw oysters are &quot;a tradition,&quot; says Guy Fieri. Family-owned since 1919, the classic NOLA establishment is also known for irresistible fried-oyster sandwiches, fried shrimp and soft-shell crab.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: From the Sea<br/>Cookin&#x27; It Old School</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/casamentos-restaurant-restaurant2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.10105,29.92059,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cafe on the Route</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cafe on the Route</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baxter Springs, KS 66713 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6208565646" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(620) 856-5646</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cafeontheroute.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cafeontheroute.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cafe+on+the+Route%2C+1101+Military+Ave.%2C+Baxter+Springs%2C+KS+66713&amp;ll=37.024650,-94.735278" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1101 Military Ave.<br/>Baxter Springs, KS 66713</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Aztec Chicken, Biscuits and Gravy, Steak and Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Triple D&#x27;s road trip across Route 66, Guy discovered Cafe on the Route and their killer crusted catfish. As for the legendary kicks - they&#x27;ve got that, too. How about Aztec chicken with a rum glaze, avocado and chiles? For a decadent dessert, enjoy deep-fried cheesecake.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Route 66</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ks/baxter-springs/cafe-on-the-route-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.73528,37.02465,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>BBQ Shack</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">BBQ Shack</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Paola, KS 66071 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9132945908" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(913) 294-5908</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thebbqshack.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thebbqshack.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=BBQ+Shack%2C+1613+E+Peoria+St%2C+Paola%2C+KS+66071&amp;ll=38.570081,-94.858184" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1613 E Peoria St<br/>Paola, KS 66071</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ, Chicken Wings, &quot;Atomic Buffalo Turds&quot; Jalapeno Poppers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy Fieri, host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, stops by BBQ Central in Paola, KS, and tucks into some real deal, authentic barbecue.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Real Deal BBQ<br/>Amazing Appetizers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ks/paola/bbq-shack-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-94.85818,38.57008,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Avery&#x27;s on Tulane</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Avery&#x27;s on Tulane</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans 70119 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.averysontulane.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.averysontulane.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Avery%27s+on+Tulane%2C+2510+Tulane+Ave%2C+New+Orleans+70119&amp;ll=29.960541,-90.088315" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2510 Tulane Ave<br/>New Orleans 70119</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Husband and wife team Justin and Christy Pitard are putting their twist on local favorites at Avery&#x27;s on Tulane. Don&#x27;t miss the Oysters Rockefeller Po Boy, made with crispy fried oysters and creamy spinach sauce on a garlic-butter baguette. &quot;That is gangster,&quot; raved Guy. He also loved the Fried Potato Salad, saying, &quot;I am officially, 100% ripping that off.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eating Up New Orleans</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/averys-on-tulane-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.08831,29.96054,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Wallace Station</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Wallace Station</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Versailles, KY 40383 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8598465161" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(859) 846-5161</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.wallacestation.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.wallacestation.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Wallace+Station%2C+3854+Old+Frankfort+Pike%2C+Versailles%2C+KY+40383&amp;ll=38.121252,-84.693978" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3854 Old Frankfort Pike<br/>Versailles, KY 40383</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwiches, Fresh Bread, White Cheddar Mornay</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Check out Wallace Station in Midway, KY, a sandwich joint putting local flavor into their homemade bread, on Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, with host, Guy Fieri.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Farm To Table</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/versailles/wallace-station-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.69398,38.12125,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Virgil&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Virgil&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bellevue, KY 41073 &middot; &#9733; 2.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8594913287" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(859) 491-3287</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.virgilscafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.virgilscafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Virgil%27s+Cafe%2C+710+Fairfield+Ave%2C+Bellevue%2C+KY+41073&amp;ll=39.108678,-84.479954" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">710 Fairfield Ave<br/>Bellevue, KY 41073</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Andouille Sausage</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For a Triple D first, Guy headed to Virgil&#x27;s Cafe for the fried-to-perfection frog legs. Virgil&#x27;s scratch-made philosophy translates to every inch of the menu, from the Chicken and Andouille Etouffee made with housemade sausage and their very own garlic bread to the perfectly dreamy bananas Foster.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Porkapalooza</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/bellevue/virgils-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.47995,39.10868,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rick&#x27;s White Light Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rick&#x27;s White Light Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Frankfort, KY 40601 &middot; &#9733; 4.6 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5026969104" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(502) 696-9104</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rickswhitelightdiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rickswhitelightdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rick%27s+White+Light+Diner%2C+114+Bridge+St%2C+Frankfort%2C+KY+40601&amp;ll=38.195497,-84.879058" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">114 Bridge St<br/>Frankfort, KY 40601</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oyster Po&#x27; Boy with French Bread, Chef Rick&#x27;s Classic French Bread, Louisiana Crawfish Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The regulars at Rick&#x27;s White Light Diner say you&#x27;ll get lunch and a show when you order from Rick Paul. Guy had front-row seats to the dinner entertainment as Rick served up his authentic Cajun cuisine, like Louisiana crawfish pie and oyster po&#x27; boys. Guy says Rick &amp;quot;can&#x27;t even spell bland.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You Called It</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/frankfort/ricks-white-light-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.87906,38.19550,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Parkette Drive In</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Parkette Drive In</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lexington, KY 40505 &middot; &#9733; 3.1 (15 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8592548723" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">859-254-8723</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.theparkette.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.theparkette.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Parkette+Drive+In%2C+1230+E+New+Circle+Rd.%2C+Lexington%2C+KY+40505&amp;ll=38.031266,-84.452952" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1230 E New Circle Rd.<br/>Lexington, KY 40505</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Double Burger, Parkette&#x27;s Famous Kentucky Poor Boy</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Parkette is bringing back the golden age of drive-in eateries the old-fashioned way, with classics like the Fisherman&#x27;s Special and banana splits. Try their Kentucky-style &amp;quot;Poor Boy,&amp;quot; double stacked and loaded with fillings, for an irresistible old-school burger your taste buds won&#x27;t soon forget.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Top 10 Burgers<br/>You Found Em</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/lexington/parkette-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.45295,38.03127,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>J.J.McBrewster&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">J.J.McBrewster&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lexington, KY 40503 &middot; &#9733; 2.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8592240040" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(859) 224-0040</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://jjmcbrewsters.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">jjmcbrewsters.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=J.J.McBrewster%27s%2C+3101+Clays+Mill+Rd+%23301%2C+Lexington%2C+KY+40503&amp;ll=38.002837,-84.545874" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3101 Clays Mill Rd #301<br/>Lexington, KY 40503</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Turkey with Melon Sauce, Almond Candy</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Named after the family&#x27;s best friend, J.J. McBrewster&#x27;s is known for scratch-made cooking. Try the hickory-smoked goat platter and mutton dinner. Guy claims the barbecue Melon Sauce at this Western Kentucky eatery should be renamed the &amp;quot;Rich Mahogany&amp;quot; for its dark, smoky flavor.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sauced and Spiced</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/lexington/jjmcbrewsters-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.54587,38.00284,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Smokey Valley Truck Stop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Smokey Valley Truck Stop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Olive Hill, KY 41164 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6062865001" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(606) 286-5001</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/olive-hill/smokey-valley-truck-stop-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/olive-hill/smokey-valley-truck-stop-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Smokey+Valley+Truck+Stop%2C+60+Bond+Ct%2C+Olive+Hill%2C+KY+41164&amp;ll=38.298683,-83.209033" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">60 Bond Ct<br/>Olive Hill, KY 41164</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Coconut Cream Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smokey Valley Truck Stop lost the gas station part of its business years ago, but the locals kept coming. Guy had to check out the &amp;quot;just-like-Mom-used-to-make&amp;quot; cooking, including fluffy biscuits with handmade sausage gravy, giant smoky burgers and a coconut cream pie topped with toasted coconut.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Like Mama Made</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/olive-hill/smokey-valley-truck-stop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-83.20903,38.29868,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Irish Rover</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Irish Rover</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Louisville 40206 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5028993544" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">502-899-3544</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.theirishroverky.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.theirishroverky.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Irish+Rover%2C+2319+Frankfort+Ave%2C+Louisville+40206&amp;ll=38.253414,-85.701779" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2319 Frankfort Ave<br/>Louisville 40206</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Louisville spot evokes the flavors of Ireland with its hearty dishes inspired by owner Michael Reidy&#x27;s homeland. &quot;Righteous,&quot; Guy declared after tucking into cabbage rolls stuffed with a wine-and-whiskey-laced mixture of ground lamb, vegetables and seasonings. Another standout is the Cottage Pie, which starts with a comforting stew composed of beef, potatoes, vegetables and Guinness. Once ready, the stew is ladled into a sourdough bread bowl, then topped with potatoes and shredded Cheddar cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef, Lamb and Pig</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/louisville/irish-rover-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-85.70178,38.25341,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Shanty</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Shanty</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wadsworth, IL 60083 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8473360262" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">847-336-0262</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.theshantyrestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.theshantyrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Shanty%2C+38995+N+US+Hwy+41%2C+Wadsworth%2C+IL+60083&amp;ll=42.428646,-87.937448" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">38995 N US Hwy 41<br/>Wadsworth, IL 60083</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Steaks, Whiskey Burger, Tequila and Orange Salmon and Blackened Conch Filet Mignon</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Don&#x27;t judge a book by its cover at this 80-year-old joint serving classic burgers, steaks and pasta dishes. Try the best-selling Whiskey Shrimp that Guy called &quot;dynamite.&quot; Surf &#x27;n&#x27; turf lovers should indulge in the conch and filet mignon duo that&#x27;s got a bit of Cajun spice.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ultimate Bacon Fest<br/>Dives Worth a Drive<br/>Triple D Nation: Poke, Pork and Chicken Parm</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/wadsworth/the-shanty-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.93745,42.42865,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Charlie Parker&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Charlie Parker&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Springfield, IL 62704 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2172412104" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">217-241-2104</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.charlieparkersdiner.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.charlieparkersdiner.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Charlie+Parker%27s%2C+700+North+St%2C+Springfield%2C+IL+62704&amp;ll=39.766003,-89.663595" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">700 North St<br/>Springfield, IL 62704</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Horseshoe Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Housed in a former military Quonset hut (think of a giant metal meatloaf), Charlie Parker&#x27;s is serious about its portion sizes. Guy loved the 16-inch pancakes but had a field day with the &amp;quot;Horsehoe&amp;quot; dish, made to order with your choice of bread and meat and topped with cheese sauce and fries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big Bites<br/>Regional Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/springfield/charlie-parkers-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-89.66360,39.76600,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Seafood Lady</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Seafood Lady</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Louisville, KY 40203 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5022109381" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">502-210-9381</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/seafoodlady502/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/seafoodlady502</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Seafood+Lady%2C+617+W+Oak+St%2C+Louisville%2C+KY+40203&amp;ll=38.235397,-85.764565" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">617 W Oak St<br/>Louisville, KY 40203</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Full Combo Platter, The Hulk</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Locals head to this former tire shop for a taste of seafood served Florida-style. Owner Nichelle Thurston lures in the crowds with delectable dishes made from her grandfather&#x27;s recipes. One bite of the full combo platter and Guy was hooked. This seafood-centric dish comes heaped with jumbo shrimps, a snow crab cluster, smoked sausages, an ear of corn and a Cajun boiled egg, all doused in a Cayenne-spiked sauce. Another hit is The Hulk: a housemade waffle topped with fried lobster and shrimp.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mega Mouthfuls</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/louisville/the-seafood-lady-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-85.76456,38.23540,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Table Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Table Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Louisville, KY 40203 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tablecafe.org/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tablecafe.org</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Table+Cafe%2C+1800+Portland+Ave%2C+Louisville%2C+KY+40203&amp;ll=38.264528,-85.777648" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1800 Portland Ave<br/>Louisville, KY 40203</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Pork Sandwich, Smoked Chicken Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Community is at the heart of The Table, which offers fresh American eats made from locally sourced ingredients. Meals here are pay-what-you-can, with some diners opting to help out around the cafe in lieu of plunking down cash. Menu mainstays include the smoked pork sandwich. The pork butt is hit with a barbecue spice rub before being smoked slow and low. The shredded meat is heaped onto a kaiser roll, then topped with housemade condiments: chili mayo and a pickled relish known as chow-chow.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey-giving</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/louisville/the-table-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-85.77765,38.26453,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bourree</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bourree</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70118 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5045104040" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">504-510-4040</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bourreenola.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bourreenola.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bourree%2C+1510+South+Carrollton+Ave%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70118&amp;ll=29.949833,-90.127483" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1510 South Carrollton Ave<br/>New Orleans, LA 70118</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hot Sausage Meat Pies, Daiquiris, Spicy Shrimp Boudin, Beef Tallow Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy heads to this little Cajun smoke house for a righteous taste of New Orleans. Their flaky hot sausage meat pies are cooled down with a rockin&#x27; house-made poblano ranch and the beef tallow fries are &quot;stupid good,&quot; according to Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Pied to Fried</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/bourree-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.12748,29.94983,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Saucy Porka</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Saucy Porka</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago 60606 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3122852303" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(312) 285-2303</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://saucyporka.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">saucyporka.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Saucy+Porka%2C+335+S+Franklin+St%2C+Chicago+60606&amp;ll=41.877149,-87.635015" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">335 S Franklin St<br/>Chicago 60606</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Asian Style Paella, Pork Pozole</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Latin fare meets traditional Asian dishes at this Chicago hot spot. From pork carnitas pho soup to arrozo con edamame, Saucy Porka brilliantly balances the fusion of flavors. We recommend trying the Asian Style Paella (Chinese Lap Chang pork sausage, spicy sausage, pork carnitas, edamame, bean sprouts and scallions) or the Pork Pozole (smoky guajillo peppers and tomato base soup served with pickled cabbage, cilantro and corn tortillas).</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fusion of Flavors</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/saucy-pork" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.63502,41.87715,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tacopocalypse</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tacopocalypse</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Des Moines 50309</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5155560571" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(515) 556-0571</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ia/des-moines/tacopocalypse" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ia/des-moines/tacopocalypse</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tacopocalypse%2C+407+East+5th+St.%2C+Des+Moines+50309&amp;ll=41.590072,-93.611117" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">407 East 5th St.<br/>Des Moines 50309</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Vegetarian Seitan Andouille Burrito</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">With a chef who used to be a metal musician, Tacopocalypse naturally specializes in the realm where creative meets outrageous. The taco and burrito flavor combinations are incredibly unique here, with fillings like wasabi brisket and bacon chorizo, and plenty of vegan and vegetarian options, like andouille-spiced seitan. Start with the masa fries, with a Guy-approved topping of kimchi and queso.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fish, Fries and Feet</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ia/des-moines/tacopocalypse" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.61112,41.59007,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Smokey D&#x27;s BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Smokey D&#x27;s BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Des Moines, IA 50309 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5152432747" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(515) 243-2747</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.smokeydsbbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.smokeydsbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Smokey+D%27s+BBQ%2C+5055+NW+2nd+St.%2C+Des+Moines%2C+IA+50309&amp;ll=41.651764,-93.619082" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5055 NW 2nd St.<br/>Des Moines, IA 50309</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Apple Dumpling, Smoked Wings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">There&#x27;s a reason Smokey D&#x27;s racks up so many awards: The team prepares some of the best BBQ in the Midwest, with three full smokers turning out brisket, ribs and more around the clock. You can&#x27;t go wrong with any of the meats, but Guy recommends the smoked chicken wings in particular, which come smothered in your choice of house sauces. For a decadent finish, order the apple dumpling. This sweet yet tangy dish comprises crisp dough and syrup-soaked soft dough, with tart apple tucked inside.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Flavortown Favorites<br/>Fresh Fish &amp; Funky Chicken<br/>Dynamite Desserts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ia/des-moines/smokey-ds-bbq" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.61908,41.65176,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Patton&#x27;s Restaurant &amp; Catering</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Patton&#x27;s Restaurant &amp; Catering</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Des Moines, IA 50316 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5152652203" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(515) 265-2203</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pattonsrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pattonsrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Patton%27s+Restaurant+%26+Catering%2C+1552+East+Grand+Ave.%2C+Suite+D%2C+Des+Moines%2C+IA+50316&amp;ll=41.594619,-93.592990" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1552 East Grand Ave., Suite D<br/>Des Moines, IA 50316</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern Fried Chicken and Red Velvet Waffles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A little taste of Louisiana in the Midwest, this authentic Southern gem spins out convincing takes on classics like fried fish, barbecue ribs and a modern take on fried chicken and waffles, with sides like red beans and rice that left Guy speechless.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Chowfest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ia/des-moines/pattons-restaurant-and-catering" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.59299,41.59462,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mi Patria</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mi Patria</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">West Des Moines, IA 50266 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5152222755" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(515) 222-2755</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mipatriaecuador.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mipatriaecuador.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mi+Patria%2C+1410+22nd+St.%2C+West+Des+Moines%2C+IA+50266&amp;ll=41.594648,-93.736139" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1410 22nd St.<br/>West Des Moines, IA 50266</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Set in an unassuming strip mall, this Des Moines hot spot might at first look like an unlikely place to serve amazing Ecuadorian cuisine. But locals flock to Mi Patria for authentic South American ceviche and empanadas.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fresh Fish &amp; Funky Chicken</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ia/des-moines/mi-patria" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.73614,41.59465,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>George the Chili King</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">George the Chili King</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Des Moines, IA 50310 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5152779433" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(515) 277-9433</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.georgethechiliking.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.georgethechiliking.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=George+the+Chili+King%2C+5722+Hickman+Rd.%2C+Des+Moines%2C+IA+50310&amp;ll=41.614679,-93.696936" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5722 Hickman Rd.<br/>Des Moines, IA 50310</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Specialty Dish: Chili; Tenderloin Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bet you didn&#x27;t know there was a royal family of chili, but the residents of Des Moines named the original owner of this classic drive-in the Chili King, and the rest is history. Obviously, the name of the game is chili, but Guy also recommends the Tenderloin - a Des Moines staple made from tenderized fried pork shoulder. Try it all without ever having to leave your car.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oldies But Goodies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ia/des-moines/george-the-chili-king" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.69694,41.61468,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Flying Mango</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Flying Mango</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Des Moines 50310</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5152554111" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">515-255-4111</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://flyingmango.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">flyingmango.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Flying+Mango%2C+4345+Hickman+Rd.%2C+Des+Moines+50310&amp;ll=41.615266,-93.677682" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4345 Hickman Rd.<br/>Des Moines 50310</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Catfish Cakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Flying Mango&#x27;s unique name is a hint at the bold, original food it serves. Chef Mike Wedeking offers a menu of Southern barbecue with Caribbean influences. The Memphis-style ribs are popular, but Guy recommends trying the house-smoked catfish cakes.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Fried and Smoked<br/>Takeout: Sendin&#x27; the Surf &amp; Turf<br/>Fish, Fries and Feet</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ia/des-moines/flying-mango" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-93.67768,41.61527,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dixie Quick&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dixie Quick&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Council Bluffs, IA 51503 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7122564140" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(712) 256-4140</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.dixiequicks.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.dixiequicks.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dixie+Quick%27s%2C+157+W.+Broadway%2C+Council+Bluffs%2C+IA+51503&amp;ll=41.262286,-95.845477" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">157 W. Broadway<br/>Council Bluffs, IA 51503</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eggs Benedict, Texas Chile Pepper Steak</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dixie Quick&#x27;s owner, Rene Orduna, grew up working at his family&#x27;s Mexican restaurant, and then traveled the world. So when he got to Council Bluffs, Iowa, he put everything he learned into one eclectic menu. Guy said the Texas Chile Pepper Steak was &#x27;&#x27;one of the best pepper steaks I&#x27;ve ever had.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Where the Locals Eat</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ia/council-bluffs/dixie-quicks-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-95.84548,41.26229,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Momma&#x27;s Mustard, Pickles &amp; BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Momma&#x27;s Mustard, Pickles &amp; BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Louisville, KY 40207 &middot; &#9733; 4.1 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5029386262" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">502-938-6262</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://mommasbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">mommasbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Momma%27s+Mustard%2C+Pickles+%26+BBQ%2C+102+Bauer+Ave%2C+Louisville%2C+KY+40207&amp;ll=38.252881,-85.662259" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">102 Bauer Ave<br/>Louisville, KY 40207</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Wings, Beef Ribs, Pickles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kansas native Chad Cooley delivers the smoky flavors of his home state to Kentucky by way of this barbecue joint. &quot;Good smoke, nice rub&quot; Guy said after tearing into a basket of chicken wings. The wings are hit with a spice-laden dry rub, smoked over hickory wood, fried and then dusted once more with dry rub before being served with a side of buttermilk ranch dressing. Another standout are the beef ribs, which are paired with pickles made from a recipe handed down from Cooley&#x27;s mom.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Carnivore Creations</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/louisville/mommas-mustard-pickles-and-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-85.66226,38.25288,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Grind Burger Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Grind Burger Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Louisville, KY 40206</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5028517333" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">502-851-7333</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.grindburgerkitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.grindburgerkitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Grind+Burger+Kitchen%2C+829+E+Market+St%2C+Louisville%2C+KY+40206&amp;ll=38.253446,-85.736624" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">829 E Market St<br/>Louisville, KY 40206</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Veggie Burger, Cuban Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owners Liz and Jesse Huot started off serving grass-fed beef burgers from a tiny trailer, but demand soon grew to the point that they were able to open a brick-and-mortar spot. In addition to the beef patties, they offer a veggie option that left Guy impressed. &quot;Such phenomenal texture,&quot; he said of the patty, which is made from a well-seasoned blend of roasted vegetables, quinoa, pumpkin seeds and more. It&#x27;s slathered with smoked tomato ketchup, dressed with lettuce and tomato, and placed on a fluffy bun.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brunch, Bologna and Burgers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ky/louisville/grind-burger-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-85.73662,38.25345,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jersey&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jersey&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Carmel, IN 46032 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3178467760" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(317) 846-7760</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/in/carmel/jersey-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/in/carmel/jersey-cafe-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jersey%27s+Cafe%2C+13710+N+Meridian+St%2C+Carmel%2C+IN+46032&amp;ll=39.987640,-86.138685" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">13710 N Meridian St<br/>Carmel, IN 46032</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wildwood Cheese Steak, Chicken Salad Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jersey native Blair Laing is making Garden State classics and 33 different cheese steaks. Guy fell head over heels when he bit into the Wildwood Cheese Steak with blue cheese, meatballs and rib eye. The chicken salad sandwich with homemade bread and the loaded chips with BBQ sauce also impressed.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ultimate Bacon Fest<br/>Fully Loaded</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/in/carmel/jersey-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.13868,39.98764,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Triple XXX Family Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Triple XXX Family Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">West Lafayette, IN 47906 &middot; &#9733; 4.1 (14 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7657435373" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">765-743-5373</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.triplexxxfamilyrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.triplexxxfamilyrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Triple+XXX+Family+Restaurant%2C+2+N+Salisbury+St%2C+West+Lafayette%2C+IN+47906&amp;ll=40.422708,-86.905398" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2 N Salisbury St<br/>West Lafayette, IN 47906</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Double Cheeseburger, Triple XXX Root Beer</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple XXX is named after a brand of root beer that has been served here since the 1920s, but it&#x27;s the burgers that have put this spot on the map. Made from sirloin butt that&#x27;s ground in-house, these &quot;chopped steaks&quot; won Guy over when he stopped in on Triple D. &quot;That&#x27;s a good burger,&quot; he declared of one option featuring two cheese-smothered patties nestled on a toasted bun.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers<br/>Knockout Burger Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/in/west-lafayette/triple-x-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.90540,40.42271,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Zydeco&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Zydeco&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Mooresville, IN 46158 &middot; &#9733; 4.9 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3178343900" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(317) 834-3900</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.zydecos.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.zydecos.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Zydeco%27s%2C+11+E+Main+St%2C+Mooresville%2C+IN+46158&amp;ll=39.612567,-86.374356" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">11 E Main St<br/>Mooresville, IN 46158</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tasso, Boudin, Spicy Barbecued Shrimp</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">New Orleans native Chef Carter Hutchinson has proclaimed Zydeco the Cajun embassy of Indiana. Guy loved the combination of flavors in the spicy barbecued shrimp with Cajun smoked pork. The boudin according to Guy was &amp;quot;super tender&amp;quot; and he liked the Creole mustard on top.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homemade &amp; Homebrewed</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/in/mooresville/zydecos-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.37436,39.61257,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>South Side Soda Shop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">South Side Soda Shop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Goshen, IN 46526 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5745343790" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">574-534-3790</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.southsidesodashopdiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.southsidesodashopdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=South+Side+Soda+Shop%2C+1122+S+Main+St%2C+Goshen%2C+IN+46526&amp;ll=41.571753,-85.829803" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1122 S Main St<br/>Goshen, IN 46526</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chili, Homemade Sandwiches, Phosphates, Malts, Shakes, Green River Soda</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This old-school spot serves up American classics like a beef and bean chili laden with plenty of spices that Guy calls &quot;a home run.&quot; Owner Nick Boyd also keeps customers with a sweet tooth satisfied by churning out fresh, flaky pastries, while his wife, Charity, serves &#x27;50s-style floats and phosphates. One cult favorite is the Green River Soda, a retro flavor that&#x27;s a big hit with the kids, thanks to its super-sweet taste and its ability to turn your tongue green if you guzzle enough of it.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Retro<br/>Dynamite Desserts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/in/goshen/south-side-soda-shop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-85.82980,41.57175,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Zest! Exciting Food Creations</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Zest! Exciting Food Creations</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Indianapolis, IN 46220 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.zestexcitingfood.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.zestexcitingfood.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Zest%21+Exciting+Food+Creations%2C+1134+E+54th+St%2C+Indianapolis%2C+IN+46220&amp;ll=39.851459,-86.138688" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1134 E 54th St<br/>Indianapolis, IN 46220</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Asiago Cheese Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All the recipes at Zest! come from owner Valerie Vanderpool&#x27;s imagination -- and lucky for Guy, she&#x27;s willing to share. On DDD, Guy demolished the tomato bon bons. As for the fried chicken breaded in Asiago cheese and served with rosemary-Gorgonzola polenta, that&#x27;s just &#x27;golden-funka-cruncha.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bar Food and Bon Bons</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/in/indianapolis/zest-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.13869,39.85146,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Barking Dog Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Barking Dog Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Indianapolis, IN 46205 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.barkingdogindy.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.barkingdogindy.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Barking+Dog+Cafe%2C+115+E+49th+St%2C+Indianapolis%2C+IN+46205&amp;ll=39.842654,-86.154063" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">115 E 49th St<br/>Indianapolis, IN 46205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">&quot;Bark Lard&quot; BLT</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At The Barking Dog, you can feed yourself a hearty plate of cherry pie or the signature &quot;Bark Lard&quot; BLT with special tomato jam. But you can also feed your dog. As Guy discovered on Triple D, just tell them your dog&#x27;s name and they&#x27;ll make a special platter for your favorite barker.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Signature Twists</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/in/indianapolis/the-barking-dog-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.15406,39.84265,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Tamale Place</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Tamale Place</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Indianapolis, IN 46224 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3172489771" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(317) 248-9771</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thetamaleplace.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thetamaleplace.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Tamale+Place%2C+5226+Rockville+Rd%2C+Indianapolis%2C+IN+46224&amp;ll=39.765842,-86.249264" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5226 Rockville Rd<br/>Indianapolis, IN 46224</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Tamales</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Each of the 150,000 tamales made each year at The Tamale Place are handmade and hand-tied. As Guy learned on DDD, that means the masa for the tamales is made with freshly ground corn every day. It&#x27;s also used for everything from tacos to tortilla chips to the just-like-grandma&#x27;s apple pecan tamale.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Real Deal Mexican<br/>You Can Only Get It Here</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/in/indianapolis/the-tamale-place-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.24926,39.76584,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>3 Sisters Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">3 Sisters Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Indianapolis, IN 46220 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3172575556" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">317-257-5556</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/3-Sisters-Cafe-140804079297532/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/3-Sisters-Cafe-140804079297532</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=3+Sisters+Cafe%2C+6360+Guilford+Ave%2C+Indianapolis%2C+IN+46220&amp;ll=39.871923,-86.143117" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6360 Guilford Ave<br/>Indianapolis, IN 46220</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ham-and-Cheese Sandwich, Raspberry Lemon Corn Cakes, Blueberry Goat Cheese Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This 1896 Victorian house serves both vegetarians and meat lovers alike with a Southern spin. The ham-and-cheese sandwich stuffed with wilted kale and bacon has been deemed &amp;quot;outstanding&amp;quot; by Guy. And don&#x27;t sleep on the housemade desserts: Guy recommends both the raspberry lemon corn cakes and the blueberry goat cheese pie.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Signature Sandwiches<br/>Dynamite Desserts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/in/indianapolis/3-sisters-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-86.14312,39.87192,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Creole Creamery - Uptown</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Creole Creamery - Uptown</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70115 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5048948680" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">504-894-8680</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.creolecreamery.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.creolecreamery.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Creole+Creamery+-+Uptown%2C+4924+Prytania+St%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70115&amp;ll=29.924461,-90.108545" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4924 Prytania St<br/>New Orleans, LA 70115</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sundaes, Ice Cream</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ever tried Lavender Honey-flavored ice cream? How about Sweet Potato Sassafras Praline? The only place that has unique flavors like these is The Creole Creamery in New Orleans. Guy called Head Chef Bryan Gilmore a wizard, and it&#x27;s easy to see why - he&#x27;s made over 400 flavors of ice cream.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brain Freeze</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/the-creole-creamery-uptown-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.10855,29.92446,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Old Coffeepot Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Old Coffeepot Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">New Orleans, LA 70116 &middot; &#9733; 2.6 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5045243500" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(504) 524.3500</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.theoldcoffeepot.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.theoldcoffeepot.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Old+Coffeepot+Restaurant%2C+714+Saint+Peter+St%2C+New+Orleans%2C+LA+70116&amp;ll=29.958158,-90.065160" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">714 Saint Peter St<br/>New Orleans, LA 70116</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jambalaya and Blackened Red Fish</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Old Coffeepot is more than 100 years old and yet its recipes embody a fresh, classic take on New Orleans French Quarter cuisine. It was the first time Guy witnessed tomato sauce in jambalaya. The from-scratch green bean casserole was also seriously tasty with its thick cremini mushroom sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Signature Twists</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/la/new-orleans/the-old-coffee-pot-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-90.06516,29.95816,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Twisted Soul Cookhouse &amp; Pours</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Twisted Soul Cookhouse &amp; Pours</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlanta, GA 30318 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.twistedsoulatl.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.twistedsoulatl.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Twisted+Soul+Cookhouse+%26+Pours%2C+1133+Huff+Rd+NW%2C+Atlanta%2C+GA+30318&amp;ll=33.789128,-84.426118" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1133 Huff Rd NW<br/>Atlanta, GA 30318</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern Seafood Louie, Southern Marinated Fried Chicken, Sweet Tea Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Customers flock to Twisted Soul Cookhouse &amp; Pours in Atlanta, for Chef Deborah Vantrece&#x27;s globally-inspired fusion soul food. Guy loved the Southern Seafood Louie Salad, a play on the traditional Crab Louis salad, with poached crab, shrimp and lobster, roasted corn vinaigrette, avocado-spiked hoe cakes and mango vinaigrette over baby arugula. &quot;There&#x27;re not many salads that I would order again. I would order that every time,&quot; he said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Whole Lotta Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/twisted-soul-cookhouse-and-pours-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.42612,33.78913,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Highlander</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Highlander</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlanta 30308 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4048720060" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(404) 872-0060</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thehighlanderatlanta.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thehighlanderatlanta.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Highlander%2C+931+Monroe+Dr%2C+Atlanta+30308&amp;ll=33.779733,-84.367600" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">931 Monroe Dr<br/>Atlanta 30308</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jamaican Jerk Chili, Jalapeno Corn Fritters, Pasta-Rella (Mozzarella Sticks)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A strip mall doesn&#x27;t sound like the usual location for a dive bar, but Jeff Merback and his crew at The Highlander in Atlanta already have 16 years of success under their belt. Guy was blown away by Head Chef Ice Jahumpa&#x27;s mozzarella sticks, which are wrapped in pasta prior to frying.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Amazing Appetizers<br/>Triple D Nation: Beef, Barbecue and Bar Food<br/>Bar Food</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/the-highlander-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.36760,33.77973,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Silver Skillet</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Silver Skillet</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlanta, GA 30318 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4048741388" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">404-874-1388</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thesilverskillet.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thesilverskillet.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Silver+Skillet%2C+200+14th+St%2C+Atlanta%2C+GA+30318&amp;ll=33.786238,-84.394261" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">200 14th St<br/>Atlanta, GA 30318</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Skillet Country Ham, Chicken Fried Steak, Lemon Icebox Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">As a quintessential Southern diner, The Silver Skillet has been featured in country music videos and TV shows, including Triple D. Since 1967, they&#x27;ve been serving all the stick-to-your-ribs classics, including the famed Lemon Icebox Pie and Guy&#x27;s favorite: grits and ham.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Real-Deal Diners<br/>Just Like Yesterday</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/the-silver-skillet-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.39426,33.78624,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The General Muir</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The General Muir</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlanta, GA 30329</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6789279131" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">678-927-9131</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thegeneralmuir.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thegeneralmuir.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+General+Muir%2C+1540+Avenue+Pl%2C+Atlanta%2C+GA+30329&amp;ll=33.801037,-84.327484" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1540 Avenue Pl<br/>Atlanta, GA 30329</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Chicken Dinner, Bagels</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Flashes of the South find their way into Chef-Owner Todd Ginsberg&#x27;s modern Jewish deli. Locals throw elbows over his fried chicken dinners on Fridays. They often feature pastrami-braised collard greens. Ginsberg cites one of the biggest links between Jewish and Southern cuisine as preserving meat, and more specifically, the less prized cuts of meat.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef It Up</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/the-general-muir-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.32748,33.80104,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pijiu Belly</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pijiu Belly</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlanta 30318</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://pijiubelly.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">pijiubelly.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pijiu+Belly%2C+678+10th+St.+NW%2C+Atlanta+30318&amp;ll=33.781310,-84.409697" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">678 10th St. NW<br/>Atlanta 30318</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crispy Pork Belly Sandwich, Yangnyeom Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For amazing Asian-fusion cuisine in Atlanta head to Pijiu Belly.Don&#x27;t miss the Crispy Pork Belly Sandwich smothered in house-made peach hoisin sauce or the hot and spicy Yangnyeom Chicken.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Belly, Beef and Bratwurst</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/pijiu-belly-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.40970,33.78131,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Joy Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Joy Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlanta, GA 30305 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4048160306" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">404-816-0306</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://joycafeatl.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">joycafeatl.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Joy+Cafe%2C+316+Pharr+Rd+NE%2C+Atlanta%2C+GA+30305&amp;ll=33.837385,-84.377220" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">316 Pharr Rd NE<br/>Atlanta, GA 30305</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Joy&#x27;s Famous Shrimp &amp; Grits, Biscuit and Gravy</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Guy was craving elevated Southern classics while in Atlanta, he headed to a somewhat unexpected spot: a strip mall. Tucked away in this nondescript locale is a charming cafe dishing up hearty comfort foods. Chef-Owner Joy Beber&#x27;s passion shines through in dishes like the flavorful shrimp and grits laced with a housemade hot sauce and the gravy-smothered biscuits topped with tequila-spiked chorizo.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homeland Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/joy-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.37722,33.83738,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fox Bros. Bar-B-Q</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fox Bros. Bar-B-Q</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlanta 30307 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4045774030" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">404-577-4030</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.foxbrosbbq.com/index.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foxbrosbbq.com/index.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fox+Bros.+Bar-B-Q%2C+1238+DeKalb+Ave+NE%2C+Atlanta+30307&amp;ll=33.761066,-84.347476" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1238 DeKalb Ave NE<br/>Atlanta 30307</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fox Bros. &quot;Burger,&quot; Everything Plate</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Twin brothers Jonathan and Justin Fox are serving up a hearty taste of their home state at this Texan barbecue joint in Atlanta, where they smoke around 10,000 pounds of pork and brisket weekly. Guy is a fan of the Fox Bros. &quot;Burger,&quot; which stars hickory-smoked brisket topped with a melty pimento cheese patty, peppered bacon, pickles, tomato and onion, all on a toasted bun.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Biscuits to Brisket<br/>Triple D Nation: Chili Three Ways<br/>Takeout: Cross-Country Delivery</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/fox-bros-bar-b-q-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.34748,33.76107,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hankook Taqueria</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hankook Taqueria</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlanta 30318 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4043528881" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(404) 352-8881</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hankooktaqueria.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hankooktaqueria.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hankook+Taqueria%2C+1341+Collier+Rd.%2C+Atlanta+30318&amp;ll=33.811491,-84.431673" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1341 Collier Rd.<br/>Atlanta 30318</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bibim-Bop</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A good meal for Alton Brown typically costs $10 or less. It&#x27;s no wonder then that he fell in love with Hankook Taqueria&#x27;s Bibim-bop made with sliced rib eye, soy sauce, fried egg and the red pepper &quot;sweet heat&quot; sauce. At $7 this Korean street food goes a long way, especially with some sesame fries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mega Meat and Sweet Treats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/hankook-taqueria-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.43167,33.81149,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Folk Art</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Folk Art</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlanta, GA 30342 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4045374493" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">404-537-4493</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://folkartrestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">folkartrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Folk+Art%2C+465+North+Highland+Ave+NE%2C+Atlanta%2C+GA+30342&amp;ll=33.766635,-84.352943" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">465 North Highland Ave NE<br/>Atlanta, GA 30342</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meatball Burger, Pulled Pork Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This grocery store-turned-restaurant serves up creative spins on diner classics. Guy headed to this cozy spot to check out menu favorites like the Meatball Burger. This towering creation comes stacked with three patties smothered with melty provolone cheese, caramelized onions and mushrooms, and blanketed in housemade marinara sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tri-Continent Cuisine</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/folk-art-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.35294,33.76663,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Colonnade</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Colonnade</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlanta, GA 30324 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4048745642" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">404-874-5642</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.colonnadeatl.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.colonnadeatl.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Colonnade%2C+1879+Cheshire+Bridge+Rd.+NE%2C+Atlanta%2C+GA+30324&amp;ll=33.809564,-84.361341" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1879 Cheshire Bridge Rd. NE<br/>Atlanta, GA 30324</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kangaroo Filet, Knuckle Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">It&#x27;s the second oldest restaurant in Atlanta, but Chef Ryan Cobb is on the culinary cutting edge. Guy thought that the kangaroo filet with spicy sweet-and-sour sauce was reminiscent of sirloin. The knuckle sandwich filled with lobster and marinated tomatoes on a focaccia roll floored Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Better Than Ever</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/colonnade-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.36134,33.80956,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Galewood Cookshack</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Galewood Cookshack</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7734708334" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">773-470-8334</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/galewood-cookshack-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/galewood-cookshack-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Galewood+Cookshack%2C+Chicago%2C+IL&amp;ll=41.878114,-87.629798" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;"><br/>Chicago, IL</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">North Carolina-Style Pulled Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, host Guy Fieri discovers the Gailwood Cook Shack, a BBQ RV in Chicago, IL, that brings North Carolina-style pulled pork to just about anyone in the area.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Off the Hook Specials</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/galewood-cookshack-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.62980,41.87811,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Garifuna Flava</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Garifuna Flava</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60629 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7737767440" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 776-7440</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://garifunaflava.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">garifunaflava.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Garifuna+Flava%2C+2516-2518+W+63rd+St%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60629&amp;ll=41.779496,-87.686937" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2516-2518 W 63rd St<br/>Chicago, IL 60629</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hudut Baruru, King Fish</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From roasted chicken to oxtails to empanadas, Guy&#x27;s a fan of the traditional Belizean dishes served at Garifuna Flava on the south side of Chicago. Chef Yolanda Castillo treated him to homemade hudut baruru, or mashed plantains, with tikini, a peppery cabbage and fish stew, on Triple D.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You Can Only Get It Here</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/garifuna-flava-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.68694,41.77950,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Del Seoul</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Del Seoul</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60614 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://delseoul.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">delseoul.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Del+Seoul%2C+2568+N.+Clark+St%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60614&amp;ll=41.929470,-87.642941" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2568 N. Clark St<br/>Chicago, IL 60614</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">K-Town Chicken Wings, Kaibi Poutine</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Del Seoul is owned by a brother and sister team who turn out creative Korean cuisine with California influences in Chicago. Be careful, you might start dreaming about the crispy K-Town Chicken Wings.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Far East Flavorfest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/del-seoul-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.64294,41.92947,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>DMK Burger Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">DMK Burger Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60657 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7736986482" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 698-6482</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.dmkburgerbar.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.dmkburgerbar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=DMK+Burger+Bar%2C+2954+N+Sheffield+Ave%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60657&amp;ll=41.936056,-87.654147" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2954 N Sheffield Ave<br/>Chicago, IL 60657</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bison Burger, Salmon Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Michael Kornick is making more than a dozen types of gourmet burgers. The unique and contrasting &amp;quot;monster flavors&amp;quot; of the bison burger with blueberry barbecue sauce, goat cheese and marinated onions impressed Guy. He also enjoyed the salmon burger with Thai curry mayonnaise and Asian coleslaw.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Slammin&#x27; Sammies<br/>Top 10 Burgers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/dmk-burger-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.65415,41.93606,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>MFK</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">MFK</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60614</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7738572540" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">773-857-2540</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://mfkrestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">mfkrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=MFK%2C+432+W+Diversey+Pkwy%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60614&amp;ll=41.933058,-87.640730" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">432 W Diversey Pkwy<br/>Chicago, IL 60614</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cataplana</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Score a table at this tiny spot and you&#x27;ll be rewarded with a pour of crisp txakolina and a plate of boquerones, pristine anchovy fillets perched on smoky grilled baguettes. For your main, order the cataplana. This tomato-and-anise-flavored stew is larded with bits of cobia collar and fresh shrimp.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Culinary Journey</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/mfk-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.64073,41.93306,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Chilam Balam</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Chilam Balam</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60657 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7732966901" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 296-6901</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.chilambalamchicago.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.chilambalamchicago.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Chilam+Balam%2C+3023+N+Broadway+St%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60657&amp;ll=41.936775,-87.644281" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3023 N Broadway St<br/>Chicago, IL 60657</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Flautas, Memelas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chilam Balam puts a &amp;quot;punk rock twist&amp;quot; on organic and farm-fresh Mexican tapas. According to Guy, the chicken flautas with pickled cabbage and homemade queso had great crunch and flavor. The combination of textures in the memelas with aged goat cheese, black beans and pea shoots also impressed.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homemade &amp; Homebrewed</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/chilam-balam-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.64428,41.93677,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Chicago Brauhaus</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Chicago Brauhaus</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago 60625 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7737844444" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 784-4444</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/chicago-brauhaus-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/chicago-brauhaus-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Chicago+Brauhaus%2C+4732+N+Lincoln+Ave.%2C+Chicago+60625&amp;ll=41.967442,-87.688058" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4732 N Lincoln Ave.<br/>Chicago 60625</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sauerbraten, Rindsrouladen, Liver Dumpling Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Harry Kempf has brought classic and comforting German dishes from his homeland to Chicago. Guy enjoyed the &quot;big flavor&quot; and tenderness of the sauerbraten and the rindsrouladen, a beef roll. Loyal customers enjoy the liver dumpling soup and listening to the live polka band.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Coast to Coast Chow</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/chicago-brauhaus-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.68806,41.96744,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>La Scarola</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">La Scarola</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago 60654 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3122431740" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(312) 243-1740</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://lascarola.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">lascarola.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=La+Scarola%2C+721+W+Grand+Ave%2C+Chicago+60654&amp;ll=41.891044,-87.646838" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">721 W Grand Ave<br/>Chicago 60654</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Chop a la Gabe, Pasta Fagioli</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Whenever Guy is rolling through Chicago he stops to eat at La Scarola. Chef and owner Armando Vasquez&#x27;s serves up unbeatable Italian food and a welcoming atmosphere that Guy can&#x27;t get enough of. To make Guy&#x27;s go-to order, Veal Chop a la Gabe, a huge 10-ounce pork chop is pounded thin, breaded and fried until crisp and then topped with a lemon, garlic sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Around the World<br/>Takeout: All Over the Menu</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/la-scarola-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.64684,41.89104,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cemitas Puebla</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cemitas Puebla</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60607 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3124559200" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">312-455-9200</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cemitaspuebla.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cemitaspuebla.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cemitas+Puebla%2C+817+W+Fulton+Market%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60607&amp;ll=41.909739,-87.717667" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">817 W Fulton Market<br/>Chicago, IL 60607</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mexican Sandwich, Cemitas Puebla Salsa Verde</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Visit one of Cemitas Puebla&#x27;s locales for a rare breed of sandwich and a taste of Mexican history. This eatery is the only one of its kind in Chicago serving cemitas, authentic poblano sandwiches made on sesame seed rolls slathered with avocado and chipotle adobo, then stuffed with meaty fillings.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grabbin&#x27; a Sandwich</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/cemitas-puebla-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.71767,41.90974,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bella Luna Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bella Luna Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago 60654 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3127512552" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(312) 751-2552</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.chicagobellaluna.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.chicagobellaluna.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bella+Luna+Cafe%2C+731+N+Dearborn+St%2C+Chicago+60654&amp;ll=41.896012,-87.629651" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">731 N Dearborn St<br/>Chicago 60654</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Deep-Dish Pizza, Ravioli</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you are in the the River North region of Chicago and craving old school Italian head to Danny Alberga&#x27;s Bella Luna Cafe. Try the crispy deep-dish sausage pizza with hand-crushed tomato sauce and the massive handmade sausage ravioli.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Pork to Pasta</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/bella-luna-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.62965,41.89601,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>bopNgrill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">bopNgrill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60626 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7736543224" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 654-3224</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://bngrill.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">bngrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=bopNgrill%2C+6604+N+Sheridan+Rd%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60626&amp;ll=42.002825,-87.661327" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6604 N Sheridan Rd<br/>Chicago, IL 60626</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Umami Burger, Korean Philly Cheesesteak Eggrolls</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this food counter, Chef Will Song is cooking up some &amp;quot;righteous&amp;quot; all-American classics with a Korean spin. The umami burger topped with truffled mushroom duxelle, sun-dried tomato confit, and togarashi mayo sent Guy to euphoria and he couldn&#x27;t get enough of the Korean Philly cheesteak eggrolls.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Goin&#x27; the Extra Mile<br/>Top 10 Burgers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/bopngrill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.66133,42.00283,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Big &amp; Little&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Big &amp; Little&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60610 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3129430000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(312) 943-0000</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bigandlittleschicago.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bigandlittleschicago.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Big+%26+Little%27s%2C+860+N+Orleans+St%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60610&amp;ll=41.898347,-87.637554" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">860 N Orleans St<br/>Chicago, IL 60610</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Belly Po Boy, Beer-battered Fish and Chips</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Two chefs used their life savings to start this gourmet fast-food restaurant. Guy says that the foie gras with fries is &quot;decadent&quot; and perfectly medium-rare. The pork belly po&#x27; boy with maple mayo Guy described as &quot;chicharrones meets pulled pork.&quot; Still hungry? Try the beer-battered fish and chips.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Poke, Pork and Chicken Parm<br/>Chicago&#x27;s Finest<br/>Pizza, Pancakes and Pork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/big-littles-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.63755,41.89835,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Capone&#x27;s Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Capone&#x27;s Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Coeur d&#x27;Alene, ID 83814 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2086674843" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(208) 667-4843</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.caponespub.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.caponespub.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Capone%27s+Pub%2C+751+N+4th+St%2C+Coeur+d%27Alene%2C+ID+83814&amp;ll=47.680155,-116.781239" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">751 N 4th St<br/>Coeur d&#x27;Alene, ID 83814</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roasted Garlic Chicken Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The pizza dough recipe at this mom-and-pop shop is tried and true. According to Guy, the roasted garlic chicken pizza is &quot;Mmm, good.&quot; They also serve pub food like the ultimate burger on a homemade bun, which Guy claimed was &quot;off the hook.&quot; The cheesesteak is another local favorite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Wings &#x27;n&#x27; Things<br/>Wings &#x27;n Things<br/>Pizza Party</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/coeur-dalene/capones-pub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-116.78124,47.68016,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tiki Iniki</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tiki Iniki</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Princeville 96722 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tikiiniki.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tikiiniki.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tiki+Iniki%2C+5-4280+Kuhio+Hwy%2C+Princeville+96722&amp;ll=22.214315,-159.472858" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5-4280 Kuhio Hwy<br/>Princeville 96722</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Iniki Burger, Shrimp Rangoon, Sweet Sticky Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You probably know Todd and Michele Rundgren as rockers from the 1970s, but on the island of Kauai they&#x27;re known for serving up tropical drinks and Hawaiian-inspired dishes at their own Tiki bar. While theatmosphere is 100% fun, they&#x27;re serious about cooking interesting dishes like their signature Iniki Burger. To make the patties, ground beef is blended with cubes of spam, a combination that adds a surprising bit of sweetness to the burger. The mouthwatering patty is topped with house-made pickles and slaw, onion compote and provolone cheese. &quot;People are going to dig it,&quot; Guy said between bites.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">International Infusion</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/princeville/tiki-iniki-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-159.47286,22.21431,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jimmy&#x27;s Down the Street</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jimmy&#x27;s Down the Street</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Coeur d&#x27;Alene, ID 83814 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2087653868" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(208)765-3868</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.jimmysdownthestreet.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jimmysdownthestreet.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jimmy%27s+Down+the+Street%2C+1613+E+Sherman%2C+Coeur+d%27Alene%2C+ID+83814&amp;ll=47.673492,-116.762511" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1613 E Sherman<br/>Coeur d&#x27;Alene, ID 83814</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Caramel Pecan Roll, Chicken and Dumplings, Breakfast Burritos, Hash</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After a hard day at work, locals like to come here to enjoy a hearty home cooked meal. Guy said the firm and tender dumplings in the chicken and dumpling soup were &amp;quot;righteous.&amp;quot; The nutty monster caramel pecan roll had a great doughy texture too. Also popular are the breakfast burritos and hash.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Favorites With A Twist</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/coeur-dalene/jimmys-down-the-street-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-116.76251,47.67349,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hanalei Poke Food Truck</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hanalei Poke Food Truck</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hanalei, Hawaii 96714</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8088555574" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 855-5574</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/hanalei/hanalei-poke-food-truck-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/hanalei/hanalei-poke-food-truck-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hanalei+Poke+Food+Truck%2C+5-5190+Kuhio+Hwy%2C+Hanalei%2C+Hawaii+96714&amp;ll=22.202844,-159.497415" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5-5190 Kuhio Hwy<br/>Hanalei, Hawaii 96714</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Local Boy, Kealia Plate, Hanalei Bowl, Spicy Ahi Sushi Roll</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jeremy Burwell is known for having the freshest poke in Hawaii, and for good reason: the fish he serves is so local that Jeremy, the chef-owner, catches it himself. His popular food truck serves up twists on the classic poke bowl, like the Kealia Plate, an Ahi tuna-based bowl mixed with fresh mint, macadamia nuts and watermelon. Guy said the unusual ingredients bring the dish&#x27;s flavors and texture to the next level. &quot;I&#x27;ve tried all kinds of flavors, I&#x27;ve never had this in a Poke bowl,&quot; he raved.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Standout Seafood</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/hanalei/hanalei-poke-food-truck-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-159.49742,22.20284,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>South Maui Fish Company</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">South Maui Fish Company</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kihei 96753 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8084198980" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 419.8980</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://southmauifishco.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">southmauifishco.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=South+Maui+Fish+Company%2C+1794+South+Kihei+Rd.%2C+Kihei+96753&amp;ll=20.735758,-156.453493" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1794 South Kihei Rd.<br/>Kihei 96753</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">South Maui Fish Company believes in a high quality experience by upholding their principle of sustainability. Patrons get to choose from a selection of freshly caught seafood, and their dishes are prepared with locally sourced produce and ingredients. Their fish is cooked to order or can be purchased uncooked to take home.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Taste of the Tropics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/restaurants-in-kihei/south-maui-fish-company" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-156.45349,20.73576,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Three&#x27;s Bar and Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Three&#x27;s Bar and Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kihei, HI 96753 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8088793133" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-879-3133</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://threesbarandgrill.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">threesbarandgrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Three%27s+Bar+and+Grill%2C+1945+S+Kihei+Rd%2C+Kihei%2C+HI+96753&amp;ll=20.731641,-156.451525" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1945 S Kihei Rd<br/>Kihei, HI 96753</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Three friends run this fusion restaurant in Hawaii that serves up legit ramen and killer Asian beer can chicken. Guy loved the fragrant broth of the ramen paired with the kimchi mushrooms and chicken soy sauce. &quot;This isn&#x27;t your everyday Sunday chicken,&quot; Guy mused over the orange-hoisin glazed bird served with wok-fried brussels sprouts with bacon.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Barbecue, Batter and Beer Can Chicken</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/restaurants-in-kihei/threes-bar-and-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-156.45153,20.73164,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cafe Pesto</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cafe Pesto</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hilo 96720</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8089696640" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 969-6640</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.cafepesto.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cafepesto.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cafe+Pesto%2C+308+Kamehameha+Ave+%23101%2C+Hilo+96720&amp;ll=19.723739,-155.085065" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">308 Kamehameha Ave #101<br/>Hilo 96720</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cafe Pesto has it all - including seafood, breakfast and brunch, dessert and a selection of beverages. From their beginnings as a pizzeria (they have that too!) to their expansion of locally and historically inspired dishes prepared with care, Cafe Pesto seeks to create a dining experience that allows guests to &quot;drift back in time awakened to the present only by the colorful and provocative meal presentations.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mouthwatering Meat</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/cafe-pesto" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-155.08506,19.72374,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hilo Bay Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hilo Bay Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hilo 96720 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8089354939" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 935-4939</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://hilobaycafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">hilobaycafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hilo+Bay+Cafe%2C+123+Lihiwai+Street%2C+Hilo+96720&amp;ll=19.725126,-155.070510" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">123 Lihiwai Street<br/>Hilo 96720</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hilo Bay Cafe has served fresh, contemporary and locally sourced and inspired dishes since 2003. Now located on Hilo Bay with views of the ocean, Mauna Kea, and Hilo&#x27;s downtown area, the restaurant is frequented by tourists and locals looking to enjoy good food, a selection of drinks and fun atmosphere.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cookin&#x27; from Scratch</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/hilo-bay-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-155.07051,19.72513,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sweet Home Waimanalo</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sweet Home Waimanalo</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Waimanalo, HI 96795 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8082595737" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 259-5737</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sweethomewaimanalo.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sweethomewaimanalo.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sweet+Home+Waimanalo%2C+41-1025+Kalanianaole+Hwy%2C+Waimanalo%2C+HI+96795&amp;ll=21.340206,-157.703813" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">41-1025 Kalanianaole Hwy<br/>Waimanalo, HI 96795</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulled-Pork with Bok Choy Slaw, Tofu Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Committed to a healthy lifestyle, owner Joanne Kapololu uses only fresh local ingredients. Originally Guy was skeptical about the tofu burger, but he ended up loving its &quot;outrageous&quot; flavor. The pulled-pork with bok choy slaw, Okinawan sweet potatoes and corn bread also impressed Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Top 10 Burgers<br/>Goin&#x27; the Extra Mile</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/waimanalo/sweet-home-waimanalo-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.70381,21.34021,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Germaine&#x27;s Luau</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Germaine&#x27;s Luau</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kapolei, HI 96707 &middot; &#9733; 2.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8089496626" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 949-6626</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.germainesluau.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.germainesluau.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Germaine%27s+Luau%2C+91-119+Olai+St%2C+Kapolei%2C+HI+96707&amp;ll=21.296470,-158.105473" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">91-119 Olai St<br/>Kapolei, HI 96707</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lomi Lomi, Kalua Pig (Roasted Pig)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On a special Hawaiian Triple D, Guy headed to Germaine&#x27;s Luau in search of the quintessential luau experience. For more than 30 years, Germaine&#x27;s has crafted the traditional party, complete with roasted pig cooked in an &amp;quot;imu&amp;quot; underground pit and an all-you-can eat buffet of tasty Hawaiian dishes.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Goes Hawaiian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kapolei/germaines-luau-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-158.10547,21.29647,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Brigit &amp; Bernard&#x27;s Garden Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Brigit &amp; Bernard&#x27;s Garden Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kahului, HI 96732 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8088776000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-877-6000</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://brigitandbernards.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">brigitandbernards.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Brigit+%26+Bernard%27s+Garden+Cafe%2C+335+Hoohana+St%2C+Kahului%2C+HI+96732&amp;ll=20.883803,-156.461343" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">335 Hoohana St<br/>Kahului, HI 96732</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brigit &amp; Bernard&#x27;s Garden Cafe is a German gem in the middle of paradise. Swiss-born Chef and Owner Bernard Weber is dishing out impressive apple strudel and to-die-for beef roulade with house-made spaetzle that keeps the locals coming back for more.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sandwiches, Spaetzle and Sticky Wings</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kahului/brigit-and-bernards-garden-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-156.46134,20.88380,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Highway Inn</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Highway Inn</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Waipahu, HI 96797</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8086774345" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 677-4345</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.myhighwayinn.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.myhighwayinn.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Highway+Inn%2C+94-226+Leoku+St%2C+Waipahu%2C+HI+96797&amp;ll=21.379154,-158.024678" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">94-226 Leoku St<br/>Waipahu, HI 96797</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Haupia, Lau Lau, Kalua Pig</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This third-generation Hawaiian restaurant has been making traditional island plates since 1947. The iconic Lau Lau pork dish consists of pork wrapped in taro leaves. The beef Pipikaula most impressed Guy on his trip; it&#x27;s marinated, hung to dry and then grilled and sliced right on the flat top.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Goes Hawaiian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/waipahu/highway-inn-hookipa-catering-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-158.02468,21.37915,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Elena&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Elena&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Waipahu, HI 96797 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8086768005" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-676-8005</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.elenasrestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.elenasrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Elena%27s%2C+94-866+Moloalo+St%2C+Waipahu%2C+HI+96797&amp;ll=21.384974,-158.002473" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">94-866 Moloalo St<br/>Waipahu, HI 96797</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lechon Special, Fried Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Elena&#x27;s is serving up Filipino cuisine with a Hawaiian twist. Guy can&#x27;t get enough of the Lechon Special, which is chopped crispy pork tossed with tomatoes and onions. Another must-try is the fried pork, which is made out of boneless pork butt and served with a side of pickled ong choy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Deep-Fried Favorites<br/>Island Flavor<br/>Triple D Nation: A Family Affair</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/waipahu/elena_s" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-158.00247,21.38497,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Thai Mee Up</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Thai Mee Up</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kahului 96732</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8082143369" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-214-3369</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kahului/thai-mee-up-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kahului/thai-mee-up-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Thai+Mee+Up%2C+591+Haleakala+Hwy%2C+Kahului+96732&amp;ll=20.888369,-156.447776" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">591 Haleakala Hwy<br/>Kahului 96732</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Stuffed Chicken Wings, Fried Pork Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy heads to Thai Mee Up for Thai-inspired Hawaiian food right by the airport. Their &quot;out-of-bounds&quot; stuffed chicken wing with sweet-and-sour plum sauce is crispy on the outside and bursting with veggies and rice noodles on the inside. Their boneless pork ribs also take Guy to new heights. &quot;On a scale of 1 to 100 that&#x27;s a 101,&quot; he says of the immaculate dish. &quot;This is like a freight train to Flavortown.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Trifecta</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kahului/thai-mee-up-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-156.44778,20.88837,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Maui Fresh Streatery</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Maui Fresh Streatery</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kahului 96732 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8083447929" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-344-7929</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://mauifreshstreatery.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">mauifreshstreatery.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Maui+Fresh+Streatery%2C+Roaming+Food+Truck%2C+Kahului+96732&amp;ll=20.893058,-156.463010" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Roaming Food Truck<br/>Kahului 96732</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Farm-to-Table Street Food, Okonomiyaki, Pohole Fern Laphet Took Salad</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Kyle Kawakami keeps it fresh at his food truck, where his ever-changing menu features farm-to-table street food. A new lineup is created every two weeks, using seasonal ingredients and incorporating different regional or ethnic themes. Follow @MauiFreshStreatery on social media to see what he&#x27;s currently cooking up, and to track timing and location.The Okonomiyaki is one of the most unique dishes that Guy has ever had in a food truck.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Global Comes Local<br/>Flavor Adventure</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kahului/maui-fresh-streatery-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-156.46301,20.89306,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Big Wave Shrimp Truck</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Big Wave Shrimp Truck</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Haleiwa, HI 96712 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8083662016" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 366-2016</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://bigwaveshrimp.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">bigwaveshrimp.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Big+Wave+Shrimp+Truck%2C+66-521+Kamehameha+Hwy%2C+Haleiwa%2C+HI+96712&amp;ll=21.579471,-158.105524" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">66-521 Kamehameha Hwy<br/>Haleiwa, HI 96712</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Korean BBQ Short Ribs, Coconut Shrimp, Lemon Pepper Shrimp</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this mobile restaurant the shrimp is always fresh and the customers are always happy. Guy loved the crunchy coconut shrimp, while locals couldn&#x27;t get enough of the spicy and lemon pepper shrimp. In addition to shrimp, the truck sells delicious Korean BBQ short ribs.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Flavortown Medley<br/>Fun in the Sun</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/haleiwa/big-wave-shrimp-truck-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-158.10552,21.57947,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Matteo&#x27;s Osteria</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Matteo&#x27;s Osteria</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wailea 96753</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8088918466" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 891-8466</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.matteosmaui.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.matteosmaui.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Matteo%27s+Osteria%2C+161+Wailea+Ike+Pl%2C+Wailea+96753&amp;ll=20.688747,-156.436783" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">161 Wailea Ike Pl<br/>Wailea 96753</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">In addition to its extensive wine menu (as every osteria should have), Matteo&#x27;s Osteria has classic Italian fare such as salad, pizza and pasta with some vegan options.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Domestic &amp; Abroad</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/wailea-maui/matteo-s-osteria" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-156.43678,20.68875,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Poke Stop Mililani-Mauka LLC</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Poke Stop Mililani-Mauka LLC</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Mililani, HI 96789</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8086263400" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 626-3400</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.poke-stop.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.poke-stop.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Poke+Stop+Mililani-Mauka+LLC%2C+95-1840+Meheula+Pkwy%2C+Mililani%2C+HI+96789&amp;ll=21.468072,-158.002441" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">95-1840 Meheula Pkwy<br/>Mililani, HI 96789</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Poke, Furikake Salmon</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Those unfamiliar with the traditional Hawaiian poke dish can look to Guy for advice. The first time he savored Chef Elmer Guzman&#x27;s chopped salmon fish poke, he called it mega gangster fresh. But the real surprise was from the mainland fish called oi&#x27;o mashed into a &amp;quot;killer seafood gazpacho.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homegrown And Homemade</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/mililani/poke-stop-at-mililani-mauka-llc-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-158.00244,21.46807,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fleetwood&#x27;s on Front St.</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fleetwood&#x27;s on Front St.</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lahaina, HI 96761 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8086696425" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-669-6425</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.fleetwoodsonfrontst.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fleetwoodsonfrontst.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fleetwood%27s+on+Front+St.%2C+744+Front+St%2C+Lahaina%2C+HI+96761&amp;ll=20.873675,-156.678333" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">744 Front St<br/>Lahaina, HI 96761</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bitty&#x27;s Herb-Roasted Chicken, Bourbon-Glazed Pork Belly, Beef Wellington</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mick Fleetwood of Fleetwood Mac serves up rock and roll next to his favorite recipes including a dish inspired by his mom&#x27;s best chicken recipe. Bitty&#x27;s herb-roasted chicken is marinated, sous vide and then seared to achieve a harmonic conversion of super crispy skin and mouth-watering tenderness. Bourbon-glazed pork belly and Sammy Hagar&#x27;s favorite, Beef Wellington, also steal the show. &quot;It looks high end but it eats comfort,&quot; Guy said of the spot-on dishes.

</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Trifecta</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/lahaina/fleetwood-s-on-front-st-" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-156.67833,20.87368,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rick&#x27;s Press Room Grill &amp; Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rick&#x27;s Press Room Grill &amp; Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Meridan 83642 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2082880558" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">208-288-0558</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/meridan/ricks-press-room-grill-bar-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/meridan/ricks-press-room-grill-bar-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rick%27s+Press+Room+Grill+%26+Bar%2C+130+East+Idaho+Street%2C+Meridan+83642&amp;ll=43.611304,-116.390610" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">130 East Idaho Street<br/>Meridan 83642</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Chops with Polenta, Potato Crusted Salmon</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy says, &quot;the pork chops are the size of Cleveland&quot;; they&#x27;re so enormous, they can easily be a combo of two chops made into one. Paris-trained Chef Rick Valenzuela serves up unique concoctions like Rick&#x27;s salmon in Potato, which is glued together with his salmon paste.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Name That Cook<br/>Grilling Greats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/meridan/ricks-press-room-grill-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-116.39061,43.61130,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Donnie Mac&#x27;s Trailer Park Cuisine</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Donnie Mac&#x27;s Trailer Park Cuisine</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boise, ID 83702</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2083849008" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">208-384-9008</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/boise/donnie-macs-trailer-park-cuisine-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/boise/donnie-macs-trailer-park-cuisine-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Donnie+Mac%27s+Trailer+Park+Cuisine%2C+1515+W.+Grove+St.%2C+Boise%2C+ID+83702&amp;ll=43.619070,-116.213142" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1515 W. Grove St.<br/>Boise, ID 83702</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mac and Cheese, Corn Dressing for Southern Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy Fieri, host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, uncovers Donnie Mac&#x27;s Trailer Park Cuisine in Boise, ID, a tire store turned diner where they&#x27;ll put just about anything in their mac and cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Only At This Joint</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/boise/donnie-macs-trailer-park-cuisine-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-116.21314,43.61907,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Donn&#x27;s Hilltop Kodiak Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Donn&#x27;s Hilltop Kodiak Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boise, ID 83716</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2083388859" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">208-338-8859</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.kodiakgrill.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.kodiakgrill.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Donn%27s+Hilltop+Kodiak+Grill%2C+12342+East+Highway+21%2C+Boise%2C+ID+83716&amp;ll=43.571003,-116.030739" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">12342 East Highway 21<br/>Boise, ID 83716</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Portobello Pesto Burger, Pot Roast Beef Sandwich, Sweet Potato Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Join host, Guy Fieri, of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, at Donn&#x27;s Hilltop Cafe &amp; Kodiak Grill in Boise, ID, a local landmark that was brought back to life and is now serving up some classic American cuisine.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old Time Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/boise/donns-hilltop-kodiak-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-116.03074,43.57100,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pizzalchik</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pizzalchik</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boise 83714 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2088537757" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">208-853-7757</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/boise/pizzalchik-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/boise/pizzalchik-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pizzalchik%2C+7330+W+State+St%2C+Boise+83714&amp;ll=43.668730,-116.279703" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7330 W State St<br/>Boise 83714</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wild Forest Mist Pizza, Effin Good Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">With a name like Pizzalchik (a union of pizza, salad and chicken), you can expect that this place will serve mighty creative fusion pies. Go whole hog with the two-in-one barbecue chicken-topped Effin Good Pie, which also corrals pineapple, bacon and green onions. Or try Guy&#x27;s fave, the Wild Forest Mist, studded with freshly ground elk sausage and wild mushrooms, which he called &quot;the perfect combo.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza Party<br/>Barbequed, Baked, and Brined</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/boise/pizzalchik-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-116.27970,43.66873,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Westside Drive In</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Westside Drive In</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boise, ID 83702 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2083422957" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(208) 342-2957</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cheflou.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cheflou.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Westside+Drive+In%2C+1939+W+State+St%2C+Boise%2C+ID+83702&amp;ll=43.625912,-116.215063" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1939 W State St<br/>Boise, ID 83702</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ice Cream Potato, Prime Rib, Fingers Steaks, Meatloaf Sandwich, Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Most drive-ins serve burgers and fries, but here a gourmet chef is dishing out delicious meals to the cars that roll through. The prime rib, a Friday and Saturday special, was &amp;quot;out of bounds&amp;quot; according to Guy. The finger steaks with cocktail sauce and the meatloaf sandwich are also delicious.&amp;nbsp;estside&#x27;s Ice Cream Potato is a nod (with a wink) to the state&#x27;s famous export but also a tasty treat when served in a puddle of warm chocolate sauce.&amp;nbsp;Though at first blush it looks like a loaded baked potato, it features a glob of vanilla ice cream rolled in a layer of dirt-hued cocoa and crowned with a tuft of whipped cream.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Who&#x27;Da Thunk It?</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/boise/chef-lous-westside-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-116.21506,43.62591,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bar Gernika</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bar Gernika</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boise, ID 83702 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2083442175" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">208-344-2175</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bargernika.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bargernika.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bar+Gernika%2C+202+S+Capitol+Blvd%2C+Boise%2C+ID+83702&amp;ll=43.614072,-116.202967" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">202 S Capitol Blvd<br/>Boise, ID 83702</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Solomo Sandwich (Marinated Pork Loin with Pimientos), Lamb Grinder, Beef Tongue</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Located on Boise, Idaho&#x27;s, Basque Block, Bar Gernika is serving up Basque comfort food. Guy loved the marinated pork and peppers in the Solomo Sandwich. The lamb grinder was &amp;quot;nice and juicy&amp;quot; and Guy drained the accompanying au jus. Feeling brave? Try the beef tongue served in a garlic tomato sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Little Bit of Everywhere</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/id/boise/bar-gernika-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-116.20297,43.61407,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hank&#x27;s Haute Dogs</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hank&#x27;s Haute Dogs</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Honolulu, HI 96813 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8085324265" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 532-4265</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hankshautedogs.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hankshautedogs.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hank%27s+Haute+Dogs%2C+324+Coral+St%2C+Honolulu%2C+HI+96813&amp;ll=21.297929,-157.861039" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">324 Coral St<br/>Honolulu, HI 96813</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicago Dogs, Lobster Dogs, Pineapple Relish</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Don&#x27;t be fooled by its Hawaiian address, because Hank&#x27;s Haute Dogs has an unheard-of dedication to bringing authentic Chicago-style hot dogs to the mainland. Just ask Guy, who visited on DDD. Along with a genuine Chicago Vienna dog, Hank&#x27;s special Lobster Sausage is unique and &amp;quot;the dog you want.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Goes Hawaiian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/honolulu/hanks-haute-dogs-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.86104,21.29793,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Marietta Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Marietta Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Marietta 30060 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (20 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7704239390" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">770-423-9390</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mariettadiner.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mariettadiner.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Marietta+Diner%2C+306+Cobb+Parkway+S%2C+Marietta+30060&amp;ll=33.944549,-84.517838" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">306 Cobb Parkway S<br/>Marietta 30060</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spanakopita (Spinach Pie), Burgers, Fettuccine Alfredo, Chicken Saltimbocca</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Marietta Diner may be in Georgia but Gus Tselios knew it could resemble the big Greek family diner he grew up with in New York. Today nearly 3,000 people visit each day to order from the 500-item menu. But Guy knew to try the Greek lasagna, pastitsio, as it&#x27;s some of the best around.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Goin&#x27; Big and Bringin&#x27; Home<br/>A World of Flavors<br/>Real-Deal Diners<br/>Triple D Nation: Where&#x27;s the Beef?</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/marietta/marietta-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.51784,33.94455,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Southern Soul Barbeque</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Southern Soul Barbeque</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">St Simons Island, GA 31522 &middot; &#9733; 4.9 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9126387685" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">912-638-7685</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.southernsoulbbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.southernsoulbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Southern+Soul+Barbeque%2C+2020+Demere+Rd%2C+St+Simons+Island%2C+GA+31522&amp;ll=31.159619,-81.387943" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2020 Demere Rd<br/>St Simons Island, GA 31522</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brunswick Stew, Pulled Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Southern Soul Barbeque, they like their ribs sweet -&amp;nbsp;and they mean sweet. Guy learned firsthand what this meant: Each rib gets coated in brown sugar and tupelo honey. The result is super tender ribs and pulled pork with a unique woody smokiness.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big-Time Barbecue<br/>Old Time Attitude</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/st-simons-island/southern-soul-barbeque-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.38794,31.15962,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Matthew&#x27;s Cafeteria</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Matthew&#x27;s Cafeteria</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tucker 30084 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7709392357" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">770-939-2357</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.matthewscafeteria.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.matthewscafeteria.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Matthew%27s+Cafeteria%2C+2299+Main+St.%2C+Tucker+30084&amp;ll=33.852259,-84.213985" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2299 Main St.<br/>Tucker 30084</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Biscuits and Gravy, Brunswick Stew, Sweet Potato Souffle</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The general philosophy of Matthew&#x27;s Cafeteria in Tucker, Ga., is &#x27;&#x27;if it ain&#x27;t broke, don&#x27;t fix it,&#x27;&#x27; which is why they&#x27;ve been making the same dishes for over 50 years. Guy said the biscuits and gravy were hands down some of the best, and the Brunswick stew is stuffed with chicken smoked in-house.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: From Pork to Pot Pie<br/>Diner&#x27;s Drive-ins and Dives: Best from the Road<br/>All Stacked Up<br/>Where the Locals Go</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/tucker/matthews-cafeteria-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.21398,33.85226,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blackwater Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blackwater Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">St. Simons Island, GA 31522 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9126346333" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(912) 634-6333</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.blackwatergrill.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.blackwatergrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blackwater+Grill%2C+260+Redfern+Village%2C+St.+Simons+Island%2C+GA+31522&amp;ll=31.162680,-81.389828" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">260 Redfern Village<br/>St. Simons Island, GA 31522</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Low Country Boil, Blackwater&#x27;s Shrimp and Grits</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For a tried-and-true sea-to-table restaurant, Guy couldn&#x27;t miss Blackwater Grill on Georgia&#x27;s St. Simons Island. The local catch, grouper, doubles as the signature with its creamy daufuskie sauce. Even with local seafood, the menu heads south for Cajun faves like spicy gumbo and shrimp and grits.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Farm To Table</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/st-simons-island/blackwater-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.38983,31.16268,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>90 Miles Cuban Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">90 Miles Cuban Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60647 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7732272822" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 227-2822</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.90milescubancafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.90milescubancafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=90+Miles+Cuban+Cafe%2C+2540+W+Armitage+Ave%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60647&amp;ll=41.917685,-87.691804" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2540 W Armitage Ave<br/>Chicago, IL 60647</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fricase de pollo, Slow-roasted Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Alberto Gonzalez may have left Cuba, but he brought his grandmother&#x27;s recipes so he could continue to cook rich and savory Cuban cuisine. Guy was impressed by the balance of flavors found in the fricase de pollo served with rice, beans and maduros. The slow-roasted pork pleased Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crazy for Chicken<br/>Savory Standouts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/90-miles-cuban-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.69180,41.91768,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Panozzo&#x27;s Italian Market</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Panozzo&#x27;s Italian Market</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60605 &middot; &#9733; 1.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/panozzos-italian-market-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/panozzos-italian-market-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Panozzo%27s+Italian+Market%2C+1303+S+Michigan+Ave%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60605&amp;ll=41.865608,-87.623810" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1303 S Michigan Ave<br/>Chicago, IL 60605</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meatball Sandwich, Crescentina</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef John Asbaty is bringing Italian comfort food classics to Chicago. Guy likes how the spice and acid from the peppers balance the sweetness from the currants in the meatball sandwich. The porchetta on the fried crescentina bread is &quot;melt-in-your-mouth good.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Seafood &amp; Sammies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/panozzos-italian-market-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.62381,41.86561,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Outrigger Pizza Company</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Outrigger Pizza Company</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kihei, HI 96753 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8082802985" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-280-2985</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.outriggerpizzas.com/Outrigger/Main.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.outriggerpizzas.com/Outrigger/Main.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Outrigger+Pizza+Company%2C+1819+S+Kihei+Rd%2C+Kihei%2C+HI+96753&amp;ll=20.734835,-156.452451" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1819 S Kihei Rd<br/>Kihei, HI 96753</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lilikoi Pizza, Italian Sausage Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef-owner Kevin Laut has been slinging wood-fired pizzas from a custom trailer he built himself since 2009. The dough he uses for his thin-crust pizzas is made daily, by hand, on the cart. His signature creation, the Lilikoi pie, was inspired by the flavors of Hawaii. This beauty comes loaded with yellow passion fruit glaze, sweet peppers, mozzarella cheese and pulled pork.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Great Gear</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/maui/the-outrigger-pizza-company-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-156.45245,20.73483,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Like Poke</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Like Poke</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kahului, HI 96732 &middot; &#9733; 2.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8087578402" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-757-8402</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/maui/like-poke-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/maui/like-poke-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Like+Poke%2C+591+Haleakala+Hwy%2C+Kahului%2C+HI+96732&amp;ll=20.888336,-156.447244" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">591 Haleakala Hwy<br/>Kahului, HI 96732</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Poke, Baked Poke, Fried Poke</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef-Owner Danny Kalahiki has been serving fresh poke out of his food truck since 2009. The fresh-caught tuna is cut into extra-large cubes to ensure the fish&#x27;s natural flavor isn&#x27;t overpowered by the seasonings. The tuna is then tossed with watercress, red onions, poke seasoning and a housemade poke sauce. &quot;It&#x27;s so tender that before I even bit into it, it started to melt,&quot; Guy said of the fish. &amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Soakin&#x27; Up Maui</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/maui/like-poke-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-156.44724,20.88834,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Star Noodle</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Star Noodle</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lahaina, HI 96761 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8086675400" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-667-5400</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.starnoodle.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.starnoodle.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Star+Noodle%2C+286+Kupuohi+Street%2C+Lahaina%2C+HI+96761&amp;ll=20.885276,-156.674481" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">286 Kupuohi Street<br/>Lahaina, HI 96761</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hapa Ramen, Vietnamese Crepe</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Star Noodle boasts an innovative menu of island-inspired Asian fare like hapa ramen (which features fresh noodles cranked out daily on an 80-year-old machine from Japan). Guy raves about the Vietnamese Crepe: a crunchy shell stuffed with a coconut milk-laced mixture of shrimp and pork. It&#x27;s served with fresh lettuce leaves to create make-your-own wraps. &quot;This might be in the top 25 most-unique items I&#x27;ve ever seen on Triple D,&quot; Guy says.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Creole, Cold Cuts and Crepes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/maui/star-noodle-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-156.67448,20.88528,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fat Daddy&#x27;s Smokehouse</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fat Daddy&#x27;s Smokehouse</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kihei, HI 96753 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8088798711" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-879-8711</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.fatdaddysmaui.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fatdaddysmaui.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fat+Daddy%27s+Smokehouse%2C+1913+S+Kihei+Rd%2C+Kihei%2C+HI+96753&amp;ll=20.732322,-156.452027" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1913 S Kihei Rd<br/>Kihei, HI 96753</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">St. Louis-Style Pork Ribs, Burnt Ends</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owner Chris Schobel grew up smoking meats in Pennsylvania, so when he moved to Maui in 2013, he decided to revive a struggling barbecue joint. Schobel&#x27;s style borrows from both North Carolina and Texas: The ribs are hit with a dry rub, smoked for five hours, then served with a vinegar-laced barbecue sauce that incorporates beef fat for added flavor. A standout side is the cornbread made from a creamed-corn batter.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Soakin&#x27; Up Maui</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/maui/fat-daddys-smokehouse-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-156.45203,20.73232,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Da Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Da Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kahului, HI 96732 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8088717782" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-871-7782</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://dakitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">dakitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Da+Kitchen%2C+425+Koloa+St.+%23104%2C+Kahului%2C+HI+96732&amp;ll=20.887692,-156.455143" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">425 Koloa St. #104<br/>Kahului, HI 96732</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Notorious B.I.G. Moco, Kalbi Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crowds line up for Hawaiian classics at this can&#x27;t-miss joint by the Maui airport. One flavor-packed favorite is the Notorious B.I.G. Moco, a spin on the Hawaiian comfort-food staple known as loco moco. A gravy-slicked hamburger patty comes perched on a mound of fried rice and topped with housemade chili, shredded cheese, Portuguese sausage, bacon, mushrooms and onions. A fried egg adds to the richness.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Soakin&#x27; Up Maui</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/maui/da-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-156.45514,20.88769,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Original Thai</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Original Thai</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kailua-Kona, HI 96740 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kailua-kona/original-thai-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kailua-kona/original-thai-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Original+Thai%2C+75-5629+Kuakini+Hwy%2C+Kailua-Kona%2C+HI+96740&amp;ll=19.642851,-155.996604" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">75-5629 Kuakini Hwy<br/>Kailua-Kona, HI 96740</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">SSS Duck, Larb Wrap</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Original Thai, owner Sa&#x27;ing Schueler is serving up a creative mixture of Thai and Chinese cuisine. The SSS Duck is a gorgeous dish that is braised and then fried until crispy and topped with a special spicy sweet and sour sauce. &quot;This is crazy,&quot; said Guy. &quot;I would fly from California to come and have this twice a year.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Far East Flavorfest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kailua-kona/original-thai-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-155.99660,19.64285,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Miso Phat Sushi</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Miso Phat Sushi</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kihei, HI 96753 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8088916476" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-891-6476</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.misophat.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.misophat.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Miso+Phat+Sushi%2C+1279+S+Kihei+Rd+%23108%2C+Kihei%2C+HI+96753&amp;ll=20.749633,-156.454721" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1279 S Kihei Rd #108<br/>Kihei, HI 96753</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">TNT Roll, Lilikoi Ice Cream</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This unassuming joint is tucked away in a strip mall, but don&#x27;t let its no-frills appearance fool you. Inside you&#x27;ll find bright sushi rolls made from fish so fresh it&#x27;s pulled straight from owner Shawn Steadman&#x27;s boat (affectionately named the Shiso Phat). &amp;quot;It&#x27;s so fresh it&#x27;s almost jumping into my mouth,&amp;quot; Guy said of the TNT, a shrimp tempura roll topped with ahi poke. Another standout is the lilikoi ice cream: a tangy frozen treat made from Hawaiian passion fruit.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Global Greats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/maui/miso-phat-sushi-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-156.45472,20.74963,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Umekes</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Umekes</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kailua-Kona 96740 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8082380571" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 238-0571</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.umekesrestaurants.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.umekesrestaurants.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Umekes%2C+74-5599+Pawai+Place%2C+Kailua-Kona+96740&amp;ll=19.644004,-155.998407" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">74-5599 Pawai Place<br/>Kailua-Kona 96740</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kanaka Poke, Heartbreaker</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Kailua-Kona joint is the spot for fresh flavors and locally-sourced ingredients. Favorites include Lau Lau (tender pork and Hawaiian salt wrapped in taro leaves and steamed for 10 hours) and slow-roasted Kalua pork. The restaurant also features a full bar and outdoor seating for a truly tropical experience.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Worldwide Delivery<br/>Italian, Hawaiian and Colombian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kailua-kona/umekes-fishmarket-bar-grill" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-155.99841,19.64400,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mike&#x27;s Huli Huli Chicken</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mike&#x27;s Huli Huli Chicken</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kaneohe, HI 96744 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8082776720" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 277-6720</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/mikeshulihulichicken/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">sites.google.com/site/mikeshulihulichicken</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mike%27s+Huli+Huli+Chicken%2C+47-525+Kamehameha+Hwy%2C+Kaneohe%2C+HI+96744&amp;ll=21.458670,-157.838453" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">47-525 Kamehameha Hwy<br/>Kaneohe, HI 96744</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Huli Huli Chicken, Char Siu Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mike&#x27;s Huli Huli Chicken slow-roasts their chicken on the wood-fire rotisserie, which results in juicy meat that is also as crispy as you can get without frying it, Guy says. He couldn&#x27;t leave without also getting a taste of the char siu pork, which is red Chinese pork with a sweet, smoky taste.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Best of the Beach<br/>Grillin&#x27;, Chillin&#x27; and Huli Huli Chicken</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kaneohe/mike_s-huli-huli-chicken" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.83845,21.45867,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dean&#x27;s Drive Inn</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dean&#x27;s Drive Inn</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kaneohe, HI 96744</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8082471300" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 247-1300</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/deansdriveinn" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/deansdriveinn</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dean%27s+Drive+Inn%2C+45-773+Kamehameha+Hwy%2C+Kaneohe%2C+HI+96744&amp;ll=21.410592,-157.798660" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">45-773 Kamehameha Hwy<br/>Kaneohe, HI 96744</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ginger Soy Ono, Ahi Cakes, Broiled Teriyaki Beef</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dean&#x27;s Drive Inn is the epitome of casual gourmet. The laid-back atmosphere, coupled with the delicious food, puts this joint on Guy&#x27;s radar. Local favorites include the ginger soy ono (a popular Hawaiian white fish), the ahi cakes topped with Greek chili aioli sauce and the broiled teriyaki beef.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Island Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kaneohe/dean_s-drive-inn" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.79866,21.41059,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>He&#x27;eia Kea Pier General Store and Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">He&#x27;eia Kea Pier General Store and Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kaneohe, HI 96744 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8082352192" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 235-2192</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.heeiapier.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.heeiapier.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=He%27eia+Kea+Pier+General+Store+and+Deli%2C+46-499+Kamehameha+HWY%2C+Kaneohe%2C+HI+96744&amp;ll=21.444255,-157.809825" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">46-499 Kamehameha HWY<br/>Kaneohe, HI 96744</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Stir Fried Beef, Limu Salad, Luau Stew</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This hole-in-the-wall serves fresh locally sourced Hawaiian comfort food. Guy loved the stir-fried beef and said it was &amp;quot;bustin&#x27; out with flavor.&amp;quot; The limu salad with freshly harvested gorilla seaweed Guy called &amp;quot;funky, fresh and good.&amp;quot; Locals rave about the luau stew with tender pork shoulder.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Unconventional Comforts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kaneohe/heeia-kea-pier-general-store-and-deli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.80982,21.44425,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Uahi Island Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Uahi Island Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kailua, HI 96734 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8082664646" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 266-4646</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.uahiislandgrill.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.uahiislandgrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Uahi+Island+Grill%2C+131+Hekili+St+%23102%2C+Kailua%2C+HI+96734&amp;ll=21.392299,-157.742704" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">131 Hekili St #102<br/>Kailua, HI 96734</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Thai Red Curry Grilled Fish, Mandarin Duck Confit</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Uahi Island Grill is a self-proclaimed contemporary Hawaiian restaurant. Guy loves the fresh grilled fish in a spicy Thai red curry served with green papaya salad. If you&#x27;re more in the mood for meat, try the slow-poached Mandarin duck confit with an anise-orange glaze, which Guy declares &quot;spot-on.&quot;&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Island Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kailua/uahi-island-grill" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.74270,21.39230,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Camille&#x27;s on Wheels</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Camille&#x27;s on Wheels</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kailua, HI 96734</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8082821740" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 282-1740</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.camillesmeals.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.camillesmeals.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Camille%27s+on+Wheels%2C+Roaming+Food+Truck%2C+Kailua%2C+HI+96734&amp;ll=21.402222,-157.739444" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Roaming Food Truck<br/>Kailua, HI 96734</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chimichurri Beef Tacos, Mango Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Camille may always be on the move, but her GPS and Twitter feed help locals and foodies alike find her food truck. Guy was a fan of her chimichurri beef tacos topped with pico de gallo, cabbage and crema de mirin mayo. Customers also rave about the mango pie.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Coast to Coast Chow<br/>Food Truckapalooza</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kailua/camilles-on-wheels-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.73944,21.40222,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Boots &amp; Kimo&#x27;s Homestyle Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Boots &amp; Kimo&#x27;s Homestyle Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kailua, HI 96734</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8082637929" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 263-7929</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Boots-Kimos-Homestyle-Kitchen/135351636508369" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Boots-Kimos-Homestyle-Kitchen/135351636508369</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Boots+%26+Kimo%27s+Homestyle+Kitchen%2C+151+Hekili+St%2C+Kailua%2C+HI+96734&amp;ll=21.391668,-157.741243" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">151 Hekili St<br/>Kailua, HI 96734</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mochiko Chicken, Kalbi Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Boots &amp;amp; Kimo&#x27;s offers a menu full of authentic Hawaiian food. Guy digs the Mochiko chicken, which is made from boneless chicken thighs that are marinated, fried and then served with macaroni potato salad and rice. He also raves about the Hawaiian-style kalbi ribs, which are both spicy and sweet.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">International Family Style</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/kailua/boots---kimo_s-homestyle-kitchen" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.74124,21.39167,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Kuma&#x27;s Corner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Kuma&#x27;s Corner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60618 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7736048769" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">773-604-8769</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.kumascorner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.kumascorner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Kuma%27s+Corner%2C+2900+W+Belmont+Ave%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60618&amp;ll=41.939544,-87.700450" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2900 W Belmont Ave<br/>Chicago, IL 60618</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mastodon, The Slayer, Kuma Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When this bar opened, it was all about craft brews and music, but soon the burgers (almost all named for bands) caught on. Graham Elliot is fan of the Mastodon, a beefy patty topped with strips of crispy bacon and a squirt of bourbon-laced barbecue sauce, plus a slice of melty cheese and a pile of fried onions. It&#x27;s the perfect fuel for rocking the night away.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Their Own Way</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/kuma-s-corner" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.70045,41.93954,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Wrecking Bar Brewpub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Wrecking Bar Brewpub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlanta, GA 30307 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4042212600" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">404-221-2600</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.wreckingbarbrewpub.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.wreckingbarbrewpub.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Wrecking+Bar+Brewpub%2C+292+Moreland+Ave+NE%2C+Atlanta%2C+GA+30307&amp;ll=33.762321,-84.349747" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">292 Moreland Ave NE<br/>Atlanta, GA 30307</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">House Pastrami Sandwich, Specialty Beers, Cheddarwurst Corn Dogs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Housed in an old mansion, this funky little brewpub is keeping it local, with specialty beers that are brewed onsite and upscale bar food made with regionally sourced ingredients. &quot;Down here at the pub, they scratch-make everything,&quot; Guy explained. Even the meats are cured in-house, like the pastrami that Guy enjoyed in a flavorful sandwich layered with meat, kimchi and melted cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Finger Lickin&#x27; Food</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/wrecking-bar-brewpub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.34975,33.76232,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>White Palace Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">White Palace Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60607 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3129397167" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(312) 939-7167</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.whitepalacegrill.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.whitepalacegrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=White+Palace+Grill%2C+1159+S+Canal+St%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60607&amp;ll=41.867550,-87.638968" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1159 S Canal St<br/>Chicago, IL 60607</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Veal Parmesan, Short Rib Dinners</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, host Guy Fieri discovers a true urban oasis at the White Palace Grill in Chicago, Il, a 68-year-old, American institution where 3 a.m. means veal parmesan and short rib dinners.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Open 24/7</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/white-palace-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.63897,41.86755,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tre Kronor</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tre Kronor</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60625 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7732679888" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 267-9888</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.trekronorrestaurant.com/#/home" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.trekronorrestaurant.com/#/home</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tre+Kronor%2C+3258+W+Foster+Ave%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60625&amp;ll=41.975912,-87.710989" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3258 W Foster Ave<br/>Chicago, IL 60625</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meatballs with Lingonberries, House-Cured Gravlax</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Get drunken salmon gravlax made with aquavit and other new twists on traditional Nordic food at Tre Kronor. Try the classic Swedish Meatballs with mashed potatoes and lingonberry sauce and the Danish Aebleskivers made with apples to satisfy your sweet tooth before heading out.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Global Grub</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/tre-kronor-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.71099,41.97591,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Depot Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Depot Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60644</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7732878422" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 287-8422</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/the-depot-american-diner-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/the-depot-american-diner-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Depot+Diner%2C+5840+W+Roosevelt+Rd%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60644&amp;ll=41.865757,-87.770833" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5840 W Roosevelt Rd<br/>Chicago, IL 60644</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pot Roast Sandwich, Apple Pancakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Depot Diner is operating under new ownership since Triple D stopped there, but don&#x27;t worry about missing out on Thanksgiving flavors with that famous turkey sandwich because they&#x27;re still making it the same way. Come ready to eat with your hands and use lots of napkins.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Upper Crust</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/the-depot-american-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.77083,41.86576,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Manny&#x27;s Cafeteria and Delicatessen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Manny&#x27;s Cafeteria and Delicatessen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60607 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3129392855" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(312) 939-2855</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mannysdeli.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mannysdeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Manny%27s+Cafeteria+and+Delicatessen%2C+1141+S.+Jefferson+St.%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60607&amp;ll=41.867793,-87.642063" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1141 S. Jefferson St.<br/>Chicago, IL 60607</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kugel, Corned Beef Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">As a Jewish food specialist, Ted Allen calls Manny&#x27;s noodle kugel &quot;classic&quot; and a &quot;great way to gain a lot of weight.&quot; The kugel in itself merits a trip to Chicago, but diners nationwide head to Manny&#x27;s for all the tasty Jewish fare, including the chicken soup and massive corned beef sandwiches.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tasty Traditions</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/ted-allen-noodle-kugel-mannys-cafeteria-and-delicatessen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.64206,41.86779,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tufano&#x27;s Vernon Park Tap</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tufano&#x27;s Vernon Park Tap</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60607 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3127333393" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(312) 733-3393</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/tufanosrestaurant/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">sites.google.com/site/tufanosrestaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tufano%27s+Vernon+Park+Tap%2C+1073+W.+Vernon+Park+Place%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60607&amp;ll=41.872875,-87.654017" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1073 W. Vernon Park Place<br/>Chicago, IL 60607</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Stuffed Shells, Lemon Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For more than 80 years, Tufano&#x27;s Vernon Park Tap has been dishing out old-school Italian dishes. The James Beard award and solid Chicago fan base prove the quality of their classic dishes. The way Guy sees it, their signature lemon chicken is nothing short of a &quot;bodacious bird.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All in the Family<br/>Just Like Yesterday</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/tufanos-vernon-park-tap-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.65402,41.87288,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Original Vito &amp; Nick&#x27;s Pizzeria</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Original Vito &amp; Nick&#x27;s Pizzeria</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60652 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (12 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7737352050" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 735-2050</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://vitoandnicks.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">vitoandnicks.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Original+Vito+%26+Nick%27s+Pizzeria%2C+8433+South+Pulaski+Rd%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60652&amp;ll=41.739274,-87.721318" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">8433 South Pulaski Rd<br/>Chicago, IL 60652</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cheese and Egg Pizza, Italian Beef Pizza, Thin Crust Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Thin-crust pizza may be blasphemy in Chicago, but The Original Vito &amp;amp; Nick&#x27;s thin-crust pizza has been winning over locals for more than 90 years. Guy dropped by for the signature cheese and egg pizza. Stop by if you want a slice because Vito &amp;amp; Nick&#x27;s doesn&#x27;t deliver.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diner&#x27;s Drive-ins and Dives: Best from the Road<br/>Best of Pizza<br/>Something from Everywhere</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/the-original-vito-nicks-pizzeria-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.72132,41.73927,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Taste of Peru</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Taste of Peru</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60626 &middot; &#9733; 4.6 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7733814540" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 381-4540</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tasteofperu.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tasteofperu.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Taste+of+Peru%2C+6545+N+Clark+St%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60626&amp;ll=42.001323,-87.671275" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6545 N Clark St<br/>Chicago, IL 60626</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lomo Saltado (Sauteed Rib Eye with French Fries), Beef Heart, Papa Rellena (Stuffed Potatoes)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Peruvians and Chicagoans both head to Taste of Peru in Chicago for authentic chicken tamales, Anticuchos (beef heart kebabs) and Guy&#x27;s favorite: Lomo Saltado. Along with succulent fried beef, onions and tomatoes, this dish adds french fries, making it what Guy calls &quot;right on-point goodness.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Home And Away<br/>Global Flavor Faves<br/>Triple D Nation: Global Goodies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/taste-of-peru-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.67127,42.00132,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nana</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nana</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60608 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3129292486" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(312) 929-2486</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.nanaorganic.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.nanaorganic.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nana%2C+3267+S+Halsted+St%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60608&amp;ll=41.834539,-87.646180" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3267 S Halsted St<br/>Chicago, IL 60608</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pupusas, Shrimp and Oyster Po&#x27; Boy</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s visit to Nana&#x27;s was a lesson in sustainability. Run by a crew of four siblings and Nana, their mother, the restaurant is all about local, organic produce. On Triple D, Guy devoured the sizzling pupusas. As for the shrimp and oyster po&#x27; boys, you could eat those morning, noon and night.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Primetime Pork<br/>Gettin&#x27; Fresh</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/nana-organic-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.64618,41.83454,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Irazu</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Irazu</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60647 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7732525687" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 252-5687</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.irazuchicago.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.irazuchicago.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Irazu%2C+1865+N+Milwaukee%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60647&amp;ll=41.915537,-87.685056" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1865 N Milwaukee<br/>Chicago, IL 60647</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicharron, Pepito Sandwiches</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A mother-son duo brings the flavors of Costa Rica to Chicago at the family-friendly Irazu. On Triple D, Guy sampled two traditional dishes: classic fried Chicarron with pico de gallo; and Pepito sandwiches made with steak, onions and black beans, before telling Chef Henry Cerdas, &amp;quot;You rocked it.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Latin Street Food<br/>Global Flavor Faves</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/irazu-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.68506,41.91554,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Alley</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Alley</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Aiea 96701 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8084886854" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 488-6854</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.aieabowl.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.aieabowl.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Alley%2C+99-115+Aiea+Heights+Dr%2C+Aiea+96701&amp;ll=21.378619,-157.929736" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">99-115 Aiea Heights Dr<br/>Aiea 96701</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oxtail Soup, Grilled Coca Cola-Marinated Turkey Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">It may be located within a bowling alley, but The Alley Restaurant is cooking up some of the best dishes on the island. Take the Oxtail Soup, for example, which is simmered with Chinese spices, ginger, mushrooms and peanuts. Guy also recommends the Grilled Coca Cola-Marinated Turkey Sandwich.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Righteous Bites<br/>Takeout: Ordering All Kinds of Flavor<br/>Triple D Nation: Slurpin&#x27; Soup</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/aiea/the-alley-restaurant-" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.92974,21.37862,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Opal Thai Food</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Opal Thai Food</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Honolulu, HI 96817 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8083818091" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-381-8091</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Opal-Thai-Food/104259789661580" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Opal-Thai-Food/104259789661580</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Opal+Thai+Food%2C+1030+Smith+St%2C+Honolulu%2C+HI+96817&amp;ll=21.630130,-158.072114" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1030 Smith St<br/>Honolulu, HI 96817</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Glazed Garlic Chicken Wings, Larb with Pork, Pad Thai</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Opel is a Bangkok native and is cooking up classic Thai favorites as well as creating some new ones. Guy could not keep his hands off of the glazed garlic chicken wings topped with fried basil. The larb with pork and veggies in a lettuce wrap and the pad thai noodles also impressed Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crazy for Chicken<br/>All Family, All the Time<br/>Triple D Nation: Italian, Thai and Pie</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/honolulu/opal-thai-food-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-158.07211,21.63013,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nico&#x27;s at Pier 38</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nico&#x27;s at Pier 38</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Honolulu, HI 96817 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8085401377" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 540-1377</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.nicospier38.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.nicospier38.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nico%27s+at+Pier+38%2C+1133+N+Nimitz+Hwy%2C+Honolulu%2C+HI+96817&amp;ll=21.318587,-157.877667" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1133 N Nimitz Hwy<br/>Honolulu, HI 96817</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Marlin Burger, Fried Ahi Belly, Opah with Crab Stuffing</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">French-born owner Nico Chaize came to Hawaii as a foreigner, but Hawaii soon became his home. Guy found him at the Honolulu fish auction at 5:30 in the morning, hand-selecting opah fish for the day&#x27;s special. And although his fish is gourmet, he serves it takeout style without the gourmet price.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Cultural Cookin&#x27;<br/>Triple D Goes Hawaiian<br/>Best of the Beach</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/honolulu/nicos-pier-38-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.87767,21.31859,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rainbow Drive-In</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rainbow Drive-In</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Honolulu, HI 96815 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8087370177" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-737-0177</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rainbowdrivein.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rainbowdrivein.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rainbow+Drive-In%2C+3308+Kanaina+Ave%2C+Honolulu%2C+HI+96815&amp;ll=21.275926,-157.814545" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3308 Kanaina Ave<br/>Honolulu, HI 96815</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Loco Moco (Rice, Hamburger, Egg, Homemade Gravy), Burgers, Chili Hot Dogs, Macaroni Salad</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eating at Rainbow Drive-In has been a Hawaiian tradition for over 50 years, with locals and tourists lining up for the legendary mixed and Loco Moco plates. Guy&#x27;s Loco Moco included a hamburger patty, fried egg, rice and &amp;quot;are-you-kidding-me?&amp;quot; gravy. As Guy says, this is fast food Hawaiian-style. It hasn&#x27;t changed much since it was founded in 1961 by Seiju Ifuku, who learned to cook during World War II while serving in the Army. It&#x27;s located just outside Waikiki, making it popular with hungry surfers and locals looking for a quick, hearty and affordable meal.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fast Food Their Way</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/honolulu/rainbow-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.81454,21.27593,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Murphy&#x27;s Bar &amp; Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Murphy&#x27;s Bar &amp; Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Honolulu, HI 96813 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8085310422" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 531-0422</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://murphyshawaii.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">murphyshawaii.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Murphy%27s+Bar+%26+Grill%2C+2+Merchant+St.%2C+Honolulu%2C+HI+96813&amp;ll=21.310143,-157.863446" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2 Merchant St.<br/>Honolulu, HI 96813</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Shepherd&#x27;s Pie, Murphy&#x27;s Best Corned Beef &amp; Cabbage</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Located in downtown Honolulu, Murphy&#x27;s Bar and Grill doesn&#x27;t serve traditional island cuisine. As Guy learned on DDD, Murphy&#x27;s brings the luck of the Irish to locals. The &amp;quot;shovel fest&amp;quot; begins with open-faced turkey sandwiches, homemade shepherd&#x27;s pie and the best pint of Guinness on the island.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bringin&#x27; It Home</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/honolulu/murphys-bar-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.86345,21.31014,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Honky Tonk BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Honky Tonk BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60608 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3122267427" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(312) 226-7427</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://honkytonkbbqchicago.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">honkytonkbbqchicago.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Honky+Tonk+BBQ%2C+1800+S+Racine%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60608&amp;ll=41.857790,-87.656767" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1800 S Racine<br/>Chicago, IL 60608</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brisket, Beef Tips, Ribs, Honky Tonk Sweet and Spicy Salad Dressing</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You can&#x27;t get more Honky Tonk than the Memphis in May award-winning pulled pork that&#x27;s served at this Chicago championship-BBQ eatery. From St. Louis spares to baby backs to the big beef short ribs, they&#x27;re serving up real-deal slow cooked barbecue with three signature sauces.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Barbequed, Baked, and Brined<br/>Meaty Masterpieces</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/honky-tonk-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.65677,41.85779,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hopleaf Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hopleaf Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60640 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7733349851" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 334-9851</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://hopleaf.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">hopleaf.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hopleaf+Bar%2C+5148+N.+Clark+St.%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60640&amp;ll=41.975818,-87.668513" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5148 N. Clark St.<br/>Chicago, IL 60640</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mussels</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This bar doesn&#x27;t know the meaning of pub food. They&#x27;re nixing regular fries and burgers and adding in none other than head cheese (that&#x27;s pig&#x27;s head) charcuterie. Or, try a duck and Gruyere crepe. Add a side of frites to that and order from the lengthy menu of beers, and you&#x27;ll never barhop again.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Belly Up</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/hopfleaf-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.66851,41.97582,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jawaiian Irie Jerk Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jawaiian Irie Jerk Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Honolulu, HI 96816 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8083882916" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(808) 388-2916</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://jawaiianiriejerk.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">jawaiianiriejerk.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jawaiian+Irie+Jerk+Restaurant%2C+1137+11th+Ave.%2C+Honolulu%2C+HI+96816&amp;ll=21.282569,-157.800172" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1137 11th Ave.<br/>Honolulu, HI 96816</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jerk Wings, Jamaican Goat Curry</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this restaurant Chef Caswell Simmonds is serving up Jamaican fare with an &amp;quot;aloha&amp;quot; attitude. Guy described eating the savory jerk wings as a &amp;quot;party in his mouth.&amp;quot; The Jamaican goat curry, a classic Caribbean recipe and a local favorite, Guy called &amp;quot;off the hoof.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grilling Greats<br/>Dynamic Dishes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/honolulu/jawaiian-irie-jerk-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.80017,21.28257,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fresh Catch</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fresh Catch</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Honolulu, HI 96816 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8087357653" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">808-735-7653</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.freshcatch808.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.freshcatch808.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fresh+Catch%2C+3109+Waialae+Ave%2C+Honolulu%2C+HI+96816&amp;ll=21.288079,-157.810036" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3109 Waialae Ave<br/>Honolulu, HI 96816</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ahi Poke with Limu Seaweed, Smoked Tako Poke (Smoked Octopus)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Restaurant owner, chef and octopus wrangler Reno Henriques uses only the freshest seafood to make over 30 types of poke, a traditional raw fish Hawaiian salad. Guy adored the ahi poke with limu seaweed. Feeling adventurous? Try the spicy smoked octopus topped with tobiko, an island favorite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Coastal Cuisine<br/>Surf &#x27;N&#x27; Turf Jackpot</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/hi/honolulu/fresh-catch-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-157.81004,21.28808,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Glenn&#x27;s Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Glenn&#x27;s Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60613 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7735061720" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 506-1720</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.glennsdiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.glennsdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Glenn%27s+Diner%2C+1820+W+Montrose+Ave%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60613&amp;ll=41.961738,-87.675514" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1820 W Montrose Ave<br/>Chicago, IL 60613</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Wings, Alaskan Red King Crab Legs, Baby Back Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Although Glenn&#x27;s Diner steps outside diner norms with a menu boasting 16 different kinds of fish (including a few straight from Hawaii), Guy was surprised to learn they do breakfast their way too. Here, you can order more than 25 kinds of cereal, everything from Cap&#x27;n Crunch to Cheerios.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Not What You&#x27;d Expect</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/glenns-diner-restaurant2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.67551,41.96174,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sun Wah BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sun Wah BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60640</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7737691254" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">773-769-1254</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sunwahbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sunwahbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sun+Wah+BBQ%2C+5039+N+Broadway%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60640&amp;ll=41.974028,-87.659628" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5039 N Broadway<br/>Chicago, IL 60640</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Whole Roasted Suckling Pig, Crispy Duck</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This family-operated restaurant has some of the best and most authentic Chinese barbecue in Chicago. Served up Hong Kong-style, menu highlights include peanut butter egg rolls, crispy Beijing duck and a whole roasted suckling pig that Rahm Fama says is &quot;mouthwateringly delicious.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Pork to Pasta</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/sun-wah-bbq-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.65963,41.97403,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Smoque BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Smoque BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chicago, IL 60641 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7735457427" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(773) 545-7427</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.smoquebbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.smoquebbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Smoque+BBQ%2C+3800+N+Pulaski+Rd%2C+Chicago%2C+IL+60641&amp;ll=41.950185,-87.727698" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3800 N Pulaski Rd<br/>Chicago, IL 60641</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ Beans, Brisket, Macaroni and Cheese, Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoque is all about barbecue tradition; even the baked beans are infused with smoky flavor. The ribs are simply irresistible, as they&#x27;re coated in a Memphis-style dry rub and glazed with a sweet, tangy barbecue sauce. Guy can&#x27;t get enough of the brisket, which he declares &quot;capital T, tender.&quot;&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Real Deal BBQ<br/>BBQ Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/il/chicago/smoque-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.72770,41.95019,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ivan&#x27;s Cookhouse</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ivan&#x27;s Cookhouse</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">North Miami Beach, FL 33181</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3059444826" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-944-4826</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://ivanscookhouse.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">ivanscookhouse.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ivan%27s+Cookhouse%2C+14815+Biscayne+Blvd%2C+North+Miami+Beach%2C+FL+33181&amp;ll=25.910118,-80.157370" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">14815 Biscayne Blvd<br/>North Miami Beach, FL 33181</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Griot, Grilled Whole Snapper, Grilled Octopus</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From his post inside an open-plan kitchen, Chopped champion Ivan Dorvil plates up sizzling staples from his native Haiti, including griot. To make the Haitian classic, Chef Dorvil marinates pork shoulder in a vibrant bath of sour orange juice blended with herbs, spices and Scotch bonnet peppers. The pork is then seared, boiled and fried, resulting in a dish that&#x27;s &quot;super, super tender,&quot; Guy says. It&#x27;s served with plantains, black mushroom rice and pikliz (a fiery pickled-cabbage condiment).</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sausage, Seafood and Shawarma</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/north-miami-beach/ivans-cookhouse-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.15737,25.91012,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blue Marlin Fish House Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blue Marlin Fish House Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">North Miami Beach, FL 33160 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3059578822" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(305) 957-8822</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.facebook.com/BlueMarlinFishHouseMiami" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/BlueMarlinFishHouseMiami</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blue+Marlin+Fish+House+Restaurant%2C+2500+NE+163rd+St%2C+North+Miami+Beach%2C+FL+33160&amp;ll=25.925394,-80.149707" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2500 NE 163rd St<br/>North Miami Beach, FL 33160</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Mahi Mahi, Smoked Fish Dip, Fried Grouper</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This fish house was on the brink of destruction until some new owners revived the seafood eatery. Guy enjoyed the smoked mahi mahi and described it as flaky, creamy, soft and smoky. The smoked fish dip won his heart with its creamy texture and &amp;quot;full flavors.&amp;quot; Be sure to try the fried grouper too.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/north-miami-beach/blue-marlin-fish-house-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.14971,25.92539,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Havana Hideout</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Havana Hideout</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Lake Worth, FL 33460 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5615858444" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(561) 585-8444</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.havanahideout.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.havanahideout.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Havana+Hideout%2C+509+Lake+Ave%2C+Lake+Worth%2C+FL+33460&amp;ll=26.615541,-80.053756" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">509 Lake Ave<br/>Lake Worth, FL 33460</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hideout Empanada, Fresh Made Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Enjoy a slice of paradise on the tropical patio of this food truck. While known for its sangrias and tacos, the truck also impressed Guy with a toasty Cuban sandwich. While there is a new owner, they&#x27;re still serving up the same delicious bites like pionono, a sweet and spicy fried stuffed plantain.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Little Bit of Everywhere</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/lake-worth/havana-hideout-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.05376,26.61554,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tampa Bay Brewing Company</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tampa Bay Brewing Company</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tampa, FL 33605 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8132471422" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(813) 247-1422</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tampabaybrewingcompany.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tampabaybrewingcompany.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tampa+Bay+Brewing+Company%2C+1600+E+8th+Ave%2C+Tampa%2C+FL+33605&amp;ll=27.960655,-82.441628" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1600 E 8th Ave<br/>Tampa, FL 33605</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crispy Hot Wings, Thai Curry Mussels</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">With an on-site brewery and 12 house beers on tap, this family-owned spot proves that beer&#x27;s not just for drinking. The kitchen infuses a bevy of entrees with brews, from the crispy wings with Red Eye Ale cider sauce to the Thai Curry Mussels With Wild Warthog Weizen, which Guy deemed &amp;quot;prime time.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homemade &amp; Homebrewed<br/>Late Night Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/tampa/tampa-bay-brewing-co-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.44163,27.96065,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Taco Bus</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Taco Bus</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tampa, FL 33603 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (12 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8132325889" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(813) 232-5889</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://tampatacobus.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">tampatacobus.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Taco+Bus%2C+913+E+Hillsborough+Ave%2C+Tampa%2C+FL+33603&amp;ll=27.996070,-82.471754" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">913 E Hillsborough Ave<br/>Tampa, FL 33603</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Torta Chilorio, Butternut Squash Tostada</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Taco Bus operates out of a 35-foot school bus and is always open. According to Guy, the torta chilorio, which is filled with pulled pork, cheese, cilantro, cabbage and tomatoes, is &quot;out of bounds.&quot; The butternut squash tostada hailing from the Yucatan is a fan favorite for its good texture.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Breakfast, Lunch and Dinner<br/>Mex to the Max</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/tampa/taco-bus-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.47175,27.99607,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Danny&#x27;s All-American Diner &amp; Dairy Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Danny&#x27;s All-American Diner &amp; Dairy Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tampa 33610 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8137400606" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(813) 740-0606</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://dannysamericandiner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">dannysamericandiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Danny%27s+All-American+Diner+%26+Dairy+Bar%2C+4406+N+Falkenburg+Rd%2C+Tampa+33610&amp;ll=27.985574,-82.335403" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4406 N Falkenburg Rd<br/>Tampa 33610</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Triple Play Burger, Chili Cheeseburger, Cuban Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Athletics and food unite at this diner where all the burgers are named after sports Hall of Famers. Try the Triple D Triple Play burger with mojo pork and pastrami invented by Guy. If you&#x27;re not afraid to get messy, try the juicy chili cheeseburger or the Cuban with capicolla and Genoa salami.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Coast to Coast Classics<br/>Grilling Greats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/tampa/dannys-all-american-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.33540,27.98557,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Alpine Steakhouse</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Alpine Steakhouse</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sarasota, FL 34231 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9419223797" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(941) 922-3797</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.alpinesteak.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.alpinesteak.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Alpine+Steakhouse%2C+4520+S+Tamiami+Trail%2C+Sarasota%2C+FL+34231&amp;ll=27.288062,-82.531030" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4520 S Tamiami Trail<br/>Sarasota, FL 34231</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">TurDucKen</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Alpine Steakhouse is famous for one thing: TurDucKen. Guy found this place on Triple D, but added it to The Best Thing I Ever Ate. The TurDucKen begins with turkey. Then andouille sausage, duck, chicken, and much, much more are added. Twelve hours in the oven and you have the king of all birds.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ultimate Turkey Fest<br/>Talkin&#x27; Turkey</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/sarasota/alpine-steakhouse-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.53103,27.28806,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Federal Miami</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Federal Miami</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami, FL 33137</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3057589559" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(305) 758-9559</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thefederalmiami.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thefederalmiami.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Federal+Miami%2C+5132+Biscayne+Blvd%2C+Miami%2C+FL+33137&amp;ll=25.823442,-80.187438" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5132 Biscayne Blvd<br/>Miami, FL 33137</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Buffalo Style Pig Wing, Venison Chili</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Federal is a modern American tavern that offers comforting, scrumptious dishes. The Buffalo Style Pig Wing, served with blue cheese mousse and pickled celery and carrots, has Guy reaching for more. Another menu item he recommends is the venison chili with grit fries, chipotle and Cotija cheese.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grillin&#x27;, Chillin&#x27; and Huli Huli Chicken</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/the-federal-miami" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.18744,25.82344,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Whisk</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Whisk</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami, FL 33143</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7862688350" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(786) 268-8350</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.whiskgourmet.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.whiskgourmet.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Whisk%2C+7382+SW+56th+Ave%2C+Miami%2C+FL+33143&amp;ll=25.702655,-80.284431" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7382 SW 56th Ave<br/>Miami, FL 33143</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Okra, Braised Baby-back Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Siblings Brendan and Kristin Connor put their own twist on traditional low-country dishes at Whisk. Guy recommends the cornmeal-fried okra, which combines fresh fish flavor with a crunchy texture. He&#x27;s also a convert of the beer-braised baby back ribs, which he calls &quot;tender, porky, fall-apart-y.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dynamite Duos</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/whisk" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.28443,25.70266,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Scully&#x27;s Tavern</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Scully&#x27;s Tavern</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami 33173 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3052717404" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-271-7404</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.scullystavern.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.scullystavern.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Scully%27s+Tavern%2C+9809+SW+72nd+St%2C+Miami+33173&amp;ll=25.702142,-80.351998" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">9809 SW 72nd St<br/>Miami 33173</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Escargot, Buffalo Wings, Mahi Mahi Sandwiches</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Guy dropped by Scully&#x27;s Tavern he wasn&#x27;t expecting Belgian escargot and garlic butter, but Scully&#x27;s regulars are enamored of the French dish from Scully&#x27;s eclectic menu. For a real treat, try the potato chip-encrustedmahi-mahi sandwich. It&#x27;s &quot;melt-in-your-mouth delicious.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Fried and Smoked<br/>Something Different<br/>Takeout: Bold Bites Brought Home<br/>Amazing Appetizers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/scullys-tavern-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.35200,25.70214,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sakaya Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sakaya Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami 33127 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3055768096" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(305) 576-8096</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sakayakitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sakayakitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sakaya+Kitchen%2C+3401+N+Miami+Ave%2C+Miami+33127&amp;ll=25.809351,-80.194191" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3401 N Miami Ave<br/>Miami 33127</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Duck Sandwich, Chunk&#x27;d Tots</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Korean fusion eatery Sakaya has many in Miami raving about its Cracklin&#x27; duck sandwich. Smothered in a special Korean sauce called ssamjang to add some serious Asian flavor, it had Guy declaring &quot;game over.&quot; Guy also loved the Chunk&#x27;d tots: a mixture of tater tots and bulgogi (marinated beef).</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Cross-Country Delivery<br/>Extra Helpings<br/>Triple D Nation: Meat Lovers<br/>Triple D Nation: Surf and Turf<br/>Keepin&#x27; It Real</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/sakaya-kitchen" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.19419,25.80935,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mojo Donuts and Fried Chicken</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mojo Donuts and Fried Chicken</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami, FL 33165 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3052236656" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-223-6656</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.mojodonuts.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mojodonuts.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mojo+Donuts+and+Fried+Chicken%2C+8870+Bird+Rd%2C+Miami%2C+FL+33165&amp;ll=25.732678,-80.339558" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">8870 Bird Rd<br/>Miami, FL 33165</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Brulee Sandwich, Abuelita Doughnut</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This artisan doughnut shop in Miami is creating sweet mouthwatering masterpieces and some savory surprises. There are over 200 varieties of hand-rolled and hand-cut doughnuts. For a sweet treat, try the Abuelita which is stuffed with rice pudding and topped with swirls of dulce de leche. The adventurous should try the Chicken Brulee Sandwich. In this creation, crispy chicken tenders are sandwiched inside a bruleed doughnut, topped with a mild cheddar sauce and showered in bacon. &quot;This changes the fried chicken sandwich game,&quot; said Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rollin&#x27; in the Dough</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/mojo-donuts-and-fried-chicken-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.33956,25.73268,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mr. &amp; Mrs. Bun</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mr. &amp; Mrs. Bun</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami, FL 33193 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.mrandmrsbuns.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mrandmrsbuns.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mr.+%26+Mrs.+Bun%2C+15572+Sunset+Dr%2C+Miami%2C+FL+33193&amp;ll=25.706083,-80.330994" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">15572 Sunset Dr<br/>Miami, FL 33193</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Asado con Palta, Pollo Chi Jao Kai, Aji de Gallina Bites</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gian Carlo Accinelli and his wife are putting their love on the line all in the name of their buns at Mr. &amp; Mrs. Bun. The Peruvian couple serve all of their unique sandwiches on their signature, house-made buns. For the Asado con Palta sandwich, slow-cooked eye of round is piled on a fresh bun with avocado and crispy onions and then served with the jus from the cooked meat. &quot;That is without question one of the best sandwiches I&#x27;ve had in a long time,&quot; said Guy. &quot;It&#x27;s actually giving me goose bumps.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lights-Out Latin</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/mr-and-mrs-bun-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.33099,25.70608,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Milly&#x27;s Empanada Factory</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Milly&#x27;s Empanada Factory</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami, FL 33183 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3057911848" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-791-1848</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.millysfactory.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.millysfactory.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Milly%27s+Empanada+Factory%2C+13911+SW+66th+St%2C+Miami%2C+FL+33183&amp;ll=25.706148,-80.420620" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">13911 SW 66th St<br/>Miami, FL 33183</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Empanadas, Pabe Yo-Yo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Milly Martinez has been serving up authentic Venezuelan food in South Florida for more than two decades. Now her son, Jose Atencio, is taking the cuisine to another level with some creative riffs on the classics. The Pabe Yo-Yo is like a Venezuelan Monte Cristo with bread made of sweet plantains surrounding ham and queso blanco which is then deep fried and stuffed with braised beef. &quot;This crazy,&quot; said Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">International Intrigue</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/millys-empanada-factory-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.42062,25.70615,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Miami Smokers</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Miami Smokers</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami, FL 33125 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7865205420" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">786-520-5420</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://miamismokers.com/home/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">miamismokers.com/home</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Miami+Smokers%2C+306+NW+27th+Ave%2C+Miami%2C+FL+33125&amp;ll=25.775656,-80.239498" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">306 NW 27th Ave<br/>Miami, FL 33125</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Damn Hot Wings, Thai Sweet and Sour Wings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The distinctive smell of smoked meats wafting out the doors of this charcuterie joint has proven irresistible to many a passerby. Step inside to order sandwiches like the Floridian, which Guy called &quot;dynamite.&quot; A wild boar sausage is ground in-house, then nestled on a baguette slicked with avocado puree. It&#x27;s topped with spicy mayo, pickled peppers and onions, and one unusual addition: orange segments.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked, Grilled and Fried</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/miami-smokers-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.23950,25.77566,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Latin House Burger &amp; Taco Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Latin House Burger &amp; Taco Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami 33183 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7869536331" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">786-953-6331</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.latinhousegrill.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.latinhousegrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Latin+House+Burger+%26+Taco+Bar%2C+8695+SW+124th+Ave%2C+Miami+33183&amp;ll=25.687969,-80.393599" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">8695 SW 124th Ave<br/>Miami 33183</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chimi Burrito, Lobster Lollipop</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy goes crazy for the Chimi Burritos at Latin House. The tortilla is stuffed with &quot;Chuchi&quot; rice, three cheeses, sweet plantains and a protein of your choice. It is flash-fried and then topped with pico de gallo, avocado lime sauce and crema sauce. The lobster lollipops are also a treat.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Around the World<br/>Deep-Fried Favorites<br/>From Meatballs to Lollipops</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/latin-house-burger---taco-bar" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.39360,25.68797,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>LOBA</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">LOBA</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami, FL 33138</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7865366692" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(786) 536-6692</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.lobarestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.lobarestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=LOBA%2C+7420+Biscayne+Blvd%2C+Miami%2C+FL+33138&amp;ll=25.843591,-80.184678" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7420 Biscayne Blvd<br/>Miami, FL 33138</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Patacon, Lentil Croquettes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Latin joint is a serving up some serious comfort food and is a favorite among the locals. Stand-out dishes include the Patacon (an11-inch fried plantain with rib-eye steak, pork belly, rice, guacamole, pico de gallo and chimichurri) and Lentil Croquettes (served withbeet tzatziki and avocado).The restaurant is open for brunch, lunch and dinner.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Italian, Hawaiian and Colombian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/loba" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.18468,25.84359,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>La Camaronera Restaurant &amp; Fish Market</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">La Camaronera Restaurant &amp; Fish Market</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami, FL 33135 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3056423322" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(305) 642-3322</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.garciabrothersseafood.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.garciabrothersseafood.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=La+Camaronera+Restaurant+%26+Fish+Market%2C+1952+W+Flagler+St%2C+Miami%2C+FL+33135&amp;ll=25.772296,-80.227667" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1952 W Flagler St<br/>Miami, FL 33135</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Camarones Fritos (Breaded Shrimp), Cangrejo Moro (Stone Crab), Fried Fish, Hush Puppies</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Since 1976, Camaronera has been serving and selling fresh seafood the Little Havana way. On Triple D, Guy learned that means that every lobster, shrimp and green plantain gets coated in golden batter and fried. For the best fish-fry, locals order the signature Pan con Minuta snapper sandwich.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Between the Bread<br/>Best of the Beach<br/>Old Time Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/la-camaronera-restaurant-fish-market-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.22767,25.77230,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jamaica Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jamaica Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami, FL 33173 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3055962585" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-596-2585</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.jamaicakitchen.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jamaicakitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jamaica+Kitchen%2C+8736+SW+72+St%2C+Miami%2C+FL+33173&amp;ll=25.700992,-80.335325" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">8736 SW 72 St<br/>Miami, FL 33173</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oxtail, Pig Tails &amp; Beans, Pork &amp; Hamchoy, Spicy Beef Patty, Curry Goat</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oxtail, curried goat and steamed peas with pig tail are just some of the local favorites at Jamaica Kitchen. The family-operated joint has passed down its Jamaican-Chinese recipes for generations. Guy loved the pork belly with pickled mustard greens and fiery-hot beef patties.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">World Class Flavor<br/>A Taste of Everywhere</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/jamaica-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.33532,25.70099,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tap Tap Haitian Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tap Tap Haitian Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami Beach 33139 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3056722898" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-672-2898</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami-beach/tap-tap-haitian-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami-beach/tap-tap-haitian-restaurant-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tap+Tap+Haitian+Restaurant%2C+819+5th+St%2C+Miami+Beach+33139&amp;ll=25.774807,-80.136556" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">819 5th St<br/>Miami Beach 33139</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Marinated Pork, Malanga Fritters, Pwason Gwosel (Whole Haitian Snapper)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Once a filmmaker in Haiti, Katherine Kean&#x27;s trip inspired her to open Miami&#x27;s Tap Tap, a Haitain eatery with bright, colorful murals. On Triple D, Guy devoured Haitian-raised Chef Gary Sanon-Jules&#x27;s tender Kurobuta pork griot and the malanga fritters with the not-so-Haitian watercress sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You Can Say That Again</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami-beach/tap-tap-haitian-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.13656,25.77481,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Taquiza</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Taquiza</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami Beach 33139 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3052032197" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(305) 203-2197</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.taquizatacos.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.taquizatacos.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Taquiza%2C+1351+Collins+Ave%2C+Miami+Beach+33139&amp;ll=25.785012,-80.130705" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1351 Collins Ave<br/>Miami Beach 33139</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Totopos (Chips), Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Situated on Miami Beach&#x27;s main drag, Taquiza draws the crowds hungry for well-made tacos and primo people-watching. Even the chips are far from standard, as the masa (dough) is made in-house, using non-GMO blue corn from Mexico. &quot;Outrageous,&quot; Guy declared. He also dug the tacos, trying one version stuffed with marinated hanger steak and another filled with crisp toasted grasshoppers and fresh guacamole.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">South Beach Sizzle</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami-beach/taquiza-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.13070,25.78501,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>M.E.A.T. Eatery and Tap Room</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">M.E.A.T. Eatery and Tap Room</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Islamorada, FL 33036 &middot; &#9733; 3.9 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3058523833" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-852-3833</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://meateatery.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">meateatery.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=M.E.A.T.+Eatery+and+Tap+Room%2C+Mile+Marker+88+on+US+1+Oceanside+88005+Overseas+Hwy%2C+Islamorada%2C+FL+33036&amp;ll=24.971270,-80.556835" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Mile Marker 88 on US 1 Oceanside 88005 Overseas Hwy<br/>Islamorada, FL 33036</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wings, Pork Rinds</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">As the name suggests, this spot is a meat-lovers&#x27; haven. The menu is chock-full of burgers, barbecue and other meaty dishes, as Guy found out when he stopped by on Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives. Both the wings and the pork rinds had him hooked.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hot Meat and Cool Veg</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/islamorada/meat-eatery-and-tap-room-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.55683,24.97127,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hofbrau Beer Hall</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hofbrau Beer Hall</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami Beach, FL 33139</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3055388066" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-538-8066</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://hofbraumiami.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">hofbraumiami.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hofbrau+Beer+Hall%2C+943+Lincoln+Rd%2C+Miami+Beach%2C+FL+33139&amp;ll=25.790730,-80.138624" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">943 Lincoln Rd<br/>Miami Beach, FL 33139</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sauerbraten, Currywurst</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This spot is a stateside version of the classic Hofbruhaus beer hall in Germany, so the menu features traditional recipes from the homeland, with a few modern twists. Hofbrau&#x27;s version of sauerbraten features beef knuckle that&#x27;s soaked for seven days in a spice-and-herb-laced wine marinade, braised, then drenched in a rich gravy that Guy wanted to drink by the bucketful. A side of pretzel dumplings completes the dish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">South Beach Sizzle</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami-beach/hofbrau-beer-hall-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.13862,25.79073,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Green Turtle Inn</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Green Turtle Inn</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Islamorada, FL 33036 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3056642006" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-664-2006</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.greenturtleinn.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.greenturtleinn.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Green+Turtle+Inn%2C+81219+Overseas+Hwy%2C+Islamorada%2C+FL+33036&amp;ll=24.912395,-80.641380" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">81219 Overseas Hwy<br/>Islamorada, FL 33036</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turtle Chowder</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When in Islamorada, Fla., Guy just had to head to this local fixture to try none other than the restaurant&#x27;s signature turtle chowder. The Green Turtle Inn has been dishing up this popular dish for decades, along with other Southern favorites.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos, Turtles and Tri-Tip</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/islamorada/green-turtle-inn-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.64138,24.91239,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Islamorada Shrimp Shack</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Islamorada Shrimp Shack</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Islamorada, FL 33036 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3056648433" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-664-8433</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.islamoradashrimpshack.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.islamoradashrimpshack.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Islamorada+Shrimp+Shack%2C+81901+Overseas+Hwy%2C+Islamorada%2C+FL+33036&amp;ll=24.919091,-80.633737" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">81901 Overseas Hwy<br/>Islamorada, FL 33036</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Shrimp Fritters, Senator-Style Hook and Cook</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Shrimp dishes may be a specialty at this spot, but Chef-Owner Jill Jahn doesn&#x27;t stop there, as Guy found out when he visited. Chef Jahn served him veggie-laced shrimp fritters with a spicy remoulade sauce, then cooked up a freshly caught mangrove snapper that Guy brought straight from the boat to her kitchen and had him declaring this Florida Keys native the &quot;real deal.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoke and Seafood</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/islamorada/islamorada-shrimp-shack-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.63374,24.91909,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Flakowitz of Boynton Bakery &amp; Deli Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Flakowitz of Boynton Bakery &amp; Deli Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boynton Beach, FL 33437 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5617424144" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(561) 742-4144</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.flakowitzofboynton.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.flakowitzofboynton.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Flakowitz+of+Boynton+Bakery+%26+Deli+Restaurant%2C+7410+W+Boynton+Beach+Blvd%2C+Boynton+Beach%2C+FL+33437&amp;ll=26.526242,-80.162687" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7410 W Boynton Beach Blvd<br/>Boynton Beach, FL 33437</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Matzo Ball Soup, Stuffed Cabbage, Corned Beef Sandwich, Potato Knish</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Although it&#x27;s located in Florida, this diner is serving up New York-style Jewish deli classics. Guy indulged in the comforting matzo ball soup and couldn&#x27;t get enough of the stuffed cabbage with sweet and sour sauce. If you&#x27;re hungry, try the overstuffed corned beef sandwich or the hot potato knish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Holiday Hoopla<br/>Biscuits, Bagels and BLT&#x27;s</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/boynton-beach/flakowitz-of-boynton-bakery-deli-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.16269,26.52624,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Keegan&#x27;s Seafood Grille</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Keegan&#x27;s Seafood Grille</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Indian Rocks Beach, FL 33785 &middot; &#9733; 3.9 (15 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7275962477" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(727) 596-2477</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.keegansseafood.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.keegansseafood.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Keegan%27s+Seafood+Grille%2C+1519+Gulf+Blvd%2C+Indian+Rocks+Beach%2C+FL+33785&amp;ll=27.898657,-82.847876" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1519 Gulf Blvd<br/>Indian Rocks Beach, FL 33785</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gumbo, Grouper Sandwich, Keegan&#x27;s She Crab Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Guy Fieri, stops by Keegan&#x27;s Seafood Grille, in Indian Rocks Beach, FL, a local favorite where the cuisine has a Mediterranean twist.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Seaside Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/indian-rocks-beach/keegans-seafood-grille-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.84788,27.89866,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jose&#x27;s Real Cuban Food</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jose&#x27;s Real Cuban Food</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bradenton, FL 34210 &middot; &#9733; 4.1 (15 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9417954898" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(941) 795-4898</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://josesrealcubanfood.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">josesrealcubanfood.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jose%27s+Real+Cuban+Food%2C+8799+Cortez+Rd+W%2C+Bradenton%2C+FL+34210&amp;ll=27.461464,-82.649786" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">8799 Cortez Rd W<br/>Bradenton, FL 34210</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Piccadillo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">One bite of Jose&#x27;s Lechon Asado at Jose&#x27;s Real Cuban Food and Guy knew it was the real deal. His seal of Triple D approval didn&#x27;t end there. Cuban-born Jose Baserva uses his mother&#x27;s recipes in recreating authentic Cuban sandwiches and mouthwatering piccadillo, which Jose calls &quot;Cuban&quot; ground beef.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/bradenton/joses-real-cuban-food-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.64979,27.46146,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Local</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Local</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Coral Gables, FL 33134</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3056485687" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-648-5687</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://thelocal150.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">thelocal150.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Local%2C+150+Giralda+Ave.%2C+Coral+Gables%2C+FL+33134&amp;ll=25.751139,-80.257775" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">150 Giralda Ave.<br/>Coral Gables, FL 33134</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Belly BLT, Roasted Bone Marrow, Hen and Dumplings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This local eatery is a one-stop shop for craft brews and what Guy called &quot;amped-up, down-home cooking.&quot; They&#x27;re slinging Southern-inspired dishes that incorporate unexpected twists, such as the signature Roasted Bone Marrow. Femur bones are brined, coated in a housemade barbecue spice and roasted, then topped with whipped horseradish butter, relish and mixed greens for an ultra-rich bite. Another standout is the Lamb Belly BLT.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chew and Brew</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/coral-gables/the-local-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.25778,25.75114,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Butcher Shop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Butcher Shop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">West Palm Beach 33401 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5618122336" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(561) 812-2336</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.butchershopbeergarden.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.butchershopbeergarden.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Butcher+Shop%2C+209+6th+Street%2C+West+Palm+Beach+33401&amp;ll=26.719088,-80.051175" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">209 6th Street<br/>West Palm Beach 33401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Igor and Fred Niznik, a father-son duo, took on the creative challenge of opening a restaurant and combined their passion for food, beer and quality to transform a butcher shop into a dining hotspot. The full service butcher shop is still a feature of the restaurant; patrons can order cuts and all of the meat for the restaurarnt is cut in-house.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mouthwatering Meat</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/west-palm-beach/the-butcher-shop-beer-garden---grill" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.05117,26.71909,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cholo Soy Cocina</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cholo Soy Cocina</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">West Palm Beach 33405 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5616197018" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(561) 619-7018</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="cholosoycocina.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">cholosoycocina.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cholo+Soy+Cocina%2C+3715+S+Dixie+Hwy%2C+West+Palm+Beach+33405&amp;ll=26.677840,-80.054775" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3715 S Dixie Hwy<br/>West Palm Beach 33405</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Feed your senses with a trip to the only gourmet latin street food in town: Cholo Soy Cocina. Borrowing an Ecuadorian slang term for the country&#x27;s indigenous people, &quot;Cholo&quot; also means &quot;mixed or ghetto.&quot; It&#x27;s a name that reflects an original Latin -American fusion food experience that begins before your first delicious bite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pasta, Potatoes and Pescatarian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/west-palm-beach/cholo-soy-cocina" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.05478,26.67784,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ted Peters Famous Smoked Fish</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ted Peters Famous Smoked Fish</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">South Pasadena, FL 33707 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7273817931" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(727) 381-7931</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://tedpetersfish.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">tedpetersfish.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ted+Peters+Famous+Smoked+Fish%2C+1350+S+Pasadena+Ave%2C+South+Pasadena%2C+FL+33707&amp;ll=27.755909,-82.737233" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1350 S Pasadena Ave<br/>South Pasadena, FL 33707</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Famous Smoked Fish Dinner</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Alton&#x27;s favorite smoked fish isn&#x27;t necessarily business in the front and party in the back. Instead, at Ted Peters Famous Smokehouse, the mullet, smoked in red oak, simply tastes like heaven. Guy visited, too, witnessing the 56-year-old method for making the legendary mahi-mullet fish spread.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fun in the Sun<br/>Viewer&#x27;s Choice</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/south-pasadena/ted-peterrsquos-famous-smoked-fish-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.73723,27.75591,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>13 Gypsies</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">13 Gypsies</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Jacksonville, FL 32204 &middot; &#9733; 3.1 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9043890330" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(904) 389-0330</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.13gypsies.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.13gypsies.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=13+Gypsies%2C+887+Stockton+St%2C+Jacksonville%2C+FL+32204&amp;ll=30.315095,-81.689063" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">887 Stockton St<br/>Jacksonville, FL 32204</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spanish Chorizo with Honey Sauteed Pears, Roman-Style Gnocchi</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The philosophy of 13 Gypsies is Old World techniques with Old World flavors from Spain. Guy got a kick out of the Roman Gnocchi because instead of little pillows, 13 Gypsies brings back an &amp;quot;original&amp;quot; flat version of gnocchi. As for Guy&#x27;s all-time favorite dish? The tasso. One word: porkiliciousness.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Globetrottin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/jacksonville/13-gypsies-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.68906,30.31509,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Whale&#x27;s Rib</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Whale&#x27;s Rib</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Deerfield Beach, FL 33441 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (12 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9544218880" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">954-421-8880</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.whalesrib.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.whalesrib.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Whale%27s+Rib%2C+2031+NE+2nd+St%2C+Deerfield+Beach%2C+FL+33441&amp;ll=26.316699,-80.076565" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2031 NE 2nd St<br/>Deerfield Beach, FL 33441</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oysters Rockefeller, Whale Juice, Dolphin Sandwich (Mahi Mahi Sandwich)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A little bit of the signature honey mustard called &quot;Whale Juice&quot; goes a long way alongside the amazing local seafood at this funky little joint. Try their spin on oysters Rockefeller, loaded with spinach, tomatoes and oozing, mouthwatering cheese. The mahi mahi sandwich is also a standout.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Best of the Beach<br/>Only At This Joint</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/deerfield-beach/whales-rib-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.07656,26.31670,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sonny&#x27;s Famous Steak Hogies</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sonny&#x27;s Famous Steak Hogies</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hollywood 33024 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9549890561" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">954-989-0561</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sonnysfamoussteakhogies.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sonnysfamoussteakhogies.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sonny%27s+Famous+Steak+Hogies%2C+1857+N+66th+Ave%2C+Hollywood+33024&amp;ll=26.011499,-80.221017" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1857 N 66th Ave<br/>Hollywood 33024</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Steak Hoagie (Philly Cheesesteak), Meatball Hoagie, Sandwiches</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Take a ride down to Sonny&#x27;s to see why &quot;folks are lining up just like back in 1958&quot; to get a cheese steak. Their sandwiches haven&#x27;t changed since Sonny left it in the hands of his son John, who&#x27;s rolling the bread the same way it was made back when they first opened.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Upper Crust<br/>Super Sandwiches<br/>Takeout: Real Deal Delivery<br/>Triple D Nation: Diners, Drive-Ins and Delis</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/hollywood/sonnys-famous-steak-hogies-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.22102,26.01150,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Irie Island Eats</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Irie Island Eats</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Marathon 33050 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3055099398" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(305) 509-9398</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://irieislandeats.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">irieislandeats.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Irie+Island+Eats%2C+4540+Overseas+Highway%2C+Marathon+33050&amp;ll=24.713842,-81.084313" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4540 Overseas Highway<br/>Marathon 33050</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Irie Island Easts is dedicated to preparing meals that taste good and creating a dining experience that feels good. They are inspired by cuisine of islands around the world and pride themselves on using fresh ingredients in a farm-to-table sourcing style and cooking over a wood fire.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pig&#x27;s Feet, Mojo and Chow-Chow</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/irie-island-eats" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.08431,24.71384,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Castaway Waterfront</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Castaway Waterfront</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Marathon 33050 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3057436247" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(305) 743-6247</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://castawayfloridakeys.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">castawayfloridakeys.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Castaway+Waterfront%2C+1406+Ocean+View+Ave.%2C+Marathon+33050&amp;ll=24.704275,-81.109707" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1406 Ocean View Ave.<br/>Marathon 33050</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Castaway Waterfront proudly serves fresh seafood, as well as feature sushi, steak and beer on the menu.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Taste of the Tropics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/castaway-waterfront" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.10971,24.70428,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Kababi Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Kababi Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sunrise 33351 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/restaurants-in-sunrise/kababi-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/restaurants-in-sunrise/kababi-cafe-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Kababi+Cafe%2C+3828+N.+University+Dr%2C+Sunrise+33351&amp;ll=26.171140,-80.255936" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3828 N. University Dr<br/>Sunrise 33351</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you&#x27;re looking for real-deal Iranian in Florida, Kababi Cafe is the place to go. Chef and owner Hamid Shirdelbrings authentic flavors from his childhood growing up in Iran to this beloved spot. Guy loved the Bagali Polo, lamb shank with dill rice and the Fesenjan, a thick, tangy stew of chicken, pomegranate and pureed walnuts. He called it, &quot;Iranian comfort food 101.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Vikings to Wings</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/restaurants-in-sunrise/kababi-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.25594,26.17114,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Herbie&#x27;s Bar &amp; Chowder House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Herbie&#x27;s Bar &amp; Chowder House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Marathon, FL 33050 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3057436373" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(305) 743-6373</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="herbiesbar.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">herbiesbar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Herbie%27s+Bar+%26+Chowder+House%2C+6350+Overseas+Hwy%2C+Marathon%2C+FL+33050&amp;ll=24.717997,-81.068623" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6350 Overseas Hwy<br/>Marathon, FL 33050</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Herbie&#x27;s has been a part of the Keys dining scene since the 1940&#x27;s, making it the oldest continually operated restaurant in Marathon! Originally named Maggie&#x27;s Chowder House, it operated until the Konrath family purchased in the the 1950&#x27;s, and was renamed Fishnet&#x27;s Bar and Chowder House. In the 1960&#x27;s with new owner&#x27;s, it was donned Herbie&#x27;s. Fast-forward to 2014 and we have the Herbie&#x27;s of today. Owners Peter and Shirley Demaras have combined their experience in the culinary arts as well as their knowledge of craft beer, and brought back true scratch cooking sure to please whatever your palatial needs are.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pasta, Potatoes and Pescatarian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/herbie-s-bar---chowder-house" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.06862,24.71800,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Grampa&#x27;s Bakery &amp; Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Grampa&#x27;s Bakery &amp; Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Dania Beach 33004 &middot; &#9733; 2.8 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9549232163" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">954-923-2163</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.grampasbakery.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.grampasbakery.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Grampa%27s+Bakery+%26+Restaurant%2C+17+SW+First+Street%2C+Dania+Beach+33004&amp;ll=26.050690,-80.144077" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">17 SW First Street<br/>Dania Beach 33004</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pancakes, Lamb Shank, Cake, Cookies</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pancakes and dinner rolls may be diner staples, but most restaurants can&#x27;t say they&#x27;ve made them entirely from scratch like Grampa&#x27;s. Starting as a small bakery, owner Ronnie Grampa expanded to a full-blown eatery complete with classic dishes like tender lamb shank, which got Guy&#x27;s seal of approval.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Best of Breakfast<br/>Comfort Food<br/>Triple D Nation: Smothered and Covered</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/dania-beach/grampas-bakery-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.14408,26.05069,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Culhane&#x27;s Irish Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Culhane&#x27;s Irish Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlantic Beach, FL 32233 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9042499595" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(904) 249-9595</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.culhanesirishpub.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.culhanesirishpub.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Culhane%27s+Irish+Pub%2C+967+Atlantic+Blvd%2C+Atlantic+Beach%2C+FL+32233&amp;ll=30.325728,-81.410747" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">967 Atlantic Blvd<br/>Atlantic Beach, FL 32233</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guinness Beef Stew, Lamb Burger Sliders</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This pub&#x27;s signature dish is quintessentially Irish: The Guinness Beef Stew made with Angus beef is marinated in Guinness and slow-cooked with vegetables and seasonings for a &quot;rich, flavorful&quot; result, Guy says. He also raves about the Blarney Lamb Sliders with curry aioli and the Dingle Fish Pie.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Late Night Legends<br/>Comfort Food With Attitude</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/atlantic-beach/culhanes-irish-pub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.41075,30.32573,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>California Tacos To Go</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">California Tacos To Go</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tampa, FL 36613 &middot; &#9733; 3.9 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9419718226" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(941) 971-8226</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.californiatacostogo.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.californiatacostogo.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=California+Tacos+To+Go%2C+1450+Skipper+Rd%2C+Tampa%2C+FL+36613&amp;ll=28.081429,-82.443805" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1450 Skipper Rd<br/>Tampa, FL 36613</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">California Fish Taco</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you head over to California Tacos to Go in Tampa, Fla., expect a quick, al fresco experience. As Guy learned on Triple D, they serve their tacos in an outdoor patio only -- like Guy&#x27;s perfect California fish taco made with super thinly sliced cabbage slaw and spicy white chile sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Kraut to Couscous</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/tampa/california-tacos-to-go-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.44380,28.08143,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Fish House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Fish House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Key Largo, FL 33037 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3054514665" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-451-4665</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.fishhouse.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fishhouse.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Fish+House%2C+102401+Overseas+Hwy%2C+Key+Largo%2C+FL+33037&amp;ll=25.124286,-80.413012" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">102401 Overseas Hwy<br/>Key Largo, FL 33037</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Matecumbe, Smoked Fish Dip, Key Lime Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Part cafe, part local market, this Key Largo restaurant offers fresh seafood for dining in and takeout. Both Bobby and Guy are fans of the Matecumbe. This house specialty features locally caught fish that&#x27;s topped with a salsa made from lemon, tomatoes, onions and capers, then quickly baked in a searing-hot convection oven. This simple approach results in a &quot;delicate, tender&quot; dish, Guy says.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoke and Seafood</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/key-largo/the-fish-house-restaurant-seafood-market-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.41301,25.12429,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>DiGiorgio&#x27;s Cafe Largo</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">DiGiorgio&#x27;s Cafe Largo</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Key Largo, FL 33037 &middot; &#9733; 2.0 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3054514885" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-451-4885</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.keylargo-cafelargo.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.keylargo-cafelargo.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=DiGiorgio%27s+Cafe+Largo%2C+99530+Overseas+Hwy%2C+Key+Largo%2C+FL+33037&amp;ll=25.093057,-80.443033" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">99530 Overseas Hwy<br/>Key Largo, FL 33037</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Veal Chop Florentine, Truffle Lobster Mac and Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Snowbirds from the East Coast flock here when they want a taste of authentic Italian-American cuisine. A must-try is the Veal Chop Florentine, which is dipped in a mixture of panko breadcrumbs and shredded Parmesan cheese, topped with prosciutto and mozzarella, then roasted and finished with a mushroom-studded Marsala wine sauce. The result is &quot;tender, salty, crunchy (and) garlicky,&quot; Guy declared.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">International Appeal</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/key-largo/digiorgios-cafe-largo-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.44303,25.09306,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pilot House Marina &amp; Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pilot House Marina &amp; Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Key Largo, FL 33037</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3054513142" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-451-3142</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://pilothousemarina.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">pilothousemarina.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pilot+House+Marina+%26+Restaurant%2C+13+Seagate+Blvd%2C+Key+Largo%2C+FL+33037&amp;ll=25.087895,-80.440510" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">13 Seagate Blvd<br/>Key Largo, FL 33037</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Harvey&#x27;s Fish Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This waterfront complex seemingly has it all: a glass-bottom bar with live music and drink specials, an attached marina and a restaurant with seafood dishes that lure both tourists and locals alike. Guy tried a grilled cheese sandwich stuffed with fresh black grouper and was hooked.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Succulent Sandwiches</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/key-largo/pilot-house-marina-and-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.44051,25.08789,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pirate Republic Seafood</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pirate Republic Seafood</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fort Lauderdale 33315 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://piraterepublicseafood.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">piraterepublicseafood.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pirate+Republic+Seafood%2C+400+SW+3rd+Avenue%2C+Fort+Lauderdale+33315&amp;ll=26.117280,-80.146172" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">400 SW 3rd Avenue<br/>Fort Lauderdale 33315</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Don&#x27;t be fooled by the pirate theme at this seafood restaurant in Fort Lauderdale, Florida, the food is the real deal. Brazillian-born owners Claudia and Roberto Guerios, spent most of their life on the Caribbean and they&#x27;re bringing legit global flavors to their cuisine. Everything is fresh and delicious but don&#x27;t miss the Seafood Moqueca, a coconut-laced, tomato seafood stew with a touch of spice from a homemade pepper sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sicilian and Seafood</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/ft-lauderdale/pirate-republic-seafood-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.14617,26.11728,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Meatball Stoppe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Meatball Stoppe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Orlando 32822 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4072706505" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">407-270-6505</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/orlando/the-meatball-stoppe-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/orlando/the-meatball-stoppe-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Meatball+Stoppe%2C+7325+Lake+Underhill+Rd%2C+Orlando+32822&amp;ll=28.539717,-81.286691" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7325 Lake Underhill Rd<br/>Orlando 32822</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Traditional Meatballs, Vegetarian Meatballs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">As the name suggests, meatballs are the inspiration behind this family-run Orlando restaurant. Chef-Owner Isabella Morgia di Vicari dresses up the comforting classic in a myriad of different ways. Guy Fieri and Justin Warner opted for Nonna&#x27;s Traditional meatballs made of ground pork. These beauties are punched up with a bit of cayenne pepper, baked for 12 minutes and then simmered in roasted tomato sauce and chicken stock. &quot;It&#x27;s a cross between light and dense,&quot; said Guy after biting into one of the juicy meatballs, which come served over creamy polenta. For those diners who prefer to skip the meat, the restaurant also offers a vegetarian option made of roasted vegetables and lentils. &quot;They&#x27;re super tender,&quot; Guy declared.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wonder Women</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/orlando/the-meatball-stoppe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.28669,28.53972,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Se7en Bites Bakeshop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Se7en Bites Bakeshop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Orlando 32803 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4072030727" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">407-203-0727</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Se7enbites/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/Se7enbites</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Se7en+Bites+Bakeshop%2C+617+Primrose+Dr%2C+Orlando+32803&amp;ll=28.551856,-81.347152" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">617 Primrose Dr<br/>Orlando 32803</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Pot Pie, Vanilla Bean Bourbon Bacon Moon Pie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The menu at this cozy bakery tucked away in Orlando&#x27;s Milk District extends beyond confections, as Guy discovered when he stopped by on Triple D. Favorites include a chicken pot pie featuring a flaky, buttery crust stuffed with exquisitely seasoned chicken, mirepoix, potatoes and peas in a silky bechamel sauce. When it comes to dessert, there are plenty of decadent choices. One of the most indulgent options, however, is the Vanilla Bean Bourbon Bacon Moon Pie. &quot;That is legit,&quot; said Guy after sampling the sweet treat, which features silky homemade marshmallows laced with vanilla and bourbon.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Dinner and Dessert That Delivers<br/>Wonder Women</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/orlando/se7en-bites-bakeshop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.34715,28.55186,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Saigon Noodle and Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Saigon Noodle and Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Orlando, FL 32803 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4075327373" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">407-532-7373</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.saigonnoodleandgrill.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.saigonnoodleandgrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Saigon+Noodle+and+Grill%2C+101+N.+Bumby+Avenue%2C+Orlando%2C+FL+32803&amp;ll=28.544237,-81.351802" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">101 N. Bumby Avenue<br/>Orlando, FL 32803</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pho, Shaking Beef</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy brings fellow Food Network Star Justin Warner to Saigon Noodle Grill for phenomenal pho, shaking beef and other authentic Vietnamese classics.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Beef and Barbecue</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/orlando/saigon-noodle-and-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.35180,28.54424,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Pastrami Project</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Pastrami Project</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Orlando 32803 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3218042686" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">321-804-2686</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pastramiproject.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pastramiproject.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Pastrami+Project%2C+825+N+Magnolia+Ave%2C+Orlando+32803&amp;ll=28.545980,-81.376741" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">825 N Magnolia Ave<br/>Orlando 32803</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">New-York Style Pastrami Sandwiches, Bagel and Lox, Reuben Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If it seems like The Pastrami Project&#x27;s George Markward has studied the New York deli scene it&#x27;s because he has. The former IT guy dishes out legit classics from his Jewish deli-on-wheels. Guy gushes about the juicy New York-style pastrami and the luscious lox.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Multicultural Cooking</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/orlando/the-pastrami-project-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.37674,28.54598,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Singleton&#x27;s Seafood Shack</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Singleton&#x27;s Seafood Shack</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlantic Beach, FL 32233 &middot; &#9733; 2.9 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9042464442" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">904-246-4442</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/singletonsmayport/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/singletonsmayport</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Singleton%27s+Seafood+Shack%2C+4728+Ocean+St%2C+Atlantic+Beach%2C+FL+32233&amp;ll=30.394587,-81.430555" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4728 Ocean St<br/>Atlantic Beach, FL 32233</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Shrimp, Minorcan Clam Chowder, Collard Greens</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Singleton Seafood Shack has Cajun fried shrimp, steamed shrimp and even shrimp burgers (and the seafood&#x27;s so local you can hear the boats pull up). But Guy&#x27;s DDD trip saw another side to the shack with The Sheepshead signature fish, perfectly grilled with Singleton&#x27;s own blackening spice blend.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Surf &#x27;n Turf</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/atlantic-beach/singletons-seafood-shack-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.43056,30.39459,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Munch&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Munch&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">St. Petersburg, FL 33705 &middot; &#9733; 2.6 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7278965972" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(727) 896-5972</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://munchburger.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">munchburger.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Munch%27s%2C+3920+6th+St+S%2C+St.+Petersburg%2C+FL+33705&amp;ll=27.732978,-82.640543" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3920 6th St S<br/>St. Petersburg, FL 33705</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Creamed Chipped Beef</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Before Munch&#x27;s became the go-to spot for fried chicken and shepherd&#x27;s pie, it was Munch&#x27;s Restaurant &amp;amp; Sundries, selling candy and toys and even acting as a post office. When Guy swung by, he only saw a St. Petersburg, Fla., institution serving up tasty, legit hash and a killer Creamed Chipped Beef.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grillin&#x27; and Smokin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/st-petersburg/munchs-restaurant-sundries-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-82.64054,27.73298,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>11th Street Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">11th Street Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami Beach, FL 33139 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3055346373" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(305) 534-6373</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.eleventhstreetdiner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.eleventhstreetdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=11th+Street+Diner%2C+1065+Washington+Ave%2C+Miami+Beach%2C+FL+33139&amp;ll=25.781806,-80.132296" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1065 Washington Ave<br/>Miami Beach, FL 33139</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Chops with Apples and Raisins</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Since 1992, locals looking for late-night food in Miami&#x27;s South Beach have turned to the 11th Street Diner. Locals love ordering the Argentinian steak any time of day. But Guy couldn&#x27;t get enough of the flavor-packed pork chops with apples and a raisin, calling it one of Triple D&#x27;s greatest chops.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">American Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami-beach/11th-street-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.13230,25.78181,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lou&#x27;s Beer Garden</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lou&#x27;s Beer Garden</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami Beach, FL 33141</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3057047879" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-704-7879</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://lousbeergarden.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">lousbeergarden.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lou%27s+Beer+Garden%2C+7337+Harding+Ave%2C+Miami+Beach%2C+FL+33141&amp;ll=25.859122,-80.121902" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7337 Harding Ave<br/>Miami Beach, FL 33141</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Paella, Vongola</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Don&#x27;t let Lou&#x27;s location in the backyard of a boutique hotel fool you: The food here &quot;isn&#x27;t from your average snack shack,&quot; Guy declares. The menu changes seasonally, but keep an eye out for the paella. Calasparra rice is soaked in homemade chicken stock and plenty of saffron, then mixed with chorizo, roasted red peppers, clams, shrimp, mussels and calamari to create a dish bursting with rich seafood flavors.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">South Beach Sizzle</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami-beach/lous-beer-garden-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.12190,25.85912,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mrs. Potato</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mrs. Potato</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Orlando, FL 32811 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4072900991" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">407-290-0991</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mrspotato.net/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mrspotato.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mrs.+Potato%2C+4550+S.+Kirkman+Rd%2C+Orlando%2C+FL+32811&amp;ll=28.496211,-81.458750" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4550 S. Kirkman Rd<br/>Orlando, FL 32811</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Carne Seca Rosti Potato, Chicken Catupiry Baked Potato</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Potato lovers go now to Mrs. Potato where the humble spud is elevated to delicious heights. Try their signature rosti potato, which is like the biggest hash brown you&#x27;ve ever seen stuffed with whatever your heart desires. &quot;I want like ten of these to go,&quot; says Guy of a Brazilian dried beef-stuffed dome of deliciousness. For the most-indulgent baked potato you&#x27;ve ever tasted, order one of their huge Idaho spuds filled with pulled chicken and Catupiry, a Brazillian cream cheese. &quot;That is ridonkulous,&quot; gushes Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey, Taters and Dogs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/orlando/mrs-potato-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.45875,28.49621,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bad Boy Burrito</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bad Boy Burrito</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Key West, FL 33040 &middot; &#9733; 2.6 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3052922697" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(305) 292-2697</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.badboyburrito.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.badboyburrito.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bad+Boy+Burrito%2C+1220+Simonton+St%2C+Key+West%2C+FL+33040&amp;ll=24.549279,-81.796128" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1220 Simonton St<br/>Key West, FL 33040</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kobe Beef Burrito, Fish Taco</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Local hot spot Bad Boy Burrito serves up some of the best, most-authentic Mexican food in the area. A favorite item is the &quot;hot, salty, sweet&quot; Kobe beef burrito stuffed with beans, rice and other tasty fillings. Guy is equally impressed with the Cayo Hueso Fish Tacos made with locally caught fish.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kickin&#x27; It in Key West</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/key-west/badboy-burrito" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.79613,24.54928,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Garbo&#x27;s Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Garbo&#x27;s Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Key West, FL 33040 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3053043004" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-304-3004</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://garbosgrillkw.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">garbosgrillkw.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Garbo%27s+Grill%2C+409+Caroline+St+%28between+407+Caroline+St+and+a+parking+lot%29%2C+Key+West%2C+FL+33040&amp;ll=24.555059,-81.779987" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">409 Caroline St (between 407 Caroline St and a parking lot)<br/>Key West, FL 33040</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Umamiburger, Korean BBQ Taco</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eli and Kenna Pancamo bring a fun attitude and serious culinary edge to their food truck, Garbo&#x27;s Grill. Guy was won over by the Umamiburger smothered in chipotle Gouda, calling his first taste of this topping a &quot;history-making moment in Triple D.&quot; The sweet, spicy Korean BBQ tacos are also a hit.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Food Truckapalooza<br/>Kickin&#x27; It in Key West</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/key-west/garbo_s-grill" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.77999,24.55506,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>D.J.&#x27;s Clam Shack</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">D.J.&#x27;s Clam Shack</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Key West, FL 33040 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3052940102" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(305) 294-0102</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.djsclamshack.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.djsclamshack.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=D.J.%27s+Clam+Shack%2C+629+Duval+St%2C+Key+West%2C+FL+33040&amp;ll=24.554077,-81.801224" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">629 Duval St<br/>Key West, FL 33040</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lobster Rolls, Conch Fritters, Garlic Butter Clams</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Key West is known for fresh seafood, and D.J.&#x27;s Clam Shack serves some of the freshest around. Guy digs into the garlic butter clams that are buttery with a spicy zing, thanks to the jalapeno spice. Other popular menu items include lobster rolls and conch fritters.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Extra Helpings<br/>Kickin&#x27; It in Key West</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/key-west/dj_s-clam-shack" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.80122,24.55408,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fat One&#x27;s Hot Dogs &amp; Italian Ice</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fat One&#x27;s Hot Dogs &amp; Italian Ice</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Orlando, FL 32809 &middot; &#9733; 2.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.fatonedogs.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fatonedogs.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fat+One%27s+Hot+Dogs+%26+Italian+Ice%2C+8001+South+Orange+Blossom+Trail%2C+Orlando%2C+FL+32809&amp;ll=28.446654,-81.393917" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">8001 South Orange Blossom Trail<br/>Orlando, FL 32809</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gone Hollywood, Mac Daddy, The Fat One</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For a taste of Coney Island in Orlando stop by Joey Fatone&#x27;s Florida Mall kiosk where he serves up creative hot dogs and Italian ices. Try the guacamole-topped Gone Hollywood or the mac and cheese laden Mac Daddy and then cool off with a legit Italian ice.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey, Taters and Dogs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/orlando/fat-ones-hot-dogs-and-italian-ice-stand" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-81.39392,28.44665,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mrs. Robino&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mrs. Robino&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wilmington, DE 19801</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mrsrobinos.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mrsrobinos.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mrs.+Robino%27s%2C+520+North+Union+St%2C+Wilmington%2C+DE+19801&amp;ll=39.750185,-75.572257" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">520 North Union St<br/>Wilmington, DE 19801</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef Braciole, Meat Ravioli</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This old school Italian joint has been serving up homemade ravioli for five generations. Owner Andrea Wakefield still follows the same red sauce recipe that her great grandmother used in the 1940s. Guy was blown away by the Beef Braciole, which is braised in the oven for three hours and served with a side house-made spaghetti. The meat is so tender, Guy could cut it with a fork. &quot;Tender, it pulls apart, crazy,&quot; he said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef Bonanza</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/de/wilmington/mrs-robinos-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.57226,39.75018,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blue Collar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blue Collar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami, FL 33138 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3057560366" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-756-0366</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bluecollarmiami.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bluecollarmiami.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blue+Collar%2C+6730+Biscayne+Blvd%2C+Miami%2C+FL+33138&amp;ll=25.837844,-80.184624" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6730 Biscayne Blvd<br/>Miami, FL 33138</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Big Ragout, Rock Shrimp Mac &amp; Cheese, Spicy Oxtail</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy heads to this spot to indulge in The Big Ragout Sandwich, a hearty meal featuring five kinds of meats smothered in cheese and served on a roll. Also try the Rock Shrimp Mac &amp; Cheese: A zesty three-cheese sauce is dressed up with wild rock shrimp, then mixed with pasta and finished with bacon.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Wings &#x27;n&#x27; Things<br/>All Stacked Up<br/>Cross Country Comfort Food</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/blue-collar" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.18462,25.83784,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Benny&#x27;s Seafood Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Benny&#x27;s Seafood Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami, FL 33165 &middot; &#9733; 1.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3052271232" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(305) 227-1232</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bennyseafood.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bennyseafood.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Benny%27s+Seafood+Restaurant%2C+2500+SW+107th+Ave.%2C+Miami%2C+FL+33165&amp;ll=25.745837,-80.368651" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2500 SW 107th Ave.<br/>Miami, FL 33165</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mofongo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Triple D, Benny&#x27;s Mofongo caught Guy off guard. Mofo what? The Mofongo dish is a Puerto Rican favorite and now, Guy&#x27;s too, as he added it to The Best Thing I Ever Ate. Made with mashed-up plantains, fried pork skin and then muddled with a baseball bat, this dish is a home run.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">In the Family</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/bennys-seafood-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.36865,25.74584,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blackbrick</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blackbrick</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Miami, FL 33137 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3055738886" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">305-573-8886</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.midtownchinese.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.midtownchinese.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blackbrick%2C+3451+NE+1st+Ave%2C+Miami%2C+FL+33137&amp;ll=25.809357,-80.191936" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3451 NE 1st Ave<br/>Miami, FL 33137</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Har Gow Shrimp Dumpling, Xinjiang Cumin-Lamb Dumpling, Dan Dan Mian, Gong Bao Rabbit, Grandma&#x27;s Red Oxtail, General Tso&#x27;s Florida Gator</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For a modern take on regional Chinese cuisine, head to Blackbrick. Dim sum options include crystal shrimp dumplings, chicken siu mei, cumin-lamb dumplings and barbecued pork buns. Noodles are made in-house for dishes like the dan dan mian, which tosses spicy Szechuan pork ragu with bucatini. Guy is obsessed with dan dan mian. &quot;I can&#x27;t figure out how to get it in my face fast enough,&quot; said Guy between bites.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old Faces, New Places</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/fl/miami/blackbrick-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-80.19194,25.80936,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cabbage Town Market</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cabbage Town Market</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlanta, GA 30312</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/cabbage-town-market-closed-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/cabbage-town-market-closed-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cabbage+Town+Market%2C+198+Carroll+St.+SE%2C+Atlanta%2C+GA+30312&amp;ll=33.749208,-84.368035" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">198 Carroll St. SE<br/>Atlanta, GA 30312</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Totally Unexpected</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/cabbage-town-market-closed-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.36804,33.74921,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Buttermilk Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Buttermilk Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Atlanta 30342 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6787323274" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">678-732-3274</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://buttermilkkitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">buttermilkkitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Buttermilk+Kitchen%2C+4225+Roswell+Rd+NE%2C+Atlanta+30342&amp;ll=33.869841,-84.380614" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4225 Roswell Rd NE<br/>Atlanta 30342</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Biscuit, Lox Plate</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Guy wanted to try the best biscuits in Atlanta, he made a beeline for this spot. Chopped champion Suzanne Vizethann serves Southern staples like the Chicken Biscuit: Sweet tea-brined chicken is double-dredged for extra crunch, fried, then served on a buttery biscuit smothered in red pepper jam.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Biscuits to Brisket<br/>Takeout: Carnivore Delivery<br/>Rockstar Chefs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ga/atlanta/buttermilk-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-84.38061,33.86984,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Farmer &amp; The Cow</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Farmer &amp; The Cow</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wilmington, DE 19801 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3024075957" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(302) 407-5957</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/de/wilmington/farmer-and-the-cow-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/de/wilmington/farmer-and-the-cow-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Farmer+%26+The+Cow%2C+413+N+Market+St.%2C+Wilmington%2C+DE+19801&amp;ll=39.740636,-75.551283" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">413 N Market St.<br/>Wilmington, DE 19801</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">That&#x27;ll Do Pig Burger, Bacon Jam Mac and Cheese, Fried Chicken Skins</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Even though head chef Jasper Singh is a vegetarian, the menu at this cozy Wilmington joint doesn&#x27;t skimp on meaty dishes-the restaurant is known for their killer burgers, like the That&#x27;ll Do Pig burger. The burger is made by topping a thick beef patty with three different kinds of pork: sweet bacon jam, hearty thick cut bacon slices and a house-made bacon mayo, which is all topped off with a layer of crunchy tater tots. Guy thought the burger was so amazing, he joked that they should rename the restaurant &quot;The Pig and the Cow&quot; in its honor.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crazy Chicken and Twisted Burgers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/de/wilmington/farmer-and-the-cow-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.55128,39.74064,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Locale BBQ Post</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Locale BBQ Post</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wilmington 19805</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3025104929" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">302-510-4929</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://localebbqpost.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">localebbqpost.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Locale+BBQ+Post%2C+1014+N.+Lincoln+St%2C+Wilmington+19805&amp;ll=39.754085,-75.568100" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1014 N. Lincoln St<br/>Wilmington 19805</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brisket, Pork Butt</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">While looking for a space to produce pickles for his growing enterprise, Wilmington Pickling Company, Chef Daniel Sheridan stumbled upon a building on the edge of Little Italy and a concept for a whole new venture started coming to life. With the goal of pairing barbecue with pickles, Sheridan teamed up with a couple of other food-loving locals, Mike Gallucio and Justin Mason. Locale BBQ Post took off like hickory wood in a smoker upon opening, selling out of meat by 2 p.m. on its first day. Now well past its infancy, the place still draws the crowds for its wide selection of &#x27;cue smoked with flavorful cherry wood.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A World of Barbecue</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/de/wilmington/locale-bbq-post-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.56810,39.75409,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Stoney&#x27;s Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Stoney&#x27;s Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wilmington 19803 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.stoneyspub.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.stoneyspub.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Stoney%27s+Pub%2C+3007+Concord+Pike%2C+Wilmington+19803&amp;ll=39.799658,-75.547445" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3007 Concord Pike<br/>Wilmington 19803</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fish and Chips, Roast Beef &amp; Yorkshire Pudding</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Mike Stone got off the road, after years of being a record promoter for the biggest names in the music business, he opened up this legit English pub in Wilmington, Delaware. Stoney&#x27;s Pub makes all the classics, including an unbeatable Fish and Chips and amazing Yorkshire Pudding served with rare roast beef. &quot;You&#x27;re going to have to pry this out of my hands,&quot; said Guy of thegravy-laced classic.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">British, Hawaiian and Mexican</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/de/wilmington/stoneys-pub-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.54744,39.79966,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Luigi Vitrone&#x27;s Pastabilities</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Luigi Vitrone&#x27;s Pastabilities</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Wilmington, DE 19805 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://ljvpastabilities.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">ljvpastabilities.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Luigi+Vitrone%27s+Pastabilities%2C+415+N.+Lincoln+St%2C+Wilmington%2C+DE+19805&amp;ll=39.749012,-75.571794" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">415 N. Lincoln St<br/>Wilmington, DE 19805</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Arancini, Veal Scaloppini Rollatini</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For a taste of Little Italy in Wilmington, head to this funky spot for unforgettable Italian food. Since 1988, Chef and Owner Luigi Vitrone has been serving up regional Italian cuisine in a restaurant that looks like a funky apartment in Milan in the 1970s. Diners love the Gorgonzola-stuffed Arancini and the decadent Veal Scaloppini Rollatini.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sausage, Shawarma and Scaloppini</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/de/wilmington/luigi-vitrones-pastabilities-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-75.57179,39.74901,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Wilson&#x27;s Holy Smoke BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Wilson&#x27;s Holy Smoke BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fairfield, CT 06824 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2033197427" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(203) 319-7427</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.wilsons-bbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.wilsons-bbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Wilson%27s+Holy+Smoke+BBQ%2C+1851+Post+Rd.%2C+Fairfield%2C+CT+06824&amp;ll=41.140903,-73.264252" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1851 Post Rd.<br/>Fairfield, CT 06824</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Memphis Baby Back Ribs, St. Louis Ribs, Pulled Chicken Sandwich, Black-Eyed Pea Salad, Pulled Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy first met pit master Ed Wilson in brisket cooking school. Their reunion couldn&#x27;t have been better, as Wilson served Memphis-style baby back ribs, St. Louis ribs, North Carolina-style pulled pork and, to top it off, a tender chicken sandwich. &amp;quot;Ain&#x27;t no joking,&amp;quot; Guy says. &amp;quot;That bird&#x27;s smoking.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diner&#x27;s Drive-ins and Dives: Best from the Road<br/>BBQ &amp; More<br/>BBQ Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ct/fairfield/wilsons-holy-smoke-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.26425,41.14090,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Super Duper Weenie</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Super Duper Weenie</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fairfield 06825 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2033343647" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">203-334-3647</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.superduperweenie.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.superduperweenie.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Super+Duper+Weenie%2C+306+Black+Rock+Tpke%2C+Fairfield+06825&amp;ll=41.164187,-73.233283" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">306 Black Rock Tpke<br/>Fairfield 06825</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">New Englander Hot Dog, The New Yorker Hot Dog</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">What started as the Super Duper Weenie truck became too small for owner Gary Zemola, who today sells nearly 2,000 dogs each week from his new, permanent locale. Guy&#x27;s glad he could stop by because the hot dogs live up to their name, thanks to handmade toppings and house-baked rolls. Inspiration for the menu&#x27;s hot dog offerings stretches from California to New York, but the house favorite is the New Englander that&#x27;s generously topped with sauerkraut, bacon, raw white onions, mustard and relish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Sendin&#x27; the Surf &amp; Turf<br/>All Kinds of Fast Foods</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ct/fairfield/super-duper-weenie-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.23328,41.16419,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Merritt Canteen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Merritt Canteen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bridgeport 06606 &middot; &#9733; 2.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2033721416" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(203) 372-1416</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.merrittcanteen.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.merrittcanteen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Merritt+Canteen%2C+4355+Main+St%2C+Bridgeport+06606&amp;ll=41.219251,-73.215925" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4355 Main St<br/>Bridgeport 06606</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chili Dogs, Fried Soft-Shell Crab, New England Clam Chowder</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Customers have been coming to this hot dog, burger and seafood eatery for generations. Fans love the deep-fried and grilled hot dogs topped with the fiery hothouse chili. The crispy fried soft-shell crab and the New England clam chowder are &quot;wicked good.&quot; For dessert, try the deep-fried cheesecake.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fully Loaded</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ct/bridgeport/merritt-canteen-inc-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.21592,41.21925,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Corey&#x27;s Catsup and Mustard</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Corey&#x27;s Catsup and Mustard</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Manchester 06040 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8604327755" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(860) 432-7755</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://catsupandmustard.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">catsupandmustard.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Corey%27s+Catsup+and+Mustard%2C+623+Main+St%2C+Manchester+06040&amp;ll=41.773841,-72.521071" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">623 Main St<br/>Manchester 06040</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Auntie Laurie&#x27;s Burger, 7-Burger, Sweet Potato Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owner Corey Wry knows how to make some dreamy burger combos. One of the Triple-D fan-favorite burgers is Auntie Laurie&#x27;s burger on a pretzel bun. If you&#x27;re a meat lover, try the 7-Burger stuffed with BBQ brisket, bacon and a double patty. For a side of fries, order the Sweet Potato with Maple Mayo.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Favorites With A Twist</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ct/manchester/coreys-catsup-and-mustard-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-72.52107,41.77384,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mambo&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mambo&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Glendale, CA 91201 &middot; &#9733; 2.8 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8185458613" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">818-545-8613</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mambosla.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mambosla.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mambo%27s+Cafe%2C+1701+Victory+Blvd%2C+Glendale%2C+CA+91201&amp;ll=34.161572,-118.300127" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1701 Victory Blvd<br/>Glendale, CA 91201</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cuban Sandwich, Tostones Rellenos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Mambo&#x27;s Cafe, the Cuban sandwiches have some serious &quot;mojo,&quot; or sauce made of lemon juice, garlic and seasonings. Not in the mood for a sandwich? Try the Tostones Rellenos, a shrimp ceviche with twice-fried plantains.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Deep-Fried Favorites<br/>Family Style<br/>Triple D Nation: A Little Lighter</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/glendale/mambos-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.30013,34.16157,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Chomp Chomp Nation</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Chomp Chomp Nation</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Irvine, CA 92612 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9496371688" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(949) 637-1688</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.chompchompnation.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.chompchompnation.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Chomp+Chomp+Nation%2C+Irvine%2C+CA+92612&amp;ll=33.658895,-117.828212" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;"><br/>Irvine, CA 92612</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crab Cake, Halal Lamb Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Inspired by Singaporean cuisine, Chef Gina Galvan is cooking up some &quot;exotic tropical Chinese food&quot; in a food truck. Guy loved the crunchy, sweet and salty crab cake topped with slaw and spicy ketchup. The halal lamb burger topped with curry yogurt and edamame sprouts is a &quot;package deal,&quot; said Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fun in the Sun<br/>Real Deal Roots</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/irvine/chomp-chomp-nation-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.82821,33.65890,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mama Cozza&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mama Cozza&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Anaheim, CA 92804 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7146350063" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">714-635-0063</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mamacozzas.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mamacozzas.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mama+Cozza%27s%2C+2170+W+Ball+Rd%2C+Anaheim%2C+CA+92804&amp;ll=33.817310,-117.957639" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2170 W Ball Rd<br/>Anaheim, CA 92804</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza, Chicken Pisano</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Get a taste of old-school Italian at Mama Cozza&#x27;s, home to 20 scratch-made sauces that pretty much guarantee a quality Italian dish. Try Mama&#x27;s sauce or Domery&#x27;s sauce, and don&#x27;t leave without having some pizza here. Guy says, &amp;quot;they&#x27;re doing it the way real Italians do it!&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tried and True<br/>Pizza Party</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/anaheim/mama-cozzas-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.95764,33.81731,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pete&#x27;s Breakfast House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pete&#x27;s Breakfast House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ventura, CA 93001 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8056481130" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(805) 648-1130</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.petesbreakfasthouse.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.petesbreakfasthouse.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pete%27s+Breakfast+House%2C+2055+E+Main+St%2C+Ventura%2C+CA+93001&amp;ll=34.278073,-119.269513" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2055 E Main St<br/>Ventura, CA 93001</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pancake Roll, Chorizo Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this diner, an English husband and wife are livin&#x27; the American dream and serving up breakfast all day. Guy claims that the pancake roll with yogurt and berries is &amp;quot;righteous.&amp;quot; Want a burger? Try the chorizo burger with fiery hot habanero salsa, avocado and flavor that is &amp;quot;out of bounds.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Passin&#x27; The Baton</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/ventura/petes-breakfast-house-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.26951,34.27807,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Paul&#x27;s Live from New York</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Paul&#x27;s Live from New York</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Eureka 95501</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7074425800" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 442-5800</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/PaulsLiveFromNY" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/PaulsLiveFromNY</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Paul%27s+Live+from+New+York%2C+604+F+St%2C+Eureka+95501&amp;ll=40.800919,-124.166007" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">604 F St<br/>Eureka 95501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Margherita Pizza, Sicilian Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Paul&#x27;s Live is a New York pizza joint with one little twist - it&#x27;s in California. Here, you can find &quot;old-school, authentic, East Coast pie.&quot; Guy&#x27;s favorite is the margherita pizza. Deep-dish fans, take note: Paul&#x27;s Sicilian pizza is good enough to have changed Guy&#x27;s mind about thick crusts.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Extra Helpings<br/>All Things New York<br/>Triple D Nation: Guy&#x27;s Going Home</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/eureka/paul_s-live-from-new-york" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-124.16601,40.80092,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bless My Soul Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bless My Soul Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Eureka, CA 95501</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7074431090" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 443-1090</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.blessmysoulcafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.blessmysoulcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bless+My+Soul+Cafe%2C+29+Fifth+St%2C+Eureka%2C+CA+95501&amp;ll=40.801474,-124.170613" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">29 Fifth St<br/>Eureka, CA 95501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crawfish and Shrimp Etouffee</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy swings by Bless My Soul Cafe to sample Creole fusion dishes served up by Mama Janisse. Mama&#x27;s signature green Creole sauce adds some kick to various dishes on the menu, including the crawfish and shrimp etouffee. Regulars return to Bless My Soul for the scrumptious eats and Mama&#x27;s sassy charm.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Extra Helpings<br/>Keepin&#x27; It Real</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/eureka/bless-my-soul-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-124.17061,40.80147,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sabroso! Mexican Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sabroso! Mexican Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Garden Grove, CA 92843 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7145377080" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(714) 537-7080</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://sabrosomexgrill.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">sabrosomexgrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sabroso%21+Mexican+Grill%2C+13129+Harbor+Blvd%2C+Garden+Grove%2C+CA+92843&amp;ll=33.772538,-117.920511" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">13129 Harbor Blvd<br/>Garden Grove, CA 92843</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Tamale, Chamorro Plate</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The chef at Sabroso! decorated the menu with his mom&#x27;s recipes from Mexico, so you know you are going to taste true homestyle cooking here. Both the Chamorro plate and the pork tamale (which Guy praises for having the perfect masa-to-pork ratio) deliver Mexican flavor with a Californian twist.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">California Cruisin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/garden-grove/sabroso--mexican-grill" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.92051,33.77254,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Brick and Fire</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Brick and Fire</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Eureka, CA 95501 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7072688959" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 268-8959</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.brickandfirebistro.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.brickandfirebistro.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Brick+and+Fire%2C+1630+F+St%2C+Eureka%2C+CA+95501&amp;ll=40.792326,-124.163823" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1630 F St<br/>Eureka, CA 95501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mushroom Cobbler, Oysters</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy heads to California to check out Brick and Fire&#x27;s Mushroom Cobbler featuring ingredients from Chef Jim Hughes&#x27; garden. It is stuffed with an array of wild mushrooms that have been oven-roasted, stewed in butter and then made into a creamy cobbler mix that is topped with biscuits and cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Extra Helpings<br/>Big Time Bites<br/>Triple D Nation: Stuffed Stuff</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/eureka/brick-and-fire" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-124.16382,40.79233,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cafe Nooner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cafe Nooner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Eureka, CA 95501</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7074434663" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 443-4663</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cafenooner.net/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cafenooner.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cafe+Nooner%2C+409+Opera+Alley%2C+Eureka%2C+CA+95501&amp;ll=40.803981,-124.166667" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">409 Opera Alley<br/>Eureka, CA 95501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulled Pork Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Joe and Lorrena Filgas quit their corporate jobs to start Cafe Nooner, a Creole-Mediterranean fusion restaurant. Local, organic ingredients are used here to create tantalizingly fresh dishes. Guy can&#x27;t get enough of the Creole-seasoned pulled pork sandwich that is crispy, tender and full of flavor.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Extra Helpings<br/>Dynamite Duos</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/eureka/cafe-nooner" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-124.16667,40.80398,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Johnny Garlic&#x27;s (Windsor, CA)</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Johnny Garlic&#x27;s (Windsor, CA)</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Windsor, CA 95492 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7078368300" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">707-836-8300</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.johnnygarlics.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.johnnygarlics.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Johnny+Garlic%27s+%28Windsor%2C+CA%29%2C+8988+Brooks+Rd.+S.%2C+Windsor%2C+CA+95492&amp;ll=38.549577,-122.806411" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">8988 Brooks Rd. S.<br/>Windsor, CA 95492</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sashimi Won Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Only at Guy&#x27;s restaurant can you get a little Italian, Mexican, Cajun and Asian. The grilled-onion-and-garlic tortilla stack, inspired by Guy&#x27;s mom, has &amp;quot;dynamite&amp;quot; texture and flavor. Guy&#x27;s Sashimi Won Tacos dressed with eel sauce were double gold winners at the Sonoma County Harvest Fair.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Unexpected Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/windsor/johnny-garlics-pasta-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.80641,38.54958,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sol Food Puerto Rican Cuisine</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sol Food Puerto Rican Cuisine</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Rafael, CA 94901 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4154514765" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">415-451-4765</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.solfoodrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.solfoodrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sol+Food+Puerto+Rican+Cuisine%2C+901+Lincoln+Ave%2C+San+Rafael%2C+CA+94901&amp;ll=37.971787,-122.524220" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">901 Lincoln Ave<br/>San Rafael, CA 94901</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pastelon de Carne, Bistec Sandwich, Mofongo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This authentic Puerto Rican comfort food restaurant is channeling the flavors of the Caribbean. Guy was won over by the Pastelon de Carne, a hearty dish that locals liken to lasagna. Ground beef is seasoned with adobo, then studded with olives and layered over a base of sweet plantains. And don&#x27;t sleep on the bistec sandwich that comes stuffed with melty Swiss cheese, tender sirloin, grilled onions and avocado slices. &quot;That&#x27;s like [a] Puerto Rican-Cuban-Philly cheesesteak,&quot; Guy declared.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">World Class Flavor<br/>Go-To Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-rafael/sol-food-puerto-rican-cuisine-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.52422,37.97179,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cannery Row Brewing Company</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cannery Row Brewing Company</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Monterey, CA 93940 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8316432722" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(831) 643-2722</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.canneryrowbrewingcompany.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.canneryrowbrewingcompany.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cannery+Row+Brewing+Company%2C+95+Prescott+Ave%2C+Monterey%2C+CA+93940&amp;ll=36.615456,-121.900757" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">95 Prescott Ave<br/>Monterey, CA 93940</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Parmesan Pretzel, Short Rib Grilled Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy ventures to the Cannery Row Brewing Company for some &quot;high-end bar grub.&quot; Everyone&#x27;s favorite is the Parmesan pretzel with beer cheese dip. But you won&#x27;t want to miss out on the short rib grilled cheese either, complete with one slice of bread that&#x27;s entirely blanketed by provolone.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old Standards, New Styles</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/monterey/cannery-row-brewing-company" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.90076,36.61546,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Monterey&#x27;s Fish House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Monterey&#x27;s Fish House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Monterey, CA 93940 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8313734647" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(831) 373-4647</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Monterey-Fish-House/214672488573192" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Monterey-Fish-House/214672488573192</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Monterey%27s+Fish+House%2C+2114+Del+Monte+Ave%2C+Monterey%2C+CA+93940&amp;ll=36.602122,-121.865765" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2114 Del Monte Ave<br/>Monterey, CA 93940</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oak Grilled Oyster, Sicilian Holiday Pasta</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Monterey&#x27;s Fish House is all about fresh seafood. Guy feasts on oak-grilled oysters, which are slathered with butter and garlic, then served with a spicy cocktail sauce. He follows them up with the Sicilian Holiday Pasta, which features housemade linguini dressed up with seasonal fish and seafood.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">California Cruisin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/monterey/monterey_s-fish-house" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.86576,36.60212,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rosine&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rosine&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Monterey, CA 93940 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8313751400" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(831) 375-1400</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rosinesmonterey.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rosinesmonterey.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rosine%27s%2C+434+Alvarado+St%2C+Monterey%2C+CA+93940&amp;ll=36.599126,-121.894905" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">434 Alvarado St<br/>Monterey, CA 93940</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lasagna, Minestrone Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rosine&#x27;s is a local favorite when it comes to Italian meals. The towering portions of lasagna feature &quot;superrich&quot; layers of ground chuck, red sauce and a creamy mix of cheeses. The minestrone soup is also worth a taste. Guy loves that it includes atypical ingredients like cabbage and shredded beef.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Stuffed and Twisted</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/monterey/rosine_s-" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.89491,36.59913,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Wild Plum Cafe &amp; Bakery</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Wild Plum Cafe &amp; Bakery</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Monterey, CA 93940 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8316463109" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(831) 646-3109</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://thewildplumcafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">thewildplumcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Wild+Plum+Cafe+%26+Bakery%2C+731+Munras+Ave%2C+Monterey%2C+CA+93940&amp;ll=36.594787,-121.893078" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">731 Munras Ave<br/>Monterey, CA 93940</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Porchetta</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Wild Plum is dedicated to organic and sustainable cuisine. Everything here, aside from the ketchup and mustard, is made from scratch. A hit item is the porchetta, which features pork loin stuffed with roasted pork shoulder and then wrapped in bacon and served on a bed of hand-fried potatoes.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Day Dining</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/monterey/the-wild-plum-cafe---bakery" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.89308,36.59479,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Loulou&#x27;s Griddle in the Middle</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Loulou&#x27;s Griddle in the Middle</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Monterey, CA 93940 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8313720568" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(831) 372-0568</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.loulousgriddle.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.loulousgriddle.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Loulou%27s+Griddle+in+the+Middle%2C+Municipal+Wharf+No.+2%2C+Monterey%2C+CA+93940&amp;ll=36.602365,-121.889779" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Municipal Wharf No. 2<br/>Monterey, CA 93940</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Abalone Slider, Dungeness Crab</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Loulou&#x27;s abalone slider is the perfect dish for a self-proclaimed &quot;abalone junkie&quot; like Guy. The bun is grilled, slathered with aioli, topped with the abalone and slaw, then served with a side of fruit slaw. If you are at Loulou&#x27;s between November and June, don&#x27;t miss out on the Dungeness crab.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">West Coast Cookin&#x27;<br/>Righteous Bites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/monterey/loulou_s-griddle-in-the-middle" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.88978,36.60237,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>A Taste of Home Cooking</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">A Taste of Home Cooking</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Arvada, CO 80002 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3034232737" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(303) 423-2737</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.facebook.com/ATasteofHomeCooking" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/ATasteofHomeCooking</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=A+Taste+of+Home+Cooking%2C+12365+58th+Ave.%2C+Arvada%2C+CO+80002&amp;ll=39.801896,-105.137510" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">12365 58th Ave.<br/>Arvada, CO 80002</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dinner Cannoli</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">With &amp;quot;home cooking&amp;quot; in the name, it&#x27;s no surprise that everything here, from the honey mustard sauce to the sauerkraut, is made by hand. With that handmade attitude, Guy had to drop by for the savory cannoli. Forget about sweet ricotta, these are packed with homemade sausage and provolone cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cannoli, Fritters and Wings</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/arvada/a-taste-of-home-cooking-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.13751,39.80190,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Spice Island Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Spice Island Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Colorado Springs, CO 80903 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7194738280" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">719-473-8280</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://spiceislandgrill.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">spiceislandgrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Spice+Island+Grill%2C+10+N+Sierra+Madre+St%2C+Colorado+Springs%2C+CO+80903&amp;ll=38.835071,-104.828025" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">10 N Sierra Madre St<br/>Colorado Springs, CO 80903</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Curry Goat, Jerk Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Colorado Springs may seem like an unlikely place to find Jamaican food, but Guy is in luck when he swings by this spot for the curry goat. The meat is cooked with the bone in, then left to simmer in a concoction of garlic, ginger and Jamaican curry powder, resulting in a tender, flavorful dish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of Meat</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/colorado-springs/spice-island-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.82802,38.83507,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Piglatin Food Truck</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Piglatin Food Truck</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Colorado Springs, CO 80903 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7193471144" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">719-347-1144</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.piglatintruck.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.piglatintruck.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Piglatin+Food+Truck%2C+Roaming+Food+Truck%2C+Colorado+Springs%2C+CO+80903&amp;ll=38.841342,-104.816278" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Roaming Food Truck<br/>Colorado Springs, CO 80903</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Stacked Arepa</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this food truck focused on pork fusion, hungry locals line up for dishes like the stacked arepa that had Guy exclaiming, &quot;Prime time!&quot; The traditional Colombian fried cake is loaded with melty mozzarella cheese, pineapple pulled pork and spinach, then finished with cilantro, lime juice and Sriracha for added kick.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Piggin&#x27; Out</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/colorado-springs/piglatin-food-truck-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.81628,38.84134,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Paravicini&#x27;s Italian Bistro</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Paravicini&#x27;s Italian Bistro</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Colorado Springs 80904 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7194718200" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">719-471-8200</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.restaurantji.com/co/colorado-springs/paravicinis-italian-bistro-/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.restaurantji.com/co/colorado-springs/paravicinis-italian-bistro-</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Paravicini%27s+Italian+Bistro%2C+2802+W+Colorado+Ave%2C+Colorado+Springs+80904&amp;ll=38.850188,-104.867128" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2802 W Colorado Ave<br/>Colorado Springs 80904</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Veal Giuseppe</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The rough translation of para vicini is &quot;for the neighborhood,&quot; and it&#x27;s exactly that community spirit that Chef-Owner Franco Pisani has captured. He&#x27;s built a loyal following with his devotion to fresh, hearty Italian meals made from family recipes. &quot;That&#x27;s a real-deal, old-school Italian dish,&quot; Guy declared of the Veal Giuseppe, which comes loaded with cherry peppers, Kalamata olives and sausage.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Isle-talian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/colorado-springs/paravicinis-italian-bistro-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.86713,38.85019,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Bagel Delicatessen &amp; Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Bagel Delicatessen &amp; Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver 80222 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3037566667" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">303-756-6667</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bageldeli.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bageldeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Bagel+Delicatessen+%26+Restaurant%2C+6439+E+Hampden%2C+Denver+80222&amp;ll=39.654200,-104.914089" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6439 E Hampden<br/>Denver 80222</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chopped Liver, Egg Salad, Tongue Sandwiches, Matzo Ball Soup, Brisket Knishes, Kishke</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Jewish Deli is serving up all the classics from chopped liver and egg salad to tongue sandwiches. Guy was enthused by the &quot;dynamite&quot; flavoring of the matzo ball soup. The flaky brisket knishes paired with red horseradish and the meaty and savory kishkes with au jus are customer favorites.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Holiday Hoopla<br/>Triple D Nation: Diners, Drive-Ins and Delis<br/>From Mozz to Matzo Balls</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/the-bagel-delicatessen-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.91409,39.65420,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Steuben&#x27;s Food Service</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Steuben&#x27;s Food Service</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver, CO 80203 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (14 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3038301001" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(303) 830-1001</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.steubens.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.steubens.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Steuben%27s+Food+Service%2C+523+E+17th+Ave%2C+Denver%2C+CO+80203&amp;ll=39.743548,-104.980361" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">523 E 17th Ave<br/>Denver, CO 80203</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roasted Chicken, Ribs, Lobster Roll, Hand-cut Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The place used to be an auto garage, but now it&#x27;s a neighborhood restaurant serving up everything from Southern to Italian favorites. Guy adored the overflowing lobster roll, while customers enjoy the hand-cut fries, roasted chicken and ribs with meat so tender that it just falls off the bone.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Between the Bread<br/>Signature Sandwiches</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/steubens-food-service-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.98036,39.74355,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sam&#x27;s No. 3</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sam&#x27;s No. 3</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver, CO 80210 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3035341927" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(303) 534.1927</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.samsno3.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.samsno3.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sam%27s+No.+3%2C+1500+Curtis+St%2C+Denver%2C+CO+80210&amp;ll=39.746282,-104.995692" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1500 Curtis St<br/>Denver, CO 80210</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kickin&#x27; Green Pork Chili, Kitchen Sink Burrito</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy swung by on Triple D to visit a viewer favorite, Sam&#x27;s No. 3 Diner. The signature Kickin&#x27; Green Pork Chili is served on everything from fries to burgers to the beloved Kitchen Sink Burrito. Warning -- this burrito&#x27;s packed with bacon, ham, sausage, mushroom, green peppers and even gyro meat.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Porktastic</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/sams-no-3-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.99569,39.74628,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Just BE Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Just BE Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver, CO 80202</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://justbekitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">justbekitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Just+BE+Kitchen%2C+2364+15th+St%2C+Denver%2C+CO+80202&amp;ll=39.756071,-105.009141" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2364 15th St<br/>Denver, CO 80202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">In a time when everyone you know seems to have different dietary needs, this restaurant is the place where everyone can eat together. All of their dishes are free of dairy, gluten, refined sugar, soy, corn, and all legumes-but they&#x27;re not missing any flavor! Guy was impressed with the &quot;healthy&quot; chicken and dumplings, which are made with cassava flour dumplings. &quot;This is legit chicken and dumplings,&quot; he said. &quot;I&#x27;ll have it by the quart!&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Down-Home Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/jude-be-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.00914,39.75607,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Maria Empanada</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Maria Empanada</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver 80210 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3039342221" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">303-934-2221</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://mariaempanada.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">mariaempanada.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Maria+Empanada%2C+1298+South+Broadway+Ave%2C+Denver+80210&amp;ll=39.693202,-104.987195" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1298 South Broadway Ave<br/>Denver 80210</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Empanada</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef-Owner Lorena Cantarovici moved from Argentina with $300 in her pocket and a craving for her homeland&#x27;s empanadas on her mind. In 2011, she opened this spot and now cranks out up to 1,500 empanadas per day. These dough-wrapped beauties come stuffed with a flavorful filling of seasoned ground beef, onions and red pepper. &quot;It&#x27;s light ... simple; that&#x27;s what an empanada&#x27;s supposed to be,&quot; Guy declared.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Shipped, Sweet and Savory<br/>By Hand and By Fork<br/>Triple D Nation: Stuffed Stuff</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/maria-empanada-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.98719,39.69320,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Welton St. Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Welton St. Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver 80205</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3032966602" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(303) 296-6602</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/welton-st-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/welton-st-cafe-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Welton+St.+Cafe%2C+2736+Welton+St%2C+Denver+80205&amp;ll=39.755231,-104.977035" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2736 Welton St<br/>Denver 80205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Virgin Island Pates, Smothered Pork Chops</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Denver&#x27;s Five Points neighborhood recently became the culinary center of the city, but this Caribbean spot was way ahead of the curve. For 20 years they&#x27;ve been slinging scratch-made soul food to hungry Coloradans, like Virgin Island pates, deep fried pockets of dough stuffed with ground beef and cheese, and smothered pork chops.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mom and Dad</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/welton-st-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.97703,39.75523,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dae Gee Korean BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dae Gee Korean BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver 80206 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7206399986" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">720-639-9986</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.daegee.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.daegee.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dae+Gee+Korean+BBQ%2C+827+Colorado+Blvd%2C+Denver+80206&amp;ll=39.729725,-104.941098" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">827 Colorado Blvd<br/>Denver 80206</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Unlimited Korean BBQ</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Given Colorado&#x27;s food scene, Guy was certain he could find an &quot;off-the-hook&quot; Korean barbecue spot. Dae Gee (which means &quot;pig&quot; in Korean) did not disappoint. The crowds flock here for the Unlimited Korean Barbecue, which features a mouthwatering array of meats and sides (beef bulgogi, chicken bulgogi, kimchee pancakes, fish cakes and more). &quot;Outstanding,&quot; Guy declared of the feast.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Comin&#x27; from All Over the Map<br/>Triple D Nation: Around the World<br/>Taste of Asia</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/dae-gee-korean-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.94110,39.72972,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Putah Creek Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Putah Creek Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Winters, CA 95694 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5307952682" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(530) 795-2682</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.putahcreekcafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.putahcreekcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Putah+Creek+Cafe%2C+1+Main+St%2C+Winters%2C+CA+95694&amp;ll=38.521983,-121.969187" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1 Main St<br/>Winters, CA 95694</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cioppino, Herb Chicken Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Everything at Putah Creek Cafe is made fresh, right down to the homemade sausage and killer gravy. But the top-notch cioppino made with crab and shrimp had to be Guy&#x27;s favorite. Want something just as impressive? How about a dynamite herb chicken pizza made from the trailer-towed pizza oven outside?</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Signature Twists<br/>West Coast Cookin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/winters/putah-creek-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.96919,38.52198,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>North End Caffe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">North End Caffe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Manhattan Beach 90266 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3105464782" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(310) 546-4782</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.northendcaffe.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.northendcaffe.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=North+End+Caffe%2C+3421+N+Highland+Ave%2C+Manhattan+Beach+90266&amp;ll=33.899534,-118.417386" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3421 N Highland Ave<br/>Manhattan Beach 90266</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Linguine Carbonara with Pancetta, Kahlua Pig Monte Cristo Egg Rolls (Cooked in Banana Leaf)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After buying a one-way ticket to Rome, John Atkinson returned home to Manhattan Beach, Calif., and opened his version of gourmet short order. He learned the trick to a great pasta carbonara. As for the signature Kahlua Pig Monte Cristo Egg Rolls? Guy said they were &quot;supercalifragilistic tender.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Bold Bites Brought Home<br/>Surf &#x27;n Turf</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/manhattan-beach/north-end-caffe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.41739,33.89953,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Duarte&#x27;s Tavern</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Duarte&#x27;s Tavern</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Pescadero, CA 94060 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6508790464" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(650) 879-0464</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.duartestavern.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.duartestavern.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Duarte%27s+Tavern%2C+202+Stage+Rd%2C+Pescadero%2C+CA+94060&amp;ll=37.252196,-122.382778" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">202 Stage Rd<br/>Pescadero, CA 94060</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crab Cioppino, Abalone Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy is convinced that this fourth-generation family-owned tavern, which uses locally sourced produce and seafood, makes the best Crab Cioppino. Generous portions of Dungeness crab, clams and shrimp are bathed in a light tomato sauce seasoned with cumin, which gives the dish a healthy kick. Guy is also a fan of the tavern&#x27;s take on a classic California specialty, a seafood-centric sandwich that features abalone stuffed between two slices of homemade sourdough bread.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Local Flavor<br/>All Stacked Up</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/pescadero/duartes-tavern-restaurant2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.38278,37.25220,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Gott&#x27;s Roadside Tray Gourmet (formerly Taylor&#x27;s Automatic Refresher)</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Gott&#x27;s Roadside Tray Gourmet (formerly Taylor&#x27;s Automatic Refresher)</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">St. Helena, CA 94574 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7079633486" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 963-3486</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://gottsroadside.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">gottsroadside.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Gott%27s+Roadside+Tray+Gourmet+%28formerly+Taylor%27s+Automatic+Refresher%29%2C+933+Main+Street%2C+St.+Helena%2C+CA+94574&amp;ll=38.501897,-122.465448" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">933 Main Street<br/>St. Helena, CA 94574</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Wisconsin Burger, Fries, Milk Shakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gott&#x27;s Roadside Tray Gourmet won a James Beard Award for Best American Classic, so it&#x27;s no surprise this Napa Valley staple serves up amazing hamburgers. The special is the Wisconsin burger, with grilled mushrooms, bacon and melted cheddar cheese. As Guy said, &#x27;&#x27;It&#x27;s all about the quality.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Retro<br/>Triple-D Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/st-helena/gotts-roadside-formerly-taylors-automatic-refresher-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.46545,38.50190,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cafe Citti</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cafe Citti</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Kenwood, CA 95452 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7078332690" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 833-2690</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cafecitti.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cafecitti.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cafe+Citti%2C+9049+Sonoma+Hwy%2C+Kenwood%2C+CA+95452&amp;ll=38.418103,-122.550244" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">9049 Sonoma Hwy<br/>Kenwood, CA 95452</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Polenta ai Funghi Porcini</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Located in the heart of Sonoma wine country, Cafe Citti bills itself as a casual Italian trattoria. Chef Luca hails from Lucca, Italy, and all his dishes bring handmade to the table. On his DDD visit, Guy called the ravioli an &amp;quot;orchestra of flavors,&amp;quot; and he loved the homey polenta with porcini sauce</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bringin&#x27; It Home<br/>Amazing Italian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/kenwood/cafe-citti-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.55024,38.41810,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Russian River Pub</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Russian River Pub</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Forestville 95436 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7078877932" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">707-887-7932</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.russianriverpub.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.russianriverpub.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Russian+River+Pub%2C+11829+River+Rd.%2C+Forestville+95436&amp;ll=38.504202,-122.941226" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">11829 River Rd.<br/>Forestville 95436</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Pub Burger, Chicken Wings, Seared Ahi Tuna Salad, Beef Tri-Tip Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For more than 25 years, Russian River Pub has been the go-to place for good ol&#x27; family fun. Just ask Guy, who considers the pub his stompin&#x27; grounds for him and his son. Don&#x27;t be fooled by the pool tables and cabin decor. You can order grilled pesto chicken, beef tri-tip and Ahi tuna salad.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">American Cookin&#x27;<br/>Diners, Drive-ins and Dives<br/>Takeout: Bold Bites Brought Home</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/forestville/russian-river-pub-restaurant2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.94123,38.50420,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Paul&#x27;s Coffee Shop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Paul&#x27;s Coffee Shop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fountain Valley, CA 92708 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7149653643" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(714) 965-3643</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://paulscoffeeshopfountainvalley.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">paulscoffeeshopfountainvalley.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Paul%27s+Coffee+Shop%2C+16947+Bushard+St%2C+Fountain+Valley%2C+CA+92708&amp;ll=33.716832,-117.963694" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">16947 Bushard St<br/>Fountain Valley, CA 92708</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">(Ground Beef Gravy on Toast), Bulgogi (Korean Beef Barbecue), Chicken Fried Steak, Loco Moco</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Marines and veterans from all forces are all welcome at Paul&#x27;s Coffee Shop. Owner Phil Martinez, a former marine, takes this &quot;military coffee shop&quot; to new levels, as Guy swung by for some of their knock-out chicken fried steak, pork chops and the SOS plate, an actual lunch tray with toast and gravy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You Called It</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/fountain-valley/pauls-coffee-shop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.96369,33.71683,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Brats Brothers - CLOSED</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Brats Brothers - CLOSED</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sherman Oaks, CA 91423 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8189864020" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(818) 986-4020</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sherman-oaks/brats-brothers-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sherman-oaks/brats-brothers-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Brats+Brothers+-+CLOSED%2C+13355+Ventura+Blvd%2C+Sherman+Oaks%2C+CA+91423&amp;ll=34.147173,-118.424275" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">13355 Ventura Blvd<br/>Sherman Oaks, CA 91423</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spaetzle</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Have a craving for handmade bratwurst? Follow Guy&#x27;s lead and head over to Brats Brothers, which draws diners from across the globe eager to sample some delectable sausages. Savor a classic brat made from pork or veal, or indulge in an exotic option like a wild boar andouille or a kangaroo sausage.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gone Global</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sherman-oaks/brats-brothers-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.42427,34.14717,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mountain Shadows Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mountain Shadows Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Colorado Springs, CO 80904 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7196332122" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">719-633-2122</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/colorado-springs/mountain-shadows-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/colorado-springs/mountain-shadows-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mountain+Shadows+Restaurant%2C+2223+W+Colorado+Ave%2C+Colorado+Springs%2C+CO+80904&amp;ll=38.844884,-104.859403" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2223 W Colorado Ave<br/>Colorado Springs, CO 80904</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rocky Mountain Roast Beef Sandwich, Cinnamon Rolls</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This spot won Guy over with its heaping portions of comfort food. The massive cinnamon rolls are made from a buttery dough that comes bathed in a decadent glaze that Guy calls &quot;maple madness.&quot; And one monster of a sandwich comes piled with cheese-smothered slices of roast beef, mushrooms and bacon.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">East-West Flavorfest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/colorado-springs/mountain-shadows-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.85940,38.84488,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rasta Pasta</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rasta Pasta</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Colorado Springs, CO 80903 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7194816888" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">719-481-6888</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rastapastacs.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rastapastacs.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rasta+Pasta%2C+405+N+Tejon+St%2C+Colorado+Springs%2C+CO+80903&amp;ll=38.839877,-104.822932" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">405 N Tejon St<br/>Colorado Springs, CO 80903</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rasta Pasta</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The unusual dishes at this Caribbean pasta joint had Guy exclaiming, &quot;You guys are crazy!&quot; He tried the namesake Rasta Pasta, a flavorful penne dish studded with tender jerk chicken. True to this kitchen&#x27;s creative vibe, the chicken is prepared in a unique way. Instead of being rubbed down with spices, it&#x27;s cooked in a bath of orange juice and jerk seasoning. &quot;What a funky dish,&quot; Guy declared.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Isle-talian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/colorado-springs/rasta-pasta-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.82293,38.83988,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Skirted Heifer</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Skirted Heifer</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Colorado Springs, CO 80903 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7196353276" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">719-635-3276</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://skirtedheifer.com/#home" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">skirtedheifer.com/#home</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Skirted+Heifer%2C+204+N+Tejon+St%2C+Colorado+Springs%2C+CO+80903&amp;ll=38.836922,-104.823486" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">204 N Tejon St<br/>Colorado Springs, CO 80903</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Hangover, The Pueblo Farmer</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The deliciousness is in the details at this burger joint, from the locally sourced meat to the scratch-made condiments. A must-try is The Hangover: A simply seasoned patty comes topped with cream cheese, crispy bacon and a horseradish-spiked tomato sauce that Guy said &quot;really takes it over the top.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Between the Bread</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/colorado-springs/skirted-heifer-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.82349,38.83692,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Front Range Barbeque</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Front Range Barbeque</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Colorado Springs, CO 80904 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7196322596" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">719-632-2596</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://frbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">frbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Front+Range+Barbeque%2C+2330+W+Colorado+Ave%2C+Colorado+Springs%2C+CO+80904&amp;ll=38.846304,-104.860692" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2330 W Colorado Ave<br/>Colorado Springs, CO 80904</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Sloppy Pig Sandwich, Meatloaf</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef-Owner Brian Fortinberry, who hails from Alabama, draws on an arsenal of family recipes to make his delectable Southern dishes. Guy stops by to tackle the towering sandwich known as The Sloppy Pig, which stars a meaty trio of tender pulled pork, grilled kielbasa sausage and pecan-smoked bacon.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Legacies</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/colorado-springs/front-range-barbeque-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.86069,38.84630,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lauer-Krauts</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lauer-Krauts</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Brighton 80601 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3036549700" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(303) 654-9700</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://lauer-krauts.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">lauer-krauts.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lauer-Krauts%2C+26+S+6th+St%2C+Brighton+80601&amp;ll=39.986214,-104.815095" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">26 S 6th St<br/>Brighton 80601</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Krautburger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">With a whole family of sauerkraut fanatics to support her, Robin Lauer-Trujillo opened Lauer-Krauts, a play on her maiden name, Lauer, and homemade sauerkraut recipe. But Guy came for one thing: the Krautburger, a flaky German-Russian pastry pocket stuffed with beef and sauerkraut.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Kraut to Couscous<br/>Takeout: Goin&#x27; Big and Bringin&#x27; Home<br/>Best of the West<br/>Triple D Nation: From Pork to Po&#x27; Boys</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/brighton/laura-krauts-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.81510,39.98621,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Zoe Ma Ma</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Zoe Ma Ma</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boulder, CO 80302</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3035456262" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">303-545-6262</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.zoemama.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.zoemama.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Zoe+Ma+Ma%2C+2010+10th+St%2C+Boulder%2C+CO+80302&amp;ll=40.017572,-105.282521" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2010 10th St<br/>Boulder, CO 80302</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Steamy Buns, Za Jiang Mian</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For quick, super yummy street food head to Zoe Ma Ma and try the huge pork-filled Steamy Buns and the Za Jiang Mian with house-made noodles, pork and julienne vegetables. &quot;This is the best fast Asian food I&#x27;ve seen in 10 years,&quot; said Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mom&#x27;s Kitchen</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/boulder/zoe-ma-ma-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.28252,40.01757,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Foolish Craig&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Foolish Craig&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boulder, CO 80302 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3032479383" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(303) 247-9383</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.foolishcraigs.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foolishcraigs.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Foolish+Craig%27s+Cafe%2C+1611+Pearl+St%2C+Boulder%2C+CO+80302&amp;ll=40.019327,-105.274493" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1611 Pearl St<br/>Boulder, CO 80302</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fresh Baked Breads, BLT Guacamole, Butter Rum Caramel Crepe Cake</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">While Foolish Craig&#x27;s is known for its crepes, the cafe also bakes bread daily and serves soups and salads too. Guy loves the warm toasted oatmeal stout bread with the BLT Guacamole. For dessert he recommends ordering the decadent 21-layer butter rum caramel crepe cake with cream cheese frosting.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Crepes to Kreplach</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/boulder/foolish-craigs-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.27449,40.01933,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Aloy Thai Cuisine</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Aloy Thai Cuisine</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boulder, CO 80302 &middot; &#9733; 3.9 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3034402903" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">303-440-2903</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.aloythai.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.aloythai.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Aloy+Thai+Cuisine%2C+2720+Canyon+Blvd%2C+Boulder%2C+CO+80302&amp;ll=40.017274,-105.259061" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2720 Canyon Blvd<br/>Boulder, CO 80302</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Khao Soi, Lemongrass Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For amazing Thai in Boulder, head to Aloy Thai. Chef and Owner Kim Naka and her daughters are creating authentic dishes like fragrant Kao Soi and spicy Lemongrass Chicken. Guy loved the combination of sweet, sour and heat in the chicken, remarking &quot;it&#x27;s not just a drum solo ... it&#x27;s the whole band rockin&#x27;.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">College-Town Champs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/boulder/aloy-thai-cuisine-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.25906,40.01727,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Audrey Janes</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Audrey Janes</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boulder 80304 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3034422032" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">303-442-2032</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.thepizzagarage.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thepizzagarage.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Audrey+Janes%2C+2675+13th+St%2C+Boulder+80304&amp;ll=40.025132,-105.280779" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2675 13th St<br/>Boulder 80304</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spicy Pig Pizza, Meatball Grinder</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Audrey Sherman combined her passion for pizza with the teachings of Tony Gemignani, the heavy weight champ of global pizza competitions, to create her popular pizza shop. Her fabulous dough is the soul of her killer pies and is also used to make the roll for her massive meatball grinder.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Kinds of Comfort<br/>Takeout: Bringing Comfort Home</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/boulder/audrey-janes-pizza-garage-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.28078,40.02513,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Sink</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Sink</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Boulder, CO 80302 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3034447465" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(303) 444-7465</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thesink.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thesink.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Sink%2C+1165+13th+St%2C+Boulder%2C+CO+80302&amp;ll=40.008486,-105.276575" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1165 13th St<br/>Boulder, CO 80302</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Texas Onion Straw Burger, Pesto Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Located in a former frat house, The Sink is serving up quality scratch-made bites. According to Guy, the crust of The Buddah Basil pesto pizza is as much of a treat as its center, which has pizza and pesto sauces, artichoke hearts and Parmesan. Like spicy? Try the Texas Onion Straw Burger.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gettin&#x27; Fresh</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/boulder/the-sink-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.27657,40.00849,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Samples Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Samples Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Longmont, CO 80501 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sampleslongmont.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sampleslongmont.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Samples+Restaurant%2C+370+Main+St%2C+Longmont%2C+CO+80501&amp;ll=40.165289,-105.102247" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">370 Main St<br/>Longmont, CO 80501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Poutine Burger, Korean BBQ Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Married social workers Mark and Carmen Sample combined their love of food and helping others into a restaurant. Bring your appetite for the towering Poutine Burger which is piled high with fried cheese curds and drenched in a house-made gravy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Poutine, Pizza and Pork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/longmont/samples-world-bistro-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.10225,40.16529,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Post Chicken &amp; Beer</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Post Chicken &amp; Beer</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Longmont, CO 80501 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7205882883" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">720-588-2883</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.postchickenandbeer.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.postchickenandbeer.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Post+Chicken+%26+Beer%2C+1258+S.+Hover+Rd%2C+Longmont%2C+CO+80501&amp;ll=40.144522,-105.130185" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1258 S. Hover Rd<br/>Longmont, CO 80501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Chicken, Chicken Chicharrones</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken and beer are a match made in heaven, especially when thechicken is crispy, crunchy perfection. Chef and owner Brett Smith uses a pressure cooker and a unique flouring system to create some of the best chicken Guy has ever had. Guy also loved their unique chicken chicharrones, fried chicken skin served with a pinto bean hummus.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bird and Beef</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/longmont/the-post-chicken-and-beer-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.13019,40.14452,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Roost</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Roost</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Longmont, CO 80501 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3038273380" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">303-827-3380</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://theroostlongmont.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">theroostlongmont.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Roost%2C+526+Main+St.%2C+Longmont%2C+CO+80501&amp;ll=40.168410,-105.102115" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">526 Main St.<br/>Longmont, CO 80501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bangin&#x27; Cauliflower, Perfect Pork Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Roost is a neighborhood spot with a righteous menu and a heartfelt mission. A diner-favorite is the Bangin&#x27; Cauliflower which is lightly coated in rice flour, fried until crispy and tossed with their signature sweet and spicy sauce. The Perfect Pork Burger is made with local meat topped with house-made kimchi and blistered shishitos and served on buns made across the street. &quot;There&#x27;s nothing I would do different,&quot; Guy said after a taste.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sammies and Spice</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/longmont/the-roost-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.10212,40.16841,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Il Porcellino</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Il Porcellino</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver 80212</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="ttp://ilporcellinodenver.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">ttp://ilporcellinodenver.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Il+Porcellino%2C+4324+W.+41st+Ave%2C+Denver+80212&amp;ll=39.772403,-105.043685" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4324 W. 41st Ave<br/>Denver 80212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Denver spot is a charcuterie lover&#x27;s paradise. Chef-owner Bill Miner makes 45 different kinds of salumi in house. Opt for the meats plain or get them in one of their incredible sandwiches, like the Hoggie Sandwich, which is ciabatta bread layered with ham, soppressata, capicola, pickled peppers, tomatoes, romaine and garlic aioli. &quot;That is the definition of an Italian deli sandwich,&quot; Guy said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Beef to Bao</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/il-porcellino-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.04369,39.77240,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Valencia Luncheria</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Valencia Luncheria</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Norwalk, CT 06851 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2038468009" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">203-846-8009</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.valencialuncheria.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.valencialuncheria.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Valencia+Luncheria%2C+164+Main+St%2C+Norwalk%2C+CT+06851&amp;ll=41.125818,-73.419051" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">164 Main St<br/>Norwalk, CT 06851</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pernil Arepa (Pork Venezuelan Pocket Sandwich), The Morning After, Strong Island, Red Smitty</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Valencia Luncheria took Guy by surprise, as he&#x27;d never had the Venezuelan tortilla called an arepa. The thick tortilla gets fried and then stuffed with both savory and sweet fillings. Think roasted pork shoulder, tender shredded chicken, ceviche and even Nutella and cream cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Something from Everywhere</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ct/norwalk/valencia-luncheria-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.41905,41.12582,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Black Duck Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Black Duck Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Westport, CT 06880 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2032277978" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">203-227-7978</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.blackduckwestport.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.blackduckwestport.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Black+Duck+Cafe%2C+605+Riverside+Ave%2C+Westport%2C+CT+06880&amp;ll=41.120328,-73.369708" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">605 Riverside Ave<br/>Westport, CT 06880</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Steamers, Clams Casino, Black Duck Burger, Steak au Poivre</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Located on a barge under a bridge, this spot cooks over 75,000 clams a year. Guy thought the steamers had a great natural flavor and enjoyed drinking the accompanying clam broth. &amp;quot;That&#x27;s just simple goodness right there,&amp;quot; Guy declared of the bacon-topped clams casino. Another standout is the Black Duck Burger.&amp;nbsp;Sauteed peppers, onions and mushrooms smother a 6-ounce Angus burger patty - available in a 3/4-pound size for heartier appetites.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ultimate Bacon Fest<br/>Go-To Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ct/westport/black-duck-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-73.36971,41.12033,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>O&#x27;Rourke&#x27;s Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">O&#x27;Rourke&#x27;s Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Middletown, CT 06457 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8603466101" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(860) 346-6101</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.orourkesmiddletown.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.orourkesmiddletown.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=O%27Rourke%27s+Diner%2C+728+Main+St%2C+Middletown%2C+CT+06457&amp;ll=41.565576,-72.652610" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">728 Main St<br/>Middletown, CT 06457</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Colcannon, House Baked Ham, Irish Trilogy of French Toast</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Middletown locals love O&#x27;Rourke&#x27;s so much that when it burned down in 2006, they helped raise over $300,000 to rebuild it. Guy sampled some unexpected American and Irish favorites like Colcannon, House Baked Ham and an Irish Trilogy of French Toast</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Northeast Feast<br/>Places You Sent Me</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ct/middletown/orourkes-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-72.65261,41.56558,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tocabe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tocabe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver 80211 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7205248282" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(720) 524-8282</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tocabe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tocabe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tocabe%2C+3536+W+44th+Ave%2C+Denver+80211&amp;ll=39.776496,-105.034255" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3536 W 44th Ave<br/>Denver 80211</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bison Ribs, Indian Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tocabe is neither a diner nor drive-in nor dive. Yet Guy still visited it on Triple D because of the off-the-hook hominy salsa. Tocabe brings a modern interpretation to American Indian food for lucky Denver locals -- the fry bread, bison ribs and overflowing Indian tacos are all must-tries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: From Brisket to Bison<br/>Takeout: Ordering All Kinds of Flavor<br/>Grillin&#x27; and Smokin&#x27;<br/>Crazy for Chicken</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/tocabe-american-indian-eatery-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.03426,39.77650,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>CoraFaye&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">CoraFaye&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Aurora, CO 80011 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3033335551" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">303-333-5551</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.corafayes.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.corafayes.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=CoraFaye%27s+Cafe%2C+16251+E+Colfax+Ave%2C+Aurora%2C+CO+80011&amp;ll=39.757611,-104.940924" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">16251 E Colfax Ave<br/>Aurora, CO 80011</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rabbit, Ox Tail, Catfish, Chit&#x27;lins</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The authentic Southern recipes at CoraFaye&#x27;s Cafe in Denver have been in owner Priscilla Smith&#x27;s family for centuries, including chitlins - a stew with pig intestines. Guy devoured the rabbit - tender and covered in gravy - with sides of rice, collard greens and yams.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Timeless Traditions</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/aurora/cora-fayes-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.94092,39.75761,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Feisty Pint</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Feisty Pint</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Grand Junction 81501 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9706445555" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(970) 644-5555</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="feistypint.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">feistypint.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Feisty+Pint%2C+359+Colorado+Ave%2C+Grand+Junction+81501&amp;ll=39.066237,-108.566851" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">359 Colorado Ave<br/>Grand Junction 81501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Feisty Pint has traditional features of a pub: 26 beers on tap; mounted televisions; and bar fare like tacos, burgers, wings and fries. However, if you&#x27;re a feisty patron, you can attempt either of their food challenges: The Feisty Challenge Burger, three angus patties with spicy toppings, or the Roadkill Challenge, three pounds of tater tot hash topped with bacon, jalapenos, onions, cheese and eggs.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos, Tots and Chops</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/grand-junction/the-feisty-pint" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-108.56685,39.06624,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Prohibition</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Prohibition</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver, CO 80203 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3038324840" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(303) 832-4840</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.prohibitiondenver.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.prohibitiondenver.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Prohibition%2C+504+E+Colfax+Ave%2C+Denver%2C+CO+80203&amp;ll=39.739867,-104.980897" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">504 E Colfax Ave<br/>Denver, CO 80203</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Balsmic Braised Short-Rib Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Most bars in Denver have some kind of hamburger, but Prohibition offers a dish that&#x27;s a little more unique and upscale than the norm - a balsamic braised short rib burger created by Head Chef Toby Prout. The juicy, slow-cooked rib quickly earned Guy&#x27;s seal of approval.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Festival of Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/prohibition-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.98090,39.73987,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hops &amp; Pie</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hops &amp; Pie</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver, CO 80212 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3034777000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">303-477-7000</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hopsandpie.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hopsandpie.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hops+%26+Pie%2C+3920+Tennyson+St%2C+Denver%2C+CO+80212&amp;ll=39.771374,-105.043707" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3920 Tennyson St<br/>Denver, CO 80212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beer Braised Brisket Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">With a name like Hops &amp;amp; Pie, it&#x27;s no shock that this Denver joint specializes in beer and pizza. However, Guy was caught off-guard by one of the menu items - the beer-braised brisket pie. His verdict was that the dough was &#x27;&#x27;just remarkable,&#x27;&#x27; and the contrast of flavors (think brisket, bacon, pickled jalapeno and caramelized onion) was &#x27;&#x27;dynamite.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kings and Queens of &#x27;Cue</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/hops-and-pie" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.04371,39.77137,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Highland Tavern</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Highland Tavern</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver, CO 80211 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (12 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3034331990" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(303) 433-1990</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.highlandtavern.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.highlandtavern.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Highland+Tavern%2C+3400+Navajo+St%2C+Denver%2C+CO+80211&amp;ll=39.764629,-105.003877" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3400 Navajo St<br/>Denver, CO 80211</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bombshell Sammich, Tavern Tots, Pork Rinds</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Visit this neighborhood bar for some &amp;quot;outrageous&amp;quot; bites. Guy appreciated the Tavern Tots and the Bombshell Sammich with house pastrami, Swiss cheese, a fried egg, slaw and brown mustard on rye bread. For some crunchy deliciousness try the pork rinds, which Guy said were the best he has ever had.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos and Tots<br/>Amazing Appetizers<br/>Deep Fried All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/highland-tavern-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.00388,39.76463,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cafe Brazil</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cafe Brazil</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver, CO 80211 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3034801877" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">303-480-1877</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cafebrazildenver.com/bottom.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cafebrazildenver.com/bottom.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cafe+Brazil%2C+4408+Lowell+Blvd%2C+Denver%2C+CO+80211&amp;ll=39.777104,-105.034367" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4408 Lowell Blvd<br/>Denver, CO 80211</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bolinhos, La Julianna</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This funky little spot serves up contemporary South American dishes filled with fresh, vibrant flavors. Diners head here for favorites like the bolinhos, a Brazilian snack staple that had Guy hooked. Mashed sweet potatoes, shrimp, eggs, two Spanish salumi and three types of cheese are kneaded together (along with red chile flakes and Sriracha for some kick), then formed into balls and deep-fried.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tri-Continent Cuisine</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/cafe-brazil-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.03437,39.77710,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blue Pan Pizza</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blue Pan Pizza</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver 80212 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://bluepandenver.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">bluepandenver.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blue+Pan+Pizza%2C+3930+West+32nd+Ave%2C+Denver+80212&amp;ll=39.761973,-105.038972" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3930 West 32nd Ave<br/>Denver 80212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Blue Pan is a funky pizza joint giving Denver a taste of Detroit. Michigan natives, owner Giles Flanagin and Chef Jeff &quot;Smoke&quot; Smokevitch, brought the crispy pan pizza style and other tasty creations to the Mile High CIty. Blue Pan is named after the autoparts pan that a man from Sicily used while trying to recreate Sicilian-syle pizza in Michigan. &quot;It&#x27;s dynamite,&quot; said Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hometown Inspiration</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/blue-pan-pizza-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.03897,39.76197,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Biju&#x27;s Little Curry Shop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Biju&#x27;s Little Curry Shop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver, CO 80205 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3032923500" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">303-292-3500</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.littlecurryshop.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.littlecurryshop.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Biju%27s+Little+Curry+Shop%2C+1441+26th+St%2C+Denver%2C+CO+80205&amp;ll=39.759525,-104.986551" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1441 26th St<br/>Denver, CO 80205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Biriyani with Beef, Vindaloo Chicken Bowl</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy couldn&#x27;t help but munch on this restaurant&#x27;s staple ingredient: fresh curry leaves that are blended with a heat-packed combo of spices and chile peppers to create the robust base that starts off all the South Indian bowls served here. Diners can choose from beef, chicken and vegetarian options.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tri-Continent Cuisine</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/bijus-little-curry-shop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.98655,39.75953,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bang!</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bang!</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver, CO 80211 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3034551117" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">303-455-1117</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/bang-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/bang-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bang%21%2C+3472+W+32nd+Ave%2C+Denver%2C+CO+80211&amp;ll=39.761932,-105.033995" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3472 W 32nd Ave<br/>Denver, CO 80211</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meatloaf</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bang! describes its cuisine as &quot;new American, classics with our little twists.&quot; Take, for example, the righteous gumbo served with a slice of warm jalapeno cornbread. Guy called the gumbo &quot;killer,&quot; but his Flavortown GPS quickly led to Bang!&#x27;s signature meatloaf drizzled with spicy homemade ketchup.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/bang-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.03399,39.76193,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Atomic Cowboy</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Atomic Cowboy</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver, CO 80206 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3033777900" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(303) 377-7900</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.denbisco.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.denbisco.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Atomic+Cowboy%2C+3237+E+Colfax+Ave%2C+Denver%2C+CO+80206&amp;ll=39.740380,-104.949098" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3237 E Colfax Ave<br/>Denver, CO 80206</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Elmer Biscuit Sandwich, Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Atomic Cowboy is home to both the Denver Biscuit Co. and Fat Sully&#x27;s Pizza. Guy enjoyed the flaky Elmer biscuit sandwich with smoked pork butt and homemade barbecue sauce. At Fat Sully&#x27;s, Guy loved the crunchy thin crust of the huge 26-inch pizza, which is made to order.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dynamic Duos<br/>Triple D Nation: Poke, Pork and Chicken Parm<br/>Pizza Party</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/atomic-cowboy-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-104.94910,39.74038,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Axios</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Axios</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Denver, CO 80212 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7203282225" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">720-328-2225</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://axiosdenver.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">axiosdenver.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Axios%2C+3901+Tennyson+St%2C+Denver%2C+CO+80212&amp;ll=39.771176,-105.044129" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3901 Tennyson St<br/>Denver, CO 80212</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Arni Psito (Slow-Braised Lamb Ribs), Torta Kataifi (Greek Pastry Tort)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">&quot;Not your average Greek restaurant by any means,&quot; Guy declared of Axios, where owner Telly Topakas draws on traditional recipes from the motherland and tweaks them with modern touches (think lighter dishes without so much oil). &quot;Where has that been all my life?&quot; Guy asked of the exquisitely charred lamb ribs, which are paired with roasted garlic-and-feta mashed potatoes, onions, leeks, mushrooms and fennel.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homeland Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/denver/axios-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.04413,39.77118,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Momona</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Momona</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chico 95928</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://momonachico.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">momonachico.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Momona%2C+230+W.+3rd+St%2C+Chico+95928&amp;ll=39.728863,-121.840870" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">230 W. 3rd St<br/>Chico 95928</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mochiko Chicken Bao, Chico Ramen</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Momona was started by three friends hoping to fill in a culinary gap in Chico, CA. They brought in the food they wanted to eat which was great noodles and baos that combined Hawaiian and Asian flavors. Guy loved the unique combination of flavors in the Mochiko Fried Chicken Bao and the Chico Ramen.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Not Your Everyday Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/restaurants-in-chico/momona-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.84087,39.72886,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Rawbar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Rawbar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chico, CA 95928</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.rawbarchico.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rawbarchico.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Rawbar%2C+346+Broadway+St%2C+Chico%2C+CA+95928&amp;ll=39.728646,-121.840175" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">346 Broadway St<br/>Chico, CA 95928</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tom Kha Thai Steamer, Pork Belly Bibimbap</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This pan-Asian joint goes above and beyond the average sushi menu with items like Tom Kha Thai Steamer and Pork Belly Bibimbap. After moving to Chico, California from San Francisco 20 years ago, owner and chef Darren Chadderdon realized he missed the diverse Asian flavors available in the big city. He decided to take things into his own hands, and traveled to Thailand to take cooking classes before returning home to open his own restaurant. The Tom Kha Thai Steamer, a sweet and spicy seafood soup, blew Guy away: &quot;I wanted that to be great,&quot; he said after the first bite. &quot;It&#x27;s not great, it&#x27;s phenomenal!&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Standout Seafood</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/restaurants-in-chico/the-rawbar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.84018,39.72865,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Upper Crust Bakery &amp; Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Upper Crust Bakery &amp; Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chico 95928</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.uppercrustchico.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.uppercrustchico.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Upper+Crust+Bakery+%26+Cafe%2C+130+Main+Street%2C+Chico+95928&amp;ll=39.730481,-121.840875" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">130 Main Street<br/>Chico 95928</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Black Bean Chili, Korean Pork Salad</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This local favorite makes excellent bread and pastry but also legit food. The popular Black Bean Chili has good old-school flavor, but it&#x27;s kicked up with a tangy cilantro pesto and served with jalapeno-cheddar challah muffins. Diners also rave about the Korean Pork Salad.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Coming Together in Cali</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/restaurants-in-chico/upper-crust-bakery-and-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.84087,39.73048,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sin of Cortez</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sin of Cortez</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chico 95926 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://sinofcortezchico.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">sinofcortezchico.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sin+of+Cortez%2C+2290+Esplanade%2C+Chico+95926&amp;ll=39.752540,-121.856691" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2290 Esplanade<br/>Chico 95926</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cortez French Toast, Dragon Potatoes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners come to Daniele Ius place for an amazing breakfast experience. The popular Cortez French Toast is the perfect marriage between cinnamon rolls and French toast. &quot;If you like French toast it doesn&#x27;t get much more creative than that,&quot; said Guy. The spicy Dragon Potatoes are another favorite. Guy compared the dish to a gigantic, deconstructed carnitas burrito.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burger and Breakfast</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/restaurants-in-chico/sin-of-cortez-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.85669,39.75254,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Spirito&#x27;s Italian Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Spirito&#x27;s Italian Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Real Carlsbad, CA 07202 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7607207111" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(760) 720-7111</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://spiritositaliandiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">spiritositaliandiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Spirito%27s+Italian+Diner%2C+2508+El+Camino%2C+Real+Carlsbad%2C+CA+07202&amp;ll=33.180318,-117.324901" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2508 El Camino<br/>Real Carlsbad, CA 07202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spaghetti with Spirito&#x27;s Original Gravy and One Meatball</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spirito&#x27;s Italian Diner may be nestled in a strip mall, but that didn&#x27;t mean Guy couldn&#x27;t enjoy some &amp;quot;old-school Jersey gravy.&amp;quot; Owner Mike Spirito has been keeping his family&#x27;s recipes alive with pizza napoletana, &amp;quot;monster&amp;quot; ravioli and the signature Roman meatballs, made with raisins and pine nuts.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From the Heart</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/real-carlsbad/spiritos-italian-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.32490,33.18032,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tub&#x27;s Fine Chili and Fancy Fixin&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tub&#x27;s Fine Chili and Fancy Fixin&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Culver City, CA 90230 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3105926070" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">310-592-6070</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tubschili.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tubschili.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tub%27s+Fine+Chili+and+Fancy+Fixin%27s%2C+4263+Overland+Ave%2C+Culver+City%2C+CA+90230&amp;ll=34.011583,-118.400786" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4263 Overland Ave<br/>Culver City, CA 90230</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey Drive Chili, Double-Barrel Dingo Dog</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef-Owner Rick Hodges and his wife, Margie, are slinging more than six varieties of chili daily at their Wild West-themed restaurant. Each portion is served in an individual toasted flatbread tub (hence the restaurant&#x27;s name), which Guy thought was a great touch. He stopped here to sample the Turkey Drive Chili, which features roasted ground turkey seasoned with plenty of chili powder and Cajun spices.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Bowlful of Soul</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/culver-city/tubs-fine-chili-and-fancy-fixins-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.40079,34.01158,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>900 Grayson Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">900 Grayson Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Berkeley, CA 94710 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5107049900" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(510) 704-9900</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.900grayson.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.900grayson.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=900+Grayson+Restaurant%2C+900+Grayson+St%2C+Berkeley%2C+CA+94710&amp;ll=37.855183,-122.292301" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">900 Grayson St<br/>Berkeley, CA 94710</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken and Buttermilk Waffle, Steak Frites</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy may have visited 900 Grayson for his Triple D Goes Tailgating special, but that didn&#x27;t mean 900 Grayson was serving nachos. Instead, they feature dishes from the East to the South, like the LadyBoy prawn salad or the Demon Lover chicken and waffles plate topped with spicy buttermilk gravy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Goes Tailgatin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/berkeley/900-grayson-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.29230,37.85518,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bette&#x27;s Oceanview Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bette&#x27;s Oceanview Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Berkeley, CA 94710 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5106443230" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">510-644-3230</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bettesdiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bettesdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bette%27s+Oceanview+Diner%2C+1807+4th+St%2C+Berkeley%2C+CA+94710&amp;ll=37.869885,-122.300328" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1807 4th St<br/>Berkeley, CA 94710</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Scrapple, Pancakes, Scones</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ever since Bette Kroening opened her Berkeley, Calif., diner, she&#x27;s been dishing out home-style favorites to adoring local fans. Guy couldn&#x27;t get enough of the Philadelphia-style scrapple and even an apple brandy pancake souffle that&#x27;s light, airy and, as regulars say, like &amp;quot;eating a cloud.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">And The Kicker Is...<br/>Real-Deal Diners</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/berkeley/bettes-oceanview-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.30033,37.86988,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Meal Ticket</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Meal Ticket</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Berkeley, CA 94706 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5105266325" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(510) 526-6325</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mealticketrestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mealticketrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Meal+Ticket%2C+1235+San+Pablo+Ave%2C+Berkeley%2C+CA+94706&amp;ll=37.881067,-122.295688" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1235 San Pablo Ave<br/>Berkeley, CA 94706</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulled Pork with Coconut Curry</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Scottish-born chef Jimmy Carter is &amp;quot;whipping up a little American Southern,&amp;quot; and a little punch of flavor gets thrown into every bite at Meal Ticket. He&#x27;s making great fusion food with dishes like the pulled pork with coconut curry, which has Thai-Southern flair with a little Mexican in the mix.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sweet &#x27;n Savory</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/berkeley/meal-ticket-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.29569,37.88107,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bubba&#x27;s Fine Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bubba&#x27;s Fine Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Anselmo 94960</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4154596862" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 459-6862</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bubbas-diner.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bubbas-diner.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bubba%27s+Fine+Diner%2C+566+San+Anselmo+Ave%2C+San+Anselmo+94960&amp;ll=37.975646,-122.562458" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">566 San Anselmo Ave<br/>San Anselmo 94960</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ahi Tuna Pot Stickers, Soft-Shell Crab BLT, Kobe Beef Meatloaf, Creme Brulee French Toast</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Bubba&#x27;s Diner, they believe that &quot;great ingredients turn out really good quality food.&quot; The Ahi Tuna Pot Stickers with homemade wrappers served on a bed of wilted spinach melted in Guy&#x27;s mouth, as did the Soft-Shell Crab BLT. Locals like the Kobe beef meatloaf and Creme Brulee French Toast.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Biscuits, Bagels and BLT&#x27;s</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-anselmo/bubbas-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.56246,37.97565,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sherman&#x27;s Deli &amp; Bakery</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sherman&#x27;s Deli &amp; Bakery</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Palm Springs, CA 92262</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7603251199" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">760-325-1199</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.shermansdeli.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.shermansdeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sherman%27s+Deli+%26+Bakery%2C+401+E.+Tahquitz+Canyon+Way%2C+Palm+Springs%2C+CA+92262&amp;ll=33.822831,-116.543233" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">401 E. Tahquitz Canyon Way<br/>Palm Springs, CA 92262</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey Pastrami, Beef n&#x27; Latkas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you follow the intoxicating aroma of fresh-baked rye bread in Palm Springs you could find yourself at Sherman&#x27;s Deli &amp; Bakery. Once there, try the house-made turkey pastrami which is layered on that fabulous bread. &quot;If that&#x27;s the only thing that you sold here I could expect lines all the way to Wisconsin,&quot; said Guy. Or try the real-deal latkes that serve as the &quot;bread&quot; for meltingly tender brisket topped with creamy horseradish sauce. Be sure you don&#x27;t leave without a taste of the fan-favorite banana tart.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey, Taters and Dogs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/palm-springs/shermans-deli-and-bakery" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-116.54323,33.82283,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rick &amp; Ann&#x27;s Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rick &amp; Ann&#x27;s Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Berkeley, CA 94705 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5106498538" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(510) 649-8538</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rickandanns.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rickandanns.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rick+%26+Ann%27s+Restaurant%2C+2922+Domingo+Ave%2C+Berkeley%2C+CA+94705&amp;ll=37.858586,-122.244178" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2922 Domingo Ave<br/>Berkeley, CA 94705</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Buttermilk Pancakes, Mom&#x27;s Macaroni and Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this eatery, the special is comfort food with flair. Guy is a fan of the jalapeno pesto flank steak sandwich with sauteed bell peppers and Jack cheese. The brined and smoked pork chops with homemade apple sauce, potato pancakes and sour cream also receive rave reviews.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Goes Tailgatin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/berkeley/rick-anns-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.24418,37.85859,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Frankinbun</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Frankinbun</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Palm Springs, CA 92264 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7603184841" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">760-318-4841</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.frankinbun.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.frankinbun.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Frankinbun%2C+540+S+Indian+Canyon+Dr%2C+Palm+Springs%2C+CA+92264&amp;ll=33.815112,-116.545488" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">540 S Indian Canyon Dr<br/>Palm Springs, CA 92264</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Vegan Dog, Chicken and Waffle on a Stick</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Stop by Frankinbun for one of the best vegan dishes Guy has ever had. The meat-free hot dog is crafted from brown rice flour, black eyed peas and aromatics and then topped with a dynamite house-made chili. Plus, try their handheld version of chicken and waffles which consists of Bavarian chicken apple sausage surrounded by a crisp waffle shell served with maple syrup.

</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Trifecta</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/palm-springs/frankinbun-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-116.54549,33.81511,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>HoBo&#x27;s BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">HoBo&#x27;s BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Temecula, CA 92591 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9516933227" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">951-693-3227</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://hobosbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">hobosbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=HoBo%27s+BBQ%2C+30590+Rancho+California+Rd%2C+Temecula%2C+CA+92591&amp;ll=33.510024,-117.125938" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">30590 Rancho California Rd<br/>Temecula, CA 92591</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ Lasagna, Lumber Jack Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners flock to Hobo&#x27;s for the best barbeque in Southern California. Guy tries the lasagna, a unique dish of pulled pork and chicken layered with pasta sheets, cheese and barbeque sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Beef and Barbecue</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/temecula/hobos-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.12594,33.51002,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Schooner or Later</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Schooner or Later</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Long Beach, CA 90803 &middot; &#9733; 2.7 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5624303495" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(562) 430-3495</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.schoonerorlater.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.schoonerorlater.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Schooner+or+Later%2C+241+N+Marina+Dr%2C+Long+Beach%2C+CA+90803&amp;ll=33.752191,-118.108256" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">241 N Marina Dr<br/>Long Beach, CA 90803</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Mess ((Potatoes, Ham, Eggs and Cheese), Belgian Waffle, Crab Omelet with Avocado, Italian Omelet with Marinara</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">There&#x27;s no rush at Schooner or Later in Long Beach, Calif. (a schooner is a 24-ounce chalice of beer). The breakfast and lunch landmark&#x27;s bangin&#x27; Belgian waffle and fluffy crab omelet with avocado are perfection. Hit the jackpot with The Mess: griddled eggs with ham, peppers, onion and cheese.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Off the Hook Specials</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/long-beach/schooner-or-later-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.10826,33.75219,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Starling Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Starling Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Long Beach, CA 90814 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5624332041" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(562) 433-2041</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.starlingdiner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.starlingdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Starling+Diner%2C+4114+E+3rd+St%2C+Long+Beach%2C+CA+90814&amp;ll=33.767962,-118.144363" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4114 E 3rd St<br/>Long Beach, CA 90814</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pot Roast, Scone</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The star item on the menu at Starling Diner is the slow-roasted pot roast. Polenta, potatoes and chuck roast seared in butter are wrapped up in a gravy-topped tortilla to make one tantalizing dish that Guy calls a &quot;power bomb of flavor.&quot; Also try the fluffy scones served with orange honey butter.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old Standards, New Styles</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/long-beach/starling-diner" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.14436,33.76796,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Delancey Pizzeria &amp; Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Delancey Pizzeria &amp; Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Hollywood, CA 90028</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3234692100" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">323-469-2100</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://delanceyhollywood.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">delanceyhollywood.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Delancey+Pizzeria+%26+Bar%2C+5936+Sunset+Blvd.%2C+Hollywood%2C+CA+90028&amp;ll=34.097814,-118.319236" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5936 Sunset Blvd.<br/>Hollywood, CA 90028</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">&quot;Gramercy&quot; Pizza, Potato Gnocchi with Wild Boar, Sage and Olives</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owner George Abou-Daoud opened this joint as an homage to the Italian restaurants in downtown Manhattan, and it&#x27;s apparent once you open the menu, filled with pizzas named after New York streets - think Fulton, Crosby and Mercer. Pork lovers, opt for the Gramercy. In addition to featuring red sauce and melted mozzarella, this pork-centric pie comes loaded with pepperoni, sausage, bacon, soppressata and guanciale. Once cooked, the pizza is brushed with a garlic-infused olive oil. &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chew and Brew</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/hollywood/delancey-pizzeria-and-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.31924,34.09781,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>At Last Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">At Last Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Long Beach 90802 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5624374837" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(562) 437-4837</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.jmchefcatering.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jmchefcatering.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=At+Last+Cafe%2C+204+Orange+Ave%2C+Long+Beach+90802&amp;ll=33.767963,-118.176730" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">204 Orange Ave<br/>Long Beach 90802</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Honey-Marinated Pork Chops with Granny Smiths and Cranberries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners who visit At Last Cafe say &quot;at last&quot; for the flavorful dishes, reasonable prices and fresh ingredients. On Triple D, Guy was also saying &quot;I&#x27;d eat that on a shoe&quot; about the super tender and juicy pork chops and the homemade polenta made with a rich and creamy portabella mushroom sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Holiday Hoopla<br/>Porkapalooza</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/long-beach/at-last-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.17673,33.76796,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Factory Gastrobar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Factory Gastrobar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Long Beach, CA 90807</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5625954020" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(562) 595-4020</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thefactorylb.com/The_Factory_Gastrobar/Home.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thefactorylb.com/The_Factory_Gastrobar/Home.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Factory+Gastrobar%2C+4020+Atlantic+Ave%2C+Long+Beach%2C+CA+90807&amp;ll=33.830948,-118.184760" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4020 Atlantic Ave<br/>Long Beach, CA 90807</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Open-faced Grilled Asparagus Sandwich, Pig n&#x27; Grits</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Named after Andy Warhol&#x27;s famed art studio, The Factory Gastrobar specializes in comfort food that is seasonal, sustainable, local - and aesthetically pleasing. Guy recommends the open-faced grilled asparagus sandwich and the pig &#x27;n&#x27; grits made with beer-braised, all-natural, organic pulled pork.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Standards to Standouts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/long-beach/the-factory-gastrobar" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.18476,33.83095,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tavern on 2</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tavern on 2</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Long Beach, CA 90803 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5628564000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(562) 856-4000</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://tavernon2.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">tavernon2.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tavern+on+2%2C+5110+E+2nd+St%2C+Long+Beach%2C+CA+90803&amp;ll=33.760398,-118.135674" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5110 E 2nd St<br/>Long Beach, CA 90803</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pig Tails, Belly and Sucker</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">&lt;p&gt;Tavern on 2 features a gastropub menu that draws influences from Asian and Mexican cuisine. Guy recommends the pig tails, which are fried and covered in a sticky, spicy Asian sauce. For a unique take on surf and turf, try the &quot;incredibly flavorful&quot; Belly &amp;amp; Sucker, composed of pork belly and octopus.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Extra Helpings<br/>All Day Dining</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/long-beach/tavern-on-2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.13567,33.76040,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Banshee</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Banshee</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chico 95928 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.thebansheechico.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thebansheechico.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Banshee%2C+134+West+2nd+St%2C+Chico+95928&amp;ll=39.730111,-121.841171" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">134 West 2nd St<br/>Chico 95928</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pho French Dip, Bahn Mi Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners say The Banshee is Chico&#x27;s best kept secret. Chef Will Brady&#x27;s food combines his Boston background with his time in Southeast Asia into true fusion comfort food. The Pho French Dip is made with braised beef and topped with house-made pickled cucumbers, onion, carrots and spicy mayo and then dipped in a spicy broth. &quot;You&#x27;re taking folks international and they don&#x27;t need a passport,&quot; said Guy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Coming Together in Cali</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/restaurants-in-chico/the-banshee-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.84117,39.73011,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Scolari&#x27;s Good Eats</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Scolari&#x27;s Good Eats</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Alameda, CA 94501 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5105212400" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(510) 521-2400</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.scolarisgoodeats.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.scolarisgoodeats.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Scolari%27s+Good+Eats%2C+1303+Park+St%2C+Alameda%2C+CA+94501&amp;ll=37.762771,-122.244366" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1303 Park St<br/>Alameda, CA 94501</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nashville Hot Fried Chicken Sandwich, Blueberry Bacon Blue Cheese Burger au Poivre</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Good eats, indeed. This Triple D destination offers up American fare that includes a must-try Nashville Hot Fried Chicken Sandwich and a Blueberry Bacon Blue Cheeseburger that&#x27;s an absolute winner. Bonus: While waiting for your food, enjoy a drink from the Lucky 13 bar, located adjacent to Scolari&#x27;s.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Playin&#x27; Chicken</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/alameda/scolaris-good-eats" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.24437,37.76277,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Granzella&#x27;s Restaurant &amp; Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Granzella&#x27;s Restaurant &amp; Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Williams, CA 95987 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.granzellas.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.granzellas.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Granzella%27s+Restaurant+%26+Deli%2C+451+6th+St%2C+Williams%2C+CA+95987&amp;ll=39.155775,-122.148594" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">451 6th St<br/>Williams, CA 95987</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Muffuletta, Reuben</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Guy was growing up, his familywould stop at Granzella&#x27;s Deli on road trips for the best muffuletta ever. Stop in and try one of their 30 different sandwiches.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Between the Bread</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/restaurants-in-williams/granzellas-restaurant-and-deli" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.14859,39.15577,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Grana</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Grana</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Chico 95928</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.granachico.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.granachico.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Grana%2C+198+E.+2nd+St%2C+Chico+95928&amp;ll=39.730912,-121.839819" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">198 E. 2nd St<br/>Chico 95928</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Braised Pork Ragu, Chicken Leg</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners head to Grana for pasta and comfort food done right. This centerpiece of this farm-to-table restaurant is the oven that Chef Jeff King had imported from Italy. Two must-try dishes are the Braised Pork Ragu topped with a bright salsa verde and the deceptively simple Braised Chicken Leg served with dreamy white cheddar polenta and braised greens.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Coming Together in Cali</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/restaurants-in-chico/grana-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.83982,39.73091,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Restaurant 415</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Restaurant 415</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fort Collins, CO 80524 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9704070415" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">970-407-0415</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://thefourfifteen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">thefourfifteen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Restaurant+415%2C+415+S+Mason+St%2C+Fort+Collins%2C+CO+80524&amp;ll=40.582328,-105.079199" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">415 S Mason St<br/>Fort Collins, CO 80524</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Americano Del Sur Pizza, Blackened Cauliflower Steak</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This quirky neighborhood spot uses locally sourced ingredients in unexpected ways to craft innovative dishes like the Americano Del Sur pizza. Guy raves about the bite provided by the thinly sliced tomatillos that adorn this creative pie, which also features garbanzo beans and fresh jalapenos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Biscuits to Brisket</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/fort-collins/restaurant-415" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.07920,40.58233,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lodge Sasquatch Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lodge Sasquatch Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fort Collins, CO 80524</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9706822369" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">970-682-2369</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://lodgefoco.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">lodgefoco.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lodge+Sasquatch+Kitchen%2C+151+N+College+Ave%2C+Fort+Collins%2C+CO+80524&amp;ll=40.588155,-105.077604" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">151 N College Ave<br/>Fort Collins, CO 80524</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Green Chili, Habanero Parmesan Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple-D alum Aaron May and former NFL player Jared Allen are the dynamite duo behind this spot, which has a mountain-lodge vibe and hearty dishes to match. Guy is a fan of the flavorful chili, which comes loaded with beer-braised pork butt and pureed green chiles for added kick.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Name That Kitchen</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/co/fort-collins/lodge-sasquatch-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-105.07760,40.58816,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Grand Harbor</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Grand Harbor</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Burlingame 94010 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6503479888" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(650) 347-9888</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://grandharborsf.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">grandharborsf.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Grand+Harbor%2C+1492+Old+Bayshore+Hwy%2C+Burlingame+94010&amp;ll=37.598244,-122.364296" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1492 Old Bayshore Hwy<br/>Burlingame 94010</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Buns, Dim Sum Chicken Feet, Lobster in Garlic Sauce</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This San Francisco destination is one of the biggest Triple D joints ever, with seating for more than 450 people. Serving up traditional Chinese fare, Grand Harbor regulars rave about the pork buns,dim sum chicken feet and a selection of fresh seafood. Bonus: The restaurant&#x27;s view of the San Francisco Bay is absolutely spectacular.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On the Hook and In the Bun</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/burlingame/grand-harbor" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.36430,37.59824,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Giusti&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Giusti&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Walnut Grove, CA 95690 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9167761808" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">916-776-1808</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.giustis.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.giustis.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Giusti%27s%2C+14743+Walnut+Grove-Thornton+Road%2C+Walnut+Grove%2C+CA+95690&amp;ll=38.223639,-121.507193" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">14743 Walnut Grove-Thornton Road<br/>Walnut Grove, CA 95690</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Shanks</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This funky former saloon that&#x27;s off the beaten path has&#x27;t changed that much in a hundred years, from the fixtures to the main courses. Stop by to enjoy homemade classics such as the lamb shanks with polenta that Guy calls &amp;quot;beyond fall of the bone tender&amp;quot; and Grandma&#x27;s minestrone recipe.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/walnut-grove/giustis-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.50719,38.22364,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Zazu Kitchen + Farm</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Zazu Kitchen + Farm</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sebastopol, CA 95472 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7075234814" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">707-523-4814</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://zazukitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">zazukitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Zazu+Kitchen+%2B+Farm%2C+6770+McKinley+%23150%2C+Sebastopol%2C+CA+95472&amp;ll=38.403757,-122.821687" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6770 McKinley #150<br/>Sebastopol, CA 95472</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rodeo Jaxs, Bacon-in-the-Batter Waffle, Porcini Noodle Stroganoff</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At ZAZU kitchen + farm, Chef Duskie Estes and her husband Chef John Stewart are serving up true farm-to-table dishes with a creative flair. Their menus change daily based upon the ingredients they grow and source from the surrounding area. Guy loved their Bacon-in-the-Batter Waffle served with house-made bacon toffee and bourbon gelato. Get anything with their house-cured bacon!</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Sandwiches to Stroganoff</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sebastopol/zazu-kitchen-and-farm-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.82169,38.40376,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Naglee Park Garage</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Naglee Park Garage</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Jose, CA 95112 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4082861100" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(408) 286-1100</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.nagleeparkgarage.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.nagleeparkgarage.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Naglee+Park+Garage%2C+505+E+San+Carlos+St%2C+San+Jose%2C+CA+95112&amp;ll=37.336858,-121.876192" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">505 E San Carlos St<br/>San Jose, CA 95112</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Herb Marinated NY Steak, Lamb Meatballs w/ a Cucumber Mint Sauce, Brussels Sprouts</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Although this auto-repair shop turned grub stop may be small, &amp;quot;the flavor&#x27;s big.&amp;quot; So says Guy, who devoured the 10-ounce burger patties served with handmade everything, from the fries and ketchup to the mayonnaise. But the real end-of-the-meal kicker? A side of Brussels sprouts with smoky bacon.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort Food Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-jose/naglee-park-garage-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.87619,37.33686,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Falafel&#x27;s Drive-In</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Falafel&#x27;s Drive-In</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Jose, CA 95128 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4082947886" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">408-294-7886</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.falafelsdrivein.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.falafelsdrivein.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Falafel%27s+Drive-In%2C+2301+Stevens+Creek+Blvd%2C+San+Jose%2C+CA+95128&amp;ll=37.323653,-121.935043" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2301 Stevens Creek Blvd<br/>San Jose, CA 95128</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Falafel, Gyros, Tabouli, Banana Shakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The motto at Falafel&#x27;s Drive-In goes, &amp;quot;Feeling awful? Have a falafel.&amp;quot; On DDD, Guy couldn&#x27;t have agreed more. These fried chickpea balls are made with fresh herbs and a perfect blend of spices. Regulars know when getting their &amp;quot;falafel fix&amp;quot; that a refreshing banana shake is the perfect complement.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Totally Fried<br/>Dynamite Desserts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-jose/falafels-drive-in-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.93504,37.32365,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Los Tapatios</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Los Tapatios</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Jose, CA 95127</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4087296199" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">408-729-6199</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.myspace.com/lostapatiosrestaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.myspace.com/lostapatiosrestaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Los+Tapatios%2C+354+N+White+Rd%2C+San+Jose%2C+CA+95127&amp;ll=37.375824,-121.836140" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">354 N White Rd<br/>San Jose, CA 95127</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Guy Fieri, discovers some homemade authentic Mexican food at Los Tapatios, in San Jose, CA, a former lunch truck that upgraded to a full-blown restaurant.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">One of a Kind</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-jose/los-tapatios-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.83614,37.37582,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jay Bee&#x27;s Bar-B-Q</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jay Bee&#x27;s Bar-B-Q</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Gardena, CA 90247 &middot; &#9733; 1.9 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3105321064" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">310-532-1064</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Jay-Bees-Bar-B-Que/206073332762093" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Jay-Bees-Bar-B-Que/206073332762093</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jay+Bee%27s+Bar-B-Q%2C+15911+S+Avalon+Blvd%2C+Gardena%2C+CA+90247&amp;ll=33.886749,-118.265434" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">15911 S Avalon Blvd<br/>Gardena, CA 90247</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ Sandwiches, Ribs, Pulled Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy Fieri tracks down Jay Bee&#x27;s Bar-B-Que, in Gardena, CA, for some down-home BBQ served from a shack on the median of a Los Angeles highway on Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Real Deal BBQ</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/gardena/jay-bees-bar-b-que-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.26543,33.88675,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fab Hot Dogs</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fab Hot Dogs</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Reseda, CA 91335 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8183444336" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">818-344-4336</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.fabhotdogs.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fabhotdogs.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fab+Hot+Dogs%2C+19417+Victory+Blvd.%2C+Reseda%2C+CA+91335&amp;ll=34.186811,-118.556230" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">19417 Victory Blvd.<br/>Reseda, CA 91335</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Deep Fried Hot Dogs, Burritos, Sweet and Spicy Onion Relish</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you&#x27;re skeptical on how authentic Mexican food could be in Milwaukee, you&#x27;ll change your mind after trying the mole at Cempazuchi. Owner Bryce Clark has been traveling to Mexico and seeking out recipes to deliver unique authentic dishes like duck tacos and Fajitas de Nortenos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Tacos and Dogs</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/reseda/fab-hot-dogs-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.55623,34.18681,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Emma Jean&#x27;s Holland Burger Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Emma Jean&#x27;s Holland Burger Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Victorville, CA 92394 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7602439938" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(760) 243-9938</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/victorville/emma-jeans-holland-burger-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/victorville/emma-jeans-holland-burger-cafe-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Emma+Jean%27s+Holland+Burger+Cafe%2C+17143+N.+D+St.%2C+Victorville%2C+CA+92394&amp;ll=34.561028,-117.313943" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">17143 N. D St.<br/>Victorville, CA 92394</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Trucker Special Sandwich with Roasted Tri-Tip</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Follow Guy Fieri, host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, on America&#x27;s most famous road, Route 66, to Emma Jean&#x27;s Holland Burger Cafe in Victorville, Ca for some classic comfort food.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Route 66<br/>All Stacked Up</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/victorville/emma-jeans-holland-burger-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.31394,34.56103,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nighthawk Breakfast Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nighthawk Breakfast Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Venice, CA 90292</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4248354556" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">424-835-4556</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.nighthawkrestaurants.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.nighthawkrestaurants.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nighthawk+Breakfast+Bar%2C+417+Washington+Blvd%2C+Venice%2C+CA+90292&amp;ll=33.981379,-118.463123" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">417 Washington Blvd<br/>Venice, CA 90292</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Drunken French Toast, Biscuit Bao</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nighthawk Breakfast Bar specializes in serving breakfast for dinner. Chef and owner Chef and Owner Jeremy Fall is all about pushing the envelope on beloved childhood flavors. The Drunken French Toast is a crispy creation topped with cognac sauteed pears, mascarpone mousse and a dash of pear brandy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Breakfast, Brisket and Belly</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/venice/nighthawk-breakfast-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.46312,33.98138,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Original Barone&#x27;s Famous Italian</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Original Barone&#x27;s Famous Italian</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Valley Glen, CA 91401 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8187826004" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">818-782-6004</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.baronesfamousitalian.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.baronesfamousitalian.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Original+Barone%27s+Famous+Italian%2C+13726+Oxnard+St%2C+Valley+Glen%2C+CA+91401&amp;ll=34.179124,-118.432117" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">13726 Oxnard St<br/>Valley Glen, CA 91401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Thin-Crust Pizza, Cheese Lasagna</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This family-owned eatery is famous for slinging rectangular thin-crust, Neapolitan-style slices, which they&#x27;ve been doing since well before pizza made it to the West Coast in a big way. Back in the 1940s, Barone&#x27;s owners set out to re-create the Italian-style pizza popular in New York using the only tool available - a sheet pan - and thus the signature slices were born. Another must-try is the ricotta and Parmesan lasagna, served with meatballs and housemade marinara sauce.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Global Greats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/valley-glen/the-original-barones-famous-italian-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.43212,34.17912,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Baby Blues BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Baby Blues BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Venice 90291 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3103967675" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(310) 396-7675</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.babybluesvenice.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.babybluesvenice.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Baby+Blues+BBQ%2C+444+Lincoln+Blvd.%2C+Venice+90291&amp;ll=34.000318,-118.465437" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">444 Lincoln Blvd.<br/>Venice 90291</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulled Pork, Ribs, BBQ, Triple-X Sauce with Roasted Hot Peppers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern California maybe isn&#x27;t the first place someone would think of when looking for great barbecue, but Baby Blues BBQ in Venice Beach smokes their pulled pork for 16-18 hours. They also make their own &#x27;&#x27;XXX&#x27;&#x27; hot sauce with Scotch bonnet and poblano peppers, which knocked Guy&#x27;s socks off.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Best of the West Roundup<br/>BBQ</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/venice/baby-blues-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.46544,34.00032,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Smitty&#x27;s Wings &amp; Things</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Smitty&#x27;s Wings &amp; Things</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Stockton, CA 95203 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2092277479" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">209-227-7479</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/stockton/smittys-wings-and-things-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/stockton/smittys-wings-and-things-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Smitty%27s+Wings+%26+Things%2C+946+Acacia+St%2C+Stockton%2C+CA+95203&amp;ll=37.960114,-121.306611" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">946 Acacia St<br/>Stockton, CA 95203</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Damn Hot Wings, Thai Sweet and Sour Wings</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Former NFL player Steve Smith has traded in the pigskins for wings, which he slings at this Stockton joint. One popular option is the Damn Hot, which Guy called a &quot;good old-fashioned funky, crunchy wing.&quot; For this dish, the wings are coated in a paprika-laced flour mix, fried and then slathered in a fiery sauce whose heat factor is kicked up with cayenne, smoked jalapenos and green chiles.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked, Grilled and Fried</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/stockton/smittys-wings-and-things-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.30661,37.96011,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Midtown Creperie</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Midtown Creperie</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Stockton, CA 95204 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2099419070" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">209-941-9070</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://midtowncreperie.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">midtowncreperie.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Midtown+Creperie%2C+2319+Pacific+Ave%2C+Stockton%2C+CA+95204&amp;ll=37.972006,-121.301120" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2319 Pacific Ave<br/>Stockton, CA 95204</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crepe, Beignet</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For a taste of New Orleans in the midst of Stockton, Calif., Guy made a beeline for this Miracle Mile restaurant. In addition to crepes (both savory and sweet), this spot also serves up its own twist on traditional beignets (chocolate or caramel dipping sauce, anyone?).</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos, Turtles and Tri-Tip</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/stockton/midtown-creperie-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.30112,37.97201,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Burger Me</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Burger Me</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Truckee, CA 96161 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5305878852" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(530) 587-8852</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.burgermetruckee.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.burgermetruckee.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Burger+Me%2C+10418+Donner+Pass+Rd.%2C+Truckee%2C+CA+96161&amp;ll=39.325508,-120.191220" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">10418 Donner Pass Rd.<br/>Truckee, CA 96161</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, &quot;The Italian Stallion&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy Fieri, host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, grabs a bite to eat at Burger Me in Truckee, CA, a warehouse-turned burger spot where everything is fresh and made to order.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers &#x27;n More<br/>Top 10 Burgers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/truckee/burger-me-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-120.19122,39.32551,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Gian&#x27;s Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Gian&#x27;s Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Stockton, CA 95204</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2094690108" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">209-469-0108</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://giansdeli.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">giansdeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Gian%27s+Deli%2C+2112+Pacific+Ave%2C+Stockton%2C+CA+95204&amp;ll=37.971402,-121.300288" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2112 Pacific Ave<br/>Stockton, CA 95204</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ravioli in Meat Sauce, Sausage and Pepper Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This authentic Italian deli churns out 4,000-plus ravioli a week using a ravioli machine that dates back more than a century. &quot;I have seen really cool kitchen equipment in my day,&quot; Guy said of the gear. &quot;This might be the coolest.&quot; The deli&#x27;s signature ravioli are stuffed with a combination of beef, cheese, spinach and Swiss chard, then served with a homemade Bolognese-style meat sauce</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Great Gear</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/stockton/gians-deli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.30029,37.97140,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Asian Experience</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Asian Experience</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Taft, CA 93268</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6617631815" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">661-763-1815</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.asianexp.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.asianexp.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Asian+Experience%2C+215+Center+St%2C+Taft%2C+CA+93268&amp;ll=35.139618,-119.455475" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">215 Center St<br/>Taft, CA 93268</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tom Yum Kung, Pad Thai</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy heaps the praise on this restaurant&#x27;s Pad Thai and Tom Yum Kung soup, calling it &amp;quot;nice and light and bright and fresh.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">To Bakersfield and Beyond</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/Taft/asian-experience-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.45548,35.13962,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Green Papaya Food Truck</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Green Papaya Food Truck</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Stockton, CA 95205 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2099818733" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">209-981-8733</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.greenpapayafoodtruck.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.greenpapayafoodtruck.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Green+Papaya+Food+Truck%2C+Stockton%2C+CA+95205&amp;ll=37.964259,-121.256914" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;"><br/>Stockton, CA 95205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kao Piek, Green Papaya Salad, Nam Kao</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">In a first for Guy, he checked out this food truck dishing up Laotian street food, which Chef-Owner Mony Vangsoulatda characterizes as &quot;spicy, sour (and) bitter.&quot; Guy tried the Kao Piek, a garlicky, chile-laced chicken soup featuring noodles that Chef Vangsoulatda makes herself. &quot;These noodles got some texture and some bite,&quot; Guy exclaimed, declaring the dish one of the top three Asian soups he&#x27;s ever tried.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">International Appeal</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/stockton/green-papaya-food-truck-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.25691,37.96426,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jax at the Tracks</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jax at the Tracks</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Truckee, CA 96160 &middot; &#9733; 2.5 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5305507450" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(530) 550-7450</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.jaxtruckee.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jaxtruckee.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jax+at+the+Tracks%2C+10144+W+River+St%2C+Truckee%2C+CA+96160&amp;ll=39.327434,-120.184096" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">10144 W River St<br/>Truckee, CA 96160</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Morning Addiction Breakfast, Kobe Beef Meatloaf and Meatballs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">JAX at the Tracks may be an old-school diner, but all the dishes have an upscale, gourmet twist. Owner Bud Haley redid everything when he took over, including the menu. For a DDD first, Guy couldn&#x27;t help but love the housemade English muffin used for the Crab Cake Eggs Benedict.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort Food With Attitude</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/truckee/jax-at-the-tracks-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-120.18410,39.32743,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Schellville Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Schellville Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sonoma, CA 95476 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7079965151" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 996-5151</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.schellvillegrill.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.schellvillegrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Schellville+Grill%2C+22900+Broadway%2C+Sonoma%2C+CA+95476&amp;ll=38.244382,-122.448882" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">22900 Broadway<br/>Sonoma, CA 95476</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Tri Tip Sandwich with Fruit BBQ Sauce, Lasagna, The Yahoo Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">To get to Schellville Grill you will need to search off the beaten path. Once you&#x27;re there, you can&#x27;t miss the &amp;quot;Tuscan-style&amp;quot; signatures that Chef Matthew Nagan creates, including a twelve-layer eggplant lasagna that Guy called &amp;quot;outstanding,&amp;quot; or The Yahoo Burger with Creamy Chipotle Sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grilled, Smoked And Sauced</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sonoma/schellville-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.44888,38.24438,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sunflower Caffe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sunflower Caffe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sonoma, CA 95476</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7079966645" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 996-6645</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sonomasunflower.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sonomasunflower.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sunflower+Caffe%2C+421+1st+St+W%2C+Sonoma%2C+CA+95476&amp;ll=38.293441,-122.458915" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">421 1st St W<br/>Sonoma, CA 95476</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Burger, Borscht, Smoked Duck Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Located in the heart of California&#x27;s wine country, this espresso and wine bar celebrates food, wine and art. Guy enjoyed the creamy feta and tangy chimichurri in the lamb burger and he devoured the borscht made with fresh local produce. The smoked duck sandwich with melted Gruyere is also popular.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Mozz to Matzo Balls</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sonoma/sunflower-caffe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.45891,38.29344,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>W.O.W - Worth Our Weight</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">W.O.W - Worth Our Weight</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Rosa, CA 95405 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7075441200" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 544.1200</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.worthourweight.org/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.worthourweight.org</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=W.O.W+-+Worth+Our+Weight%2C+1021+Hahman+Dr%2C+Santa+Rosa%2C+CA+95405&amp;ll=38.441553,-122.685679" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1021 Hahman Dr<br/>Santa Rosa, CA 95405</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nectarine Scones, Huevos Rancheros with Pulled Pork and Pico de Gallo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The name behind W.O.W. - Worth Our Weight comes from its payment policy, as you only pay what you think is fair. Here, deserving youth receive tuition-free culinary training. Guy happily paid extra for his nectarine scones and pulled pork huevos rancheros -- he donated a pretzel car.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Funky Finds</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-rosa/wow-worth-our-weight-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.68568,38.44155,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Zoftig Eatery</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Zoftig Eatery</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Rosa, CA 95404 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.zoftigeatery.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.zoftigeatery.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Zoftig+Eatery%2C+57+Montgomery+Dr%2C+Santa+Rosa%2C+CA+95404&amp;ll=38.442186,-122.703490" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">57 Montgomery Dr<br/>Santa Rosa, CA 95404</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Korean Burrito, Maccabi Bowl</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy was shooting Guy&#x27;s Grocery Games in Santa Rosa when his buddy brought him the Korean Burrito from Zoftig Eatery. He loved it so much he needed to put the place on DDD. At Zoftig, chef and owner Matt Spector taps into his fine-dining background to spice up the menu, sourcing local but peppering the menu with international flavor. The Korean Burrito is packed with marinated, local ground beef, pickled vegetables, kimchi, fresh herbs, avocado and barbeque sauce. &quot;I&#x27;m going to drown in my own drool,&quot; Guy said before digging into it.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Big Burgers to Little Italy</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-rosa/zoftig-eatery-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.70349,38.44219,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cochon Volant BBQ Smoke House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cochon Volant BBQ Smoke House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sonoma, CA 95476</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cochonvolantbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cochonvolantbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cochon+Volant+BBQ+Smoke+House%2C+18350+Sonoma+Highway%2C+Sonoma%2C+CA+95476&amp;ll=38.311627,-122.480513" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">18350 Sonoma Highway<br/>Sonoma, CA 95476</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Chicken, WTF Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rob Larman and his wife are serving up old school barbeque in the heart of California wine country at Cochon Volant. Chef Larman puts his unique spin on fried chicken by soaking it in a sweet-and-spicy brine laced with granny smith apples and pasilla chile paste. &quot;This is a chef&#x27;s fried chicken,&quot; said guy between bites. Their other claim to fame is the towering WTF Burger. A seared beef patty is topped with 14-hour smoked brisket, smoked pork shoulder, house-cured maple bacon, a fried chipotle pork cake, melted cheddar cheese and house-made barbeque sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meaty Mashup</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sonoma/cochon-volant-bbq-smoke-house-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.48051,38.31163,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Willie Bird&#x27;s Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Willie Bird&#x27;s Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Rosa, CA 95404 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7075420861" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 542-0861</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.williebirdsrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.williebirdsrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Willie+Bird%27s+Restaurant%2C+1150+Santa+Rosa+Ave%2C+Santa+Rosa%2C+CA+95404&amp;ll=38.426003,-122.713206" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1150 Santa Rosa Ave<br/>Santa Rosa, CA 95404</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey Scallopini, Turkey-Fried Steak</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, host Guy Fieri visits Willie Bird&#x27;s Restaurant, in Santa Rosa, CA, where every dish on the menu includes turkey.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Talkin&#x27; Turkey</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-rosa/willie-birds-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.71321,38.42600,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Taqueria Molcajetes</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Taqueria Molcajetes</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Rosa, CA 95401 &middot; &#9733; 2.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-rosa/taqueria-molcajetes-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-rosa/taqueria-molcajetes-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Taqueria+Molcajetes%2C+1195+W+College+Ave%2C+Santa+Rosa%2C+CA+95401&amp;ll=38.446446,-122.740778" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1195 W College Ave<br/>Santa Rosa, CA 95401</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Molcajete Mixto, Tacos Pastor</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and owners Zacarias Martin and Dionicia Valdovinos are serving up authentic Mexican food with influences from Guadalajara and Michoacan. The food incorporates chilis and spices, like cloves, and many of their dishes make use of the use of the molcajete, the traditional Mexican mortar and pestle. The Molcajete Mixto is a mixture of steak, chicken, shrimp and vegetables served inside a smoking-hot molcajete. Guy was in heaven, calling the it, &quot;without question, one of the best Mexican food experiences I have ever had.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Regional Recipes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-rosa/taqueria-molcajetes-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.74078,38.44645,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hank&#x27;s Creekside Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hank&#x27;s Creekside Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Rosa, CA 95405 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7075758839" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 575-8839</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hankscreeksidesr.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hankscreeksidesr.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hank%27s+Creekside+Restaurant%2C+2800+4th+St.%2C+Santa+Rosa%2C+CA+95405&amp;ll=38.449293,-122.688951" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2800 4th St.<br/>Santa Rosa, CA 95405</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Corned Beef Hash, Eggs Benedict, Pancakes, Cinnamon Walnut French Toast</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">In Guy&#x27;s hometown of Santa Rosa, Calif., his favorite place to get a meal on the weekend has always been Hank&#x27;s Creekside, where owner Hank Vance grinds the whole wheat for his famous pancakes in-house. He also serves up Homemade Corned Beef Hash, Eggs Benedict and Cinnamon-Walnut French Toast.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">House Specials<br/>Triple-D Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-rosa/hanks-creekside-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.68895,38.44929,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Johnny Garlic&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Johnny Garlic&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Rosa, CA 95405 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7075286368" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 528-6368</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.johnnygarlics.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.johnnygarlics.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Johnny+Garlic%27s%2C+1460+Farmers+Ln%2C+Santa+Rosa%2C+CA+95405&amp;ll=38.434076,-122.687485" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1460 Farmers Ln<br/>Santa Rosa, CA 95405</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sashimi Won Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Only at Guy&#x27;s restaurant can you get a little Italian, Mexican, Cajun and Asian. The grilled-onion-and-garlic tortilla stack, inspired by Guy&#x27;s mom, has &amp;quot;dynamite&amp;quot; texture and flavor. Guy&#x27;s Sashimi Won Tacos dressed with eel sauce were double gold winners at the Sonoma County Harvest Fair.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Unexpected Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-rosa/johnny-garlics-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.68748,38.43408,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Simply Vietnam Express</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Simply Vietnam Express</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Rosa, CA 95403</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://simplyvietnamexpress.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">simplyvietnamexpress.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Simply+Vietnam+Express%2C+3381+Cleveland+Ave%2C+Santa+Rosa%2C+CA+95403&amp;ll=38.474235,-122.732216" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3381 Cleveland Ave<br/>Santa Rosa, CA 95403</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pho, BBQ Pork, Egg Rolls</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For authentic Vietnamese food made with love, head to this Fieri-family favorite. Chef and co-owner John Nguyen serves up the recipes that mother and co-owner Be Nguyen cooked as a chef in Vietnam.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meaty Mashup</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-rosa/simply-vietnam-express-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.73222,38.47423,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>La Texanita</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">La Texanita</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Rosa 95407 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7075251905" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">707-525-1905</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.latexanita.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.latexanita.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=La+Texanita%2C+1667+Sebastopol+Rd%2C+Santa+Rosa+95407&amp;ll=38.427847,-122.738307" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1667 Sebastopol Rd<br/>Santa Rosa 95407</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sopes, Huaraches, Ceviche &quot;Colima Style&quot;, Carne Asada Taco, Posole</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">In their hometown of Santa Rosa, Calif., Guy and his son Hunter have been longtime fans of La Texanita. Owner Alma Mendez&#x27;s carne asada taco is served on handmade tortillas, and one of Guy&#x27;s favorites is the posole - an authentic Mexican pork stew.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Best of the West Roundup<br/>Global Grub<br/>Triple D Nation: Guy&#x27;s Going Home</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-rosa/la-texanita-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.73831,38.42785,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Grand Ole BBQ y Asado</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Grand Ole BBQ y Asado</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">El Cajon 92021 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://grandolebbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">grandolebbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Grand+Ole+BBQ+y+Asado%2C+15505+Olde+Highway+80%2C+El+Cajon+92021&amp;ll=32.855459,-116.837624" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">15505 Olde Highway 80<br/>El Cajon 92021</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Tacos, El Borracho Beef Rib</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Andy Harris used to be a tour manager for rock bands, firing up his smoker for the crews. His food was so successful he decided to open a restaurant to bring Texas barbecue to San Diego. He teamed up with Chef Ami Cisneros to elevate barbecue to the next level. Don&#x27;t miss the massive El Borracho Beef Rib with house-made queso and pickled red onion relish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A World of Barbecue</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-diego/grand-ole-bbq-y-asado-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-116.83762,32.85546,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Alforon</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Alforon</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Diego, CA 92115 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.alforon.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.alforon.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Alforon%2C+5965+El+Cajon+Blvd%2C+San+Diego%2C+CA+92115&amp;ll=32.760271,-117.069102" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5965 El Cajon Blvd<br/>San Diego, CA 92115</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Soujouk Flatbread, Ouzi Lamb</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After growing up around his father&#x27;s restaurant in Lebanon, George Salameh decided to open up his own spot serving up traditional Lebanese dishes in San Diego. Locals flock here for the delicious flatbreads, like the one topped with Soujouk: a cumin-heavy blend of spices and ground meat topped with white Lebanese cheese. &quot;I could have a hundred of those,&quot; Guy said after just one bite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">International Infusion</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-diego/alforon-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.06910,32.76027,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Studio Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Studio Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Diego, CA 92123 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (11 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8587156400" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">858-715-6400</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.studiodiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.studiodiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Studio+Diner%2C+4701+Ruffin+Rd%2C+San+Diego%2C+CA+92123&amp;ll=32.825168,-117.127064" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4701 Ruffin Rd<br/>San Diego, CA 92123</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Monte Cristo (Deep-Fried Turkey, Ham and Cheese), Fish &amp; Chips</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Studio Diner carries breakfast &#x27;round the clock -- and lunch and dinner, too. Take it from Guy, who says &quot;everything is top-notch&quot; here. Owner Stu Segall insists on flying in whole belly clams and lobster from Maine, and for a real late-night treat, divulge in the deep-fried favorite: Monte Cristo.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Open 24/7<br/>Triple D Nation: Fried, Baked and Barbecued</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-diego/studio-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.12706,32.82517,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tommy&#x27;s Joynt</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tommy&#x27;s Joynt</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94109 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4157754216" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">415-775-4216</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tommysjoynt.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tommysjoynt.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tommy%27s+Joynt%2C+1101+Geary+Blvd%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94109&amp;ll=37.785462,-122.421802" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1101 Geary Blvd<br/>San Francisco, CA 94109</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Corned Beef, Roast Beef, Roasted Turkey, Lamb Shanks, Hot Sandwiches</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A neighborhood favorite for more than 60 years, Tommy&#x27;s Joynt is a German hofbrau serving fresh-carved hot meat sandwiches packed full of turkey, pastrami, brisket, ham and more. Need a recommendation? Guy says the corned beef &amp;quot;just melts in your mouth&amp;quot; and the roast beef is &amp;quot;better than prime rib.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diner&#x27;s Drive-ins and Dives: Best from the Road<br/>Long Time Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/tommys-joynt-restaurant2" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.42180,37.78546,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jo&#x27;s Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jo&#x27;s Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Diego, CA 92103 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.josdinermissionhills.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.josdinermissionhills.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jo%27s+Diner%2C+807+W+Washington+St%2C+San+Diego%2C+CA+92103&amp;ll=32.749757,-117.170644" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">807 W Washington St<br/>San Diego, CA 92103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Short Rib French Dip, French Onion Soup, Jo&#x27;s Meatloaf</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This unusual diner was once a French bistro, so when owner Ric Libiran decided to switch up the menu, he kept the upscale bistro attitude. Guy loved the Short Rib French Dip, which is served with decadent jus made from more than four hours of braising: &quot;The only problem with this is that you didn&#x27;t serve it in a kiddie pool so I can get in with the sandwich and the jus,&quot; he said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef Bonanza</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-diego/jos-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.17064,32.74976,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>El Indio Mexican Restaurant and Catering</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">El Indio Mexican Restaurant and Catering</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Diego, CA 92103 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6192990333" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(619) 299-0333</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.el-indio.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.el-indio.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=El+Indio+Mexican+Restaurant+and+Catering%2C+3695+India+St%2C+San+Diego%2C+CA+92103&amp;ll=32.742281,-117.180145" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3695 India St<br/>San Diego, CA 92103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Taquitos, Tortillas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s love of taquitos met its match at El Indio, where this &quot;home of the great taquito&quot; has been dishing tasty Mexican cuisine for more than six decades. Regulars flock for the handmade chile rellenos and, if you&#x27;re waiting in line, you might get a hot-off-the-press tortilla.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: A Family Affair<br/>Family Owned</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-diego/el-indio-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.18014,32.74228,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Front Porch</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Front Porch</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4156957800" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 695-7800</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thefrontporchsf.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thefrontporchsf.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Front+Porch%2C+65A+29th+St.%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA&amp;ll=37.743670,-122.421993" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">65A 29th St.<br/>San Francisco, CA</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dr. Pepper Short Ribs, Sweet Tea Brined Pork Chop, Vegan Scramble</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Be it the rocking chairs out front or the food, The Front Porch is the funky little neighborhood joint with plenty of charm. Guy swung by this South-meets-San Francisco joint and doled out his share of love for the &quot;killer,&quot; &quot;outstanding&quot; and &quot;succulent&quot; Dr. Pepper short ribs and shrimp and grits.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Servin&#x27; Up San Francisco<br/>West Coast Cookin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/the-front-porch-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.42199,37.74367,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tee Off Bar &amp; Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tee Off Bar &amp; Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94121 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4157525439" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 752-5439</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.teeoffbarandgrill.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.teeoffbarandgrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tee+Off+Bar+%26+Grill%2C+3129+Clement+St%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94121&amp;ll=37.781445,-122.492956" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3129 Clement St<br/>San Francisco, CA 94121</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Double Pork Chop with Apricot Relish, Paul&#x27;s Crafty Mac N Cheese with Pancetta</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy calls Tee Off Bar &amp;amp; Grill a &amp;quot;five-star dive bar.&amp;quot; The husband-and-wife-owned spot is known for high-end, homemade dishes like Double Pork Chops With Apricot Relish and Deep-Fried Sweet Corn, but it&#x27;s their signature dish, Paul&#x27;s Crafty Mac N Cheese, that has Guy promising to come back for more.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Steaks and Chops</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/tee-off-bar-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.49296,37.78145,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Crest Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Crest Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Diego, CA 92103 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6192952510" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(619) 295-2510</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.crestcafe.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.crestcafe.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Crest+Cafe%2C+425+Robinson+Ave%2C+San+Diego%2C+CA+92103&amp;ll=32.746804,-117.160758" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">425 Robinson Ave<br/>San Diego, CA 92103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Butter Burger, Crest Burger, Balboa Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Situated in one of San Diego&#x27;s 24-hour neighborhoods, Crest Cafe serves up outrageous comfort food for both morning (raspberry ricotta French toast) and night. One bite of the signature Butter burger, and Guy&#x27;s fingers weren&#x27;t dry for long: &amp;quot;This is a level of juice you haven&#x27;t seen before.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners, Drive-ins and Dives Sneak Peek<br/>Neighborhood Knockouts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-diego/crest-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.16076,32.74680,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tiger!Tiger!</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tiger!Tiger!</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Diego, CA 92104</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.tigertigertavern.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tigertigertavern.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tiger%21Tiger%21%2C+025+El+Cajon+Boulevard%2C+San+Diego%2C+CA+92104&amp;ll=32.755377,-117.136760" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">025 El Cajon Boulevard<br/>San Diego, CA 92104</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Belly Bahn Mi, Hot Mushroom Sandwich, Chicken Shawarma Sausage</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tucked away in San Diego&#x27;s North Park neighborhood is this farm-to-table pub that serves a variety of local beers and a diverse rotating menu that is designed to go with the brews. You won&#x27;t miss the meat in entrees like the Hot Mushroom Sandwich: A head of beech mushroomsis deep fried and topped with scallion aioli and a house-made pickled celery and cabbage slaw. &quot;I could eat one of these every day!&quot; Guy said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crazy Chicken and Twisted Burgers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-diego/tiger-tiger-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.13676,32.75538,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Blue Water Seafood Market &amp; Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Blue Water Seafood Market &amp; Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Diego, CA 92103 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (15 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6194970914" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(619) 497-0914</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bluewaterseafoodsandiego.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bluewaterseafoodsandiego.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Blue+Water+Seafood+Market+%26+Grill%2C+3667+India+St%2C+San+Diego%2C+CA+92103&amp;ll=32.742054,-117.179801" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3667 India St<br/>San Diego, CA 92103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sea Bass Taco, Halibut Sandwich, Cioppino, Oyster Shooters, Clam Shooters</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The two brothers that run this eatery lure in the locals with their fresh fish, which is the main ingredient in every dish they serve. Guy thought the fresh sea bass taco with lemon garlic butter was &quot;outstanding.&quot; The cioppino with wahoo, mahi mahi, ahi tuna and scallops gives a spicy kick. Other standouts include the halibut sandwich, oyster shooters and clam chowder.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Coastal Cuisine<br/>All Stacked Up<br/>Their Own Way</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-diego/blue-water-seafood-market-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.17980,32.74205,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Show Dogs Fine Sausages</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Show Dogs Fine Sausages</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94102 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4155589560" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 558-9560</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://showdogssf.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">showdogssf.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Show+Dogs+Fine+Sausages%2C+1020+Market+St%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94102&amp;ll=37.782054,-122.410932" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1020 Market St<br/>San Francisco, CA 94102</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">House Maple Pork, House Merguez, Fried Chicken Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Show Dogs has scratch-made written all over its rock-out menu. Guy&#x27;s trip included two showstoppers. First, a fried chicken sandwich that&#x27;s &amp;quot;like a Pink Floyd concert -- classic.&amp;quot; As for the headliner? Try the House Merguez, lamb sausage topped with mission-fig chutney and house-made Dijon mustard.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Neighborhood Knockouts<br/>Deep Fried All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/show-dogs-fine-sausages-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.41093,37.78205,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Senor Sisig</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Senor Sisig</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:18557474455" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1 (855) 747-4455</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.senorsisig.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.senorsisig.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Senor+Sisig%2C+Roaming+Food+Truck%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA&amp;ll=37.789018,-122.391506" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Roaming Food Truck<br/>San Francisco, CA</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Senor Sisig Tacos, Sisig Nachos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The signature sour pork Sisig tacos at Senor Sisig have been a hit with Los Angelinos, Filipino-fusion fans and Guy himself, who called these tacos &amp;quot;salty, spicy goodness.&amp;quot; If you want to ramp up the spice, make sure to grab a plate of the Buffalo wings glazed with a savory adobo-chipotle sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cannoli, Fritters and Wings</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/senor-sisig-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.39151,37.78902,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rocco&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rocco&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94103 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4155540522" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">415-554-0522</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.roccoscafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.roccoscafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rocco%27s+Cafe%2C+1131+Folsom+St%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94103&amp;ll=37.775963,-122.408454" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1131 Folsom St<br/>San Francisco, CA 94103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bolgnese, Chicken Piccata, Linguini with Clams and White Sauce</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Rocco&#x27;s, the Italian food is made from scratch, following Chef Don Dial&#x27;s grandpa&#x27;s recipes. The deep and sweet flavors in the Bolognese sauce were &amp;quot;killer&amp;quot; according to Guy. He also enjoyed the &amp;quot;super tender&amp;quot; chicken piccata. The house favorite is the linguini with clams and white sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Incredible Italian<br/>All Over the Map</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/roccos-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.40845,37.77596,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Crazee Burger</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Crazee Burger</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Diego, CA 92104 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6192826044" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(619) 282-6044</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://crazeeburger.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">crazeeburger.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Crazee+Burger%2C+4201+30th+Street%2C+San+Diego%2C+CA+92104&amp;ll=32.754227,-117.129983" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4201 30th Street<br/>San Diego, CA 92104</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ostrich, Alligator and Angus Beef Burgers, Turkey Burger with Orange Mustard Glaze</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">With a name like Crazee Burger, it&#x27;s no surprise that Chef Lothar Manz serves burgers that are far different than your typical fare, including ones made with ostrich, venison and kangaroo meat. Guy never thought he&#x27;d be eating an alligator burger, but he was sold on the first bite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Top 10 Burgers<br/>Grabbin&#x27; a Sandwich</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-diego/tiolis-crazee-burger-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.12998,32.75423,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pizzeria Luigi</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pizzeria Luigi</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Diego 92102 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6192333309" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">619-233-3309</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pizzerialuigi.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pizzerialuigi.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pizzeria+Luigi%2C+1137+25th+St%2C+San+Diego+92102&amp;ll=32.717641,-117.140077" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1137 25th St<br/>San Diego 92102</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Donatello, El Diablo, Capone Meat-Lover Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">It only took one bite of Pizzeria Luigi&#x27;s Capone meat-lover pizza for Guy to instantly become a fan (he has since deemed it his favorite West Coast pizza). The Donatello pie delivers equally delicious flavors with sweet mozzarella, garlic, spinach and creamy ricotta dollops all over.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Tastier at Home<br/>All San Diego, All the Time<br/>Best of Pizza<br/>Real Deal Italian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-diego/pizzeria-luigi-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.14008,32.71764,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Radio Africa &amp; Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Radio Africa &amp; Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94124 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4154202486" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">415-420-2486</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.radioafricakitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.radioafricakitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Radio+Africa+%26+Kitchen%2C+4800+3rd+Street%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94124&amp;ll=37.734755,-122.391082" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4800 3rd Street<br/>San Francisco, CA 94124</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Jambalaya, Seared Ahi Tuna, Saffron Prawns</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef-Owner Eskender Aseged left quite the impression when he appeared on Guy&#x27;s Grocery Games - so much so that Guy made sure to check out Aseged&#x27;s Ethiopian joint when he was in San Francisco. Follow Guy&#x27;s lead and order the seared tuna. It&#x27;s topped with chermoula, a Moroccan cilantro and parsley sauce, and served over a bed of sauteed vegetables. &quot;I don&#x27;t want this dish to end,&quot; Guy exclaimed.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Asia, Africa and India</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/radio-africa-and-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.39108,37.73476,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nopalito</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nopalito</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94122 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4152339966" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 233-9966</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.nopalitosf.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.nopalitosf.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nopalito%2C+1224+9th+Ave%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94122&amp;ll=37.765712,-122.466433" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1224 9th Ave<br/>San Francisco, CA 94122</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Torta de Chilorio</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Mexican joint is &amp;quot;everything but boring,&amp;quot; Guy says. Everything is local and sustainable and completely homemade - right down to the tortillas. But the Torta de Chilorio, made with hot pork chorizo, queso fresco and bread soaked in adobo sauce? It&#x27;s unlike any sandwich he&#x27;s ever had.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Global Flavor Faves<br/>From the Heart</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/nopalito-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.46643,37.76571,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>OB Noodle House</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">OB Noodle House</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Diego, CA 92107 &middot; &#9733; 4.6 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6194506868" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(619) 450-6868</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://obnoodlehouse.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">obnoodlehouse.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=OB+Noodle+House%2C+2218+Cable+St%2C+San+Diego%2C+CA+92107&amp;ll=32.751332,-117.244829" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2218 Cable St<br/>San Diego, CA 92107</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pho, Tofu Lettuce Wraps</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When you visit OB Noodle House, make sure to pronounce the signature dish, Pho, correctly. It&#x27;s &quot;fuh&quot; and not &quot;fo.&quot; You&#x27;ll be glad you did, because the expert blend of spices and meats makes for one unbelievable flavor. As Guy says, &quot;You&#x27;re going to have a pretty tough time finding it this good.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Global Flavor Faves<br/>All San Diego, All the Time<br/>Triple D Nation: Flavortown Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-diego/ob-noodle-house-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.24483,32.75133,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hob Nob Hill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hob Nob Hill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Diego, CA 92101 &middot; &#9733; 2.6 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6192398176" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(619) 239-8176</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hobnobhill.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hobnobhill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hob+Nob+Hill%2C+2271+First+Ave.%2C+San+Diego%2C+CA+92101&amp;ll=32.729191,-117.163779" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2271 First Ave.<br/>San Diego, CA 92101</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken and Dumplings, Roast Tom Turkey</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">San Diegoans know Hob Nob Hill as a historical landmark. The menu never changes and that&#x27;s the way they like it. On DDD, Guy raved about the fall-apart corned beef. But the comforting chicken and dumplings were the real deal - he called them &amp;quot;the definition of chicken and dumplings.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Stacked Up<br/>Just Like Yesterday</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-diego/hob-nob-hill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.16378,32.72919,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pazzo</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pazzo</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Carlos, CA 94070 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6505911075" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(650) 591-1075</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pazzosancarlos.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pazzosancarlos.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pazzo%2C+1179+Laurel+St.%2C+San+Carlos%2C+CA+94070&amp;ll=37.499103,-122.252169" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1179 Laurel St.<br/>San Carlos, CA 94070</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ricotta Gnocchi with Artichoke, Lemon and Mint</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This San Carlos destination puts its spin on classic Italian food with wood-fired pizzas and handmade pastas. The restaurant makes a knockout Ricotta Gnocchi with artichoke, lemon and mint that&#x27;s absolutelyworth your time and taste buds.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Italian, Hawaiian and Colombian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-carlos/pazzo" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.25217,37.49910,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Refuge</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Refuge</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Carlos, CA &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6505989813" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(650) 598-9813</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.refugesc.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.refugesc.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Refuge%2C+963+Laurel+St%2C+San+Carlos%2C+CA&amp;ll=37.501880,-122.255286" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">963 Laurel St<br/>San Carlos, CA</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pastrami Burger, Belgian Beer, Ribeye Cheesesteaks</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Refuge&#x27;s pastrami sandwich knows no bounds, and for this upscale Bay Area pub, it rivals East Coast legends, as in &amp;quot;OMG&amp;quot; delicious. Hardcore pastrami fans must try the pastrami burger. After one bite, Guy admitted: &amp;quot;You could be a hardcore New Yorker, but nothing will prepare you for that.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Super Sandwiches<br/>Meat Lover&#x27;s Paradise</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-carlos/refuge-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.25529,37.50188,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Patrick&#x27;s Roadhouse</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Patrick&#x27;s Roadhouse</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Monica, CA 90402 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3104594544" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(310) 459-4544</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.patricksroadhouse.info/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.patricksroadhouse.info</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Patrick%27s+Roadhouse%2C+106+Entrada+Dr.%2C+Santa+Monica%2C+CA+90402&amp;ll=34.027876,-118.518413" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">106 Entrada Dr.<br/>Santa Monica, CA 90402</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Governator&#x27;s Special Breakfast</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">As a Santa Monica institution with an unmistakable neon green exterior, Patrick&#x27;s Roadhouse has been specializing in eclectic burgers for more than 35 years. On Triple D, Guy becomes a fan of The Governator egg dish but for something more upscale, try the Rockefeller burger with caviar spread.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Blue Plate Special</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-monica/patricks-roadhouse-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.51841,34.02788,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Savoy Cafe &amp; Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Savoy Cafe &amp; Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Barbara, CA 93101 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8059626611" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(805) 962-6611</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://thesavoycafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">thesavoycafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Savoy+Cafe+%26+Deli%2C+24+W+Figueroa+St%2C+Santa+Barbara%2C+CA+93101&amp;ll=34.421956,-119.704091" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">24 W Figueroa St<br/>Santa Barbara, CA 93101</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Turkey Pasilla Fritters, Chicken Marsala</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Paul and Kathy Shields are cooking and baking up some fresh and delicious meals. Guy thought the turkey pasilla fritters made with free-range turkey meat and served with a side of quinoa mango salad were outstanding. Locals favor the chicken Marsala.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Outside the Box</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-barbara/savoy-cafeacute-deli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.70409,34.42196,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mac&#x27;s Fish &amp; Chip Shop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mac&#x27;s Fish &amp; Chip Shop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Barbara, CA 93101 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8058971160" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(805) 897-1160</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.macssb.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.macssb.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mac%27s+Fish+%26+Chip+Shop%2C+503+State+St%2C+Santa+Barbara%2C+CA+93101&amp;ll=34.416792,-119.695894" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">503 State St<br/>Santa Barbara, CA 93101</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fish and Chips, Haggis Balls</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A British couple visits California and what do they decide to do? Start a British comfort food shop! Guy and his son loved these &quot;real deal&quot; fish and chips made with wild Alaskan cod. The bangers with a side of mash also garnered praise. Feeling brave? Try the fried haggis balls.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Global Traditions<br/>Deep Fried All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-barbara/macs-fish-chip-shop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.69589,34.41679,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Lito&#x27;s Mexican Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Lito&#x27;s Mexican Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Barbara, CA 93103 &middot; &#9733; 3.9 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8059621559" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(805) 962-1559</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.litosmexfoodsb.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.litosmexfoodsb.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Lito%27s+Mexican+Restaurant%2C+514+E+Haley+St%2C+Santa+Barbara%2C+CA+93103&amp;ll=34.422395,-119.689288" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">514 E Haley St<br/>Santa Barbara, CA 93103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Carnitas, Pazole</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The authentic Mexican recipes make the food at this family-operated restaurant irresistible. Guy liked the juicy flavor of the carnitas, which can be ordered in a taco, burrito, enchilada or torta. The pork stew pozole also impressed Guy; he recommends topping it with cabbage, cilantro and lime.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mex to the Max<br/>Scratch Made Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-barbara/litos-mexican-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.68929,34.42240,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Q Restaurant and Wine Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Q Restaurant and Wine Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94118 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4157522298" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">415-752-2298</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.qrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.qrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Q+Restaurant+and+Wine+Bar%2C+225+Clement+Street%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94118&amp;ll=37.782882,-122.461700" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">225 Clement Street<br/>San Francisco, CA 94118</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Duck Confit, Smoked Pork, Carne Adovada</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A neighborhood diner in the Richmond district of San Francisco, Q Restaurant specializes in &quot;funky, American comfort.&quot; Try the Pulled Pork or Funky American-Style Duck Confit, made over 16 days, finished in the deep fryer and served with polenta and asparagus. Guy&#x27;s take: &quot;So worth it!&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">PIZZA, PORK AND PAPRIKASH</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/q-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.46170,37.78288,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pier 23 Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pier 23 Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco 94111 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4153625125" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 362-5125</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pier23cafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pier23cafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pier+23+Cafe%2C+Pier+23%2C+San+Francisco+94111&amp;ll=37.741376,-122.376027" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Pier 23<br/>San Francisco 94111</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Oven Roasted Whole Dungeness Crab, Fish Tacos, Duck Poppers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy says if you&#x27;re looking for live music, fresh delicious seafood, a huge patio and good times, you&#x27;ve got to head to Pier 23. Many come for the legendary NorCal oven-roasted Dungeness crab, but if you have room for more, try the duck jalapeno poppers.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Sendin&#x27; the Surf &amp; Turf<br/>Fresh And Funky</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/pier-23-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.37603,37.74138,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pica Pica Arepa Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pica Pica Arepa Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94103 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4154005453" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 400-5453</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.picapica.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.picapica.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pica+Pica+Arepa+Kitchen%2C+401+Valencia+St%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94103&amp;ll=37.766451,-122.421683" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">401 Valencia St<br/>San Francisco, CA 94103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Arepa Beef Pabellon</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Triple D, Guy called the arepas at Pica Pica a &amp;quot;corn pocket wonder.&amp;quot; The gluten-free tortilla acts as the container for dozens of Pica Pica&#x27;s dishes. Guy&#x27;s pick? The Arepa Beef Pabellon stuffed with shredded beef, sweet plantains and a black bean spread. Vegetarians, note: Tofu is available here.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">That&#x27;s Fresh<br/>Super Sandwiches</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/pica-pica-arepa-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.42168,37.76645,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>KoJa Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">KoJa Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA &middot; &#9733; 2.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4159927394" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 992-7394</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.facebook.com/KoJaKitchen" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/KoJaKitchen</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=KoJa+Kitchen%2C+Roaming+Food+Truck%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA&amp;ll=37.774929,-122.419416" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Roaming Food Truck<br/>San Francisco, CA</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Short Rib Koja (Short Rib Between Two Rice Cakes), Short Rib Kamikaze Combo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">KoJa Kitchen not only redefines food truck cuisine, but owner and Chef Alan Tsai is reinventing traditional Korean-Japanese eats too. KoJa short ribs are kiwi-marinated, then placed between two rice patties. Guy couldn&#x27;t believe his taste buds. This is &amp;quot;Asian food at its best,&amp;quot; he said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Servin&#x27; Up San Francisco</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/koja-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.41942,37.77493,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>HRD Coffee Shop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">HRD Coffee Shop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94107 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4155432355" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 543-2355</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hrdcoffeeshop.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hrdcoffeeshop.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=HRD+Coffee+Shop%2C+521+%23A+3rd+St%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94107&amp;ll=37.781202,-122.395225" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">521 #A 3rd St<br/>San Francisco, CA 94107</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Korean Loco Moco</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">San Francisco locals swear by HRD for its Korean-style breakfasts. On Triple D, Guy hunkered down on the huge spicy pork and kimchee breakfast burrito. Want another pick-me-up? Try the Korean Loco Moco made with a hodgepodge of kimchee-fried rice and burger patty all atop sunny-side eggs.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You Can Only Get It Here<br/>Amazing Asian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/hrd-coffee-shop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.39523,37.78120,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>El Nuevo Frutilandia</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">El Nuevo Frutilandia</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94110 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4156482958" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">415-648-2958</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.frutilandiasf.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.frutilandiasf.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=El+Nuevo+Frutilandia%2C+3077+24th+St%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94110&amp;ll=37.752433,-122.413454" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3077 24th St<br/>San Francisco, CA 94110</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ropa Vieja, Mofongo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This classic spot in the Mission District dishes up Puerto Rican and Cuban favorites. Guy was impressed by Chef-Owner Rafael Frias&#x27; version of ropa vieja, which is made from a recipe passed down by the restaurant&#x27;s previous owners. &quot;I like that there&#x27;s real texture to the meat,&quot; Guy declared of the dish, which features tender, shredded chuck roll that&#x27;s sauteed with peppers, onions and tomatoes.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">International Appeal</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/el-nuevo-frutilandia-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.41345,37.75243,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Norton&#x27;s Pastrami and Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Norton&#x27;s Pastrami and Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Barbara, CA 93103 &middot; &#9733; 4.6 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8059653210" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(805) 965-3210</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.nortonspastrami.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.nortonspastrami.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Norton%27s+Pastrami+and+Deli%2C+18+W+Figueroa+St%2C+Santa+Barbara%2C+CA+93103&amp;ll=34.422006,-119.703820" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">18 W Figueroa St<br/>Santa Barbara, CA 93103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pastrami Dog, PLT</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Norton&#x27;s is bringing East Coast pastrami to the West Coast, and it&#x27;s being cooked six different ways. Guy could barely handle the pastrami dog --- a quarter-pound hot dog topped with pastrami and sauerkraut. The PLT with crispy pastrami, lettuce and tomato is a tasty spin on an old classic.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old Faves, New Craves<br/>All Stacked Up</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-barbara/nortons-pastrami-deli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.70382,34.42201,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Gaffey Street Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Gaffey Street Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Pedro, CA 90731 &middot; &#9733; 2.8 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3105486964" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">310-548-6964</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.gaffeystreetdiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.gaffeystreetdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Gaffey+Street+Diner%2C+247+N.+Gaffey+St.%2C+San+Pedro%2C+CA+90731&amp;ll=33.745010,-118.292661" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">247 N. Gaffey St.<br/>San Pedro, CA 90731</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">&quot;Great for What Ails You&quot; John Wayne Breakfast, Omelet, Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Drive by this joint and it&#x27;d be a mistake, says Guy on Triple D. This husband-and-wife duo defies expectations by making everything by hand, from orange juice to biscuits. But the John Wayne &amp;quot;hangover&amp;quot; dish is legendary: eggs, home fries, sausage wagons and cheese all covered in Spanish sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Breakfast</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-pedro/gaffey-street-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.29266,33.74501,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Miller&#x27;s East Coast Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Miller&#x27;s East Coast Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4155633542" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">415-563-3542</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.millerseastcoastdeli.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.millerseastcoastdeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Miller%27s+East+Coast+Deli%2C+1725+Polk+St%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA&amp;ll=37.792773,-122.421398" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1725 Polk St<br/>San Francisco, CA</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Noodle with Mazo Ball Soup, Reuben, Stuffed Derma, Potato Latke Delight</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Miller&#x27;s East Coast Deli may be in San Francisco, but that doesn&#x27;t mean it can&#x27;t dish out one hearty bowl of matzo ball soup. Add to that, &amp;quot;nothing&#x27;s been lost in translation&amp;quot; from east to west, as Guy dove right into the potato latkes with uber tender cuts of corned beef and pastrami.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Servin&#x27; Up San Francisco<br/>Holiday Hoopla</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/millers-east-coast-deli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.42140,37.79277,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dottie&#x27;s True Blue Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dottie&#x27;s True Blue Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94103 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4158852767" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 885-2767</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://dotties.biz/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">dotties.biz</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dottie%27s+True+Blue+Cafe%2C+28+6th+St%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94103&amp;ll=37.781709,-122.410029" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">28 6th St<br/>San Francisco, CA 94103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cornbread and Jalapeno Jelly, Buttermilk Dill Bread, Veggie Chili</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The food at this cafe is so delicious that patrons are willing to wait hours for one of the 40 seats inside. Guy thought that the cornbread and jalapeno jelly made a perfect combo and he appreciated the flavorful buttermilk dill bread. The veggie chili was appreciated for its complex flavors.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort Cookin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/dotties-true-blue-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.41003,37.78171,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>CatHead&#x27;s BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">CatHead&#x27;s BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94103 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4158614242" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">415-861-4242</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://catheadsbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">catheadsbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=CatHead%27s+BBQ%2C+1665+Folsom+St%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94103&amp;ll=37.770075,-122.415187" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1665 Folsom St<br/>San Francisco, CA 94103</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulled Pork Biscuit Sandwich, Smoked Lamb Shoulder</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Co-owners Pamela Schafer and Richard Park are bringing the best flavors of down-home barbecue to San Francisco at CatHead&#x27;s BBQ. This joint takes its name from the &quot;cathead&quot; biscuit - a Southern staple that&#x27;s the size of a cat&#x27;s head. It&#x27;s also one of the rare spots in the city with a barbecue pit. As such, Guy had to try the classic pulled pork biscuit sandwich served with a housemade mustard slaw and a side of pickles.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Great Gear</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/catheads-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.41519,37.77008,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Broken Record</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Broken Record</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94112 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4159631713" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 963-1713</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.brokenrecordsanfrancisco.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.brokenrecordsanfrancisco.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Broken+Record%2C+1166+Geneva+Ave%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94112&amp;ll=37.714326,-122.436926" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1166 Geneva Ave<br/>San Francisco, CA 94112</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roasted Mushroom Polenta</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Take a drive to the southern tip of San Francisco and you&#x27;ll be in good company at the Broken Record. Guy&#x27;s Triple D crew marveled at the more than 300 kinds of whiskey. But Guy got a real kick out of the food, including the creamiest roasted mushroom polenta. The real kicker -- it&#x27;s only $8.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern Flavor<br/>Late Night Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/broken-record-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.43693,37.71433,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Joe&#x27;s Cable Car</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Joe&#x27;s Cable Car</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94112 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4153346699" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 334-6699</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.joescablecar.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.joescablecar.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Joe%27s+Cable+Car%2C+4320+Mission+St.%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94112&amp;ll=37.728461,-122.431903" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4320 Mission St.<br/>San Francisco, CA 94112</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Patty Melt, &quot;The Joe&quot; Burger, &quot;The Cable&quot; Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A burger to us is fresh ground steak to Joe. At Joe&#x27;s Cable Car, the meat is the star (that and his neon-orama dining room). Fresh chuck is ground daily to attain griddle glory as a patty melt or burger (favorite topper: avocado). Guy&#x27;s verdict? Big. Juicy. Bananas (contains no actual banana).</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Rings and Fries</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/joes-cable-car-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.43190,37.72846,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Grubstake Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Grubstake Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">San Francisco, CA 94109 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4156738268" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 673-8268</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sfgrubstake.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sfgrubstake.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Grubstake+Diner%2C+1525+Pine+St.%2C+San+Francisco%2C+CA+94109&amp;ll=37.789363,-122.420842" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1525 Pine St.<br/>San Francisco, CA 94109</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Chops, Kale Soup, Linguica, Omelettes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy Fieri, host of Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, visits the Grubstake Diner, an old-time American restaurant in downtown San Francisco, that serves up Portuguese specialties.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">One of a Kind</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/san-francisco/grubstake-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.42084,37.78936,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Santa Cruz Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Santa Cruz Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Cruz, CA 95060 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8314267151" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">831-426-7151</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.santacruzdiner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.santacruzdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Santa+Cruz+Diner%2C+909+Ocean+St%2C+Santa+Cruz%2C+CA+95060&amp;ll=36.980395,-122.021892" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">909 Ocean St<br/>Santa Cruz, CA 95060</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Reubens, Pork and Shrimp Spring Rolls, Shrimp and Salmon Cakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Classic diner fare meets Vietnamese comfort food at this homey California spot. The family-friendly diner serves everything from eggs Benedict to spicy Thai coconut soup, and Guy says the pho (a rice noodle soup with thinly sliced beef and broth) is &amp;quot;crazy good.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners Times Three</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-cruz/santa-cruz-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.02189,36.98040,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Aldo&#x27;s Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Aldo&#x27;s Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Santa Cruz, CA 95062 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8314263736" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(831) 426-3736</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.aldos-cruz.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.aldos-cruz.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Aldo%27s+Restaurant%2C+616+Atlantic+Ave%2C+Santa+Cruz%2C+CA+95062&amp;ll=36.963970,-122.002798" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">616 Atlantic Ave<br/>Santa Cruz, CA 95062</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cioppino, Fried Calamari, Ravioli</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Aldo&#x27;s Restaurant is the ideal location for fresh seafood dining. Situated on the scenic Santa Cruz harbor, Aldo&#x27;s brings in fresh seafood daily, everything from calamari to salmon. Guy devoured the cioppino. As for the handmade ravioli - he&#x27;d order those by the thousands.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Twists And Traditions</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/santa-cruz/aldos-harbor-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.00280,36.96397,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ramona Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ramona Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ramona, CA 92605 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7607898656" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(760) 789-8656</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/ramona/ramona-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/ramona/ramona-cafe-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ramona+Cafe%2C+628+Main+St.%2C+Ramona%2C+CA+92605&amp;ll=33.044894,-116.862647" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">628 Main St.<br/>Ramona, CA 92605</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Cordon Bleu, Cinnamon Rolls</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This small-town cafe doesn&#x27;t know the meaning of small. Guy learned that all the dishes at Ramona&#x27;s are standout winners, handmade by owner Sonja Vanderveen. He loved the deep-fried cordon bleu with melted Swiss. To top it off, Sonja&#x27;s giant pecan cinnamon rolls could barely fit in his mouth.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Totally Fried</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/ramona/ramona-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-116.86265,33.04489,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oxnard 93030 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8053858980" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(805) 385-8980</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/oxnard/the-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/oxnard/the-kitchen-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Kitchen%2C+529+S+A+St%2C+Oxnard+93030&amp;ll=34.197072,-119.179015" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">529 S A St<br/>Oxnard 93030</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lamb Burger, Meatloaf Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this multitasking diner, owner Cathie Moreno is cooking, baking and brewing. Guy loved the hint of mint from the lamb burger paired with an acidic red pepper relish inside a fresh homemade bun. Locals recommend ordering the meatloaf sandwich and enjoying a nice cold beer with it.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Multitaskers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/oxnard/the-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.17901,34.19707,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Don Chow Tacos</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Don Chow Tacos</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90017 &middot; &#9733; 2.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.donchowtacos.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.donchowtacos.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Don+Chow+Tacos%2C+Roaming+Food+Truck%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90017&amp;ll=34.054380,-118.267280" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Roaming Food Truck<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90017</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ Chinese Pork Taco, Kung Pao Chicken Chimales (Chinese-Mexican Tamales)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Don Chow Tacos Los Angeles food truck fuses Chinese and Mexican cuisines to create such unique dishes as Chimales (Chinese-Mexican tamales, meat-stuffed masa wrapped in corn husks and steamed). Also worth a try: Kung Pao Chicken Tacos and the sweet &#x27;n&#x27; smoky Chinese BBQ Pork Burritos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Food Truckapalooza<br/>Fast Food Their Way</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/don-chow-tacos-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.26728,34.05438,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Food Fix Truck</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Food Fix Truck</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Modesto, CA 95350 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://foodfixtruck.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">foodfixtruck.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Food+Fix+Truck%2C+Roaming+Food+Truck%2C+Modesto%2C+CA+95350&amp;ll=37.669746,-120.999103" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Roaming Food Truck<br/>Modesto, CA 95350</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Root Beer Pulled Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This family-run food truck is all about community, from its origins as a crowd-funded project on Kickstarter to its use of regionally sourced ingredients. And the locals are certainly lining up for the creative comfort foods cranked out here, as Guy found out when he swung by to chow down on the Root Beer Pulled Pork.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Succulent Sandwiches</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/modesto/food-fix-truck" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-120.99910,37.66975,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Commonwealth</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Commonwealth</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Modesto, CA 95354 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2092487451" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">209-248-7451</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.commonwealthmodesto.com/#about" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.commonwealthmodesto.com/#about</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Commonwealth%2C+1022+11th+St%2C+Modesto%2C+CA+95354&amp;ll=37.641942,-120.999833" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1022 11th St<br/>Modesto, CA 95354</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Craft Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The allure of craft brews is what first drew many locals to Commonwealth, but it&#x27;s the food that keeps them coming back. The craft tacos are one crowd-pleaser that Guy just had to try. &quot;There&#x27;s so much flavor in each one,&quot; he declared of the trio that included a banh mi taco layered with cilantro, jalapenos, pickled carrots, red radish and pulled pork tossed with a housemade umami sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked, Grilled and Fried</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/modesto/commonwealth-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-120.99983,37.64194,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bauer&#x27;s 66 1/2</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bauer&#x27;s 66 1/2</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Modesto, CA 95350</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2099851199" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">209-985-1199</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Fan-of-Bauers-66-12-Skillet-Grill-118063374879974/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/Fan-of-Bauers-66-12-Skillet-Grill-118063374879974</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bauer%27s+66+1%2F2%2C+1700+McHenry+Ave%2C+Modesto%2C+CA+95350&amp;ll=37.669562,-120.992243" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1700 McHenry Ave<br/>Modesto, CA 95350</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Octavian Sandwich, Lamburgerini (Lamb Burger)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this cool little spot in Modesto, Chef-Owner Tye Bauer serves up a tantalizing array of dishes inspired by his Portuguese and German ancestries. Guy headed here on Diners Drive-Ins and Drives to chow down on the three-meat Octavian Sandwich (think Portuguese sausage, pulled pork and Portuguese braised beef) and a lamb burger topped with mushrooms, bacon and gorgonzola.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hot Meat and Cool Veg</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/modesto/bauers-66-1-2-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-120.99224,37.66956,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Park&#x27;s Finest</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Park&#x27;s Finest</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90026 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2134812800" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(213) 481-2800</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://theparksfinest.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">theparksfinest.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Park%27s+Finest%2C+1267+W+Temple+St%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90026&amp;ll=34.066441,-118.254039" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1267 W Temple St<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90026</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ann&#x27;s Cornbread Bibingka</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">What started as a catering company soon became a hidden hot spot for Los Angelinos looking for tried-and-true Filipino comfort food. Guy loved the barbecue beef short ribs paired with a sharp crema horseradish sauce. And diners better watch out -- the addictive Bibingka cornbread is a real winner.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">L.A. Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/the-parks-finest-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.25404,34.06644,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Chichen Itza Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Chichen Itza Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90007</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2137411075" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">213-741-1075</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.chichenitzarestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.chichenitzarestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Chichen+Itza+Restaurant%2C+3655+S+Grand+Ave%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90007&amp;ll=34.017316,-118.278304" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3655 S Grand Ave<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90007</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Longaniza Asada, Cochinita Pibil</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Serving the cuisine of Yucatan, Mexico, this counter-service Downtown restaurant is popular for its Cochinita Pibil - pork cooked in banana leaves.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mex to the Max<br/>Griddles and Vittles</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/chichen-itza-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.27830,34.01732,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fat Sal&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fat Sal&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90024 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8556824373" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(855) 682-4373</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.fatsalsdeli.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fatsalsdeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fat+Sal%27s%2C+972+Gayley+Ave%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90024&amp;ll=34.062529,-118.448030" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">972 Gayley Ave<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90024</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fat Jerry, Meat Luv&#x27;rz Pizza Roll, Big Fat Fatty</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fat Sal&#x27;s is everything health-conscious LA is not and deliciously so. Guy gets his hands on a Fat Jerry sandwich stacked with cheese steak, chicken fingers, mozzarella sticks, bacon, fried eggs and fries. He also indulges in the Meat Luv&#x27;rz pizza roll stuffed with beef, pepperoni and sausages. Jeff and Audrey Dunham were in to taste their 13-pound creation: Big Fat Fatty. This mega sandwich features five burger patties, five fried eggs, ribeye, pastrami and bacon topped with a basket of fries, onion rings, chicken fingers and mozzarella sticks.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ultimate Bacon Fest<br/>Righteous Bites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/fat-sal-s" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.44803,34.06253,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Azla Ethiopian Vegan</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Azla Ethiopian Vegan</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90007 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2137457455" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">213-745-7455</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://azlavegan.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">azlavegan.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Azla+Ethiopian+Vegan%2C+3655+S+Grand+Ave%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90007&amp;ll=34.017356,-118.278405" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3655 S Grand Ave<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90007</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Misir Wot, Injera</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy called Azla and Nesanet Abegaze &quot;culinary ambassadors,&quot; as they serve a meatless take on traditional Ethiopian cuisine at their restaurant. The mother-daughter team&#x27;s standouts include the misir wot, a flavorful stew made from red lentils cooked down with onions, tomatoes and pungent spices sourced straight from Ethiopia. &quot;There&#x27;s a ton of flavor in that,&quot; Guy declared after dipping into the dish with a piece of injera, the spongy flatbread that&#x27;s traditionally used for scooping up food.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cosmopolitan Comfort</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/azla-ethiopian-vegan-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.27840,34.01736,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Polka Restaurant &amp; Catering</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Polka Restaurant &amp; Catering</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90065</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3232557887" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">323-255-7887</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.polkarestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.polkarestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Polka+Restaurant+%26+Catering%2C+4112+Verdugo+Rd%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90065&amp;ll=34.125447,-118.231575" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4112 Verdugo Rd<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90065</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pierogis, Stuffed Cabbage, Goulash, Naleiniki (Crepes)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Katherine Dabrowski grew up helping her mom in the kitchen and now she is sharing her Polish dishes at Polka. Guy devoured the pierogi done three ways - with meat, sauerkraut and potato. The goulash impressed with its tender meat and gnocchi. For dessert, try the creamy filled crepes.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mama&#x27;s Cookin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/polka-restaurant-catering-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.23158,34.12545,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Horse Thief BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Horse Thief BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90013</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2136250341" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">213-625-0341</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.horsethiefbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.horsethiefbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Horse+Thief+BBQ%2C+324+S.+Hill+St%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90013&amp;ll=34.051206,-118.249386" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">324 S. Hill St<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90013</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Chicken Sandwich, Pork Belly</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy said the bark is worth every bite at this barbeque joint in Los Angeles. The fried chicken sandwich was so good Guy predicted a line down the street for it and jokingly dubbed the smoked pork belly his favorite salad.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Barbecue, Batter and Beer Can Chicken</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/Horse-thief-bbq-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.24939,34.05121,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Harold &amp; Belle&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Harold &amp; Belle&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90018 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3237359023" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">323-735-9023</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.haroldandbellesrestaurant.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.haroldandbellesrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Harold+%26+Belle%27s%2C+2920+West+Jefferson+Boulevard%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90018&amp;ll=34.025450,-118.327922" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2920 West Jefferson Boulevard<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90018</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">File Gumbo, Shrimp &amp; Crawfish Etouffee</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Opened in 1969 by a pair of Louisiana transplants, this joint is still serving classic Creole dishes. Try the classic standout gumbo, or opt for the crawfish etouffee. This dish starts with an old-school roux made from shrimp stock and a mix of tomato and cream of mushroom soups, which surprised Guy. Loaded with spices and tender crawfish tails, the resulting etouffee is &quot;deep and rich and creamy,&quot; Guy says.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Creole, Cold Cuts and Crepes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/harold-and-belles-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.32792,34.02545,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Loleta Cheese Factory</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Loleta Cheese Factory</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Loleta, CA 95551 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7077335470" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 733-5470</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.loletacheese.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.loletacheese.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Loleta+Cheese+Factory%2C+252+Loleta+Dr%2C+Loleta%2C+CA+95551&amp;ll=40.641043,-124.223666" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">252 Loleta Dr<br/>Loleta, CA 95551</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spicy Habanero Jack.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When a student of former high school teacher Bob Laffranchi asked him how cheese is made, Bob decided to find out. Since then, the self-taught cheese maker has been running Loleta Cheese Factory, which makes 5,000 pounds of cheese daily using local milk. Guy&#x27;s favorite? The spicy habanero Jack.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s Hometown Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/loleta/loleta-cheese-factory" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-124.22367,40.64104,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jimtown Store</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jimtown Store</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Healdsburg, CA 95448 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7074331212" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 433-1212</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://jimtown.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">jimtown.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jimtown+Store%2C+6706+Highway+128%2C+Healdsburg%2C+CA+95448&amp;ll=38.668900,-122.817485" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6706 Highway 128<br/>Healdsburg, CA 95448</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jimtown Chain Gang Chili</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The cornucopia of spices used for the luscious brisket sandwich at Jimtown Store goes hand in hand with the bounty of fresh vegetables and herbs found in owner Carrie Brown&#x27;s garden. The nationally recognized country store was also a DDD favorite, as Guy loved the thick &amp;quot;standup&amp;quot; Chain Gang Chili.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Porktastic</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/healdsburg/jimtown-store-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.81749,38.66890,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Squeeze Burger (formerly Squeeze Inn)</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Squeeze Burger (formerly Squeeze Inn)</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sacramento, CA 95820 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9163868599" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">916-386-8599</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sacramento/squeeze-inn-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sacramento/squeeze-inn-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Squeeze+Burger+%28formerly+Squeeze+Inn%29%2C+5301+Power+Inn+Rd%2C+Sacramento%2C+CA+95820&amp;ll=38.526736,-121.408555" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5301 Power Inn Rd<br/>Sacramento, CA 95820</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Squeezeburger with Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This tiny burger joint is short on space, but customers pack in for favorites like the Squeezeburger with Cheese. A 1/3-pound patty is heaped with so much cheese (more than half a pound) that the topping forms a crisp skirt of sorts after a turn on the flat top. &quot;That thing is money,&quot; said Guy of the cheese-blanketed burger, which comes topped with dill pickles, tomatoes, mustard and mayonnaise.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers<br/>Knockout Burger Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sacramento/squeeze-inn-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.40856,38.52674,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Golden Bear</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Golden Bear</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sacramento, CA 95816 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9164412242" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(916) 441-2242</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.goldenbear916.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.goldenbear916.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Golden+Bear%2C+2326+K+St%2C+Sacramento%2C+CA+95816&amp;ll=38.574029,-121.475488" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2326 K St<br/>Sacramento, CA 95816</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sausage and &#x27;Slaw Pizza, Banh Mi Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Golden Bear quickly became a Sacramento, Calif., favorite and Guy couldn&#x27;t agree more. His visit changed his attitude about slaw, as he called The Sausage and &#x27;Slaw pizza with homemade sausage and smoked slaw &quot;out of control.&quot; The taco with citrus-achiote chicken&#x27;s also a flavor town winner.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Pork to Tofu<br/>West Coast Cookin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sacramento/the-golden-bear-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.47549,38.57403,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jamie&#x27;s Broadway Grille</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jamie&#x27;s Broadway Grille</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sacramento, CA 95818 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9164424044" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(916) 442-4044</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.jamiesbroadwaygrille.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jamiesbroadwaygrille.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jamie%27s+Broadway+Grille%2C+427+Broadway%2C+Sacramento%2C+CA+95818&amp;ll=38.565892,-121.507674" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">427 Broadway<br/>Sacramento, CA 95818</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Garlic Steak Sandwich (Filet Mignon Sandwich), Smoked Prime Rib</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The only way you&#x27;ll find this unmarked dive bar is if you know to look for its green awning. The filet mignon sandwich with toasted garlic bread left Guy speechless. He also appreciated the melt-in-your-mouth smoked prime rib with au jus. Be sure to check out their rotating daily specials too.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Funky Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sacramento/jamies-bar-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.50767,38.56589,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Johnny Garlic&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Johnny Garlic&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Roseville 95678</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9167892000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">916-789-2000</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/roseville/johnny-garlics-roseville-ca-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/roseville/johnny-garlics-roseville-ca-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Johnny+Garlic%27s%2C+10505+Fairway+Dr.%2C+Roseville+95678&amp;ll=38.792415,-121.291136" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">10505 Fairway Dr.<br/>Roseville 95678</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sashimi Won Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Only at Guy&#x27;s restaurant can you get a little Italian, Mexican, Cajun and Asian. The grilled-onion-and-garlic tortilla stack, inspired by Guy&#x27;s mom, has &quot;dynamite&quot; texture and flavor. Guy&#x27;s Sashimi Won Tacos dressed with eel sauce were double gold winners at the Sonoma County Harvest Fair.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Unexpected Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/roseville/johnny-garlics-roseville-ca-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.29114,38.79241,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Dad&#x27;s Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Dad&#x27;s Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sacramento, CA 95818 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9164473237" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(916) 447-3237</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://ilovedadskitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">ilovedadskitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Dad%27s+Kitchen%2C+2968+Freeport+Blvd%2C+Sacramento%2C+CA+95818&amp;ll=38.550889,-121.489200" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2968 Freeport Blvd<br/>Sacramento, CA 95818</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bacon and Blue Cheese Burger, Hot Blonde</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Dad&#x27;s Burger is so popular that when the current owners bought the restaurant, they kept it on the menu. Guy describes the signature 8-ounce bacon and blue cheese-encrusted beef patty as the most &amp;quot;righteous&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;juiciest&amp;quot; burger ever. If you prefer chicken, try the Hot Blonde with avocado.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Soup and Sandwiches</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sacramento/dads-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.48920,38.55089,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Gatsby&#x27;s Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Gatsby&#x27;s Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sacramento, CA 95825 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9169770102" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(916) 977- 0102</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.gatsbysdiner.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.gatsbysdiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Gatsby%27s+Diner%2C+2598+Alta+Arden+Expressway%2C+Sacramento%2C+CA+95825&amp;ll=38.599511,-121.402091" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2598 Alta Arden Expressway<br/>Sacramento, CA 95825</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beet Sliders, Beef Rouladen, Brined Pork Chops</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Visit Gatsby&#x27;s Diner for Old World European comfort food and unique vegetarian dishes. The pastrami-marinated beet sliders with green goddess dressing and homemade chips were meaty and tender according to Guy. Meat lovers should try the flavorful beef rouladen or the brined pork chops.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Little Twisted<br/>Top 10 Burgers</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sacramento/gatsbys-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.40209,38.59951,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cafe Rolle</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cafe Rolle</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Sacramento, CA 95819 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9164559140" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(916) 455-9140</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.caferolle.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.caferolle.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cafe+Rolle%2C+5357+H+St%2C+Sacramento%2C+CA+95819&amp;ll=38.568250,-121.436420" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5357 H St<br/>Sacramento, CA 95819</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Quiche Lorraine, Grilled Ham and Brie Cheese Sandwich, Chicken Pate and Goat Cheese Sandwich, Chilled Lentil Salad</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Quiche on a salad and a grilled ham and Brie cheese sandwich are just some of the French country-style favorites at this deli. Guy appreciated the nice and rich flavors of the chicken pate and goat cheese sandwich and loved the &quot;floral notes&quot; found in the chilled lentil salad with roasted prawns.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A Little Bit of Everywhere<br/>West Coast Cookin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/sacramento/cafe-rolle-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.43642,38.56825,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Gorilla Barbeque</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Gorilla Barbeque</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Pacifica 94044 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6503597427" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(650) 359-7427</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.gorillabbq.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.gorillabbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Gorilla+Barbeque%2C+2145+Coast+Highway+1%2C+Pacifica+94044&amp;ll=37.613037,-122.487820" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2145 Coast Highway 1<br/>Pacifica 94044</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pork Ribs, Beef Brisket, Philly Cheese Steak, Mac n&#x27; Cheese</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy had to check out Gorilla Barbeque, which is housed in a bright orange boxcar. Regardless of size, Gorilla Barbeque still grills 1,500 pounds of meat each week. The Philly cheese steak with barbecued brisket explodes with flavor, just like the mac &#x27;n&#x27; cheese baked with a Goldfish cracker crust.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Funky Finds in &#x27;da House<br/>BBQ &amp; More<br/>BBQ Legends</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/pacifica/gorilla-barbeque-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.48782,37.61304,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tamarindo Food Truck</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tamarindo Food Truck</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Orange County, CA</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7146409371" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">714-640-9371</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://tamarindotruck.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">tamarindotruck.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tamarindo+Food+Truck%2C+Roaming+Food+Truck%2C+Orange+County%2C+CA&amp;ll=33.717471,-117.831143" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Roaming Food Truck<br/>Orange County, CA</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Drunken Torta (Steak Marinated in Beer), Chicken Chilaquiles</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tamarindo serves Mexican dishes made with organic, local ingredients. Guy declares his love for the drunken torta, which dresses up flank steak with salsa, onion, tomatoes, arugula, bean spread and mayo. Another must-try dish is the chicken chilaquiles with achiote marinade for a tangy, spicy taste</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Food Truckapalooza<br/>Grillin&#x27;, Chillin&#x27; and Huli Huli Chicken</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/orange-county/tamarindo-food-truck" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.83114,33.71747,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Southern Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Southern Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oakland, CA 94602 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5103362013" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(510) 336-2013</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://southerncafe2000.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">southerncafe2000.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Southern+Cafe%2C+2000+MacArthur+Blvd%2C+Oakland%2C+CA+94602&amp;ll=37.801088,-122.218378" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2000 MacArthur Blvd<br/>Oakland, CA 94602</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Chicken, Southern-Style Oxtails</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Southern flavors reach the west coast at this Oakland hot spot. Comfort food favorites include Beef Meatloaf, Southern Fried Chicken, slow-cooked Oxtails, Macaroni and Cheese, Collard Greens and more. Plus,the Peach Cobbler and Banana Pudding are absolute winners.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ Bites and Southern Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/oakland/southern-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.21838,37.80109,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hodads</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hodads</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ocean Beach, CA 92107 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (18 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6192244623" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(619) 224-4623</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hodadies.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hodadies.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hodads%2C+5010+Newport+Ave%2C+Ocean+Beach%2C+CA+92107&amp;ll=32.747050,-117.251339" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5010 Newport Ave<br/>Ocean Beach, CA 92107</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bacon Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hodads&#x27; burgers don&#x27;t simply have bacon strips on top. Instead, this funky joint adds an entire bacon patty to the mix. They really &quot;put the shama lama in ding dong,&quot; Guy says of his favorite burger, which includes two sizzling beef patties and cheese - a &quot;run-down-your-arm burger,&quot; for sure.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Carnivore Delivery<br/>All San Diego, All the Time<br/>Seaside Eats<br/>Top 10 Burgers<br/>Triple D Nation: Burgers, Burritos and Biscuits</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/ocean-beach/hodads-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.25134,32.74705,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>W.E.P.A.! at Brix 581</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">W.E.P.A.! at Brix 581</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oakland, CA 94607</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4157247274" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(415) 724-7274</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.brix581.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.brix581.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=W.E.P.A.%21+at+Brix+581%2C+581+5th+Street%2C+Oakland%2C+CA+94607&amp;ll=37.799228,-122.278364" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">581 5th Street<br/>Oakland, CA 94607</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicharron Mofongo, Canoa</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Puerto Rican hot spot is known for its bold flavors and (bottomless) brunch bashes. Regulars love the Chicharron Mofongo and Canoa, but the restaurant also offers up some incredible vegan options.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">East Coast, West Coast</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/oakland/wepa-at-brix-581" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.27836,37.79923,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Souley Vegan</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Souley Vegan</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oakland, CA 94607 &middot; &#9733; 4.6 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5109221615" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">510-922-1615</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.souleyvegan.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.souleyvegan.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Souley+Vegan%2C+301+Broadway%2C+Oakland%2C+CA+94607&amp;ll=37.797011,-122.276079" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">301 Broadway<br/>Oakland, CA 94607</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Okra Gumbo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef-Owner Tamearra Dyson serves up Creole classics and soul food favorites with a surprising twist: All the dishes offered at her restaurant are vegan. Guy just had to check this creative menu out, so he stopped in to try Chef Dyson&#x27;s okra gumbo and her meatless spins on succulent sandwiches.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hot Meat and Cool Veg</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/oakland/souley-vegan-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.27608,37.79701,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Clove and Hoof</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Clove and Hoof</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oakland, CA 94611 &middot; &#9733; 2.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5105471446" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">510-547-1446</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://cloveandhoofoakland.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">cloveandhoofoakland.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Clove+and+Hoof%2C+4001+Broadway%2C+Oakland%2C+CA+94611&amp;ll=37.827850,-122.256905" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4001 Broadway<br/>Oakland, CA 94611</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cheesesteak, Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A mecca for ethically minded carnivores and anyone who loves top-quality meat, Clove and Hoof houses both a butcher shop and restaurant under one roof. Owners John Blevins and Analiesa Gosnell use only antibiotic-free and hormone-free meat in their dishes, like the cheesesteak that Guy stopped in to try.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Succulent Sandwiches</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/oakland/clove-and-hoof-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.25690,37.82785,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cosecha Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cosecha Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oakland, CA 94607 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5104525900" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">510-452-5900</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cosechacafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cosechacafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cosecha+Cafe%2C+907+Washington+St%2C+Oakland%2C+CA+94607&amp;ll=37.801927,-122.274653" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">907 Washington St<br/>Oakland, CA 94607</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Carne Adovada, Pork Belly Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Staying true to its name (cosecha translates to &quot;harvest&quot;), this Mexican spot determines many of its dishes based on which ingredients are in season. Guy stopped by this high-energy cafe to chow down on two pork-centric dishes: carne adovada (braised pork seasoned with guajillo chile) and pork belly tacos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos, Turtles and Tri-Tip<br/>West Coast Cookin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/oakland/cosecha-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.27465,37.80193,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Beer Belly</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Beer Belly</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90020 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2133872337" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(213) 387-2337</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://beerbellyla.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">beerbellyla.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Beer+Belly%2C+532+S+Western+Ave%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90020&amp;ll=34.064338,-118.308578" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">532 S Western Ave<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90020</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Grilled Cheese Sandwich, Duck Fat Fries, Duck French Dip, Spicy Chicken Wings, Deep Fried Twinkie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The duck-centric menu and rotating craft-beer selection keep the locals coming back to Beer Belly. Follow Guy&#x27;s lead and order the duck-fat fries topped with crisp fried duck skin and tender duck confit. Or opt for the grilled cheese. This towering, four-cheese creation is essentially two sandwiches stacked together, with a layer of maple syrup-drenched bacon in the middle and a fried egg on top.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Super Sandwiches<br/>Unlikely Partners</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/beer-belly-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.30858,34.06434,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Belly &amp; Snout</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Belly &amp; Snout</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90006 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3236434170" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">323-643-4170</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bellyandsnout.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bellyandsnout.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Belly+%26+Snout%2C+974+S+Western+Ave%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90006&amp;ll=34.053374,-118.308843" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">974 S Western Ave<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90006</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sisig Hot Dog, Pork Adobo Grilled Cheese, Oxtail Chili Tater Tots</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef-Owner Warren Almeda serves up American twists on classic Filipino dishes at this Koreatown joint. Guy just had to try the Sisig Hot Dog. As the name suggests, this dog is dressed up with sisig (a Filipino mixture of ground pork belly and pork snout, made in-house daily), in addition to garlic crema, pickled red onions, radishes, green onions, a fried egg and the Filipino citrus known as calamansi.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Asia, Africa and India</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/belly-and-snout-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.30884,34.05337,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Biergarten</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Biergarten</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90004</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3234664860" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">323-466-4860</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.biergartenla.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.biergartenla.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Biergarten%2C+206+N+Western+Ave%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90004&amp;ll=34.074855,-118.308884" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">206 N Western Ave<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90004</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Drunk Chicken, German Fried Rice</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Set in the heart of Koreatown, this modern beer hall fuses pub food and Korean flavors, with dishes like beer-infused, roasted Drunk Chicken, German Fried Rice in beer gravy, and a Bratwurst Corn Dog.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Indulgent Dishes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/biergarten-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.30888,34.07485,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mom&#x27;s Tamales</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mom&#x27;s Tamales</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90031 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3232269383" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">323-226-9383</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.momstamales.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.momstamales.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mom%27s+Tamales%2C+3328+Pasadena+Ave.%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90031&amp;ll=34.083827,-118.213458" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3328 Pasadena Ave.<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90031</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tamales, Chile Relleno</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For delicious homemade tamales, drop by Mom&#x27;s Tamales and sample one of eight options, all steamed and using scratch-made batter. The corn and cheese, chicken mole and beef tamales are particularly noteworthy. Also worth a try: specialties like stuffed peppers, queso fresco and sopes asadas.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">You Picked &#x27;Em</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/moms-tamales-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.21346,34.08383,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rutt&#x27;s Hawaiian Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rutt&#x27;s Hawaiian Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90066 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3103986326" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(310) 398-6326</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.ruttscafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.ruttscafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rutt%27s+Hawaiian+Cafe%2C+12114+W+Washington+Blvd%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90066&amp;ll=33.997172,-118.424681" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">12114 W Washington Blvd<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90066</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hawaiian Royale, Laulau Plate</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rutt&#x27;s is the go-to place for Hawaiian food in Los Angeles. Guy recommends the Hawaiian Royale with its tasty mix of teriyaki beef and scrambled eggs. Another pick is the Lau Lau plate: a flavorful blend of pork and butterfish wrapped in taro leaves. Locals love the large portions and value prices.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">California Cruisin&#x27;<br/>By Land and Sea</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/rutt_s-hawaiian-cafe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.42468,33.99717,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Catelli&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Catelli&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Geyserville 95441 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7078573471" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 857-3471</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mycatellis.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mycatellis.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Catelli%27s%2C+21047+Geyserville+Ave%2C+Geyserville+95441&amp;ll=38.706726,-122.904494" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">21047 Geyserville Ave<br/>Geyserville 95441</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef Meatball Sliders</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After 55 years in business, Catelli&#x27;s closed in 1991. But in 2010, brother-sister duo Domenica and Nick Catelli reopened the restaurant and brought the old family recipes back to life. Guy stopped by for Jack&#x27;s Covelo Beef Meatball Sliders. But the ravioli? Two words: handmade perfection.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bar Food and Bon Bons<br/>Amazing Italian<br/>Takeout: Home Delivery<br/>Triple D Nation: From the Sea</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/geyserville/cattelis-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.90449,38.70673,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Clendenen&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Clendenen&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fortuna, CA 95540</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7077252123" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707)725-2123</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://clendenensciderworks.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">clendenensciderworks.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Clendenen%27s%2C+96+S+12th+St%2C+Fortuna%2C+CA+95540&amp;ll=40.584869,-124.154582" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">96 S 12th St<br/>Fortuna, CA 95540</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Apple Cider</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy claims Clendenen&#x27;s apple cider is the best he&#x27;s ever had. They grow their own apples in an orchard that dates back to 1879. After the apples are pressed, they are sold immediately for the freshest apple cider in Fortuna, which Guy likens to &quot;nectar from the gods.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s Hometown Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/fortuna/clendenen-s" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-124.15458,40.58487,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hotel Ivanhoe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hotel Ivanhoe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ferndale, CA 95536</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7077869000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 786-9000</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://hotel-ivanhoe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">hotel-ivanhoe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hotel+Ivanhoe%2C+315+Main+St%2C+Ferndale%2C+CA+95536&amp;ll=40.575903,-124.264959" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">315 Main St<br/>Ferndale, CA 95536</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken Cacciatore</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hotel Ivanhoe is where Guy got his first kitchen job. Tucked away in his hometown of Ferndale, this American-Italian restaurant serves &quot;old-school Italian&quot; fare like chicken cacciatore, which Guy calls &quot;one of the most comforting things you could eat.&quot; The risotto with Italian sausage is also a hit.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s Hometown Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/ferndale/hotel-ivanhoe" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-124.26496,40.57590,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ferndale Elementary Jr. High Pretzel Cart</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ferndale Elementary Jr. High Pretzel Cart</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ferndale, CA 48220 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Ferndale-Elementary-Jr-High-Pretzel-Cart/111900728874264?sk=timeline" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Ferndale-Elementary-Jr-High-Pretzel-Cart/111900728874264?sk=timeline</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ferndale+Elementary+Jr.+High+Pretzel+Cart%2C+Ferndale%2C+CA+48220&amp;ll=42.458404,-83.138095" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;"><br/>Ferndale, CA 48220</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pretzels</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Guy was growing up in Ferndale, California, he set up his own pretzel cart to earn some extra money. In order to pass on the opportunity to learn about the food industry to other students, Guy personally built this cart so that Ferndale students can raise money year-round.&amp;nbsp;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s Hometown Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/ferndale/ferndale-elementary-jr--high-pretzel-cart" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-83.13810,42.45840,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Humboldt Sweets</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Humboldt Sweets</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ferndale, CA 95536 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (13 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7077864683" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 786-4683</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.humboldtsweetsbakery.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.humboldtsweetsbakery.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Humboldt+Sweets%2C+614+Main+St%2C+Ferndale%2C+CA+95536&amp;ll=40.578037,-124.262115" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">614 Main St<br/>Ferndale, CA 95536</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Caramel-Pecan Cinnamon Roll, Ham and Cheddar Scone</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The quintessential mom-and-pop place, Humboldt Sweets cranks out what Guy calls &quot;cinnamon rolls gone wild.&quot; These jumbo-sized caramel-pecan cinnamon rolls are gooey and sweet. Another popular item on the menu is the ham and cheddar scone with a side of bacon gravy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s Hometown Tour<br/>Dynamite Desserts</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/ferndale/humboldt-sweets" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-124.26212,40.57804,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Ferndale Meat Co.</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Ferndale Meat Co.</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Ferndale, CA 95536 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7077864501" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(707) 786-4501</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/ferndale/ferndale-meat-co-" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/ferndale/ferndale-meat-co-</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Ferndale+Meat+Co.%2C+376+Main+St%2C+Ferndale%2C+CA+95536&amp;ll=40.576105,-124.263920" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">376 Main St<br/>Ferndale, CA 95536</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Italian Sausage</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ferndale Meat Co. is the local butcher shop in Guy&#x27;s hometown. The specialty here is the &quot;outstanding&quot; Italian sausage composed of equal portions of beef and pork seasoned with six different spices and red wine. Guy recommends dipping the sausage in applesauce for an extra pop of flavor.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy&#x27;s Hometown Tour</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/ferndale/ferndale-meat-co-" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-124.26392,40.57610,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Haggo&#x27;s Organic Taco</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Haggo&#x27;s Organic Taco</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Encinitas, CA 92024 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7607536000" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(760) 753-6000</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.haggosorganictaco.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.haggosorganictaco.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Haggo%27s+Organic+Taco%2C+1302+N+Coast+Hwy+101%2C+Encinitas%2C+CA+92024&amp;ll=33.070757,-117.304443" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1302 N Coast Hwy 101<br/>Encinitas, CA 92024</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fish Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">It&#x27;s hard to find a shack near the beach with fish tacos &#x27;&#x27;bordering on gourmet,&#x27;&#x27; but that&#x27;s exactly what Guy thought of Haggo&#x27;s Organic Taco near Leucadia, Calif. Owner James Haggard uses &#x27;&#x27;at least 95 percent&#x27;&#x27; organic ingredients in all of his dishes and cooks halibut with his own dry rub.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Pound Cake to Pot Pie</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/encinitas/haggos-organic-taco" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-117.30444,33.07076,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Rudy&#x27;s Can&#x27;t Fail Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Rudy&#x27;s Can&#x27;t Fail Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Emeryville, CA 94608 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5105941221" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(510) 594-1221</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.rudyscantfailcafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.rudyscantfailcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Rudy%27s+Can%27t+Fail+Cafe%2C+4081+Hollis+St%2C+Emeryville%2C+CA+94608&amp;ll=37.830960,-122.285993" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4081 Hollis St<br/>Emeryville, CA 94608</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chili Cheeseburger, Burgers</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rudy&#x27;s is all about creating a welcoming environment where &amp;quot;all walks of life&amp;quot; can feel at home. So far, they haven&#x27;t failed, with a 20-burger menu and classic breakfast specials. For what Guy might call a hunch-worthy bite, try The Monster Chili Cheeseburger with two patties and scratch-made chili.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Goes Tailgatin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/emeryville/rudys-cant-fail-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.28599,37.83096,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bludso&#x27;s BBQ</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bludso&#x27;s BBQ</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90036 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3239312583" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">323-931-2583</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.bludsosbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.bludsosbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bludso%27s+BBQ%2C+609+N+La+Brea+Ave%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90036&amp;ll=34.082092,-118.344144" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609 N La Brea Ave<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90036</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ribs with Spicy BBQ Sauce, Deep-Fried Turkey, Collard Greens</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This Compton location is closed, but you can still get Bludso&#x27;s craveworthy &#x27;cue at the Hollywood locale. The joint serves up Texas-style barbecue like the ribs with a side of spicy barbecue sauce that won over Guy Fieri. Owner Kevin Bludso really goes all out at the holidays with deep-fried turkeys injected with a decadent concoction of butter and seasonings, which he refers to as &quot;liquid gold.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Big-Time Barbecue<br/>Kings and Queens of &#x27;Cue</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/compton/bludsos-bbq" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.34414,34.08209,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Oinkster</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Oinkster</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Eagle Rock, CA 90041 &middot; &#9733; 3.1 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3232556465" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(323) 255-6465</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.theoinkster.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.theoinkster.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Oinkster%2C+2005+Colorado+Blvd%2C+Eagle+Rock%2C+CA+90041&amp;ll=34.139509,-118.210521" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2005 Colorado Blvd<br/>Eagle Rock, CA 90041</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulled Pork with BBQ Carolina Sauce, Oinkster Pastrami Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The house-cured pastrami at The Oinkster redefines slow fast food says owner Andre Guerrero. Guy couldn&#x27;t agree more. The signature Oinkster pastrami sandwich was best described as &amp;quot;liqua smoka porka flavor,&amp;quot; and with homemade ketchup and perfect onion rings, the meal was totally on-point.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Stacked, Stuffed and Loaded</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/eagle-rock/the-oinkster-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.21052,34.13951,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>From Scratch Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">From Scratch Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Carmel, CA 93923 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8316252448" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(831) 625-2448</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.fromscratchrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fromscratchrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=From+Scratch+Restaurant%2C+3626+The+Barnyard%2C+Carmel%2C+CA+93923&amp;ll=36.540407,-121.906986" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3626 The Barnyard<br/>Carmel, CA 93923</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Biscuit and Gravy, Brisket Chili</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Scratch is what Guy calls &quot;old school in hyperdrive.&quot; They take classics and inject them with more flavors. For example, the biscuit and gravy consists of a handmade biscuit topped with a sausage patty and gravy. Another must-try is the brisket chili that is both spicy and sweet.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cross-Country Classics<br/>All-American All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/carmel/from-scratch-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.90699,36.54041,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Little Napoli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Little Napoli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Carmel, CA 93923 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8316266335" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(831) 626-6335</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://chefpepe.com/restaurants/little-napoli/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">chefpepe.com/restaurants/little-napoli</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Little+Napoli%2C+Corner+of+Dolores+St+%26+7th+St%2C+Carmel%2C+CA+93923&amp;ll=36.553783,-121.922683" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">Corner of Dolores St &amp; 7th St<br/>Carmel, CA 93923</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Baked Cannelloni &quot;Tricolore&quot;, Il Pescatore &quot;Cioppino Rosso&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For Southern Italian cuisine that will &quot;knock your mama out the rocking chair,&quot; Guy heads to Little Napoli. Enjoy the simplicity of the Baked Cannelloni &quot;Tricolore,&quot; with its blend of sauces, or savor the spicy Il Pescatore &quot;Cioppino Rosso,&quot; featuring fresh seafood and just the right amount of heat.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Standards to Standouts<br/>West Coast Cookin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/carmel/little-napoli" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-121.92268,36.55378,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Chili John&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Chili John&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Burbank, CA 91506 &middot; &#9733; 3.7 (12 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:8188463611" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">818-846-3611</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/burbank/chili-johns-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/burbank/chili-johns-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Chili+John%27s%2C+2018+W+Burbank+Blvd%2C+Burbank%2C+CA+91506&amp;ll=34.179999,-118.333711" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2018 W Burbank Blvd<br/>Burbank, CA 91506</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chili Over Spaghetti, Chili Dogs, Chili Tamales</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The chili recipe at this 1950s-style diner is so old that it came with the building when the LoGuercio family bought the place. Laced with beef cracklings and two secret spice blends, this meaty chili tastes extra delicious served over spaghetti and topped with cheese, onions and oyster crackers.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chicken, Chili and Chowder</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/burbank/chili-johns-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.33371,34.18000,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Golden State</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Golden State</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90036 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3237828331" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(323) 782- 8331</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.thegoldenstatecafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thegoldenstatecafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Golden+State%2C+426+N+Fairfax+Ave%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90036&amp;ll=34.079054,-118.361135" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">426 N Fairfax Ave<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90036</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pulled Pork Sandwich, Grass Fed-Lamb Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Owners James Starr and Jason Bernstein cook up clever dishes with all-Californian ingredients. Guy&#x27;s favorite was the pulled pork sandwich with pickled jalapenos and onions and a killer hot mustard sauce. The grass fed-lamb burger with yogurt dill sauce and sweet potato fries was &amp;quot;rock star&amp;quot; too.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hittin&#x27; the Grill</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/the-golden-state-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.36114,34.07905,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cha Cha Chili</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cha Cha Chili</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90032</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3232228900" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">323-222-8900</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://chachachili.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">chachachili.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cha+Cha+Chili%2C+4625+Valley+Blvd%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90032&amp;ll=34.062834,-118.183273" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4625 Valley Blvd<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90032</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Korean Philly Cheesesteak, Bulgogi Taco</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Korean and Mexican cuisines come together at this casual restaurant in dishes like&amp;nbsp;kimchee quesadillas and Korean short rib burritos.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Intercontinental Flavorfest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/cha-cha-chili-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.18327,34.06283,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Little Jewel of New Orleans</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Little Jewel of New Orleans</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles 90012 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2136200461" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">213-620-0461</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://littlejewel.la" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">littlejewel.la</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Little+Jewel+of+New+Orleans%2C+207+Ord+St%2C+Los+Angeles+90012&amp;ll=34.060099,-118.238083" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">207 Ord St<br/>Los Angeles 90012</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crawfish Mac N Cheese, Po&#x27; Boys, Cochon de Lait</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This restaurant brings Cajun flavors to Chinatown, with po&#x27; boys, muffulettas and breakfast beignets. A standout is the crawfish-laced mac and cheese that incorporates caramelized onions, white wine and a Creole spice blend.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Intercontinental Flavorfest<br/>Rockstar Chefs<br/>Triple D Nation: From Pork to Po&#x27; Boys</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/the-little-jewel-of-new-orleans-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.23808,34.06010,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Republica Empanada</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Republica Empanada</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Mesa, AZ 85210</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4809691343" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">480-969-1343</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://republicaempanada.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">republicaempanada.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Republica+Empanada%2C+204+East+1st+Ave%2C+Mesa%2C+AZ+85210&amp;ll=33.413138,-111.825956" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">204 East 1st Ave<br/>Mesa, AZ 85210</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cubano Empanada, Arroz con Pollo</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Republica Empanada is all about family and Latin-American comfort food. Try the classic Arroz con Pollo or the Cubano Empanada which is filled with slow-cooked shredded pork, ham, mozzarella cheese and pickles.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mom&#x27;s Kitchen</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/restaurants-in-mesa/republica-empanada-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.82596,33.41314,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Aloha Kitchen</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Aloha Kitchen</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Mesa, AZ 85210 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (12 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4808972451" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">480-897-2451</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://alohakitchen.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">alohakitchen.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Aloha+Kitchen%2C+2950+S+Alma+School+Rd%2C+Mesa%2C+AZ+85210&amp;ll=33.360715,-111.859381" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2950 S Alma School Rd<br/>Mesa, AZ 85210</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Manapua , Kalbi (Korean-Style Short Ribs)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Can&#x27;t get to Hawaii? Aloha Kitchen will transport you to the islands on a plate. Lynn Tso and her husband Ray are serving classic Hawaiian plate lunches and marinated meats to the people in the Arizona dessert. Try the super soft Manapua steamed pork buns or the Korean-style short ribs.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rollin&#x27; in the Dough</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/restaurants-in-mesa/aloha-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.85938,33.36072,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>La Piazza</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">La Piazza</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Glendale 85301 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6238473301" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(623) 847-3301</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.lapiazzaalforno.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.lapiazzaalforno.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=La+Piazza%2C+5803+W+Glendale+Ave%2C+Glendale+85301&amp;ll=33.538396,-112.183975" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5803 W Glendale Ave<br/>Glendale 85301</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza, Chicken Cacciatore</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A father-son operation, the duo churns out delicious pizzas and Italian favorites. Guy couldn&#x27;t keep his hands off of the Italian Stallion, a pizza loaded with sopressata, Parma prosciutto, Italian sausage, and pepperoni. Still hungry? Try the baked spaghetti pie topped with fresh mozzarella.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Worldwide Delivery<br/>A Burger, A Bowl and a Slice<br/>Triple D Nation: Steak, Sausage and Salami<br/>Pizza Party</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/glendale/la-piazza-al-forno-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.18398,33.53840,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Thee Pitts Again</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Thee Pitts Again</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Glendale, AZ 85308 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9703875027" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(970) 387-5027</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.theepittsagain.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.theepittsagain.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Thee+Pitts+Again%2C+5558+W+Bell+Rd%2C+Glendale%2C+AZ+85308&amp;ll=33.639361,-112.179093" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5558 W Bell Rd<br/>Glendale, AZ 85308</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">BBQ, Cheryl&#x27;s Cole Slaw, Roger&#x27;s Wife Cheryl&#x27;s Simple Chili</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The award-winning Thee Pitts Again in Glendale, Ariz., has barbecuing accolades stacked over and under the fridge. On Triple D, Guy loved the low-and-slow smoking technique for the succulent pulled pork. As Guy also learned, the technique makes for super tender turkey and catfish, too.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Neighborhood Joints<br/>Ultimate Turkey Fest</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/glendale/thee-pitts-again-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.17909,33.63936,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Haus Murphy&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Haus Murphy&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Glendale, AZ 85301 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6239392480" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">623-939-2480</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.hausmurphys.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.hausmurphys.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Haus+Murphy%27s%2C+5739+W+Glendale+Ave%2C+Glendale%2C+AZ+85301&amp;ll=33.538419,-112.182952" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5739 W Glendale Ave<br/>Glendale, AZ 85301</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sauerbraten, Pork Schnitzel with Paprika Gravy, Wiener Schnitzel</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Haus Murphy&#x27;s, you&#x27;ll find hearty food made from scratch that owner Rose Hoffman grew up with in Munich. Enjoy a big pretzel and a beer, let the sauerbraten tickle your sweet and sour taste buds, or try a German sour roast served with potatoes and cabbage.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Family Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/glendale/haus-murphys-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.18295,33.53842,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Curry Corner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Curry Corner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tempe, AZ 85281 &middot; &#9733; 4.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4808941276" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(480) 894-1276</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://currycornertempe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">currycornertempe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Curry+Corner%2C+1212+E+Apache+Blvd%2C+Tempe%2C+AZ+85281&amp;ll=33.415243,-111.919667" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1212 E Apache Blvd<br/>Tempe, AZ 85281</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tandoori Chicken, Goat Karahi</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Curry Corner in Tempe, Ariz., may look like a typical Pakistani restaurant at first, but it&#x27;s home to some of the best chicken Guy&#x27;s ever had on Triple D - specifically, the Tandoori chicken tikka, topped with garam masala. Another specialty is the tender Goat Karahi.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fun in the Sun<br/>A Festival of Flavor</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/tempe/curry-corner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.91967,33.41524,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Gloria&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Gloria&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90034 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3108380963" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">310-838-0963</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.glorias-cafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.glorias-cafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Gloria%27s+Cafe%2C+10227+Venice+Blvd%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90034&amp;ll=34.021554,-118.402718" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">10227 Venice Blvd<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90034</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Carne Adobada, Seven Seas Soup</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Since 1981, Gloria Flores has been sharing her traditional El Salvadoran cooking to adoring Los Angeles locals. Guy&#x27;s visit on Triple D left him scraping his plate of Adobada, a pork stew with a rich tomato sauce. And he was absolutely bowled over by the Seven Seas Soup brimming with crab legs and shrimp. &quot;That is delicious - deep, deep flavor,&quot; Guy exclaimed.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">World Class Flavor<br/>Globetrottin&#x27;</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/glorias-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.40272,34.02155,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Nickel Diner</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Nickel Diner</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles 90012 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2136238301" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(213) 623-8301</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://nickeldiner.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">nickeldiner.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Nickel+Diner%2C+524+S+Main+St%2C+Los+Angeles+90012&amp;ll=34.057107,-118.238903" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">524 S Main St<br/>Los Angeles 90012</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mac and Cheese, Fried Catfish, Maple Bacon Donut</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Go sweet and savory at this 1940s-era eclectic diner with California flair. You&#x27;ll find donuts smothered in bacon, upside-down floor lamps and funky names for dishes, like &quot;Hangover Helper&quot; and &quot;Smac and Cheese.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Breakfast, Lunch and Brunch<br/>Blast From the Past</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/nickel-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.23890,34.05711,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Chino Bandido</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Chino Bandido</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Phoenix, AZ 85032 &middot; &#9733; 4.1 (17 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6023753639" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">602-375-3639</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.chinobandido.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.chinobandido.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Chino+Bandido%2C+15414+N+19th+Ave+Suite+K%2C+Phoenix%2C+AZ+85032&amp;ll=33.626421,-112.100230" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">15414 N 19th Ave Suite K<br/>Phoenix, AZ 85032</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pollo Diablo, Jade Red Chicken, Machaca</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chino Bandido&#x27;s Chinese-Mexican-Jamaican dishes have garnered lifelong fans. Guy loved the fusion, calling it one of the most original on DDD. The best part? The menu has more than 90,000 combinations. For a spicy option try the Pollo Diablo, Jade Red Chicken and Jerk Fried Rice. Pow!</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Fried, Baked and Barbecued<br/>Takeout: Bold Bites Brought Home<br/>A World of Flavors</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/phoenix/chino-bandido-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.10023,33.62642,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>St. Francis</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">St. Francis</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Phoenix, AZ 85012 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6022008111" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(602) 200-8111</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.stfrancisaz.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.stfrancisaz.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=St.+Francis%2C+111+E+Camelback+Rd%2C+Phoenix%2C+AZ+85012&amp;ll=33.508994,-112.071273" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">111 E Camelback Rd<br/>Phoenix, AZ 85012</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pig Dip, Rustic Iron Skillet Pancake, Moroccan Meatballs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef Aaron Chamberlin likes to cook everything over an open fire just like when he was a boy scout. Guy adored the smoky and creamy Pig Dip filled with pork, prosciutto and fennel onion marmalade. The rustic Iron Skillet Pancake with berry compote and the Moroccan meatballs also impressed.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Traditional Gone Wild</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/phoenix/st-francis-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.07127,33.50899,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jitlada</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jitlada</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles 90027 &middot; &#9733; 2.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3236633104" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(323) 663-3104</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.jitladala.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jitladala.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jitlada%2C+5233+W.+Sunset+Blvd.%2C+Los+Angeles+90027&amp;ll=34.098123,-118.303789" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5233 W. Sunset Blvd.<br/>Los Angeles 90027</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tom Yum Soup, Green Curry, Crying Tiger Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">There&#x27;s regular Thai food and then there&#x27;s Jitlada. Guy swore that if the chef of Jitlada won GGG he would come to the restaurant, and he was not disappointed. &quot;This is one of the best Thai experiences I have ever had,&quot; Guy said after tasting the Green Curry and the Tom Yum Soup.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sammies and Spice<br/>Takeout: Sendin&#x27; the Surf &amp; Turf</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/jitlada-thai-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.30379,34.09812,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Barrio Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Barrio Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Phoenix 85006 &middot; &#9733; 4.7 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6026360240" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">602-636-0240</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.barriocafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.barriocafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Barrio+Cafe%2C+2814+N+16th+St%2C+Phoenix+85006&amp;ll=33.479016,-112.047989" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2814 N 16th St<br/>Phoenix 85006</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chiles en Nogada, Tilapia Wrapped in Banana Leaves, Cochinita Pibil, Yucatan Pulled Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Barrio Cafe you will find some real-deal Mexican food. Guy loved the almond sauce in the Chiles en Nogada, or chicken-stuffed chiles. The tilapia wrapped in banana leaves was a &quot;package deal,&quot; and the Cochinita Pibil and Yucatan pulled pork were bursting with flavor.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: From the Sea<br/>Peppers, Pork and Poutine<br/>Best of the West<br/>Takeout: Global Comes Local</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/phoenix/barrio-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.04799,33.47902,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Matt&#x27;s Big Breakfast</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Matt&#x27;s Big Breakfast</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Phoenix, AZ 85004 &middot; &#9733; 3.9 (18 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6022541074" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">602-254-1074</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mattsbigbreakfast.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mattsbigbreakfast.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Matt%27s+Big+Breakfast%2C+825+N.+1st+St.%2C+Phoenix%2C+AZ+85004&amp;ll=33.457457,-112.072302" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">825 N. 1st St.<br/>Phoenix, AZ 85004</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Waffles, Bacon, The Chop &amp; Chick (Breakfast Pork Chops with Eggs)</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy isn&#x27;t usually a breakfast fan but he&#x27;ll stop by Matt&#x27;s Big Breakfast anytime of day. He orders the Chop &amp; Chick, a giant Iowa pork rib chop that&#x27;s marinated in a tangy pesto sauce and served with 2 eggs. It&#x27;s &quot;good eats&quot; and possibly the closest thing to green eggs and ham.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Triple D Nation: Burgers, Burritos and Biscuits<br/>Big Breakfast</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/phoenix/matts-big-breakfast-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.07230,33.45746,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Roberto&#x27;s Authentic Mexican Food</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Roberto&#x27;s Authentic Mexican Food</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Phoenix, AZ 85086 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (16 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6234651515" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(623) 465-1515</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.Robertosaz.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.Robertosaz.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Roberto%27s+Authentic+Mexican+Food%2C+39510+N.+Daisy+Mountain+Dr.+Suite+%23170%2C+Phoenix%2C+AZ+85086&amp;ll=33.844333,-112.133900" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">39510 N. Daisy Mountain Dr. Suite #170<br/>Phoenix, AZ 85086</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Carne Asada, Salsa</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Visitors to Roberto&#x27;s Authentic Mexican Food come back saying they serve &amp;quot;true Mexican food.&amp;quot; Guy experienced firsthand the killer green chile sauce used for everything from the juicy tacos al pastor made with pork and pineapple to the chimichanga burritos. Guy asked to be a chimichanga ambassador.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Like Mama Made</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/phoenix/robertos-mexican-food-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.13390,33.84433,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>La Santisima Gourmet Taco Shop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">La Santisima Gourmet Taco Shop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Phoenix, AZ 85006 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6022546330" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">602-254-6330</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.lasantisimagourmet.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.lasantisimagourmet.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=La+Santisima+Gourmet+Taco+Shop%2C+1919+N+16th+St%2C+Phoenix%2C+AZ+85006&amp;ll=33.469201,-112.047393" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1919 N 16th St<br/>Phoenix, AZ 85006</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nogada Taco, Oaxacan Black Mole Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Once you&#x27;ve chosen tacos, like Mexico City-style chicken tinga or spicy Yucatan pork shoulder, top it with fresh salsa from the abundant salsa bar.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sweet, Savory and Saucy</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/phoenix/la-santisima-gourmet-taco-shop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.04739,33.46920,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bludso&#x27;s Bar &amp; Que</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bludso&#x27;s Bar &amp; Que</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles 90036 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:3239312583" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(323) 931-2583</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.barandque.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.barandque.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bludso%27s+Bar+%26+Que%2C+609+N+La+Brea+Ave%2C+Los+Angeles+90036&amp;ll=34.082092,-118.344144" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">609 N La Brea Ave<br/>Los Angeles 90036</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This spot is in California, but if you close your eyes, &quot;you&#x27;ll think you&#x27;re in Texas,&quot; says Madison Cowan. The barbecue served here indeed has its roots in the Lone Star State, as owner Kevin Bludso learned how to smoke meats from his Texan grandmother. The crowds pack in for the &#x27;cue, which includes succulent pork ribs and chickens. The meats are massaged with customized dry rubs laden with secret spices, then marinated overnight and smoked over both oak and pecan woods. For meat lovers with massive appetites, Madison recommends The Lunch Tray. This option features a selection of smoky meats and satisfying sides, including brisket, pulled pork, Texas hot links, collard greens, mac and cheese, corn bread and more.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Real Deal Delivery</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/bludsos-bar-and-que-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.34414,34.08209,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Eastside Market Italian Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Eastside Market Italian Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90012 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2132502464" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(213) 250-2464</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.esmdeli.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.esmdeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Eastside+Market+Italian+Deli%2C+1013+Alpine+St%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90012&amp;ll=34.065134,-118.246496" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1013 Alpine St<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90012</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">D.A. Special</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Situated in L.A.&#x27;s original Little Italy, the Eastside Market Italian Deli has been serving Los Angelinos classic Italian dishes since 1929. Take note of the D.A. Special. Guy devoured every last bit of sausage, meatball, roast beef and pastrami on this sandwich of &amp;quot;incomparable deliciousness.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">L.A. Eats</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/eastside-market-italian-deli-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.24650,34.06513,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>La Tostaderia</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">La Tostaderia</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Los Angeles, CA 90013 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.grandcentralmarket.com/vendors/440/la-tostadera" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.grandcentralmarket.com/vendors/440/la-tostadera</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=La+Tostaderia%2C+317+S+Broadway%2C+Los+Angeles%2C+CA+90013&amp;ll=34.050822,-118.248935" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">317 S Broadway<br/>Los Angeles, CA 90013</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">For tostadas with a towering twist and more elevated Mexican classics head to La Tostaderia which is tucked away in Grand Central Market in L.A. The chef was born in Mexico and later went back to culinary school to learn more about flavor profiles and it shows. Guy was impressed by the tender octopus tostada and blown away by the cheesy shrimp burger.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ocean Coasts and Great Lakes</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/los-angeles/la-tostaderia-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.24893,34.05082,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Muertos Kitchen &amp; Lounge</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Muertos Kitchen &amp; Lounge</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bakersfield, CA 93301</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6613242557" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">661-324-2557</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Muertos-Kitchen-and-Lounge/427183267301272" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.facebook.com/pages/Muertos-Kitchen-and-Lounge/427183267301272</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Muertos+Kitchen+%26+Lounge%2C+1514+Wall+St%2C+Bakersfield%2C+CA+93301&amp;ll=35.375872,-119.019425" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1514 Wall St<br/>Bakersfield, CA 93301</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Popcorn Pork, Lamb Tacos</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This 19th-century firehouse serves eclectic dishes, including Basque-style Lamb Tacos with blue cheese, and crispy Popcorn Pork with chipotle dip.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Globe Tasting</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/bakersfield/muertos-kitchen-and-lounge-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.01942,35.37587,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Salty&#x27;s BBQ &amp; Catering</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Salty&#x27;s BBQ &amp; Catering</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bakersfield, CA 93312 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6615878437" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">661-587-8437</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://saltysbbq.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">saltysbbq.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Salty%27s+BBQ+%26+Catering%2C+9425+Rosedale+Hwy%2C+Bakersfield%2C+CA+93312&amp;ll=35.383215,-119.107513" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">9425 Rosedale Hwy<br/>Bakersfield, CA 93312</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Salty&#x27;s Special Sandwich, Tri-Tip, Pulled Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This &quot;real deal barbecue,&quot; including oak-grilled tri-tip, chicken and smoky pulled pork, is worth a road trip.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roadtrippin<br/>Fun in the Sun</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/bakersfield/saltys-bbq-and-catering-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.10751,35.38322,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Eight Noodle Shop</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Eight Noodle Shop</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Napa, CA 94559</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.eightnoodleshop.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.eightnoodleshop.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Eight+Noodle+Shop%2C+1408+Clay+St%2C+Napa%2C+CA+94559&amp;ll=38.298014,-122.290076" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1408 Clay St<br/>Napa, CA 94559</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Kimchi Fried Rice, Pork Ramen</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A this tiny spot in Napa, Chef and owner David Lu is putting out delicious Asian cuisine with fresh local ingredients. Guy loved the Kimchi Fried Rice with braised beef cheeks and the house-made ramen.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Bacon and BBQ</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/napa/eight-noodle-shop-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.29008,38.29801,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Aunt Mary&#x27;s Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Aunt Mary&#x27;s Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Oakland, CA 94609 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5106019227" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(510) 601-9227</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.auntmaryscafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.auntmaryscafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Aunt+Mary%27s+Cafe%2C+4307+Telegraph+Ave%2C+Oakland%2C+CA+94609&amp;ll=37.831861,-122.264167" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4307 Telegraph Ave<br/>Oakland, CA 94609</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Potlikker Gravy, Pain Perdue, Shrimp and Grits</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Texan native Jack Stewart came to California, he started an artisanal Southern comfort food diner. Guy downed the potato and collard green pancakes topped with Potlikker Gravy and enjoyed the French toast-like Pain Perdue. Try the shrimp and grits and kick it up a notch with Tabasco Gravy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Favorites With A Twist</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/oakland/aunt-marys-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-122.26417,37.83186,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>24th Street Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">24th Street Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bakersfield, CA 93301 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6613238801" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">661-323-8801</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://24thstreetcafe.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">24thstreetcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=24th+Street+Cafe%2C+1415+24th+St%2C+Bakersfield%2C+CA+93301&amp;ll=35.380830,-119.018060" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1415 24th St<br/>Bakersfield, CA 93301</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chili, Pumpkin Pancakes</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This retro diner excels at comfort classics, including chili, biscuits, pancakes and burgers.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Sweet, Savory and Saucy</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/bakersfield/24th-street-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.01806,35.38083,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>KC Steakhouse</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">KC Steakhouse</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bakersfield, CA 93301 &middot; &#9733; 4.5 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6613229910" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">661-322-9910</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.kcsteakhouse.net" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.kcsteakhouse.net</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=KC+Steakhouse%2C+2515+F+St%2C+Bakersfield%2C+CA+93301&amp;ll=35.382268,-119.023770" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2515 F St<br/>Bakersfield, CA 93301</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lobster Mac &amp; Cheese, Stuffed Pork Chops</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Open since 1939, this retro steakhouse serves down-home classics like Chicken Piccata, Stuffed Pork Chops and Lobster Mac &amp;amp; Cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Atlantic to Pacific</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/bakersfield/kc-steakhouse-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.02377,35.38227,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Moo Creamery</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Moo Creamery</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bakersfield, CA 93309 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6618611130" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">661-861-1130</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.moocreamery.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.moocreamery.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Moo+Creamery%2C+4885+Truxtun+Ave%2C+Bakersfield%2C+CA+93309&amp;ll=35.370585,-119.056076" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4885 Truxtun Ave<br/>Bakersfield, CA 93309</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">PB&amp;B Burger, Bacon Ice Cream</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tucked into an industrial park near the railroad tracks, this ice cream shop and restaurant serves creative burgers - including a&amp;nbsp;peanut butter-topped burger with bacon jam - and homemade ice cream.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ultimate Bacon Fest<br/>Sweet, Savory and Saucy</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/bakersfield/moo-creamery-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.05608,35.37059,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mad Greek Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mad Greek Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Baker, CA 92309 &middot; &#9733; 3.4 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:7607334354" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(760) 733-4354</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.themadgreekcafe.com/index.html" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.themadgreekcafe.com/index.html</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mad+Greek+Restaurant%2C+72112+Baker+Blvd%2C+Baker%2C+CA+92309&amp;ll=35.266788,-116.074120" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">72112 Baker Blvd<br/>Baker, CA 92309</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Gyros</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The middle of the desert might not seem like the best place to open a Greek diner, but the Mad Greek Restaurant has been attracting crowds for over 20 years. Chef Larry Dabour uses his grandmother&#x27;s recipes for specialties like gyros, spanakopita (spinach pie) and shawarma - Guy&#x27;s favorite.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Classics<br/>Triple-D Classics</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/baker/mad-greeks-diner-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-116.07412,35.26679,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pyrenees Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pyrenees Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bakersfield, CA 93305</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6613230053" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">661-323-0053</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/bakersfield/pyrenees-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/bakersfield/pyrenees-cafe-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pyrenees+Cafe%2C+601+Sumner+St%2C+Bakersfield%2C+CA+93305&amp;ll=35.376931,-118.994367" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">601 Sumner St<br/>Bakersfield, CA 93305</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Fried Garlic Chicken, Oxtail Stew</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Set just off the Southern Pacific Railroad in East Bakersfield, this local institution has served served excellent Basque dishes since the 1930s. Guy deemed the Fried Garlic Chicken &amp;quot;outstanding,&amp;quot; saying it would be the example if he ever served the dish.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">To Bakersfield and Beyond</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/bakersfield/pyrenees-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-118.99437,35.37693,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Athena&#x27;s Greek Cafe &amp; Bakery</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Athena&#x27;s Greek Cafe &amp; Bakery</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bakersfield, CA 93312 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6615882324" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">661-588-2324</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/bakersfield/athena-s-greek-cafe-and-bakery-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/bakersfield/athena-s-greek-cafe-and-bakery-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Athena%27s+Greek+Cafe+%26+Bakery%2C+2900+Calloway+Dr%2C+Bakersfield%2C+CA+93312&amp;ll=35.386279,-119.109531" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2900 Calloway Dr<br/>Bakersfield, CA 93312</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dolmades, Beef Pasta</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This authentic Greek restaurant specializes in baked goods, hearty entries and beef-stuffed cabbage leaves in lemon sauce that Guy finds delicious.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">To Bakersfield and Beyond</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/bakersfield/athena-s-greek-cafe-and-bakery-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.10953,35.38628,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Flyway Brewing Company</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Flyway Brewing Company</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">North Little Rock, AR 72114</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://flywaybrewing.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">flywaybrewing.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Flyway+Brewing+Company%2C+314+Maple+St%2C+North+Little+Rock%2C+AR+72114&amp;ll=34.756753,-92.268841" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">314 Maple St<br/>North Little Rock, AR 72114</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Handmade Pretzels, Gumbo Cheese Fries</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This funky brew pub was dreamt up by two buddies that met in college. At first, Matt Foster and Jess McMullen&#x27;s brewery served pretzels with a variety of sauces. Later, they brought on Chef Georgina Jones to add dishes with a Southern-flair to the menu, like the soul-satisfying Gumbo Cheese Fries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pretzels, Pork and Paella</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ar/Flyway-brewing-company-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.26884,34.75675,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Mama Roomba</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Mama Roomba</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Bakersfield, CA 93301 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6613226262" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">661-322-6262</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mamaroomba.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mamaroomba.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Mama+Roomba%2C+1814+Eye+St%2C+Bakersfield%2C+CA+93301&amp;ll=35.375696,-119.019842" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1814 Eye St<br/>Bakersfield, CA 93301</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Latin Fried Chicken</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This eclectic Bakersfield restaurant can satisfy multiple cravings with its&amp;nbsp;Mexican, South American and Caribbean dishes, including habanero-spiced fried chicken.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Atlantic to Pacific</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ca/bakersfield/mama-roomba-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-119.01984,35.37570,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Los Taquitos Mexican Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Los Taquitos Mexican Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Phoenix 85044 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (16 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4807534370" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(480) 753-4370</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.ltgrill.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.ltgrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Los+Taquitos+Mexican+Grill%2C+4747+E+Elliot+Rd%2C+Phoenix+85044&amp;ll=33.348062,-111.982021" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4747 E Elliot Rd<br/>Phoenix 85044</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Tacos, Camarones a La Diabla</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At this Mexican restaurant, five sisters and a brother are pumping out 300 tacos a day the way Mom used to do it. Guy was head over heels for the carnita taco, calling it &quot;killer.&quot; The savory Bombero Sauce was &quot;excellent&quot; as well; he appreciated the spicy kick it gave to the Bombero Burrito.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Mex to the Max<br/>Triple D Nation: Chili Three Ways<br/>All Over the Map</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/phoenix/los-taquitos-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.98202,33.34806,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Tacos Chiwas</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Tacos Chiwas</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Phoenix 80202 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6023588830" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">602-358-8830</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.tacoschiwas.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tacoschiwas.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Tacos+Chiwas%2C+1923+East+McDowell+Rd%2C+Phoenix+80202&amp;ll=33.465545,-112.040096" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1923 East McDowell Rd<br/>Phoenix 80202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Barbacoa Tacos, Gorditas</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Comin&#x27; from All Over the Map<br/>Bird and Beef</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/phoenix/tacos-chiwas-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.04010,33.46554,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Duce</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Duce</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Phoenix, AZ 85004 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6028663823" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">602-866-3823</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://theducephx.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">theducephx.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Duce%2C+525+S+Central+Ave%2C+Phoenix%2C+AZ+85004&amp;ll=33.442484,-112.073576" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">525 S Central Ave<br/>Phoenix, AZ 85004</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beer Can Chicken, Mac &amp; Cheese Muffins, S&#x27;mores Cheesecake</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">No need to feel guilty about indulging in the savory delights at The Duce in Phoenix - there&#x27;s a gym connected to the restaurant for getting back into shape afterward. So go ahead and feast on comfort food faves like Beer Can Chicken, S&#x27;mores Cheesecake and Mac &amp;amp; Cheese Muffins (they blew Guy away).</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Pound Cake to Pot Pie<br/>Wildest Joints</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/phoenix/the-duce" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.07358,33.44248,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Fold: Botanas &amp; Bar</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Fold: Botanas &amp; Bar</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Little Rock, AR 72202</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://thefoldlr.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">thefoldlr.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Fold%3A+Botanas+%26+Bar%2C+3501+Old+Cantrell+Rd%2C+Little+Rock%2C+AR+72202&amp;ll=34.764974,-92.311295" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3501 Old Cantrell Rd<br/>Little Rock, AR 72202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bison Burrito, Cornmeal Waffle</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This restaurant is serving up righteous Mexican comfort food in a retro service station in Little Rock. The unique joint was the brainchild of a silent partner who brought together co-owner Bart Barlogi and co-owner Chef Alex Smith. The dynamite Bison Burrito is stuffed with ground bison, black beans, caramelized onions and lots of pepper jack cheese and topped with house-made ranchero sauce.For brunch, try their savory cornmeal waffles topped with braised pork, salsa verde, queso fresco and a fried egg.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Meaty Mashup</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ar/little-rock/the-fold-botanas-and-bar-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.31130,34.76497,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>La Terraza Rum &amp; Lounge</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">La Terraza Rum &amp; Lounge</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Little Rock, AR 72205</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ar/little-rock/la-terraza-rum-lounge-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ar/little-rock/la-terraza-rum-lounge-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=La+Terraza+Rum+%26+Lounge%2C+3000+Kavanaugh+Blvd%2C+Little+Rock%2C+AR+72205&amp;ll=34.758871,-92.326585" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3000 Kavanaugh Blvd<br/>Little Rock, AR 72205</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pernil al Horno, Paella</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Get a seat outside on the beautiful, tree-lined terrace at Chef Armando Bolanos&#x27;s spot in Little Rock. For taste of authentic Venezuelan cuisine, try the slow-roasted Pernil al Horno, which is drenched in a thick demi-glace gravy and accompanied by killerbacon-studded beans and rice. Also try the seafood-packed, Valencian-style paella which is served tableside.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pretzels, Pork and Paella</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ar/little-rock/la-terraza-rum-lounge-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.32658,34.75887,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Root Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Root Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Little Rock, AR 72202 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.therootcafe.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.therootcafe.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Root+Cafe%2C+1500+Main+St%2C+Little+Rock%2C+AR+72202&amp;ll=34.734262,-92.273142" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1500 Main St<br/>Little Rock, AR 72202</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pimento Cheeseburger, Old World-Style Bratwurst</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jack and Corri Sundell are taking the food business and DIY to a whole new level at their farm-to-table spot in Little Rock. They grind the meat in house for the Pimento Cheeseburger and handle it as little as possible before it&#x27;s cooked, then top it with spicy pimento cheese, 14-day, house-made sweet pickles and garlic vinaigrette. Guy also loved the Old World-Style Bratwurst which is made by hand and then topped with house-fermented slaw.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Bacon and BBQ</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ar/little-rock/the-root-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.27314,34.73426,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bruno&#x27;s Little Italy</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bruno&#x27;s Little Italy</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Little Rock, AR 72201</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.brunoslittleitaly.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.brunoslittleitaly.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bruno%27s+Little+Italy%2C+310+Main+St%2C+Little+Rock%2C+AR+72201&amp;ll=34.745954,-92.270834" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">310 Main St<br/>Little Rock, AR 72201</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lasagna Imbotito, Toasted Ravioli</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brothers Vince Bruno and Gio Bruno are keeping tradition alive at the Italian restaurant that their father started in 1948 in Little Rock. Generations of families return to this old-school joint where the classic Italian dishes hardly ever change. Guy loved the handmade Toasted Ravioli and the towering Lasagna Imbotito.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Big Burgers to Little Italy</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ar/little-rock/brunos-little-italy-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-92.27083,34.74595,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Forno Rosso Pizzeria &amp; Catering</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Forno Rosso Pizzeria &amp; Catering</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Juneau 99801</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.fornorossoalaska.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fornorossoalaska.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Forno+Rosso+Pizzeria+%26+Catering%2C+5346+Commercial+Blvd%2C+Juneau+99801&amp;ll=58.357709,-134.484036" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">5346 Commercial Blvd<br/>Juneau 99801</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Reinbeer Pizza, Nakenna Special</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This pizzeria isn&#x27;t trying to sling New York or Chicago-style pies: their menu is distinctly Alaskan. Guy and Hunter tried the Reinbeer pie, which is made from light, house-made dough topped white sauce, red onion, jarlsberg cheese and Alaskan reindeer sausage that have been marinated in an amber ale. Another standout is the Nakenna special, a pie topped with melty fresh mozzarella and prosciutto.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eating Alaska</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/juneau/forno-rosso-pizzeria-and-catering-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-134.48404,58.35771,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Zerelda&#x27;s Bistro</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Zerelda&#x27;s Bistro</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Juneau, AK 99801 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.zereldasbistro.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.zereldasbistro.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Zerelda%27s+Bistro%2C+9351+Glacier+Highway%2C+Juneau%2C+AK+99801&amp;ll=58.366755,-134.591236" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">9351 Glacier Highway<br/>Juneau, AK 99801</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Brisket Pho, Smoked Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Chef-Owner Abby LaForce met her husband Jeremy Barnett, they mashed up her love for Asian food with his love for barbeque, and Zerelda&#x27;s Bistro was born. Diners flock here for the fun mash-ups, like the Brisket Pho: Brisket is smoked for more than three hours until its tender, and is then added to a house-made pho broth with rice noodles, white and green onions, and sesame oil. &quot;That smoke kick is killer,&quot; Guy said of the soup.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Northern Southern</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/juneau/zereldas-bistro-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-134.59124,58.36676,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>V&#x27;s Cellar Door</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">V&#x27;s Cellar Door</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Juneau, AK 99801 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://vscellardoor.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">vscellardoor.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=V%27s+Cellar+Door%2C+222+Seward+St%2C+Juneau%2C+AK+99801&amp;ll=58.301239,-134.408456" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">222 Seward St<br/>Juneau, AK 99801</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Korean Chicken Fusion Nachos, Korean Short Ribs</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This unique fusion spot serves up a mix of Mexican-Korean dishes inspired by the time owner Venietia Santana spent living in Mexico City. Hunter and Guy had the Korean Chicken Fusion Nachos, which showcase the best of both cuisines: Chips are piled high with cheese and beans before they&#x27;re topped with tangy marinated chicken. The mouthwatering dish is finished with a scoop of guacamole and a drizzle of sour cream and fusion sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eating Alaska</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/juneau/vs-cellar-door-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-134.40846,58.30124,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pucker Wilson&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pucker Wilson&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Juneau, AK 99801</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.puckerwilsons.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.puckerwilsons.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pucker+Wilson%27s%2C+311+Whittier+St%2C+Juneau%2C+AK+99801&amp;ll=58.299579,-134.414133" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">311 Whittier St<br/>Juneau, AK 99801</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Philly Cheesesteak, Cowboy Sundae</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">After a stint living in Australia, owner Chad Edwards moved back to Juneau to open this funky truck-even in the dead of winter, people line up down the street for his food. Guy and Hunter loved his unconventional takes on classic sandwiches, like the Philly Cheesesteak served on ciabatta instead of a traditional hoagie. They also raved about the Cowboy Sundae, Pucker Wilson&#x27;s take on poutine: barbeque pulled pork and savory slaw served on a bed of hand-cut fries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eating Alaska</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/juneau/pucker-wilsons-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-134.41413,58.29958,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Silver Gulch Brewing and Bottling Co.</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Silver Gulch Brewing and Bottling Co.</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fox, AK 99712</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9074522739" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">907-452-2739</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.silvergulch.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.silvergulch.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Silver+Gulch+Brewing+and+Bottling+Co.%2C+2195+Old+Steese+Highway%2C+Fox%2C+AK+99712&amp;ll=64.978019,-147.543568" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2195 Old Steese Highway<br/>Fox, AK 99712</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beer, Ale Battered Onion Rings, Stout BBQ Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Join Guy at the Silver Gulch Brewery in Fox, AK, the Northernmost brewery in the country. The restaurant serves everything from sandwiches to salads to pizzas in a friendly, casual atmosphere. Try the Porter Beer Cheese Soup.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners, Drive-Ins &amp; Dives: A North Pole Christmas</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/fox/silver-gulch-brewing-and-bottling-co-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-147.54357,64.97802,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Salty&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Salty&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fairbanks, AK 99701</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9074574992" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">907-457-4992</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.saltysonsecond.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.saltysonsecond.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Salty%27s%2C+706+2nd+Ave%2C+Fairbanks%2C+AK+99701&amp;ll=64.843640,-147.724594" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">706 2nd Ave<br/>Fairbanks, AK 99701</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Two friends, with more than thirty years of combined food experience, set out to change the culture of great dining in Fairbanks. Salty&#x27;s offers homemade food, brunch, a bar and cozy ambience.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Alaskan Adventure</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/fairbanks/salty-s-on-2nd" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-147.72459,64.84364,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Hungry Robot</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Hungry Robot</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fairbanks, AK 99701</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9073478117" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(907) 347 - 8117  </a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.thehungryrobot.org/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thehungryrobot.org</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Hungry+Robot%2C+910+Old+Steese+Hwy.%2C+Fairbanks%2C+AK+99701&amp;ll=64.852140,-147.690680" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">910 Old Steese Hwy.<br/>Fairbanks, AK 99701</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Hungry Robot makes theirdough and sauces from scratch, prepares all pizzas to order and bakes them in 90 seconds in their wood fired oven.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spicin&#x27; Things Up</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/fairbanks/the-hungry-robot" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-147.69068,64.85214,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Jazz Bistro</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Jazz Bistro</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fairbanks, AK 99701 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9073283663" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">907-328-3663</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.jazzbistroon4th.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.jazzbistroon4th.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Jazz+Bistro%2C+527+4th+Avenue%2C+Fairbanks%2C+AK+99701&amp;ll=64.842367,-147.718001" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">527 4th Avenue<br/>Fairbanks, AK 99701</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Jazz Bistro on 4th specializes in Cuban and Latin cuisine and featureAfro Cuban and Latin live jazz performances.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Alaskan Adventure</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/fairbanks/jazz-bistro-on-4th" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-147.71800,64.84237,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Country Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Country Cafe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">North Pole, AK 99705 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9074888454" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">907-488-8454</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/north-pole/country-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/north-pole/country-cafe-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Country+Cafe%2C+235+North+Santa+Claus+Ln.%2C+North+Pole%2C+AK+99705&amp;ll=64.755954,-147.353118" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">235 North Santa Claus Ln.<br/>North Pole, AK 99705</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Holiday Turkey Dinner, Cranberry-Glazed Ham</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The North Pole&#x27;s Country Cafe has enough holiday giddyup for all nine reindeer. Guy was ready for a long winter&#x27;s nap after polishing off their butter-basted Turkey Dinner with homemade stuffing. Eating local? Order the Cranberry-Glazed Ham, lacquered with wild Alaskan cranberry sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners, Drive-Ins &amp; Dives: A North Pole Christmas</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/north-pole/country-cafe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-147.35312,64.75595,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Pagoda Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Pagoda Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">North Pole 99705 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9074883338" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(907) 488-3338</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.pagodanorthpole.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.pagodanorthpole.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Pagoda+Restaurant%2C+431+Santa+Claus+Lane%2C+North+Pole+99705&amp;ll=64.758811,-147.354078" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">431 Santa Claus Lane<br/>North Pole 99705</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pagoda Steak, Alaskan King Crab Legs with Ginger, Walnut Shrimp</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">It&#x27;s a Triple D holiday essential to relive the famous Chinese restaurant dinner scene from &#x27;A Christmas Story. Pagoda Restaurant loads Hollywood flavor into every nook and cranny of their tangy Alaskan King Crab Legs with Ginger. Beefing up this holiday? Black peppery Pagoda Steak is your ticket.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Tastier at Home<br/>Diners, Drive-Ins &amp; Dives: A North Pole Christmas</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/north-pole/pagoda-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-147.35408,64.75881,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Elf&#x27;s Den Restaurant &amp; Lounge</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Elf&#x27;s Den Restaurant &amp; Lounge</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">North Pole, AK 99705 &middot; &#9733; 3.2 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9074883268" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">907-488-3268</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/north-pole/elfs-den-restaurant-lounge-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/north-pole/elfs-den-restaurant-lounge-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Elf%27s+Den+Restaurant+%26+Lounge%2C+2556+Mistletoe+Rd%2C+North+Pole%2C+AK+99705&amp;ll=64.750735,-147.328455" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2556 Mistletoe Rd<br/>North Pole, AK 99705</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Almond-Crusted Beef Tournedo with Brown Gravy and Bearnaise, Reindeer Sausage Hoagie</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">On Food Network&#x27;s Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, host Guy Fieri, discovers Elf&#x27;s Den Restaurant &amp; Lounge in North Pole, AK, where they&#x27;re dishing out hearty American classics in a rustic setting.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners, Drive-Ins &amp; Dives: A North Pole Christmas</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/north-pole/elfs-den-restaurant-lounge-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-147.32845,64.75074,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cookie Jar Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cookie Jar Restaurant</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fairbanks, AK 99701 &middot; &#9733; 3.5 (12 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9074798319" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(907) 479-8319</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.cookiejarfairbanks.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.cookiejarfairbanks.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cookie+Jar+Restaurant%2C+1006+Cadillac+Ct.%2C+Fairbanks%2C+AK+99701&amp;ll=64.854564,-147.745337" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1006 Cadillac Ct.<br/>Fairbanks, AK 99701</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Prime Rib, Cinnamon Roll Wreath, Ginger Snap Cookies</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Cookie Jar started with just sweets back in 1986. Today their bag full of tricks has way more than gingersnaps, snickerdoodles and snowballs (oh, my!). Tender Prime Rib Au Jus had Guy melting in his chair - the perfect spot to settle in with one of their glazed holiday Cinnamon Roll Wreaths.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Diners, Drive-Ins &amp; Dives: A North Pole Christmas</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/fairbanks/cookie-jar-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-147.74534,64.85456,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Big Daddy&#x27;s BBQ &amp; Banquet</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Big Daddy&#x27;s BBQ &amp; Banquet</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fairbanks, AK 99701 &middot; &#9733; 3.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9074522501" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(907) 452-2501</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://bigdaddysbarb-q.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">bigdaddysbarb-q.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Big+Daddy%27s+BBQ+%26+Banquet%2C+107+Wickersham+St.%2C+Fairbanks%2C+AK+99701&amp;ll=64.843861,-147.725999" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">107 Wickersham St.<br/>Fairbanks, AK 99701</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Smoked Turkey, Beef Brisket</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Big Daddy&#x27;s BBQ &amp; Banquet, they&#x27;re serving the &quot;northern most southern barbecue.&quot; Guy&#x27;s DDD visit to the Fairbanks, Ala. favorite wasn&#x27;t complete without sampling the finger-licking Arkansas-style ribs and smoked turkeys from Chef Harold Groetsema, aka Big Daddy.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Holiday Hoopla<br/>Diners, Drive-Ins &amp; Dives: A North Pole Christmas</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/fairbanks/big-daddys-bbq-banquet-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-147.72600,64.84386,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Hari Om</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Hari Om</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fairbanks, AK 99701</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9073283218" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(907) 328-3218</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/fairbanks/hari-om-cuisine-of-india" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/fairbanks/hari-om-cuisine-of-india</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Hari+Om%2C+1528+S.+Cushman+St.%2C+Fairbanks%2C+AK+99701&amp;ll=64.834284,-147.717323" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1528 S. Cushman St.<br/>Fairbanks, AK 99701</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Hari Om Cuisine of India combines cuisine, flavors and cooking techniques from the North-West Frontier of India to create dishes that are fresh and authentic.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Savory Meat and a Little Sweet</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/fairbanks/hari-om-cuisine-of-india" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-147.71732,64.83428,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Paradise Valley Burger Co.</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Paradise Valley Burger Co.</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Scottsdale, AZ 85260 &middot; &#9733; 4.8 (6 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6025354930" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(602) 535-4930</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.paradisevalleyburgercompany.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.paradisevalleyburgercompany.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Paradise+Valley+Burger+Co.%2C+15689+North+Hayden+Rd.%2C+Scottsdale%2C+AZ+85260&amp;ll=33.627419,-111.895280" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">15689 North Hayden Rd.<br/>Scottsdale, AZ 85260</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Country Fried Burger; Booze Burger</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When it comes to burgers, this Phoenix institution knows no bounds. Paradise Valley Burger Co.&#x27;s patties are exceptionally creative and universally appealing. Guy tried the country-fried burger, which features a deep-fried patty, green chili gravy and crisp onions.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Arizona All-Stars<br/>Takeout: Best of the West Roundup</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/phoenix/paradise-valley-burger-co" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.89528,33.62742,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Joe&#x27;s Farm Grill</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Joe&#x27;s Farm Grill</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Gilbert, AZ 85296 &middot; &#9733; 3.6 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4805634745" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(480) 563-4745</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.joesfarmgrill.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.joesfarmgrill.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Joe%27s+Farm+Grill%2C+3000+East+Ray+Rd.+Bldg.+1%2C+Gilbert%2C+AZ+85296&amp;ll=33.321663,-111.726252" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">3000 East Ray Rd. Bldg. 1<br/>Gilbert, AZ 85296</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Burgers, Ahi Tuna Burger, Pizza, Sandwiches</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Not a whole lot of burger joints can boast about having farm-fresh ingredients, but then again, most burger joints don&#x27;t have a whole produce farm on their property either. At Joe&#x27;s Farm Grill, try the ahi tuna burger with Asian slaw; Guy thought it was &#x27;&#x27;out-of-bounds ahi.&#x27;&#x27;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Real Deal Fast Food<br/>Best of the West<br/>Triple D Nation: Where&#x27;s the Beef?</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/gilbert/joes-farm-grill-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.72625,33.32166,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sal&#x27;s Gilbert Pizza</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sal&#x27;s Gilbert Pizza</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Gilbert, AZ 85296 &middot; &#9733; 4.9 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4806332226" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">480-633-2226</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://gilbertpizzaaz.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">gilbertpizzaaz.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sal%27s+Gilbert+Pizza%2C+1150+S+Gilbert+Rd%2C+Gilbert%2C+AZ+85296&amp;ll=33.329015,-111.790665" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1150 S Gilbert Rd<br/>Gilbert, AZ 85296</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ziti Pizza, Lasagna Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This pizzeria is a slice of New Yorkin the middle of the desert. Some of the signature pizzas are Italian mash-ups, putting classics like lasagna, ziti and spaghetti and meatballs on top of pies.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Roadtrippin</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/gilbert/sals-gilbert-pizza-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.79067,33.32902,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Fat Olives</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Fat Olives</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Flagstaff 86004 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9288530056" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">928-853-0056</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.fatolivesflagstaff.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.fatolivesflagstaff.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Fat+Olives%2C+2308+E+Route+66%2C+Flagstaff+86004&amp;ll=35.205164,-111.614710" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2308 E Route 66<br/>Flagstaff 86004</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Belgio Dulce Pizza, Kenai Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Fat Olives, Chef and Owner John Conley is making true Neapolitan pizza using an oven handcrafted in Italy, handmade mozzarella and the finest &quot;00&quot; Caputo flour. The Belgio Dulce Pizza is a creative mix of brussels sprouts, house-made Calabrian chile oil, honey and pistachios on a cream base.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Flavortown Comes Home<br/>Old Faces, New Places</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/flagstaff/fat-olives-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.61471,35.20516,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Salsa Brava</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Salsa Brava</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Flagstaff, AZ 86004 &middot; &#9733; 3.1 (14 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9287795293" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(928) 779-5293</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.salsabravaflagstaff.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.salsabravaflagstaff.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Salsa+Brava%2C+2220+E+Route+66%2C+Flagstaff%2C+AZ+86004&amp;ll=35.203905,-111.615713" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2220 E Route 66<br/>Flagstaff, AZ 86004</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Navajo Taco, Tableside Guacamole, Coconut Shrimp</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you want to eat Chef John Conley&#x27;s giant Navajo Taco, you can use your fork and knife, or follow Guy&#x27;s advice and dig in with your hands. The &quot;King-Kong-meets-popover&quot; tacos are Chef John&#x27;s idea of Mexican cuisine that uses big flavors like cilantro cream sauce, roasted pork and fresh salsa.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Real Deal Mexican<br/>Return to Route 66</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/flagstaff/salsa-brava-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.61571,35.20391,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Inca&#x27;s Peruvian Cuisine</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Inca&#x27;s Peruvian Cuisine</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tucson, AZ 85750 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.incasperuviancuisine.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.incasperuviancuisine.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Inca%27s+Peruvian+Cuisine%2C+6878+E+Sunrise+Dr%2C+Tucson%2C+AZ+85750&amp;ll=32.202120,-110.759941" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6878 E Sunrise Dr<br/>Tucson, AZ 85750</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Seco de Carne con Frijoles, Lomo Saltado</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Head to Inca&#x27;s Peruvian Cuisine for a first-class culinary ticket to Peru in Tucson. Try the Seco de Carne con Frijoles, beef braised in cilantro and Peruvian sauce, and the Lomo Saltado, marinated beef tenderloin sauteed with onions and tomatoes and poured over crispy fries.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pizza, Pork and Peru</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/tucson/incas-peruvian-cuisine-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-110.75994,32.20212,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Brandy&#x27;s Restaurant &amp; Bakery</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Brandy&#x27;s Restaurant &amp; Bakery</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Flagstaff, AZ 86004 &middot; &#9733; 3.8 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:9287792187" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(928) 779-2187</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.brandysrestaurant.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.brandysrestaurant.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Brandy%27s+Restaurant+%26+Bakery%2C+1500+E+Cedar+Ave%2C+Flagstaff%2C+AZ+86004&amp;ll=35.219215,-111.620667" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1500 E Cedar Ave<br/>Flagstaff, AZ 86004</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Beef Stew</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Brandy&#x27;s, an eclectic range of food with a homey feel is being served. According to Guy, the Southwestern beef stew was a &amp;quot;cornucopia of flavors.&amp;quot; The flat iron steak with chimichurri and a sweet potato corn cake did not disappoint either. Locals enjoy the currant fish cakes too.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Their Own Way</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/flagstaff/brandys-restaurant-bakery-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.62067,35.21921,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Renee&#x27;s Organic Oven</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Renee&#x27;s Organic Oven</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tucson, AZ 85715 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5208860484" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">520-886-0484</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.reneesorganicoven.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.reneesorganicoven.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Renee%27s+Organic+Oven%2C+7065+E+Tanque+Verde+Rd%2C+Tucson%2C+AZ+85715&amp;ll=32.244129,-110.856296" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7065 E Tanque Verde Rd<br/>Tucson, AZ 85715</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Spinach Dip Calzone, The Tailored Tony</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Renee&#x27;s Organic Oven, husband and wife team Steve and Renee Kreager are serving up Italian classics their own way. The Tailored Tony is like a Sloppy Joe made for a healthier palate. For this open-faced focaccia local organic beef is infused with tomatoes and topped with melted provolone and roasted red peppers. Also try the Spinach Dip Calzone. Guy described it as a cross between the best jalapeno popper you&#x27;ve ever had, a gigantic perogi and a chicken sandwich.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Rollin&#x27; in the Dough</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/tucson/renees-organic-oven-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-110.85630,32.24413,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Cafe Tumerico</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Cafe Tumerico</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tucson 85716 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5202406947" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(520) 240-6947</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.tumerico.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.tumerico.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Cafe+Tumerico%2C+2526+E.+6th+St%2C+Tucson+85716&amp;ll=32.227700,-110.934689" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2526 E. 6th St<br/>Tucson 85716</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Nopalitos Tacos, Carne Asada Plate</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When Wendy Garcia moved to the states from Mexico she ditched the carnivore life and starting cooking things her own way. She uses fried jackfruit for her Carne Asada plate and serves it with eggplant chicharron and crispy soy chorizo. The dish was so good Guy had to call his mother and tell her all about it. Also try the cactus tacos. Nopalitos are cooked down with cashew sauce and loaded into tortillas with cabbage and pickle veggies and topped with cashew cream.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Lights-Out Latin</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/tucson/cafe-tumerico-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-110.93469,32.22770,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Thumb</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Thumb</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Scottsdale 85260 &middot; &#9733; 4.4 (9 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4805138186" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(480) 513-8186</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.thethumb.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.thethumb.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Thumb%2C+9393+East+Bell+Rd.%2C+Scottsdale+85260&amp;ll=33.639369,-111.879258" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">9393 East Bell Rd.<br/>Scottsdale 85260</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Pigs and Grits</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The Thumbis a gas station, car wash, craft shop, wine cellar and competition-style barbecue restaurant, all in one. Chef and owner Kipp Lassetter is a former surgeon, and here he runs a fine operation. Chicken, pork and brisket are all smoked in-house. Try the smoked and fried pork over creamy grits with jalapeno bacon.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Arizona All-Stars</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/scottsdale/toms-thumb" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.87926,33.63937,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Slanted Rice Vietnamese Bistro</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Slanted Rice Vietnamese Bistro</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Scottsdale, AZ 85250 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4806963116" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">480-696-3116</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.slantedrice.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.slantedrice.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Slanted+Rice+Vietnamese+Bistro%2C+6149+N.+Scottsdale+Rd.%2C+Scottsdale%2C+AZ+85250&amp;ll=33.527635,-111.924585" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6149 N. Scottsdale Rd.<br/>Scottsdale, AZ 85250</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Crispy Clay Pot, Crispy Pork Egg Rolls</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">A native of Vietnam, chef and owner Hue Tran describes the food at Slanted Rice Vietnamese Bistro as 90% Vietnamese and 10% fusion. Don&#x27;t miss the vegetable packed egg rolls rolled in lettuce and fresh mint and served with a spicy-sweet vinaigrette.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Poutine, Pizza and Pork</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/scottsdale/slanted-rice-vietnamese-bistro-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.92458,33.52763,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Perk Eatery</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Perk Eatery</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Scottsdale, AZ 85254 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (5 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4809986026" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(480) 998-6026</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.perkeatery.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.perkeatery.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Perk+Eatery%2C+6501+E+Greenway+Pkwy+%23159%2C+Scottsdale%2C+AZ+85254&amp;ll=33.624963,-111.941890" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">6501 E Greenway Pkwy #159<br/>Scottsdale, AZ 85254</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Breakfast Enchiladas, Chicken over the coup, Wine Country French Toast</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">If you&#x27;re craving a classic American breakfast with a Southwest twist, visit Perk Eatery. The tender pork shoulder in the breakfast enchiladas impressed Guy, as did the gravy over crispy sausage and sage stuffing. Locals enjoy the Wine Country French Toast with roasted grapes and Brie cheese.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dynamic Duos</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/scottsdale/perk-eatery-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.94189,33.62496,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Zemam&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Zemam&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Tucson, AZ 85716 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:5203239928" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">520-323-9928</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="www.zemams.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.zemams.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Zemam%27s%2C+2731+E.+Broadway+Blvd%2C+Tucson%2C+AZ+85716&amp;ll=32.221591,-110.931827" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2731 E. Broadway Blvd<br/>Tucson, AZ 85716</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Yedero Wat, Yegomen Alicha</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and Owner Amanuel Gebremariam is bringing the bold flavors and traditions of East Africa straight to Arizona. Guy loved everything saying, &quot;each one of the dishes is individually its own little song and what comes together is the Ethiopian musical.&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">International Intrigue</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/tucson/zemans-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-110.93183,32.22159,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Panini Pete&#x27;s</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Panini Pete&#x27;s</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fairhope 36526 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2519290122" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(251) 929-0122</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.paninipetes.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.paninipetes.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Panini+Pete%27s%2C+42+1%2F2+South+Section+St%2C+Fairhope+36526&amp;ll=30.522109,-87.902952" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">42 1/2 South Section St<br/>Fairhope 36526</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Italian Caprese Panini, Homemade Mozzarella, Turkey Panini</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Anyone looking for a fast-food restaurant that is a little more upscale than just burgers and fries should check out Panini Pete&#x27;s in Alabama. The Italian caprese panini is made with fresh mozzarella and homemade dressing, and the turkey panini has some of the most tender turkey Guy&#x27;s ever tried.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Real Deal Fast Food<br/>Takeout: Flavortown Comes Home</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/al/fairhope/panini-petes-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.90295,30.52211,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Sunset Pointe</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Sunset Pointe</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fairhope 36532 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2519907766" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">251-990-7766</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.sunsetpointefairhope.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.sunsetpointefairhope.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Sunset+Pointe%2C+831+N.+Section+St%2C+Fairhope+36532&amp;ll=30.541898,-87.898354" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">831 N. Section St<br/>Fairhope 36532</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Eastern Shore Bouillabaisse, Gulf Snapper Throats</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Chef and Owner Pete Blohme is making show-stopping seafood in Alabama including an amazing bouillabaisse and a dish with a prized cut of meat from red snapper. He is also the chef and owner of one of Guy&#x27;s other favorite joints, Panini Pete&#x27;s.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Old Faces, New Places<br/>Takeout: Flavortown Comes Home</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/al/fairhope/sunset-pointe-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.89835,30.54190,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Gumbo Shack</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Gumbo Shack</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Fairhope, AL 36532 &middot; &#9733; 2.4 (7 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2519284100" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">251-928-4100</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://gumboshackfairhope.com/index.php" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">gumboshackfairhope.com/index.php</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Gumbo+Shack%2C+212+1%2F2+Fairhope+Ave.%2C+Fairhope%2C+AL+36532&amp;ll=30.523008,-87.906010" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">212 1/2 Fairhope Ave.<br/>Fairhope, AL 36532</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Homemade Gumbo, Spicy Crawfish Boil, Red Beans and Rice</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">When you&#x27;re hungry for serious Creole food, head on down to Gumbo Shack. The local favorite has bands playing every weekend, gumbo ranked #6 on Alabama&#x27;s Top 100 Foods to Eat Before You Die, and crawfish so spicy Guy Fieri almost couldn&#x27;t handle it.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bar Food</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/al/fairhope/gumbo-shack-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.90601,30.52301,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Manci&#x27;s Antique Club</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Manci&#x27;s Antique Club</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Daphne, AL 36526 &middot; &#9733; 3.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:2516269917" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(251) 626-9917</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.mancisantiqueclub.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.mancisantiqueclub.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Manci%27s+Antique+Club%2C+1715+Main+St%2C+Daphne%2C+AL+36526&amp;ll=30.603497,-87.902858" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">1715 Main St<br/>Daphne, AL 36526</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Shrimp Po&#x27; Boy, Soft Shell Crab Sandwich, Jazzy Burger, Jezebel Sauce</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Anyone looking to try a po&#x27; boy in Daphne, Alabama, should check out Manci&#x27;s Antique Club, a storied institution that started as a gas station in 1924. It&#x27;s currently owned by Gwen Manci and her husband, Alex, who serve Southern classics and other comfort food favorites. Guy was a fan of the shrimp po&#x27; boy and the Jazzy Burger, topped with Jezebel sauce - &#x27;&#x27;the craziest sauce I&#x27;ve ever had,&#x27;&#x27; Guy said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Small Town Sensations<br/>Better Than Ever</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/al/daphne/mancis-antique-club-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-87.90286,30.60350,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>DeFalco&#x27;s Italian Eatery, Grocery &amp; Deli</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">DeFalco&#x27;s Italian Eatery, Grocery &amp; Deli</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Scottsdale, AZ 85257 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (4 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4809908660" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(480) 990-8660</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.defalcosdeli.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.defalcosdeli.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=DeFalco%27s+Italian+Eatery%2C+Grocery+%26+Deli%2C+2334+N+Scottsdale+Rd%2C+Scottsdale%2C+AZ+85257&amp;ll=33.474068,-111.927033" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2334 N Scottsdale Rd<br/>Scottsdale, AZ 85257</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Italian Sausage, Centurion Calzone, Sausage With Peppers Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At DeFalco&#x27;s in Scottsdale, Ariz., the Italian sausage is made with a nearly century-old family recipe that has brought in locals for decades. This spice-laden delicacy is available in sandwich form as the star of the sausage with peppers option that left Guy impressed. The Centurion calzone truly is a meal fit for a warrior, with two layers of mozzarella and sliced sopressatta - Guy said it rivals most NYC delis.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">All Stacked Up<br/>Timeless Traditions</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/scottsdale/defalcos-italian-eatery-grocery-and-deli" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.92703,33.47407,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bootleggers Modern American Smokehouse</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bootleggers Modern American Smokehouse</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Scottsdale, AZ 85251 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (1 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4804049984" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">480-404-9984</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://bootleggerssmokehouse.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">bootleggerssmokehouse.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bootleggers+Modern+American+Smokehouse%2C+7217+E+1st+St%2C+Scottsdale%2C+AZ+85251&amp;ll=33.492001,-111.925606" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">7217 E 1st St<br/>Scottsdale, AZ 85251</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Boot Dumplings, French Dip Sandwich</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">ChefKevin Slade found his calling on the barbecue circuit. He infuses his American gastropub cuisine with real-deal smoked meat and kicked-up sauces. Try the crispy Boot Dumplings which are filled with smoked pork belly and shrimp and drizzled with a house-made mango-chipotle barbecue sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Breakfast, Brisket and Belly</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/scottsdale/bootleggers-modern-american-smokehouse-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.92561,33.49200,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Andreoli Italian Grocer</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Andreoli Italian Grocer</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Scottsdale 85258 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (3 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:4806141980" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">480-614-1980</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://andreoli-grocer.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">andreoli-grocer.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Andreoli+Italian+Grocer%2C+8880+E+Via+Linda%2C+Scottsdale+85258&amp;ll=33.569475,-111.889791" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">8880 E Via Linda<br/>Scottsdale 85258</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Prosciutto</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Andreoli&#x27;s is the kind of restaurant that makes Italians a little less homesick. This authentic Italian market not only sells imported goods - they make their own takes on international classics in-house. Here, fresh-cured prosciutto hangs in the walk-in, and bread bakes to crusty perfection in the wood-fired oven.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Takeout: Ordering All Kinds of Flavor<br/>Arizona All-Stars<br/>Triple D Nation: A Taste of Italy<br/>Incredible Italian</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/scottsdale/andreoli-italian-grocer" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.88979,33.56947,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Bun Daddy Food Truck</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Bun Daddy Food Truck</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Juneau 99801</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/juneau/bun-daddy-food-truck-restaurant" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/juneau/bun-daddy-food-truck-restaurant</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Bun+Daddy+Food+Truck%2C+350+Whittier+St%2C+Juneau+99801&amp;ll=58.299481,-134.413716" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">350 Whittier St<br/>Juneau 99801</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">The owners of this seasonal stand are thinking outside the bun-the bao bun, that is. Their entire kitchen is located in a renovated camper van, where they make just one item: Asian-style steamed buns stuffed with unique fillings, almost like a fusion taco. Guy loved the pork belly in the Belly of the Beast Bun. &quot;This is not your typical bun,&quot; he says. &quot;You&#x27;re rocking it!&quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">From Beef to Bao</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/juneau/bun-daddy-food-truck-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-134.41372,58.29948,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>In Bocca Al Lupo</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">In Bocca Al Lupo</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Juneau 99801</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.inboccaallupoak.com/" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.inboccaallupoak.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=In+Bocca+Al+Lupo%2C+120+2nd+St.%2C+Juneau+99801&amp;ll=58.301013,-134.408806" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">120 2nd St.<br/>Juneau 99801</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">King Crab Pappardelle, Salsiccia Pizza</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Guy never expected to find incredible Italian food in Juneau, Alaska, but that&#x27;s what they&#x27;re serving up here: Italian classics with an Alaskan twist, like the King Crab Pappardelle. House-made noodles are coated in a creamy bisque sauce, mixed with chunks of fresh crab and topped with lemon creme fresh. &quot;It&#x27;s two of my favorite things: crab bisque and a pasta dish,&quot; Guy said.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Cruisin&#x27; Capital Cities</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/ak/juneau/in-bocca-al-lupo-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-134.40881,58.30101,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Giuseppe&#x27;s On 28th</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Giuseppe&#x27;s On 28th</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Phoenix, AZ 85016 &middot; &#9733; 4.0 (10 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6023811237" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">(602) 381-1237</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.giuseppeson28th.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.giuseppeson28th.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Giuseppe%27s+On+28th%2C+2824+E+Indian+School+Rd%2C+Phoenix%2C+AZ+85016&amp;ll=33.496255,-112.020529" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2824 E Indian School Rd<br/>Phoenix, AZ 85016</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Bolognese Ragu, Pork Shanks, Osso Buco</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">At Giuseppe&#x27;s you&#x27;ll find a world-class musician turned chef who&#x27;s serving some authentic Italian food. Guy admitted that the Bolognese ragu with fresh made pasta was &quot;crazy good&quot; and better than his own. The &quot;super flavored&quot; pork shanks are a treat. He also enjoyed the osso buco done three ways.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Primetime Pork<br/>Homestyle</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/phoenix/giuseppes-italian-kitchen-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.02053,33.49626,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>The Wild Thaiger</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">The Wild Thaiger</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Phoenix 85004 &middot; &#9733; 5.0 (2 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6022418995" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">602-241-8995</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.wildthaiger.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.wildthaiger.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=The+Wild+Thaiger%2C+2631+N+Central+Ave%2C+Phoenix+85004&amp;ll=33.477909,-112.073382" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">2631 N Central Ave<br/>Phoenix 85004</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Dragon Eggz, Papaya Salad, Coconut Pork</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">This fiery Thai restaurant gets playful with spicy flavors and classic preparations, for dishes like Dragon Eggz - pork, crab and shrimp dumplings - and boar in chile sauce.</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Amazing Asian<br/>Globe Tasting<br/>Takeout: Real Deal Delivery</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/phoenix/the-wild-thaiger-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-112.07338,33.47791,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>Over Easy</name><description><![CDATA[<div style="color:#D62828;font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px;">DINERS, DRIVE-INS AND DIVES</div><h2 style="margin:6px 0 10px 0;font-size:52px;">Over Easy</h2><div style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#777777;">Phoenix, AZ 85018 &middot; &#9733; 4.3 (8 reviews)</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;"><div><b>Phone:</b> <a href="tel:6024683447" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">602-468-3447</a></div><div><b>Web:</b> <a href="http://www.eatatovereasy.com" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">www.eatatovereasy.com</a></div><div><b>Address:</b> <a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=Over+Easy%2C+4730+E+Indian+School+Rd%2C+%23123%2C+Phoenix%2C+AZ+85018&amp;ll=33.494986,-111.979825" style="color:#0066CC;text-decoration:underline;">4730 E Indian School Rd, #123<br/>Phoenix, AZ 85018</a></div></div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">SPECIAL DISHES</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Ham Steak with Red Eye Gravy, Chicken-Fried Steak, Banana French Toast</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">ABOUT</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Come to Over Easy for a quality scratch-made Sunday brunch with a Midwest touch. Guy admitted that the savory red-eye gravy on a ham steak was better than his own. The chicken-fried steak was enjoyed for its tomato jam and potato hash browns. The banana French toast made with brioche was &amp;quot;dynamite.&amp;quot;</div><div style="color:#D62828;font-weight:bold;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;">FEATURED ON</div><div style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:22px;">Comfort Cookin&#x27;<br/>Deep-Fried Favorites</div><div style="font-size:30px;"><a href="https://www.foodnetwork.com/restaurants/az/phoenix/over-easy-restaurant-restaurant" style="color:#D62828;text-decoration:underline;">View on Food Network &rarr;</a></div><div style="color:#777777;font-size:22px;margin-top:22px;">Source: Food Network</div>]]></description><drawOrder>10</drawOrder><Style><IconStyle><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/red-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.8</scale></LabelStyle></Style><Point><coordinates>-111.97982,33.49499,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
